ben: sidny opera houser ashpashe thaka suijarlander pratinidhitbakari brijit macmohan desher visesh suvidhaprapth kridavidder yeman rupo jayi misheli jonske santar, cychel chalna evan daude prajeet kare ei kridda pratham sonar padak jitechillen.
guj: sydney opera house aaspaasma yojayeli spardhama brigit mekmohane sweetgralandu pratinidhitva karine taran, saycle chalaavavi ane dodwani ramatma pahelo suvarn padak jitava loksamarthan dharavataan grih kheladi misheli jonson jevaan kheladine haraavyo, jemane rajat padak malyo.
hin: sidney opera house kii prishthbhumi main switzaraland kii brijet macmohan ne pasandida gharelu khilaadi misheli jones, jinhen rajat padak mila, ko haraate hue tairaaki kii, saaikal chalaai or daud laga kar khel main swarna padak jeeta .
kan: sydney opera housein avarandalli aayojislagidd i krideyalli switzerlandannu pratinidhisid brijit makmahon iju, cycling mattu otdalli belpiannu gedd mikili jonsrantah nechchin aatitheya kridapatugaiannu hindikki modal chinnad padkavannu gittisidru.
mal: sydney oppara hasiൻre parisarsliൽwech, switzeർlaaൻdin pratinidhikarichch brijit makmahൻ, wellimedaൽ nedia misheൽ joൺsineppolull annatile priyaray kaayikatarae parajaypetutti, ninthukayu cychiൾ chavittukyu otukyu cheit matsaratile aadya swaർnamedaൽ karsthamaki.
ori: sidni opera houser pariveshtani madhyare anusthit, stajaralandra pratinidhith karuthiva brijit myakmahon pahanri, sicel chalai, eban daudi ehi khether pratham srna padak hasal karithile, sethakar pring misheli jonsank bhadi gharoi kreedhavithnku harai, yie ruple padak pithile.
pan: sidney opera house de aale-duale sthit svisszarland di numaindgi karan vaali brisit macmohan ne tiraqi keeti ate khed vich pahile son tagme lai daudi, chandi jitan vaali mishel jones varge pasandida gharelu athlits nuun haraya|
tam: sidney opera housein suzlil natant ant vilyatle switzerlandch sernt brijit machmahon nichalum sacclingum otamum menokondu muthal tangap pathakkaddait tattichenjhar, atil vellib pathakum vendo misheli jones bonthe ulnaddu adravbettn veerargans avar tolkadithar.
tel: sydney opera house parisarall jarigin i kridallo switzerland ki praatinidhyam vahinchin brijit memahan it kotti, cycl tokki, parugu tisi indulo rajata geluchukunibhisht maiscale jones vanti stanik kridakarul odinchi swarna pataka geluchukundi.
urd: sidney opera house ke gurdonvah main kaayam, sweatzerland kii numandagi karne wali breggsit make maahvan ne tairaqi kii, saikal chalaai or khel main sone kaa pahalaa tamgaa haasil karne ke liye dauden, mishaili jonez jaisi maqbool gharelu khilaadiyo ko haraa kar jinhon ne chaandi kaa tamgaa jeeta.
eng: Set in the surroundings of the Sydney Opera House, Brigitte McMahon representing Switzerland swam, cycled and ran to the first gold medal in the sport, beating the favoured home athletes such as Michelie Jones who won silver.

ben: con jivanu upar kaaj karbe sei anuyayi aigulo anti-viral, anti-fungal, anti-protoboal evan antibiotic hiseve vibhajit.
guj: sukshmajivanuona jooth par karaati asarne aadhare temane anti-wirals, anti-fungal, anti-protocols ane antibiotics tarike vargikrut karvama aave che.
hin: jin sookshmaanuon ke samooh par ye kaam karti hai, us aadhaar par inhen vyresarodhi, fungsrodhi, protocoarodhi tathaa pratijaivik aushadhiyon ke rup main vargeekrut kiya jaataa he.
kan: ivugannu avu prenam biruv sookshmajivi gumpige anugunavagi vairanu-nirodhkgalu, shilindhra-nirodhkgalu, protosov-nirodhkgalu mattu pratijivakagalu endu vargikarislaguttade.
mal: badhikkunn sukshmajiviute waർggae atisthanmaki iv anti viral, anti fangal, anti protosols, anti biotis ennigyne varggikaricappettiriunnu.
ori: yeun bhootaanu goshthigudik upare eha kaam karithaye, sehi anuyani egudiku bhootaanu pratirodhi, kavak pratirodhi, protojoa-pratirodhi, eban pratijaibik bhavare shrenibhukt karayaishi.
pan: inhan nuun anti- vistyle, anti- fungel, anti-protogaal ate roganunashaka vich vargikaran kitha gya hai oh jise jivanus te com karade hannnai
tam: ews ent vaka nunnurigolin midhu vinapurikindena anpatep boruttu, antti-viral, antti-bangal, antti-protosowal manllum anttiiotic ena vakipaduttapadukindena.
tel: ivi prabhavan chupe sukshmajivas samuhaniki anugunanga vitini anti virals, anti fungals, anti protojovals, mariyu anti bayotiksuga vargikarincharu.
urd: inhen in jaraasam ke group ke lihaaz se jin par asar andaz hote hain, anti wiral, anti fungal, anti protozoliz or anti bivitics ke tuur par darja band kiya jataa hai.
eng: These are classified as anti-virals, anti-fungals, anti-protozoals and antibiotics according to the group of microbes they act upon.

ben: bharter drut arth lenden vyavastha- upiai-ke anyanya kshetrer anurup vyavasthar sang samyukta karaar pashapashi bharter arth lenden vyavasthagulike anyanya kshetrer sang samyukta karaar sambhabanati arth preran sah antasimant arth lenden vyavasthagulike unnat kare tulbe.

hin: bharat kii sabase twarit bhugtan pranali - upiai - ko anya kshetradhikaron ke usee ke samaan bhugtan pranaaliyon se jodne kii jari pahal sahit bharat kii bhugtan pranaaliyon ko anya kshetradhikaar kii pranaaliyon se jodne kii sambhaavna se dhan ke preshan sahit seemaa-paar ke saath bhugtan vyavasthaaon main sudhaar hoga.
kan: bharatad vegavad pavati vyavastheyad you.pi.i.annu itare kshetravyaptigamallin antahude vyavasthegalondige paraspar coodisuvudakke present xarialliruva upakramavannu olagondante, bharatad pavati vyavasthegamannu itare kshetravyaptigalondige sanyojisabahudad sadhayteyu deshgal naduve gadiachey hanad ravaneyu seridante pavati sadhanagainnu adhikgolisuttade.
mal: indiaille pettennu panamadaykanavunn nilevilull yu.pi.ai. sampradayam atupolayull mat adhikarparidhikali panambakkunn sampradayathslumai bandhippicanural ippol natannuvarunn udyams ulpete indiaille panamadaical sampradayase mat adhikarparidhikalilak bandhippikunnatinull saddhyat atavukൾ ulppatayull atirti katannull panamadaical samvidhanae mechchappetuttu.
ori: bharatar drut arth pradaan brivastha - eu.pi.aai. - ku anyanya kshetragudikare rahithiva samaprakarar bubasthagudik sahit aanthah-sanyojan karibar chalit padakshep samet, bharatar arth pradaan bubasthagudiku anyanya kshetragudik sahit sanyukt karibar sambhavana simapar arth pradaan bubasthagudiku parivarddhit karib, yeunthire arth preran madhya antarbhukt .
pan: bharat de bhugtan karan wale shaylia da doosare adhikar khetraan naal jodan di sambhawana, jise vich hun chal riha bharat da turant on waala yu.pi.aai duje adhikar khetraan vich naal di shaylia naal jodan naal duusari sarbhada di bhugtan ate bheji hoi rakmas vich wadha aiga I
tam: indiavin yubis enepatum duridab panamseluttal amaipai velinadugalil ull idebonde amibbugaluton parasparam inaikkhapattuk kontrukkum natwatiky udpat, indiavin panamseluttal amibbugans velinadugaluton inippadarkana satium, panam anuppudal ullitt ellthantia panamseluttal arbadugans membaduddhum.
tel: saguthunn bharat shighra chellimp vidhana - yupiai nu - itar adhikaar paridhullo gal atuvanti vidhanalatho jodinche pratham yatnanto saha itar adhikaar paridhulatho bharat chellimp vidhanath jodinche sadhyat, dabbu badililato batu sarihaddulu dati jarige chellimp erpats merugu parustundi.
urd: bhaarat ke adaegi ke nizaam ko digar dayera akhtiyaar se mansilk karne kaa imkan, bishmol bhaarat ke tej adaegi ke nizaam - yu pii aai - ko digar dayera akhtiyaar main isi tarah ke nizaam ke saath baham marabot karne kii jari pahal ke, tarasailaat zar ke bishmol sarhad paar adaegi ke intazaamat ko behatar banaaye gaa.
eng: The possibility of linking India's payment systems to other jurisdictions, including the ongoing initiative of interlinking India's fast payment system - UPI - with similar systems in other jurisdictions, will enhance cross-border payment arrangements, including remittances.

ben: lajar die graficke vashpibhoot kare sei bashptike ek hilliam bayumandal sheethal karaar pariksha, 1984-te pratham carboner guchchha sanakt karen erick e. ralphing, donald em. kax evan andrw caldor.
guj: erik e. rohlphing, donald em. cox, ane andryu kalder dwara pahelivar 1984maa carbon cluster shodhi kalwama avyan hatan, aa prayogoma graphitanu ek ksh-kiran dwara bashpibhawan karvama aavyu hatu ane varalne helium vayumandal dwara thandi padwama aavi hati.
hin: carbon cluster kaa pataa pehali baar erik e. rohlfing, donald em. cox or andru kalder ne 1984 main lagaaya tha, un prayogon main jinamein kaale sise ko leisure se vashpit kiya gaya or is vaashp kaa helium ke vaataavaran main drutashithan kiya gaya.
kan: 1984ralli errick e. rolfing, donald em. cox, mattu andrew caldor, lesarnind grafitannu aviagisi aa aviannu hiliyamne avarandalli tanisuv prayoggamalli modalbarige ingalad guchgainnu patteyhachchidaru.
mal: lesർ kond graphite bashpikarikkayu oru hilium antarikshattaൽ aa bashpam tanuppikkayu cheit parikshanlila eric e. roൾfing, donaൾd e. kocks, aaൻdru kaaൽdoർ ennivർ 1984ൽ kaaർbൺ klasterukൾ adyamai contupitikunnat.
ori: carbon clushtaragudik 1984 masihare prathame erik e. rolefing, donald em. kaks o andru kaldornk dra sandhan karayaithila, sehi sabu pariksha dra yeunthare graphitku lejar madhumare bashpare parinat karagala eban sehi bashpaku eka hilidham parimandal dra sheetal karayaithila.
pan: carbon guchhe pahili war 1984 vich aric e. ralphing, donald ium. kax ate andru kolder duara labhia gaia,prayogan vich leisure duara grapit nuun washpikrit kita gya ate washp nuun healium vayumandal duara tada kita gya see|
tam: carbon tralle mudanmudalil eric. e. rolbing, donald em. cox, andrew khaldor akhioral 1984il khandawiapattanu; itu, lesar mulam grafite avyaxpattu ant aviy heliam suzlil kulirvixppatt chodanlil nickdandatu.
tel: karban samuhalani modat 1984lo aric e rolfing, donald a kaks mariyu andru koldor, graphit ni leger to bashpibhavinchi, aa avirini hilium paryavarailo challarchin prayoga gurtincharu.
urd: carbon ke jhuramuton ko pahali bar 1984 main erik aye rohlfing, donald em cox or endrew coldoor ne in tajarbat main dariyafat kiya tha jahaan graphite ko leizar ke zarie bukhaaraat main tabdel kiya gaya or bukhaaraat ko helium ke maahaul se thanda kiya gaya.
eng: Carbon clusters were first detected by Eric A. Rohlfing, Donald M. Cox, and Andrew Kaldor in 1984, in experiments where graphite was vaporised by a laser and the vapour was quenched by a helium atmosphere.

ben: use aadhan evan vidyupravah thek vikirna has, seguli upare kono "pratikria" prabhava nei, evan bartaman samay seguli dwara pratyakshbhave prabhavit has na (varang atite seguli thek vikirna kshetrer paribartansmuher anukram thek parokshabhave upadit has eti) bale vidyupravah evan aadhan (us) thek bahu durer kono tadi-chumbakian kshetrake tadi-chumbakian bikiran (iemar) bale.
guj: ek electromagnetic field karants ane charjis (psorsis) kartaan taddan alag che, tene electromagnetic radieshan (i.em.ar.) kahevaaya che; te charjis ane strotamana karantsmathi radiat kartu hovathi any teomathi koi ‘feedbek’ aasar hoti nathi, ane te vartamanma sidhi rite temanathi aasar pamtu nathi (joke, te aadkatari rite bhutkaalma temathi radiet thatan fildsma shrenibaddha pherfar dwara peda thai che).
hin: vidyut pravaah or aavesh (strot) se bahut dur ke vidyut chumbakeey kshetra ko vidyut chumbakeey vikiran (i.em.aar.) kaha jaataa he kyonki yah strot ke pravaah or aavesh se vikeern karata he, iskaa unpar koi "pratikriyaatmak" prabhaav nahin hota he or vartmaan samay main usase pratyaksh rup se prabhavit bhi nahin hota he (balki, yah apratyaksh rup se jo purv main kshetra main vikeern hue kramik parivartanon se utpann hota he).
kan: vidyudpravahgalu mattu vidyudaveshgalind (moolagalu) tumb doordalliruva ondu vidyutkantiya kshetravannu vidyutkantiya vikiran (i.em.aar.) ennalaguttade, idu muldallin vidyudaveshgalu mattu vidyudpravahgalind horehommuttadeyaddarind, avugal mele "pratyadan" prenamvannu hondiruvudill, mattu prasakt samayadalli avugalind nervagi prabhavitavu agiruvudill (adkkint hechu nijavagi, adu i hinde avugalind prasarisid kshetragakallad kramanugat badlavanegalind parokshvagi utpattiagiruttade).
mal: vidyuchaktipravahattiൽninnu chaർju(prabhavakendranoൾ )kaliൽninnu valare akann oru vaidyutakantikamandlate, at prabhavakendrattile chaർjukaliൽninnu pravahaliൽninnu vikirate cheiyunnatukondu, atin avaikkumeൽ "fidbak" prabhava illatatukondu, at waർttamanakalat avyaൽ pratyakashmai baadhicppetatatukondu (at oteoce bhutakalat vikirate cheyyapret mandlasille matresute oru paramparayaൽ parokshamai utpadippicppetunnatan) vaidyutakantikavikirate (i.e.aaർ) enne viliunnu.
ori: vidbhaut pravah eban vidbhaut shakti (uts) tharu bahu durre thiva vaiduthik chumbakiya kshetraku vidbhaut-chumbakiya bikiran (i.em.aar.) kuhayaaye karan eha utsare thiva vidbhaut shakti eban vidbhaut pravahru bikiran karen, semanank upare kaunsi “prathikria” prabhab padi nathaaye, eban eha madhya semanank dra sidhasaikh bhave varttaman samaure prabhavita hue naahin (baran, eha paroksh bhavare atitre bikiran karuthiva kshetragurikar parivarttanar karam dra utpaadit hoithaye).
pan: ik electromagnaetic field nuun karants ate charjan (sarotaan) ton bohut daur electromagnaetic radiation (i aim aar ) kiha janda hai kiunki ih sarotaan vich charge ate karants ton radiat hunda hai, uhanaas 'te koi "feedback" prabhav nahi hunda, ate maujuda same vich uhanaas duara sidhe for 'te prabhavit nahi hunda (sagon ih asidhe for 'te pichhe uhanaas ton baahar nikalan wale khetraan vich tabdilia de kram vich paidaa hunda hai)
tam: minnottas manllum minnuttalilrundhu (min aadharangs) vegu turam ull woru minkandab pulatai minkantak katirvichu (eemar) enbhar, anendal atu min aadhartil minnuttas manllum minnottalilrundhu katirvichai welipadudukintu, avadhqin midhu "pinnutt" vilaivike kontirupadill, manllum nical kalatil avadhqin neradit dakkaduku alavatill (majhak, atu kadand kalatil avashrilrundhu katirvichak velievic pulangalin woru varisaiyana mabanglal mahimukamak urbattyakintu).
tel: vidyut pravahal mariyu chharj la(molal) nudi chala duranga unn vidyut-ayaskant paridhini vidyut-ayaskant prasaran antar(ienar), andukante adi mulaloni vidyut chharj lu mariyu pravahal nudi prasaristundi, vatipai "pratispandan" prabhavan kaligi unddu, mariyu present kalamlo vatiche neruga prabhavitamavadu (pratiga vatinudi gattlo prasarinchabadin kshetrala krammin marpul vall adi parokshanga utpatti avutundi).
urd: krint or charge (makha) se bahut daur waaqa barqnatesi maidan barqnatesi ishua (e em aar) kahalaata hai chunki ye makha main charge or krint se ishtaaai ikhraaj kurta hai, ye in par koi "fed bek" asar naheen hota, or maujod vakt main in se brah rasat mutasar bhi naheen hota (balki, ye maazi main in se shuaa ries hone waale maidaanon main tabadeliyon ke tasalasal ke zarie bolwasta paida hota hai).
eng: An electromagnetic field very far from currents and charges (sources) is called electromagnetic radiation (EMR) since it radiates from the charges and currents in the source, has no "feedback" effect on them, and is also not affected directly by them in the present time (rather, it is indirectly produced by a sequence of changes in fields radiating out from them in the past).

ben: han, 9m shatabdite khanan kara janapriya ellora guhagulote panchta prachin jain guhaar ekata samashti royas aar eta aurangaader anyatam aakarshanian smritistambh৷
guj: haaa ji, isavisana 9me sadima jenu utkhanan karayu, paanch prachin gufaono samuh janiti ellora gufaao paase mali aavyo, je aurangabad smarkonu ek sauthi rasaprad smarak che.
hin: haan. 9ve shatabdi isvi main khudaai kar ke banaai gai paanch puraani jain gufaaon kaa yah samooh ellora kii gufaaon main he or aurangabad kii sabase rochak jagahon main se he.
kan: haa, janapriyavad ellora guhegamalli samanya shakeya 9nae shatmandalli utsananavadanth aidu praachin jain guhalayagal samuchchay ide, adu aurangabadin atyant kutuhlkari smarakagamalli ondagide.
mal: ate, prashastmay ellora guhakl, potuvarea ompatan nutandil khanana cheitedukapettu aurangabad smarkaniർmmitikal et aakarshakvumay anch jainguhalute sangy und.
ori: han, 9ma shatabdeere khanan heithiva panchati prachin jainas gumfar samooh lokapriya ellora gumphare rahichi aau segoik aurangabadar sabutharu aakarshaniya manument bhitharu gotieku bujhaae .
pan: haa, 9 vin sadi isavi vich khudaai keeti gai, panch prachin jain guphawaan da ik smooh prasidh ellora guphawaan vich pia hai ate aurangabad de sabh ton dilachasap samaraks vichon ik hai.
tam: parthen, pou 9aam nooxantileye agalvaraichiil khandawioppatt ellora kukaikalil irukkum aindhu packmaiyana samanak kukaikas aurangafadil irukkum miguch suvarasyaman iangsil ondu.
tel: chusan, krish 9va shatabdanlo travvabadin aidu puraatan jain guhal samudayam prasiddh ellora guhalalo undi, ivi atyant asaktikarman aurangabad kattada okatiga nilustai.
urd: haan, 9vaein sadi isvi main in kii khudaai kii gai thi, ellora ke mashhuur gaaron main panch purane jain gaaron kaa majamua hai or ye orang aabaad ke sab se dilachasp yaadgaaron main se ek hai.
eng: Yes, Excavated back in the 9th century CE, a conglomeration of five ancient Jain caves lie at the popular Ellora Caves and make for one of the most interesting Aurangabad monuments.

ben: udaharanswarup, paksthali nimn pi.aich rekha (1 thek 4-r madhye) bahu anujiv yeguli pater madhye dhoke, tader janya maratmak hate par.
guj: jemke, petno nicho pe.ech. (1thi 4 jetalo) e tema dakhal thatan sukshma sajivo mate ghatak che.
hin: udhaaharan ke liye, pet kaa kam piech (1 se 4 ke bich) vibhinn sookshmjivon ke liye jo pet main pravesh karte hai, ghaatak ho saktaa he .
kan: udaharanege, jairad piech kadimairuvudu (1rind 4r varege) adnnu praveshisuv anek sookshmajivigalige marakwagiruttade.
mal: vayrille kushanera pi.ech . mulym (1 mutal 4 vare) atil praveshiunn pal sukshmajivikalku marakaa.
ori: udaharan srup, pakhsthalir nimn matrar piech (1 ru 4 madhyare aasuthiva) eha madhyaku pravesh karuthiva anek anujeevank pin maratmak hoithaye .
pan: udaharan de tor te, ait pi.aich (1 ton char tak) dhid de under aun wale jivanus lai ghatak hai I
tam: udarantingu, viril pies kuraivak (1 muthal 4 varai) irindhal athatakul varum pal nunnurigos setvidup.
tel: udaharanku, udaranlo unde takkuv pihech (1 nudi 4 varaku sthillo), danloki praveshinche anek sukshmakrimulku pranantakamainadi.
urd: misaal ke tuur par, pet kaa kam pii yach (1 se 4 tak) in bahut se khurd jarsuumon ke liye mahalak hai jo is main daakhil hote hain.
eng: For example, the low pH (ranging from 1 to 4) of the stomach is fatal for many microorganisms that enter it.

ben: evan keu yadi asanyami (hay thake), samarthya anuyayi tara nijeder asanyam thek nirast kareque; evan atit o bhavishyater tulana pratyek kshetre tader pita, mata evan gurujander baadhya hay thakar fale tara aro bhalo thakave o sukhe thakave.
guj: ane jo koine koi kutev hoya ane teo potani rite e kutevathi mukt thayan hoya, ane temana bhutkal ke bhavishyakal virudh mata-pitaa tatha vadilo pratye ajnankit banyaan hoya, to darek prasange evu vartan karavathi teo bahetar ane vadhu aanandi jeevan maani shakashe.
hin: or yadi kuch log asanyamee (the), to jitna unase ho saktaa tha unhone utana asanyam tyaag diya tha; tathaa bhoot or bhavishya ke bhi vipareet, apane pita or mata or bado ke prati aagyaakaari ho kar, prayek avasar par isi tarah ke vyavhaar ke saath ve zyaada khush rahete hue behatar jivan bithaayenge.
kan: mattu kalavaru bhogaloluparagiddaradare, ig tamm kailadamattige tamm bhogalolupatheyannu nillisiddare; tande, tayi mattu heriarige vidheyaragi, gatakalkke virudhvagi bhavishyadalliu, prati sanderbhadallu higeye nadedukollutta avaru innashtu uttamawagi mattu hechu santoshwagi baluttare.
mal: matramall, chilr atmaniantranmillatavarayirunnengil tawslaൽ avunnatra avar aa atmaniantranmillayk viramamitukyu panjattetilninn vyatyastamai bhaviiൽ achonotu ammayot muthirnavrotu anusaranyullavarayirikkayu cheit, oro sandarttil angne pravartikunnatuway, kututal mechchamayu santoshamayu jivikkayu cheyu.
ori: eban yadi kichhi jan eha bhitharu asanyami thile, semane nij asanyamathaku nij samarthya anuyani rokipariyanthi; eban nij pita, mata, o badmanank prati ajnadhin hoi, atitar baipareetare o bhavishtathare madhya, pratyekati avasarare epari aacharan hetu, semane eka unnat o adhik sukhadayak jeevan vanychive.
pan: ate jeee kuchh (san) andaroni , unhaa ne jo unhaa di shakti vich see, unhaa de sanjam ton hat gaye han; ate aapne pitaa ate matra ate bazurgan de prati aagiakari, atit de virodh vich ve bhavikh vich, har mauke 'te ish tarhaa com karke, uh bihtar ate hor khushi naal jeewan batit karange.
tam: chirgettup bhonavarkalak irunth chiller, tanglal iantvarai chirgette niruttik kondars, tangas pevchorukkum periyavarlukum kioppatindhu nadandars, kadand kalatuku mashiamak tarbodhum varungalatil ovvoru chandarpatil ittaku nataddai mulam avarkas melum chicint, inpaman valwai anubhavipargas.
tel: evaraina vicchalvidiga (undi) unte, gataniki alage bhavisyattuku virudhanga tam shakti koddi vaaru tam vicchalviditnanni manukoni, vaari tallidandrul pat, peddal pat vidheyat kaligi untar, prati sandarbhatlo ala pravartinchada dwara vaaru merugga, marint santoshnga jivistar.
urd: or agar kuch be itdal (the), to unhon ne apni be itdali tark kardi jaisaa ki in ke akhtiyaar main tha, or apne baap or maa or bado ke farmanbardaar hue, maazi ke barkhilaf or mustaubal main bhi, har mauqaa par aisa amal kar ke, wo behatar or zyaada khushaali kii zindagi guzaarein ge.
eng: And if some (were) intemperate, they have ceased from their intemperance as was in their power; and obedient to their father and mother and to the elders, in opposition to the past also in the future, by so acting on every occasion, they will live better and more happily.

ben: chal (chaler papad o prakriajat khadya tiri chada) evan gamer kshetre japan swaynsampoorn also, anyanya dana o pashukhadya shasyer prayojner 50% deshtiqu aamdani karte has, evan ardhek maser joganer janye aamdanir uparei nirbhar kare.
guj: japan chokha (sivayake fatakda banaavavaama upayog thatan chokha ane prakriya karela khadyapadartho) ane ghauni babate samanya rite atmanirbhar hova chhataan, aa deshe tena anaya anaj ane lilan pakni jaruriatona lagbhag 50% aayat karva ja pade che ane teno masan addho purvatho pan aayat par aadhar raakhe che.
hin: haalanki japan chaaval (chaaval ke kurkure vyanjan or prasanskrit khaadya padaarthon main iske prayog ke alaava) or gehun main aatmanirbhar he, lekin desh ko anya anaaj or chaara fasalon kaa 50% aayaat karnaa padataa he or maance kii aadhi aapurti ke liye aaayaaton par nirbhar rahata he.
kan: japan sadharanwagi akki (akkiya biskattugalu mattu sanskarisid aahar paxarwagal tayarickeyallin ader banakeyannu horatupadisi) mattu godhia vishayavagi swavalambiagideyadaru, aa deshvu tanage aavashyakavad itar dhaanya hagu mevin belegal sumaru 50%ashtannu amadu madicolsbeku mattu adu mas poorikeya ardhdashtu pramanakkagi amadugainnu avalambiside.
mal: nellyl (ris krakkarukalu sanskarichch bhakshyawastukkalu untakkunnatile atiൻre upyogamoike) gotampl jappaൻ potuwe swayamparyaptamanankil mat dhanyathutayu kalittetvicalutayu ekadesha 50 shatamantolam rajyatin iokkumati cheyendivarikayu avarute masavashyatiൻre pakutik iokkumatie ashrayikkayu cheiyunnu.
ori: yadio japan sadharanthati chaul (chaul krakar eban prakriakrit khadya thiarire ehar bbbaharaku chhaadi) o gaham kshetrare atmanirbharashil, ehi deshati nishchit bhavare nizer anyanya shasya eban pashukhadya fasalsabu aavashyakatar 50% amadhani karithaye tatha nizer mas aavashyakata anupooranr arddhek pin amadhani upare nirbhar karithaye .
pan: halanki japan chaaval ate kanak lai sajai-nirbhar hai ( choula de biskutate processd khane di varton ton alava ) mulak nuun duje anaaj te chara fasalas lai lagabhaga 50% aayat karna penda hai ate mass di adhi purti lai aayat te nirbhar rihna penda hai I
tam: japan valakkamak arice (arice vadagangs manllum pathanamseit unvukhalil payanbaduttapatum arice taveer) manllum kodhums urbattil tanniriu pellrull fodhilu, mabbbb daniyas manllum divaanap bhairil sumar 50% devie annadu ishakkumati seyy wantulldu, melum tan iricchit devain badiavuku ishakkumatiaie sarndulldu.
tel: godhum mariyu vari sagolo japan sadharannga swayansamruddhi kaligi unnappatiki (biyapu pindi checkkal mariyu prakriaparambadin aaharal tayarilo viniog minaha), i desha itar dhanyal mariyu pashuul met avasarala 50% varaku digumati chesukovalasi wastendi, alage masa avasaranlo saganiki paga digumtulapai aadharpadutundi.
urd: agarache japan chaval(sivaay chaval ke papad or proces shudaa guzaaun ko banane main is ke istemaal ke) or gandam ke maamle main aam tuur par khud muktafee hai, taahim malik ko apni zaruuryat ke digar anaaj or chaare kii fasalon kaa takreeban 50 faisad darhamad karna padataa hai or ye apni gosht kii nisif farahami ke liye daraamdaat par manhsir hai.
eng: Although Japan is usually self-sufficient in rice (except for its use in making rice crackers and processed foods) and wheat, the country must import about 50% of its requirements of other grain and fodder crops and relies on imports for half of its supply of meat.

pan: maansik sihat peshewar jiven ki manovigyani, manovigyaan vich aim di, manovigyaan vich diproma, jaaa manovigyaan vich rashtirya board de diplomet nuun puura karke apnia yogatas ; ik ton bood ik aim bi bi asa medical consil aaf india center ton hasil karade han|

urd: nafasyati sahat ke pesha var afarad jese saiciatrist medical konsil of india ke marcuz se em bi bi es kii digree haasil karne ke baad nafasyat main em dee, nafasyati tibb main diploma (dee pii em) yaa nafasyat main neshnal board (dee en bi) ke diplomet mukammal karke apni ahlet haasil karte hain.
eng: Mental health professionals such as psychiatrists acquire their qualifications by completing an MD in Psychiatry, a Diploma in Psychiatric Medicine (DPM), or Diplomate of National Board (DNB) in Psychiatry; following an MBBS from a Medical Council of India center.

ben: paryaton shilper unnayan, parikalpana o niyantran vyavastha chada samajik, sanskruthik evan arthnaitik vikrutir fale bahat hate par ya paryatak o sthanian manusher samparker madhye die prativalit have.
guj: malkhagat aayojan ane niyantran vina samazik, sanskruthik and aarthik vikrutine karne pravasan vikas ataki shake,je pravasi ane sthanik lokona sambandhoma pratibimbit thayu hoya che.
hin: uchit yojana or niyantran tantron ke bina, saamaajik, saanskrithik or aarthik vikrutiyon se paryaton vikaas kaa ant ho saktaa he jo paryatakon or sthaneey logon ke bich ke sambandhon main parilakshith hoga.
kan: yojane mattu niyantranad vyavasthegalilladiddare, pravasodyamad pragatiyu samajik, sanskruthik mattu aarthik vikrutigainnu untumaduvudarondige conegolkbahudagiddu, adu pravasigaru mattu sthaliya gener naduvan sambandhadalli pratibimbitvaguttade.
mal: aasutran samvidhanaso niyantran samvidhanaso illatayaൽ samuhikavu sanskarikavu sampattikavumay vaikrutacaote vinodasanjaraviksanatin antyam kuricppetukayu at sancharikൾku nattukaർkkumirilull bandhttiൽ pratiphalikukayu cheyu.
ori: yojana eban nivnthran brivasthaman narahile, paryaton kshetrare abhivriddhi sheshre samajik, sanskrutik o arthanitik kshetrayojana eban nivnthran brivasthaman narahile, paryaton kshetrare abhivriddhi sheshre samajik, sanskrutik o arthanitik kshetrare nakaratmak parivarttanar karan hoipare, yaha paryletak o sthaniya lokamanank madhur samparkare parilakshith heb.re nakaratmak parivarttanar karan hoipare, yaha paryletak o sthaniya lokamanank madhur samparkare parilakshith heb.

tam: ditamidudal manllum kaddupattu arbadus illavital, surchaula valarchi nindfoi samuk, kalachchar, poruladhar batipugans erbadutalam, itu subaulap bhayanilukum ullur malukum itieyana ulvil pratifalikkum.
tel: pranalik vese mariyu kattudilam chese yantranga lekapote, samajik, samskritik mariyu ardhik vakrikarnlato paryatak abhivruddhi antamavavacchu, ivi paryatkulu mariyu stanik prajal madhyalo bandhavyala pratibimbinchavacchu.
urd: mansuba bindi or control mechanism ke bagaiyr, siyaahat kii tarakkee maashruti, muqaafati or iqtsaadi bigaad kii bina par khatm hosakti hai, jis kii akasi siyaahon or mukami logon ke darmiyaan taalkat main hogi.
eng: Without planning and controlling mechanisms, the development of tourism may end by having social, cultural and economic distortions, which will be reflected in the relationship between tourists and local people.

guj: havaana wapamanana niyamanma paanini varal pramukh bhumika bhajve che kaaran ke te grahni sapati parathi saura urja ane thermal kiranotsurgane shoshi le che.
hin: hawa ke taapmaana ko niyamit rakhane main jal vaashp ek mahatvapurn bhoomika nibhaataa he kyonki yah grah kii sataha par se saura urja or ooshmaa vikiran ko sokh letaa he.
kan: niraviyu saura shaktiannu mattu bhoomiy melmaiind shakhad vikirangalannu hirikolluvudarind, gaaliya ushnanshavannu niyantrisuvalli adu pramukh patravannu vahisuttade.
mal: bhoomiute uparitalattiൽninnull saroർjjavu tapavikiranvu agira cheiyunnu ennatinaൽ vayuviൻre tapanil kramikarikunnatiൽ niravi oru pradhanpank vahikunnu.

pan: bhaaf hawa de wapamana nuun niyamat karan vich ik mouth bhumika nibhaunda hai kiunki oh graha ton aun vaali suraj di shakti ate thermal radiation nuun sama lendi hai I

urd: aabi bukhaaraat hawa ke darja hararat ko manzim karne main ahim kirdaar adaa karte hain kyonki ye siyaare kii satah se shamsi tawanai or hari tabikari ko jazb kiralete hain.
eng: Water vapor plays a major role in regulating air temperature because it absorbs solar energy and thermal radiation from the planet's surface.

ben: 2ya bhagti (anuchnaed na. 17-24) sammelner nathikaran o paryavekshan evan seguli vastawayaner janya dalguli newa padakshap parichalana kare.
guj: bhag be (kalam 17-24) sanmelanna hevaal ane dekharekh vishe ane paksho tarakthi tena paalan matena paglannu sanchalan kare che.
hin: dwitiya bhaag (anuchhed 17-24) sammelan ke prativedan or nigaraanee tathaa partiyon dwaara ise lagu karne ke liye uthaae gaye kadamon ko niyantrit karata he.
kan: bhaag II (17-24 vidhigalu) i oppandad varadigarike hagu melvicharaneyannu mattu idannu kaaryagatagolislu pakshagalu kaigolluv kramagainnu nirdeshisuttade.
mal: kൺweൻshൻre vivaranvu nirikshanvu, atotoppa kakshikൾ av natappilakkuvanetutt natapatikalu niyantriunnatan randambhaga (vakuppukൾ 17-24).
ori: bhaag-2 (anuchchheda 17-24) sammeghnar reporting eban parylevekshan tatha ehaku karyankaari kariva pin pakshamanank dra niaithiva padakshepasabur tattbadhan karithaye.
pan: bhaag-II (artical 17-24) sammelan di reporting ate nigrani ate ishnoo lagu karan lai parties duara chuke gaye kadama nuun niyantrit karada hai|
tam: bhagam II (vidis 17-24) udapatikys veliiduvatu manllum ganganipates, atusarnt trupiners adaich seyalbadutt edukkum natwatikigalas kddialukintu.
tel: rendav bhagan kanvension (nibandhanalu 17-24) yokk nivedan mariyu paryavekshan, alage vatini amaluparichenduku bhagswamulu tisukune charyal niyantristundi.
urd: jaz dum (dafaa 17-24) kunvanshan kii reporting or nigranee or is ke nafaaz ke liye frican kii taraf se uthae gaye ikdamaat ko manzbat kurta hai.
eng: Part II (Articles 17-24) governs the reporting and monitoring of the Convention and the steps taken by the parties to implement it.

ben: ei vishanguli dike kheyal rekhe, mudrasphiti abhikshepty dvitiya tin mase 7.1 shatanshe; iii tin mase 6.5 shatanshe; evan chaturth tin mase samanbhave bharsamya baja rekhe 5.8 shatansh sah 2022-23-e 6.7 shatanshe dhare rakha hayes.
guj: aa karnone dhyanma leta, phugavano andaaz 2022-23maa 6.5. taka par jalwai rahyo che, 7.1. taka kyu2 ni sathe; 6.5. taka kyu3; ane 5.8. taka kyu4, samanrupe santulit jokhamo sathe
hin: in karkon ko dhyaan main rakhte hue, mudrasphiti 2022-23 main 6.7 pratishat par bane rahane par anumaanit he, jahaan jokhimon ko samaan rup se santulit karte hue duusari timahi main 7.1 pratishat; teesri timahi main 6.5 pratishat; or chauthi timahi main 5.8 pratishat rahane kii ummid he.
kan: i anshgainnu gananege tegeducondu, handubbarad munnandajannu 2022-23ralli 6.7 pratishatvendu ulisicoreelagiddu, sambhavya apayagainnu samanvagi saridugisuvudarondige, 2nae traimasikadalli 7.1 pratishat; 3nae traimasikadalli 6.5 pratishat; hagu 4nae traimasikadalli 5.8 pratishtadashtu iralide.
mal: i ghankaellam pariganich, randa padattil 7.1 shatmana, munnam padattil 6.5 shatmana, nalam padattil 5.8 shatmana, ennigyne apakatsaddhyat orupole samatulitapettirie 6.7 shatamanmenn 2022- 23 le panapperupattiൻre matip nilenirtiiriunnu.
ori: ehi karakagudiku bichaaraku nei, cu2pin 7.1pratishat, cu3 pin 6.5 pratishat, eban cu4 pin 5.8 pratishat thai, mudrasaheethir prakshepan 2022-23 pin 6.7 pratishat rakhayaishi, yeteveleki bipadar aashankaguik samabhavare santhulit hoi rahichhi .
pan: ihnas karks nuun dekh ke mahingai da prakhep saal 2022-23 vich 6.7 pratisht see, kuater 2 vich 7.1 pratisht, kuater 3 vich 6.5 pratisht ate kuater 4 vich 5.8 pratisht , ate khetre ait ton ait han I
tam: intak karnilc karuddil kondu, itarkalukkuch cham otukidu alittapin, 2022- 23kkan panavikkum moddhatil 6.7 satvikithamagaum, erandam khalanduku 7.1 satvikithamagaum, moonssam khalanduku 6.5 satvikithamagaum, nankam khalanduku 5.8 satvikithamagaum irukkum endu ganixpattatu.
tel: i karkal pariganaloki tisukuntu, samamain santhulith nashtalato 7.1 shata vadd ku2; 6.5 shata vadd ku3; mariyu 5.8 shata vadd ku4 to, 2022-23 lo dravyolban prakshepan 6.7 shata vadd nilichindi.
urd: in awamil kaa lihaaz karte hue, 2022-23 main afrat zar kii tijwez ko 6.7 faisad par barkaraar rakha gaya hai, jis main duusari sa mahi main 7.1 faisad par, teesri sa mahi main 6.5 faisad par, or chothi sa mahi main 5.8 faisad par hai, jin main khatarat masavi tuur par mitwajan hain.
eng: Taking into account these factors, the inflation projection is retained at 6.7 percent in 2022- 23, with Q2 at 7.1 percent; Q3 at 6.5 percent; and Q4 at 5.8 percent, with risks evenly balanced.

ben: khadya upadan, arthaniti o nirapattar upar era prabhaver drun jivanurodh pratirodher shaktikeo swasthy, jatiya nirapatta evan arthanitir prati ashanka hiseve vivechana kara has.
guj: khadya utpadan, arthvyavastha ane suraksha par tena prabhaavane karne, antimcrobial pratikaarne aarogya, rashtriya suraksha ane arthtantra mate khataro manvama aave che.
hin: khaadya utpaadan, arth vyavastha or suraksha par roganurodhi pratirodh ke prabhaavon ke kaaran, ise swasthya, rashtriya suraksha or arth vyavastha ke liye bhi khatra mana jaataa he.
kan: aahar utpadane, aarthikate mattu rakshaneya mele sookshmajivi-nirohak pratirodhvu biruv prenamdindagi adnnu aarogya, rashtriya bhadrate mattu aarthikategu apayakariendu pariganislagide.
mal: bhakshyotpadanttayu, sampad vyavastyeyu, surakshayeyu badhikumennatinaൽ aaൻrimicrobial pratirodha end vishyam arogyattinu deshiyasurakshayk sampad vyavasoyk nerayull oru bhishaniai karutapetunnu.
ori: khadya utpadan, arthaneethi eban nirapatta upare ehar prabhab hetu anujeeveerohak pratirodh ssthya, jatiya suraksha eban arthaneethi pin madhya eka bipad boli vivechana karayaithaye.
pan: roganunashaka pratirodh de bhojan utpadan, arth vivstha ate sudkhya te aasar kaaran , oh sihat,rashtiri sudkhya ate arth-prabandh nuun ve ik dhamki pesh karada hai I
tam: unu urbhatti, poruladaram, bhadukafu akhiyavain midhu nunnuir ethirfu kondull dakkattal atu chugataram, desab bhadukafu manllum poruladhartirkum ore acchuduttalagak karudapadukintu.
tel: aahar utpatti, aarthikavyavasthi mariyu bhadratalapai dini prabhavan valan, sukshmajivanashak avarodhanni arogya, jaatiya bhadrat mariyu ardhikavyavasthaku apayanga pariganinchabadutondi.
urd: anti microbell mazaahimat ko gazaai paidavar, maishith or salaamati par is kii asar andaazi kii vajah se sahat, qaumi salaamati or maishith ke liye bhi khatare samajha jataa hai.
eng: Because of its effect on food production, economy and security, antimicrobial resistance is also considered a threat to health, national security and the economy.

guj: hyderabadni karmachari rajya vima nigam medical coleje ar.sii.ai.ne prototip viksavavaama madad kari, jayaare post grejuate institut of medical agyukeshan and risrche tabibi upayog mate utpadanonan parikshan, maanyata ane swikruti apavavama madad kari.

kan: hyderabadinalliruva naukarar rajya vimaa nigamad vaidyakiya caleju, aar.si.i.ge mulmadariannu abhivruddhi padisuvalli sahay moditadare, vaidyakiya shikshan mattu sanshodhaneya snatakottar sanstheyu parikshegalu, drisikaran, mattu vaidyakiya balkege utpannagainnu angikarisuvalli nervayitu.
mal: hidrabadille amplois state inshurans corpation medicalcolej proteoty viksanttil ar.si.ai. ye sahayichpol, post grajuvate institute of medical ajukeon and reserch medical upyogattinull utpannavute pariksha, sadhukarana, swikaryat ennivil sahayichu.
ori: karmachari rajya bimaa nigam messical kalej, hidrabad, aar.si.aai. ku mooterup bikashare sahayatha karithila, yeteveleki snatakottar chikitsa shiksha eban anusandhan sansthan chikitsa kshetrare bbbahar pin dravngurikar pareekshan, vaidhakaran, eban skaranre sahayatha karithila .
pan: karamchari raj bimaa nigam medical kalaj, hyderabad, ne ra.si.i di pratiroop vikas vich madad kiti see, naal hi post grajuate institute aaf medical ajukeshan and risarch ne padarths di chikitsa de upyog lai azamaaish, pramanikta, ate swikriti kiti I
tam: hyderabadil ull manilat tokhilauar ittusutik katak maruduvak kalluri mulauruvai uruvakk archis-ku udaviyatu, adevele maruduvak kalvi manllum araichikan mudugalpap pailagam maruduvap payanpattukkak dayaripugalch sodittal, chariparthal manllum angikrittaluku udaviyatu.
tel: arsiaiku,hyderabadloni udyogul state insurence carporesion medical kaleji prototype rupakalpanalo sahayam cheyaga, postgradyuyet institute aaf medical adyukesion and riserch vedya viniog kos utpattula parikshinchada, dhruvikrinchada mariyu aamodanlo sahayam chassindi.
urd: ampilaez state anshurnce corporation medical college, hyderabad ne prototipe taiyaar karne main aar si aai kii madad kii, jabaki post grejawet insiti tute of medical ajokeshan and risurj ne misanuaat ke tabi istemaal ke liye jaanchne, tosiq karne or manzoor karne main madad kii.
eng: Employees' State Insurance Corporation Medical College, Hyderabad, helped RCI in prototype development, while the Postgraduate Institute of Medical Education and Research helped in the testing, validation, and acceptance of products for medical use.

ben: kudhar sang ladaie, ganamadhyam taaraka evan sanshlisht naagarikder kshamtake ekatara karte, 1997-e kansart, kridanushthan evan anyanya caryakram samanvit telod named ekati abhiyan shuru kare ef.e.o.
guj: 1997maa, bhukh saame lajva mate epa.e.o.e telecood sharu karyu, je sangeetana karyakrmo, khelkudni ghatnaao, ane anaya pravrittio dwara madhyamo, janitan vyaktitvo ane chintatur nagarikoni shaktino labh levani jhumbesh hati.
hin: 1997 main epa.e.o. ne telefood shuru kiya jo sangeet samaaroh, khel-kud ke kaarykram or anya kriyaaon kaa abhiyaan tha jisase media, khyaati praapt vyaktiyon or logon kii chintaa karne vaale nagarikon ke samarthy ko kaam main laayaa ja sake or logon kii bhukh mitaane main madad mil sake.
kan: 1997ralli, f.e.o. hasivin virudh horaduvalli sahayakkagi madhyamgalu, hesarant vyaktigalu, mattu sambandhapatt nagarikar shaktiannu balsicoreelu sangeet kacherigalu, kridakutagalu, mattu itar chatuvatikegal andolanavad telephudnnu prarambhisitu.
mal: vishppinetire porataൻ sahayikunnatinai mediutayu prashastvyaktikalutayu talparyamull paranmarutayu shakti prayojanappetuttunnatinuventi kachchericautayu kaayik paripatikalutayu mat pravർttanautayu oru pracharanpravർttanmay telifudin 1997ൽ eph. e. o tuikkankurichu.
ori: 1997 masihare, ef.e.o. kshudha sahit lakei kariva nimanthe, ganamadhum, khathanama brekthith tatha samprukt nagarikamanankar kshamathaku bbbahar karivaku sangeeth samaroh, kreeda karyankram, tatha anyanya karyankalaper eka abhiyaan, 'telephud'r shubharambh karithila .
pan: 1997 vich, aif e o ne bhukhamari naal ladan lai media, naamwar hasatia ate sabandhat nagariks di taaqat nuun vartade hoe, sangeet samaroh, kheds ate hor gatividhia vaali ik teli-food muhim di shuruaat keeti |
tam: efeo 1997il, pattiniku ethrana borattil udhav utagangs, prablangas manllum aggaraull gutimakalin saktiys onaudrattus nokil kachcheries, vilyaddu nicktchis, innapitt natwatikis adangy delifut enjh pracharattait tuakiyadu.
tel: 1997 lo, apeo telicood nu prarambhinchindi, idi sangit sammernalu, krida karyakramas, mariyu itar karyakramal dwara, prasar vyavasthi, pramukhulu, mariyu sambandhit paurul shaktini upayoginchukoni aakalini tarimikottenduku uddeshinchin udyaman.
urd: 1997 main, epa aye oo ne bhakmari se ladaaii main madad ke liye tele food kaa aagaaz kiya, jo concert, khelon kii taqaareb, or digar sargharmiyon par mushtamil jaria ablaag, namor shakhasyat, or digar phikar mand shaharyon kii taakat kaa faaydaa uthane kii ek muhim hai.
eng: In 1997, FAO launched TeleFood, a campaign of concerts, sporting events, and other activities to harness the power of the media, celebrities, and concerned citizens to help fight hunger.

ben: aadalat etao dekhe ye vyaktigat tathy o satyer gopanita hal gopanictar adhikarer ekati apariharya aansh evan seijanya eti badhyatamulak ye si.bi.de.si jari karaar janya tathy sangrher samay naagarikder sarbottama swarthke agradhikar dite have, shudhu seisb vyaktigat tathy sangrah kara have ya aavashyak evan shudhumatra sei uddeshyei vyabhhar kara have yar janya sangrah kara hachche.

guj: 2005maa te paanch khandona dariyan jalmargne taranari pratham stree banii, jema jibraltrane samudradhuni, tyranian sii, kukani samudradhuni, grisma toronosni khadi (kasandrani khadi), californiana kinara paase aaveli ketalina chenal, ane dakshin africana keptaun najik three ankar bethi robin yland sudhino samavesh thai che.
hin: 2005 main ve paanch mahadwipon ke samudri channelon main, jinamein jibraltar jalsandhi, tirhenian sagar, cook street, greece main toronic khadi (kasandra kii khadi), california tat se dur catalina channel shaamil hai, or thri ankar be se dakshin africa ke kep toun ke paas roben dweep tak tairne vaali pehali mahila baniin.
kan: aake 2005ralli, jibraltar jalsandhi, tiranian samudra, kuk jalsandhi, greecenlliruva toroneos khari (kasandra khari), californiad kadalatiradindachegiruv catlina kaluve mattu thri aankar colliind dakshin afrikad cape town baliya robin dwipadvarege seridante aidu khandgal kadalgaluvegaladyant ijid modal mahileyenicidru.
mal: 2005l avar jibraltter katlidk, tiranan katal, cook katlidk, grisile toronius galf (galf of kasandra), kalipornia tiratintuttull katalin chanal, tri ankar beilninn dakshinafricaile kep toninu sameepattull roban dwip ennivyutepate anchu bhukhandslilull katlcchanlulk kuruke ninthia aadya vanitai.
ori: 2005re se panychoti mahadesh dei yauthiva samudrik chanelku pahanriki pari hoithiva pratham mahila hoithile, ethi madhyare thila stret af jivraltor, tirenian saagar, kuk stret, greesre thiva toronios galph (galph af kasandra), kaliffornnia kostre avasthit katalina chanel, eban dakshin africar kep taun nearest thini ankar beru tharu raven dp paryyant.
pan: oh pahili mahilaan bani jise ne 2005 vich panch mahandipa de samudra vich tiraqi kiti, jise vich strate aaf jibralter, tirenian saagar, cook strate, greece vich toronose khaadi (kasandara di khaadi), kelephornia de tat ton catalina channal, ate three ankar be ton li ke cape tien, ngkhani africa de nede robane tapu tak.
tam: 2005il avar aindhu khandanglil ull katal kalvaxil nindichent muthal penmaniyakat digalandar, avarkhil jibralder jalasandi, dairenien katal, kug jalasandi, kirisil ull doronius valaikuda (kassandra valaikuda), california kataloram ull katalina kalwai, dhennaprikail tiri aangar pe muthal cape town arukeyull raban diu varilan bakuti akhiyawe atankum.
tel: 2005lo aidu khandolaloni samudr jal margalgunda, stretit aaf jibraltor, di tyrinian si, kuk stretit, grees loni toronius galf (galf aaf kasandr), kaliphornia thiran kyatlina chhanel, mariyu dakshinafrica, kep town samipan tri yankar be nudi robine island varaku idin modati mahil ayindi.
urd: 2005 main wo panch baar aazamon se nikle hue bahari rudbaron ko teer kar abor karne wali pahali khatun bin gai, jin main aabanaae gibraltar, bahaira tirani, aabanaae coke, unan main khalij toronavis (khalij cosandra), california ke sahil se alihada catalina chainal, or janubi africa ke cape taun ke qareeb three enkar be se ruban jazere tak shamil hain.
eng: She became the first woman to have swum across sea channels off five continents in 2005, including the Strait of Gibraltar, the Tyrrhenian Sea, Cook Strait, Toroneos Gulf (Gulf of Kassandra) in Greece, the Catalina Channel off the California coast, and from Three Anchor Bay to Robben Island near Cape Town, South Africa.

ben: gram ek mahamari chhadie pade evan ashramer bachchader surakshar kshetre aami spost bipad dekhte pelam.
guj: aa gaamma plag fati nikalyo ane men ashramana baalakoni suraksha mate dekhitu jokham joyu.
hin: gaanv main plig fail gaya, or mujhe ashram ke bacchon kii suraksha suspasht rup se khatre main dikhi.
kan: i habalielli plaigu rogavu taledoritu, hagu ashramad makkal surakshatege spasht apayaviruudu nann arivige banditu.
mal: i gramttil plag potipurapetukayu ashramtille kuttiute surakshak pratyakashmay apakat khan kanukayu cheitu.
ori: ehi gramre plag badhi bapigala, eban mun ashramar pilamanank suraksha prati rahithiva prattaksh bipadaku dekhiparuthili .
pan: pind vich palag fail gya, ate minuun ashram de bachya di sudkhya khatre vich dikhi|
tam: intak gramat woru kollanoi dakhiyadu, ashramatil ull kuiandaikalin bhadukappengu apattu iruppads ennal telivakap parkk mudindatu.
tel: i gramlo plague chellaregindi, ashramanlo unn pilll bhadrataku spashtanga muppu unnti naku kanabadindi.
urd: is gaauun main tatoon foot padaa, or main ne ashrama ke bachchon kii salaamati ke liye wakaah khatare dekha.
eng: A plague broke out in this village, and I saw evident danger to the safety of the Ashram children.

ben: aponi ki manoyog sahakare help paijguli padesilen evan punkhanupunkhabhave samasati shudhrachillen?

mal: tangs sahayapeju shraddhichuvayikkayu prashna purnnamai pariharikkayu cheituo?
ori: aapan 'help' prushthagudiku dhyanpoorvak padhivanthi tatha samasyatir samadhan sampoorna bhavare kariyanthi ki ?
pan: ki tusin madad pania nuun dhiaan naal padhia hai ate saoesia nuun changi tarhaa hal kita hai?

eng: Have you carefully read the help pages and thoroughly fixed the problem?

ben: prachintam udahraner madhye mesopotamiar sahar-rajya laagash o ummar (anumanik 2100 christpurbabd) madhye shanti sukti evan mishrian farav dvitiya ramses o hitteit raja iii hatusili madhye ekati sukti 1258 christpurvabdev samapth has.
guj: sauthi sharuatna udaharnoma mesopotemiana shaher-rajya legash ane umma (andaje i.sa. purve 2100) vachcheni shanti samajutino ane egyptna faoro ramses bija tatha hitite raja hetusilis trija vachche i.sa. purve 1258maa puree thayeli sandhino samavesh thai che.
hin: ligash or ummaa (lagbhag 2100 isa purv) ke mesopotamia ke shahar-rajyon ke bich shanti samjhaute or 1258 isa purv main misr ke firo remeses dwitiya or hitti samraat hatthusili tritiy ke bich hua samjhauta sabase praarambhik udaahranon main se do hai.
kan: praachintam udaharanegamalli, mesapatemiad naggar-rajyagalad lagaash mattu ummagal naduvin shanti oppandgalu (sa.sha.pus. sumaru 2100) hagu egyptin fero ramsis II mattu hitits raj hattucili III ivar naduvan odambadikeyu serive.
mal: mesoppotemiaൻ nagar-sansthanalay lagashu ummayu tammilull samadhan utampatikൾ (ekadesha 2100 bi. si. i), egyptile faroveyay ramses rantamanu hitite rajavay hattusilis munnamanu tammiൽ 1258 bi. si. iiൽ angikarichch utampati enniv et adyakalatte udaharanwsliൽ uൾppetunnu.
ori: sarvaprachin udaharan gudik madhyare ajji mesopotamiya naggar-rastra lagash o umma madhyare hoithiva shanthi chukthisabu (anumanic khri.pus. kal 2100), eban mishariya farao ramses-2du o hitight raja, hattusilis-3ank madhyare eka rajinama, yaha khri.pus. kal 1258re sksharith hoithila.
pan: sabh ton purania udahranas vich messonpotemia de shahir laagash ate uma (lagabhaga 2100 isa poorav) de wichkaar shanti sandhia hoia han ate misri phirun ramses II ate hiti king, hetusilis III, wichkaar ik samjhota, 1258 bi see i vich samapat hora|
tam: its micub packmaiyana udarankalil mespadomic nagar arasugalana lakash manllum ummavinku itieyana amaiti oppandangalum (sumar kimu 2100), egyptia prown vamch erandam ramchas manllum hittaya mannan moonssam hattuchillisuku itie kimu 1258il menokoloppatt udapatikes atankum.
tel: tott toli udaharanlalo mesopotemia naggar rajs ayin lagash mariyu umma (sumaruga kripu 2100) madhyan shanti oppandalu, alage egyptki chendin rendav faro rameses mariyu hitti raju ayin mudav hattusillis madhyan kripu 1258 lo mugicin oppanda unnai.
urd: mesopotemia kii shahari riyasato lagash or amaa (takreeban 2100 kabel messiah) ke darmiyaan aman maaade or misri fersaun ramses dum or hatiti baadshaah, hatosiles som ke darmiyaan 1258 kabel messiah main mukammal hone waala maahda qadim misaalon main shamil hai.
eng: Among the earliest examples are peace treaties between the Mesopotamian city-states of Lagash and Umma (approximately 2100 BCE) and an agreement between the Egyptian pharaoh Ramses II and the Hittite king, Hattusilis III, concluded in 1258 BCE.

ben: eti nciclopadia britannika, inkarporated kartruk prakashith has; sansthati astitva sei 18sh shatak thek, yadio shatabdi jure bivinn samay eti malikana parivartit hayes.
guj: e ensyclopidia britannika, incorporeshan dwara prakashith che, aa company chhek 18me sadithi astitvama che, joke teni malki anek deshoma anekavar badlaati rahi che.
hin: ise ek company britanika vishwakosh, ink. dwaara prakashit kiya gaya he, jo 18veen shatabdi ke aasapaas se astitv main he, haalanki pichhali kuch shatabdiyon main iskaa swaamitv kai baar badla he.
kan: idannu enciclodeedia britannika, ink. prakatiside; shatmanagaluddakku halvaaru sal i sansthey malikatvadalli badlavaneyagideyadaru idu 18nae shatmanadindalu astitvadallide.
mal: eൻcychlopodia britanika iൻkoർparated aan at prasidhikaricht; i company patinettanutandumutൽ niloniൽkkunnatanangil atiൻre utamasthavkasham nutandukൾ katannupokave palatavan kaimaom cheyyappettitnd.
ori: eha 'anciclopissia britanika, nigamit', dra prakashit hoithaye; companeeti 18sh shatabdee tharu rahiasichhi, yadio eha shatabdee shatabdee dhari vibhinna samaure malikana parivarttit karichhi .
pan: ih insaiclopydia britanica duvaara prakashit kiti gai hai; ih sangat 18 ve sadi ton chal rahi hai haalaaki us di malklat inhan sadia vich kai war badal chuki hai I
tam: itu encycklobidia britannika ing niruvanattal velitepattatu, inniruvanum 18aam noorthandu muthal iangivarukintu enfodhilu noorthandus netuk palamurai adan urimayalars malliuner.
tel: idi ancyclopedia britannika, ink; che prachurinchabadindi, shatabdaluga anekamars yajmanya marinppatiki, i company 18va shatabda nudi unnadi.
urd: ye insaayclopedya britanica, inkorported kii taraf se shaya kiya gaya hai. ye company 18 vaein sadi se maujuud hai, agarache sadiyon ke dauraan mukhtalf auqat main is kii milkiyat tabdel hui hai.
eng: It is published by Encyclopedia Britannica, Inc.; the company has existed since the 18th century, although it has changed ownership various times through the centuries.

ben: sahityik shilp hal sahityer samast kaaj ya shaili, vishyawastu, charitra kimba galper dhanch sunder. gitikabita, natak, chot galp evan upanyas era udaharan.
guj: sahityik kala e sunder shaili, vishay, patro ke vartatathyoma thayelam sahityik caryo che. kaavyona shabdo, natako, laghu vartao ane navalkatha badhan tena namuna che.
hin: saahitiyik kala, sahitya se sambandhit kritiyaan hai jo style, vishay, kirdaar yaa kahani main behtareen hoti hai. gaai jane vaali kavitaayen, naatak, laghu kathaayen or upanyaas sabhi udhaaharan hai.
kan: sahitya kalegalu andre sundaravaad shaili, vishay, patragalu athwa kathawastuvann hondiruvanth sahitya kritigalu. bhavagitegalu, naatakagalu, sann kathegalu mattu kadambarigalu ivell adkke udaharane.
mal: shailecondo , vishyankondo , kathapatralalo, kathagatiyalo sundarmay sahityakruthikalaa sahityakalkal ennuvilicunnat . bhavaganathmak kavit, nataka, cherukatha, novalu ennivellam udaharanjasa.
ori: sahitik kala heudi, sehisabu sahithya kruti, yeunguik style, vishatwastu, charitra kimba kaahaniku nei sundar hoithaye. geeti kavitha, natak, kshudra galp eban upanyas adi sabu tahar udaharan.
pan: sahitak kalaavaas saahit dis uh rachnavaan han jo shaili, theme, kirdaar, jaaa kahaani vich khubasurat han I gitakari kavitaas, naatak, chotia kahania ate novel ih sabh udaharan han.
tam: style, theme, kadabatras, katapoku madhriana vishyakalil anokialike kondull ilakkiab patibbugans ilakkiyak kalai endu goorukhirom. patal kavitis, natakngs, chiruktis, butinas ivastin udarans.
tel: saahithi kallu anevi style, itivritta, patral, leda kathan paranga andmains sahitya rachnal. geya kavitlu, natakal, laghu kathalu, inca navalls anni udaharanale.
urd: litereri art wo udabi kaam hote hain jo aslob , modua, harauf, yaa kahani ke lihaaz se khubasurat hote hain. geet, drame, mukhtsar kahaaniyan or naval, sab is kii misaaleen hain.
eng: Literary arts are works of literature that are beautiful in style, theme, characters, or storyline. Lyric poems, dramas, short tales, and novels are all examples.

ben: pathogener kshayaprapti nischit also, pathogenic rupe phire gie roger janma dewa tader pakshe atyant viral.
guj: ekavar roganus nabalan pade to te khub ja viral che ke te potana mul rogaanu swarupama parat thai ane tyar pachhi te rog peda kare che.
hin: yah dekhte hue ki rogaanu ksheen hai, bahut hi kam sambhaavna he ki ve rogajanak rup punah waapas aaen or baad main beemaari kaa kaaran bane.
kan: rogkarakagal shaktigundisilagiddare, avugalu tamm rogkarak rupakke hindiruguudu mattu munde rogavannutumaduvudu bailwe aparup.
mal: roganul shakti kshayichchavaanengiൽ av rogakaranmakunn stati matanganu tutr rogamundakanu ull saddhyat angeyaom apuർvvama.
ori: roganugudikar prabhab ksheen kari diayaithiva sthale, semane nizer rogakari roopaku pratyavarttan kariva tatha paravartti samaure rog srushti kariva attant birala .
pan: ih dekhade hoe ki jarasim ait hunde han, uhanaas lai aapne jarasim roop vich vaapis auna ate bood vich bimari da kaaran banna bohut ait hunda hai|
tam: noikrumies veriamirent niliil irupatal, are noyuruvakk niliku mindu noi erbadudhuvadarkana waifu mik, mik aritu.
tel: aa vyadhikarak krimulu kshinimpajeyabadtai kabatti, avi vat vyadhikarak rupaniki tirigi vetali, tadanantaram roganni kaliginchada anedi chala arudu.
urd: chunki pathogen taraqeeq shudaa hote hain, is liye intihaai kamyab soraton main wo apni pathojenic shukla main waapas ate or is ke nattejey main bemaari kaa sabab banate hain.
eng: Given that pathogens are attenuated, it is extremely rare for them to revert to their pathogenic form and subsequently cause disease.

ben: pashchimghat evan arab sagarer madhyavarti 720 kimi dirgha elaka jure ekaguchchha gopan saikat evan khandi avasthan.
guj: paschim ghat ane arabi samudrani vachcheni 720 kimi lambi patti upar, ghanan badhan ajanya kinarao ane khadio aaveli che.
hin: pashchimi ghati or arab sagar ke bich 720 ki.me. lambii pattee main kai chupe hue samudri tat or sankri khadiyaan hai.
kan: paschim ghattagalu mattu arabbi samudrad naduvin 720 ki.me. uddad bhoobhagadalli halvaaru gupt kadaltiragalu hagu colligalive.
mal: paschim ghatateutayu arabikkataliൻreyu idilull 720 kilometർ nilemulla bhoomiute tundiൽ oru kutte ariappetatt katൽttirlu aruvilu olinjukithkunnu.
ori: pashchim ghat eban arab saagar madhyare thiva eka 720 ki.mi. deergha pattikare anek lukkait belabhumi eban kshudra nadeemaan rahichhi .
pan: pattmi ghat te arabia saagar de vichale 720 kilometre lambi patti vich chhupe hoe tat ate kande han I
tam: merkut todarchi malikum arabic katlukkum itie ull 720 kimi nilmull nilatundil vellie theriyatapati parbal katankarum kaliksum ulsana.
tel: paschim kanumal mariyu arabia samudra madhyan 720 kimi la podevati kanthbhumipai marugun unn anek samudrathiras, keyal unnai.
urd: mugharabi ghat or bahaira arab ke darmiyaan 720 kilometre lambii pattee par poshida bechuun or khaadiyo kii badi taadaad maujuud hai.
eng: On a 720 km long strip between the Western Ghats and the Arabian Sea, lie a host of hidden beaches and creeks.

ben: 6.4.6 dhara vyakhya kare prajna kaunsuli dakhil karen ye, ukt dharati ekati gurudand bahan kare; ye ukt dharati caryakari sansthar tarfe kono bhuler janya telephones kathavarta anya hastkshap athva bhul jayga chalith karaar kshetre prayojya anyatha naya; evan bartaman mammla nalisher antargat caryakalapaguli rilaencer na hay ek nitihin grahaker hawa 6.4.6 dharati prayukt have na.
guj: kalam 6.4.6 na arthaton par vidvan vakile rajuat kari hati ke uparokt kalam bhaare dand vahan kare che; operaterni koi khamine karne kolni chhedchhad athva khota routingna kissama aa kalam aakarshit thai che anyatha nahi; ane vartaman kissama thayela caryoni fariyaad anaitik grahakane laagu pade che ane relaysne nahii, tethi kalam 6.4.6 hethal fariyaad thai shake nahi.
hin: khand 6.4.6 kii vyakhya karte hue, vidwaan vakil ne kaha ki ukt khand ke liye baari harjaana he; ukt khand prachaalak kii ore se hui galati hone par kol ke saath hera-pheri yaa kol ko galat tareeke se root kiye jane par lagu hota he or yah kisi anya kaaran hone par lagu nahin hota; evam is vartmaan maamle main shikaayat kiye gaye krity reliance ne nahin balki kisi aniatik abhidaata ne kiye hai, isliye khand 6.4.6 lagu nahin ho saktaa.
kan: kalam 6.4.6.annu vyakhyaan madid vidvanmanya vakilaru, sadri kalam dodda mottad zulmaneannu hondiruvudendu, karegamalli akram hastakshep athwa tappad samparkadantah nirvahakar mele dosharopavannu madebahudad sandarbhagamalli matrave sadri kalam anvayvaguudendu, hagillade hodare anvayvaguudillavendu; hagu present prakarandalli aapadit krityagainnu yaradaru niyambaahir chandadaranigashte aropisabahudu hortagi rilyansgallavaddarind kalam 6.4.6.annu anvayislu sadhayvillvendu mandisidru.
mal: 6.4.6 end vakuppine vyakhyaniumpoൾ, aa vakuppanusrich valioru pichha chumattamennu, aa vakup operadeerute bhagattuninnull etho pichhavukondulla ketupatukalo kolukalute thetay rutingo undayal matrame sangatamaku ennu, i kaseil parati karanmay pravrittika nitibodhamillat upabhoktavinte bhagattuninnanennu rilayansiൽninnallennu atinaൽ 6.4.6 end vakup badhakamakanavillennu punditnay abhibhashakan bodhippitchu.
ori: up-dhara 6.4.6 r bakhya upare, subijnya adhivaktha yukthi rakhithile ye ukt dharatire eka kathor dand rahichhi; aparetarank taralaru ghatithiva kichhi truti janit 'kal tamparing' kimba 'trutipurna rauting' abhiyog kshetrare ukt dharati loda hue eban anytha nuhen; eban yehetu varttmanar mammlatire abhiyog karayaithiva karyangudik pin jane neetihin grahak daadi eban rilaens daadi nuhen, dhara 6.4.6 adhinare aavedan karayyparib naahin .
pan: khand 6.4.6 di vyakhya karade hoe vidawan wakil ne pesh kita ki ukat dhaara vich bhaari juramaana hai, ukat dhaara operator de kite nuksaan kaaran on walia kalas de taping jaaa galat rooting de mammlas 'te centerit hai ate ih kise hor kaaran 'te lagu nahi hunda; ish vartaman maamle vich jo shikaitaan kitia han , karwaia rilines ne nahi balki ik beiman gaahak ne kitia han, ish lai khand 6.4.6 lagu nahi hoo sakda|
tam: kararind valakkaringr sattaprivu 6.4.6 kuritu virekum alicumbodhu, menopati sattaprivu pery aparatat vidikakudiyatu enllum; menopati sattaprivantu abaratreyn truple edovoru kuraibadu karanmak assibbugans otukkattle alltu dhawmak inaittal suanilkalil prayogixpaduvatu enllum; anal tarboty vanggil pukaralicoppatt seyals woru nermayyanuchu chandadharar meete chattapadukintu reliance mitall enpatal sattaprivu 6.4.6-ai prayogik mudiyadhu enllum tan vatat munvaitar.
tel: upanibandhan 6.4.6 vivaran pimmat, sadru upanibandhan bhari jarimana vidhistundani; kals lo jokyam chesukovada leda kalsunu tappu daari pattinchada operator vapu tappida karnangane tapp maremi kaani sandarbhallo sadru upanibandhan upayuktiloki wastendani; mariyu present kesulo firyad chembadd karyakalapalku karna ock vichakshanarahit chandadarudide kani rilien varidi kadani, upanibandhan 6.4.6 ni ashrainchalerni vidwattugal nyayavadi savinyanga nivedincharu.
urd: shuq 6.4.6 kii tashrih par fazil vakil ne kaha ki mazkora shuq main bhaari jurmaana aayad kiya gaya hai; ki mazkora shuq oprator kii kisi galati kii vajah se kaalon ke saath ched chhad yaa galat roating ke maamlat main nafiz hoti hai jabaki duusari soorat main naheen; or chunki maujod maamle main shikayat karda carrwaiyaan ek be emaan subskariber se mansoob hain na ki reliance se, is liye shuq 6.4.6 kaa istemaal naheen kiya jaa saktaa.
eng: On the interpretation of clause 6.4.6, learned counsel submitted that the said clause carries a heavy penalty; that the said clause is attracted in cases of tampering or wrong routing of calls attributable to some fault on the part of the operator and not otherwise; and since in the present case the actions complained are attributable to an unscrupulous subscriber and not to Reliance, clause 6.4.6 cannot be invoked.

ben: tejascrian isotoper kramavardhaman chahida evan parmanvik vigyane unnat gaveshanar purvabhas pae, 1970-ei tulanamulkabhave uchchatar neutron pravah yukt arevati parmanvik culli prayojanita anubhut hayesil, yar fale tromber bark-e shesh percent aar-5 (paravartikale dhruva parmanvik culli name parichit) parmanvik cullities nirman evan sampadan caryakar hayesil.
guj: redioisotopsni vadhati jati mang ane parmaanu vigyanma adyatan sanshodhanane jotaan, chhek 1970na dayakama tulanatmak rite uncha neutron pravah sathe bija riektrani jarur janai, je chhevate bi.e.ar.sii. trombe khaate ar-5 riector (jenu pachhi dhruv riector namakan thayu) na bandhkam ane arambhma parinamyu.
hin: 1970 ke dashak main hi vikiran samasthanik kii badhati maang kaa purvanumaan lagaakar or nabhikeey vigyaan main acchhee pragati se ho rahe shodh ke kaaran tulanaatmak rup se adhik nautron abhivah vaale ek or riector kii aavashyaktaa mahasoos hui jiske parinamswaroop bi.e.aar.si., trombay main aar-5 riector (baad main jise dhruv riector kaa naam diya gaya) kaa nirmaan evam use pravartan main laana chaalu hua.
kan: radioisotopugalige hechuv bedike mattu anuvigyandalli unnat sanshodhanayannu mundalochisi, tulanatmakavagi adhik neutron harivull innondu riactorin agatyavannu 1970r dashakadashtu hindeye managanalagittu, conege ader prenamvagi trambayalliruva bi.e.aar.si.yalli aar-5 riactorin (amele dhruv riactor endu marunamkarnavagide) nirman mattu caryarambhwayitu.
mal: radio aisotoppukൾku anavshastrattile melekidilull gaveshanttinumulla vairunn aavashya munkuticntatinaൽ taratamyen ucrnn neutron flaksulla matoru anavriacarinte aavashya 1970 kalilttane anubhavppetukayu atotukka (pilkalat dhruv riacter enne punർnamakarna cheyyapret ) ar 5 riacarinte nirmmattil pravർttanarambhtil avasanikkukayu cheitu.
ori: redioisotap eban anbik vigyanare unnat gaveshanar bahuthiva chahidar poorvanuman kari, apekshakrit adhik neutran pravah heuthiva annga eka riaktorar aavashyakata bahu poorvaru 1970 dashakare anubhava karayaithila, yahaki parisheshre tramber bi.e.aar.si. thare thiva aar-5 riactor (pare 'dhrub riactor' bhavare punaynamit) r nirmanr karan hoithila .
pan: radioteps di vadhadi mang nuun dekhade hoe te parmanu vigyaan vich takneeki khoj kaaran, ik hor uddh nautran fainks wale riector di lod 1970 vich pai see jise kaaran R-5 riector (bood vich ish da naame dhruva riector vich badal ditaa see ) ,b.e.ra.si, tarubae vich ish di sanrchana keeti gai see I
tam: katriyakk oraghat tanimangalin devai adhikaripu parchiya ganipu, anuvial araichiil peru munnenram akhiyavainal 1970kalileye oppetalvil uir neuran payam kont innuru uly avasium endu unrappattatu, its vilaivak irutiil trambe pigarci maiyatil aar-5 anu uly (binner dhuruva anu uly endu payar majhpattatu) amaicopattu seyalpant dodangiyadu.
tel: samastanikmulku mariyu parmaanu shastralo adhunathan parishodhanaku perugutunn avasarmunu uhinchi, 1970la natike adhikatar neutran pravahan gal marok riyactor aavashyakat kaligindi, tudaku adi bark, trambe lo ar-5 riyactor(aa taruvat dhruv riyaktoruga peru marbadindi) nirmana mariyu arambhaniki parinminchindi.
urd: nevaclair since main radio aasotopes or jadid tahaqiq kii badhati hui talab kii pesh goi karte hue, nisbatan zyaada neutron bahaav ke saath ek or ri actor kii zarurat ko 1970 kii duhai main mahasuus kiya gaya, jis ke nattejey main balakhir bi aye aar si, trumbe main aar 5 ri actor (baad main jis kaa naam dhruva ri actor rakha gaya) kii tamir par mantaj hawa.
eng: Foreseeing a growing demand for radioisotopes and advanced research in nuclear science, the necessity for another reactor with comparatively higher neutron flux was felt way back in the 1970s, which ultimately resulted in the construction and commissioning of the R-5 reactor (later renamed as Dhruva reactor) at BARC, Trombay.

ben: arthshastra anuyayi ekati swarna baa karsh chhil 80 rattir saman (1 masha = 5 ratti maner vittite).
guj: arthshastra mujab ek swarna athva karsha 80 ratti barabar thati hati (1 masha = 5 rattina aadhare).
hin: arthshaastra ke anusaar, ek suvarna yaa karsh 80 rattiyon ke baraabar tha (1 maasha = 5 ratti ke maanak ke anusaar)
kan: arthshastrad prakaar, ondu swarna athwa karshavu 80 rattigalige samanvagittu (1 maajh=5 ratti emb pramankavannu adhrislagide).
mal: arteshastra anusrich, (5 rati oru mash end kanakil) 80 rattikalk samama oru swarna athva oru kർsh
ori: 'arthshastra' anusaare, eka srna ba karsh 80 rati sahit saman thila ('1 masha = 5 rati' manak upare aadhar kari) .
pan: arthshastra de anusaar, ik sarwan jaaa karsha 80 batia de barabar see (1 maasha= 5 ratti miar de aadhar 'te)|
tam: arthashasthratin pati, woru swarnam alltu karsham 80 rattilukkuch samam (adavatu 1 masha = 5 rutti enum taranilin adippatail).
tel: arthashastra prakara, ock swarna lek karsh 80 rattilaku samana(1masha = 5 rattis ane pramana prakara)
urd: arth shastra ke mutabik, ek swarn yaa krish 80 ratti ke barabar tha (jis kii buniyaad 1 mashaa = 5 ratti mayar par hai).
eng: According to Arthashastra, one svarna or karsha was equal to 80 rattis (based on the 1 Masha = 5 Ratti standard).

ben: eta eman cono prakriar kshetre hate par ya ekati jiv thek udbhuth has (ya halo endogenic) evan pariweshe sada deya (pariwesh dwara pravesh karano).
guj: e sajivama (jemke antarjat) sharu thati koi pan prakia ane paryavaranne pratibhav aapti (paryavaranne anakul thati) babato ange hoi shake.
hin: yah aisi kisi bhi prakriya ke liye kah sakate hai jo kisi jeev ke andar utpann hoti he (yani antarjaat) or vaataavaran ke prati pratikriyaatmak hoti he (vaataavaran dwaara samrohit).
kan: adu jiviya owgade aarambhwaguv (andare, antarvardhak) mattu parisarkke spandisuv (parisarad prenamvagi untaguv) yavude prakriayannu suchisabahudu.
mal: oru anujivikutel (uda:endojenus) utaledukkunnatu paristateot pratikariunnatu (paristateyaൽ pakappetunnatu) ay etu prakriayeyu atin suchippikkaൻ kaniyu.
ori: eha yekunsi prakriaku bujhithaye yahaki eka jeeva madhyare srushti hoithaye (arthath antarjat) eban parivesh prati prathikria dekhaithaye (parivesh dra prabhavita) .
pan: ih kise ve prakiria da havaala de sakda hai, jo kise jeev de under paidaa hundi hai (bhav andoganus) ate watavarna nuun jawaab dindi hai (watavarna duara ulajhi hoi)|
tam: itu, ore urinatagul donasi (adavatu agatokaram) suzlukkud tagavamaddukh kollum (suzluku vayappatudal) evvoru nicktomuries kurikalam.
tel: adi ock pranilopal udbhavinchi (anaga endogenus), (paryavarana dwara praveshinchi) paryavarananki pratispandinche edaina prakrian suchinchavacchu.
urd: ye koi bhi aisa amal hosakta hai jo jandarake indra paida hota hai yani, druvan jandaar) or maahaul se rudamal kurta hai (maahaul ke jaria tarbet yaafita).
eng: It can refer to any process that originates within an organism (i.e., endogenous) and responds to the environment (entrained by the environment).

ben: yakhan pulish 154 dhara adhine thaka sanvidhibaddha prayojaniyataguli paalan kare na, nirdhari caryadhara takhan akhil bhartiya ayurvigyan sansthaner maamala, gangadharer maamala, hari sinher maamala evan minu kumari maamla kshetre sarasarivave virodhe chhil.
guj: jayare police kalam 154 heyelni vaidhanik aavashyakataonu paalan karti nathi tyaare ol india institut of medical sayns case, gangadharno case, hari sinhano case, ane minu kumarina kesama marg prapya che.
hin: gangadhar kaa maamla, hari singh kaa maamla, or minu kumari kaa maamla, akhil bhartiya ayurvigyaan santhaan ke in sabhi maamalon main vah rasta shaamil tha jo liya ja saktaa tha jab police dhara 154 ke kanoonee daayitv kaa paalan karne main asafal rahe.
kan: kalam 154r adiyalli policeru kanoonuvihit kramagainnu kaigolldiddag, anusarisabekad vidhanvu akhil bharat vaidyakiya vigyan sansthey prakaran, gangadhar prakaran, hari singh prakaran, mattu minu kumari prakarangamalli nervagi vadavishayavagittu.
mal: sekshൻ 154 prakaram niyamparamai ventav police niർvahikunnillengiൽ swikariavunn way, oൾ india iൻstitute of medicaൽ sayൻsas case, gangadhർ case, hari singh case, minu kumari case ennivakaliൽ pratyakashmay prashnmairunnu.
ori: police dhara 154 antargat bidhisammat aavashyakatagudiku karyankaari nakariva samaure, upalavdh thiva upanti sidhasaikh 'akhil bharatiya aajurvigyan pratishthan' mammla, ganggadharank mammla, hari sinhank mammla, eban meenu kumarink mammla sahit virodhabhasare thila .
pan: jadon police bhaag 154 de kaanooni zarurtaan nuun puura nahi kardi taan us da marg all india institute aaf medical sinas case, gangadhar case, hari singh case ate minu kumari de case vich lagu hai I
tam: kavalturiner brivu 154in keel ull avasiuman satt natwatikiss edukkad podhu aduttu enna seyy wants enpatu, aal india institute off medical scincess vanku, gangadran vanku, hari singh vanku, meena kumari vanku akhiyavail neradip praschaniak exundatu.
tel: polisuvaru sekshan 154 krind chattaparamin charyal tisukoni sandarbhatlo andubatulogal vyavahar kram akhil bharat vedya vigyan sansth kesu, gangadhar kesu, hari singh kesu mariyu minu kumari kesullo neruga virudhanga unnadi.
urd: police ke zarie kanoonee taqaazon ko dafaa 154 ke tahat anjaam na diye jane par jo dastyab shudaa tareeqa car hota hai, wo aal india insiti tute of medical sincez ke maamle, gangadhar ke maamle, hari singh ke maamle, or menu kumari ke maamle main brah rasat zer bahas tha.
eng: The course available, when the police do not carry out the statutory requirements under Section 154 was directly in issue in the All India Institute of Medical Sciences case, Gangadhars' case, Hari Singhs' case, and Minu Kumaris' case.

ben: amiya chakravarty (30she november 1912-6i march 1957) 1940 evan 1950-era dashaker ekajan bhartiya chalachchitra parichalak, chitranatyakar o prayojak, evan hindi cinemar pradhan chalachchitra parichalak chhillen.
guj: amiy chakravarti (30 november 1912 - 6 march 1957) bhartiya film nirdeshak, patakatha lekhak ane nirmata hata ane 1940 ane 1950na dayakaoni hindi filmona teo agrim nirdeshak hata.
hin: amiy chakravarti (30 navambar 1912 -6 march, 1957) ek bhartiya film nirdeshak, patakatha lekhak or nirmaataa the jo 1940 or 1950 ke dashakon main hindi cinema ke agrani film nirdeshak the.
kan: amiya chakravarty (30 navembar 1912-6 march 1957) obb bhartiya chalanchitra nirdeshak, chitrakathegaar, hagu nirmapakaragiddaru mattu 1940 hagu 1950r dashakagamalli hindi chitrarangadallin munchuni chalanchitra nirdeshakaragiddaru.
mal: amiy chakravarty (1912 november 30 -- 1957 march 6 ) oru indian chalachchitrasamvidhayakanu tirkkathakrittu nirmmatavu, 1940kall 1950kall hindi sinimaile munnirasamvidhayakanumairunnu.
ori: ameeth chakravartti (30 november 1912-6 march 1957) jane bharatiya chakchchitra nirddeshak, chitranatya lekhak eban nirmata thile, yie 1940 o 1950 dashakare hindi cinemar pramukh nirddeshak thile.
pan: amia chakravarti (30 november 1912-6 march 1957) ik bharati film niradeshk, patakatha lekhak see, ate 1940 ate 1950 de hindi cinema vich niramata ate pramukh film niradeshk ve san|
tam: amiya chakravarti (30 november 1912-6 march 1957) ore indiat tirippat iyakuner, trikkadai edutupower manllum dayaripazar, melum avar 1940gus manllum 1950kalin indit tiraulagil munnanit tirippat iyakunarag irundaver.
tel: amiya chakravarti (30 november 1912-6 march 1957) ock bhartiya chitra darshak, screen play rachyit mariyu nirmat, mariyu 1940lu mariyu 1950laloni hindi cinemalku pradhan darshak.
urd: aamay chakravarti (30 navamber 1912-6 march 1957) ek hindustani film director, screen righter, or prodeusar the, or 1940 or 1950 kii duhaiyon ke hindi cinema main marof film director the.
eng: Amiya Chakravarty (30 November 1912-6 March 1957) was an Indian film director, screenwriter, and producer, and the leading film director in Hindi cinema of the 1940s and 1950s.

ben: ekati besh bada pradarshani, sanrakshnagar evan karmakshetra elaka sah tahri maidane grand mishrian sangrahashala hal prachin mishrian sangrahashala dirgha pratikshit prathmik pratisthapan.
guj: dha grand ijipshian muzium e lamba samaythi jeni rahe jovati hati tevu midan taharirma avelu mul sthanantarit tirthrup ijipshian sangrahasthan che, jema ghanu motu pradarshan, sangrah ane karyasthal kshetro che.
hin: grand misri sangrahalay midaan taharir main sammaanya misri sangrahalay kaa bahu-pratikshit praathmik pratisthaapan he jisamen pradarshnee, bhandaaran or kaary sthaan ke liye zyada badi jagah he.
kan: tahrir chowkadalliruva egypshan vastesangrahalayakke atyant mahattvad badaliad, dirghkaldind nirikshislagutthiruv grand egypshan vastesangrahalayavu innu bahishtu doddadad pradarshan, sangrahane mattu kelasad kacheriya jagagainnu hondiralide.
mal: pradർshanttinu , sambhranattinu, pravർttanattinumulla kututൽ vishalmay itanjhulla midaൻ tahririe adaricappedunn egypshyaൻ musiyattin, ere kalatte kattirippinushes praiamikamai pakar kititan graൻd egypshyaൻ musium.
ori: 'grand egyptian meujiyam' heudi mi'daan tahreer thare thiva suprasiddh egyptee meujiumr deergha-pratikshit pradhan bikalp, yaharaki adhik vishal pradharshani, bhandaran kshamta, eban karmakshetraman rahichhi .
pan: mahaan misri ajaib ghar, midan taharir vich sthit satikaryog misri ajaib ghar di lambi der ton udik kar rahi punar sthapna hai, jise vich bada pradarashani khetra, stores ate com-kaaj da sthal hai I
tam: tahreer chatukkathil ull manmayana egyptia arungatchyattsqup patilak netungalam katrundhu pradan maderitak vandhulldu than egyptia maha arungatsium, ingu melum periyalvil katchip porullum semibbup bagudi paniit vasadikalum ulsana.
tel: midan tahrir loni ganyamin igipshian sangrahalayaniki baduluga marint pedd pradarshan, bhandara mariyu karyalaya pradeshalato di grand igipshian museum annaolgano vechi chustunnaprathamik punahsthapana.
urd: grand misri mauseum maidan taharir main kaabil ehtiram misri mauseum kaa buniyadi mutbadal hai, jis kaa tavel urse se intazaar tha, jis main bahut badi numaayish, storis or kaam kii jagah ke ilaka hain.
eng: The Grand Egyptian Museum is the long-awaited primary replacement for the venerable Egyptian Museum in Midan Tahrir, with much bigger exhibition, storage and workplace areas.

mal: punch, myർpuർ enni mekhalkalile kalapasettutർnnu khibർ pakhtuൻkhwaiൽ ninnull pakistaൻ pintunyot kudia pashttooൺ gotra itapealukarattutർnnu aa maharaj indyayute sainiksahaya teti.
ori: punch eban mirapur anychalre vidroh, eban pakistan-samarthith khivar pakhatunakh anchader pashthun aadivasi hastakshep pare maharaaja bharatiya samaric sahayatha magithile .
pan: punachh ate mirpur khetra vich bagawats ate khibar-pakhtunkhwa ton pakistani hamait praapat pastuni kabile di dakshandazi ton bood maharaja ne bharati fouj ton sahita mangi|

urd: ponch or mir pur ke ilaakon main baghawaton or pakistan kii pashto panahi wali khebar pakhtonkhwa se pashtun qubaili dakhil andaazi ke baad, maharaja ne hindustani faujee amudad talab kii.
eng: Following the rebellions in the Poonch and Mirpur areas and the Pakistan-backed Pashtun tribal intervention from the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, the Maharaja asked for Indian military assistance.
