ben: april 2020-r shuru dike, adhikarta corona viracer janya yakshmar sambhavya ekati tikake africa pariksha karaar vishay du'jan parsi vigyani adhyapak jaa pal meera evan camil lakht-era mantavyer virodhita kare da. jan kengasan take "nyakkarajanak evan jatividveshmulak" bale abhihit karen.
guj: april, 2020na arambhe nirdeshak do. jhon kengasonge be french vaignaniko, professor jin-pole meera ane chemil lochani avi tikaane ‘ghrunaspad ane rangabhedi’ ganavi tiraskrit kari hati ke corona virus mate sambhavit tubarculosis rasinu parikshan africama karvama aavashe.
hin: april 2020 kii shuruyaat main nideshak, dow. jon ankengesong ne do french vaigyanik -professor jon-paul mira or kameel louct kii tippaniyon kii ninda karte hue un tippaniyon ko "ghrinaaspad or jativaadee" bataaya kyonki in vaigyanikon ne suzav diya tha ki ek sambhavya tapedic ke tike kaa coronavirus ke liye pareekshan africa main kiya jaae.
kan: 2020r april tingala aarambhdalli, kshayarogad sambhavya lasikeyondannu koronavirasgagi africdalli prayogisi nodebekemb salahe nididd profesar jaan-pal mira mattu kyami lact emb ibbaru french vigyanigal helikeyannu nirdeshak da. jaan nekengasang, "asahyakar mattu varnabhed dhoraneind kudiruvudu" endu khandisidru.
mal: kshayrogapratirodhasadhyatyull oru vaxiൻ corona viralinayi africail parakshichunokcook end chhaang pol mira, kamil lokt enni franch profsarmarute abhiprayae "verupulawakkunnatu vanshiavirodh"mulatumanen 2020 april tutkkatiൽ diacter do. john kengsong apalpitchu.
ori: 2020 apriller aarmbhare, korona bhiras nimanthe eka sambhavya tuvarakulosis tikaa africare pariksha karayau boli paramarsh deithiva duijan ferasi vaigyanic, ubhay prafesar jan pal mira o kamili lotank manthavagudiku nirddeshak du. jan kingasang "aruchikar o varna-vaishambabadi" kahi ninda karithile.
pan: 2020 di shuruaat vich, niradeshk daa. jon ningasong ne doo french vigyania, profesar jine paal mara ate camil lochat duara keeti tipni ki coronavirus lai ik sambhavi tapadik vaccines nuun america vich "ghenauni ate naslwadi" on di ninda keeti |
tam: perasiriarkas jeen-pal mira manllum kamil lasht enjh erandu french vinjanis afbrikail korona virasuku woru kufippitt kachnoyd tadupuc velcsayuma endu sodikk wants enak karuddut therivittaths 2020 april dodakkathil iyakkunar doctor jaan kengachang khanditu atu "aruvaruppan inavad" karutu endu gurinar.
tel: 2020 april modatlo, iddru french shastravettalin proteesar gene-pal mira, kamil locht, kshaypai panicheyagal ock tikaani africalo karonavirus kos parikshinchalani suchistu chacin vyakhyas director doctor. john kangasong , "jugupsakarmainavi mariyu jatyahankaramainavi" ga khandincharu.
urd: april 2020 ke avayal main, diericter doctor jaan nikkingswing ne do francisi sincedanon, prophesar rhian pal meraa or camil lokht ke in tabaaron kii mazamat karte hue inhen "nagwar or nasal prastaan" qaraar diya jin main kaha gaya tha ki coruna virus ke liye mumkin tap diq ke waxine ko africa main aazamaaya jaanaa chahiye.
eng: In early April 2020, Director Dr. John Nkengasong condemned remarks by two French scientists, Professors Jean-Paul Mira and Camille Locht suggesting that a potential tuberculosis vaccine for the coronavirus be tested in Africa as "disgusting and racist".

ben: islamic bangla taar sukshma sutir kapad evan sari upadan, visesh kare jamdani janya prasiddh, ya mughal darbar thek hukumanama paesil.
guj: islamic bengal tena uttam sutarau kapad ane sario mate janitu hatu, khas karine jamdani, jeni mang to mughal darbarmathi aavati hati.
hin: islamic bengal apane sarvottam sooti vastron or saadiyon ke utpaadan ke liye janaa jaataa tha, khaas kar ke jamdani ke liye, jise mughal darbar kaa samarthan praapt tha.
kan: islami bengalvu ader atyuttam hatti battegalu mattu siregal, visheshwagi, moghal aasthanadind sannadugagannu paded jamdaniya utpadanegagi hesaruvasiagittu.
mal: mughal rajdhaniilninn avashyapat shraddheyamay jandaniulpate et mikachch paruttittunikalu sarilu nirmmikunnatil islamic bengal peruketirunnu.
ori: islamiya beng nizer utkrushtatam sutabuna kapdaa eban shadhi nimanthe prasiddhi arjan karithila, visheshtah 'jamadhani', yahaki mogul darbarar skruti labh karithila .
pan: islamik bengal nuun sabh ton vadhia kapaah fabric ate saria, khaas for 'te jamadani de utpadan lai jaanya janda see, jise nuun mughal adaalat ton varant mile san |
tam: islamier ant bengalam dalisirent paruddi adies manllum pudavaikalin ushpattikup peyarbervrundatu, atil jamdani kufippittakkadu, athangu mughalay araswailrundhu kolmudal korikis vandana.
tel: islamik bengal dani uttam nulu vastras mariyu chiral tayari, mukhyanga jandani, ki prasiddhi chendindi, vitikai mughal aasthana nudi uttarulu labhinchevi.
urd: islamic bengal ko behtareen kapaas ke kapade or saadiyo kii taiyaari ke liye tasalim kiya jatatha, khaas tuur par jamudani, jis ne mughal adaalat se warrant haasil kiye the.
eng: Islamic Bengal was noted for its production of the finest cotton fabrics and saris, notably the Jamdani, which received warrants from the Mughal court.

ben: 2021 saler 15i september antarjatik ganatantra deebs smaran sansad tube chalu kara hayesil bharter up-rashtrapati shri em. venkaia naidu, bharter pradhanmantri, shri narendra modi evan loksvar spikar, shri om birlar august upsthitite, nayadilli sansad bhavan samyukta sadane.
guj: 15 september, 2021 na roj antarrashtriya lokshahi divasni ujwani antargat navi delhima sansad bhavan aeneksi khaate bharatna uparashtrapati shri em. venkaiya naidu, bharatna vadapradhan shri narendar modi, ane loksabha adhyaksha shri om birlani prabhavak upsthitema sansad tivinu lokarpan karvama aavyu hatu.
hin: 15 sitambar 2021 ko antarrashtriya loktantr diwas manaane ke liye sansad bhawan anexi, nai dilli main bharat ke up-raashtrapati, shri em. venkayya naidu, bharat ke pradhanmantri, shri narendra modi, tathaa loksabhaa adhyaksh, shri om birla kii garimamay upasthiti main sansad tii.ve. aarambh kiya gaya.
kan: 2021r ceptembar 15randu antarashtriya prajaprabhutva dinad smornarth, bharatad uprashtrapati shri em. venkayya naydu, bharatad pradhan mantri shri narendra modi mattu loksabha speekar shri on birla ivar gauravanvit upasthtiyalli navdehlia sansat bhavanad avarandalliruva saudhadalli sansad ti.vi.yannu lokarpane madlayitu.
mal: 2021 septembർ 15n antarashtra janadhipatyadinam achrichukond newdaൽhiile paർlameൻr mandirattiൻre anaksiൽ uparashtraprati shri e. venkayy naidu, pradhanmantri narendramodi, loksabha spikkർ shri on biർle ennivarute mahaniya sannidhyattiൽ sൻsad tivi udghatna cheyyappettiriunnu.
ori: aantharjatik ganatantra divasar smritiraksha kari, 15 september 2021 re, nooadilhir sansad upabhaban thare bharatar up-rashtrapati, shri em. bhenkaya naidu, bharatar pradhanamanthri, shri narendra modi, lokasabha vachaspati shri om birlankar mahimaant upastatire 'sansad ti.bhi.'r shubharambh karayaishi .
pan: 15 September 2021 da intersrashtirya loktantar divas nuun yaad karan lai agast vich navin dilli de sansad bhavan vich sansad ti.vi arambh kitha gya jise vich bharat de vit-rashtrapati shri aim. winkeatch naidu, rashtrapati shri narendra modi ate spikar,lok sabha shri om birla shaamil san I
tam: 15 september 2021 andu sarwatech jananayak dint ninaiukurum vitmak putudilliil ull natalumanow inipbuk kddittil india dunai janadhipati thiru em. vengaiya naidu, indiab pratamar thiru narendra moti, makalvai sabanayekaar thiru om birla akhiorine medgu munnelil sansat dolicadsi dodangappatatu.
tel: 2021 september 15 na antarjatiya prajaswamy dinotsav sansmarnardha, new delhiloni parliament bhavan anex lo bharat uprashtrapati shri venkay nayu, bharat pradhani shri narendra modi, lok sabh spikar shri om birlal bhavy samakshanlo sansad tivi prarambhinchabadadi.
urd: 15 sitambar 2021 ko jamhorit ke alami din ke mauqaa par nai dahali main parlemint house anexi main nib sadar jamhori hind janaab em vyankya naidu, vazeer aazam janaab narendra modi or lok sabha ke spikar janaab om birla kii masaud maujudagi main sansad tii vee kaa afatitah kiya gaya .
eng: Commemorating the International Day of Democracy on 15 September 2021, the Sansad TV has been launched in the august presence of the Vice-President of India, Shri M. Venkaiah Naidu, the Prime Minister of India, Shri Narendra Modi and Speaker, Lok Sabha, Shri Om Birla at the Parliament House Annexe in New Delhi.

ben: ei dharati 1970-era dashake manosamiksha o darshaner madhyam evan tarapar 1980-r dashake itihasher madhyam vitarkke agie nie gie nijer punravritti ghata.
guj: aa rachnariti potane 1970na dayakama manovishleshan ane filsufi charchaane aagal karine punravartit kare che ane pachhi 1980na dayakama itihasane.
hin: yah pravriti 1970 ke dashak main manovishleshan or darshan ke madhyam se or phir 1980 ke dashak main itihaas ke madhyam se bahes ko aage badhaate hue doharaai jane vaali thi.

urd: is pattern ne 1970 kii duhai main nafasyati tajjiye or falsafe ke saath bahas ko aage badhaate hue khud ko doharaaya, or fir 1980 kii duhai main taarikh ke saath.
eng: This pattern would repeat itself in the 1970s with psychoanalysis and philosophy pushing the debate along, and then history in the 1980s.

ben: chhabity mukti pawar 10 bashwar pare arbaj khan ekati saakshakare balesillen ye, chhabiti bajet 30 koti (2020 sale 57 koti taka baa 7 koti 2 laksh markin dollarer saman) thek 49 kotite (2020 sale 93 koti baa 12 koti markin dollarer saman) barano hayesil yar fale tar besh kshati has, tave vismayakar safalyer pare trini salmaan khaner parishramik die diesillen.
guj: filmani rajuatna das varsh bad arbaz khaane ek mulakatma janavyu hatu ke filmanu bajet 30 crod (2020maa 57 crod athva 72 lakh america dollar jetla)thi vadhine 49 crod (2020maa 93 crod athva 1.20 crod america dollar jetla) thai gayu hatu, jene karne aene thodi khot gai hati, pan bhavy safalta malyan bad tene salman khaanne pagar chukavyo hato.
hin: film relies hone ke 10 saal baad arbaj khan ne ek saakshaatkaar main kaha ki film kaa bajet 30 karod (2020 main 57 karod yaa you.es. 72 lakh dollar ke baraabar) se badhaakar 49 karod (2020 main 93 karod yaa you.es. 120 lakh dollar ke baraabar) kar diya gaya tha), jisase unhen kuch nuksaan hua, lekin baari safalataa ke baad, ve salmaan khan kaa vetan de sake.
kan: cinema bidugadeyad 10 varshagal nantar, sandarshanavondaralli arbaz khan, cinemad bajet 30 kotiind (2020ralli 57 koti athwa you.es.$7.2 dashalakshakke sam) 49 kotige (2020ralli 93 koti athwa you.es.$12 dashalakshakke sam) airikeyad prenam tanage ondishtu nashtagaladvadaru bhaari yashassin nantar tanu salman khange sambalavannu nididenendu heliconderu.
mal: chitram purattikaeni 10 varshattinu sheea nalkia oru abhimukhttil arbas khan, 30 koti (2020l 57 koti allengil 7.2 dashalaksha american dollar) yairunn chitrattiൻre bajat 49koti (2020l 93 koti allengil 12 dashalaksha american dollar) yai tanic kueach nashtamuntakicond uyർttiyatayu, pakshe chitrattiൻre gambhiravijayattettutർnn salman khan shampalam naൽkiyatayu parannu.
ori: film mukthilabh karibar 10 barsh pare, arawaj khan eka saakshaatkare kahithile ye filmatir vajetku 30 koti (2020re eha 57 koti ava eu.es.$7.2 niqut seh saman)ru 49 kotiku badei dia yaithila (2020re eha 93 koti ava eu.es.$12 niqut seh saman), yaha falre tanku kichhi kshati sahiva pin padithila, kintu ehar birat safamta pare, se salman khanank betan deithile.
pan: film di relies ton 10 saal bood, arabaaz khan ne ik interviu vich kiha ki film da bajat 30 karod ton vadha ke (2020 vich 57 karod jaaa you asa $ 7.2 million de barabar) 49 karod (2020 vich 93 karod jaaa you asa $ 12 million de barabar) kar ditha gya, jise naal us nuun kujh ghats pia, per yaadagaar safalta ton bood, usne salaman khan nuun tankhaah diti|
tam: indet tirippadam veleyaqi 10 andugalukqup pingu arpas khan woru nerkaolil pesumbodhu, pattin budget 30 kotiilrundhu (2020il 57 koti alltu yues$7.2 millionuku nickrantu) 49 kotiak (2020il 93 koti alltu yues$12 millionuku nickrantu) uirdoppattatagaum, itsal avaruku chil nashangs ettpttatagaum, eninu adan amogh vexikqup pingu salman kanukurya sambawatai than valangiyathagaum gurinar.
tel: chitra vidudalan padeval taruvat, arbaj khan ock intervulo, aa chitra vyayam 30 kots (2020 lo 57 kots leda yues $7.2 milian ku samana) nudi 49 kots (2020 lo 93 kots leda yues $12 milian ku samana) varaku perigindani, tadwara ataniki konni nashtal kaligayani, kani dani bhari vijaya taruvat, atanu salman khanku vetana chellinchanani telipad.
urd: film kii reliz ke 10 saal baad arbaz khan ne ek intervayo main bataya tha ki film kaa bijat 30 karod (57 main 7 karod yaa 2.2020 milin america dollar ke masavi) se badhaa kar 49 karod (93 main 12 karod yaa 2020 milin america dollar ke masavi) kridya gaya tha, jis kii vajah se in ko kuch nuqasaan uthaanaa pade, lekin is kii badi kaamyabi ke baad unhon ne salamaan khan kaa mishahraa adaa kridya.
eng: 10 years after the film's release, Arbaaz Khan stated in an interview that the film's budget was hiked from 30 crore (equivalent to 57 crore or US$7.2 million in 2020) to 49 crore (equivalent to 93 crore or US$12 million in 2020), leading to few losses for him, but after the monumental success, he paid the salary for Salman Khan.

ben: 1920-era dashak thek peshadari engineearra dhatuvidya aagrahi chhillen ya poorve aitihyagat karushilp viseshjader ecchetia kshetra chhil.

hin: 1920 ke dashak se vyavsaayik ejiniyaron ne teerandaji main dilchaspee lenaa shuru kar diya he, jo ki pehle is kaushal ke paaramparik visheshgyon kaa vishisht kaaryakshetra tha.
kan: 1920r dashakadindichege, vrittipar enjinierugalu billugarikeyalli asakti talediddu, alliyavarege adu sampoornavagi sampradayik naipunyagarar kshetravagittu.
mal: munp parampragat karkashal vidagdhrute pratyek mandlamairunn ampattil 1920kal mutal proyenal enginiers tatparya aduttututkai.
ori: 1920 dashak tharu, pesadar yanthreemane teerandhaj prati aagrah pradarshan kariyanthi, yaha agru paramparik karigari vishewjnyamanank stantra kshetra thila.
pan: 1920 de dahaake ton, peshewar enginirs ne tir andaazi vich dilachaspi lai hai, jo pahilaan rivaaiti shilpkari mahrs da khaas domen see|

tel: gattlo sampraday chetipanul nipunul pratyek anshamin viluvidyalo,1920la nudi, vrittiparamin enginirle asakti kanabarustunnar.
urd: 1920 kii duhai ke baad se, pesha var engineeron ne teer andaazi main dilchaspee lee hai, jo pahele ravayati dastakaree mahrain kaa khasusi maidan tha.
eng: Since the 1920s, professional engineers have taken an interest in archery, previously the exclusive domain of traditional craft experts.

ben: bimanbandare mit o greet parisheba paryatakder pashapashi sansthar janyao ekati gurutvapurna seva yehetu eti paryatakder aagman baa prasthaner samay druttar cliarenc sahaitar madhyam sthananter, malapatra bahan o pariwarsah bhraman sahayya kare evan bimanbandarer madhye die drut, nirjhanjhat o nirapada chalan nischit kare.
guj: vimanmathak parani meet and greet seva pravasio ane company mate agatyani seva che karanke te pravasione aagman ane prasthaan samaye jhadpi sahaya kare che; badali, malsaman ane parivarik yatrama madadarup thai che ane vimanmathak par gatishil, saral ane salamat margni khatari aape che.
hin: vimaanapttan par swaagat seva aagantukon or company donon hi ke liye ek atyant mahatvapurn seva he kyonki yah aagantukon ko aagaman yaa prasthaan ke samay twarit or aasaan pargaman, sthanantaran, saamaan, or parivaar-sahit yatraaon main sahaayak hoti he, or hawaii adde se sheeghra, baadharahit or surakshit maarg sunishchit karti he.
kan: vimaan nildandalli ʼsandhisi swagatisuv seveʼyou pravasigarige berondu nildan ya margakke vimaan badlaisuvalli, samanu saranjamugal vishayavagi mattu kutumbadondigin prayandalli nervagutta, aagaman athwa nirgamnagal parvangiannu vegavagi padeyuvalli sahakarisuvudarind mattu vimaan nildanad mukhantar tvarit, sugam mattu surakshitwagi haduhoguvikeyannu khatripadisuvudarind, adu pravasigaru hagu sanstheyavaribbarigu bahu mukhyavad seveyagide.
mal: varavil pokl sancharie fast-track cliaraൻsilute sahayikunnatinal kaimarengൾ, yatrasamans, kutubasametamull yatra enniviൽ sahayikunnatinal eiർpoർttilute surakshitmay katannupokൽ udhapunalkunnuvennatinal eiർpoർttille meat aaൻd greet sർvis sancharikൾku companikkukutiyu oru supradhan sevena.
ori: viman bandar thare dekha-saakshaat seva ubhay company eban parywakamanank pin eka guruthpurna seva, karan eha paryletkankar aagman kimba prasthaan samaure sthanantar, bagej eban parivarika bhramanar subidha pradaan kari fast-trak cliurance prakriaku sahaj karithaye, eban viman bandar dei eka chanychal, sahaj o nirapad yatra sunishchit karithaye.
pan: hawai ada 'te suagat seva sailania ate company dovan lai hi bohut mahatavpuuran seva hai kiunki ih sailania nuun agman ate vidaai samen sukhe sair sapate, tabaadle vich madad ate parivar samet safar vich sahai hundi hai ate hawai aade 'te cheti, nirvighan ate sudkhfat awajai nuun nishchit kardi hai|
tam: viman nilaiyatil ull varaverbuch sevai subaulap bhayanilukum niruvanangalukum woru muqgiyach sevaiyag vihangukintu, anendal atu bhayaniluku varuki manllum puchapadu munayangana virivagak katakk udavukintu, vimanam maderudal, udymile, kudumpub payanam akhiyawe sarndu udavilikkintu, manllum viman nilaiyatil viraivagat tanguddinwhi bhadukappak vanduselvats urudiseigintu.
tel: vimanashrayal vadd kalisi palkarinchada paryatkulku alage companyki ock pradhan sev, andukante idi paryatkul aagamnal leda nishkramnalku anumatula vegwanta cheyatanii, badililku, samanku, kutumb prayananki sahay padutundi, mariyu vimanashray gunda vegwantamin, sulabhamin mariyu surakshitmin margani nishchayparustundi.
urd: hawaii ide par meet and great service siyaahon ke saath saath company ke liye bhi ek ahim khidamat hai, kyonki ye siyaahon ko aamad yaa rawaanagi par muntakli , saaman or khandaan ke saath safar main madad dete hue fast trek clayerens main madad faraham krati hai , or hawaii ide se tej , khushguar or mahfuz guzargah ko yaqini banaati hai.
eng: Meet and Greet Service at the airport is an important service for tourists as well as for the company, since it helps the tourists in fast-track clearance through arrivals or departures, helping with transfers, baggage and family travel and ensures a swift, smooth and safe passage through the airport.

ben: kronas taar pitar sang vishwasaghatkta karesil evan taar santan sei ekai kaaj karbe ei bhay se riyar pratity santanke janmalaver sang sange kede khay nit.
guj: karanke chronse tena pitaa sathe gaddari kari hati, tethi tene bhay hato ke tenu santan pan evu ja karshe ane tethi darek vakhte jayare rea janma aapti, te santanne jhuntvi leto ane khai jato.
hin: kronas ne apane pita kaa saath vishwasghaat kiya tha, isliye use dar tha ki uske apane bachche bhi uske saath aisa hi karenge, or isliye har baar jab riya bachche ko janm detii thi, vah bachche ko chin kar kha jaataa tha.
kan: kronas tann tandege vishwasadroh bagediddavanaddarind, aat tann makkalu adnne maduttarendu bhayapattidd, hagagi prationdu bariu riya maguvige janma nididag, aat adnnu kasiducondu tinduhakuttidd.
mal: taൻ tante peitavin vanchichirunnuvennatinal tante santatikalu atupole cheyumenn kronas bhayakkukayu atinaൽ ria oro tavan prasavicchaposhu afzal kunine tattiparichetut tinnukyu cheitu.
ori: yehetu kronas nij pitank seh vishsaghatakata karithile, tanku bhan thila ye tank santaan madhya tank sahit epari karive, tenu pratyeka thar yeve riya janma deuthile, se pilatiku chhazinei ta'ku khaideuthile.
pan: kiunki karons ne aapne pitaa nuun dhoka ditaa see, us nuun dar see ki us di aulad ve ohi karegi, ish lai jini war ria ne janam ditha, os ne aw kho ke kha lya I
tam: kuronas tanatu tandaikud durogam iraittwitatal tanatu pillagalum adepolach seywars ena anjainan, eneway reyaukqup pinkkum ovvoru kuiandaes avan gavvich sentu dindwitan.
tel: chronus atadi tandriki drohan chacin karnanga, atadi santana ade pani chestudemonni bhayapadi, riya prasavinchin pratisari atadu aa biddhan lakkuni tinesevad.
urd: chunki crons ne apne vald ko dhoki diya tha, is liye use dar tha ki is kii oulad bhi aisa hi karee gi, lahza jab bhi riya ne bacche ko janm diya, wo bacche ko chin kar kha gaya.
eng: Because Cronus had betrayed his father, he feared that his offspring would do the same, and so each time Rhea gave birth, he snatched up the child and ate it.

ben: ei uparodher upar vitti kare sarkar 2006 saler 1la january agekar aadhikarik padmaryadar (pi.bi.o.aar) nicher pratiraksha penianbhogider penshner yathest unnati karaar evan 1997 saler 10i octoberer ager penianbhogider 1997 saler 10i octoberer pare penianbhogider samatulya karaar siddhanth niech৷
guj: aa bhalamanona aadhare, 1 january, 2006 pahelana adhikari hoddathi nichina sanrakshan nivritti vetandharko (pe.bi.o.ar.)na nivritti vethanma khasso sudharo karavaano ane 10 october, 1997 pahelamna nivritti vetandharcone 10 october, 1997 pachhina nivritti vetandharko samakaksh laavavaano nirnay lidho che.
hin: in anushansaaon ke aadhaar par sarkaar ne officer shrenee se neeche vaale surakshakarmi pension-bhogiyon (pi.bi.o.aar.) kii 1 janvari 2006 se pehle kii pension main kaaphi had tak sudhaar karne or 10 oktober 1997 se pehle ke pension-bhogiyon ko 10 oktober 1997 ke baad vaale pension-bhogiyon kii barabari par le aane kaa faisla kiya he.
kan: i shifarasugal aadharad mele, sarkaarvu 2006r janvary 1kke munchin adhikari shrenigint keeigin sena pinchanidarar (pi.bi.o.aar.) nivrutti vethanvannu gananiyavagi hechislu mattu 1997r october 10kke munchin pinchanidararannu 1997r october 10r nantarad pinchanidararige samanvagisalu thirmaniside.
mal: i shupaർshakalute atisthantiൽ 2006 january 1n mumpural ofisർ rangin tajayull (pi. bi. o. aaർ) pratirodh peൻshൻkarute peൻshൻ ganyamai mechchappetuttanu 1997 octobeർ 10n mumpural peൻshൻkare 1997 octobeർ 10n sheshmulla peൻshൻkaaർk tulyamakanu sർkkaർ thirumanichittund.
ori: ehi suparishagudikar aadharare, sarkar 1 january 2006 poorbar afisar shreneeru nimnare thiva (pi.bi.o.aar.) pratiraksha vibhagiya pension upabhoktamanankar pensionre guruthpurna sudhar anivaku tatha 10 october 1997 poorbar pension upabhoktamananku 10 october 1997 parar pension upabhoktamanank seh saman staraku anivaku nishpatti grahan kariyanthi .
pan: inhan farmaisha de aadhar te sarkaar ne 1 janvari 2006 ton pihals di penshs nuun sawaaran da faislas lya hai, afasar rank de niche (pi.bi.o.aar) de penyanara di rakhia karna ate 10 October 1997 ton pihals de penyanara nuun 10 October 1997 ton bood de penyanara de saman lyana I
tam: arasu indep parinduraikalin feril, 1 january 2006ku mundaiy adhikaribe patvikkuk kiull ranuv oyvudium beruvargalin (bipioar) oyvudhiyatts ganiumak adhikarixum, 10 october 1997ku mundaiy oyvudium beruvargalin nilaiys 10 october 1997kqup bindaiy oyvudium beruvargalukkuch samamak axum mudivusaitulldu.
tel: i sifarsul aadharanga, prabhutvan rakshan shakha oficer ryanku krindi pinganudarul (pibioar) 1 january 2006 ku poorvapu pinganuni gananiyanga penchalani mariyu 10 october 1997 ku poorvapu pinganudarul 10 october 1997 taruvati pinganudarulku sarisamana cheyalani niriinchindi.
urd: in sifaarshat kii buniyaad par hukuumat ne yakam janvari 2006 se kabel ke afasar se kam durje ke faujee panshneron (pii bi oo aar) kii panshan main khaatir khwaah behatari lane or 10 aktubar 1997 se kabel ke panshneron ko 10 aktubar 1997 ke baad ke panshneron ke barabar lane kaa faisla kiya hai.
eng: On the basis of these recommendations, the Government has decided to substantially improve the pension of pre-1 January 2006 defense pensioners below officer rank (PBOR) and bring pre-10 October 1997 pensioners on par with post-10 October 1997 pensioners.

ben: prathamti upadanshilata udrekkari ekati upabhokta arthaniti, evan parerti sarvagrasi samajik niyantraner madhyam hisabe parikalpit ek ghatti arthaniti.
guj: pahelu utpadakta vadharva matenu grahakonu arthtantra che, jayaare tyarapachhinu ekahaththu samazik niyantran mate rachvama avelu anntanu arthtantra che.
hin: pehali utpaadakta paidaa karne ke liye abhikalpit upabhokta arthvyavastha he, jabaki baad vaali sarvasattavadi saamaajik niyantran ke agent ke rup main abhikalpit abhaav arthvyavastha he.
kan: modalaneyadu grahak arthvyavasthayagiddu utpadakateyannu tarlu roopugondiddare, amelindu korate aarthikateyagiddu kendrikrut samajik niyantranad sadhanvagi roopitwagide.
mal: utpadankshamat janippikkaൻ rupakalpan cheit oru upabhoktru sampadvyavasthaa adyattetengiൽ samagradhipatyaparamay samuhikaniantranttiൻre oru ejൻrai rupakalpan cheit oru kshamasampadvyavasthaa rantamattet .
ori: poorvati utpadan briddhi kariva nimanthe parikanpit eka khauti arthvavastha hoithiva bele, parati heudi sarvadhikarbadi samajik nivnthrakar karyankaari shakti bhavare parikanpit eka abhab arthvavastha .
pan: pahila ik upbhogata arth vivstha hai jo utpadakta nuun paidaa karan lai tiar kitha gya hai, jadon ki duja ik ghat arth vivstha hai jo sampuuran tanashahi samajik niyantaran de tor vajon tiar keeti gai hai.
tam: mundaiyadhu urbhadit diddn abhivirudhi sayes nokil vativamicoppatt nugarvor poruladhar murai, anal bindyyadhu sarvadikar samukak kaddupattin upagranmak vihangum nokil vativamicoppatt paxakuraib poruladhar murai.
tel: modatidi utpadakat kalagachesenduku rupudiddabadin viniogadarul aarthik vyavasthi kaaga, rendavadi sarvadhikar samajik niyanthran karkanga rupudiddabadin korat aarthik vyavasthi.
urd: ol alzikar ek saarfi maishith hai jise paidavari salaahit ko badane ke liye tashkeel diya gaya hai, jabaki mokhir alzikar ek kisri maishith hai jise matalaq alaanaan samaji zaabte ke aamil ke tuur par tashkeel gaya hai.
eng: The former is a consumer economy designed to engender productivity, while the latter is a shortage economy designed as an agent of totalitarian social control.

ben: hindu vivah ine anusar, vivahanushthaner ek masser madhye bier nivandhikaran karaate have.

ben: prathamti poorve evan pratity manbantarer pare pratyekatite ekati krut-yug (satya yug) sah ekati manbantar-sandhya (sanyog yug) thake.
guj: pahelani agouna ane pachhina darek manwantar e manwantar-sandhya (sandhikal) che je dareconi lambaai krut-yug (sathyan-yug) jetali che.
hin: pratham or uske baad hone vaale prayek manwantar se pehle aati he manwantar-sandhya (jodne vaala antaraal), jisamen se prayek kii avadhi krit-yug (sat-yug) ke baraabar hoti he.
kan: modalaneyadakke poorvadalli mattu prati manvantarad nantar ondu manvantar sandhyeyiddu (sandhi kaal), prationder kalavadhiyu krithayugadashtide (satya yug).
mal: adyatte manvantaratin mumpu oro manvantaratin sheshvu oronninu oru kruthayugattiൻre (satyayugam) daiർghyamull oru manvantarasandhya (bandhippikkunn kalaghtea)und.
ori: prathamatir poorvaru eban pratyeka manntharar pare eka manntar-sandhya (yog avadhi) rahichhi, pratyekatir samay sima krith-yug (satya yug) pari.
pan: pichle ate harek manwantara ton bood manwantara-sandhya (lagau di miad) ounda hai, jise di lamai krit-yug (satyug) hundi hai I
tam: muthal manwandratingu munnatagaum ovvoru manwandratisqup pinkum woru manwandra sandhya (inikum kalam) irukkum, atu ovvonem woru kirit yugatin (saty yugam) kaal alavaik kontrukkum.
tel: toli manwantraniki mundu mariyu prati manvantaram taruvat ock manwantar sandhya (sandhi kalam) untundi, prati okati krit yugan (satya-yugan) ant nidivito.
urd: pahele kii pairvi kurta hawa or har manuntara ke aage aane waala manuntara manuntara-sandhy (rabt kii muddat) hai, har ek kii twalat krita yug( satya-yug) jitani hoti hai.
eng: Preceding the first and following each manvantara is a manvantara-sandhya (connection period), each with a length of Krita-yuga (Satya-yuga).

ben: anchalik vidyudwahi tarajali pratham aantansanyog sthapan kara has 1991-era october mase, yakhan uttar-poorv o purbanchalian vidyudwahi tarasaliguli aantansanyog karano has.

ben: bhartiya sankhya vyavsthati pashchathya vyavasthar dasher chaturth shakti hay shoonyer anurup: ek, dash, ekasho, ek hazar, evan dash hazar.
guj: bhartiya sankhyankan paddhati jharoth mateni pashchimi paddhatine dasna chotha gunank dwara anurup chheh ek, das, so, ek hajaar, ane das hajaar.
hin: bhartiya sankhya pranali pashchimi pranali se dahaai ke shoonyakoti se chauthe ghaat tak samaan hai: ek, das, sau, ek hazaar, or das hazaar.
kan: bhartiya sankhya paddhatiyu sonneind hattar ghat nalkarvarege pashchatya paddhatige anurupawagide: ondu, hattu, ondu nuru, ondu savir mattu hattu savir.
mal: pujyam mutൽ naluvarayull pattiൻre ghatasliൽ indiaൻ sankhyasampradayam pashchathyasampradayavumai samyapatunnund: one, pat, nur, aira, patinaira.
ori: bharatiya sankhya brivastha shoonya sankhya kshetrare, dashar chaturth ghat paryyant, pashchatya brivasthar anurup hoithaye: eka, dash, eka shah, eka hajaar, eban dash hajaar.
pan: bharati ank pranali kos di ghat char de madhium naal sifar de lai pattmi pranali naal mail khandi hai: ik, kos, ik sau, ik hajaar, ate kos hajaar|
tam: india en mures mengatya en mures pattin poojjia aduku muthal nankam aduku varai - adavatu ondu, battu, nooru, oeram, pattaram akhiyavauku - one vitmak ulsana.
tel: padi sunna nudi nalugav ghatankalku bharat ankaganit vyavasthi pashchatya vyavasthaku anugunanga untundi: okati, padi, vand, ock vayi, mariyu padi velu.
urd: hindustani adaadi nizaam safraveen se lay kar chothi das kii kaut tak mugharabi nizaam se karibi mamaslit rakhata hai: ek, das, ek so, ek hazaar, or das hazaar.
eng: The Indian numbering system corresponds to the Western system for the zeroth through the fourth powers of ten: one, ten, one hundred, one thousand, and ten thousand.

ben: pradhan filter capasitr sadharant kshater upar ye prakaar plastic film lagano thake tate morano thake, kaaran aguli kam kharche hai voltege vidyu pradaan kare evan hatto gale ya evan sav-nirama baishishtya sah banano.

kan: mukhyatantiy shodhak sanchayakagalu samanyavagi surali suttid plastic film madrigal hodikeyolagiruttve ekendare ivu kadime kharchinalli adhik vibhavantar nirdharanagalannu niduttve mattu ivannu tammind taave riperiaguvante hagu beseyaballante rachisabahudagide.
mal: kushanera chilviൽ uyർnn retingukൾ nalkunnatinal , svayn sharippetuttunnatu fyusiblu acamennatinal maiൻs phyൽreraർ kapacitirukൾ saadharan plastic philimiൻre avarana naൽkappet otukkiarupattilakiyatan.
ori: mukhya filtar kapasitargudik sadharanthati gudeihoi rahithiva plastic aavaranre samputit hoi rahithae karan egudik nimn dharare uchch bholtej haar pradaan karithaye eban egudiku s-upachaaraksham eban gajnaksham karayipare .
pan: mouth filter kapesters 'te aam for 'te plastic di parat charhi hundi hai, kiunki ih ait kimat te uch voltage pradaan karade han ate sajai-muranmat wale ate piglanshil ve banaye jaa sakde han |
tam: meins bilder kepacittars kuraint selavil adhik voltage rating valangum manllum tanak urugich sarishaydukollum vittil dayaaricappat mudi enpatal, are botwak surul plastic patlatinul amaindull vakaiych charndvayag irukkinsona.
tel: main filter kapasitar sadharannga plastic poralavanti vatito kappubadi untai, andukante ivi hechch voltes viluvalan takkuv dharku andistai mariyu vitini watantat avi baguchesukunela mariyu karigipoyela cheyavacchu.
urd: manz filter copisetar aam tuur par baandhi gayiplastic work kii ikssam main gulaaf band kiye jate hain is liye ki ye kam keemat main aali voltes ke madarj pesh karte hain or inhen khud drumani or galane ke laayak banaaya jasakta hai.
eng: Mains filter capacitors are usually encapsulated in wound plastic film types since these deliver high voltage ratings at a low cost and may be made self-healing and fusible.

ben: bi.es.i-r banisya kshetrati prasaarit kare die, 2001 evan 2002-e icuity derivativeguli sah es.and.pi bi.es.i sensex vikalpaguli unnayan saadhit has.
guj: 2001 ane 2002maa es.&pe bi.es.i. sensex vikalponi sathosath ikvity derivatives pan vikas thayo, jenathi bi.es.i.na trading plateformanu vistaran thayu.
hin: 2001 or 2002 main bi.es.i. ke vyapaar manch kaa vistaar karte hue hissedari sanjaton ke saath-saath es. and pi. bi.es.i. sensex vikalpon kaa vikaas hua.
kan: adkkanusarvagi, bi.es.i.y vyapaar vedikeyannu vistarisutta 2001 mattu 2002ralli equity vyutpannagal jotege es&pi bi.es.i. sensex aaykegal belvanigeyu modlayitu.
mal: atin pinnale bi. es. iyute vyapaar vedi vishalmakicond 2001lu 2002lu ikvity derivetivukalumai es & pi bi. es. i seൻsexille opshanulute viksana natannu.
ori: paravartti samaure, 2001 eban 2002 masihare, sadharan anshar butpannagulik samet, 'es. and pi. bi.es.i. sencex' bikalpagurikar srushti hoithila, yahaki 'bi.es.i.'r banijik kshetratiku samprasarit karithila .
pan: asa.and pi bombe stok ekschange sainsekas de vikalp di pragati nirpekhata derivatives de naal saal 2001 ate 2002 vich hoi, jise naal bombe stok ekschange da wapar manch ve bada hoia I
tam: itait doderndu 2001 manllum 2002il chambangu taruvippugaluton cherttu es&bhi piesi cencex vasadis uruvaki piesi-in vanikat talam virivatandatu.
tel: 2001 mariyu 2002lo utpannal vatatobat ass&pi biessi censex ampikal vruddhiki daari tisi, biessi vartak vedikani vistruta chassindi.
urd: isi ke peeche ecweti mushtqat ke saath es and pii bi es e sensex aapshanz kii tarakkee 2001 or 2002 main waaqa hui, jis ne bi es e ke tizaarati plate farm ko vasit di.
eng: The development of S&P BSE SENSEX options along with equity derivatives followed in 2001 and 2002, expanding the BSE's trading platform.

ben: dipstambh, krush evan ghore modhnike anusaran kara ekati rathke centra kare nirmit gowar tabloti dharmian sampreethi pradarshan kare.
guj: govani jhankhi dharmik ekaragita pradarshit kare che, jema dipastambh, cross ane ghode modani pachhi rath par dhyaan kendrit thai che.
hin: goa kii jhaanki dharmik sadbhaavna darshaati he jisamen dipastambh, cross or ghode modani par dhyanakarshan kiya gaya he or uske peeche rath he.
kan: dipastambh, shilube mattu ghode modniya hinde baruttiruv ondu rathdondige govaad stabdhachitravu dharmik samarasyavannu pradarshisuttade.
mal: dipastambhavu kurishu rath pintuterunn ghode modniyu kendramakicond matasamanvay aduttukattunntan goayute tablo.
ori: goar prajnapan mech deepastambha, karush eban eka viman dra anusrit 'ghode modni' upare dhyan kendrit kari dharmik samanyaku pradarshit karen .
pan: goa di jhaaki dipastamba, karass ate ghode modni ik rath 'te centerit dharmic iksurata nuun darsoundi hai|
tam: goavin oppanike katcil dipasthampam, silurai manllum kote motnee, adait doderndu woru rathmum eduppagak gattapadutan mulam atu math nallinakaddai welipadudhuatak amaindulldu.
tel: goa yokk chihn pradarshan, deep sthambha, shiluv, mariyu ock ratha vent wastenn ghode modni pai drushti centrikarinchi matparamin samarsyanni pradarshistondi.
urd: goa kaa tablo dipascumba, saleb, or ghode modani or is ke baad ek rath par tawaja merccoz karte hue majahabi hum aahangi ko dikhaata hai.
eng: The tableau of Goa showcases religious harmony by focusing on the Deepastambha, the Cross, and Ghode Modni followed by a chariot.

ben: 'dakshina ganga' name parichit godavari halo ganga pare dvitiya dirghatam evan dakshina bharter dirghatam nadee.
guj: godavari e ganga pachhini biji sauthi lambi che, ane ‘dakshin ganga’ tarike olkhati aa nadi dakshin bharat sauthi lambi nadi che.
hin: ganga ke baad godavari duusari sabase lambii he or dakshin bharat kii sabase lambii nadi he jise 'dakshin ganga' bhi kaha jaataa he.
kan: ganga nadiy nantar godavari eradne atidodda nadiyagide hagu adu dakshin bharatad atyant dodda nadi, adnn ʼdakshin gangaʼ antlu kareetare.
mal: ganga kavignal et nilemulla nadiyay godavari dakshinentyille et nilemulla nadia, atin dakshingang ennu perund.
ori: godabari heudi gangga pare dtiya deerghatam, eban dakshin bharatar sabuthu deergha nadi, yaha 'dakshin gangga' bhave parichit.
pan: godavari ganga ton bood dooji sabh ton lambi nadi hai ate ngkhani bharat di sabh ton lami nadi jo 'darshina ganga' de naame naal jaani jandi hai|
tam: gangaw aduttu, erandavatu mik nilman nadi godavari, itu tennindavin mik nilman nadi, its dakshin ganga appatinnum solwars.
tel: gang taruvat godavari rendav ati podevanadi, alage dakshinadilone atipodwan nadiga 'dakshin gang'ga kuda peru unnadi.
urd: ganga ke baad godavari doosaraa sab se tavel or janubi hindustan kaa sab se tavel dariya hai jise 'dakshina ganga' ke naam se bhi jaanaa jataa hai.
eng: Godavari is the second longest after Ganga, and the longest river in Southern India also known as 'Dakshina Ganga'.

ben: 22 na dhara upadhara (2) anuyayi, anumati pete chawa kono vyaktike sathik kartrupaksher kache likhit avedan karte have.
guj: kalam 22 ni peta-kalam (2) mujab manjuuri melvavaa maangti vyaktie saksham adhikarine lekhith araji karvi jaruri hoya che.
hin: khand 22 ke upkhand (2) ke anusaar, aavedak ko anumati paane ke liye sakasham praadhikari ko likhit main ek aavedan patr jamaa karnaa hoga.
kan: kalam 22r up-kalam (2)ralli anumati padeya bayasuv vyaktiyu saksham adhikarige likhitha arjianneu sallisabekendu vidhislagide.
mal: sekshൻ 22le sab-sekshൻ (2), anumati thedunn vyakti bandhappet adhikari rekhamulam oru apeksh naൽkanamenne vyavasthi cheiyunnu.

pan: sacshan 22 da sab sacshan (2) ih mangda hai ki jo banda samarath atharty nuun likh riha hai oh ijazat li ke likhe I
tam: anumati peni virumbhupower urya anyayatidam eduddupurvamak vinnapick wants endu brivu 22in duniprivu (2) goorukintu.
tel: sekshan 22 yokk sub-sekshan (2) prakara ock anumati pond kore vyakti samarthadhikarki likhitapoorvatkanga argini samarpinchukovata avasarparustundi.
urd: dafaa 22 kii zeli dafaa (2) mataliba krati hai ki wo shaks jo izzaazat haasil karne kii khwaahish rakhata hai use hakim majaaz ko tahariri tuur par ek darkhwaast deni chahiye.
eng: Sub-Section (2) of Section 22 requires the person desiring to obtain permission to make an application in writing to the Competent Authority.

ben: appler pracharak gai kawasaki brand nie ei gondamitic "hatha pawa konokichu" balle 2014-e aami vyakhya karechhilam ye appler panyer sang "avishwasya ek vyaktigat sampark royas manusher".
guj: apalana pravakta gay kavasakie brand matena jhanunne ‘kashunk evu jene thokar khavadavi che,’ kahi umeryu ke 2014maa men samajavyu hatu ke ‘loko apple utpadano sathe ekadam vyaktigat sambandh baandhi de che.’
hin: appal enjeelwaadi gaay kawasaki ne brands kattarta ko "aisa kuch jo bas sanyog se hua tha," bataate hue kaha ki 2014 main unhone bataaya tha ki appal utpaadon ke saath "logon kaa anokhaa vyaktigat sambandh he".
kan: brand bagegin huchchu abhimanvu "aksmattagi kandukondaddu" embudagi apple pracharak gai kavasaki heliddaradare, apple utpannagalondige "janaru nambalagadshtu garvad khasagi bandhavyavannu hondiddare" endu naanu 2014ralli vivarisidde.
mal: appyൾ uൽppannavlumai "alukൾk avishvasaniyamavidha vyaktiparmay oru bandhamanult" enne naൻ 2014ൽ vishadikarichirie, appyൾ suvisheshakൻ gay kavasaki braൻd bhrantin "yadruschikamai kitia one" enna visheshippicht.
ori: 'apal'r pracharak gaaya kasaki brandra andh samarthanaku kahiyanthi ye "epari kichhi yaha aaksmika bhavare dekhivaku missithila," yeteveleki mun 2014 masihare bujhaai kahichhi ye 'apal' jinishgudik sahit "lokamanankar eka avishsaniya bhave brekthigat sampark rahichhi" .
pan: apal de prachark gaai kawasaki ne brand di cuttdta baare kiha hai ki " kujh ajiha jo achaanak mile gya " jadon ki mai 2014 vich samjhaya see ki apal de utpads naal "locals da niji sabandh hai"|
tam: apple prachchar birangi guy kawasaki frant vellie "taesseyalagak khandakind ondu" endu azikibar, adevele naan ituparri 2014il villcumbodhu, apple dayarippugaluton "maluku oruvit apoorvamana maansik uddu ulldu" endu guinen.
tel: yapple suvisheshvakt gai kavasaki brand pat moorkhabhimananni "anukoni vidhnga erpadinadi" gaperconi, yapple utpattulato "prajalku atyant sannihith bandhavyam undi" ani 2014 lo nenu vivarinchanu.
urd: apple ke mublig gaai kavasaki ne brand ke junun ko "aisi cheez jo achanak dariyafat hojay" kaha hai, jab ki aaiyo ne2014 main vizahat kii thi ki apple kii misanuaat ke saath "avaam kaa ek hairat angez tuur par zaati taalluk hai."
eng: Apple evangelist Guy Kawasaki has called brand fanaticism "something that was stumbled upon," while I've explained in 2014 that "people have an incredibly personal relationship" with Apple's products.

ben: bharter manchitre ratnakhchit mukuter matan basano kashmir rutur sang sang taar rang paribartan kare - shite yakhan pahaar barfer carpete mora thake, takhan masrun dhaler upar ski kara ya o slej gaddi chale; basante o grishm madhur shishire dhaka bagan, tarangait hrad ei upatyakatique shwasaruddhakarabhave sunder kare tole.
guj: bharatna naksha par ratnajdit tajni jem shobhatu kashmir tena rang rituo sathe parivartit kare che - shiyalama, jayare parvato par barphani jajam patharay jaaya che, tyaan halwa dholavo par skiing ane slage safari thai che ane vasanth tatha unalama, madh jevaan jhakalwala udyano, laherta talavo khinne shwasa adhdhar kari de tevi sunder banaave che.
hin: bharat ke maanchitr par ratnajtit mukut kii tarah jadaa hua kashmir mausam ke saath apane rang badalata he – sheet ritu main, jab parvaton par him kii kaaleen bich jaati he, tab mand dhalaanon par ski karnaa or slage par sawari karnaa; vasant or greeshm main, madhuras se bhare falon ke bagan, laharon vaali jhilein is ghati ko asaadhaaran rup se khubasurat banaate hai.
kan: bharatad bhoopatdalli ratnakhchit kiritdanthiruv kashmirevu rituvige anusarvagi tann rangannu badalisuttade - chaligaldalli, parvatgalu himavrutwadag, alli nasuvoregal mele ski madebahudu mattu slez gadialli hogabahudu; vasant hagu besageya kalagamalli, jenumanjinind toyd hannin totgalu mattu kiruderegaleluv sarovargalu i kaniveyannu berginind usiru hidiuvantaguvashtu manoharvagisuttve.
mal: indyayute bhupatattiൽ ratnam patichch oru kirit polairikunn kashmiർ rutukkൾkkanusrich nirum marunnu - shaityakalat pർvatangൾkkumeൽ mannuparavatanikൾ viricappetukayu ilancherivukaliൽ skiing sledge ridiagumundakukayu cheyu; vasantakalattu venൽkkalattu teൻ tullikൾ kiniunn panttottesu olam wettunn tatakanglu tajvaraye vismayakaramavidha manoharmakkukyu cheyu.
ori: bharatar manachitre eka ratnanchit mukut pari rahithiva kashmir ritu sahit nij rang badalithaye - sheeta kalre yeve baraf pahaad upare galichaa pari bichhei hoiyaaye, tahar mrudu gadani upare skiing eban slej riding anusthit hoithaye; basant o greeshma kalre, madhusikta fatvagichaman o tarangait hrad upatkkatiku akalpaniya bhave ramanti karithaye.
pan: jive bharat de nakshe ute kashmir ik johar taj wang sajia hoya hai oda hi oh mousam anusaar aapne ranga badalda hai , jadon paharia te baraf di ik chaadar bich jandi hai , othe kolan te sking ate saledaj safari hundi hai; basant te garamia vich bageeche, chal-chal kardi jhils jo ish vaadee nuun hor ve khubasurat banaunde han I
tam: india varaipattil mani paditt makudam pol viveerukkum kashmiri, paruv kalangaluku aup tan vannach chayaless marikkolkintu - kulir kalatil compalam pol malakalap bani portyl podhu malacharivukalil banicharuku vilyates banicharuku vandies kanalam; vachand manllum kodai kalankalil denbanit tuli patarnt palathotasum chicirolai ariesum sutt indep balladakhil manatike kollakollum evillaku domarikkolkintu.
tel: bharatvaesh pax pai ratna kiritmla amrchi unn kashmir kalalato dani rangulu marchukuntundi, shitakalamlo kondalapine manchu tivachis kappinpp, skiing mariyu sledge pine swari, vasantakalamlo mariyu vesavilo tene-manchu pands totel, all sarassulu i lowen adbhut andangal daniga chestai.
urd: hindustan ke nakshe par taj kii tarah arasta kashmir apne rang mausamon ke saath badalataa hai - sardiyon main , jab pahaadon par barf kii chadar bich jaati hai tab naram dhalawaanon ke saath saath skiing or salej par sawari kii jaati hai. mausam bihar or mausam garma main, shahad kii shabnam waale bagat, laharaati jhelen vaadee ko hairat angez tuur par haseen banaditi hain.
eng: Set like a jeweled crown on the map of India, Kashmir changes its hues with seasons - in winter, when snow carpets the mountains, there is skiing and sledge riding along the gentle slopes; in spring and summer, the honey-dewed orchards, rippling lakes make the valley breathtakingly beautiful.

ben: ekati hal apushti, ya madhye royas barer vruddhi hras (badus andaje kam uchchata), kshaya (uchchata andaje kam ozon), ojner swalpata (badus andaje kam ojan) evan microneutryenter ghatti baa apratulata (jaruri vitamin o mineraler abhav).
guj: ek che kuposhan, jema vamanta (umarna pramanma ochhi unchai), nirbalata (unchaina pramanma ochhu vajan), ochhu vajan (umarna pramanma ochhu vajan) ane sukshma poshakatattvoni unap ke apoornata (agatyana vitamin ke khanijatattvoni unap)no samavesh thai che.
hin: unamem se ek he alpaposhan, jisamen shaamil he vriddhirodh (umr ke anusaar kam lambaai), kshinak-rog (lambaai ke anusaar kam vazan), ati kshinkaay (umr ke anusaar kam vazan) or sookshm poshak tatv kii kami yaa aparyaaptta (mahatvapurn vitaminon or khanijon kii kami).
kan: adralli ondu kadime paushtikateyagiddu, adu kunthit belvanige (vayassige takkshtu ettaravilldiruvudu), kshinisuvike (ettarakke takkante tookavilldiruvudu), kadime took (vayassige takkshtu tookavilldiruvudu) mattu sukshma poshkansh korategalu athwa newntegamannu (mukhyavad jeevasattvaglu mattu khanijagal abhav) olagondide.
mal: valർchchamurtip (prayattinott uyaramillaym), melichiൽ (uyarattinott tukkamillaym), tukkakute (prayattinott tukkamillaym), sukshmaposhakaute kuaawo aparyaptatyo (pradhanpat jivakeutayu dhatukalutayu kull) ennivyuൾkkollunn poshakakkurvan one.
ori: gotie heudi apapushti, yaha madhyare briddhirodh (badus anusaare kam uchchatha), sharirkshan (uchchatha anusaare kam ojan), slpabhar (badus anusaare kam ojan) eban sukshma poshak abhab kimba ayatheshtatha (guruthpurna vitamin eban dhatusarar abhab) antarbhukt .
pan: ik hai kuposhan, jise vich stting (umar ton ait unchaai), barbaadi (unchaai lai ait bhaar), ate micronuterent kamia jaaa ashudhia (mahatavpuuran vitamin ate khanijan di ghat) shaamil han|
tam: ondu uttak kurai, itel valarchic gundudal (vayatap boruttu kuraivana uyaram), ilaittal (uyarattap boruttu kuraivana edai), edeke kurai (vayatap boruttu kuraivana edai), nunnuttach chattauk kuraibadu alltu paxakurai (mukhiaman vitamins manllum tadukas kuraivak iruppatu) akhiyawe atankum.
tel: okati poshkahar lopa, dinilo gitakabarea (vayasuku tagg attu lekapovada), balahin padata (attuku tagg baru lekapovada), takkuv baru undla (vayasuku tagg baru lekapovada) mariyu sukshmaposhak lopal leda korats (mukhyamin vitamins mariyu khanijal korat) vantivi untai.
urd: ek gazaait kii kamee hai, jis main stanting (umr ke liye kam onchaai), zaafa (kad ke lihaaz se kam vajan), ausat se kam vajan (umr ke lihaaz se kam vajan) or micro gazaai izza kii kamee yaa marz kulat (ahim vitamin or madaniyat kii kamee) shamil hain.
eng: One is undernutrition, which includes stunting (low height for age), wasting (low weight for height), underweight (low weight for age) and micronutrient deficiencies or insufficiencies (a lack of important vitamins and minerals).

ben: 2003-era vattel pariwesh moolayan vyavastha (bidies)-r dwara krut bangalorer bhaut, jaivik evan aarth-samajik manadandguli ekati moolayan nirdesh kare ye, bangalorer jaler gunaman evan sthalaj o jalaj bastutantraguli adarsher kachakachi also shahrer arthsamajik mapadandguli (yaan chalachal, jivaner gunaman), bayur gunaman evan shabd dushan kshatikar paryay chhil.
guj: 2003na betel anvayarmental eveluation systems (bi.i.i.es.)na benglorna bhautik, jaivik ane samazik-aarthik mapedandona tulanatmak abhyase suchavyu ke benglorni paanini gunavatta ane jameen tatha paninu paristhithek tantra adarshani najik hatu, jayaare shaherna samazik-aarthik mapedando (vahanvyavahaar, jeevanani gunavatta) havani gunavatta ane dhwani pradushan nabala hata.
hin: 2003 kii battle paryaavaran moolyankan pranali (bes) dwaara shahar ke bhautik, jaivik or saamaajik aarthik maapdandon ke moolyankan ke anusaar, bangalore kii pani kii gunvattta or sthaliy or jaleey paristhitiki tantra lagbhag adarsh the, jabaki, shahar ke saamaajik-aarthik maapdand (yatayaat, jivan kii gunvattta), vaayu gunvattta or dhwani pradooshan nimna str ke the.
kan: bontel envairanmental evalyuyeshan systemmin (bi.i.i.es.) bangalorin bhautik, jaivik mattu samajoarthik pramitigal 2003r maulyamapanvu, bangalorin nirin gunamatt mattu bhoomiy hagu nirin parisar vyavasthegalu aadarshapraia ennuvudakke hattiradalliveyadare, nagarad samajoarthik pramitigalu (vahan dattane, jeevanad gunamatt, gaaliya gunamatt mattu shabd malinya) kavpeyagive endu suchisittu.
mal: bangaloreiൻre jalagunnilvaravu bham, jal avasvyavasthakalu uttamnilvarattottuttirie, nagarattiൻre samuhiksampattikaitakalu (vahanatirk, jivita gunnilvar) vayumalinikaranvu shabdamalinikaranvu moshmanena bangaloreiൻre bhatikavu jivashastraparavu samuhik sampattikavumay ghankangute beteraൽ eൻviroൺmeൻraൽ ivalweshൻ siste(bi. i. i. es)ttiൻre 2003le oru vilyiruttൽ suchippicht.
ori: bangalorer prakritik, jaivik o samajik-aarthik mapadandgudik vishakere 2003 re 'betel enabhironamental ibhaluason sishtam' dra anusthit eka moolayanaru suchana missila ye bangalorer jal gunavathta eban sthalbhag o jaladhar parisanstha pakhapakhi aadarshamanar, matra saharar samajik-arthanitik mapadand (yanavahan chalachal, jeevanadharanr man), baur gunavathta eban shabda pradushan nimnamanar.
pan: 2003 de ik bitle watavarna mulankan pranali de mulankan ne sanket ditha ki bangalooru de bhautik, jeev-vigyanak ate samajik-arthic mapadand, bangalooru de paani di guntata ate dharati ate jal-pariavarna pranali adarsha de nede san, jadon ki shahir de samajik-arthic mapadand (trephic, jeewan di guntata) hawa di guntata ate shor pradushn mada see|
tam: 2003 battel sudduchural madipittu murai (piikees) mulam bangaloreen bhautik, uerial manllum samukap poruladhar alvukols madipidu seyyappatt podhu, bangaloreen nirth dharamum nilamsarnt manllum nirsarnt uirval sunal mandalangalum aittang micub poruttamak irukkinsona enllum, adevele ant manakrutin samukap poruladhar alvukols (bhokuvarattu nerichal, vatakkait dharam), kallerin dharam, oly mashubhadu akhiyawe moseman niliil ulsana enllum atu kufippittatu.
tel: bengalooru bhautik, jeeva, samajik aarthik paramitul taluku 2003 batelle anviranmental awalyuyesion system (biiies) moolyankna bengalooru loni niti nanyath, bhu mariyu jal jivavaran vyavasthal abhileniya viluvaku daggarga undga, naggar samajikarthik paramitulu (traphic, jivan nanyath) vayu nanyath mariyu shabda kalushya pelvanga unnayani suchinchindi.
urd: bangalore ke tabiyaai, hayatiyati or samaji maashiyati parometriz ke betal anweranmental evalyotion system (bi e e es) ke 2003 ke jaaize se patta chalata hai ki bangalore ke pani kaa mayar or jamini or aabi maahulyati nizaam misali ke qareeb the, jabaki shahar ke samaji maashiyati parametaz (traific, mayar zindagi) hawa or soti aaludagi ke mayar naaqs the.
eng: A 2003 Battelle Environmental Evaluation System (BEES) evaluation of Bangalore's physical, biological and socioeconomic parameters indicated that Bangalore's water quality and terrestrial and aquatic ecosystems were close to ideal, while the city's socioeconomic parameters (traffic, quality of life) air quality and noise pollution were poor.

ben: 28 na dhara bale ye, ekati gramka yakhan yuddher madhyam dakhle aana has takhano kohn daler dwara luptarajer anumati thake na.
guj: kalam 28 evu janave che ke bhale ek gaam yuddh dwara kabaje karayu hoya, koi pan paksha dwara luntphat karvaani manjuuri nathi.
hin: anuchhed 28 main kaha gaya he ki yuddh ke dauraan kisi gaanv par kabja karne ke baad bhi kisi bhi paksh ko lut-maar karne kii anumati nahin he.
kan: 28nae vidhiyu ondu habaliannu yuddhad moolak vashapadisicondagalu sah, yavude banakku luty madlu avkashvillvendu heluttade.
mal: yudhttil oru grama pitichetucpettaltane arunjattunn kollayu anuvadaniyamalle artikle 28 prastavikkunnu.
ori: dhara 28 kahuchhi ye epariki yetevela yuddh dra eka gramku adhikrit karayaaye, kaunsi paksha dra lutpat nimanthe anumati naahin .
pan: artical 28 vich kiha gya hai ki jadon ve yuddha vich kise pind te kabaza kitha janda hai, kise ve party duara us nuun latan di ijazat nahi hai|
tam: woru gramam foril capparopatalum endhat trupinerum adaich suryaduadil itupatakudadhu endu vidhi 28 goorukintu.
tel: yuddha dwara ock gram swadhinaparuchukobadina kuda, ye pakshamuchet kuda dopidi anumatinchabandu ani nibandhan 28 teliajestunnadi.
urd: dafaa 28 main kaha gaya hai ki jab jang ke zarie kisi gaauun par kabja kiralia jaaye tab bhi kisi bhi friq ko luut mar kii izzaazat naheen hai.
eng: Article 28 states that even when a village is captured through war, pillaging is not allowed by any party.

ben: 1967-r rajya vidhansbha nirvachane sabkati samajatantrik dal baad pade ya, evan sipiai virodhi daler maryaada hara.
guj: 1967ni rajya vidhansabha chuntanima tamam samajavadi paksho baakat thayan hatan ane sii.pe.ai. e teno virodh pakshano darajjo gumaavyo hato.
hin: 1967 ke rajya vidhansabha chunaavon main sabhi samaajawaadee partiyon kaa safaya kar diya gaya, or si.pi.ai. vipakshi dal hone kii haisiyat kho baithi.

mal: 1967le sansthan niyamsabha teranjeetupiൽ ella soshyalist paർttikalu ochivacpetukayu si. pi. aik pratipakshppaർti padvi nashtamavukyu cheitu.

pan: 1967 di raj vidhan sabha de chunaav vich tub samajavaadi parties nikal gaia san ate si.pi.i ne apni virodhi party da darja gua ditaa I
tam: 1967 maanil sattasabait terdalkalil anatu soshalich cutchiksum baduolvi adaindana, sipis ethirkatsi andast iandatu.
tel: 1967 rashtra shasansabh annikallo, anni sanghikavad parties tolgimpbaddai, sipiai dani vipaksh party hodan colpoindi.
urd: 1967 ke riyasati asambali intakhaabat main, tamaam socialist partiyon ko khatm kar diya gaya, or si pii aai ne aposeshan party kaa darja kho diya.
eng: In the 1967 state assembly elections, all socialist parties were eliminated, and the CPI lost opposition party status.

ben: parasttalguli besarkarikaran, krushi bipanan parishanguli dravibhavan, bideshi binioger pakshapati adhik mukta binioger anumodan, banking shilper besarkarikaran, aitihyagat, pradhan panya raptani baichitrya, evan khadya upadne adhik binioger saakshi thekese 1980-paravarty ratsirac evan japhir shasanguli.
guj: ratsiraka ane jhaphina 1980 pachhina samaygalae nigamonu khangikaran, khetbazar smitiona visarjan, videshi rokanani tarfen kartaan vadhu mukt rokan niyamoma sudhara, banking udyognu khangikaran, paramparik ane mul utpadanoni nikasa vishakhan ane khadya utpadanma bahola rokanu vihangavalokan karyu.
hin: ardh-sarkari sanghathanon kaa nijeekaran, krushik vipanan samitiyayon kaa vilyan, videshi niveshon kaa samarthan karne vaale adhik udaar nivesh kodon kaa anumodan, banking kshetra kaa nijeekaran, paaramparik, praathmik-utpaada aaayaaton kaa vividhikaran, tathaa khaadya utpaadan main bade hue nivesh 1980 ke baad ke ratsiraakaa or zaafi shasno ke antargat kiye gaye hai.
kan: 1980r nantar ratsiraka mattu jaffi aalvikegalu parastatelgal khaasagikaran, krishi marukatte mandaligal visarjane, videshi hoodikege poorakavad innashtu udari hoodike nitigainnu oorjitgolisuvike, banking udyamd khaasagikaran, sampradayik hagu praiamik-utpann raftugal bandwal vitarne, mattu aahar utpadaneyalli hchin hoodikeya melvicharaneyannu nodicondive.
mal: 1980 nusheshmulla ratsirak, safy bharanakutes 'parastaytalu'kal swakaryavatkariunnatinu, karshikavipanan bordu pirichuvidunnatinu, videshnikshepate anukulikunn kututal udarmay nikshepachttes sadhuvakunnatinu, banking vyavasayam swakaryavൽkkarikunnatinu sampradayikamay prathamikavibhavaute kayatumati vaividhyavatkariunnatinu, bhakshyotpadanttil kututal valia nikshapattinu melnotte vahichittund.
ori: 1980 paravartti 'ratsiraka' eban 'jafi' shasan 'parashtetal'gudikar gharoikaran, krushibhittik marketing bordgujaikar bighatan, vaideshik niveshaku suhauthiva pari adhik udar nivesh samhita, banking udogar gharoikaran, paramparik , maulik-dravya raptanir vibidhikaran, eban khadya utpadhanare adhik niveshaku parylevekshan kariasichhi .
pan: 1980 ton bood ratsirka ate jafi shasana ne parastatls de nijikaran, khetibari marketing bords nuun bhang karan, videshi nivesh de pakh vich vadhere udar nivesh kodas di pravaanagi, bakking udayog da nijikaran, ravaiti, primary utpad di vibhinnata di nigrani, niryat ate bhojan utpadan vich vadhere nivesh kita hai|
tam: 1980kqup bindaiy ratchiraka manllum jafi atchikhalin podhu arasu dodarpana niruvananglait taniarmayamacuthal, whilan chandaippadutal variangalack kalaittal, anniya mudaliddukkuch sadakaman koodudal tarayamay mudalittuch sattavidis oorjitpadutal, vangit turaiys taniarmayamacuthal, bharambariya mudanmait dayaripugalin ettrumatiil pal brivugalaich cherthal, unwud dayariple mudalitte adhikarittal akhiyawe arasu adraton nadanderina.
tel: 1980 taruvati ratshirak mariyu japhy hayanx paroksh palkul praivetikarannu, vyavasay marketing boardul radducheyadanni, videshi pettubadulku anuvuga viriviga pettubadi vidhan dhruvikrinchadanni, banking rang praivetikarannu, sampraday pradhan utpatti agumtul vidhikarannu, mariyu ahara utpattilo marint hechch pettubadini paryavekshinchai.
urd: 1980 ke baad kii ratsiraka or zafee hukuumaton ne baaqtdar sanati tanzemon kii nij kari, zardi bazar kari tanzemon ko tahalil karne, gair milki saramy kari kii hamayat karne waale zyaada labral saramy kari zaabato kii tosiq, bankaree sanaat kii nij kari, ravayati, buniyadi misanuaat kii baramdaat main tanua or gazaai paidavar main zyaada badi saramy kari kii nigranee kii.
eng: The post-1980 Ratsiraka and Zafy regimes have overseen the privatization of parastatals, the disbanding of agricultural marketing boards, the ratification of more liberal investment codes favoring foreign investment, the privatization of the banking industry, the diversification of traditional, primary-product exports, and greater investment in food production.

ben: ei rutugatbhave baishishtyasuchak sampradaguli bivinn jivan gaian royas, ya tader jalbayur rutuvichitrya dwara pradhanath wapamatra o vrushtipater harer kshetre vapkbhave prabhavit has.
guj: aa mosemi vishisht samudaayo vaividhyapurna jeevasrushti dharave che, je teni abohvana mosamipanathi, khas karine wapamana ane varsaadna darathi khub prabhavit thai che.
hin: ye mausami taur par vishisht samoohon ke vividh jeev hai jo kaaphi zyada jalwaayu ke mausam tatv se prabhavit hote hai, vishesh rup se taapmaana or varsha kii maatra se.
kan: aaya rituvige takkantiruv i visishtvad samudayagalu vaividhyamay jeevarupagainnu hondiddu, avu avugal havamanad rituvige anugunavagiruvikeind, mukhyavagi wapamana hagu avakshepan dargalind mahattaravagi prabhavitvaguttave.
mal: avayute kalavasthaute rutukrama, pradhanmayu tapanilyu marryute totu, karyamai badhikkunn vaividhyamaർnn jeevajalanoൾ kalavasthaparamai savisheshatakalulla i samuteslilund.
ori: ehi ritugat bhavare stantra samoohaguthikare bhinna bhinna prakaarar jeeva rup rahithae yeungudikaki segurikar jalbaur ritukalinatha dra, mukhitah wapamatra eban bristipat haar dra, vishesh bhave prabhavita hoithaye .
pan: ih mousam mutabik alag samajik samooha de vividh roop han jinhan da mousam de badalan naal, ziadatar wapamana te barish de dar kaaran, bohut prabhav penda hai I
tam: indep paruvakalam-charnt pratyek inanglul palverupatt uirin vativas ulsana, are dam chitoshnap paruvakalatinal, kurippak veppanil manllum manipobivu vikithankalal, mikunth dakkaduku aalakinchuna.
tel: i kalangun vilakshanmain jatulas vat vatavaran paristhitulu valan, mukhyanga ushnograth mariyu avakshepan nishpattulu valan hechchuga prabhavitamaye vibhinn jeevaroopas unnai.
urd: mausami lihaaz se khasusiyat rakhane wali in birdariyon kii zindagayon kii mukhtalf shaklen hoti hain jo apni aab va hawa or mausami mutabikt balkhsus darja hararat or barindagi kii shrah se bahut zyaada mutasar hote hain.
eng: These seasonally distinctive communities have diverse life forms that are greatly impacted by the seasonality of their climate, mainly temperature and precipitation rates.

ben: pallabder nirmaner prachintam udaharan halo 610 christpurbabd thek 690 christpurvabder samarkar pathar ket banano mandir evan 690 christpurbabd evan 900 christpurvabder madhye banano kathamogat mandir.
guj: pallava bandhkam shailina sauthi joona namuna i.sa.purve 610thi i.sa.purve 690 jetla joona ane malkhakiya bandhkamwala mandiro i.sa.purve 690thi i.sa.purve 900 vachchena patharmathi kotrela mandiro che.
hin: pallav nirmaan ke pracheenatam udhaaharan hai chattan kaat kar banaae gaye mandir jo 610 isvi se lekar 690 isvi ke bich banaae gaye the or sanrachanagat mandir jo 690 isvi se lekar 900 isvi ke bich banaae gaye.
kan: sa.sha. 610rind sa.sha. 690r varegin avadhiya guhantar devalayasgalu mattu sa.sha. 690 hagu sa.sha. 900r naduvin avadhige serid rachanik devsthanagalu pallav nirmitigal praachintam nidarshanagalagive.
mal: 610 si. i mutൽ 690 si. i varayull kalatte kalliൽ kottiyetutt kshetraslu, tunukalu uttaralumulla kshetraslu pallavaniർmmitikaute et adyatte udaharanjasa.
ori: pallab sthapatir prachinatam udaharangudik hela 610 christabdharu 690 christabd samafer shail-khodith mandirman eban 690 christabdharu 900 christabd samafer gajahoithiva mandirman .
pan: palwa imarats de nirman de sabh ton agete udaharan pammer ton katte hoe mandir han jo 610 ton 690 isavi de han ate dhanchagat mandir jo 690 ate 900 isavi de vich bane san I
tam: pallavar kddumanangalin micub packmaiyana edutoukgaddugalak vihangubhavai, kibe 610 muthal kibe 690 varilan kaalakttin kudaivarike koilsum kibe 690 muthal kibe 900 varilan ghatamibbook koilsum akum.
tel: pallavas kattadal tott toli udaharani kri. sh. 610 nudi 690 varaku nati raatini chekki nirminchabadin alayas, mariyu kri. sh. 690 mariyu 900 madhya nati nirmanatmak alayas.
urd: pallav kii tamir kii ibtidai misaaleen 610 isvi se 690 isvi tak taraashe gaye chataani mandir or 690 isvi or 900 isvi ke darmiyaan tamir kiye gaye sakhti mandir hain.
eng: The earliest examples of Pallava constructions are rock-cut temples dating from 610 CE to 690 CE and structural temples between 690 CE and 900 CE.

urd: sab se ahim baat, hum naheen jaante ki kab or kaise museebat hamare daravaazon par dastak de gi.
eng: Most importantly, we don't know when and how misfortune knocks at our doors.

ben: 2021-era mahila ragabi vishwakaper navam sanskarnti purvaparikalpit 18i september thek 18i octoberer samaysuchi thek pichie 8i october thek 12i november 2022-e neujiland anushtit has.
guj: 2021no rugby vishv cap, navamo mahila rugby vishv cap newthilandma 8 october ane 12 november 2022 vachche yojayo hato, je pahelam nirdharit 18 septemberthi 18 october, 2021 vachche ayojit thanar hato pan mulathvi rahyo hato.
hin: 2021 rugby vishwa cap, mahila rugby vishwa cap kaa nauvaan sanskaran, 18 sitambar se 18 oktober 2021 kii apane mul rup se nirdhaarit kaarykram se multavee kar ke 8 oktober se 12 november 2022 ke bich newjiland main yojit kiya gaya.
kan: mahila ragby vishv kapn ombhattane aavruttiyad 2021 ragby vishv kapannu, modalalli nigadiyagidd 2021r ceptembar 18rind october 18r varegin velapattianneu mundudalagi, 2022r october 8 mattu navembar 12r naduve newjilandnalli nadeslayitu.
mal: adyam 2021 septembർ 18 mutൽ octobeർ 18varayull samayakramatiൽ natattaൻ thirumaniachirunn ompatan vanitha rugby lokakapaya 2021 rugby lokakap, 2022 octobeർ 8nu novembർ 12nu idilai nusilaൻdeൽ wech natannu.
ori: mahila ragvi vish kapra navam sanskaran, '2021 ragvi vish cup', 8 octoberaru 12 november 2022 madhyare newjiland thare hoithila, yahakuki mooru present hoithiva 18 septemberru 18 october 2021r karyannirghant tharu ghurchai diayaithila .
pan: 2021 ragbi vishwa cup, mahila ragbi vishwa cup da nauvaan sanskarna, newzealand vich 8 october ate 12 november 2022 de wichkaar yojit kita gya see, ih18 satmber ton 18 october 2021 de mul yojnabedh kargekram ton mulatavi kar ditha gya see.
tam: onpadavatu pengal rugby ulagak goppayana 2021 rugby ulagak goppai niushilandil 8 october muthal 12 november 2022 varai natabbebantu, asalil 18 september muthal 18 october 2021 varai natabenut ditamitapattrunth atu mergant datiluku otivicoppattatu.
tel: 2021 rugby world kap, mahill tommidav aavartan rugby world kap neusilandso, modat 2021 september 18 nudi 18 october varaku niriinchin karyakram pranalikaku baduluga, 2022 october 8 mariyu november 12 madhyan jarigindi.
urd: 2021 rugby world cap, khwatin ke rugby world cap kaa nawan edeshan, 8 aktubar or 12 navamber 2022 ke darmiyaan newzi land main manakad hawa, jise 18 sitambar se 18 aktubar 2021 ke asal mansuba band shadooll se mokhir kridya gaya tha.
eng: The 2021 Rugby World Cup, the ninth edition of the women's Rugby World Cup, was held in New Zealand between 8 October and 12 November 2022, postponed from the originally planned schedule of 18 September to 18 October 2021.

ben: han, itimadhyei aami amar passporter baidhata dekhe niechi, aar aapnar ekuni bala sharter sang ta manansi.

eng: Yes, I already checked my passport validity, and it complies with what you just said.

ben: ekati purna-dairghyer nirvak chalachchitra tiri karte, pariwarer jamidari bagan ekati asthayi studio nirman kara has, evan 1931 sale muktiprapth dya last kis name ekati purna-dairghyer nirvak chalachchitra prayojna karen tanra.
guj: ek puree lambaaii mungi film banaavavaa mate parivarani milkatana bagichama ek kamchalau studio ubho karaayo hato, ane temane ek puree lambaaii ‘dha last kise’ namani mungi filmanu nirman karyu hatu, je 1931maa raju thai hati.
hin: ek puri avadhi kii mook film banane ke liye, parivaar kii jameen ke bageeche main ek asthaayee studio taiyaar kiya gaya or da last kis naam kii ek purna avadhi kii mook film kaa nirmaan kiya gaya jise 1931 main pradarshit kiya gaya.
kan: purna-pramand mookie chitravondannu madlu kutumbad totd udhayandalli ondu tatkalik studiovannu nirmislayitu, mattu avaru ʼda last kisʼ emb purna-pramand mookie chitravondannu taarisi, adu 1931ralli bidugadeyayitu.
mal: avar oru mughunilanishshabdachitram nirmmikanai kutubatine astateile puntottattil oru talcalik studio nirmmikukayu 'di last kis' enne peray, 1931l purattikania oru mughunilanishshabdachitram nirmmikukayu cheitu.
ori: eka purnavapub nihshabd-chakchchitra nirman pin parivarika jamire thiva bagichaare eka asthani studio thiari karagala, eban semane eka purnavapub nihshabd-chakchchitra nirman kale, yaahaar shirshak thila, di last kis, yaha 1931 masihare mukthilabh karithila.
pan: puri lambai vaali shant film banaun lai, films astate de bagicha vich ik asthai studio banavaia gya see, ate uhanaas duara ik puri lambi shant film da nirman kita gya jo ki 1931 vich da last kise sirlekh heth relis hoi|
tam: woru mulunil maunab pattai edukk, kudumbh estate dottatil woru taiakalik studio uruvalxpattu, thi last kis enjh ant mulunil maunab pattai avarkas dayarittaner, atu 1931il velitepattatu.
tel: ock phurti nidivigal muki chitranni nirminchenduku, aa kutumbaniki chendin bhupradeshloni totlas ock tatkalik studion tayaruchesi, vaaru di last kis peruto phurti nidivigal ock muki chitranni nirminchi, 1931 lo vidudal cheshar.
urd: puri twalat wali khamosh film banane ke liye, khandaan kii jaagir ke bagat main ek aarzi eastudio banaaya gaya tha, or unhon ne 1931 main reliz hone wali di last kis ke naam se ek mukammal twalat wali khamosh film taiyaar kii thi.
eng: To make a full-length silent film, a temporary studio was made in the gardens of the family's estate, and they produced a full-length silent film titled The Last Kiss, released in 1931.

ben: august 2006-e uttarer gricetio aantansamyukta has, yar fale ekasang samyukta evan ek companke kaaj kara ekati centrian grid rupayit has.
guj: august 2006maa uttariya jal pan ekabija sathe jodvama aavi hati, tenathi ekasathe jodayeli ane ek ja aavritti par kaarya karti ek kendriya jalnu nirman thayu.
hin: agast 2006 main uttari grid ko bhi antaryojit kiya gaya jisase kendriya grid bana jo tulykaalik rup se joda gaya or ek hi aavriti par sanchaalan karata he.
kan: 2006r augustnalli uttarad gridannu sah ivugalondige samparkisi, samakalikavagi samparkitwagiruv mattu onde aavarthandalli kaareniratvagiruv kendra grid ondannu rachislayitu.
mal: siൻkranas aai bandhicppettu one frikvൻsiiൽ pravർttikunnatumay oru kendra grid rupappetuticond 2006 augustyൽ watnakൻ grid kootiyu paraspar bandhitmai.
ori: uttar greeceti madhya, agast 2006re, parasper-sanyukt hoi eka kendriya greed srushti karithila yahaki ekakalin bhavare gotie aabrittire sanyukt eban karyankaari hoithila .
pan: uttari grid ve agast 2006 vich aapas vich jud gai, jise naal cendari grid naal hi judi hoi hai ate ik warvarta te chaladi hai I
tam: 2006 afstle watakku min ghatamipum itsuton inaikkhapattu woru maiya min ghatamifu uruvaki, atu otisivak inaikkhapattu one adhirvanill iangiadu.
tel: 2006 agashtulo uttar gridn kuda anusandhaninchi ock central gridn erpat chesar, adi samakalikanga anusandhaninchabadi, ock paunahpunyamlo panichesedi.
urd: shumali grid ko bhi agast 2006 main baham joda gaya tha, jis se ek central grid tashkeel paaya jo hum vakt marabot tha or ek hi fracuency par kaam kar raha tha.
eng: The Northern grid was also interconnected in August 2006, forming a Central Grid that was synchronously connected and operating at one frequency.

ben: parmanvik bidarner janya parmanvik vidyu centragulite uraniamke has prakritik bhave baa samrudh avastha sadharant jvalani hiseve vyabhhar kara has.
guj: yurenium, kudarti athva samrudh swarupama, samanya rite parmaanu vij mathakma parmaanu vibhajan mate upayogma levaya che.
hin: prakritik yaa sanvardhit uranium kaa prayog aamtaur par nabhikeey vidyut sanyantron main nabhikeey vikhandan ke liye eendhan ke rup main kiya jaataa he.
kan: samanyavagi uraniummannu, ader naisargik athwa sanvardhit rupadalli, parmaanu vidyut sthavragamalli baijik vidalnakke indhanavagi baislaguttade.
mal: naisarggikamo sampushtmo ay yuranium anuvaidyutanilayas neukliar fishan vende indhanmai saadharan upyogiunnu.
ori: uraniam, ubhay prakritik o samrudh rupare, anbik shakti utpadan kendrare anbik bighatan nimanthe praiathanga indhan bhave brebahrut hoithaye.
pan: urenium jaaa taan kudrati jaaa sanshodhit roop vich, aan for 'te pramanu vikhanden lai pramanu power plats vich balan vajon vartia janda hai|
tam: iyaskayana alltu sevivuoppatt vatiwil ull yurenium, anukkarup pilukkan anushakti ulkalil botwak eriporulagab payanbaduttapadukintu.
tel: sadharannga anu vicchitti kos yureniam sahaj leda susampann rupao anu vidyut plantslo indhananga vadtar.
urd: uranium, kudrati yaa afazoda shukla main, aam tuur par johri anshkak ke liye johri bijli gharon main eendhan ke tuur par istemaal kiya jataa hai.
eng: Uranium, either in natural or enriched form, is commonly used as fuel in nuclear power plants for nuclear fission.

guj: bhartiya nagarik ke nivasi mateni fee packege ne aadhare roo. 200 ke 300 che.
hin: bhartiya nagarikon or rahavaasiyon ke liye package ke aadhaar par 200 yaa 300 rupee fis hogi.

ben: 1960 sale, yave thek adhyayan vishyak course aarmbh hayes, ei pratishthan niyamitbhave shikshapaddhati o suchi unnati, chalachchitrer baishishtyukt shikshar gunamanke samrudh kara evan satyikarer shreshitber centra haowar upadeshke upalvdhi karaar janya parikaamor unnati kareque.
guj: 1960maa shaikshanik abhyasakramana arambhthi ja, sansthae shikshanshastrana abhyasakramma niyamit sudharo karyo che, cinemetic shikshane gunavatta samrudh karayu che ane malkhane sanvardhit banaavyu che, te kharekhar shreshtha kendra che, avi anubhuthana adeshno ahsaas karaawe che.
hin: 1960 main shaikshanik paathyakram kii shuruyaat ke saath hi santhaan ne shiksha kii paathyacharya main lagaataar sudhaar kiya he, chalchitr-sambandhi praveenta ke mandandon ko sudhara he, or iske sahi arthon main utkrushtataa kaa centre banane ke uddeshy ko puraa karne ke liye isaki aadharbhoot sanrachana main vistaar kiya he.
kan: 1960ralli shaikshanika korsugalu aarambhwadaginind, i sanstheyu nijawagiu utkrishtteya kendravagabekemb ader anatiannu sakaragolislu niyathwagi shaikshanika pathyakramavannu uttampadisutta, cinema kalege sambandhisid kalikeya gunamattavannu hchisuvuder jotege, moolsaukaryagainnu abhivruddhipadiside.
mal: 1960 kalil akadamik passyakrama arambhichatumutal institute pathyasampradayam kramamai mechchappetuttukayu, sinimavishyakmay packnatine gunnilvar sampannamakkukyu, yatharttil oru mikavinte kendramai maranural meladhikarilute niർddesha nickvetanutakunn atisthanasakaryas vardhippikkayu cheituponnu.
ori: 1960 masihare shaikshik pathnekram aarmbh heva per tharu, anusthanati nikhmit bhavare shaikshanik pathnekramatiku unnattar karichhi, chakchchitra-sambandhiya shikshagrahair gunavattaku samrudh karichhi, eban vasthabare eka utkarshar kendra hebar kshamatatiku hridyangam kariva nimitta bhitthibhumiku parivarddhit karichhi .
pan: 1960 vich academik pathakrama di shuruvat on naal, sanstha ne niyamit tor te aapne sikhia sangari sudharia hai, films de adhian di visheshta vadhai hai ate aadhari sanrchana nuun parapat kitha hai taan jo oh aapne uttamatai sthal on da adesh puura kar sakan I
tam: 1960il muraisarnt fatippues dodangappatatu muthal, icalvi niruvanum doderndu pairumurait dittats membaduty, tirapphatak kalviin druttch seviwaky, ulghatamibbai virivubaduty ore unmaiyana dalisirent kalvi miyamaghat digahum tanatu possuppai niraiveteri vandhulldu.
tel: 1960 lo vidhyasambandha pathyakramas prarambhaminappati nudi, i sansth niyamanga shikshanku sambandhinchin pathyapranalik sthini penchukuntu, chitra sambandhit abhyasnanni susampanna chestu, nijanga ock utkrushth kendranga nilvalann adeshanni sakar chesukonenduku maulik sadupayas pempondinchukundi.
urd: 1960 main talimi corson ke aagaaz ke baad se, insiti tute ne baqaaadagi se talimi nasaab ko up grad kiya, cinema seekhney ke mayar ko behatar banaaya, or buniyadi dhaanche ko tosia di taaki is ke sahi maanon main marcuz fizalit hone kaa antadab haasil ho.
eng: Since the commencement of academic courses in 1960, the Institute has regularly upgraded the pedagogic curriculum, enriched the quality of cinematic learning, and augmented the infrastructure to realize its mandate of being truly a centre of excellence.

ben: 7i march, rashtra parichalith media evan maanvadhikar dalguli nirapatta bahini dwara sarkaari hospatal, vishwavidyalaya o mandir chatvar dakhal karaar khabar nischit kare.
guj: 7 march, rajya dwara sanchalit madhyamo ane manav adhikar juthoe behaal karyu ke salaamati dalo dwara jaher hospitalo, vishwavidyalayao ane mandirna melaono kabajo levayo che.
hin: sarkari media or maanavadhikaar sanghathanon ne 7 march ko saarvajanik aspataalon, vishvavidhyalayon or mandir parisaron par suraksha balon ke kabje kii soochna di.
kan: march 7randu, sarkaari madhyam mattu maanav hakkugal sanghagalu sarvajanik aaspatregalu, vishwavidanilayagalu mattu devsthanagal aavaranagainnu bhadrata padeyavaru vashapadisicondiruvudannu drispadisidvu.
mal: potuashupatriu sർvakalashalaku kshetraparisarvaslu surakshasen kayyadakkiyatai maaർchch 7n sർkkarin kidilull madhyamaslu, manushyavkash sanghateu sthirikarichu.
ori: 7 marchre, sarvasadharan chikitsalaya, vishvidalaya o mandir hatagudik suraksha bal dra dakhal hoi sarithiva katha sarkar-parichalit ganamadhum eban manavik adhikar sangajnamane pushti karithile.
pan: 7 march nuun, sarkari media ate manukhi adhikar samuha ne sudkhya balaan duara jantak hospitala, universitya ate mandir de mishrans 'te kabaza karan di pushti keeti|
tam: potu marudvamanil, palkaligangangs manllum koil valaganglil bhadukappup patiiner pukundu akhyrmitldai march 7 andu arasu utagamum manit urimike kulukalum urudisetana.
tel: march 7na bhadrata dalalu prabhutva asupathrus, vishwavidyalayas, aalay pranganas akraminchukunnti prabhutva-aadhvaryamloni media mariyu manavahakkul sanghal dhruvikrinchai.
urd: 7 march ko, sarkar ke zer intazaam media or insaani haquk ke girohon ne sarkari dawaakhaanon, universtiyon or mandir ke ahaaton par hifaazati daston ke kabze kii tasadiq kii.
eng: On 7 March, state-run media and human rights groups confirmed the occupation of public hospitals, universities and temple compounds by security forces.

ben: sabar janya mudir jinispatra, chickesar suyog-suvidha, oshudh aar sabarkam prayojanian jinis nie sahayyer janya ekhankar anekguli sanstha agie asese.
guj: lokoney kariyanu, tabibi suvidhao ane dawaao tatha jayaare jarur pade tyaare anaya tamam chijvastuo melvavaa mate madad karti ghanibadhi sansthao ahin che.
hin: yahan kai saare sanghathan hai jo logon ko zarurat ke hisaab se rashan, chikitsa suvidhaon or dawaaon or sabhi zaruri chizon ke liye madad de rahe hai.
kan: illi janrige dinsi, vaidyakiya saukaryagalu, aushadhigalu jotege itare agatya vastegalu bekadaglell odagisodralli anek sansthegalu neravagtive.
mal: aavashyampole palcharak sadhanangൾ, vaidyasahaya, marunnul, matu avashyavastukal enniv janangk aticchukodukkunn dharalam sanghathankal ivitaund.
ori: ethare anek sangason angnthi, yeunmane lokanku sahayya karunnthi, yemithi ki saudapatra, chikitsa suchidha o aushadh eban anyanya darkaari jinish yaha yetevela darkaar padhushi.
pan: ithe kai saria sansthavaan han jo kariane, medical sahooltaan ate dawia ate hor zaroori chizs di lod pain te locals di madad kar rahia han I
tam: inge niraiy thondu niruvanangs irukkinsona, are malukud deviku ettbb madhiri malikai chaman, marutuv vasati, marundues, mabbbb attiyayavasiab borutkalnu ellam kodudhu udaukindena.
tel: sarukulani, vedya sadupayalani, mandulu, atyavasaramin wasteul rupao anno sansthal, app avasaramaite app prajalku sayam andistunnar.
urd: vahaan bahut si tanzeemein hain jo zarurat padane par logon ko khuraaq, tabi saholyat or advyat or tamaam zaroori ashya mahiya kar rahi hain.
eng: There are a lot of organisations here which are catering help to the people, in terms of groceries, medical facilties and medicines and all the necessary items as and when it is needed.

ben: khanti saada marble die tiri evan jatil khodai die sajano ei sthapanati aurangaader vruhattam smritistambhaguli madhyeo ekata.
guj: shuddha safed arasmathi banelo baareek kotarnithi alankrut, aa smarak pan aurangabadma aavela sauthi vishal smarkomanu ek che.
hin: baarik nakkashi ke saath bilkul safed sangemarmar se bani yah sanrachana aurangabad ke sabase bade smarakon main se ek he.
kan: achch bili amritshileyalli nirmanvagi, ati sukshma kettanegalind kudiro i kattad aurangabadnalliro ati dodda smarakagalallu ondagide.
mal: shuddhamay wellmarbilel panikatippichetu sukshmamay kottupanital alankritavumay i nirmmiti aurangabad smarakalilvach et valiamil onnan.
ori: khanti dhala marblere thiari aau sukshma khodeire sajaheithiva ei strakcharta bi aurangabadar sabuthu bad manuments bhitharu gotie .
pan: shuddha chite sangmaramar da bania ate gunjaldar nakkashi naal shingaria, ih dhancha aurangabad de sabh ton bade samaraks vichon ik hai.
