ben: ei dui sahodara bhaasha uttarer chhati raje bala has evan bhartiya upamahadesh 50 kotiroo beshi sankhyak maanush burute parein, 1931-e bhartiya roopali parda shabd aasaar pare, chodonti bhartiya sarkari bhashar upare hindi evan urduke janapriya chalachchitrer bhaasha hisabe begue newar janya yeti ekai yathest kaaran.
guj: ch uttariya rajyoma bolathi ane bhartiya upakhandna 500 milian lokoney samajati be bhagini bhashao hindi ane urdu chaud adhikrut bhartiya bhashao kartaan bhartiya lokpriya cinemani bhasha banavaanu aekmatra kaaran banii, jayare 1931maa bhartiya rajatapat par dhvaninu aagman thayu.
hin: 1931 main bhartiya rajatapat par jab dhwani ai to donon milti-julati bhashaaen, hindi or urdu ko bhartiya lokapriy cinema kii bhashaaen banane ke liye baaki chaudaa bhashaaon se upar chunaa jane kaa mukhya kaaran tha ki chah uttari rajyon main inhen bolaa jaataa tha or bhartiya upmahadweep main 50 karod logon se zyada inhen samajhate the.
kan: 1931ralli bhartiya bellitherege dhvaniannu parichaisidag bhartiya janapriya cinemad bhashegalagalu hadinalku adhikrut bhartiya bhashegal mele hindi mattu urduvannu aayke madlu i eradu sahodari bhashegalu bhartiya upakhandd uttarad aaru rajyagamalli badkeyaguttave mattu 50 kotigu hechu janarige arthvaguttave emb onde karan sakayitu.
mal: 1931 l indian wellittirai shabda vannapol indian janapriyasinimaute bhashakalai matu patinal audyogik bhashakalkupari hindiyu urudu tiranketukapetan, i rand sahodar bhashakala aru vaican sansthana sansariunnatu indian upabhughandattile 500 dashalakshattilupari alukalk manassilavunnatu end karea matra matiyallo.
ori: ehi duiti bhauni bahasha cha'ti uttari rajyare bbbahar hoithaye, eban keval bharatiya up-mahadeshre ehaku 500 niqut lok bujhithanthi, enu bharatiya roopeli pardaaku yeve 1931 masihare 'shabda' aasila, ethiki tatha matra bharatiya lokapriya cinemar bahasha bhave, annga chaudhati aadhikarik bahasar urdyare, hindi o urdur charnaku yatharth boli siddh karithaye |
pan: 1931 vich jadon avaaz bharati silver sakrinte ai taan donon miladi-juldi bhashaavaan hindi ate urdu nuun bharati cinema di bhashaavaan banan de lai baaki chodas bhashaavaan ton upar chunia gya, ish da mouth kaaran see ki che uttari raajan vich inhan nuun bolian janda see ate bharati vich upmahandeep vich 50 karod locals ton ziada ishnoo samajhade han I
tam: indi, urdu enjh erandu chakodar monoigalum aaru wat manilanglil pesepattu indiat tunike khandathil 500 millionukkum menoptt makalal purindukolopadukindena, awk 1931il india vellit trikub pechut dolinutpam vandapodhu ivvirandus indiavin pathinangu arasu monoigalitaye munnurims peniru india vegujana cinemavin monoikalak mariatangu ind woru karanme podhm.
tel: bharat upkhandalo i iru sahodar bhashalu aaru uttaradi rashtralas waduklo undi 50 kots mandiki paga ardhmvutai anedi 1931lo bhartiya venditeraki dhwani parichayamanapp bharat prajadran pondin cinemaki padnalugu adhikarik bhartiya bhashalokella hindi mariyu urdun anchukovadaniki taginant karna.
urd: dono bahan zubaanen chha shumali riyasato main boli jaati hain or sirf barsgair paak va hind ke 50 karod se zyaada logon ke zarie samajhi jaati hai jis kii vajah se hindi or urdu ko chaudaa sarkari hindustani zubaanon par trigeh di gai thi jab aawaaz 1931 main hindustani pardaa semin aai taaki wo hindustani maqbool cinema kii zubaanen bin saken.
eng: The two sister languages are spoken in six northern states and understood by over 500 million people on the Indian sub-continent alone reason enough for Hindi and Urdu to be chosen above the fourteen official Indian languages to become the languages of Indian Popular cinema when sound came to the Indian Silver screen in 1931.

ben: 2014 sale singapore table tennis assosyeshner sabhapati li bi wyah ei samasyar karna padatyag karechillen, pare tar uttarsuri allen li ekajan chine janmagrahankari khelowar jheng jianer naagariktber abedner pakshe chhillen.

kan: 2014ralli, singapoor table tennis asosiyeshann adhyakshe li bi wah i vivaadd karan rajiname nididru; aakeya uttaradhikariad elen li, taruvay china-sanjat padlarad zeng jiann pauratva arjianneu bembalisidru.

ori: 2014 masihare, singapore teval tenis sanghar sabhapati, lii bi h, ehi vibadaku nei nij istafa deithile; tank uttaradhikari, elen lii, paravartti samaure jane china-janmit padlar jeng jiannk nagarikath dharakhasthaku samarthan karithile.
pan: 2014 vich, singapore teble tennis sanglen de pradhan li bi waah ne ish mude te apna asatifa de ditha; us di uttaradhikaari, elan lii ne bood vich, chin vich paidaa hoe pedalar zeng jiaan di nagarikta di arzi da samrathan kita.
tam: 2014il, singapores table tennis sangadin talaivar lee pee va indep prachin karanmak rajinama seydar, avarai aduddhuvanth alen lee binner chinaill piddnt mitip patakoti jeng jianen kudiurims vinnapatingu adravalitar.
tel: 2014 lo, i vishyamai singapore tebul tennis asosiyeshan adhyakshuram li bi wa vaidoligaru; ambe uttaradhikarini elen li, aa taruvat chainalo janminchin padlar sheing jian paurasatva darkhastuki sumukhat vyaktikarinchindi.
urd: 2014 main, singapore table tennis esosi eshan kii sadar lee bi wah ne is misile par istefa de diya, in ke janshin elan lee ne baad main ek chin main paida hue pedler jing jiyaan kii shahrit kii darkhwaast kii hamayat kii.
eng: In 2014, Singapore Table Tennis Association's president Lee Bee Wah quit over this issue; her successor, Ellen Lee, later favored the application for citizenship of Zeng Jian, a China-born paddler.

kan: grand canyan uttar arijonadalliddu, americad sanyukt sansthanagamallin dodda pravasi aakarshanegamalli ondagiruvudar jotege vishvad elu prakritik adbhutagamalli ondagide.
mal: americaൻ aikyanatukalille et pradhanpat vinodasanchar oakർshanckslilonnu locatille ethe prakrutivismayasilonnumay graൻd kanyoൺ watnakൻ arisoil statecheyunnat.
ori: grand kanyan uttar aarijonare rahichhi, eban eha heudi americar prasiddh paryletak akarshanagudik madhyaru anttam tatha vishra prakritik sapthashcharya madhyaru gotie .
pan: uttari arizona vich sthit grand canion, sanyukat raj di sabh ton badi yatru akarshan hai ate vishva de saat kudriti ajoobia wichon ik hai I
tam: grant kanyan watakku arisonavill ulldu, atu americawin mikachihant subarulat dalankalil onragaum ulagin elu iauka atikyakalil onragaum digahakintu.
tel: grand kanyan uttar arizonalo undi mariyu idi united statesloni ati gopp paryatak akarshanallo okati avateme kak prapanchaloni edu sahaj vincllo okati.
urd: di grand canen shumali arizona main waaqa hai, or ye america main siyaahon kaa shaandar marcuz hone ke alaava duniya ke saat kudrati ajayabaat main se ek hai.
eng: The Grand Canyon is in northern Arizona, and is one of the great tourist attractions in the United States as well as one of the seven natural wonders of the world.

ben: prevalent proto indo irani bhaasha thek nem aasa vedic sanskrit evan gothic avestan bhashar prachintam lipibhukt rup adbhutabhave anurup.
guj: aa bhashaona sauthi pahelam nondhayela rupama vedic sanskrit ane gathik avestan nondhapatra rite sarkhi che, je sahiyari proto-indo-iraniyanmathi avathirna che.
hin: in bhashaaon ke pracheenatam abhilikhit praaroop, vaidic sanskrit or gothic avestan ascharyajanak dhang se kaaphi samaan hai, jo ek samaan proto-hind-irani bhashaa se viksit hue hai.
kan: i bhashegal praachintam dakhlit rupagalad vaidiki sanskrit mattu gaathik avestan ivu gamnarhavagi sadrushvagiddu, onde muul-indo-iranian bhasheind huttidwagive.
mal: vaidik sanskrit, gatic avestan enni bhashakalute rekhappetuttapett et paddy rupaees potuvay proto into iranian bhashail ninn rupankontatakayal prastavyama vido samana.
ori: ehi bahasagujaikar prachinatam lipivaddh rupagudik, yatha vaidik sanskrit eban gaathik avestaan, ullekhaneelabhavare parasper sadrush atanthi, yeungudikaki eka saman pura-indo-iraniya bhasharu jaat hoiyanthi .
pan: ihnas bhashaavaan de sabh ton purana ricard kite roop, vedic sanskrit ate gathik aweston kamal de saman han, jo ki aam proto-indo-irani bhaasha ton heths han|
tam: bodhwana adi india iraniya mofiilrundhu clybrind ved sanskrudam manllum katha avestan monoigalin mikhat donmayana padivues kufippitttakk vaqail ott vatiwil ulsana.
tel: i bhashallo namodu cheyabadin roopalas atyant praachinamain vaidic sanskrit mariyu gatik avest, gananiyamin polikalu kaligi unnai, ummadi aadim indo iranian bhaash nudi vachchinavi.
urd: in zubaanon kii ibtidai darj shudaa shaklen, vedic sanskrit or guthik evastin, numayan tuur par ek jaisi hain, jo aam proto-hind-irani jubaan se nikali hain.
eng: The earliest recorded forms of these languages, Vedic Sanskrit and Gathic Avestan, are remarkably similar, descended from the common Proto-Indo-Iranian language.

ben: era kaaran hal bharter nijasv ekati atyant samrudh o paripakk deshiya chikisagath aitihya evan pashchimi jaibchikisa vigyane shaktishali bhit royas.
guj: aa e karne che karanke bharat paase pushkal samrudh ane paripakv swadeshi tabibi varso che ane teno pashchimi biomedical saynsma majbut paayo che.
hin: aisa isliye he kyonki bharat ke paas apni khud kii ek behad samrudh or paripakv swadeshi chikitsiya dharohar or pashchimi jaevchikitsa vigyaan main majboot buniyaad he.
kan: idakke karanvendare bharatavu tannade aad bail shrimant mattu paripakvavad vaidyakiya parampareyannu hagu pashchatya biomedical vigyandalli bhadravaad talhadiannu hondide.
mal: ativsampannvu pakavumay oru taddeshiya vaidyaparmparyvu pashchathya biomedical shastras udhappulla atittayu indyak ulitukontanit.
ori: ehar karan heudi bharat paakhre nizer eka ati utkrusht o paripak sdeshi chikitsa vigyanar aithihya rahichhi, eban pashchatya jaib-bheshaj vigyanare ehar bhitti sudrush.
pan: ih ish lai hai kiunki bharat di ik bohut vadhia ate puraani deshi chikitsa viraasat hai ish dis buniada pattmi biomedical vigyaan vich basi hui hai I
tam: indiaill senipana manllum mudirchiberut chont ulnaddu marutuv mripum adevele valuwana mengatya uerial marutuv anaivialkalin adittalamum ulldu enpate itaskuk karanm.
tel: induku karna bharatvaesha tandin atyant viluvagal paripakv deshiya varasatva sampad mariyu pashchatya jeevavedya shastrala gatti punadulu kaligi undi.
urd: aisa is liye kyonki bhaarat ke pas is kaa apna ek be had matmol or tarakkee yaafita desi tabi varsa hai or mugharabi baio medical alum main majboot buniyaaden hain.
eng: This is because India has an immensely rich and mature indigenous medical heritage of its own and strong foundations in western biomedical sciences.

ben: ekamatra milakha sinhai chhillen kamanwealth gemse vyaktigat swarnapadak prapak, kintu 2010 kamanwealth gemse bharter hay mahilader discus thro-e swarnapadak jite evan kamanwealth gemser athletics pratham mahila swarnapadak prapak hisabe 52 bashwar pare itihas gaden krishna punia.
guj: komanvealth ramatotsavama vyaktigat suvarn chandrak jeetnara aekmatra bhartiya athlit milkha singh hata, parantu 2010na komanvealth ramatotsavama krishna puniya 52 varsh pachhi bharat mate mahilaona chakrafenkama suvarn chandrak jithine itihash sarjyo ane athleticsma suvarn chandrak jeetanari pratham mahila banii.
hin: milkha singh ekmaatr dhaavak the jinhone rashtramandal khelon main ekal swarna padak jeeta tha lekin 2010 ke rashtramandal khelon main krishna punia ne itihaas rachaa jab mahilaon kii chakkaa phenk pratiyogita main unhone bharat ke liye 52 varsh ke baad swarna padak jeeta or rashtramandal khelon main swarna padak jeetne vaali pehali bhartiya mahila dhaavak baniin.
kan: kamanvealth kridakutadalli vaiyaktik chinnad padkavannu galisid ekik kridapatu, milkha singh agiddaru, adare 52 varshagal nantar, 2010r kamanvealth kridakutadalli, krishna poonia mahileyar chakra esetadalli chinnad padkavannu gelluv moolak mattu kamanvealth kridakutadalli athleticsnalli chinnavannu gedd modal mahileyagie itihaash nirmisidru.
mal: komanvalt gainsil oru vyaktigatasvarna nedunn oreyoru kaayikatar milkha singh irunnenkil, 52 varshabolku sheea 2010 komanvalt gainsil krishna punia streeute diskas troil swarnan medal neticond komanvalt gainsil ateaticksil swarna nedunn aadya vanitai charitra srushtichu.
ori: milkha singh ekamatra kreedavith thile yie kamanelath khelre brekthigat srna padak jitithile, kintu 52 barsh pare 2010 kamanelath khelre crishna punia mahila diskas throre bharat pin srna padak jithi itihash srushti karithile, eban kamanelath khelre aathleticsaare pratham mahila bhave eka srna padak jithi se ehi itihash srushti karithile.
pan: milakha singh ik hi khidaari see jinhan ne rashtramandal kheds vich viaktigat son tagma praapat kitha, per 2010 di rashtramandal kheds vich krishna punia ne mahila varg de discs thro vich son tagma jitt ke ithas oach ditha ate bharat vich 52 saalas bood pahili mahila bani jise ne rashtramandal kheds, athletics vich son praapat kitha I
tam: munbu milka singh mattume kamanwelt boatisil taninabar vilyadduku tangap pathakum vendo one virarag irindar, eninu 2010 kamanwelt boatisil krishna punia pengalukan vattu eritlil vendue 52 andugalukqup pingu indiaukkud tangap pathakum perduddhandadan mulamum kamanwelt boaticain tatagal vilyatle tangam vendo muthal penmaniyakat digahandatan mulamum varalar baditar.
tel: kamanvalt kridallo vyaktigat swarna pataka geluchukunn ekac kridakar milkha singh undevar, kani 2010 kamanvalt kridallo, 52 ell taruvat krishna punia bharatku mahill disease trolo swarna pataka gelychi, kamanvalt kridallo athletics lo swarna gelichin toli mahilga charitra srustinchindi.
urd: daulat mushtarki khelon main infradi talai tamagaa jeetne waale vaahid athlete milakha singh the, lekin 2010 ke daulat mushtarki khelon main, 52 saal baad krishna puniya ne khwatin ke discus thru main hindustan ke liye talai tamgaa jeet kar or daulat mushtarki khelon ke athletics main sone kaa tamgaa jeetne wali pahali khatun ke tuur par taarikh rakam kar di.
eng: Milkha Singh was the only athlete to win an individual gold medal at a Commonwealth Games, but at the 2010 Commonwealth Games, Krishna Punia created history by winning the women's discus throw gold medal for India after 52 years and as the first woman to win a gold in athletics at the Commonwealth Games.

ben: ei ghatnar bapar anveshan kare trini 'mizo eng israel?' ("mizo naki israeli?") (2004) baity likheven.
guj: temane aa samasya vishe mizo nge ijharayel? (‘mizo ke ichrayeli?’) (2004) pustak lakhyu.
hin: unhone 2004 main is mudde par ek kitaab likhi mizo nge israel? ("mizo yaa israeli?").
kan: aat i vishayavannu parishodhisutta ʼmiddo nge israel?ʼ ("middo athwa isreli?") (2004) emb pustakvannu baredru.
mal: i prashna samagramai parichukond addeha mizo nge israyel ("mizoyo israyelo") (2004) end pustak anuti.
ori: se ehi vishattiku anusheeson karithiva pustak "mizo nge ijrael?" ("mizo na ijraeli?")r rachana karithile .
pan: usne ish mude di padchol mizo nage israel? ("mizo nage?") (2004) kitaab likhi I

urd: is ne is misile kii khoj karte hue mizu nage israel? ("mizu yaa israeli?") (2004)kitaab likhi .
eng: He wrote the book Mizo Nge Israel? ("Mizo or Israeli?") (2004), exploring this issue.

ben: udvasaner samay, aguayan red armir thek palate gie poorv prussia, silecia evan pomeranear mato german pradesher bipul sankhyak basindara maara ya, keu keu thanda o anahar, keu keu sangramer samay.
guj: aagal vadhati lal sena aave te pahelam bhaagi javama germanyna purav prusia, silacia ane pomeraniana rahisho moti sankhyama marya gayan; temana ketlak thandi ane bhukh tatha ketlak ladaini kamgirima marya gayan.
hin: badhati hui laal sena se bachane ke liye purvi prashia, silesia or paumarenia ke german praanton se bhaag rahe nivaasiyon kii nirvathan ke dauraan mrityu ho gai, kuch kii thand or bhukhmaree ke kaaran or kuch kii yuddh kii ladaai ke kaaran.
kan: munnuggi baruttidd kempu seney eduru palayangiyyutta germaniy poorv prashya, sailijiy, mattu pomereni praantyagal nivasigalu sthalantaravaguv samayadalli bhaari sankhyeyalli, kalavaru chali mattu hasivinind, innu kalavaru yuddhad caryacharanegal sanderbhadalli savannappidaru.
mal: munnerunn chempatil ninn palayana cheiyunn, german pravishyakalay kilocan prashya, silasia, pomarania enni jർmmൻpravishyakalile nivasis ochinjupokalukൾkkiteiൽ tanupu patiniu karanmayu chilർ yuddhantapatikൾkkir maricchupoi.
ori: agrasar heuthiva lal sena kavalaru khasi palaton karuthiva poorb prushiar german pradeshaguik, silysia, eban pameraniar bahu sankhyak adhivasi annga sthanku apasaaran samaure mrittu baran karithile; ketek thanda eban kshudha yogun, ketek lakei samaure .
pan: ange uddh rahi laal fouj de sahmne, poorabi parshia de german raajan de vasaniks di badi ginti vich mout hoo gai, silsia ate pomerania nikaasi dauraan , kujh di tand ate bhukhamari naal, kujh di ladaai de karjan dauraan mout hoo gai|
tam: munneri varum sempataike khandu virandotic germanein kisikup prashya, silesia manllum bhomarenic makhan wachiil eralmanor uirigondaner, avarkalil woru bagudiinar kulir manllum patiniallum, manthoru bagudiinar pore natwatikkalalum ivvar mandaner.
tel: munduku saguthunn arr sainya kante munduga paripotunn turpu prashia, silesia mariyu pomeranialoni german pravinsulku chendin nivasitulu tarlimp samayaulo pedd sankhyallo, kondar chali mariyu aakali karnanga, kondar porat karyakalapalas, maranincharu.
urd: pesh kadami karne wali red army ke pahunchne se pahele faraar hote hue mishraqi prashyaa, siilecya or pomiraniya se taalluk rakhane waale german sobon ke baashandon kii badi taadaad inkhila ke dauraan halock ho gai, kuch sardi or bhok ke baais or kuch jangi carrwayon ke dauraan.
eng: Fleeing before the advancing Red Army, large numbers of the inhabitants of the German provinces of East Prussia, Silesia, and Pomerania died during the evacuations, some from cold and starvation, some during combat operations.

ben: deshiya sangbadadatader dwara ekatrit deshiya manoranjan anusthan evan tathyaguli a-deshiya darshakder janya sasta punra packej kara sambhava bale ekati matra desh samprachar karaar thek beshi caryakar eti.
guj: ek deshma prasarit karva kartaan aa vadhu kaaryaksham che kaaran ke sthanik manoranjak karyakrmo ane sthanik samacharakarmio dwara ekathi karaayeli mahiti bin-sthanik darshako mate sastama farithi pek kari shakay che.
hin: gharelu manoranjan kaarykram or samachar, gharelu karmiyon dwaara praapt jaankaree ko gaiyr-gharelu darshakon ke liye saste main ripacage kiya ja saktaa he, yah ek raashtra ko prasaarit karne kii tulana main adhik dakshatapurna he.
kan: deshiya manaranjana kaaryakramagalu mattu deshiya suddi sibbandiind sangrahisalad mahithiannu videshi shrotrugalige aggavagi hoss rupadalli presenutpadisabahudaddarind onde deshkke prasar maduvudakkint idu hechu falkariyadudagide.
mal: taddeshiyavaർttalekhakർ sampadikkunn vinodaparipatikalu vivarslu chelavu kueach vaideshik prekshakarkuventi punaravataripicam ennatinaൽ it oreyoru rajyateak prakshepa cheiyunnatinekal kututal karyakshama.
ori: gotie deshare prasaran kariva tuznare eha beshi fatprad ate karan gharoi neuj karmachareemanank dra ekatara karayauthiva gharoi manoranyjan karyankram tatha suchanassbu shasthare an-gharoi darshakamanank pin ripakej karayai parib.
pan: ih ik desh vich prasaaran karan naalon vadhere kushal hai kiu ki gharelu manoranjan program ate gharelu khabaraan de amale duara ieathi keeti jankari gair gharelu darshaks lai saste fung naal mud-pack keeti jaa sakadi hai|
tam: itu one nadduku olibharapuadai veet sikanamantu, anendal ulnadduch seite uliers thruttus takhavalles ulnattup bollutubhoku nicktchigales velinaddu neyarluku malivak madudokubbuch saitu valang mudi.
tel: idi ock deshaniki matrame prasarancheyada kante anto samarthavantanga untundi, andukante swadeshi vinod karyakramas mariyu swadeshi vaartha sibbandi sekarinchin samacharanni deshiulu kaani prekshakulku anuvuga march erparichi chavukga andinchavacchu kanuk.
urd: ye kisi ek malik main nishryat se zyaada musar hai kyonki gharelu tafarihi program or gharelu neuz staff ke jaria jamaa karda malomat ko gair gharelu samain ke liye saste tareeke se dobara istemaal kiya jasakta hai.
eng: This is more efficient than broadcasting to a single country because domestic entertainment programs and information gathered by domestic news staff can be cheaply repackaged for non-domestic audiences.

ben: ekati pradarshani khela chalakalin keu keu mantavya kare ye khelwarra jaler upar die baltake ag piche kare bhali karano cheshta karche evan tai bodhhoy bhalibal namta ei krida janya besh ekata barnanamulak naam.
guj: ek nidarshan ramat daramiyaan koie vidhan karyu ke kheladio dadane jali uparthi aagal pagel uchhali rahyan hovanu janay che ane kadaaya volibol e ramathanu varnanatmak nam hoi shake che.
hin: ek pradarshan khel ke dauraan kisi ne dippanee kii ki aisa lagata he jaise khilaadi gend ko zamin par na lagane dete hue jaal ke upar se ek taraf se duusari taraf woli maarthe chale ja rahe hai, or shaayad is khel kaa zyaada varnanaatmak naam wollyboul hoga.
kan: pradarshak pandyavondu nadeyuttiddag, aatgarru chendu nelakke taguvudaromage adnnu baleya melgadeyind attinditt hodedu dooduttiruvante toruvudannu gamnisid yaaro obbaru, i aatakke prayashah valiball embudu hechu vivarnatmak hesaragabahudendu suchisidru.
mal: valayk mukalilute kalicar angot ingot pant 'voli' cheiyunnatupole tonnunnatukond volibol end perayiriam oruvel kali krityamai vivarikunnat enne oru maatrakamatsaratinitil aaro parannu.
ori: eka pradarshan khelre, kehijane mantavi dele ye khelalimane baltiku net upare agku eban pataku shoonsaare maruthiva pari janapadushi, eban bodhhua ukt khelti pin, 'bhalival' eka adhik varnanathmak nam heb .
pan: ik pardarshani khed de doran kise ne tipni diti ki khedari geind nuun net de age- pichhe sit rehe han ate ish karke walibal naame ish khed de lai ziada thik hovega I
tam: woru katchi adietin podhu, veerars bandai valiku andap pakkamum indep pakkamum 'walli' sayvatu (maghi maghi adippatu) polat therikittu athanal ind vilyattch chittarippatangu walibal enjh payar adhikab poruttamak irukkum enat dondukintu endu yaaroon karudduch sonnars.
tel: ock pradarshan atlo, atgall net pai nudi bantini atuit visurutunnti kanapadutaru kanuk, i kriku bahusha valiball ann vivarnatmak nama saripotundani evero vyakhanincharu.
urd: mazahre ke khel ke dauraan, kisi ne kaha ki aisa lagataa hai ki khiladi gend ko jaal ke oupar aage peeche lay jaa rahe hain, or shayd wali bal is khel kaa ek or vizaahti naam hoga.
eng: During a demonstration game, someone remarked that the players seemed to be volleying the ball back and forth over the net, and perhaps volleyball would be a more descriptive name for the sport.

ben: i.de.es avasheshe e.ti kiarneer shatadhik karmchari chhantai kare, kshatipuran commie deya, bak-afis cryaklap sankuchit kare, evan e.ti kiarneer sadar daptar shesh percent shicago thek planote sthananthrit kare.
guj: priname, i.dee.es. e e. ti. kernimathi senkado karmacharis chhuta karyan, valtar ochhu karyu, vyavasthapan ekatrit karyu ane ante e. ti. kerninu vadumthak chicagothi texsasna planoma khasedyu.
hin: i.di.es. ne e.tii.karni main saikadon logon ko naukari se nikaala, muawza kam kiya, back-offis ke kaaryon ko sudrudh kiya or ant main e.tii. karni kaa mukhyalay chicago se sthanantarit karke plano, texs le gaye.
kan: i.de.es. conege e.ti. karniyalli nooraru udyogagainnu tegeduhaki, pariharavannu kadimagolisi, kacheriya sahayak aadlit kaaryagainnu krodikarisitu, mattu antimawagi e.ti. karniya kendrakacheriannu chicagodind texasin planoge sthalantarisitu.
mal: i. de. es otuviൽ e. ti kaaർniiൽ nurukanakin tosailukൾ wettichurukkukayu nashtaparihar kurikkukayu bak-ofis pravർttanangൾ ekikarikkayu avasana e. ti kaaർniute aasthana shiagoiൽninn texasille planoil matisthapickayu cheitu.
ori: i.de.es. sheshre 'e.ti. kiurni're thiva shah shah karmaniyukthiku samapt karidheithila, kshatipuran hras karidheithila, bak-afis karyangudiku mishai gotie samastibhukt karidheithila, eban parisheshre 'e.ti. kiurni'r mukhanyaku chikagoru teksasr planoku sthanantharita karidheithila .
pan: ant i di asa ne e. ti. kirne vikhe, kai hazaaraan naukaria khatam kar ditia, muaavze gata dite, back office karjan nuun idhetha kar ditha, ate akheer e. ti. kirne da mouth dafatar chicago ton plano, taxs badal ditha|
tam: eties irutiyag e.di.giarniil noorrukankkana uliarkans paninikkum sayttu, sambawattike kuraittatu, binpul aluvalkas seyalbadugans valuppaduddhiyadu, pingu e.di. giarnein talams aluvalagat sikakovilrundhu tekkesin planovinku maderiyatu.
tel: edies kramanga ati kiyarnilo vandladi udyogas nirmulinchi, jitallo kotal vidhinchi, anubandha karyakalapal samagraparichi, tudaku ati kiyarni pradhan karyalayanni chicago nudi plano, teksaski marchndi.
urd: e dee es ne balakhir aye tii kerani main saikadon milazamatein khatm kiraden, muaavja kam kiya, bek afas ke program ko zam kiya, or aakhirkaar aye tii kerani kaa sadar daphtar chicago se plano, texas muntaqal kridya.
eng: EDS eventually shed hundreds of jobs at A.T. Kearney, reduced compensation, consolidated back-office functions, and eventually relocated A.T. Kearney's headquarters from Chicago to Plano, Texas.

ben: aami visesh kare avak haesi ye se taar pratham chhabitei katta bhalo kareque!
guj: mane khas to e vatanu aashcharya thayu ke temane temani paheli ja filmma ketlu saras karyu che?
hin: main to khaas kar is baat se hairaan hoon ki usne apane debyue main kitna acha kaam kiya he!
kan: tann modal chitradalle aake eshtu olle abhinaya nididdare anth nangantu aashcharya agatte!
mal: kannichitrattiltane avar itr nannai chetatila enic pratyekich vismayam.
ori: se tangkar pratham abhinayare yepari sundar pradarshan kale, vishesh bhave mun sethire bismit!
pan: mai khaas for 'te hairaan haa ki kiven usne apni pahili film vich bakhubi com kita!
tam: tanatu muthal pattleye avar evvalou aibudamak naditllar endu viendubonen.
tel: naku annitikante ashcharya anipinchindi, tan toli chitranlone ant baga chacindo.
urd: main khaas tuur par hairaan huun ki is ne apni pahali film main kitna iccha kaam kiya!
eng: I am especially amazed by how well she did in her debut!

ben: 1591 christabdev, jan leagate pratham cembrij bibelti mudran karen, evan 1629-e king jems bibeler cembrij pholio sanskarnti mudran karen tomas evan jan baak.
guj: 1591maa pahelu cembrij bible jhon laget dwara chapavama aavyu hatu, ane 1629maa king jems biblani cembrij folio aavritti thomas ane jhon bak dwara chapavama aavi hati.
hin: 1591 main jon legat ne pehali cambridge bible chhaapi thi, or 1629 main king james bible kaa cambridge pholio sanskaran thomas or jon bak dwaara chapa gaya tha.
kan: 1591ralli, modal cambridge biblennu jaan legat mudrisidru mattu 1629ralli king james biballin cambridge pholio aavruttiannu thomas mattu jaan bak mudrisidru.
mal: 1591l john legate aadya kembrij bible achchatikkayu 1629l king jains bibilinte kembrij pholio edishan tomas and john bak purattikakkukayu cheitu.
ori: 1591 masihare, jan legetnk dra pratham kembrij bivel mudrita hoithila, eban 1629 masihare, thomas o jan baknk dra king jems bivelr kembrij folio sanskaranati mudrita hoithila .
pan: 1591 vich pahili cambrij bibal jon liget duvaara chhapi gai see ate 1629 vich king jemas bibal da cambrij folio sanskaran, thomas te jon bak duvaara chhapia gya see I
tam: 1591il, muthal cambridge bible jaan lecatal achidapattatu, pingu 1929il king james bablin cambridge polio patippai thomas and jaan pack achitanur.
tel: 1591lo john leget modati cembridge bibilnu prachurincharu, inca 1629lo thamas mariyu john bakle king jemes bakeell cembridge folio pratini prachurincharu.
urd: 1591 main, pahali cambraj bible jaan legate ne chhapi, or 1629 main, king jaimuz bible kaa cambraj folio edeshan thomas or jaan book ne shaya kiya.
eng: In 1591, the first Cambridge Bible was printed by John Legate, and in 1629, the Cambridge folio edition of the King James Bible was printed by Thomas and John Buck.

hin: is training se bachche ke jivan main anushaasan aayega.

tel: i shikshan pilll jivitanni kramshikshanalo pedutundi.
urd: ye tarbet bacche kii zindagi ko najam va zabbat de gi.
eng: This training will discipline the child's life.

hin: lekin asaliyat main, iskaa koi asar nahin hota.
kan: aadre vastavvagi ivugalind enu prayojn aagall.
mal: satyattil itellankond oru falavumill.
ori: kintu vasthabare, esabure kichhi hue naahin .
pan: per asal vich, ih kujh ve praapat nahi karade|

eng: But in reality, these get to nothing.

ben: jihadi, mujahidin o fedain halo anurup arabi shabd, ya ingreji abhidhan pravesh kareque.
guj: jehadi, mujahiddin, ane fidayin e ekasaman arabic shabdo che je angreji shabdakoshma praveshi gaya che.
hin: jihadi, mujahidin or fidaayin ek samaan arabi shabd hai jo angreji shabdkosh main aa kar chuke hai.
kan: jihadi, mujahidin, mattu fidayin embavu intahude arabbi padgalagiddu, english nighantige serpadeyagive.
mal: jihadi, mujahidiൻ, fedayiൻ enniv english bhashanighanduviൽ kayria samanthyull arabi pada.
ori: jihadi, mujahiddin o fidain saman dharanar aarabiya shabda, yeunguik inraji shabdakosh madhyare pravesh karichhi.
pan: jehadi, mujahidin ate fadeyine saman arabi shabad han jo angarezi shabadakosh vich dakhal hoo gaye han|
tam: jihadi, muzahidin, bitayen aakhiya ott sotts ibbodhu ankhil agaratiil chercopattuluna.
tel: jihadi, mujahidin mariyu fedayin anevi english padakoshanloki praveshinchin okelanti arbik padalu.
urd: jihadi, mujahden or fidain milte jalte arabi alfaaz hain jo angreji lagat main daakhil ho gaye hain.
eng: Jihadi, mujahideen, and fedayeen are similar Arabic words that have entered the English lexicon.

ben: eter katha otter manei nei.

hin: unhen aisa karne ke bare main kuch yaad nahin he.
kan: avrige idann madidde nenpill.
mal: addehttin ingtone cheit ormmayeill.
ori: tangkar eita kariva katha mane naahin .
pan: uhanaas nuun ajiha karan da kujh yaad nahi|
tam: appati woru mudalittch seytatagave avaruku gyabhagam ille.
tel: adi chessintt ayankaslu gurtu ledu.
urd: inhen aisa karne ke baare main kuch yaad naheen hai.
eng: He has no recollection of doing it.

ben: shalankayanara chhil vengi (aadhunik pedavegi)-te rajdhani sah 300 thek 440 christabd avadhi godavari evan krishna madhyavarti andhra anchal shasankari ek prachin rajbansh.
guj: salankayans e puraatan rajvansh che, jene godavari ane krishna vachchena andhra pradeshma i.sa. 300 thi 440 daramiyaan temani rajdhani vengi (aadhunik pedavegi)thi shasan karyu hatu.
hin: shalankayan ek pracheen vansh tha jo 300 se 440 isvi tak godavari or krishna nadiyon ke bich andhra kshetra par shashan karata tha or uski rajdhani vengi (aaj kaa paddvegi) thi.
kan: shalankayanru ondu praachin rajvanshwagiddu, ivaru sa.sha. 300rind 440ravarege godavari mattu krishna nadigal naduvin andhrad pradeshswannu vengiallin (aadhunik pedavegi) tamm rajdhaniind alidru.
mal: si.i. 300 mutal 440 vare wenki (aadhunik kalatte pedavegi) talasthanmai andhraile godavarik krishnayk idilull pradesha bharichirunn puraatan rajvanshmairunnu salankayananmas.
ori: salankagenamane thile eka prachin rajabansh yeunmaneki 300 ru 440 christabd paryyant godabari eban krishna madhyasth andhra anychalatiku shasan karuthile; semanankar rajadhaani bengi (aadhunik pedhavegi) thare rahithila .
pan: salankayan ik prachin rajwansh see jisane 300 ton 400 isavi tak vengi (aadhunik pedaavegi) vikhe apni rajdhani de naal godavari ate krishna de wichkaar andhra khetra utte raj kita|
tam: salangaynar enbore godavari manllum krishnauku itippatt andhrap prandhyatts vengil (navina bethavegi) dalinagaram amaitu poa 300 muthal 440 varai atchiseit woru bantya vamsam.
tel: shalankayanulu godavari mariyu krishna madhyanunn andhra prantanni krish 300 nudi 440 varaku vengi(aadhunik pedavegi) ni tam rajdhaniga chesuconi palinchin ock praachin vanshasthulu.
urd: salankayan ek qadim khandaan tha jis ne godavari or krishna ke darmiyaan andhra ke ilaka par 300 se 440 isvi tak vengi (jadid padaavegi) main apni rajdhani ke saath hukuumat kii thi.
eng: The Salankayanas were an ancient dynasty that ruled the Andhra region between Godavari and Krishna with their capital at Vengi (modern Pedavegi) from 300 to 440 CE.

ben: patrer madhye chaler gundo yoga karaar samay, taar majhe, alp pariman cora narkels yoga karte parein.
guj: jayare tame chokhano lot tapelima muko chho, tyaare vachama, jalidar naliyerna naana jaththa pan muki shako chho.
hin: jaise-jaise aap paatr main chaaval kaa aataa daal rahe hon, bich-bich main aap kam maatra main ghisa hua nariyal bhi daalen.
kan: nivu patreyotge akki hittonnu tumbisuttiruvanteye, nadunaduve, swalp pramandalli tengin turiannu serisabahudu.
mal: patrattil nicks arippoti idunnatiniteiൽ alpalpa chirkia tereyu cherkavunntan.
ori: patra madhyaku chaul chuuna dhaliva samaure, mazhire mazhire, aapan slp parimanr kora nassia madhya mishai paranthi .
pan: jiven - jiven tusi patile vich chaaval da ata mila rehe hoo naal hi thoda suka narial ve us naal mila doo I
tam: kufoil aricemawaich chercumbodhu idaitie chiritu dhuruviya dengays cherdduk kollalam.
tel: meeru patralo bium pindini vestu, madhyamadhyalo koddikoddiga cobbari turumunu kuda kalupavachchu.
urd: jese jese aap bartan main chaval kaa aataa daalate hain, beech beech main, aap ghuse hue nariyal kii thodi si muqadaar bhi shamil chriskte hain.
eng: As you add the rice flour into the container, in between, you may also add small quantities of grated coconut.

ben: yeman dharo, bivinn rajya thek dekhte pawa kanchanajangha mato himalayer anyanya parbatmalaguli advitiya evan pratity parbatmalari bhaag kare newar mato nijasv kichu baishishtya royas.
guj: jemke himalayas vividh parvatmalaono ja daadalo lai le je tane alag alag rajyomathi jova malshe, jem ke kanchanjagha ane tena jevi biji ghani badhi che, je darek aagavi che ane darek parvatmada paase vahenchwa jevu pothiku paasu che.
hin: udhaaharan ke taur par alag-alag himalay parvatamalas jo alag alag rajyon se dekhi ja sakati hai, jaise ki kanchanjanga, tathaa or bhi kai hai jo apane aap main anuthi hai or har parvatamala kii apni visheshtaayen hai.
kan: udaharanege, himalay parvatshrenigalne togo, adnn bere bere rajyagalind nodbahudu, ananyavaddu adu, kanchangange matte ade thar innu sumarive, nododakke prati shreninu tannade aad vaisishtyagalann hondiratte.
mal: udaharanttin, kanchenjung pole vividh sansthana ninn kanavunn vyatyast himalayan parvataniral, verayu mateng kanatt palatu, matramall oro parvataniraik atatinte swabhavavishesha pankuvakanumund.
ori: yemithi ki, udaharan srup himalaya parbatmalaku nia, yahaku tumhe vibhinna rajyaru dekhiparib, yemithi kanchanjanga gotie, eban ahuri anek ajji, eban pratyeka parbat shreneer nijas vaishishtya rahichhi janivapin.
pan: jiven ki udaharan vajon himala dis shrenia jo tusin bakh-bakh raajan jiven kanchanjanga, ate hor bohut saare uthe han, ik kism di hai ate har range vich sanjha karan lai isdi apni visheshta hai|
tam: udaranmak, kanchenjunga madhriana palveru manilanglil irundhu parkakutia balavitman imayamalait doters irukkinsona, itellam tanichiofutyatagaum, ovvonem tanippatt amchangalutanus irukkinsona.
tel: udaharanku vividh himalaya parvatshrenulu vividh rashtral nudi churgala kanchanjang lantivi inca anno, ockokkati okkorkanga pratyekat kaligi unnadi.
urd: misaal ke tuur par mukhtalf himalayai silsile jinhen tum mukhtalf riyasato se dekh sakati ho jese kanchan janga apni misaal aap hai or majid bahut saare hain or har silasile apni khaas khasusiyat ko pesh kurta hai.
eng: Like take for example the different Himalayan ranges which you can see from different states like Kanchenjunga, and many more are there, is one of a kind and each range have it's own feature to share.

ben: ekaki jibanyapaner janya adhiktar aadhyatmik pravrittivishishtder swabhav anuyayi tander janya sabarkam suyog-suvidha pradaan kara hato, evan ei shikshakder adhikansheroi prachur sankhyak shishya chhil.
guj: ekantama paavak jeevan jeevavaa mate vishesh aadhyatmik valan dharavanar mate temana swabhav anusaar tamam suvidhao puree padwama aavi hati ane motabhaagna aa shikshako paase moti sankhyama anuyayio hatan.
hin: aise logon ko sabhi suvidhaayen uplabdh karai jaati thim jinka aadhyatmik jhukaav hota he jisase ve apane swabhaav ke anusaar ekant main sadhu jivan yaapan karte the or inamen se adhiktar guruon ke anekon anuyaayi hote the.
kan: aadhyatmikateyatt hchin olavullvarige avar manodharmakke takkante ekantadalli parishuddhvaad jeevanavannu nadeslu ella saukaryagainnu odagislaguttittu mattu i gurugamalli hchinvarige apar shishyaru anuyayigalagiruttiddaru.
mal: aadhyatmik tatparya kututalulgwark swanta abhiruchikalkanusrich ekantatil punyajivitas nayian ella sakaryau labhyamakiirunnuvennu matramall, i gurukkanmaril micavark valia shishyasanchayvu undairunnu.
ori: nij sbhab anusaare nitsangra jeevan yapan kariva prati aadhyathmik bhavare aakrusht hoithiva brektimanank pin samast subidhasuyog yogai diayaithila, eban ehi gurumanank madhyaru adhikanshankar anek anugami shishta rahithile .
pan: ajihe locals nuun saria suvidhas ditia jandias san jinhan da adhiatam bal jhukii hunda see, jise naal uh aapne subhv anusaar sadhus jeewan batit karade san ate inhan vichon jiadantar gurus de chele hunde san|
tam: tanemail punit valveu menokollum aanmicup bhoku adhikam kondulvargaluku avaravar subhavatuku aup anatu vasadikalum saitu truppattanu, ittaku achanganul perumbalanvarluku erauman chitars irundaner.
tel: aadhyatmik asakti galwariki tam swabhavamunaku anugunanga ekantamulo tam pavitra jivital konsaginchenduku anni saukaryal andinchabadavi, alage i gurus anusarinche shishyulu adhik sankhyalo undevar.
urd: tamaam saholtein mahiya karai gai thim in logon ke liye jo apni tabiyaat ke mutabik tanhaai main zyaada ruhani tuur par paak zindgiyan guzaarne kii taraf mayil the, or in main se aksar asatou ko badi taadaad main chelon kii pairokari haasil thi.
eng: All facilities were provided for those more spiritually inclined to lead holy lives in solitude in accordance with their temperaments, and most of these teachers had large followings of disciples.

ben: bhartiya sener yuddh-kathin evan bidrohi ek aadhikarik ek praktan premikar rahasyama bhave apahrut santaner khonje yaan.
guj: yudhma kathor-lagnishoonya banela ane vidrohi swabhavana bhartiya sainya adhikari potani bhutapurv strimitrana rahasyamayi rite apaharan karayela baalkani shodhama nikale che.
hin: bhartiya sena kaa yuddh main anbhavi or baagi adhikari apni purv mahila-mitra ke bachche kii khoj main nikalataa he jiskaa rahasyamay dhang se apharan kar liya gaya he.
kan: yuddhgalindagi kathinahridayiagiruv mattu bandayagarnad bhartiya senadhikariobbanu nigurvagi apahritvad aathan maji preyasita maguvannu hudukicondu hoguttane.
mal: ere yuddhhaslaൽ daaർrhyam nediavanu vaingattavanumay oru indian armi oficer tante poorvakamukiute duruhamai tatticontupokapat kutte tetipokunnu.
ori: jane yuddh abhijna tatha vidrohi bharatiya sena adhikari rahasyaman bhavare apaharan hoithiva tank poorvathan premicar santanaku khojivaku yausanthi .
pan: ik kathor ate baagi bharati fouji adhikari apni saabaka premica de bache di bhaal vich janda hai, jise nuun ratsmai fung naal agava kita janda hai|
tam: borkal murddutanamum kddukkadankat gunmum badaitt ore india iranuv adhikari, marmaman muriil kattoppatt tanatu munnal kadaliin kuiandaiyait tetis selkioar.
tel: yudlo ratutelin ock viplavatmak bhartiya sainyadhikari, anuhyanga apaharanku gurain tan maji preyasi biddhan vatikenduku bayaluderutadu.
urd: jang se sakht or baaghi hindustani faoez kaa afasar apni sabik giral friend ke bacche kii talash main jataa hai, jise parasarar tuur par agwa kiya jataa hai.
eng: A battle-hardened and rebellious Indian Army officer goes in search of his ex-girlfriend's child, who is mysteriously kidnapped.

ben: 2000-e, ei suchakati vyabhhar kare es.and.pi bi.es.i sensex-era bhavishya suktiguli vyavasa kare bi.es.i taar siddhantamulak bazarti khule deya.
guj: derivatives marketne kholva mate 2000maa bi.es.i.e aa suchkankans upayog karine es&pe bi.es.i. sensex fyuchars contractanu trading karyu.
hin: bi.es.i. ne is suchakank kaa upyog karte hue es. and pi. bi.es.i. sensex vaayada anubandhon kaa vyapaar karke 2000 main apana sanjaat bazaar kholaa he.
kan: 2000nae varshadalli, es&pi bi.es.i. sensex mummarikeya oppandagainnu marutta bi.es.i. i suchyankavannu tann vyutpannagal marukatteyannu tereyalu bassitu.
mal: 2000ൽ es&pi bi. es. i seൻsexiൻre fyuchchർ koൺtractulute viൽppan nataticond bi. es. i atiൻre derivetivuute vipani turakkaൻ i suchik upyogichu.
ori: 2000 masihare, bi.es.i. ehi suchitiku ehar butpanna bazar kholiva nimanthe bbbahar kari, 'es. and pi. bi.es.i. sencex'r bhavishmat chukthipatra gudikar kinavika karuthila .
pan: bombe stok ekschange ne saal 2000 vich ih tatkare di varton kiti aapne derivatives bazar kholan de lai, ate asa and pi bombe stok ekschange sensex de ange de samajhutia naal wapar kitha I
tam: 2000il, piesi intak kuriitpe payanbadutti tanatu taruvippues chandaiyait dibandhu, es&bhi piesi cencex ethirnoku oppandakalil vanigum sayttu.
tel: 2000lo biessi i suchikanu upayoginchi, ass&pi biessi censex bhavisya contractul vanisyamarpidi jarips, tan utpannal vipanini arambhinchindi.
urd: 2000 main, bi es e ne is ishaariye ko apan darevatyuz mocket ko kholane, es and pii bi es e sensex futurez maahidon kii tizarat karne ke liye istemaal kiya.
eng: In 2000, the BSE used this index to open its derivatives market, trading S&P BSE SENSEX futures contracts.

ben: saptaher mazkhane yadi keu aases evan booking kare ya, seta ki have?
guj: aa saptahe koi tyaan aavine bookings karavi jaaya to thik raheshe?
hin: agar koi is hafte aakar booking kare to thik rahegaa kya?
kan: nammoru yaradru i vaar bandu buking madsidre tondre ill alva?
mal: iyanch arenkil nerituvann book cheiyunnat sakaryamairiumo?
ori: yadi kie jane ei sapthahare asanthi aau buking karanthi ta'helle changib ?

ben: roganirna, prabalata evan vyaktivishesher pashapashi chakri upar nirbhar kare, kaaj athva kajer jsgar sang manie newar asuvidha, yar sambhavya parinti hisabe aantapavyaktik sampark hastkshap sah anyder sang samasyar sang vyaktitvagat badhigulike yukt kara yete par.
guj: nidan, kathorta ane vyaktigat aadhare tatha kaaryne aadhare pan, vyaktitva vikrutine kaarya ke karyasthal sathe mel karvama mushkeli sathe jodi shakay, je sambhavit rite anyo sathe antaravyakti sambandhoma dakhalni samasya sarje che.
hin: nidaan, tivrata or vyakti ke aadhaar par tathaa kaam ke aadhaar par bhi vyaktigat vikaar kaam karne main yaa kaary-sthaan main hone vaali pareshaani se sambandhit ho sakate hai jiske parinamswaroop anya logon ke saath parsparik sambandhon main baadhaaen paidaa karke sambhavit rup se anya logon ke saath samasyaayein ho sakati hai.
kan: rognirnay, fivrate mattu aaya vyakti, jotege kelasavanne avalambisi, vyaktitva vikargalu kelas athwa kelasad sthaldondige hondikolluvallin kashtakke sambandhisirbahudagiddu, vyaktigal naduvan paraspar sambandhagamalli add baruv moolak itarrondige samasyegaluntagalu dariagaballavu.
mal: roganirnay, fivrath, sharirprakruti ennivyu jolittannayu anusrich vyaktitvavaikalyas, jolioto jolisthalattoto poruttapetanull prayasttot bandhippiavunnatu vyaktibandhansliൽ itapet matulavarumai prashnangൾ untakkunnatiൻre sadhyakali nayikunnat.
ori: nidan, teebrata, eban bsakthi tatha khodh chakiriti upare nirbhar kari brekthith bikaraku karyan kimba karyan kshetrati sahit khap khuaai chadivare heuthiva asubidha sahit sambandhit karayaithaye, yahaki bsakthi-bsakthi madhyasth samparkare baadha dei antmanank seh samasya sristir sambhavya karan hoithaye .
pan: nidan, gambhirata, ate viakti de naal naal naukari 'te nirbhar karade hoe, sakhshiet vikaar com jaaa com vaali tha naal najithn vich mushakil naal jude hoo sakde han, sambhavi for 'te aapsi sabandhs vich dakhal de ke doojia naal saoesyas paidaa kar sakde han|
tam: khandawiapatum noi, adan gadumay, badikkapatum nabhar, avritu pani akhiyavayap boruttu, alumike koladugal pani alltu paniidom sarndu suzlukup palkixlwatil ull sirmauton doderpubadutalam, ittaku suzlil atu taninabar itieyana ushukhalil batipu erbadutti pittruden prachanluku valivakukk waifuldu.
tel: rog nirdharan, fivrath, mariyu vyaktini batti, alage udyoganni batti, vyaktitva rugmatse udyog leda karyalaya nirvahinchukovailo ibbandi, vyaktul madhya sambandhallo praveshinchata vall itarulatho samasyalaku daaritise avakash undla vanti vatito mudipettvacchu.
urd: tushkhis, shiddat or firad ke saath saath kaam ke aitbaar se, shakhsiit ke akhtilal ko kaam yaa kaam kii jagah se namatane main dushvaari se mansilk kiya jasakta hai, jo mumkin tuur par bahami taalkat main madakhilat karke doosaron ke saath missale kaa baais bin saktaa hai.
eng: Depending on the diagnosis, severity, and individual, as well as the job itself, personality disorders can be associated with difficulty coping with work or the workplace, potentially leading to problems with others by interfering with interpersonal relationships.

ben: paryaton shilper aro beshi unnatir kshetre visesh visesh jayga aisav suvidha-suyog garh tulte have evan era janya sarkari pashapashi besarkari kshetrake netrutva nite have.
guj: pravasan vadhu sara vikas mate, aa savaltono je te vistarma vikas thavo joie ane aa mate jaher temaj khaangi kshetra netrutva levu joie.
hin: paryaton ke behatar vikaas ke liye, in suvidhaon ko sambandhit kshetron main viksit kiya janaa chahie or iske liye saarvajanik evam nijee kshetra ko aguai kerani chahie.
kan: pravasodyamad hchin belvanigege, i saukaryagainnu aaya sthalgamalli abhivruddhipadisabekaguttade mattu idakkagi sarkaari hagu khasagi valayagaleradu mundaltvavannu vahisicollbekide.
mal: touristtiൻre mechchapet viksanattinai i samvidhanngൾ bandhappet pradeshsliൽ vidocipikkayu ikcharyattiൽ potumekhalayu swakaryamekhalayu netrutva naൽkukyu want.
ori: paryntnar adhik unnati pin, ehi subidhasabu samprukt anychalguthikare vikashita kariva uchith, eban ethipin ubhay sarkaari eban gharoi kshetra netruth neva uchith |
pan: sair-sapate de bihtar vikas lai, ih sahooltaan sabandhat khetraan vich viksit kitia jaania chahiia han ate ish lai jantak de naal-naal niji khetra nuun ve isdi agavai karni chahidi hai|
tam: subarulat turai melum nangu valarchiet, ind vasadis andandap bakudikasil membaduttappatt wants, itasku potu manllum taniar ena iruvakait turiganum munipputon seyalpat wants.
tel: paryaton yokk merugan abhivruddhiki, sambandhit prantal lo i saukaryal abhivruddhi cheyali mariyu andukos prabhutva alage praivet rangam margdarshaktva cheyali.
urd: siyaahat kii behatar tarakkee ke liye in saholyat ko mataalika ilaakon main vasit di jani chaheyaawar is ke liye avaam ke saath saath nijee shobe ko bhi aage aana chahiye.
eng: For the better development of tourism, these facilities should be developed in respective areas and for this public as well as the private sector should take a lead.

ben: keralar soundarya royas taar prasanta prakrutite, akshubdh nadeepather pashchadavarti jale, samudrasaikat, pahari jaga, masalar chaas, udvid o pranijagat, ayurveda, nauka daud pratiyogita, prakritik bandar evan aro anek kichu jure.
guj: keralani sundarata teni prashanth prakrutima raheli che, jema shant bekavoters, samudratto, girimthako, masalana vavetaro, vanaspati ane pranisrushti, ayurveda, naukaspardhao, prakritik bandaro ane biju ghanu samavisht che.
hin: kerala kii sundarataa uski shant prakruti ke kaaran he jisamen shaamil he apravahee jal, tat, pahari ilaake, masaalon ke baag, vanaspati or jeev, ayurveda, nauka daud, prakritik bandargah or kaaphi kuch.
kan: keralad saundaryavu nirmalavad shant hinneeru, samudra tirgalu, giridhamagalu, sambar paxarwagal totgalu, sasya hagu pranisankul, ayurveda, doni pandyavaligalu, naisargik bandarugalu muntadavannu olagondiruv ader prashant prakrutialli adkawagide.
mal: prashanthmay kaylukൾ, katൽttiraൾ, hiൽ stationukൾ, sugandhvyanjanattotingoൾ, sasyajantujalanoൾ, aayuർvvet, vallankalikൾ, prakrutidattama turamukhngoൾ tuingivay uൾkkollunn keralatiൻre prasannmay prakrutiil atiൻre sandaryam.
ori: keralar saundharya tahar shaant prakruti, vistrut sthir 'bactors', belabhumi, hil-stesan, masala bagicha, udbhidharaji eban jeevajantu, aajurveda, naukadud, prakritik bandar eban ahuri anek kissire rahichhi.
pan: kerala di sundarta isde shant subhv vich hai, jise vich shant bacwater, bich, pahari station, masaale de baag, vanastpati ate jeev-jantu, ayurveda, kishti dis daudaan, kudrati bandargaha ate hor bohut kujh shaamil hai|
tam: keralavin ankke adan amaitiyana iyaiakaich suolill, suajeel chandhaman pujaikalilum, katankarkalilum, mala nakrangalilum, suvaimanch sedit dottalilum, tawar manllum vilangu inanglilum, ayurvedatil, patakup boaticasilum, ianakait turaimuganglilum innum balavaril atankyluna.
tel: kerala yokk anda dani prashanth prakrutilo undi, nishchalamin bak waters, samudr tiras, hill stasion lu, masala dinusul totel, vriksha jantu sampad, ayurveda, naval poties, sahaj naukashrayas mariyu anno.
urd: kerala kii khubasurati is kii par sukun fitarat main mazamar hai, jis main par sukun bek water, sahil, pahaadi mukaamat, masalhe ke bagat, nibataat va haivaanaat, aivar ved, kushti kii dauden, kudrati bandargahen or bahut kuch shamil hain.
eng: The beauty of Kerala lies in its placid nature, encompassing serene backwaters, beaches, hill stations, spice plantations, flora and fauna, Ayurveda, boat races, natural harbours and more.

ben: atirikt satti shapather sang aanshik ritity grihasthader janya srist hayes.
guj: gruhastho mate saat vadharana vrto sathe aanshik paalan niyath karvama aavyu che.
hin: grihasth logon ke liye aanshik rup se inke paalan ke saath hi saat atirikt vachanon kaa paalan karnaa nirdhaarit he.
kan: grihastharige aanshik palaneyannu vidhislagiddu jotege elu hechuvari vratagaliruttve.
mal: ethe adhikpratijkalumai grihasthark bhagianushilana vidhichittutet.
ori: grihasth manank pin aanshik pason bidhi pranathan karayaishi, sathoti athirikta shapath sahit .
pan: ih pakhpat puuran onha ghar-bar valyan de lai hai jinhan ne hor sat pran lae hoe han I
tam: kudumbh valwil itubaduwargaluku elu koodudal urutimovigaluton intak kaddupadu bakudiahu kuraicopattuldu.
tel: aa grihasthulku adnanga edu niyamalato kudin pakshik anushthananni nirdeshincharu.

eng: The partial observance is laid down for the householders with additional seven vows.

ben: bhanuatu evan saloman dwipapunj prakritik aakarshaner dik die cono anshe kam naya, tave yehetu ei duti desh paryatak kam has sehetu ei anchaler aakarshangulike veshirabhag kshetre yatharth muly dewa has na.
guj: vanatu ane solomon tapus pan tena kudarti aakarshanothi ochhaan nathi, joke e banne deshoma ochhaan pravasio aave che jethi e vistaroni khubi ghanivar ochhi ankay che.
hin: vanuatu or solomone dwipon main bhi prakritik aakarshanon kii koi kami nahin he, lekin chunki in dono deshon main paryatak kam jate hai, isliye in kshetron ke mahatv ko asaliyat se kam aanka gaya he.
kan: vanuatu mattu solaman dwipagallliu prakritik aakarshanegalige anenu korateill; aadagyu, aa eradu deshgaligu kadime pravasigaru baruvudarind, aa pradeshgal uttam tanagalu anek vele kadeganitvaguttave.
mal: vanvaduv solamൻ dvipukal prakrutiille oakർshandooൾk kullvonnumill; ennaൽ i randurajyaൾku kushanera vinodasanjarie labhikunnatinaൽ avitille shraddhakendranoൾk palpposhu vende vil matiarill.
ori: bhanoatu eban soloman dpare madhya prakritik akarshanar kaunsi abhab naahin; teve, yehetu sehi duiti deshaku khuv kam paryletak aasithanthi, sethakar vaishishtvaguik setheta pradhanya pinethae.
pan: vanuatu ate solomon tapu kudrati akarshana vich ait nahi han; parantu kiunki inhan donon deshs bal ait sailaani ounde han, inhan ilakas de pramukh akrshan undard rih jaande han I
tam: vanuwaddu manllum chalaman diugalilum gangaver ianakait dalangalukuk kufaivilly, eninu ivvirandu nadugalukum subaulap bhayanikalin varuki nikarlvil kuraive enpatal ibpakudikalin mukiya subarulat dalangaluku pal chandarppanglil urya mukhiyattuvam kodukkapaduadill.
tel: vanuvatu mariyu di soloman islands kuda sahaj akarshanalku yematra taggavu; ayina, i rend deshalku paryatkulu takkuvaga wastennandun, aa prantal pradhanakarshanal antaga prasiddhi pondaledu.
urd: vaanuto or sulimani jujhair par bhi kudrati praksish mukaamat kii kamee naheen hai; taahim, chunki in dono mamalik main kam siyah ate hain, is liye in ilaakon kii jhulakiyan aksar kam darja bindi kii rahati hain.
eng: Vanuatu and the Solomon Islands are also nowhere near short on natural attractions; however, as both those countries get fewer tourists, the highlights of those areas are often underrated.

ben: krishikajer (anubhumik paddhati) janya atirikt jami dakhle aana evan unnat fasal vyavasthapanar (ullamb paddhati) prayukti yeman uchch falanshil, prayog sada dewa, shakti-nivid, chaap sahanshil prakarer vyabhhar, jalsech vruddhi evan samanvit fasler pushti o surakshar dwara fasal upadne ullekhayogya vruddhi sambhava.
guj: vadharani jameenne kheti hethal lavine (horizental aproch) ane paak vyavasthapanma sudharo (vartikal aproch) lavati takanico jevi ke uchch neepj aapti antar javaabadar, saghan urja, tanav sahan karti jatono upayog, sudhareli sinchai vyavastha, ane sankalit paak poshan ane sanrakshan dwara pakna utpadanma nondhapatra vagharo shakya che.
hin: krishi ke tahat zyaada bhoomi rakh kar (kshaitij drushtikon) or behatar fasal prabandhan takneekon, jaise ki ucch-paidaavaar nivishti-pratikriyasheel, urja-gahan, tanaav-sahishnu vividhtaayen, badi hui sinchai, samanvit fasal poshan or suraksha, (kaaryakshetra drushtikon) kaa prayog karke, fasal utpaadan ko kaaphi had tak badhaayaa ja saktaa he.
kan: hchin bhoomiannu saguvalige ocpadisuvudarind (samatal vidhaan), mattu adhik iluvari niduv, poorikege spandisuv, adhikotpadaneya hagu ottadavannu sahisaball taligalu, hchin niravari, mattu samagr bele poshane hagu rakshaneyantah sudharit bele nirvahana (lamb vidhaan) tantragyanagalind bele utpadaneyalli gananiya pramand hechalvaguvudu sadhayvide.
mal: kututൽ bhumiiൽ krishichatu (tirashchinmay sameepan), nall visheelam naൽkunnatu kututൽ uർjam upyogikunnatu pratikulsahacharyangoൾ tanguvaൻ sheshiyulatumay inateute upyoga, waർdhichch jalsechana, sanyojit vimposhanwu sanrakshanvu tutangia mechchapet villparipalan sarsketikavidy(lambamay sameepan)kalilutyu villkalute utpadanttiൽ saramay waർddhanav sadhyama.
ori: shasya utpadhanare eka brihadakar abhivriddhi chadakaryan nimanthe athirikta jami aniva (bhu-samantaral paddhati) eban unnat shasya parichakana (bhu-lamb paddhati) kaushangudik yatha utkrusht utpadhanaksham nivesh prati anukul, shakti-kaindhrik o chaap-sahishnu prakaargudik, varddhit jatsechan, eban purnang shasya poshan tatha suraksha pradaan dra sambhava .
pan: fasal utpadan vich wadha , hor ilkya nuun kheti- bari (pai pahunch )ate bihtar fasal prabandh (patti pahunch) taknalogya jive ki uddh utpati imput- jawabdeh,urja tiber ate tana nuun bardaast karan valyan kisma, uddh kheti- bari te milli-juli fasal pustikata ate sudkhya naal kinhai I
tam: koodudal nilatai villychaluku udbadudhuatu (parant anukumurai) mulamum, uir makasul, ullittup balan, adddel sevivu manllum uir tangushakti kont bair vakaikalap payanbaduddhudal, nirpasantai adhikarittal, bair uttam manllum bhadukappe orunkinaittal bonthe munneriya bair melanmait tosilnudbanglp payanbadudhuatu (auint anukumurai) mulamum bair urbatty ganiumak adhikarik mudi.
tel: adanpu bhumini sagoku tecchukovata (samantar vidhana) mariyu merugan vyavasay nirvahan ( nitar vidhana), akkuv digubadi ichche, pettubadiki pratispandinche, shakti fivrath kaligi, mariyu vattidini tattukogal rakal, hechchin niti parudal mariyu samikrut sedy poshan mariyu rakshan vanti sanketikatalato pants digubadini gananiyanga penchata sadhyam.
urd: zer kashit azafee arazi (afaqi approach) or fasalon ke behatar intazaam (amodi approach) kii technologyon masalan aala paidavari in pat ke taen muwafiq , tawanai se bharpoor, or tanaav bardaasht karne wali ikssam, aabpashi main azafa, or fasalon kii marabot gazaait or tohfiz ke istemaal se fasalon kii paidavar main khaatir khwaah azafa mumkin hai.
eng: A substantial increase in crop production is possible by bringing additional land under cultivation (horizontal approach) and improved crop management (vertical approach) technologies such as the use of high-yielding input-responsive, energy-intensive, and stress-tolerant varieties, increased irrigation, and integrated crop nutrition and protection.

ben: grahak dalti tader kshetrer madhye baltiqu atke yete deve na.
guj: prapthkarta juthe dadane temana vibhagama padi raheva devo joie nahi.
hin: gend praapt karne vaale dal ko sunishchit karnaa hoga ki gend unki taraf ke court main na rah jaae.
kan: chendannu edurisuv tandvu tamm badiy ankanadodage chendu ulialu bidbaradu.
mal: swikarikunn tea cortiൻre tangute bhagat pant erenera tadinilkaൻ anuvadikkarut.
ori: risibhing dashati baltiku semanank kort madhyare abaruddh hevaku deva aadu uchith nuhen .

guj: em.ti.pe. adhinium 12 athvadiya sudhi garbhapatani vigto aape che, ek registard medical prectishnar (ar.em.pe.)no abhipray jaruri che ane 12 ane 20 athvadiya vachchena garbhapat mate be ar.em.pe.na abhipray jaruri che.
hin: chikitsiya rup se garbh samaapan adhinium ke anusaar, 12 saptaah tak ke garbh kii samaapti ke liye ek ekal panjikrut chikitsak (aar.em.pi.) kii raay aavashyak hogi, or 12 se 20 saptaah ke bich ke garbh kii samaapti ke liye do panjikrut chikitsakon ko apni raay deni hogi.
kan: 12 vargalvaregin krithak garbhapatgalige obb nondayit vaidyar (aar.em.pi) tagnabhipraia aavashyakavagiruttade, mattu 12rind 20 vargal madhyad krithak garbhapatgalige ibbaru aar.em.pi.gal abhipraia aavashyakavagiruttade endu em.ti.pi. kaydeyu vivarisuttade.
mal: 12 archavaraull garbhachvidrattin oreyoru register cheit medical practishanarutayu (ar.e.pi.) 12 mutal 20 vare archakalile garbhachvidrattin rand ar.e.pi. marutayu abhiprayam aavashyamundennu e.ti.pi. akt vyaktamakkunnu.
ori: em.ti.pi. ine pranyjal bhave kahichhi ye 12 saptah paryyant garbhapatgudik pin jane punjikrit pesadar chikitsak (aar.em.pi.)nk mat aavashyak, eban 12 ru 20 saptah paryyant samay madhyare garbhapat pin duijan aar.em.pi.nk mat aavashyak hue.
pan: aim ti pi act verve dinda hai ki 12 hafatia tak di samapati lai, ik single registerd medical practishnar (aar aim pi) di rai di lod hundi hai, ate 12 ton 20 hafatia de wichkaar di samapati lai, doo aar aim pia di rai di lod hundi hai|
tam: 12 varam varilan karuvike kalaikk oreyoru patiuseyyappatt marudarin (arempi) aalochan avasium enllum, 12 muthal 20 varam varilan karuvike kalaikk erandu arempi-kalin aalochan avasium enllum emtipe sattam vivrikkintu.
tel: 12 vaaral varaku tolgimpulaku ockk registerd medical practishanar (arampi) abhiprayam avasarmani, alage 12 nudi 20 vaaral madhya tolgimpulaku iddru arampi la abhiprayam avasarmani antipi chatta vivaristundi.
urd: em tii pii act main bataya gaya hai ki 12 hafton tak ke tabi asqat hamal ke liye ek registerd medical practishnar (aar em pii) kii ray kii zarurat hoti hai, jab ki 12 se 20 hafton ke darmiyaan asqat ke liye, do aar em pii kii ray kii zarurat hoti hai.
eng: The MTP Act details that for terminations up to 12 weeks, the opinion of a single Registered Medical Practitioner (RMP) is required, and for terminations between 12 and 20 weeks, the opinion of two RMPs is required.

ben: mati manchitrer madhye anchalti prakritik bhugol, jalbayu evan udvidsmuh vittik bivinn dharner mati chihnitkaran, barnana evan chithran, jayga gie gaveshanar madhyam nischitkaran o gaveshanagarer tathy evan ek pramanya mul manchitre chithran antarbhukt.
guj: jameen naksha banaavavaama fisiography abohwa ane vistarani vanaspationa aadhare alanlag prakarani jameene ovekhanu varnan ane rekhankan samavisht che, je kshetriya kaarya ane prayogshalani mahiti dwara pushti kare che ane pramarbhut aadhar naksha par nirupit thai che.
hin: bhu-maapan main bhuakriti vigyaan, jalwaayu or us kshetra kii vanaspati, kshetreey adhyayan or prayogshaala ke aankadon ke madhyam se tathaa ek maanak aadharbhoot maanchitr par uske chitrankan dwaara vibhinn prakaar kii mrudaaon kii pahchaan, varnan tathaa rekhankan kii pushti shaamil he.
kan: mannin mapanayu aa pradeshad bhooroopakriti, havaman mattu sasyavargad aadharad mele vividh bageya mannugal patteyhachchuvike, vistrut vivarne hagu nirupane, kshetrakaarya hagu prayogalyad dattanshad moolak drisikaran mattu pramanabaddhavaad tarnaksheyondaralli chitrisuvudannu olagondide.
mal: physiography, pradeshte kalavasth, sasyajalas, fild varkilutayull sthirikara, laborttery data ennivyu oru manak atisthan mappilutayull chitrikaranvu atisthanmaki vividhinum mannuute tirichorialu vivaranvu rekhikaranvu ulppettata soil mapping.
ori: mrittika manachithranre bhu-prakruti, jalbatou, eban samprukt anychantir brikshaltaku bhitti kari vibhinna prakaarar mrittikar chihnatikaran, varnan, eban chitran, kshetrakaryan eban gaveshanagarar tatha madhumare satyapan eban eka manak mul manachitre chitra-upasthapan prabhruti antarbhukt .
pan: bhumi di naksha-navis vich us di pachan,varnan te alag kism di miti da rekhankit karna ounda hai jo ki prakirti,jalavayu ate ilaake di vanastpati , khetra karge ton pushti te prayogshala de ankde ate satar mul nakshe te darsauna te nirbhar karada hai I
tam: mannial diddavarpadom enpatil, woru bagudiin nilak gutarial, vanil manllum davrangs adippatail vevveru man vakaikals inanganudal, vivarittal manllum vacaprittal, kauppani manllum aywakat druvu mulam urudipatudhudal, niyamman adippati varaipattil chittarittal akhiyawe atankum.
tel: mrittika lakshanchitranalo bhautikshastramu, vatavaranmu mariyu aa prantaloni vriksha sampad aadharanga vibhinn rakaal matti gurtimpu, vivaran mariyu varnan, kshetrasthai pani mariyu prayogshal dattanshm dwara nirdharan mariyu pramanic patampai chitrikaran untai.
urd: mitti kii nakshaa sazi mukhtalf kasam kii mitiyon kii shinaakht, tafsil or had bindi jo ilaka kii arji shuklayat, aab va hawa or nibataat par mibani hoti hain, maidani kaam or liboritry ke adaad va shumar ke zarie tasadiq or ek mayaari buniyadi nakshe par dikhaae jane par mushtamil hai.
eng: Soil mapping comprises the identification, description and delineation of different kinds of soils based on physiography, climate and vegetation of the area, confirmation through fieldwork and laboratory data and depicting on a standard base map.

guj: anathi rasayan mukt krushi taraf sarv sambandhitonu dhyaan kendrit thayu che, jema sajiv kheti ane jameen ane paryavaranne sudharti, punarjivitha karti ane punarsthapit karti takanicono samavesh thai che.
hin: isse sabhi sambandhit logon kaa jaivik kheti, mrudaa evam paryaavaran ko punarthik karne, usamen dobaaraa praan bharne or durust karne kii takneekon sahit rasayan-mukt krishi par dhyaan kendrit hua he.
kan: idu sambandhapatt ellaru savyav krishi mattu mannu hagu parisarvannu punah swasthigolisuv, marujeevantagolisuv, mattu poorvasthitige taruv vidhangainnu olagondante rasayanik-mukt krishiedege gamnvannu kendrikarisuvante madide.
mal: it jaivakrushi uൾppeteyull rasarahit krishiik, mannu paristatyu veendedukkukayu punarujjivipikkayu purvvastatilakkukyu cheiyunn ritikalilak bandhappet ellavarutayu kendrikrutshraddh konduvannitesnd.
ori: eha samasthankar kendrit dhyanku rasarhnikapaxarwa-mukt krushi prati udgn karithila, yeunthireki jaivik krushi, eban mrittika o pariveshar punaruddhar, punarujjeeban tatha punavasthapan karibar kaushangudik antarbhukt thila .
pan: ish ne dhiaan rasayan mukat kheti jise vich jaivik kheti ate oh taknika oundis han jo miti te watavarna nuun swas, changa ate suramtkarana bana sake us bal sabh da dhiaan khich lya hai I
tam: adanbin 11.04.2019 andu manilach sattasabait terdal natabeantu enllum, thiru oi. jaganmohan reddy 30.05.2019 andu muthalmicharagap padvienneru urutimophi edutdhar enllum munwaixpadukintu.
tel: sambandhinchin warandari drushtini, sendriya vyavasayanto batu rasayan rahit sedyam mariyu bhumi mariyu vatavaranas punaruddharinchi, punarujjivamu chessi, punasthapinche sanketik prakriyal vapu aakarshinchindi.
urd: is ne chemicliz se paak kaashtkaaree , bishmol namyati kaashtkaaree , or aisi takneekon kii taraf tamaam mataalika afarad kii tawaja mbbool karwai hai jo mitti or maahaul kii baazyabi, ehya or bahaali krati hain.
eng: This has brought focused attention of all concerned towards chemical-free farming, including organic farming, and techniques that recover, revitalize, and restore the soil and the environment.

ben: 2014-e, sarkar vima vibhag bideshi binioger uparisima 26% thek barie 49% kare dies .
guj: 2014maa vima kshetra sarkaare videshi rokanani uchchatam maryaada 26 %thi vadharine 49 % kari.
hin: 2014 main sarkaar ne beemaa kshetra main videshi nivesh kii upree seemaa 26 pratishat se badha kar 49 pratishat kar di.
kan: 2014ralli, sarkaarvu vimaa valayadalli videshi hoodikeya garisht mitiannu 26%ind 49%ge erisitu.

pan: sarkaar ne 2014 vich, videshi nivesh di uprali had, nivesh khetra vich 26% ton 49% kar diti I
tam: arasu 2014il kaffeeddut turain ayalak mudalittu ucch warumbai 26%-lirundhu 49% awk uyartylldu.
tel: 2014lo, prabhutvan bimaa ranganlo videshi pettubadul garisht parimitini 26% nudi 49%ku penchindi.
urd: 2014 main, hukuumat ne anshurnce sector main gair milki saramy kari kii balai had ko 26 faisad se badhaa kar 49 faisad kridya.
eng: In 2014, the government increased the foreign investment upper limit from 26% to 49% in the insurance sector.

ben: uparntu, nirbharayogya o samaimato anuman evan marshumi shasyer mott kheter pariman o upadan anumanguli aamdani/raptani, muly nirdharan evan gana bantner mato bipanan kaushal rupayner kshetre gurutvapurna.
guj: vadhuma, vishwasaniya ane samaysarna andajo ane mosemi pakna vavetar vistaro ane utpadan andajo aayat/nikaas, mulya nirdharan ane jaher vitaran jevi vechan vyuharchana banaavavaa mate agatyana che.
hin: iske atirikt, niryaat/aayaat, keemat niyatan evam saarvajanik vitaran jaisi vipanan sambandhi ranneetiyon ko taiyaar karne ke liye bharosemand or samayik rup se kiye anumaan evam mausam ke anusaar vishisht fasalon ko ugane kaa kshetrafal tathaa utpaadan ke anumaan mahatvapurn hai.
kan: ader jotege, raptu/amadu, bele nigadi, mattu sarvajanik vitarneyantah marukatteya kaaryatantragarhnnu roopisuvalli vishwasarh hagu sakalikavad andajugalu mattu kalanugunavad belegal ekare pradesh hagu utpadaneya andajugalu mukhyavaguttave.
mal: atinupurame, vishwastvu kalikavumay astimetukൾ, seasenukainusrichull krishibhumivistiർnnattiൻreyu utpadanttiൻreyu astimetukൾ enniv kayatumati/iokkumati, vilaniർnnayam, potuvithara tutangiyavayute vipananatantransൾ roopikarikunnatiൽ pradhana.
ori: adhikanthu, bharsayogya eban samayochit aakalan tatha ritukalin fasal heuthiva jamir pariman eban utpadan aakarnagudik raptani/aamdani, mool nirddharan, eban sarvajanin vitaran bhadi bipanan yojnagujaikar prasnuti nimanthe guruthpurna ate .
pan: ish ton ilava, bharosesand ate samen sir mosmi fasalas da rakba ate utpadan de anuman marketing rannitia jiven ki aayat/niryat, kimat nirdhaaran, ate jantak vand nuun banaun lai mahatavpuuran han|
tam: itutvir, ettrumati/ishakkumati, vil nirnayam, potu vineogam bonthe sandai mulobhayangss uruvakk, nambekaman, kalatukurya madipidugalum ekker vit paruvap bair urbhatti manllum makasul madipidugalum mukhiamakum.
tel: adnanga, nammadgin, samayochit anchanal, alage kalangun pants vistirna mariyu digubadi anchanal anevi agumati/digumati, dhar sthirikaran mariyu praja pampini vanti marketing vyuhas roopondinchukodaniki mukhyamainavi.
urd: is ke alaava, kaabil itmad or bruqt takhmaine or mausami fasal ke rakbe or paidavar ke takhmaine marketing kii hukmat amliyon kii tashkeel jese baramad/darhamad, keemton kaa tain or awami taqasim kari ke liye ahim hain.
eng: In addition, reliable and timely estimates and seasonal crop acreage and production estimates are important for the formulation of marketing strategies such as export/import, price fixation, and public distribution.

ben: 2014 saler kamanoelth gemase mahilader 55 keji freestyle vibhager quarter final babitar pratham pratipaksh chhil skatlander cathrin marsh yake se 92, 40 (shrenivinyas paent 4:1)-e prajeet kare.
guj: 2014ni rashtramandal ramatotsavani mahilao mateni freestil 55 kiloni kakshani quarters-finalsma babitano pahelo muqabalo skotlendna catherine marsh saame thayo hato, jene babitae 92 - 40 thi haravi hati. (vargikaran gun 4:1)
hin: 2014 ke rashtramandal khelon main mahilaon ke 55 ki.gra. ke freestil varg ke quarter final main, babita kii pehali pratidwandvi scotland kii catherine marsh thi jise usne 92, 40 (vargeekaran ank 4:1) se haraaya tha.
kan: 2014r kamanvealth kridakutadalli mahileyar 55 ke.ji. freestyle vibhagad quarter fainelsnalli babitar modal eduraliagidd scotlandin kathryn marshrannu aake 92, 40 antaradalli (vargikaran ankagalu 4:1) solisidru.
mal: 2014 komanvalt gainsile streeute 55 kilogram vibhagattille fri stailinte kwartor final babitute aadya ethiraliairunn scotlandinte catherine marshin avar 92, 40 n (clasiphikeon point 4:1) parajaypetutti.
ori: 2014 kamanelath khel mahila frishtil 55ke.ji. vargra, krter-finalsaare bavithank pratham pratidndh thile skatlandra karin marsh, yahanku se 92, 40 marginare harithile (bargeekaran paent 4:1) |
pan: 2014 di rashtramandal kheds vich mahilanwan di freestile 55 kilogram shreni vich babitha di pahilaan vihakh kuarter final vich skatland di catherine marsh see, jise nuun os ne 92, 40 (vargikaran ank) naal hararia see I
tam: 2014 kamanwelt boatisil 55 kilos magalir freestyle brivin kalirudip botiil babidaudan botipott muthal virangan scotlandin ketrin marsh, avarai babita 92, 40 (vakipadutal pulligus 4:1) enjh ganakil tolkadithar.
tel: 2014 kamanvalt games lo mahill 55 kejil freestiles vibhaganlo, quarter fanelsulo babit tan toli pratyarthi ayin skatland ku chendin kethrin marsh nu 92, 40 to odinchindi (4:1 vargikaran points).
urd: 2014 ke kaaman velth gamiz main khwatin ke free staele 55 kilogram zamre main, babita kii pahali harif scot land kii catherine marsh thim, jinhen unhon ne 92, 40 (darja bindi points 4:1) se shikast di.
eng: In the women's freestyle 55kg category at the 2014 Commonwealth Games, Babita's first opponent in the quarter-finals was Kathryn Marsh of Scotland, whom she beat 92, 40 (classification points 4:1).

ben: bayojyeshtha plini yoga karen ye parikalpit durtvati chhil 12 kilometer (7.5 mil) evan uddeshyati chhil cesterya evan harmiya upsagarer madhye sanyog sthapan karte sthalsandhir madhye die ekati khaal kata.
guj: plini dha elder umere che ke ayojit antar bar kilometrs (7.5 mile) hatu ane teno hetu kesatriyan ane hermaen akhato jorti bhoomi par naher banaavavaano hato.
hin: plini da elder ne yah bhi kaha ki niojit duuri 12 kilometre (7.5 mile) kii thi or iskaa uddeshy castrian or harmein khadi ko jodne ke liye thalsandhi main nahar banane kaa tha.
kan: hiriyavanad plainiyu yojit antaravu 12 kilometer (7.5 maili) agittu mattu cestrian mattu harmian colligannu samparkislu ismas mukhantar ondu kaluveyannu toduvudu idar uddeshvagittu endu heluttane.
mal: paddhtit durm 12 kilometre (7.5 mile) irunnuvennu, atine uddeshya istmasilute oru canal wetti keystrian uൾkkatalineyu hermian ulkatalineyu bandhippikkayairunnuvennu plini da elder kuticherrkunnu.
ori: plinee di elur ahuri kahiyanthi ye yojana karayaithiva duratti 12 ki.mi. thila (7.5 mayil), eban uddeshya thila kaestrian eban harmian upasagaraku sanyukt kariva nimanthe sankeerna sthalbhagati madhyadei eka canal khoshiva .
pan: palini da ailder hor jysada hai ki viuntia faasala 12 kilometre (7.5 mile) see, ate udesh see ki cestarian ate harmian khadia nuun jodan lai isthmas vichon nahir khodi jaae |
tam: ditamitapatt turam 12 kilometre (7.5 mile) eneum nilachandin valiyakak kalwai vetti gastrion manllum harmion valaikudass inippate its nogkum enllum mutt flaini gurinar.
tel: pranalik veyabadd dur 12 kilometre (7.5 mai) ani mariyu kastrian mariyu hirmian akhatal kalapatanii i kanthbhumi gunda ock kaluvanu tolchata vaari uddeshya ani, plini di elder adnanga cheptar.
urd: plani bujurg majid bataata hai ki mansuba band faasla 12 kullu meter (7.5 mail) tha, or is kaa maqsad asthms ke darmiyaan ek nahar kaatna tha taaki castrin or harmein khalijon ko joda jaa sake.
eng: Pliny the Elder adds that the planned distance was 12 kilometres (7.5 mi), and the purpose was to cut a canal through the isthmus to connect the Caystrian and Hermaean bays.

mal: ikcharyattil shraddh want, karea, oru indian visa pross cheit angikarichukavignal apekshil parankirikkunn i-mail adressila at nerit ayakcook.
ori: daakari e vishamati upare madhya satark rahive, karan gotie bharatiya visa yanch hoi anumodan pila pare, eha aavedan patrare diayaithiva i-mel thikanaku sidha pathai diayib.
pan: cripa kar ke ish baare ve dhiaan rakho, kiunki jadon bharati vizaa processd ate pravaanit on ton bood, ih aplikeshan te dite gaye i-mail pate te sidha bhejia janda hai.
tam: ind vishyatil nings rompak kavanmak irukk wants, india visavukkan puraces mudindu abruv anatum nings kodutrukkum minnenjal mughavariku atu neradiak anuppapatum.
tel: dini vishyanlo kuda meeru jagrathtaga undali, andukante bharat visa prakria purtyi aamodinchabaddak, danni darkhastulo ichchin imaile address ki neruga pampada jarugutundi.
urd: brah meharabaani is ke baare main bhi mohataat rahiin, is liye ki jab ek hindustani vese kii carrwai or manzooree ho jaati hai to use brah rasat darkhwaast par diye gaye e mail edres par bhej diya jataa hai.
eng: Please be careful about this too, as when an Indian visa has been processed and approved, it will be sent directly to the email address given on the application.

ben: prayuktigat agragati madhyam aasa parishilita evan paribartan ya taar paridhik aro prasaarit kareque, era paripreekshite media bartaman janamat gadhner janya ekati pruthak charitra arjan kareque.

hin: takneekee unnateekaran ke chalate media main ai visheshgyata or parivartan se uski pahunch itani bad gai he ki media ne ab janamat ko prabhavit karne kii ek vishisht bhoomika le lee he.
kan: madhyamd vyaptiannu mattashtu vishalgolisiruv tantragyanad belvanigegalind untad atyadhunikte mattu marpatinindagi madhyamvu indu sarvajanik abhiprayavannu roopisuv visisht gunawannu gariside.
mal: sarsketikapurogati konduvann parishkarslalu parivർttanalalu kututൽ vishalmay vyapti nedia madhyamangoൾ potujanabhiprayam rupappetuttunnatiൽ oru verit swabhava kaivaricchittund.
ori: vaishaik agragathi dra missithiva vishesh gyan eban roopantaran yogun ehar pahanchaku ahuri samprasarit kariparithiva ganamadhum, aaji janamataku prabhavita karibar eka stantra kshamta hasal karichhi .
pan: takneeki tadakia vich aadhu ate tabdilia de on naal jan sanchar madhium ik ahija roop ban gya hai jo aam locals di rai nuun badal sakda hai I
tam: tosilnutp mambadus mulam ettptt panmukh valarchi manllum mushumating balanal utagangs melum virivakas senttindhu potu makalin karuddai vativipatil woru tanippangu ashrukintu.
tel: sanketik purogti tisukuvachchin navikaran mariyu parivartanato tam paridhul vistarinchukunn media, nedu prajabhiprayanni rupudidde pratyek lakshananni santarinchukunnadi.
urd: takneekee tarakiyon ke jaria laaye jane waale nafast or tabadeli, jis ne apni rasai ko majid vasia kridya hai, ke pesh nazar media ne aaj ray aama ko dhaalane kaa ek makhsus kirdaar haasil kiya hai.
eng: Given the sophistication and transformation brought in by the technological advancements that have further widened its reach, media has acquired a distinctive character of molding public opinion today.

ben: krantiya mousumi jalbayu sah asom halo natishitoshna (grishma sarbochch 95° - 100° fahrenheit baa 35° - 38° centegrade evan sheeta sarvanimn 43° - 46° fahrenheit baa 6° - 8° centegrade) evan bhari vrushtipat o uchch ardrata bhog kare.
guj: ushnakatibandhiya yomasani abohwa sathe assam samshitoshna wapamana (unalama vadhuma vadhu 95 anshthi 100 aansh pheranhit athva 35 anshthi 38 aansh centegrade ane shiyalama ochhama ochhu 43 anshthi 46 aansh pheranhit athva 6 anshthi 8 aansh centegrade) ane bhaare varsaad ane uchch bhejwalu vatavaran dharave che.
hin: ushnkaribandheey monsoon jalwaayu hone ke kaaran assam samshitoshna he (jahaan garmiyon kaa adhiktam taapmaana 95° - 100° fahrenheit yaa 35° - 38° celsius tathaa sardiyon main 43° - 46° fahrenheit 6° - 8° celsius he) or yahan baari varsha or ucch ardrata rahati he.
kan: ushnavalayad malegalad havamanadondige asam samashitoshnavagiddu (besigeyalli garisht 95°-100° fya. athwa 35°-38° se. mattu chaligaldalli kanishth 43°-46° fya. athwa 6°-8° se.) bhaari male mattu ati ardrateyannu anubhavisuttade.
mal: assamille ushnamekhalakalavarshkalavasth mitmatu (venlkalat et kututal 95° - 100° farൻheat, athva 35° - 38° sellshyasu shaityakalat 43° - 46° farൻheat, athva 6° - 8° sellshyasu) kanatt makyu ucrnn irppavu ulatumakunnu.
ori: krantiya maushmi jalbatou rahithiva assam heudi nathisheetoshna (greeshma sarvadhik 95° - 100° pharenhit kimba 35° - 38° celciusre o sheeta sarvanimn 43° - 46° pharenhit or 6° - 8° celciusre) eban ethare prabal bristipat tatha adhik ardratha anubhut hoithaye .
pan: taptkhandi monsoon rut de naal, assam da mousam sanjami hai (garamia da uddh ton uddh 95° - 100° F jaaa 35° - 38° C ate sial vich ait ton ait 43° - 46° F or 6° - 8° C) ate bhaari varkha te uch nami anubhav karada hai I
tam: wepamandalab paruvamalaich chitoshanam kont assamil mitman tadbhaveppam ulldu (kodai kalatil adhikapatsam 95° - 100° ef alltu 35° - 38° chi manllum kulirkalatil kurainthapatsam 43° - 46° ef alltu 6° - 8° chi), adevele balatt manipovium mikunth irappathamum nilavukintu.
tel: ushnmandaliya varsh vatavarananto, assam samashitoshnanga (vesavilo gari. 95° - 100° pha. leda 35° - 38° sain. mariyu shitakalamlo kani. 43° - 46° pha. leda 6° - 8° sain.) undi, adhik varshpata pondutu, adhik tem kaligi untundi.
urd: haari monsoon kii aab va hawa ke saath, assam matidal rahata hai (mausam garma main besh trin 95 digree - 100 digree forn hite yaa 35 digree - 38 digree celsius or mausam surma main aqil trin 43 digree - 46 digree forn hite yaa 6 digree - 8 digree celsius) or shadid barish or aala nami kaa saamana kurta hai.
eng: With the tropical monsoon climate, Assam is temperate (summer max. at 95° - 100° F or 35° - 38° C and winter min. at 43° - 46° F or 6° - 8° C) and experiences heavy rainfall and high humidity.

tam: intak khandadhin kiskuk kotiil ull pal malikes erimalikalak ulsana, melum indonesiaum kamsadgaoum nichaymak dalisirent erimal subarulat dalanglak irukkinsona.

eng: Many mountains in the easternmost parts of the continent are volcanic, and Indonesia and Kamchatka are indeed great destinations for volcanic tourism.
