ben: 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000) evan 1314 (2000)-era nirna anusmaran karaar pare, 2000 saler 31she october jatisangha nirapatta parishad dwara sarvasmmatikram naari, shanti o nirapattar upar jatisangha nirapatta parishader 1325 (es/aar.i.es/1325) nirna newa hayesil.
guj: sankalp 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000) ane 1314 (2000) paachha khenchi levaya bad streeo, shanti ane salaamati vishena sanyukt rashtra suraksha parishadana sankalp 1325 (es/ar.i.es./1325)ne yu.en.ni salaamati smiti dwara 21 october 2000na roj sarvanumate apnavavaama aavyo hato.
hin: 31 oktober, 2000 ko, sankalp 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000), or 1314 (2000) ko waapas lete hue, sanyukt raashtra suraksha parishad ne mahilaon, shanti, or suraksha par sankalp 1325 (es/aar.i.es./1325) ko sarvasammati se angeekrut kiya.
kan: you.en. bhadrata mandaliyu 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000), mattu 1314 (2000) i nirnayagainnu himpaded nantar 2000da october 31randu, mahileyaru, shanti mattu bhadrateya vishayavagi vishv sansthey bhadrata mandali nirnay 1325 (es./aar.i.es./1325) idannu sarvanumatdind angikarisitu.
mal: 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000), 1314 (2000) enni prameyas pinvalichgatinushes 2000 oketober 31n yu.en. rakshasmiti stree, samadhan, suraksh enni vishayaecurichull aikyarashtrasabharakshasmitiprameyam 1325 (es./ar.i.es / 1325) ekakanthamai swikarichu.
ori: mahila, shanthi, eban suraksha sambandhiya sanyukt jati sangha nirapatta parishader prastaab 1325 (es./aar.i.es./1325)ti, poorb prastaab 1261 (1991), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000), eban 1314 (2000) sabuku samaran kari, 31 october 2000re jati sangha nirapatta parishad dra sarvasammathi krame gruhith hela.
pan: sanyukat rashtra sudkhya prishd da mataa 1325 (S/RES/1325), jo ki sanyukat rashtra sudkhya prishd duara aurataan di shanti ate sudkhya baare hai, mate 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000) ate 1314 (2000) nuun mud vichaaran magron 31 october 2000 nuun sarab-sanwati naal apnaia gya see |
tam: pengal, amaiti manllum bhadukafu kuritt ikiya nadus bhadukoppuch sabain dirmanam 1325 (es/aries/1325) 31 october 2000 andu 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000),1314 (2000) aakhiya dirmanangalait thirumpub penichu pingu aina bhadukoppuch sabaiyal orumanatak attrukkolpattatu.
tel: 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000) mariyu 1314 (2000) tirmanas raddu chacin tarvat, 2000 october 31na yu an bhadrata mandali mahiies, shanti, bhadratalku sambandhinchin aikyarajyasmiti bhadrata mandali tirmana 1325 (ass/aries/1325)nu ekagrivanga aamodinchindi.
urd: khwatin, aman, or salaamati ke baare main ikvam matahda kii salaamati konsil kii qarardad 1325 (es/aar e es/1325), 31 aktubar 2000 ko ikvam matahda salaamati konsil ne qarardadon 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296(2000) or 1314 (2000) ko waapas karne ke baad, matafiq tuur par manzoor kiya.
eng: United Nations Security Council Resolution 1325 (S/RES/1325), on women, peace, and security, was adopted unanimously by the UN Security Council on 31 October 2000, after recalling resolutions 1261 (1999), 1265 (1999), 1296 (2000), and 1314 (2000).

ben: rajya nodal sansthaguli (es.in.e) raje sarvajanin charjing centra basano, parichalana o rakshanavekshan kara evan battary adalabdal/charjing suvidhar vastawayanakari sanstha nirvachan karte adeshprapth.
guj: state nodel agensione (es.en.e.) rajyama sarvajnik charging station ane betary badalav/charging suvidhao sthapava, chalaavavaa ane jalvavaa mate amalkarta agencio pasand karvi farjiyat che.
hin: rajya nodel agenciyon (es.en.ez.) ko karyanvayan karne vaale aise sanghathanon ko anubandhit karne hetu chunane kaa adhikaar he jo rajya main saarvajanik charging steshnon or bydaree kii adla-badali/charging suvidhaon ko taiyaar karenge, chalaayenge, or banaae rakhenge.
kan: rajyadalli sarvajanik charjing kendragalu mattu swaping/charjing saukaryagal sthapane, sanchalane mattu nirvahaneyannu kaaryagatagolisuv agensigainnu aaykemadlu rajya nodal agensigalige (es.en.e.galu) aadeshislagide.
mal: sansthant potuvay chaർjing stationulu, batory maranu chaർj cheyyanumulla samvidhanau sthapikanu natattanu sanrakshikanu pravർttikkunn ejൻsie terangedukkaൻ state nodeൽ ejൻsi(es. eൻ. e)kalot niർdeshichittund.
ori: rajya nodal sanstha (es.en.e.) gudiku sarvajanin charjing stesanman tatha baterry badalaiva/ charj kariva subidhagudik sthapan, parichakana eban anurakshan kariva nimanthe karyankaari kariva sansthagudiku chanyan kariva pin nirddesh diayaishi .
pan: state nodal agencys (se.na.e) nuun laazami hai ki oh lagu karan vaali ejansia nuun chun ke lagu karan,chalaun ate sarvajanik charging stere nuun kym rakhan te raj vich batree badalan/charge di suvidha hove I
tam: manilatil potu charjing nilias manllum battery maderudal/charjing maiyangana niruvaum iakaum paramricum paniniraivenuchu muhamaikalait terndedukkumaru manilat dunaimaiy muhamiluku (esene-gus) uttaravidapattuldu.
tel: sarvajnik charging steshani mariyu byattrin marpidi chesukune/charging chesukune sadupayas nelakolpi, nadipi, konsaginche nirvahana agensi state nodel agencis (ass an elu) tappanisariga anchukovalsi untundi.
urd: riyasati noodele agensiyon (es en ez) ko riyasat main awami charjung stishno or bydaree kii tabadalaa/charjung saholyat ko install karne, chalaane or barkaraar rakhane ke lipaamil darhamad karne wali agensiyon kaa intakhaab karne kaa paaband kiya gaya hai.
eng: State Nodal Agencies (SNAs) are mandated to select implementing agencies to install, operate and maintain public charging stations and battery swapping/charging facilities in the state.

ben: 1835 christabd nagad maharaj ranjit sinher daner fale nanded-e ekati apurv sunder gurudwara nirmit has yeti sukshma khodaier kaaj sah ekati manorath swarna gambuj sambolit.
guj: maharaja ranjit singhna prayasane karne nandedma i.sa. 1835ni aasapaas ek khubasurat ane mantramugdh kartaan gurudwaranu bandhkam thayu, jema ek aakarshak zainee kotarnivalo suvarn gumbaj che.
hin: maharaja ranjit singh ke daan ke kaaran 1835 i. ke aas-paas nanded main ek sundar or asaadhaaran gurudware kaa nirmaan hua jisamen jatil nakkashi vaala ek bhavy swarna gumbad he.
kan: maharaj ranjit singan dattiindagi kri.sha. 1835r sumarige nandednalli sankirna kettnayull bhavyavad chinnad gummatvannu hondiruv ondu sundaravaad mattu vismayagolisuvanth gurudwaravu nirmangonditu.
mal: nandediൽ etand 1835l sankiർkanmay kottupanikalulla gambhiraswarnamakutattotukootia manoharavu ativismayakaravumay oru gurudwaraute niർmmanattin maharaja ranjit sindiൻre sambhavan upakarichu.
ori: maharaaja ranjith sing sampatthi danakariva falre nandeda thare, 1835 masiha pakhapakhi, eka sundar o chittakarshak gurudra nirman hoithila, yeunthire sukshma karukaryan mandit eka vishal suvarna gambuja rahichhi.
pan: maharaja ranjit singh di pratibha heth nainded vich 1935 i de lag - bhaga ik khubasurat te shaandar guruduvara di usari hoi jise da alishan gumbad see jise upar pechida ukaran kitha hoia see I
tam: maharaaja ranjit singh alitt kodyin balanak sumar kibe 1835il nandadile nutpamagach sedukuel seyyappatt pramandaman pon madem vikeell ore aukana, manatike kollacolkits gurudwara katoppattatu.
tel: ranjit singh maharaja viralam vall nanded lo kii she 1835 prantalo, sunnithmin chekkadalato kudin ock gambhirmin bengar gopuram kaligin andmains mariyu vismayam kaliginche gurudwara nirmana jarigindi.
urd: maharaja ranjit singh ke itiye se 1835 ke aas pas nanded main nafis nakashi waale ek khubasurat or dilkash gurudwara kii tamir amal main aai jis main ek azim ulishan sunahari ganbd tha.
eng: Maharaja Ranjit Singh's endowment saw the construction of a beautiful and breathtaking Gurudwara featuring an imposing golden dome with intricate carving at Nanded around 1835 A.D.

ben: drut baler aadan-pradaanta chalate thake yekhane prati dalke tinti ekatana tacher anumati dewa has yatakshan na kono ekata dal pratipksher cort balti phele jite yachche baa kono dal bhuler masul die here yachche.
guj: reli chaalu rahe che, pratyek joothane sabhang tran sparsha sudhini manjuri aapavama aave che, jyaan sudhi koi jooth pratispardhina medan par dadane jameenbhego kare che ane reli jiti jaaya che athva koi jooth bhul kare che ane reli haari jaaya che.

mal: oro timu ethir corttle pant take vintti rally netukayo oru tet varutti rally nashtappetuttukayo cheiyuvare, tutraull paramavadhi munn sparshas anuvadichirikkunn vidhttil rally tutrunnu.
ori: raliti jari rahe, yeunthireki pratyeka dashaku thinoti kramik sparsh paryyant anumati diayaaye, yeparynant eka dal baltiku pratipakshank kortku parichalit karen eban ralitiku jithithaye, kimba eka dal kaunsi bhul karithaye eban ralitiku haari yaithaye .
pan: rally jari rehindi hai ate harek team nuun tin tch di manazuuri hundi hai jad tak koi ik team vihakh de court vich geind nahi suit dindi jaaa team koi ik galti kar dendi hai ate oh rally haare jaande han I
tam: woru ani bandai aditu atu edir aniin kaqtil dharaidottu rallie wellum varai alltu dhawarisaittu ralliil dorekum varai reilli toterum, itel ovvoru anikkum adhikapatsamak moondau murai bandait dot anumatikkapadukintu.
tel: prati jattuki varusga mod sar takidulu anumatinchabadi, edo ock jattu bantini avatali jattu cortulo nelamid petti ryalini gelichevraku leda ock jattu ock tappida chessi ryalini oripoyevarku, i ryali konsagutundi.
urd: reli jari rahati hai, har tem ko lagaataar teen tich tak kii izzaazat di jaati hai, jab tak ki koi tem mukhaalf ke court main gend kii buniyaad naheen rakhti or reli jeet jaati hai yaa koi tem kisi galati kaa artikab krati hai or reli haar jaati hai.
eng: The rally continues, with each team allowed up to three consecutive touches, until either a team grounds the ball on the opponent's court and wins the rally or a team commits a fault and loses the rally.

ben: 2019 nagad ji antartainment antarpraiges limitid (jed.i.i.el) chhil essel goshthir ekamatra labh-upadak sanstha; sarvamot 20,000 koti (2020-te 21,000 koti baa 260 koti markin dollarer samatul) run punjibhuth kare goshthiti.
guj: 2019 sudhi, jhi anterteinament anterprizis limited (jhil) e essel grupani aekmatra nafo ralti company hati; aa grupe lagbhag 20,000 karohu devu ekatrit karyu hatu (je 2020maa 210 biliyan athva 2.6 biliyan yu.es. dollar barabar che.)
hin: 2019 main acel samooh main keval zee antertenment enterprijej li. (zeel) hi laabh dene vaali company thi; samooh kaa samgr karj lagbhag 20,000 karod tha (2020 main yah 210 billian ke baraabar yaa 2.6 billian amareeki dollar ke baraabar tha).
kan: 2019r hottige, zi entertaenment enterpraiss li. (jhead.i.i.el.) essel samooh sansthey ekik labhadayak companiagittu; samooh sanstheyu ottare sumaru 20,000 kotigalshtu salavannu hondittu (2020ralli 210 shatakoti athwa you.es. $2.6 shatakotige sam).
mal: 2019 ayatote si eൻraർtiൻmeൻr eൻraർprisus limitod (sed i i eൽ ) irunnu esseൽ groupyൻre labhamuntakkunn oreyoru company; groupyൻre motta kat ekadesha 20,000 koti (210 bilyanino 2020ൽ 2.6 bilyൺ yu. es dollarino tulyamay) aai kunnukutiirunnu.
ori: 2019 suddha, 'ji' entartenment entarprijes li.' (ji'l) thila 'esel grup'r ekamatra labhajanak company; ehi gostheeti motamoti 20,000 koti (2020re 21000 koti ba $260 koti americiya dollar sahit saman) r run karithila .
pan: 2019 tak, zee entertenment entarprijas limited (zeel) asal group di ikloti labh-pidi company see; jisane lagabhaga 20,000 karod (2020 vich 210 billion jaaa amareeki dollars $2.6 billion de barabar) da samsacha karza idhetha kita see|
tam: 2019il jee enderdainment enderprisas limited (jetigel) mattume essal kulumatin one lapamittum niruvanmak irundatu, andak kulumam otumottamak sumar 20,000 koti (210 billion alltu america $2.6 billionuku nikarantu) gadanpatrundatu.
tel: 2019 nati, ji entertainment enterpryces limited (jil) escell vanijya sansthaki labhas gadinche ekac companiga undindi; aa sansthaki perukupoin run motta dadapu 20,000 kots (idi 2020 lo 210 billian leda yues $2.6 billian ku samana).
urd: 2019 tak, zi intertainment interprizez lametre (zed e e el) asal group kii vaahid munaafaa paida karne wali company thi; is group ne takreeban 20,000 karod (2020 main 210 blin yaa 2.6 blin america dollar ke barabar) majamuai karz jamaa kiya tha.
eng: By 2019, Zee Entertainment Enterprises Ltd. (ZEEL) was the Essel Group's only profit-generating company; the group had accumulated an overall debt of around 20,000 crores (equivalent to 210 billion or US $2.6 billion in 2020).

ben: raaga, rangila chaupadi, ityadir upar vitti kara bhajan, janan evan oriya gangulike halaka shastriya sangeeter madhye shrenivaddha kara has, ya oriya sangeeter ekati gurutvapurna vibhag tiri kare.
guj: bhajan, janan ane raaga aadharit oria gito, rangila chaupadi vagere mali halvu shastriya sangeet bane che; je oria sangitanu mahatvanu paasu bane che.
hin: bhajan, janan, or raagon par aadhaarit oriya geet, rangila chaupadi, aadi ko halke shastreey sangeet ke tahat samoohikrut kiya jaataa he, jo oriya sangeet kaa ek pramukh anubhag he.
kan: bhajan, janan, mattu ragagainnu adhrisid oriya hadugalu, rangila chapadi muntadavannu oriya sangitad mukhya bhagavagiruv laghu shastriya sangeetdadialli vargikarislagide.
mal: bhajnu jannu ragadhishthit odiyaganau rangila chapadi tutangiyavayu odiasangitatine oru pradhanvibhagamay laghushastriyasangitatinu kisheel petuttiiriunnu.
ori: rag upare aadharit bhajan, janan, eban ossia sangeeth, rangila chaupadi, ityadiku sugam shastriya sangeeth adhinare vargeekrit karayaishi yahaki ossia sangitar eka guruthpurna ansh ganan karuni .
pan: raagaan, rangila choupdi adi 'te aadharit bhajan, janaan ate udia de git, halake sanatan sangeet de heth ankit kite gaye han, jo udia sangeet da ik mahatavpurna hisa bande han|
tam: bhajan, janan, manllum ragangs, rangila saubadi bhonrowai charnt oriya patals bharambariya mellisai enpatak vakipaduttapadukindena, ews oriya isail mukiya angamak irukkinsona.
tel: bhagen, janan, mariyu ragalapai aadharithmain oriya patal, rangila chupadi vantivi, lalit shastriya sangita kind vargikarinchabaddai, idi oriya sangitalo ock mukhyamin ansha.
urd: raag, rangeela chopadi vagairah par mibani bhajan, janan or odya gaanon ko halki claseki mousiki ke tahat group kiya gaya hai, jo odya mousiki kaa ek ahim hissaa hai.
eng: Bhajan, Janan, and Oriya songs based on ragas, Rangila Chaupadi, etc. are grouped under light classical music, which forms an important segment of Oriya music.

ben: iii paryay, atirikt dharna prabartan ghate; udaharanswarup, karmer boza laghabakari achar, anutap evan tajvadi mandir arpan karake usahit kara hat.
guj: trija tabakkama vadharana vichaaro umerayan hatan; daakhla tarike, tao shailina mandiroma karamkand, praishchit ane samarpanane protsahan apayu karanke tenathi carmik bandhanma ghatado thai shake.
hin: tisare charan main atirikt vichaar pesh kiye gaye; jaise ki prathaen, pashchaatap or taowadi mandiron main bhent chadhaane ko protsaahit kiya jaataa tha kyonki inase carmik boj kam kiya ja saktaa tha.
kan: moorne hantadalli, hchin vicharagainnu parichayislayitu; udaharanege, matachargalu, pashchattap, mattu tavo mandiragalige kanikegal sallikeyannu protsahisalayitu, ekendare ivu karmad horeyannu taggisaballavu.
mal: munnam ghattattil kututal aashays avatarippicppettu; udaharanttin, karmmabhandattiൻre bhara kurikkaൻ avumennatinal tavoist ampalas waipatukalu prayashchittavu anusthanau protsahippicppettu.
ori: tritiya paryayare, athirikta dharnasabu prachalan karagala; udaharan srup, karmkand, anuthap, eban taoisht mandiramanankare naivedhya arpan pari karyanku utsaahit karagala, karan esabu karmankar bojku upasham karib.
pan: tije padse de vich hor vichar pesh kithe gaye see; udaharan de tor te, rasmaan, toba karna ate bheta nuun taushati mandara vich utshaahit kite gaye tanki oh karma de bhaar nuun khatam kar sakan I
tam: moonssam cuttatil melum putu valimuris arimugham seyyabpattanu: edutoukattak, karm vinlin sumayike kuraikk utum nokil chadankugalum, birayachittamum, tao aalayankalil nivedanamum ukquixpattanu.
tel: mudav dashalo, adanpu aalochanal praveshpettabaddai, udaharanku, karmal bharan nudi upashamana kaliginchagalavni tavoist aalayas aacharah, prayashchit mariyu samarpanal vantivi protsahinchabaddai.
urd: teesare marahale main, azafee khayalaat mataarf kiraye gaye. misaal ke tuur par, taaost mandiron main rasomat, toba or nazaraanon kii hausalaa afzaai kii gai thi kyonki wo karam bojh ko kam chriskte the.
eng: In the third stage, additional ideas were introduced; for example, rituals, repentance, and offerings at Taoist temples were encouraged as they could alleviate the karmic burden.

ben: ei samanway kanaphusin achar evan pratisthaner sang bistrut ekati udar ganatantrik kathamor mishran ghateche, sener mate, ya atyadhik vyakticendrikta o naitik darshaner ghattite bhugate thaka pashchathya-shaili udarniti evan anamani shrenivibhag o abhijatader haate aitihasikbhave domit aitihyavahi kanaphusingbad, ubhayer thekes alada.
guj: kanphyusian dharmik vidhio ane vishal udaramat lokshahi malkhani sansthaono aa samanvay, tsengna mate pashchathya shailino udaramat, je vadhu padata vyaktivaadathi peeday che, ane jema naitik drushtino abhav che tenathi, ane paramparik kanphyusianvad, je tsengna mate kathor vanshavad ane pratibhavihin bhadra varg jene aitihasik rite sahan karyu che, tenathi judo pade che.
hin: ek vyapak udaaravaadi loktantric dhaanche ke saath kanfyushi reeti-rivaajon or samaajon ko jodne vaala yah sanshleshan pashchimi style ke udaarvaad, jo ki tseng kii nazar main atishay vyaktvaad or naitik drushti ke abhaav se grast he, or paaramparik kanfushivaad, jo tseng kii raay main aitihaasik drushti se sakht anukram tathaa drudhikrut abhijaat varg se grast he, donon hi se alag he.
kan: kanfushian matachargalu mattu sansthik paddhatigainnu innashtu vishalvad udar dristia samajik samanatheyannu puraskarisuv handardoange sammilitagolisuv i samanvaivu, tsengar prakaar, atiyad vyaktivadadind kudiruv hagu naitik dristiconad abhavakkidagiruv pashchatya shailia udarvad, mattu tsengar prakaar, itihasikavagi nishthur shreni vyavasthegalu hagu kamale kannin ganyarindagi nalugid sampradayik kanfushius math everaderindlu bhinnavagide.
mal: confyushyan anusthanau vishalmay udarajanadhipatyaghatnayotukootia sthapanu yojippichch i sangragna, amitmay vaiyaktikatayu sadacharavikshanttine abhavvu kond valayunnatai tsengh karutunn pashchathya sailiilull udarathilninnu, aivillat adhikarshreniil ninnu vaikkamillat varenyavർggattiൽninnu charitraparamai pidipicppettirunnatai tsengh karutunn sampradayik confyushyanisattil ninnu vyatirikta.
ori: ehi sanshleshanti, yaha kanafusian reetineeti o anusthangudikar eka bapak udarabadi ganatantrika dhanycha seh sammishran karithaye, taha, pashchatya style udarabad, sengnk anuyani yaha atsadhik brekthibad eban eka naitik drushtir abhab dra grast, eban paramparik kanafusianbad, yaha sengnk matre, aithihasik bhave kathor shreneevinas eban eka shakt sambhrant burg dra grast rahi aasichhi - e ubhay tharu stantra.
pan: ih sanshleshan, kanfiusian riti rivaaza ate sansthavaan nuun ik vyapak udarvaadi loktantari dhanche naal milounda hai, pattmi- shili da udarvad dovan ton vakhra hai, jo ki tseng de lai , viaktivad ate naitik drishti di ghat ate ravaiti kanfiususwad vajon bohut ziada dukhadai hai, jisda, saing nuun ,safat mahantshahi ate kulin vargan di kathin state ton itihask for utte nuksaan hoya hai.
tam: kanpucya chadangus manllum niruvan murigans innum parant taralvad jananayakak ghatamiputon pinikum intak kalvai, chengen pati alavukkadikaman tannalavadmum ohukkavial ladciuminmas baditll mengatya vaka taraivadatilrundhum,chengen pati varalarru ritiyag ashixmudiyath patinilis manllum bhitivad medhaviklin batipuku aalakyl bharambariya kanpucyattilrundhum vellupattathakum.
tel: kanfushian aacharah mariyu vistrut udarvad prajaswamy chatra kaligin sansthal i sanyojana anedi seng abhiprayam prakara, mitimirin vyaktivada mariyu naitik drushti lopaniki gurain pashchatya style udarvada, alage dhrudamin vargashreni mariyu karudukattin unntshrenul vall prabhavitamain sampraday kanfushianija, renditicy bhinnaminadi.
urd: ye tarkeeb, jo kunfyoshsee rasomat or vasia tar aazada ro jamhori sakht waale makkatab kii aamezsh hai, mugharabi andaz kii azaad khayali jo tasing ke liye had se zyaada infradit or akhlaqi basirat ke fiqdaan se dochar hai or ravayati kunfyoshit jo tasing ke liye taarikhi aitbaar se be chuk nizaam haai miratab or salbi shurafa se dochar rahi hai, dono se judagan hai.
eng: This synthesis, blending Confucian rituals and institutions with a broader liberal democratic frame, is distinct from both Western-style liberalism which, for Tseng, suffers from excessive individualism and a lack of moral vision and from traditional Confucianism which, for Tseng, has historically suffered from rigid hierarchies and sclerotic elites.

ben: vikshov kare rashtrapati evan sansader puro 225jan sansad sah samagr sarkark padatyag karaar aahvan janano sattweo 2022-era 18i april gotabaya 17jan sadasyer ekati natun mantrisbha nioga karen.
guj: rashtrapati ane tamam 225 sansdo sahit samagr sarkaranu rajinamu magatan virodh pradarshno chhataan gotabaya 18 april 2022na roj sansadma 17 sabhyona nava mantrimandalni nimanuk kari.
hin: raashtrapati or sansad ke sabhi 225 sadasyon sahit puri sarkaar ke istife kii maang ke virodh ke baavjood, gotabaia ne 18 april, 2022 ko 17 sadasyeey nae mantrimandal kii niyukti kii.
kan: rashtradhyaksharu mattu sadandallin ella 225 em.pi.galu seridante idi sarkaarve rajiname nidebekendu agrahisutta pratibhatnegalu nadeyuttiddaru, 2022r april 18randu, gotabaya 17-sadsyar hoss sachiv samputvannu niyuktagolisidru.
mal: rashtrapatiyu paർlameൻrelle motta 225 e. pimarumaica sർkkaർ puർnamayu rajivicnamennavashyapet pratishedhaluyർnnit 2022 apriൽ 18n gotabay oru putia 17 ang mantrisabhae niyamichu.
ori: rashtrapati o sansadar samast 225 em.pi.nk samet samagra sarkarr istafa davi kari pratibad chalithiva satt, 18 april 2022re, gotabaa eka nua 17-sadasya vishist manthrimandal niyukt kale.
pan: 18 april 2022 nuun, gotabaya ne rashtrapati ate sansad de saare 225 members samet puri sarkaar nuun asatifa den di mang karan de bawajood ik nava 17- memberi cabanit niukat kita|
tam: kutiarasut talaivarum paralumanttil ull mottom 225 embixum udpat mughau arasangamu rajinama seyy wants endu ghauri boratas nadandafodhilu, 2022 april 18 andu kottabay 17 ushupinarkalack kont woru putiya amycharave niyamithar.
tel: adhyaksh, inca motta 225 mandi parliament sabhyulatho saha prabhutvan yavattu rajinama cheyalani pilupunistu nirsanal jarugutu unna, 2022 april 18na gotabay 17 mandi sabhyulatho kudin kott mantrivargani niyamincharu.
urd: 18 april 2022 ko , gotabaya ne sadar or parlemint ke tamaam 225 mumbaran parlemint samet puri hukuumat se istafe kaa mataliba karne waale ihtijaj ke baavjood ek nai 17 rukani coben tashkeel di.
eng: On 18 April 2022, Gotabaya appointed a new 17-member cabinet despite the protests calling for the entire government to resign, including the president and all 225 MPs in parliament.

pan: halanki, kise ve state bar consal vich dakhla barister nuun bharat di kise ve adaalat vich pesh on ton rokda hai, bhaaven ih state bar consal de khetri adhikar khetra ton baahar hai jise vich uh dakhal han|
tam: irupinus, vankguraiver ent maanil vankguraiver kangatil patiusaithrundhallum avar indiav evvoru neetimanttil ajaraghat tataill, adevele avar patiusaitull maanil vankguraiver kangatin prantya adhikar varambhuku atu udpadadhu.

urd: taahim, kisi bhi riyasati bar konsil main indraj barrister ke hindustan main kisi bhi adaalat ke saamne pesh hone par paabandi aayad naheen kurta, khwaah ye estate bar konsil ke is ilakaai dayera akhtiyaar se baahar hi ho jis main in kaa indraj hai.
eng: However, enrollment in any State Bar Council does not restrict the Barrister from appearing before any court in India, even though it is beyond the territorial jurisdiction of the State Bar Council in which they are enrolled.

ben: se dohai deya ye, ullikhit gharti 1971 saler iner aota basti elaka avasthit evan pratham vivadi paksher kara maamala sei iner 22(1)(e) dhara thaka nishedhagnar paripreekshite upayukt kartrupaksher kono likhit anumati chada baja rakha yet na.
guj: tene avi araji kari hati ke niyath khand 1971na adhinium hethal jaher karayela jhumpadpatti vistarma avelo hato ane pratham prativadi dwara dakhal karayel daavo te kaayadaani kalam 22(1)(e)maa samavisht pratibandhne dhyane laine saksham sattadhikaarini lekhith paravaangi vina jalvavaa yogya n hato.
hin: prativaadee ne bayaan diya ki praasangik kaksh aise ilaake main sthit he jise 1971 adhinium ke tahat jhuggi jhopadi ghoshit kiya gaya he or pratham yachi dwaara daayar kiya gaya mukadmaa adhinium kii dhara 22(1)(a) main shaamil nishedh ko maddenzar rakhte hue yogya adhikari kii likhit ijaajat ke bagaiyr kanoonee praavdhaanon ke khilaaf tha.
kan: sadri coshadiyu 1971r kaideyadialli kolegeriendu ghoshitvad pradeshsdallittendu, aa kaideya parichchhed 22(1)(e)dalliruva pratibandhad prakaar, modalane prativadiyu dakhlisid mokaddameyu saksham praadhikarad likhitha anumatiillade samarthaniyavallavendu aake manaviannu sallisidlu.
mal: paramർshicpat mury 1971le niyama way prakhyapicpat cheripradeshtta statecheyunatennu, niyamattine 22 (1)(e) end vakuppil atangia nirodhanatine welichottil, uttarvadapet adhikariute rekhamulamulla anumati kootate adyakakshi phayal cheit harji nilenilkkunnatallennu avar tൻre apekshayiൽ parannu.
ori: se eka aavedan upasthapan karithile ye aalochya basagharati '1971 adhinium' anuyani ghoshit basti anychalatire avasthit thila eban sehi 'adhinium'r dhara 22(1)(ka)re antarbhukt nishedhadeshaku drushtire rakhi, kshamtapanna karttripakshank likhita anumati bina pratham prativadink dra daaer hoithiva makaddhamati anurakshaniya nathila .
pan: us ne ik dalil di arzi bhari ki vishe da kamra 1971 act de tahth jhaagi-jhomp vich sthit hai ate pahile jawabdeh vajon bharia hoia mukadma , act 22(1)(a) de tahth pratibandh samarath adhikari di likhit aagia de binaas parambadhan nahi hai I
tam: 1971aam anduch sattatin keel anaivixppatt kudisep bagudiil pat arai irundatu enpatagaum, eneway andach sattatin brivu 22(1)(e)il ull tatayske karuti dagudil anyayatin eduddupurv anumatiinti muthal pradivadi dodutt vanku ini cellupatiakatu enpatagaum avar woru vatat munvaitar.
tel: prastavit gadi 1971 yact krind prakatit murikivadlo undani mariyu modati prativadi dakhs chacin daava aa yactuloni sekshan 22(1)lo nishedha drushtya samarthadhikari likhitapoorvak anumati lekunda nirvahinchadaginadi kadani ock abhyarthann samarpinchindi.
urd: is ne ek arazdaashit daakhil kii ki sabject rome 1971 ke kanoon ke tahat maalan kuchi aabaadee ke ilaka main waaqa hai or is kanoon kii dafaa 22 (1) (aye) main shamil mamanat kii ro se pahele mudda alay ke jaria dair muqadama majaaz atharty kii tahariri izzaazat ke bagaiyr kaabil samat naheen hai.
eng: She set up a plea that the subject room was situated in the slum area declared under the 1971 Act and that the suit filed by the first respondent was not maintainable without the written permission of the Competent Authority in view of the prohibition contained in Section 22(1)(a) of that Act.

kan: visa embudu hor deshvonder valse adhikarigalu obb vyaktiya rujuvatu kagadapatragathannu parishilisid nantar aathan posportin mele moharu ottuv moolak siddhapadisuv ondu pramanpatravagide.
mal: oru vyaktiute rekhakൾ parishodhichotinushes paspoർtiൽ atayappetuttunn oru stampotukuti, oru videsharajyatiൻre immigreshൻ udyogsthർ tayyarackunn oru sakshyapatr visa.
ori: visa heudi eka pramanpatra yaha bsakthi janankar parichan patr yanch kari sarila pare tank passportre eka stamp dei eka videshi rashtrar aapravas adhikareemanank dra present karayaithaye.
pan: visa videshi awas adhikaria duara viakti de sandas di jaanch karan uparant tiar kita gya ik praman paper hai, jise lai passport 'te stamp laai jandi hai|
tam: visa enpatu, ore ayal nottin gudivaru adhikaries oruvarin sandu aavananglch charipartt pin avritu katvuchitle mudra paditwittu uruvakkum sandidhalakum.
tel: visa anedi ock videshaniki chendin pravas adhikarulu, aa vyakti pramanpatras nirdharinchin tarvat, pass port pai ock mudr acchuveyatanto tayar chese ock dhruvapatra.
urd: visa aisa certificate hai jo kisi berun malik ke ammigraishan ahadidaron ke jaria taiyaar kiya jataa hai jis main kisi firad kii asanad kii tasadiq ke baad passport par muhar lagaai jaati hai.
eng: A visa is a certificate prepared by the immigration officials of a foreign country with a stamp marked on a passport after verifying the person's credentials.

ben: karnatka amishashi tulana niramishashider sankhya beshi hawa pradhanath niramish khadyai tader ranna antarbhukt thake.
guj: karnatakama shakaharioni sankhya masaharioni sankhya kartaan vadhi jaaya che, tethi, temana bhojalay mukhyatve shakahari vangio dharavata hoya che.
hin: karnataka main shaakaahaari logon kii sankhya maansaahaari logon se adhik he; isliye unke bhojan main mukhya rup se shaakaahaari vyanjan hote hai.
kan: karnatakadalli masaharigaligint sasyaharigalu hchin sankhyeyalliddare; hagagi, avar pakapaddhatiyu pradhanvagi shakhahari tinisugalind kudide.
mal: karnatakatil sasyaharikalute enea masaharikalute antteal kudutala ; atinaൽ avarute pachakakramattil pradhanmayu ult sasyavibhavaa.
ori: karnatakare shakaharimanank sankhya aamishashimanank sankhyaku athikram kariyichhi; sutaran, semanank bhojanare mukhitah niramish khadman rahithae .
pan: karnataka raj vich vaishno khana khan valya di sankhya mass- machhi khan valya to ziada hai ish lai unhaa de khan- pan vich shakahari bhojan adhikta vich bania janda hai I
tam: karnatakatil saivam unshvargalin annikky asaivam unshvargalin annikkys veet adhikamak irupatal ant manilatin unup palakqtil perumballum saiv unvugale atankyluna.
tel: karnatakaa shakhaharul sankhya mansaharul sankhyan minchi untundi; kabatti vaari vantakalas akkuvamtuku shakhahar vantakale untai.
urd: karnataka main sabzee khuron kii taadaad gosht khuron kii taadaad se zyaada hai; is liye, in ke khaane buniyadi tuur par nibaati pakwaanon par mushtamil hote hain.
eng: The number of vegetarians exceeds the number of non-vegetarians in Karnataka; therefore, their cuisine mainly consists of vegetarian dishes.

ben: california institute af technology (caltek) parichalith nasa-arthayit jet propalshan laboratory (je.pi.el)-r matoi isro evan bhartiya mahakash vigyan o prayukti sanstha (iiesti) 2021-e ekati yoth caryakari kathamo vastavayit kare yeti sahaythe sadharan agraher sabarkam chot, majhari o diramayadi mahakash gaveshana prakalp anumodith karbe bangalooru sthit isro capacity building program afis (si.bi.pi.o)-era antargat ekati kshamtaprapth tattwabadhan comity (i.o.si).
guj: california institut of technology (keltek) dwara sanchalit nasana bhandolthi chaalti jet propalshan leboretary (je.pe.el.)ni jem, isaro ane bhartiya antariksh vigyan ane takaniki sansthan (ai.ai.es.ti.)e 2021maa sanyukt kaaryaksham malkhu amali banaavyu ke jema adhikar sampann smiti (i.o.sii.) echroni bangalooru sthit capacity building program ophis (sii.bi.pe.o.) hethal samanya hitna tamam tunka, madhyam ane lamba galana antariksh sanshodhan karyakramone manjuuri aapshe.
hin: 2021 main isro ne, jo ki california praudyogiki santhaan (caltek) dwaara prabandhit, nasa dwaara vitt poshit jet pranodan prayogshaala (je.pi.el.) ke samaan he, or bhartiya antariksh vigyaan or praudyogiki santhaan (ai.ai.es.tii.) ne ek sanyukt kaary ruparekha lagu kii jisamen bengalooru main sthit isro ke kshamta nirmaan kaarykram karyaalay (si.bi.pi.o.) ke tahat ek adhikaar-praapt nirikshan samiti (i.o.si.) sabhi laghu, madhyam, or saajha hit kii dirghakaalik antariksh anusandhan pariyojnaon ko manjuuri degi.
kan: nasa-anudanit jet propalshan laboratoriannu (je.pi.el.) californiya institute aaf technologiyu (caltech) nirvahisuttiruvante, isro hagu bhartiya antariksha vigyan mattu tantragyan sanstheyu (i.i.es.ti.) zantiagee kelas maduv yojaneyannu 2021ralli kaaryagatagolisidvu, adralli bangalorinalliruva isrod kepyacity building program afisin (si.bi.pi.o.) adiyalli baruv adhikaryut melvicharna mandaliyu (i.o.si.) saman asaktiya ell alp, madhyam mattu dirgh-avadhiya antariksha sanshodhana yojit kaaryagainnu anumodisuttade.
mal: ella potutalparyamull hrasva, maddhyakal, dirnkal, bahirakashagaveshanapaddhatikalu bengaluru aasthanmay ai.es.ar.o. yute capability bilding program ofisi (si.bi.pi.o.)nte kidilull oru anpaveർd ovർsiing committee (i.o.si.) angikarikunn vidhttil, nas dhansahaya cheiyunnatu kalipornia institute of technology (kaltek) meൽnotte vahikunnatumay jet propalshan laborttery (je.pi.el.) yepole, isroyu indian institute of spays sayans and technologyyu (ai.ai.es.ti.) 2021l oru joint variking frainwark natapaki.
ori: kaliurnnia 'institute af technology' (kaltek) dra parichalit, nasa-dra aarthik sahayatha prapth 'jet prapalsan laboratori (je.pi.el.)' pari, isro eban bharatiya antariksh vigyan eban pradhogiki sansthan (aai.aai.es.ti.) 2021 masihare, eka sanyukt bhave karboorat pradhar karyankaari karithile, yeunthire bangalorere avasthit, isror dakshata bikash karyankram karyalaya (si.bi.pi.o.) adhinare thiva eka kshamtapanna parylevekshan kamiti (i.o.si.) samast sadharan uddeshya nimanthe uddist laghu, madhum eban deergha-miadi antariksh gaveshana prakalpagudiku anumodan karib .
pan: naa.saa duvaaraan sanchit jait propalshan laboratori (jeee.pi.ail) jo ki callifornia institute aaf taknalogy (cyle.tek),i.sro ate indian institute aaf spess vigyaan ate taknalogy () ne 2021 vich ikithe kee karan da dhancha bania jise de adhin ik adhikarat nigrani kameti (i.o.si),bangaloru vich sthi, aai.asa.aar.o de samphtha nirman program dafatar de heth saare chhoti, madham ate lambi miad saanjhe hit de spess khoj projecta nuun manazuuri devegi.
tam: california institute off dechnology (kheltek) nirvakikum naacha-nidhiudavi kont jet purobalshan lebarttery (jhapiel) pol, 2021il isro india vinveli anaivial manllum tosilnutpak gangamum (isesty) woru gootuppanic ghatamibbai natamurikuk konduvandatu, adanpati bangaloreel amaindull isrovin dihan vaurfut ditt aluvalagatin (sipibhao) keel ull ore adhikarmalicoppatt meghbarvike kulu (iosi) anwattup potu nalan kont kurungal, idikkal manllum nind kaal vinveli araichit dittangalukum oppudal alikkum.
tel: kyaliphornia institute aaf teknalaji(coltek) aadhvaryamlo nasa ardhik sahakar pondin jet propalshan laboratory (jepiel) ki madrigane, 2021lo isro mariyu indian institute aaf spes science and teknalaji (aippesti) samyuktanga ock karyakramanni amaluparichai, indulo bhaganga saadhikaritgal paryavekshan smiti (iosi) bangalorulo isroki chendin kapasiti building progran afis aadhinanio (sibepio) samanya prayojnalku anni swalp, madhyam, mariyu dirgh kaalik antariksha parishodhana projectula aamodistundi.
urd: keli fornia insiti tute of tikunology (caltek) ke zer intazaam nasa kii mali iant se chalane wali jet proplashan lebartry (jai pii el) kii tarah, asaro or indian insiti tute of spes since and technology (aai aai es tii) ne 2021 main ek mushtarki varking frame varik nafiz kiya jis main bangalore main waaqa asaro ke capesti building program afas (si bi pii oo) ke tahat ek baakhtiyaar nigranee cameti (e oo si) mushtarki dilchaspee ke tamaam mukhtsar, darmiyaane or tavel muditi khilaai tahaqiq ke mansoobon ko manzooree de gi. .
eng: Like the NASA-funded Jet Propulsion Laboratory (JPL), managed by the California Institute of Technology (Caltech), ISRO and the Indian Institute of Space Science and Technology (IIST) implemented a joint working framework in 2021 in which an empowered overseeing committee (EOC) under the Capacity Building Programme Office (CBPO) of ISRO located in Bengaluru will approve all short, medium, and long-term space research projects of common interest.

ben: kono ekajner dwara pradutt noter sankhya 5ti beshi kintu 5,000 moolyer andhik haley sei noteguli prerkak nijer bank acounter khuntinati (acount nambar, shakhar naam, ishyaessi ityadi) sah bimakrit dake tar nickkbarti mudra chest shakha pathate athva nije sekhane gie seguli badale anar paramarsh dewa uchit.
guj: jyaan vyaktie raju kareli noteni sankhya 5 tukdaothi vadhu have pan mulyma 5,000thi vadhu nahi hoya, tyaare raju kartane tena/tenina bank khatani vigto (khaata number, shakhanu nam, ai.epa.es.sii., vagere) sahit aavi notsane najikani nanakiya chest shakhama bimit tupal dwara mokalvani athva teni rubaru adalabadali karvaani salaah apashe.
hin: jab die jane vaale noton kii sankhya 5 se adhik ho or unka kul mulya 5,000 se zyada ho to note badalane ke liye dene vaale vyakti ko salaah di jaati he ki ve aise note paas kii mudra tijori shakha main apane bank vivaran (khaataa sankhya, shakha kaa naam, ai.epa.es.si. ityadi) ke saath bimit dak se bhejein yaa phir swayan mudra tijori shakha jaakar note badalawa len.
kan: obb vyaktiyu sallisuttiruv notugal sankhyeyu 5kkint hechiddu, avugal maulyavu 5,000kkint kadimairuv sanderbhadalli, sallikedarnige aa notugaiannu aathan/aakeya bank khateya vivargalondige (khaate sankhye, shakheya hesaru, i.f.es.si., ityadi) hattirad khajane shakhege vimeyukt ancheya moolak kaluhisuvante athwa allige khuddagi terali avugainnu vineemay madicolluvante salahe nidelaguttade.
mal: oral samarppikkunn nottukalute enea anchil kututalu mulym 5,000 l adhikamakatayu irunnal kodukkunnayale attar nottukal atuttull kaonsi chest shakhi inshwer cheit post way addehtine/avarute (akound nampar, shakhayute per, ai.eph.es.si. muthala) bank akound vivaratecoppam ayakkukayo avite neritu chenne matietukkukayo cheiyan upadeshippet.
ori: yeun kshetrare brektijankank dra upasthapit notguyikar sankhya 5 khandaru adhik, matra moolkere 5,000 ru adhik nuhen, tenderrjankanku bimaakrit daak madhumare nij bank khatar bivaraneegudik (khata nan., shakha nam, aai.ef.es.si., ityadi) dei eka nearest prachalit mudra sindhuk thiva shakhaku ehipari notman pathaibaku kimba nijeyai sehithare segudiku badal karinevaku paramarsh diayib .
pan: jadon ik viakti col pesh kithe gaye note 5 tukarias ton uddh hai per kul rakam 5,000 ton uddh nahi hai taan rakam bhejan wale nuun salah diti jandi hai ki oh ahije note koi nede nota di tijori vich aapne khaate da verwa (khaata number, shakha da naame, aai.aif.asa.si adi) de ke bimaa karavaa deve jaaa onha di badali karavaa ledai I
tam: oruvar konduvarum nottugalin annikky ainduku mel ulldu anal madiple 5,000tts thandavilly endal, avvar nottu majochu vandavaridom ant nottuss arukil nanayab pettakak clyku tanatu vangik ganaku vivrangaluton (ganaku en, clyf payar, aiefescy kuriidu bhonrowai) kaffeeddut tapal mulam anuppumaru alltu nerag angu sentu majhric kollumaru arivudutt wants.
tel: ock vyakti samarpinchin nots 5 kante akkuv undi 5,000 viluvanu minchani yedal, atuvanti nots nivedhk bimaa chembadd tapa dwara atani/ambe banku vivaram (khata number, shakh peru, aiefessi mo) andistu sameep koshagar shakhaku pampavalsindiga leda vatini akkde swayanga marchukovalasindiga suchimpbatar.
urd: jahaan ek shaks ke zarie pesh kiye gaye noton kii taadaad 5 se zyaada hai lekin malit main 5,000 se matjaaviz naheen hai, to pesh karne waale ko mashvira diya jaaye gaa ki wo aese noton ko apne bank khate kii tafsilat (khaata number, shaakh kaa naam, aai epa es si, vagairah) dete hue bema shudaa post ke zarie karibi krinsi tijori kii shaakh ko rawaanah karee yaa vahaan zaati tuur par in kaa tabadalaa karavaa lay.
eng: Where the number of notes presented by a person is more than 5 pieces but not exceeding 5,000 in value, the tenderer shall be advised to send such notes to a nearby currency chest branch by insured post giving his/her bank account details (a/c no, branch name, IFSC, etc.) or get them exchanged thereat in person.

ben: swaksharatar haar 1991 sale 39 shatansh thek 2001 sale 47 shatansh thek 2011 sale 63.8 shatansh percent bedese.
guj: saksharata dar 1991maa 39%thi vadhine 2001maa 47%thi vadhine 2011maa 63.8% thayo che.

kan: saksharateya darvu 1991ralli 39% iddudakkint 2001ralli 47%ge, 2011ralli 63.8%ge airikeyagide.
mal: 1991ൽ 39% irunn saksharatanirak 2001ൽ 47% ayu 2011ൽ 63.8% ayu uyർnnu.
ori: sakshrata haar 1991re 39%ru 2001re 47%ku eban 2011re 63.8%ku briddhi pichhi.
pan: sakhrata dar 1991 vich 3.9% ton uddh ke 2001 vich 47% hoo gai ate 2011 vich 63.8% hoo gai|
tam: eduttarivu vikitham 1991il 39%-lirundhu 2001il 47% eneum 2011il 63.8% eneum uyarndulldu.
tel: 1991lo 39% ga unn akshrasyata rate 2001lo 47% ku, 2011lo 63.8% ku perigindi.
urd: shrah khvandagi 1991 main 39 faisad se badh kar 2001 main 47 faisad or 2011 main 63.8 faisad hogai hai.
eng: The literacy rate has risen from 39% in 1991 to 47% in 2001 to 63.8% in 2011.

eng: The high level of brand loyalty has been criticised and ridiculed, with the epithet "Apple fanboy" being applied and mocking the lengthy lines before a product launch.

ben: 145 na dhara sanshodhan kara has evan 2013-era supreme corter niyamavali dwara niyantrit has.
guj: kalam 145maa sudharo thayo ane te sarvochch adalatana 2013na niyamo dwara sanchalit thai che.

mal: artikle 145 bhedgati cheiyukayu at 2013le suprin kotatichchattes way niyantricppetukayu cheiyunnu.

ben: hitopadesh hal pakhee, pashu o manusher charitrer madhyam bozano paarthiv gnaner ekati bai.
guj: hitopadeshae pakshio, pranio ane manushyona patro dwara raju thayela dunvayi dahapanno granth che.
hin: hitopadesh ek pustak he jisamen sansaarik gyaan pakshiyon, pashuon, or manushyon ke charitron ke madhyam se prastut kiya gaya he.
kan: hitopadeshvu pakshigalu, pranigalu, mattu manushya patragal moolak lowkik vivekavannu presenutpadisuv pustakwagide.
mal: pakshis, mrigajas, manushyar enni kathapatraslilute avataricppedunn lakikavivekatine oru pustak hitopadesham.
ori: hitopadesh heudi sansarika gyanar eka pustak yahaki pakshi, pashu, eban manushya charitragudik madhumare upasthapit hoichhi .
pan: hitopadesa doonia bhar de gyan di ik kitaab hai jo ki pakshia, janwara ate inasana de kirdaara de raahi vidya dindi hai I

urd: hattupadisha, parindon, janwaron or insaanon ke kirdaron ke zarie pesh kii gai duniyavi hukmat kii ek kitaab hai.
eng: Hitopadesa is a book of worldly wisdom presented through the characters of birds, animals, and humans.

ben: gail mishrer du'ti gas sanstha, mulath fyum gas company (ef.ji.si) evan nyashnal gas company (natgyas)-era ek icuity anshidar.
guj: ji.e.ai.el. e egyptani be chhutak gas companyo name fayum gas company (epa.ji.sii.) ane nesnal gas company (netges)maa pan ikvity bhagidar che.
hin: gail bhi misr kii do khudara gas companiyon, fayum gas company (epa.ji.si.) or naishanal gas company (natgas) main equity saajhedaar he.
kan: ji.e.i.el. egyptin eradu chillare wahivatin anil companigalad fayam gas company (f.ji.si.) mattu nyashanal gas companigamalli (natgyas) equity paludarikeyannu hondide.
mal: fayu gas company (eph. ji. si), nashanൽ gas company (natgas) enni rand retaiൽ gas companikaliൽ gaiൽ oru ikvity paർttonർ koot .
ori: 'ge'l' egypter duiti khuchura gas companyr anshdhanar bhagidari madhya, yeungurikar nam hela phaum gas company (ef.ji.si.) eban nasanal gas company (nyatgas) .
pan: g.e.aai.ail misar dis doo prachun gas companie vich nirpekhata hisedaar hai jo ki fayum gas company (aif.ji.si) ate nesnal gas company (netgas) han I

tel: alage gail egyptloni rend ritile gas companian, fayu gas company (affgisi) mariyu neshanal gas company (natgyas) lalo kuda yajmanya vatadar bhagswami.
urd: gail misar main do khurda gas companiyon main ecweti partner bhi hai, yani fyom gas company (epa ji si) or neshnal gas company (net gas).
eng: GAIL is also an equity partner in two retail gas companies in Egypt, namely Fayum Gas Company (FGC) and National Gas Company (Natgas).

ben: daruchini bharte mulvave upadit evan era vyabhhar gandhvisisht dravya thek aarmbh kare aushadhi dravya hiseve has.
guj: taj mul bharat che ane e rite tena upayog sugandh dutathi laine aushadh doot tarike vistre che.

ben: "radieshan sinovectomy" athva "radiocinoviorthysis" name parichit ei chikisa paddhatitite akrant asthisanyoger sinobial gabargulite bikiran lebelyukt kana athva bikiran lebelyukt kalayad prayog kara has.
guj: aa saarwar padhdhati ke je "radieshan synovactomi" athva "readiosynoviorthesis" tarike janiti che, te asargrast sandhana synovial polashma readiolabel wala kano athva readiolabel wala coloida prasashnane niyukt kare che.
hin: upachaar ke is prakaar main, jise "vikiran shleshak-kala uchhedan" yaa " radiosinovorthosis" ke rup main janaa jaataa he, radiolabel kanikas yaa radiolabel kalil rog-grast jodon kii srav guha main injection se die jate hai.
kan: "radieshan cinovektomi" athwa "radiosinoviyorthisis" emb i chikitsa vidhandalli, vikirangrahiyendu lable madlad pruthakanagalu athwa vikirangrahiyendu lable madlad kalilagainnu baadhit kilugal cinoviad pollu bhaggamalli prayogislaguttade.
mal: radiion sinovektaomi athva radiosinovayoർttesis ennariapadunn chikitsasmpradayam baadhicpat sandhikalute sinovial kavitikal radiolabel cheyyapret parshatiulates athva radiolabel cheyyapret koloidukൾ upyogiunnu.
ori: ehi chikitsa paddhatiti yaha "radiesan sinovectomi" ba "radiocinobhiorthacis" bhavare janashuna, prabhavita ganthir sandhiras chhidrare radiolevalad kanika kimba radiolevalad koledra bbbahar karithaye.
pan: ih ilaaj vidhi, jise nuun "radiation cinovatomy" jaaa "radiosinoviorthisis" vajon jaanya janda hai, prabhavit jodaa de cynovial cavitys vich radiolabel wale kanas jaaa radioidal vich injaction raaheen dite jaande han|
tam: "radieshan chinovektamy" alltu "radiosinoviardecis" endu anoaicopatum indech sikichi muriil, badikkappatt muddukkulaikalil radio labilit tugalmangalo radio labilit gutamangalo selutopadukindena.
tel: "radio sinovektami" leda "radiosinovayortesis" ane perte gal i chikitsa vidhanaion prabhavit killsandul sainovial randhralloki radiodharmikat kalapabadin nalusulu leda radiodharmikat kalapabadin gujjun ekkinchada dwara pani chestundi.
urd: ilaaj kii is soorat main, jise "radiation sinovectomy" yaa "radio sinoviarthiss" ke naam se jaanaa jataa hai, mutasara jodun ke laaab mufasil kii khokhaliyon main radio label jaraat yaa radiolavel colitez dalaa jataa hai.
eng: This treatment modality, which is known as "Radiation Synovectomy" or "Radiosynoviorthesis," employs the administration of radiolabeled particulates or radiolabeled colloids in the synovial cavities of the affected joints.

ben: anyanya kshetre, helicopter shudhumatra andaj karte evan astra hisabe raket-bahit torpedor vyabhhar kara hayes.

hin: anya maamalon main helicopter kaa prayog keval pataa lagane ke liye kiya jaataa he or yah shastr ke rup main rocket se prakshepit tarpeado kaa prayog karata he.

mal: mat sandർbhagmaliൽ helicoptraർ paryavekshanttinumatramayu rocketilute vidunn toർpidokൾ ayudhmayu upyogichittund.
ori: anyanya drushtantgudhikare, helicoptaraku keval anuman kariva pin eban raket-prerit kshepanastragudiku astra bhavare bbbahar karayaishi .
pan: doosare mamlia vich, haileycapat siraf stleushan lai vartia janda hai ate raaket pahunchaun walia suranga hathiar de tor te varte jaande san I
tam: mabbbb chandarppanglil helikopter ulu parpatangu mattume payanbaduttapattuldu, adevele rocket-seluttal katanganai aayudamagap payanbaduttapattuldu.
tel: migta sandarbhallo, helicopter kevalam avagahan kos upayoginchi, rocket dwara pampabade tarpedose aayudhanga upayogincharu.

eng: In other cases, the helicopter has been used solely for sensing and rocket-delivered torpedoes have been used as the weapon.

ben: yemanta akhil bhartiya ayurvigyan sansthar kshetre hayes evan gangadharer kshetre punravritti karesil, era samadhano shasker kache abhiyog dakhil karaar madhyam royas.
guj: je rite ol india institut of medical sayns kesama tharavayu hatu ane gangadharna kesama punravartit thayu hatu te mujab magistrate samaksh fariyaad dakhal karine uparokt nirdharit upay upalbdh che.
hin: jaisaa ki akhil bhartiya ayurvigyaan santhaan main nirnay liya gaya tha or gangadhar ke maamle main doharaaya gaya tha, uplabdh upachaar upar bataae anusaar nyaayadhish ke saamne shikaayat ke liye ekadam taiyaar he.
kan: akhil bharat vaidyakiya vigyan sansthey prakarandalli heliruvante mattu gangadhar prakarandalli punaruchcharislagiruvante, labhyaviruv pariharavendare, mele tilisiruvante, magistretrvar sammukhadalli doornnu dakhlisuvudagide.
mal: oൾ india iൻstitute of medicaൽ sayൻsas kaseiൽ paranktu gangadharu te kaseiൽ aavർttichchatupole mukaliൽ kanichtupole majistratin mumpake parati samർppikkaa cheyyaൻ kaniavunn parihar.
ori: yepari 'akhil bharatiya aajurvigyan pratishthan' mammlare nishpatti hoithila eban ganggadharank mammlare punaravarttit hoithila, upalavdh thiva pratikarati heudi upare darshayaithiva bhadi majishtretnk nikatare eka abhiyog dakhal kariva .
pan: jive ki all india medical since sanstha te gangadhar case vich kiha gya , ilaaj oda hi hai jive ki jaj de samane shikait vich daraj kitha see I
tam: aal india institute off medical scincess vanggil karudduraicopattu gangadr vanggil mintus valiyuuttappattapati, menokuriyavaru natuvarmanee nitipathin munnelil pukarsep patiu seywate idaskana tirvakum.
tel: akhil bharat vedya vigyan sansth kesulo jarigints, mariyu gangadhar kesulo punarudghatinchints, poorvokt vidhnga nyayadhipati samakshanlo firyad dakhs cheyadame andubatulo unn parihara.
urd: jaisaa ki aal india insiti tute of medical sincez ke maamle main apanaaya gaya tha or gangadhar maamle (supera) main iaada kiya gaya tha, dastyab hal hasab bala magistrat ke aage shikayat darj karke bayaan kiya gaya hai.
eng: As was held in the All India Institute of Medical Sciences case and re-iterated in Gangadhar's case, the remedy available is as set out above by filing a complaint before the magistrate.

hin: yah mana jaataa he ki iske baad rajya vidhansabha ke chunaav 11.04.2019 main hue or shri vaai. jagmohan reddy mukhya mantri bane evam 30.05.2019 ko unhone shapath grahan kii.
kan: ader nantar 11.04.2019randu rajya vidhansabha chunavanegalu nadedvu mattu shri vai. jaganmohan reddy mukhyamantriyagee 30.05.2019randu pramanvachan swikarisidru endu nivedislagide.
mal: atinushes 11.04.2019n niyamsabha teranjeetuppukൾ natattukayu 30.05.2019n shri vai. jagൻmohൻ reddy mukhyamantriai satyapratijna cheiyukayu cheitathai bodhippicppettu.
ori: prakash thau ki, ta'pare rajya bidhansabha nirvachan ta11.04.2019rikh din hoithila eban shri i. jaganamohan reddy mukhimanthri hoithile tatha ta30.05.2019rikh din shapath grahan karithile .
pan: ish ton bood ih pesh kitha janda hai ki raj de sabha chunaav 11.04.2019 nuun hoe san ate shri vaai.jaganmohan radi mouth mantri bane ate 30.05.2019 nuun shapath lai I
tam: adanbin 11.04.2019 andu manilach sattasabait terdal natabeantu enllum, thiru oi. jaganmohan reddy 30.05.2019 andu muthalmicharagap padvienneru urutimophi edutdhar enllum munwaixpadukintu.
tel: apimmat rashtra shasan sabh annikal 11-04-2019 nadu nirvahinchabadi, shri vai. jaganmohan reddi mukhyamantri ayi 30-05-2019 nadu praman sweekar chesharani nivedinchabadindi.
urd: arz kiya jataa hai ki is ke baad 11.04.2019 ko riyasati asambali ke intakhaabat hue or janaab wai jagan mohan reddy vazeer aala bane or 30.05.2019 ko half liya.
eng: It is submitted that thereafter the elections to the State Assembly were held on 11.04.2019 and Shri Y. Jaganmohan Reddy became the Chief Minister and took oath on 30.05.2019.

guj: tokyo olampic chakra daramiyaan, hun manovaigyani paase jaish, pan men tene kyarey agrata banavi nathi ane mara shariranu dhyaan rakhyu nathi.
hin: tokio olympic chakra ke dauraan, main manovaigyanik ke paas jaataa tha lekin maine ise kabhi bhi praathamikta nahin di or apane sharir kaa dhyaan nahin rakhaa.
kan: tokio olympixn avadhialli naanu manavshastrajnar bali teraluttiddenadaru, adnnu endigu nann adyatayagisicondiralill mattu nann sharir swasthyad bagge echchar vahisalill.

urd: tokio olympic saikal ke dauraan main maahir nafasyat ke pas jaati thi, lekin main ne use kabhi trigeh naheen di or apne jism kaa khyal naheen rakha.
eng: During the Tokyo Olympic cycle, I would go to a psychologist, but I never made it a priority and didn't look after my body.

ben: mott bajater matra 3% baradd chudantamatra aparapt evan, bahul sankhyak pratishthan sah, segulite shudhumatra nimomaner parishebai nischit kara yete par.
guj: kul andajpatrana matra 3% kul maline apurta che ane moti sankhyani sansthao sathe, temane malti sevaoni matra nabali gunavattani khatari aape che.
hin: kul bajet kaa maatr 3% nihaayat aparyaapt he or, itane adhik sansthaanon main bas ek kamjor gunvattta kii sevaayen hi sunishchit kar saktaa he.
kan: ottu bajettinalli keval 3%ashtu endare anenu sakagadu mattu, sansthegalu bhaari sankhyeyalliruvag, adu avugamalli kalpe gunamttad sevegannu khatriagisabahudashte.
mal: motabajatinte veru 3% thiർttu aparyaptvu, sthapanngൾ valareyadhikamundairie availle seven gunnilvar kushanstayiriumenn ushppakukyu cheiyunnu.
ori: mot bajetra matra 3% nihathi kam ate, eban yehetu ete sankhyare anusthansabu rahichhi, semananku keval nimnamanar seva mithiva sunishchit.
pan: kul bajat da maathar 3% behad naa kaphi hai, ate badi ginti vich sansthavaan de naal, siraf uhanaas vich sevaavaan di mari guntata nuun yakini bana sakda hai|
tam: mott budgettle vellum 3% enpatu appatamana paxakurai, adhuum erauman turais ull niliil itu avacharuku dharamda sevaikalaiye urudisey mudi.
tel: phurti budgetlo kevalam 3% ghormain korat kaligistundi, mariyu sansthal pedd sankhyalo undatanto wariki nasirka seval matrame andinchagalaru.

ben: jatiya gramin swasthy mishan (in.aar.aich.em)-era mato karmasuchir madhyam bharat jure ayurveda o jaiv chikisa centragulike sah-avasthit karaar pracheshta shudhumatra jaibchikisa evan ayurveder madhye sharirik naikatya abdhii simavaddh evan ekasang chikisa parisheba pradaner moolian stare caryakari milaner sambhavana thek anek dure.
guj: nesnal rural health mishan (en.ar.ech.em.) jeva upakrmo dwara samagr bharata biomedical savalto sahitna ayurvedic kendro, e biomedicin ane ayurveda vachche matra bhautik sameeptha sudhi maryadit che ane dawaakhaana sevaona star sudhi kriyashil aikyani shakyatathi ghani dur che.
hin: rashtriya gramin swasthya mishan (en.aar.ech.em.) jaise kaaryakramon ke madhyam se puure bharat main ayurveda kendron or jaev-chikitsa suvidhaon ko sah-sthit karne ke praytn keval bhautik nikatataa tak simit hai or naidanik sevaaon ke sah-vitaran ke str tak kaaryaatmak ekikaran kii sambhaavna ummid se bahut kam he.
kan: rashtriya gramin aarogya mishannantah (en.aar.ech.em.) yojanegal moolak bharatadadyant bio-medical saulabhyagal jotege ayurveda kendragaiannu zantiagee sthapisuv yatnagalu biomedisin mattu ayurvedad naduve bhautik samipyavannu taruv mattigashte simitvagive mattu ottige vaidyakiya seveannu odagisuvashtu talmattadavaregin kaaryakari samanvyad sadhayateind bailwe dur ulidive.
mal: deshiya gramin arogya mishൻ (eൻ. aaർ. ech . e) polull paddhatikalilute indiailutnilam aayuർvedakendranslu bio medicaൽ samvidhanau oresthalat sthapicanural shramngൾ, bio medicin aayuർvedattinu idilull bhatikamay atuppattiൽmatra otuteitu ekikruthamay chikitsasevanttiൻre sukshmatalattilekulla pravർttanaparamay udgrathanttiൻre sadhyatiൽninn orupat akala.
ori: jatiya grameen ssthya mishan (en.aar.ech.em.) pari karyankram madhumare sara bharatre aajurveda kendragudik jaivabheshaj subidhathiva kendragudik sahit ekatara sthanit karibar prayas keval kaik nikatatha madhyare simit hoi rahiyaichhi, eban rogi chikitsa kshetrare babaharika digru susanhat ekatara seva pradaan karibar sambhavana eve madhya bahu durre.
pan: bharat vich ayurveda cendara de naal naal byo-medical sevaavaan di khoj karna rashtirya pendu sihat muhim (in.aar.aich.aim) simit han byo-medicean te ayurveda nede nahi han te ih daur hai koi ve donas da upyogi sanjog lai ate donas di clinical adaaigi ikithe hona I
tam: desiya uragach chugadhar iyakkum (anarhesem) bonthe ditangalin vilak india muruvatum ayurveda maiyangales uerial marutuv maiyangales cherttu amikum mushchicp boduddhavarai, are uerial maruduwates ayurvedates it ritiyag arukhil konduvarum alavukke ulsana, onrinaint maruduvach sevai valangum alavuku auman seyalbattu orunginibbai erbadudhuatu innum ganavagave ulldu.
tel: bharatvaesha vyaptanga jeeva vedya saukaryalato kudin ayurveda centrase sah-sthapananiki jaatiya gramin arogya mishan (anareche) vanti karyakramas chestunn prayatnalu jeevavaidyam ayurvedal madhya bhautik samipya varake parimitmayi samishti vaidyam andinche kriyashil anusandhanavkashaniki chala duralo unnai.
urd: qaumi dehi sahat machine (en aar yach em) jese programon ke zarie bhaarat main bive medical saholyat ke saath saath aivar ved murakz ko shariq karne kii koshishen bive medicine or aivar ved ke mabin sirf tabiyaai kurbat kii had tak mahadood hain nez tabi kudamat kii farahami kii satah par tafaali animam ke imkan se bahut daur hain.
eng: The efforts to co-locate Ayurveda centers along with bio-medical facilities across India through programs like the National Rural Health Mission (NRHM) are limited to the extent of only physical proximity between biomedicine and Ayurveda and far away from the possibility of functional integration granulated to the level of clinical service delivery together.

urd: ye kahaaniyan takhliki afasaanon kii tarah kaam krati hain, jis main vizahat kii gai hai ki ye skool kaise vajood main aayaa or use mahatma budh kii talimat ko pahunchane kaa khasusi akhtiyaar kyon haasil hai.
eng: These narratives function like creation myths, explaining how the school came to be and why it has a special authority to convey the Buddha's teaching.

ben: digital banisya: mena anchaler tarunder janya suyog, esdiji alokacitra pradarshani janya chot vyavasa, kridda tarun udyokta evan nareeder janya binioga-era mato bivinn anusthaner yojan karche antarjatik banisya centra, tara chot vyavasa evan udyoktader prayojanguli tule dhara pashapashi tader bede othar samay sahayata pradaner dike jor dicche.
guj: antarrashtriya vyapaar kendra dwara vividh karyakramonu aayojan karvama aavi rahyu che, je laghu udyogo ane udyogsahasiconi aavashyakataone rekhankit kare che ane teo dijital vyaparani jem vikse tem tene samarthan aape che : em.i.en.e. pradeshma yuvano mateni tako, es.dee.ji. mate laghu vyavasayo - tasveer pradarshan, yuva udyog sahasico ramato ane mahilao matenu rokan.
hin: aise vibhinn kaarykram antarrashtriya vyapaar centre dwaara yojit kiye ja rahe hai jo chote vyavsaayon or udhyamiyon kii aavashyaktaaon par prakaash daalate hai or unki pragati main sahaayta pradaan karte hai, jaise ki digital vyapaar: mena kshetra main yuvakon ke liye avasar, es.di.ji. ke liye chote vyavsaay - photo pradarshnee, khel ke kshetra main yuva udhyami or mahilaon main nivesh.
kan: antarashtriya vyapaar kendravu digital vyapaar: em.i.en.e. pradeshad yuvajanatege avkashgalu, es.de.ji.galigagi sann udyamgalu-chayachitra pradarshan, kridakshetradallin yuv udyamigalu, mattu investing in vimen muntad sann udyamgalu hagu udyamigal aavashyakategainnu etti torisuv mattu avaru pragatiannu sadhisid hage avarige nervu niduv vividh kaaryakramagainnu aayojisuttide.
mal: cherukit bisinassukalutayu sanrambhkarutayu aavashyak pramukhyam nalkukayu av 'digital trade' pole valarumpol avark pintun nalkukayu cheiyunn pal paripatikalu iൻraർnashanൽ trade seൻraർ sanghatipikunnu: e.i.en.e. mekhalile yuvakalkulla avasarathlu es.de.ji-photo pradർshanttinull cherukit bisinassukalu kaayikarangatte yuvasanrambhkaru strijnangൾk shaktipakaralu.
ori: antharjatiya banija kendra dra vibhinna karyankram aatojit heudi, yahaki kshudra babasan eban udogeemanank aavashyakatagudik upare guruthrope karuni eban semane dejital banija bhadi pragathi karuthiva samaure semanank pin sahayatha pradaan karen: 'mena' anychalre yuvapirink pin suyog, 'es.de.ji.'-fato pradharshani nimanthe kshudra bavasaman, kreeda kshetrare thiva yuva udjogi eban mahila manank pin arth viniyog kariva .
pan: intersrashtirya vpark center vajon kai samagam yojit kithe jaa rehe han jo chhote wapara te udmia dis lods bal dhiaan de ke onha lai sahyog de rahi hai jive ki digital wapar: nujavaana lai me.e.naa.aa ilaake vich mauke,chhote wapara lai asa.di.ji photo pardarshan, kheds vich naujavaan ate aurata lai nivesh karna I
tam: sarwatech varttak maiyam palveru nicktigaluku arbadu seykintu, are chiru vanikas manllum tophilmunaorine devikhal kothitug gatti avargaluku valarchib patil adrv alickinsona, udaranmak digitale vanigum, mena bagudiil ilairgaluku waifpalittal, estiji-galukan chiru vanikas kuritt pukippatak gangatchi, vilyaddud turaiil ilum tophilmunaorai ukquittal, pengal charndvail mudalidu saythal bhonrowai.
tel: interneshnal trade center dwara anek karyakramas nirvahinchabadutunnai, ivi chinn vyaparah mariyu parishramikavettal avasarase nokkicheppy, digital tredga edige samayaulo wariki maddatu istai: mena prantaloni yuvatku avakashalu, asdigies-photo pradarshan koraku chiru vyaparah, kridallo yuv vyavasthapakulu, mahillapai pettubadi pettada vantivi.
urd: ben alaswami tizaarati marcuz ke jaria mukhtalf takreebat kaa ahtamam kiya jaarha hai, jo chhote kaarobaron or kaarobaari afarad kii zaruuryat ko ujagar kurta hai oran ko aage badhane main madad faraham kurta hai jese degetal tizarat: em e en aye khate main naujavaanon ke liye mawaqa, es dee ji-photo numaayish ke liye chhote kaarobaar, khel main naujawan kaarobaari afarad or khwatin main saramy kari.
eng: Various events are being organized by the International Trade Center, which highlights the needs of small businesses and entrepreneurs and provides support for them as they grow like Digital Trade: Opportunities for youth in the MENA region, small businesses for the SDGs-Photo exhibition, young entrepreneurs in sport and Investing in Women.

ben: cui fal thek tiri nara aaba namer ekati howite wine arunachal pradesh thek aases evan nimn subansiri jeller hang gramer lambu -subu khadya o panian sanstha dwara upadit has.
guj: nara aabaa tarike olkhata kiwi falmathi banto safed wine arunachal pradeshmathi aave che ane te lower subansiri jillana hong gaamma lambu-subu food and beverejis dwara banavay che.
hin: arunachal pradesh main naaraa aabaa naam kii shwet sharaab kiwi fal se banaai jaati he or iskaa utpaadan nichle subansiri zile ke hogg gaanv main lambu-subu food and beverejes karata he.
kan: naara aaba endu kareyalaguv kiwi hanninind tayarislad bili drakshamadyavu arunachal pradeshad utpannavagiddu, idannu loor subansiri jilley hong habalialliruva lambu-subu good and bevarejasnvaru utpadisuttare.
mal: lower subansiri jillille hong gramttil lambu subu fod and bivareijas nirmmikunn kivippattilninnundakkunn nara aaba enne perulla oru wellvinera arunachalpradeshilninnuvarunnu.
ori: ki faru present eka sht in arunachal pradesharu aasithaye yahaku 'nara aaba' kuhayaaye eban eha nimn suvanasiri jillar hang gramre thiva 'lambu-subu phud and beverejes' dra utpaadit hoithaye .
pan: kiwi fal ton bani safid mad jise nuun naaraa aabaa kahinde han oh arunachal pradesh de herele subansiri jila de hong pind vich banadi hai ate lambu - subu food and bevergis davaaraan utpadit kiti jandi hai I
tam: kiwi baqtilrundhu dayaaricapatum nara aabha enum vellai whin arunachalap pradesatch charndatu, atu lover subansiri mawatttil ull hang gramatil irukkum lambu-supu put and pevarejas niruvanattal urbhatti seyyapadukintu.
tel: kiwi pands nudi tayarucheyabada nara aba ani piluvabada tellati wine arunachal pradesh nudi wastendi, dinni diguv subansiri jillaloni hong gramlo unde lambu-subu food and beverejes utpatti chestundi.
urd: kiwi fal se bani ek safed sharaab jise nara aabaa kehate hain arunachal pradesh se aati hai or use lower sibanseri zala ke hong gaauun main lambu-subo food and buregis taiyaar kiya jataa hai.
eng: A white wine made from kiwi fruit called Naara Aaba comes from Arunachal Pradesh and is produced by Lambu-Subu Food and Beverages at Hong village in the Lower Subansiri district.

ben: barshakale krushigat prayoggulite rimot sencing tathyer vyabhhar karte na para kshetre mul baadha halo yathest sankhya nirmegh aptical upagrahajanit tathyer aparaptata.
guj: purti sankhyama kalaud-free optical satellite datasetni aprapyata yomasani ritu daramiyaan krushini aplikeshan mate durvarti optical sensing datana upayogma ek mukhya avarodh che.
hin: paryaapt maatra main megh-mukt chakshush upgrah dataseton kii anuplabdhta monsoon ke mausam ke dauraan krishi anuprayogon ke liye chakshush sudur samvedan data kaa upyog karne main kaaphi had tak rukaawat daalati he.
kan: mod-mukt dhyuti upagrah dattanshasetgalu sakashtu sankhyeyalli labhyavilldiruvudu malegaldalli krishi sambandhit winneogagalige dhyuti dur samvedak dattanshavannu balsuvalli dodda todakagide.
mal: meghangloinera optical upagrah datasetukalute vendetra annattiൻre abhava kalavarshakkalat krishiyavashyaൾkkutakunn optical remot sensing data upyogikunnatile valioru pratibandha.
ori: yathest sankhyak megh-mukt aptikal upagrah tathabalir anupalavita heudi barsha ruture krushibhittik prajogaguik nimanthe 'aptikal rimot sensing data' bbbahar karivare eka mukhya pratibandhak .
pan: claud free aptical upgrah ankde di kami ik vighan paidaa kardi hai monsoon vich aptical upgrah di varton kheti aplikeshan de lai I
tam: podhumana annikyil megh alaiyance oleiel seyatkaikol druoud dokuppues ille, itu paruvamalike kalatil whilan payanpadugaluku oleiel dolaitur nunnuner druvulap prayogipatangu perum tatiyak irukkintu.
tel: tagin sankhyalo clour free drushya anubandha samachar samudayal alabhyat anedi varshakalamlo vyavasayik aplikeshans kos aptical sudur grahyath samacharanni vineoginchenduku ock pedd avarodha.
urd: barsaat ke mausam ke dauraan zardi istemalat ke liye aaptical remote sensong data ko istemaal karne kii khaatir claud free aaptical setalite data set kii mozon muqadaar kii adam dastyabi ek badi rukawat hai.
eng: The nonavailability of an adequate number of cloud-free optical satellite datasets is a major constraint for using optical remote sensing data for agricultural applications during the monsoon season.

ben: adhikar o maryadar prati sammaan poshan karte yate prativandhider prati baishamya pratirodh kara ya sei vishay kanavenshner 8 na dhara dalguli sachetanta baranor pratishruthir upar jor deya.

kan: i oppandad 8nae vidhiyu vikalte aadharit taratamyavannu tadeyalu hakkugalu mattu ghanateya bagge gaurayvannu uttejisuv saluvagi jagriti moodisuvalli pakshagal baddhateyannu ottiheluttade.
mal: bhinnsheshiyulavarotulla vivechana tatyan vende avkashaslkulla adravu antassu valartanural bodhvalkkarana uyartan kakshikalk vende pratibddhat convenshante artikle 8 unnipparyunnu.
ori: sammeghnar anuchchheda 8 guruth aarope karen ki pakshamane akshamtha prati bhedabhavaku pratihat kariva pin adhikar o maryada prati sammanabodhar paripason nimanthe chetana jaagran prati angeekarabaddha rahantu.
pan: sanvidhan da artical 8 apahjata vitakare da mukabala karan lai adhikars ate sanmaan nuun utshaahit karan lai jagarukta vadhaun lai parties di vachanagadhta 'te jor dinda hai|

tel: vaikalyam vichakshanku virudhanga hakkulu mariyu atmagaurva pat gauravanni pempondinche vapuga avagahan kalpinchenduku bhagswamus nibaddhathanu kanvension yokk nibandhan 8 nokki cheptundi.
urd: kunvanshan kii dafaa 8 frican ke mazori ke amitiyazi sulok kaa muqabla karne main haquk or vakaar ke ehtiram ko farvag dene ke liye shour ujagar karne ke ism par jor detii hai.
eng: Article 8 of the Convention stresses parties' commitment to raising awareness to foster respect for rights and dignity to counter disability discrimination.

ben: 1906 sale rejinald fesendener dwara pratham doorvarty audio prerane, alacjandarson alternater thek ekati tana taranga jale thanda kara carbon microphoner madhye die sarasari preran karaar anteno chalano hayesil.
guj: 1906maa reginald facnden dwara lamba antarna pratham dhwani prasaranma ellekandersan alternetter dwara prasarit karta antenane paanithi thanda thata carbon microphone marfate ek sidhu tarang moklvama aavyu hatu.
hin: 1906 main rejinald fesendan dwaara pratham lambii-duuri ke shravy prasaaran main, alexanderson olternetter se ek nirantar tarang ko sidhe sanchaar antena main jal se thande kiye gaye carbon microphone ke madhyam se bheja gaya.
kan: 1906ralli reginold fessendenn doorad eradu sthalgal naduvan mottamodal dhvani prasarandalli, alegsandersen paryayakadind ondu nirantar tarangavannu nirenind tampisid ingalad dhvanivardhakad moolak nervagi prasaran antenakke poorislagittu.
mal: 1906ൽ rejinaൾd fesseൻdൻ natattia adyatte diർghadurshabdasamprekshangsliൽ alaksandesൺ aaൾtaർnetoryൽninnull oru tutർchchayay tarangam weliankond tapa niyantricpat oru kaaർbൺ microphonilute samprekshan aaൻrinyi nerit naൽkappettirunnu.
ori: 1906 masihare reginald fecendennk dra karayaithiva pratham deergha-bbbadhan shabda sanycharanre, eka aalekjandarsan pratyavarttitraru aasuthiva eka niravachchhinna taranggaku sidhasaikh eka jal-sheethit carbon microphone madhyadei sanycharak antina madhyaku preran karayaithila .
pan: 1906 vich rejnald fasendon duara pahile lami duuri de shravni sanchars vich ik alegxendarshan altarnetter ton ik nirantar tarang sital-jal carbon microphone raaheen sanchari antine bal sidhe for te khichi gai see|
tam: 1906il reginald besandan menokont muthal netundoor radio olyparaple, alexandersen aldernatterilrundhu woru doder alai neeral-kulirutoppatt carbon microfone mulam neradiak transmitting andenauku anuppappattatu.
tel: raginald fesenden 1906 lo chacin modati sudur shabda prasaralo, ock alexandarsan alternetor nudi ock nirantrai tarangani, nitito challabarchabadd ock shabda prasarini dwara, prasara chestunn antennaloki neruga saraphra cheyabadindi.
urd: 1906 main rejinald kii jaanib se kiye gaye tavel faasale kii olen soti tarsel main aligzonderson alternitor se aane wali matavatar lahar ko pani se thande hone waale carbon microphone ke zarie brah rasat tarseli antina main daakhil kiya gaya.
eng: In the first long-distance audio transmissions by Reginald Fessenden in 1906, a continuous wave from an Alexanderson alternator was fed directly to the transmitting antenna through a water-cooled carbon microphone.

ben: 2008-9-era samay in.aar.i.ji.e 4.47 kotiroo beshi pariwarer janya karmsansthaner suyog kare deya ya 2007-8-era samay 3.39 koti pariwark antarbhukt karesil.

ori: 2008-09 masiha samaure, 'narega', 2007-08 re antarbhukt 3.39 koti paribar tuznare, 4.47 kotiru adhik paribar pin karmaniyukthi suyog yogai deithila .
pan: saal 2008-08 de khilaaph, saal 2008-09 de doran, na.re. e.g.aa ne 4.47 karod ton uddh locals nuun rozagar de mauke pradaan kithe I
tam: 2007-08 kaalakttil 3.39 koti kudumbangalukqup payanalitt narekha, 2008-09 kaalakttil 4.47 kotikum menoptt kudumbangaluku velaivaifugans valangiyadu.
tel: narega 2007-08 lo adukunn 3.39 kots kutumbalaku baduluga, 2008-09 lo, 4.47 kotlak paga kutumbalaku upadhi avakashalu kalpinchindi.
urd: saal 2008-09 ke dauraan narega ne 4.47 karod se zyaada gharaanon ko rojgaar ke mawaqa faraham kiye, jabaki 2007-08 main 3.39 karod gharaanon ko rojgaar ke mawaqa faraham kiye gaye the.
eng: During 2008-09, NREGA provided employment opportunities for more than 4.47 crore households, as against 3.39 crore households covered in 2007-08.
