ben: miyan mirer shibire, prati ekajner viruddhe charajner hisabe sepyra ingrej sainyader thek sankhya beshi haoya sattweo miraat thek khabar aasaar ag percent tader bapar ingrej aadhikarikder kono sandeh chhil na, evan khabarti aasaar pare tader sang mirater sepider kono gopan yogayog chhil kina ta jana tader pakshe kathin hay dandiesil.
guj: milan mirni chavnima sipioni sankhya angrej sainiko kartaan char jem ekthi vadhu hova chhataan, angrej adhikario paase meratthi samachar aavya tyaan sudhi temana vishe koi shanka n hati ane jayare saache ja samachar aavya tyaare temane sunishchit karvu mushkel laagyu ke teo meratna sipio sathe khaangi rite samparkma hatan ke nahi.
hin: haalanki miyaan mir shivi main angrej sainikon kii tulana main chaar ke mukaable ek rah kar sipaahiyon kii sankhya adhik thi, meerut se samachar pahunchne tak angrej afasar ke paas andeh karne koi kaaran nahin tha, or jab samachar pahunchaa, to unhen yah nishchit karne main mushkil hui ki ve gupt rup se meerut ke sipaahiyon ke saath sampark main the yaa nahin.
kan: mian mirn sena bidaradalli, sipayigalu aangl sainikarigint nalku pattu hchin sankhyeyalliddaradaru, meerutnind suddi baruvavaregu avar bagge aangl adhikarigalige yav sanshayvu iralill, mattu aa suddiyu tilid nantar, iverige avaru mirutn sipaigalondige rahasyavagi samparkadalliddaro illwo embudannu vichaarane madi nishchaisuvudu kashtvayitu.
mal: mian mere campil shippai english bharanmarute nalirti undairunnit meerutle ninnull vart varuvare english ofisarmark sanshaymonu illairunnuvennu matramall aa vart vannapothate, avar meerutille shippayilumai rahasyamai ashayvinimaium natatunnundo illayo enne udhappican prayasmaennu kantu.
ori: man mir thare thiva shivirare, yadio sipahimane inrej sainemananku chari: eka anupathare sankhyare athikram kariyaithile, meratru khabar naasiva paryyant inrej adhikareemanankar semanank upare kaunsi sandeh nathila, eban yetevela khabarati asi pahanchila, semane meratr sipahimanank sahit gupt bhavare yogayogra angnthi ki naahin janiva semanank pakshe kashtakar hoipadithila .
pan: mian mir de dera te sipahia, angarezi sainika ton char ton ik de ankde ton jiada san, angarezi afsaraan nuun onha baare koi oak nahi see per jadon mert ton ih kabar ai, onha nuun ih gal nishchit karna mushakil hoo gya ki oh emirt de sipahia naal choree-chhipe gal-baat kar rehe san jaaa nahi I
tam: miyan meer muqamil nalvaruku oruvar enjh vikittil angiley veerargans veet indiach sipaiess adhikamak irundaner enfodhilu, meeruttilrundhu seite varumvarai angiley adhikariluku endach chandekamum exvilly, eninu seite vant binnarum kuta menopati sipaisuku meerut sipaigasuton rakhsiyat doterpu ullda illaiya anpats avarkalal urudisey mudiavilly.
tel: mia mir shibera vadd, angley sainikulu okariki sipoile naluguri lekkan adhikanga unnappatiki, mirat nudi varth vachchent varaku angl adhikarulku anumanme raledu, ik varth andinapp vaaru mirat sipailatho rahasya sambhashanal chestunnaro ledo nirdarinchukode wariki kashttaram ayindi.
urd: miyaa mir ke camp main agarache sipaahiyon kii taadaad angrez sipaahiyon se char ek ke tanasib main thi, taahim meerut se khabar aane tak angrez afasuron ko in ke baare main koi shak naheen tha, or jab ye khabar pahunchi to inhen ye maalum karna mushkil ho gaya ki aayaa wo meerut ke sipaahiyon ke saath khufia tuur par robte main the yaa naheen.
eng: In the camp at Mian Mir, though the Sepoys outnumbered the English soldiers by four to one, the English officers had no suspicion about them until the news from Meerut arrived, and when the news did arrive, they found it difficult to ascertain whether they were or were not secretly in communication with the Meerut Sepoys.

ben: 2019-era hisabe bangladesher swaksharatar haar 74.7%; purushader kshetre evan 71.9% mahilader kshetre 77.4%.
guj: 2019 pramane 77.4% purusho ane 71.9% streeo sathe bangladeshno saksharata dar 74.7% che.
hin: 2019 tak bangladesh kii sakshartaa dar 74.7% he: purushon ke liye 77.4% he or mahilaon ke liye 71.9% he.
kan: bangladeshvu, 2019r velege, 74.7%dashtu saksharata darvannu hondiddu, purusharalli 77.4% mattu mahileyaralli 71.9%dashtide.
mal: 2019le kanakanusrich 74.7 shatamana bangladeshie saksharatanirak: purushanmariൽ 77.4 shatamanvu strikaliൽ 71.9 shatamanvu.
ori: 2019 suddha, bangladeshr sakshrata haar 74.7%: purushamanankar 77.4% eban mahidamanankar 71.9% .
pan: bangladesh da sakhrata dar2019 de hisaab naal 74.7% hai: maradas da 77.4% ate aurataan da 71.9%
tam: 2019aam antin nilavarapati vangadesatin eduttarivu 74.7%, itu angaluku 77.4% manllum pengaluku 71.9%.
tel: 2019 nati bangladesh aksharashyat 74.7%ga undi: purushullo 77.4%ga mariyu strilalo 71.9%ga undi.
urd: bangala desh kii khvandagi kii shrah 2019 tak 74.7 faisad hai: mardon ke liye 77.4 faisad or khwatin ke liye71.9 faisad.
eng: Bangladesh has a literacy rate of 74.7% as of 2019: 77.4% for males and 71.9% for females.

ben: 2015 saler 11i march, dah manmohan singh evan anaya panchjan abhiyukt mesurs. hindalco, suvendhu amitabh, de. bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla, evan pi.si. parkher viruddhe 1860 bhartiya dandavidheer dhara 120-bi evan 409 evan 1988-era durniti pratirodh iner dhara 13(1)(si), 13(1)(de)(iii) anusar ekajan visesh si.bi.aai bichaarak aparadher swikruti nen.
guj: 11 march, 2015na roj sii.bi.ai.na ek khas nyaayadhishe 1860na bhartiya dandasanhitani kalmo 120 bi ane 409 tatha 1988na bhrashtachar nivaran kaayadaani kalmo 13(1)(sii), 13(1)(dee)(3) hethalna gunha anvaye dow. manmohan singh ane paanch anaya aaropio mesars hindalko, subendhu amitabh, dee. bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla ane pe. sii. paarekh sameni babat dhyane lidhi.
hin: 11 march, 2015 ko ek vishesh si.bi.ai. nyaayadhish ne aparaadh kaa sangyaan lete hue doctor manmohan singh or paanch anya prativaadiyon, macers hindalco, shubhendu amitabh, di. bhattacharya, kumaar mangalam birla, or pi.si. paarekh, par bhrashtachar nivaaran adhinium, 1988 kii dhara 13(1)(si) or 13(1)(di)(iii) or bhartiya dand samhita, 1860 kii dhara 120-bi or 409 kaa ulanghan karne kaa aarope lagaaya tha.
kan: 2015r march 11randu, si.bi.i. visesh nyayadhisharobbaru, da. manamohan singh hagu itar ivaru apaditrad me. hindalco, subendu amitaabh, de. bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla, mattu pi.si. prakaash ivarugal virudh 1860r bhartiya dand samhiteya kalam 120-bi hagu 409, mattu 1988r bhrashtachar tade kaydeya kalam 13(1)(si), 13(1)(de)(iii)r adiyalli aparaadhd nyay vichaarane nadesidaru.
mal: oru pratyek si. bi. ai jadji, 2015 maaർchch 11n do. mൻmohൻ singu hiൻdaൽko company, subendu amitabh, de. bhattacharya, kumaർ mangalam biർle, pi.si. parakh enni mat anch pratikalu 1860le indiaൻ shikshaniamattille 120-bi, 409 enni vakuppukൾku, 1988le akimati nirodhan niyamattille 13(1)(si), 13(1)(de)(iii) enni vakuppukൾku anusrich kutam cheitathai conteti.
ori: 11 march 2015re, jane stantra si.bi.aai. bichaarpati du. manamohan singh o annga panch abhiyukt, yatha- mesarse. hindalako, subendhu amitabh, di. bhattacharyan, kumaar manggalam birla eban pi. si. parakhank virodhare bharatiya pinggal code, 1860r dhara 120-bi o 409 eban durniti nivaran ine, 1988r dhara 13(1)(si), 13(1)(de)(3) adhinare hoithiva ullanghanaku sagyanaku nele.
pan: 11 march 2015 nuun, ik vishesh see bi ai jaj ne bharati dandavali di dhaara 120-bi ate bharati dand sanhita di dhaara 409 ate bhrishtachar roktham act 1988 di dhaara 13 (1) (see), 13 (1) (di) (iii) sacshan tahit daa. manmohan singh ate panch hor mulazama arthat hindalko, sebandu amitaabh, di bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla ate pi. see. parakh viruddha apraadh da notice lya l
tam: 2015 march 11 andu, sicipu sipis nitipati 1860aam antu india tandana sattatil ull kushwabbrivues 120-bhi manllum 409in kithum 1988aam antu urol tatupbuch sattatil ull kushwabbrivues 13(1)(chi) manllum 13(1)(di)(iii)in kithum doctor manmohan singh manllum itar aindhu kullram sumattapattorana thiruvalr hindalco, subendu amitabh, di. bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla, bhi.chi. parkh akhiyor mitan kudwatai kawnatil edudukondar.
tel: 2015 march 11na, ock pratyek sibiai nyayamurti da manmohan singh, mariyu shriyutulu hindalco, subend amitabh, de. bhattacharya, kumar mangala birla, mariyu pi. si. parakh anu aiduguru itar ninditulupai bhartiya shiksha smruti 1860 loni 120-bi mariyu 409 sekshani, mariyu aviniti nivardhak chatta yokk 13(1)(si), 13(1)(de)(3) sekshans krind ner vicharan jaripar.
urd: 11 march 2015 ko, ek khasusi si bi aai jajj ne taziraat hind 1860 kii dafaa 120 bi or 409 or insudad badunwani act 1988 kii dafaa 13 (1) (si), 13 (1) (dee) (3) ke tahat doctor man mohan singh or digar panch miljamin yani maysarz handalko, sobindhu amitabh, dee bhattacharya, kumar mangalam birla, or bi si parakh ke khilaaf jurm kaa notice liya.
eng: On 11 March 2015, a Special CBI judge took cognizance of the offense under Sections 120-B and 409 of the Indian Penal Code, 1860 and Sections 13(1)(c), 13(1)(d)(iii) of Prevention of Corruption Act, 1988, against Dr Manmohan Singh and five other accused namely M/s. HINDALCO, Subendhu Amitabh, D. Bhattacharya, Kumar Mangalam Birla, and P.C. Parakh.

ben: fridhem hardir mate, krishna-aitihyake uttarer aitihyer sang millie dewar prabanta thaka satveo prachin "dakshini krishnabad"-era praman royas.
guj: freedhem hardina math anusaar, krishna-paramparaone uttarni prathao tarike ganavavaanu chalan hova chhataan prarambhik ‘‘dakshin krishnavad’’no puraavo che.
hin: freedam hardi ke anusaar, aarambhik "dakshini krishnavad," ke saboot mili hai haalanki krishnavad paramparaon ko uttari paramparaon se jode jane kaa adhik jhukaav rahaa he.
kan: fridhelm hardiya prakaar, krishna-sampradayagainnu uttarad parampareyavendu gottupadisuv pravruttiya hortagiu, puraatan "dakshind krishna panth"da bagge puraveide.
mal: krishna parmparyase watnakൻ parmparyansliൽ petuttunn pravantaundairie, adyakal "dakshin krishnamatattin" telivukalunten freedheൽ haർde parayunnu.
ori: fridhem hardink mat anuyani, bahu poorvaru "dakshinatya krishnapanth" thibar praman mile, yadio krishna paramparati uttaranychal parampararu utpanna boli kahibar pravantha rahichhi.
pan: fridehalam hardi de anusaar, agete "ngkhani krishnavad" da praman hai ish de bawajood ki krishna riti rivaajan nuun utari rivaajan naal jodiya janda hai I
tam: krishna mripughas vadanattch serndavai ena vakipadutum bhoku ulfodhilu aarambh kalatleye "dhennattu krishna mripu" irundathangu aadharam ulldak frithem hardy karuddut thervikwar.
tel: fridhelm hardi prakara, krishna sampradayas uttar sampradayalku aapadinchenduku moggu unnappatiki, "dakshin krishna tatwaniki" munupati sakshya undi.
urd: fredhelam hardi ke mutabik, shumali ravayat main krishna ravayat ko mukhtas karne ke rajahaan ke baavjood ibtidai "janubi krishna asm" kaa sabot maujuud hai.
eng: According to Friedhelm Hardy, there is evidence of early "southern Krishnaism," despite the tendency to allocate the Krishna-traditions to the Northern traditions.

ben: asansoler grishmakal garam o shushk evan shite halaka thanda.
guj: asanasolma garam ane suka unala tatha halwa shiyala hoya che.

ori: aasansolre uttapat o shushk greeshma kal eban haluka sheeta kal anubhut hoithaye.
pan: anasol vich garam ate khushk garami ate halaki sardi hundi hai|
tam: achanolil kodai kalam veppamagaum vantsiagaum, kulirgalam mitmagaum irukkinsona.
tel: asansollo vesavikalam vedigan, podigan mariyu shitakalam mostrugan untundi.
urd: asanasol main garam or khushk mausam garma or sardiyon kaa mausam halka hota hai.
eng: Asansol has hot and dry summers and mild winters.

ben: natun bhartiya cinemar mato aro beshi aadhunik chitranupat dekha ya yar lakshya aitihyagat baliudy nandaniktake veng phela.
guj: new indian cinema jeva vadhu aadhunik drashticon dekhaya che je parampragat bolivodna saundaryashastrane todi nakhvanu lakshya raakhe che.
hin: nae bhartiya cinema jaisaa or bhi aadhunik drushtikon aayaa he jo paaramparik bollybodi kalaatmakataa se pare hatane kaa prayaas kar rahaa he.
kan: sampradayik baliwooddin kalabhiruchiannu todedu hakuv uddeshvull bharatad hoss aleya chitradantah hechu aadhunik dristicongalu kandubaruttve.
mal: sampradayik bollywood sandaryashastravumai waypiriyuvaൻ lakshyamidunn navbharatiyasinim polayull kututal aadhunikmay pariprekshyangൾ drushyamakunnu.
ori: adhik aadhunik drushtibhangeeman yatha 'da neu indian cinema' dekhivaku missithae yahaki paramparik valiudiya saundharyabodharu alaga hebar lakshya rakhichhi .
pan: hor aadhunik paripekh jive ki nayu indian cinema aa gaye han jo ravaiti belivood sundarta ton baahar nikalan da pursharth karade han I
tam: putu yug india cinema bonthe melum chil navinuk khannottas uruvaki vaymayana baliud anogial mripai maderiyamick murbadukintu.
tel: new indian cinema vanti marint navin drushtikonal sampradayak baliod kalatmakat nudi veru padata uddeshyanga pratyakashamvutai.
urd: new indian cinema jese jadid nakta nazar jaahir hote hain jin kaa maqsad ravayati baali woden jamaliat se hat kar dagar akhtiyaar karna hai.
eng: More modern perspectives like the New Indian Cinema appear which aim to break with the traditional Bollywoodian aesthetics.

ben: field haki hal ekati dalgat khela yekhane ekati daler khelwarra bankano stick vyabhhar kare pratipaksh daler golpost baltake aghat kare, chhenche, dhakka mer baa thele die gol karaar pracheshta kare.
guj: medani hoki ek jooth ramat che ke jema kheladionu ek jooth valeli lacdiono upayog karine dadane fatakarine, pasaar karine, dhakeline athva jhataka marie pratispardhi juuthana golma nakhvana prayatno kare che.
hin: field hockey ek samuhik khel he jisamen dal ke khilaadi ghumaavdaar chhadiyon kaa prayog karke gend ko balpurvak maar kar, gend ko hawa main uda kar, dhakel kar yaa halke se maar kar virdohi dal ke gol main gend daal kar gol karne kii koshish karte hai.
kan: field hakiyu tandad aatvagiddu, idralli tandad aatgarru tudi donkagiruv kolugalind edurali tandad goln olkke chendannu hit, scoop, push, athwa flick maduv moolak golgathannu galisalu yatnisuttare.
mal: valanera stickukalupayogich aticho, scoup cheito, tallio, tattio ethir timinte goliel pantetican kaliarute oru tea shramikunn tea ga fild hoki.
ori: 'fild haki' heudi eka khel yeunthireki khelanimanankar eka dal bakr baadiman bbbahar kari eka balku aghat kari, scup kari, dhakka dei kimba haluka kshipra aghat dei pratipakshar khelanimanank golkshetra madhyaku gol karivaku prayas karithaye .
pan: field heaki ik khed hai jise vich khidaari gol lan di koshish karade han geind nuun mar ke, chak ke, dhaka de jaaa geind nuun dooji team de gol vich gol dande naal mar ke I
tam: pildu hackey enpatu oruvit ani vilyaddu, atil woru ani veerars valaint kuchitp payanbadutti edir aniin colingul bandai aditu, scoop saitu, talli alltu blic saitu cole atick mushcipargas.
tel: fild haki anedi jattuga aade aat, dinilo atgall vampu tirigin karralato bantini kodutu, laputu, nedutu, leda vidilistu eduti jattu gol loki vesi skoru chatenduku prayatnisthar.
urd: field hockey ek tem kaa khel hai jis main khilaadiyo kii ek tem mude hue dundon kaa istemaal karte hue mukhaalf tem ke gol main gend ko maarne, scope karne, dhikka dene, yaa takaraane se gol score karne kii koshish krati hai.
eng: Field hockey is a team game in which a team of players attempts to score goals by hitting, scooping, pushing, or flicking a ball into an opposing team's goal using curved sticks.

ben: prithivi prushtha thek 60 mil (100 kimi) upare, bayur rasyanik ganti uchitar upar prabalbhave nirbharshil evan bayumandalti laghutar gases (aanvik oxygen, hilliam evan hydrogen) samrudh hay ya.
guj: pruthvini sapati parathi 60 mile (100 kilometer) upar, havanu rasayanic bandharan unchai upar atyant avalambit banii jaaya che ane vatavaran halwa vayuo (atomic oxijan, hilliam ane hydrogen)thi samrudh banii jaaya che.
hin: prithvi kii sataha se 60 mile (100 ki.me.) upar hawa kii rasinic sanrachana bahut zyada oonchaai par nirbhar karti he or vayumandal main halki gaison (aanvik oxigen, helium or hydrogen) kii maatra bad jaati he.
kan: bhoomiy melmaiind 60 mailigaligint (100 ki.me.) mele, gaaliya rasayanik sanyojaneyu ettarad mele fivravagi avalambitwagiruttade mattu vatavrandalli galigint hagurvad anilgalu adhikavagiruttve (parmanvak aamlajanak, hilium mattu jalajanak).
mal: bhamoparitalattilninn 60 mile (100 kilometre) uyarattil vayuvinte rasamain uyarate shaktamai ashrayikkayu antariksha (anurupattilull oxijan, hilium, hydrajan enni) bhara kushanera vatakalal sampannamavukyu cheyu.
ori: pruthivee prushtharu 60 mayil (100 ki.mi.) upare, baur rasarhnic sanrachana uchchatha upare bahulbhave nirbharashil hoiyaaye eban baumandal haluka gasgudik (amrjan parmaanu, hilidham eban udjan) re paripurna hoiyaaye .
pan: dharati de satah ton 60 maliz (100 kilomitir) upar, hawa di rasayanak banaavat uchaayi te nirbhar hoo jandi hai ate vayumandal halaki gaisaan (atami oxygen, healium ate hidrogen) naal sampan hoo janda hai I
tam: bhumiin meshrabbilrundhu 60 milluku (100 kimi) milke, kallerin vedi ultakkum peritum uyarattych sarndulldu, ange valimandalatil ilaguana vayuxs (anunili axijan, heliam manllum hyderajan) sevivak ulsana.
tel: bhu uparita nudi 60 maithal (100 kimi) aguvan, gas yokk rasayanik mishrama anedi attu mid balanga aadharita ayi, vatavrana telican vayuvulu (parmaanu oxygen, hilium, hydrogen) to samriddha avutundi.
urd: satah jameen se 60 mail (100 kullu meter) oupar, hawa kii camiai tarkeeb majbootee ke saath artfa par manhsir ho jaati hai or fizaa halki geson (atomi oxygen, helium or hydrogen) se afazoda ho jaati hai.
eng: Above 60 miles (100 km) from Earth's surface, the chemical composition of air becomes strongly dependent on altitude and the atmosphere becomes enriched with lighter gases (atomic oxygen, helium and hydrogen).

ben: ubhay sansad bhavaner mukhya aadhikarik bharter up-rashtrapati o rajyasvar cheyarman evan loksvar spikar duto channelke sampoornbhave yukt karte sammya han yate arthaniti, karmadakshata o caryaarita nie aasa ya.
guj: tethi karkasar, kaaryakshamata ane asarkarakta laavavaa, banne gruhna mukhya adhikario - bharatna uparashtrapati ane rajyasabhana adhyaksha tatha loksabhana spikar banne chenlana ekeekaran mate sahamat thayan che.
hin: kamakharchi, dakshata or prabhavakaarita laane ke liye, dono sadanon ke peethasin adhikari -bharat ke uparashtrapati or rajya sabha ke sabhapati tathaa lok sabha ke adhyaksh - ne donon channelon ke vilay ke liye sahmati di.
kan: mitvyaya, dakshate mattu prenamkaritvavannu aagamaduv saluvagi, sansattin ubhay sadangal adhyaksharu - bharatad uprashtrapati mattu rajyasabheya sabhadhyaksha hagu loksabheya speekar - i eradu vahinigalannu vilingolislu sammathisidru.
mal: atinaൽ chelve churukkuvanu karyakshamatyu phalapraptiyu kaivarikvanu paർlameൻrelle iru sabhakalutayu adhyakshanmaർ - rajyasabha cheyaർmaanay uparashtrapatiyu loksabha spikkaru - rand chanlulu layippikkaൻ thirumanichu.
ori: tenu mitbi, daksh eban fatprad kariva pin, sansadar ubhay grihar peetasin padadhikareemane - bharatar up-rashtrapati tatha rajnsabhar sabhapati eban lokalbhar vachaspati - chanel duitiku mishaideva pin raji hoithile.
pan: arth vivstha vich nipunnata te kamyaabi de lai sansad de donon gharaan de pradhani afasar - bharat de up- mouth mantri , rajaya sabha de pradhan ate lok sabha de vakta ne donon chenla nuun jodan da faisalaa lya hai I
tam: sicanam, seyaltision manllum payaniddutalap pellum nokil natalumantting iru avaikalin talamaidangum adhikariesum - adavatu india dunai janadhipati manllum manilangalvait talaivarum makalvaich sabanayakarum - ivviru alaivarichikhales onkinikach sammadittanar.
tel: mitvyayaniki, samarthat mariyu prabhavashilathanu tisukuravadaniki ganu, parliament ubhay sabhal priseading adhikarulin bharat uprashtrapati, rajyasabh chairman mariyu lok sabh spikarle rend chhanall vilina cheyadaniki angikarincharu.
urd: chanaan cha maishith, carakardagee or mousareet lane ke liye parlemint ke dono evaanon ke presoiding afasaran yani nib sadar jamhori hind or rajya sabha ke chairman or lok sabha ke spikar ne dono chennalon ko zam karne par ittefaq kiya.
eng: So as to bring about the economy, efficiency and effectiveness, the Presiding Officers of both the Houses of Parliament - the Vice-President of India and Chairman of Rajya Sabha and the Speaker of Lok Sabha - agreed to merge the two Channels.

mal: kushanjucontirikkaanangil indyayute iokkumatiute valർchch kayatumatiute valർchchaye marikatannu.

pan: bharat da daraamad wadha ait on de bhavajood us de baramad vich wadha hoia hai I

ben: vruddhir prathmik paryay pashukhadya fasle beshi pariman protein upadan thake evan ta sahajpachy has kintu tader falan (mott pariman baa jaivabhar) kam thake.
guj: vikasana prarambhik tabakkama chara pakma protein unchu praman hoya che ane te samanya rite saraltathi pachi jaaya tevu hoya che, parantu temani upaj (biomasni kul matra) ochhi hoya che.
hin: vikaas ke bahut praanbhik charnon main chaara-fasalon main ucch maatra main protein tatv hote hai or praayah aasaani se pachne yogya hoti hai, par unki upaj (kul aaytan yaa jaev bhaar) kam hota he.
kan: mevin belegalu belvanigeya thira aarambhik hantagamalli hchin protine anshavannu hondiruttve mattu samanyavagi sulabhavagee jirnavaguttave, adare avugal iluvariyu (ottu gatra athwa jaivikarashi) kadimayiruttade.
mal: valare ilamprayattilull kalittetvilakൾ uyർnnatotiൽ proteiൻ atangiyavayu saadharan ellupattiൽ dahikunnavyumanankil avayute vidove (motta alavo , jaivadravyamo) kullwan.
ori: fasalar prarambhik starare pashukhadya fasalre adhik matrare jeevasar upadan thae, eban eha sadharanthati sahajre hajjm hoithaye, kintu ehar utpadan (mot pariman ba jaib indhan) kam rahithae .
pan: vikas de shuruaati padaavaan vich chaare dis fasalas vich protein di maataraa vadhere hundi hai ate assam for 'te aasaani naal pachanyog hundi hai, per uhanaas di paidaavaar (biomas di kul maataraa) ait hundi hai|
tam: valarchiin aarambh cuttatl divaanap bhairil uyaralu puradachatu irukkum, botwak are elitel seremanamakum, eninu avadhqin makasul (mott alavu alltu uirtral) kuraivagave irukkum.
tel: pashugras pantel perugudal toli dashallo adhik masakritulu kaligi undi, sadharannga sulabhanga jirnmavutai, kaani vat digubadi (motta parimana leda jeevapadardha) takkuvaga untundi.
urd: nishvonima ke ibtidai murahil main chaare kii fasalon main protein kii aala muqadaar hoti hai or aam tuur par aasaani ke saath hajam ho jaati hain, lekin in kii paidavar (jamla hujjam yaa biomas) kam hota hai.
eng: Fodder crops at very early stages of growth have high protein content and are usually easily digestible, but their yield (total volume or biomass) is low.

ben: seti caryanirbahi evan vigyan o karmasuchi caralay chadao, "niti, swasthy kutniti evan yogayog vyavastha", "parichalan o prashasan", "najardari evan roger khabar", "gaveshanagar vyavastha evan network", "apkalin prastuti o pratikria" evan "sadharan swasthy pratishthansmuh o gaveshana"-r sang samyukta sansthar bivinn vibhag royas.
guj: any kaaryakari ophis ane vigyan tatha program ophis uparant agencies anek vibhaago ‘niti, aarogya mutsaddigiri ane pratyayan’, ‘wahivat ane sanchalan’, ‘dekharekh ane rog buddhimatta’, ‘prayogshala paddhati ane networks’, ‘katokti mateni tayari ane pratibhav’ tatha ‘jaher aarogya ane sanshodhan’ sathe vyavahaar karva mate dharave che.
hin: kaaryakari karyaalay or ek vigyaan evam kaarykram karyaalay ke alaava agency ke kai vibhaag hai jo "niti, swasthya rajnay, or sampreshan," "prabandhan or prashasan," "aavekshan or rog aasuchana,""prayogshaala pranaliyaan or network," "apaat sthiti ke liye taiyaari or pratikriya," or "saarvajanik swasthya santhaan or shodh" par kaam karte hai.
kan: i seva sanstheyu ader kaaryakari kacheri mattu vigyan hagu yojana kacheriya jotege, "kaaryaniti, aarogya rayabhar mattu sanvahan", "nirvahane mattu aadlit", "nigavane mattu rog suddisangrah", "prayogalaya vyavasthegalu mattu jalagalu", "turtu paristati sannaddhate mattu spandane", hagu "sarvajanik aarogya sansthegalu mattu sanshodhane" ivugannu nodicolluv halvaaru vibhagagalannu sah hondide.
mal: exicautive ofisu sayൻs aaൻd program ofisu kootate "nayavu arogyanyatantravu ashayvinimavu", "manejmeൻr bharanwu", "nirikshanvu rogparyavekshanvu", "laborttery samvidhanau neitvർkkukalu", "atiyantar sahacharyaslotulla tayyaretupu pratikaranwu", "potu arogyasthapanu gaveshanvu" enniv kaikaryam cheiyunn niravadhi vibhagatelu ejൻsikund.
ori: ehar karyannirvahi addis eban eka vigyan o program addis bpatit, "neeti, ssthya kutaneethi, o yogayog", "pravandhan o prashasan", "nirikshan o badhi sambandhiya suchana", "parikshagaar brivastha o netark", "jaruri paristate nimanthe prasnuti o prathikria" eban "janassthgh anusthan o gaveshana" aadir parichakana nimanthe sansthatir anek vibhaag rahichhi.
pan: isde karjkari dafatar ate ik vigyaan ate program dafatar ton ilava, ejansi col "neeti, sihat kootaniti ate sammelan", "prabandhan ate prasashan", "nigrani ate rog khuphia", "prayogshala pranalia ate netvarak", "emerjansi tiari ate jawaab", ate "jantak sihat sansthavaan ate khoj" naal najithn wale kai bhaag han|
tam: ind muhamiku woru paniniraivenuchu aluvalagamum ore anaivial manllum panittitt aluvalagamum iruppatu matuminri, "kolka, chugadharip pechuvarts manllum dakhavaltoderpu," "melanmay manllum nirvagam," "ganganipu manllum noysar ulu," "parichodanake kuta amibbues manllum valiamibbues," "avacharakalat dayarnil manllum natwatiky", "botuch chugadhar niruvanangs manllum araichi" akhiyavataike kavaniduk kollum pal brivuesum ulsana.
tel: dani karyanirvahak karyalaya mariyu ock science and program karyalayanto pat, "vidhana, arogya dautyam mariyu samachar marpidi," "nirvahan mariyu paripalan," "paryavekshan mariyu vyadhi samachar," "prayogshal vyavasthal mariyu netvaries," "atyavasar paristateki sansiddhat mariyu pratispandan," mariyu "prajarogya sansthal mariyu parishodhan" vanti vatini nirvahinche anek vibhagal aa sansthalo unnai.
urd: is ke agzective afas or since or program afas ke alaava, agenci ke pas kai dvision bhi hain jo "polisi, sahat kii sifaarit kari or mawasalaat," "manzimint or intazaamy," "nigranee or bemaari kii intelie jins," "lebartry ke nizaam or net varik," "hangaami taiyaari or rudamal, " or "awami sahat ke udaaron or tahaqiq" se mataalak hain.
eng: Besides its Executive Office and a Science and Programme Office, the agency also has several divisions dealing with "policy, health diplomacy, and communication," "management and administration," "surveillance and disease intelligence," "laboratory systems and networks," "emergency preparedness and response," and " public health institutes and research."

ben: haora shahrer itivrutt (pratham o dvitiya khand) shirshak 1994 o 19995-te prakashith tar janmasahar haora sampoorn itihas sankalane ek agrani bhumika paalan karen adhyapak asitkumar bandopadya.
guj: professor asitkumar bandopadhaye 1994 ane 1995maa potana watan shaher haavrana sampurna itihasanu sampadan karvama payaroop bhumika bhajvi, jene haavara shahrer ithibrito (pratham ane dwitiya bhag) shirshak apayu.
hin: professor asitkumar bandopadhyaay ne 1994 or 1995 main apane grih-nagar, haavda ke sampurna itihaas ko haavda shahrar itivrutt (pehla or doosraa khand) naam se sankalit karne main mahatvapurn bhoomika nibhaai he.
kan: praadhyapakarad asitkumar bandopadhyay 1994 mattu 1995ralli haura shahrer itibrutto (modalane mattu eradne samput) emb shirshikeyadialli tamm huttoorad haurad sampoorna itihasavannu sangrahisuvalli modaligaragi kaaryanirvahisidru.
mal: 1994, 1995 enni waർshanoliൽ, haera sahareർ itibritto (one, rand walyangൾ) end granthanamattiൽ profsർ asit kumaർ bandyopadhya tൻre swadeshmay harryute sampooർnnacharitra samaharikkunnatiൽ maaർggadർshakmay pankuvahichu.
ori: prafesar asithkumar bandopadhan nij janma seher hadar sampoorna itihash sangkalan karivare mukhya bhoomika grahan karithile, yaha 'hada saharer itivritto' (pratham o dtiya khand) sheershakare 1994 o 1995 masihare prakashit.
pan: prohaisar asitkumar bandaopway ne aapne kitaab "haavada saharer itibrrito" (pihals ate duja bhaag) aapne shahir haavada da ithas saal 1994 ate 1995 vich daraj kar ke ik mahatavpuuran bhumika nibhaai hai I
tam: perasirier asidkumar bandopadhyay 1994 & 1995il tanatu chont urakiya haouravin mughaumayana varalardaait dokupadil woru munnodiagap bangu vakittar, athangu haoura chaharer idhiprito (muthal manllum erandam dokubbu) enab peyariopattatu.
tel: proteesar asit kumar bandopadhay aayan sonthur howrah sampoorna charitran 1994 mariyu 1995 lo howrah saharr itibritto perun (modati mariyu rendav bhagan) sankalana cheyadao margdarshakuluga vyavaharincharu.
urd: prophesar isit kumar bandeopadhay ne 1994 or 1995 main apne aabaai shahar haavar kii mukammal taarikh martab karne main rahanumayana kirdaar adaa kiya jis kaa unwan haavar suhrier etibretu (pahali or duusari jald) hai.
eng: Professor Asitkumar Bandyopadhyay played a pioneering role in compiling the complete history of his hometown Howrah titled as Howrah Saharer Itibrrito (First and Second Volume) in 1994 & 1995.

ben: desher pradhan nadee o jalpather madhyam barshikabhave praia 4 koti 40 laksh metric ton jahaji mal sthananter kara has.
guj: varshe lagbhag 4.40 crod metric ton mal deshni mukhya nadeeo ane jalmargo dwara vahan thai che.
hin: lagbhag 4 karod 40 lakh metric ton kaa maal har varsh desh kii pramukh nadiyon or jalmargon ke madhyam se parivahan kiya jaataa he.
kan: deshad pramukh nadigalu mattu jalmargagal moolak varshikavagi sumaru 44 dashalaksh metrick tongalshtu sarkugainnu sagislaguttade.
mal: rajyate pradhan nadis, jalmarggarhs ennivilute etand 44 dashalaksha metric ton charaka prativarsha nikkunnat.
ori: deshar mukhya nadi eban jazpathare barshik praia 4.4 koti metrik tanr maal paribehan hoithaye .
pan: desh de mouth darias te jal marga ton lagaing 44 lakh metric ton da mal salana dhoia janda hai I
tam: nottin mukiya nadihas manllum nirth tatangs valiyag anduthorum 44 million metric ton charakup bhokuvarattu selkintu.
tel: eta dadapu 4.4 kots metric tonnul saruku desh pradhan nadulu mariyu jalmargal dwara ravana avutundi.
urd: malik ke bade dariyaayon or aabi guzargahon se salana takreeban 4.4 karod metric tin jahazi maal muntaqal kiya jataa hai.
eng: About 44 million metric tonnes of cargo are moved annually through the country's major rivers and waterways.

ben: bharter samarthan afghanistaner sarkar evan janaganer chahida o agradhikar dwara parichalith has, afgan sarkarer anshidari sang caryakram chalano has evan prakalpaguli afghanistan bistrut elaka jure chhadie royas.
guj: bharat samarthan afghanistanna loko ane sarkarani aavashyakatao ane agratao dwara disha paame che; afghan sarkarani bhagidarima caryo haath dharay che, ane samagr afghanistanma bahola vistarma prakalpo prasari rahya che.
hin: bharat kaa samarthan sarkaar evam afghanistan ke logon kii jaruraton or praathamiktaaon dwaara nirdeshit hai; kaary afgani sarkaar ke saath hissedari main kiye jate hai or pariyojnaayen afghanistan ke vyapak kshetron main faili hui hai.
kan: bharatad nervu afghanistanad sarkaar mattu gener agatyagalu mattu adyategalind nirdeshitwagide; afghan sarkaarad sahbhagitvadalli kaarya chatuvatikegannu kaigolllagide, mattu afghanistandadyant vyapakwagi vividh valayagamalli yojanegathannu vistarislagide.
mal: afghanisthaൻ sർkkariൻreyu janathyutayu aavashyau muൻgananak indyayute pintutek vaikanikunnat; india afghanisthaൻ sർkkarumai pankucherukayu afganisthanitnilam vyapitchukithikunn vividhrangaslilull pravർttanapaddhatikൾ ateedukkukayu cheiyunnu.
ori: bharatar sahayatha aalganistan sarkar tatha janatank aavashyakata eban pravamikatagudik dra parichalit ate; karyankalapagudik aangan sarkarnk sahit sahabhagitare grahan karayaushi, eban prakalpagudik samagra afganisanare bhinna bhinna kshetrare bapt hoi rahichhi .
pan: bharat di sahita us di sarkaar te afganistan de locals di zarurta te tarajiha upar hai; afgani sarkaar di hisedari naal crias kitia jandias han ate afganistan de khulhe ilakaia vich com chal rehe han I
tam: aapqanistan arasu manllum makalin deviles munnurimikhales adippatiagak konde indiavin adrv amaindulldu; aapkhan arasuton gootuserndu natwatikis menokolopadukindena, adebol aapqanistan muruvatum parant pal turaikalil dittangs menokolopadukindena.
tel: bharat istunn maddattuku margdarshakal afghanistan prabhutvan mariyu prajal avasarai mariyu praadhanyathl ; afghanistan prabhutva bhagswamyanto karyakalapas chepattabadutunnai, alage afghanistan antata annoprantallo projectulu vyapinchi unnai.
urd: bhaarat kii hamayat afghanistan kii hukuumat or avaam kii zaruuryat or trigehat ke mutabik hai; sargarmiyaan afgan hukuumat ke saath sharakit main anjaam di jaati hain, or mansoobey afghanistan bhar main vasia ilaksam ilaakon main faile hue hain.
eng: India's support is guided by the needs and priorities of the Government and the people of Afghanistan; activities are undertaken in partnership with the Afghan government, and projects are spread across Afghanistan in a wide range of areas.

ben: ataev, anaya desher naagarikatva thackle bhartiya naagarikatva o bhotadhikar harate have.
guj: atle jo tame anaya deshnu nagarikatva dharavata ho, to tame bharat nagarikta gumavi beso chho ane tamaaro matdan karavaano adhikar pan.

urd: to, agar aap ke pas dusare malik kii shahrit hai to aap apni hindustani shahrit or apna vote dene kaa haq kho dete hain.
eng: So, if you posses another country's citizenship, you lose your Indian citizenship and your right to vote.

ori: udhajan bashpaku vanaspati telre mishile trans snehasar utpanna hoithaye, yaha bavasaik seka-samagreere eban adhikansh bhojanalaya tatha fast good chenre randhiva pin bbbahar karayaithaye.
pan: hidrogen vich vanastpati tel paa ke trans fat bande han jo ki aam beak kithe hoe padarths ate ziadatar restoraan ate fast food di dukanaas vich varte jaande han I
tam: mallupakkak koloubbu enpatu tawar annail hyderajanunch cherppadan mulam dayaaricapadukintu, itu vanik ritiyana bekri unvukhalilum perumbalan unavagangs manllum palgil durith unu niliangalin samaiyaliu payanbaduttapadukintu.
tel: vanijyaparanga bak chacin wasteulalo mariyu dadapu anni bhojanshalas mariyu fast food shrenulalo upayoginche shakh nuneku hydrogen cherchabadvall trance fatt erpadtai.
urd: trans charbayan tizaarati sinki hui ashya main or zyaada tar restaurant or fast food silasilon main khaana pakaane ke liye istemaal hone waale sabjiyon ke tel main hydrogen shamil karne ke nateeza main hoti hain.
eng: Trans fats result from adding hydrogen to vegetable oils used in commercial baked goods and for cooking in most restaurants and fast-food chains.

ben: grishmakal matratirikt garam, m mase nichu elakagulite wapamatra 50° centegrade (122° fahrenheit) charie ya ya tapapravaher srushti kare, yeguli pratyekati shay shay bhartiyake mer phelte par.
guj: unalo aatyantik rite garam hoya che; nichanavala vistaroma me mahinanu wapamana 50° celsius (122° pheranhite)thi pan vadhi shake che, je senkado bharatiyone maari shake tevaan fiver garamina mojan sarje che.
hin: greeshmakaal main bahut garmi hoti he; jahaan nichle ilaakon main may ke dauraan taapmaana 50 degree celsius (122 degree pheranhite) se bhi adhik ho saktaa he jisase taap lahar ke kaaran saikadon bharatiyon kii mrityu ho sakati he.
kan: besigeyalli fivravagi kaveriruttade; me tinglalli taggu pradeshgamalli 50° se.gintalu (122° fya.) hechagabahudad wapamanavu prationdu nooraru bharatiyar prana tegeyaballantah bisi gaaliya alegalige karanvaguttade.
mal: venൽkkalam atyadhik chutultan; nurukanakin indyakare kollaൻ kaviunn ushnatarangasliletikuvidha tainn pradeshsille tapanil 50 degree seൽshyasil (122 degree farൻheat) kootam.
ori: greeshmakal atsadhik bhavare garam ate; me' maasare nimnasth anychalguthikare wapamatra 50° celsius (122° pharenhit)ku athikram karipare, yahaki taap leharir karan hoithaye, yaha madhyaru pratyeka shah shah bharateeianku mari deipare .
pan: garamia vich bohut tata hoo janda hai; herele ilakaia vich wapamana , 50 ° C (122° F) ton uddh sakda hai, jise kaaran garam havaavaan chaldia han jo ki har saal sankaphaas bharatia di mout da kaaran bandia han I
tam: ingu kotialam kodikum; talwana bakudikasil mee maatam 50° chi (122° ef) veppaniliait tandlam, its vilaivak webbp alaiies undaki are ovvonem noorrukankkana indiakalin urek kutickekutia adddel kontawai.
tel: vesvi kalamlo mitimirin vedimi untundi; lottt prantallo ushnograthal 50° si (122° eff) datwacchu, ivi vandladi bhartiyul pranas harinchagal vedi galpulku daari tistai.
urd: mausam garma be had garam hota hai, nashibi ilaakon main mai ke dauraan darja hararat 50 digree celsius (122 digree forn hite) se tajaviz kar saktaa hai, jis kii vajah se garmi kii lehren paida hosakti hain jin main se harek saikadon hindustaniyon ko halock kar sakati hain.
eng: Summer is exceedingly hot; temperatures in low-lying areas may exceed 50° C (122° F) during May, leading to heat waves that can each kill hundreds of Indians.

ben: stiward evan burnet nritattvake vidyagat vishayer madhye simavaddh kare rakhar paramarsh dilh, jatigat sankhyalghu athva antarjatik sampark sambandhit lokanitite a-nrivigyanider dwara ei nititi vyabhhar nie vishayer vitarer evan byrer lokjner madhye vitark avyahat.
guj: joke steverd ane barnet evu suchavatan janaya ke nrivanshshastra e kharekhar to potane shuddha shaikshanik hetuo puratu simit rakhvu joie, vidvano ane baharna lokoe to bin-nrivanshshastrioe aa siddhanthane jaher niti vanshiya laghumtio athva antarrashtriya sambandho babate upayog karyo che, te ange charchaa kari rahyan che.
hin: yadhyapi steward or barnet is baat kii vakaalat karte dikhaai die ki maanav vigyaan ko vishuddh rup se academik maamalon tak simit rahanaa chahie, academy ke andar or baahar ke logon ne ab tak is baat par bahes karnaa jari rakhaa he ki kaise gaiyr-maanavshastriyon ne jaateey alpsankhyakon yaa antarrashtriya sambandhon ke bare main saarvajanik niti main is siddhant kaa upyog kiya he.
kan: steverd mattu barnett avaru manvashastravu tannannu tanu shuddhavagi adhyayan sambandhi vicharagaligashte simitgolisicolsbeku endu suchisuvante toridaru, manvashastrajeeralladavaru janangiya alpasankhyatar bagegin athwa antarashtriya sambandhagal kuritad sarvajanik nitielli i siddhanthavannu balsicondiruv ritigal bagege charchisuvudannu adhyayan kshetrad olagiruv janaru mattu horginvaru munduvaresiddare.
mal: narvanshshastra tikau akadamikamay karyasli svayn parimitppetanamenne stuwaർdu baർnetu niർdeshiunnatai tonnunnuvengil, vanshiy neunapakshangleyu antarashtra bandhansleyu sambandhichch potunayatiൽ narvanshshastrajshrallatavർ i tatva upyogichch ritikalecurich akadamiute akthu purattumullavർ chർchch cheiyunnat tutർnnuponnitesnd.
ori: stird eban barnat yadio matposhan karuthiva janapaduthile ye, nritatt vishamati keval shaikshik parisar madhyare simit rahiva uchith, yepari bhave an-nritttvitmane sankhyalaghu mul-adhivasi kimba aantharjatiya sampark sambandhit sarkaari neeti kshetrare ehi nitmagudiku bbbahar kariyanthi, se vishakere shikshathan bhitar o baahaar lok tark kariva jari rakhiyanthi.
pan: halanki stiverd ate barnet ih sujhv dinde jaapde san ki manav-vigyaan nuun aapne aap nuun puri tarhaa academik mammlas tak simit karna chahida hai, akedmi de anderle ate bahrle locals ne unhaa tarika 'te bahis karna jari rakhia hai ki gair-manav-vigyani ne nasli ait gintia jaaa intersrashtirya sabandhs baare jantak neeti vich ish sidhant di varton keeti hai|
tam: manuavial murill kalviyayu charndhavotu niruttikkoll wants endu stevertu manllum barnett parinduraippatu pol therindalum, manuavial charadhavars intak kolkaiys inach chinubanmainer alltu sarwatech ummvues kuritt botuk kolkail appatiellam payanbaduttyuner enpatu basari galvittriku ulleys velies iruppavars doderndu vivaditu vandhulsanar.
tel: manav shastramu ane danni kevalam vidyavisyak vyavahaaralaku matrame parimit cheyalani stuvard and barnet suchinchinappatiki, parishattu lopaly, bayati prajal manavshastrajnulu kaani vaaru alpasankhyak jatulu leda antarjatiya sambandhal gurinchi praja vidhanal siddhantanni avalambinchatampai vaari vadani konsagincharu.
urd: haalanki steward or barnet ye tijwez pesh karte hue nazar ate hain ki is lihaaz se bishrayat ko chahiye ki khud ko khalis andaz main ilmi amor tak hi mahadood rakhe, academy ke indra or baahar ke log bahas karte rahe hain ki kin tareekon se gair maahir bishrayat ne is usool ko nasli iqliton or ben alaswami taalkat se mataalak awami polisi main istemaal kiya hai.
eng: Although Steward and Barnett seemed to be suggesting that anthropology as such should restrict itself to purely academic affairs, people within and outside the academy have continued to debate the ways non-anthropologists have used this principle in public policy concerning ethnic minorities or international relations.

ben: ek adhi second halo anium evan prithvir abrtane diramayadi mandibhavaner karna parivartit hate thaka nirbhul samay (parmanvik ghari dwara parimit antarjatik parmanvik samay (tai)) evan anirbhul paryavekshit saura samay (uti1)-era madhye parthakyatike samanvit karte sthanankit vishwajanin samay (utisi)-e majhemadhye prayukt ek seconder ekati samanjasyavidhan.
guj: lip second e ek secondu samadhan che, je sankalit vaishvik samay (yu.ti.sii.) dwara chokkas samay (antarrashtriya anu samay (ti.e.ai.), je anu ghadiyalo dwara mapay che) ane achokkas solar samay (yu.ti.1)nu avalokan che; e pherfar aniyamitatao ane pruthvina paribhramanma thatan lamba samayna dhima padhvani prakriyane aabhari che.
hin: ek lip second ek second kaa samaayojan he jo samanvit vaishvik samay (you.tii.si.) main prayukt kiya jaataa he jisase sateek samay (aanvik ghadiyon se mapa gaya anterrashtriya parmanvik kaal (tii.e.ai.)) or galat saura samay (you.tii.1) ke bich saamanjasy thik kiya ja sake, or yah antar ek samaan nahin rahata tathaa yah prithvi ke ghurnan main lambey samay se hone vaali gati main kami ke kaaran hota he.
kan: hechuvari secondu embudu ondu secondin hondanikeyagiddu, adnnu nikhar samay (parmaanu gadiyaragalind aleyalad antarashtriya parmanvak samay (ti.e.i.)) mattu bhoomiy paribhramaneyallin aniyatategalu hagu dirghkalin vishambadindagi vyatyasavaguv nikharvallad gamanit saurasmayad (you.ti.1) naduvin vyatyasavannu sarihondislu samanvit sarvatrik samayakke (you.ti.si.) aagag anvayislaguttade.
mal: bhoomiute bhramanttile kramakkulavukalu diർghakalamaull vegatakushvu karea vyatyasapetunn, krityatyull samayattinu (atomic chlokookൾ upyogich athkkunn iൻrർnashanൽ atomic samaym (ti. e. ai)), krityat kushanera nirikshicppedunn sarasamayattinu idilull vyatyasate uൾkkollaൻ ko-oർdineted universൽ samay (yu. ti. si) ttin varuttunn oru secokൻr kramikarana oru lip secokൻr .
ori: eka lip second heudi gotie eka-seconder samanya yaha kevekeve kshardinated universal time (eu.ti.si.) pin lagu hoithaye, yaha sathik samay (aantharjatiya parmaanu samay (ti.e.aai.), yahaki parmaanu ghanta dra mapa yaithaye) eban anirddist bhave parylevekshan karayaithiva saur samay (eu.ti.1) madhyare thiva parthakiku samadhan kariva pin bbbahar karayaithaye, yaha pruthibir ghoornanare anishamitatha eban deerghakalin mantharatha hetu bhinna bhinna hoithaye.
pan: leap second ik second da samayojan hai, jo koordinated universal time (you ti see ) 'te international atomic time (ti e ai) stik samen vichle fark nuun mitaun lai kade-kadain lagu lagu hunda hai, jiven automic ghantias duara mapia gya ate suraji samen nuun anishchit dikhaya, dharati de ghumaao vich beniema de kaaran bakhrevan hai ate lamme kaal dauraan haulli kar dinda hai|
tam: nilnoti enpatu kusaiinch sarikattuvadaikak orunginaint potu nertil (udisi) apodavatu chercopatum woru vinadi, itu dulliya neratukum (anuk khatikarangs mulam alavidapatum sarwatech anuvial neram (dieh)) dulliyamaua ganganipusar surya nertirkum (udi1) itail vidhtyasatch sarisheyvadaikak menokolopadukintu, inge surya neram anatu bhuvich susarqiil ull chirabhachu tanmile, ninekal vegac kuraiu akhiyavatsal vedubatte welipadudhuatu kufippittakkadu.
tel: leep second anabadedi, khachchitmain samayam (interneshnal atamic time(tieai) parmaanu gadiaras koliche vidhnga) ,mariyu khachchit kaani sauraman samayam(utiai) akrammul vall mariyu dirghakal bhoobhraman vegam taggt vall vachche tedani sardtanii koardinated univarsal time (utisi)ki appudp kalipe ock kshana sardubat.
urd: ek lip second, ek second kii edgistmint hoti hai jo kabhi kabhaar mitnasq alami vakt (yu tii si) par lagu kiya jataa hai taaki ain vakt (alami johri vakt (tii aye aai), jaisaa ki johri ghadiyon ke zarie naapa jataa hai) or gair durust mishahda shudaa shamsi vakt (yu tii 1) ke mabin fark ko edgist kiya jaa sake, jo jameen kii gardish main be kaaadagiyon or tavel muditi sust ravi kii vajah se mukhtalf hota hai.
eng: A leap second is a one-second adjustment that is occasionally applied to Coordinated Universal Time (UTC), to accommodate the difference between precise time (International Atomic Time (TAI), as measured by atomic clocks) and imprecise observed solar time (UT1), which varies due to irregularities and a long-term slowdown in the Earth's rotation.

ben: sanskrute mul shabdati sadharan arth halo kono galle athva vriksher shikad, kintu alankarik arthe, kono kichur pa athva nimntam aansh athva taldesh.
guj: sanskrit sahityama mul shabdano samanya arth thai che chhod athva vrikshanu mul, pan alankarik rite, koipan vastuno sauthi nicho athva taliano bhag.
hin: sanskrit sahitya main mul shabd kaa saamaanya arth he kisi paudhe yaa vriksh kii jad, kintu lakshanik rup main, yah kisi bhi vastu kaa nichalaa hissaa yaa tal ho saktaa he.
kan: sansrut sahityadalli ʼmuulʼ emb padad samanya arthvu gid athwa marad baeru endagiddaru, sankethikavagi, yavudradde paad athwa kembhag athwa tal endaguttade.
mal: sanskritsahityattiൽ muul end wakin saadharan oru chetiutayo marattiൻreio ver enna aർtthamengil ethoru wastuviൻreyu padamenno, et tatte bhagamenno, atittat enno aan aalankarikamay aർtea.
ori: sanskrit sahityare 'mul' shabdar sadharan arth heudi eka udbhidha ba gangr cher, kintu prateekatmak arthare, eha paad ba kaunsi jinishar sabutharu nimnabhag ba talaku bujhaai thae.
pan: sanskrit saahit vich "mula" shabad da mathlab hai paude jaaa rukh dis jarhaa per alankark tor te ih kise chiiz da ve hethlas hisa hoo sakda hai I
tam: samskrit ilakyattl mula enjh sol adan valakkaman porlil woru sede alltu mrittin verek kurikkintu, eninu kuriidu ritiyag atu onguin atipagam, kioppakuti alltu atippakuti anpatek kurikkintu.
tel: sanskrit sahityamo mul ane padaniki sadharan ardha mokk leda chett veru, kani upamananga, adi padamu leda denikaina diguv bhagan leda adugu.
urd: sanskrit adab main lafz mul kaa amomi maanaa kisi pauddi yaa darkht kii jad hota hai, lekin tamisaili tuur par, kisi bhi cheez kaa py, nachala hissaa yaa penda hota hai.
eng: The usual meaning of the word mula in Sanskrit literature is the root of a plant or tree, but figuratively, the foot or lowest part or bottom of anything.

kan: i aananth mattu avakra chetanvannu dhyanisuv vyaktiyu jeevanmuktanaguttane mattu endigu duhkhvannu anubhavisuvudillavendu kathopanishattu udghoshisuttade.
mal: shashvata rujuvayatu ay itonin ar manana cheiyunnuo, aa vyakti muktanayithirunnuvennu orical duhkha anubhavikunnillennu kathopanishat uracchuparayunnu.
ori: kath upanishad drushokthi prakash karen ye, sehi bsakthi yieki ehi shashtar chinta karithaye, eban kutintir nuhen, se sdhin ate eban kadapi duhkh anubhava karinathaye.
pan: katha upanishd ne anusaar, oh viakti jo tedhi di tha amar aatamaa di soch rakhada hai, oh moksha praapat karada hai ate kade ve dukh nahi anubhav karada hai I
tam: ind nidhdhya jeevan - yemantup perwatiy all - chindenil arllum manidhar sudndram atikhistar, avaruku orupodhum kavalai erbaduvatill endu uraikiritu katopanitedam.
tel: vakramin danini kakunda, i nityamin dani gurinchi alochinche vyakti, swechh pondi annadu duhkha anubhavinckunda untadani kathopanishattu vakkanistunnadi.
urd: katha upanshad kaa kahana hai ki jo shaks is abdet par taphikar kurta hai na ki kaji kaa to wo azaad ho jataa hai or use kabhi gum kaa saamana naheen hota.
eng: The individual, asserts Katha Upanishad, who contemplates this eternal and not crooked one, becomes free and never experiences grief.

ben: shravansakrant asuvidhayukta vyaktira sadharant kathy bhashar madhyame kathopakathan karen evan shravan sahayak yantra, kaklia pratisthapan evan anyanya yantrik sahayyer pashapashi shirolipi madhyme suvidha pete parein.
guj: je lokoney sambhalwani taklif hoya teo samanya rite bolathi bhasha dwara pratyayan kare che ane sambhalwana sadhano, kochalear pratyaropan ane anaya sadhano, tatha chitra shirshak dwara phaido melvi shake che.
hin: jinhen kam sunai detaa he, ve saamanyatya bol kar apni baat vyakt karte hai or kaan kii mashiinon, karnavarti pratyaropanon, or anya upkarnon ke saath-saath anushirshakon se laabh paa sakate hai.

mal: kelvi buddhimuttuswar saadharan savadikunnat sansarabhashailute, shravana sahayi, kokliar implantul, mat upakarnws ennivyutayu chitrasutayu prayojana neticona.
ori: yeunmanankar shraban shakti kam, semane sadharanthati kathith bahasha madhumare yogayog karithanthi, eban semane shraban upakaran, karnavartt tantrika prataropan, anyanya upakaran, eban varnanathmak sheershalipi dra madhya upakrit hoi parive |
pan: jinhan nuun ait sunai dinda hai, uh aam for 'te bol ke apni gal viakat karade han ate kan dis mashins, karanavarti pratiaropanas ate hor upkarns de naal-naal sankets ton laha li sakde han|
tam: katkum dihan kuraibadu ulvars valakkamak pechu mofiil dodarpukolwargs, avargaluku sevittunaich chadanas, sevi udborutals manllum innapitt karuviesum tira vasaganglum udhav mudi.
tel: vinikidi lopangal vyaktulu sadharannga noti matato sambhashistar, mariyu vinikidi parikaras, kaclear amrikal, itar sadhanas, alage shirshikal vall labdi pondagalru.
urd: jo log ounchaa sunate hain wo amuman bol chal kii jubaan ke jaria baat karte hain or wo muavan samggi alaat, coclayer implants or digar alaat ke alaava capluning se bhi faaydaa uthaa sakte hain.
eng: People who are hard of hearing usually communicate through spoken language and can benefit from hearing aids, cochlear implants, and other devices, as well as captioning.

mal: motta khaniutayu bandhappet vyavasayautayu 90 shatamanttiൻreyu utamstharay sർkkaർ videshnikshepa thetunnu.

tam: motdach surangangs manllum atusarnt tokhilduraikalil 90% arasukkuch sondamantu, arasu itasku anniya mudalitte nadukintu.
tel: motta ganulu mariyu sambandhit parishramlas 90% prabhutva yajmanyanlo unnai, inca videshi pettubadul kos prayatnistondi.
urd: hukuumat tamaam kaanon or mataalika sanaaton ke 90 faisad kii maalik hai or gair milki saramy kari chaahati hai.
eng: The government owns 90% of all mines and related industries and is seeking foreign investment.

ben: avasheshe, grishmamandalian esia, ya poorv esiar ekati aansh evan dakshina o dakshina-poorv esiar veshirabhag aansh jure royas, yekhaner jamite chaas baa nagarayan kara has na, bivinn dharner krantiya bananchal evan hazar hazar samudrasaikat yeman maldwiper mato nirjan swarg dweep thek shuru kare thailand avasthit vishwer sabche janapriya kichu samudr saikat resort bura.
guj: chhevate, ushnakatibandhiya asia, jema purav asia ane mota bhaagna dakshin ane dakshithpurv aciano samavesh thai, jyaan kheti ke shaherikaran nathi, tyaan to anek prakarana ushnakatibandhiya junglo ane ekant aaptan maldivs jevaan swargiya tapuothi laine thilandna jagatna sauthi lokpriya dariya kinarana resorts sama hajaaro dariya kinara samel che.
hin: ant main, purvi asia or dakshin asia ke adhiktar bhaag tathaa dakshinpurvi asia, jahaan kheti nahin kii gai he or na hi uskaa shaharikaran hua he, ko samavisht karte hue ushnkaribandheey asia main vibhinn prakaar ke ushnakatibandheey jangal hai or hajaaron samudri tat hai jinamein maldive jaise ekant swarg dwipon se lekar vishwa ke sabase prasiddh thailand ke bich resort hai.
kan: coneyadagi, poorv eshyad ondu bhaag mattu bahupalu dakshin hagu aagneya eshyavannu olagondiruv, vyavasay madirad athwa nagarikrutvagirad ushnavalayad eshya bhagavu pradhanvagi vividh bageya ushnavalayad kadugalu mattu saviraaru kadaltiragalind kudiddu, ivugamalli viviktvagi svargadantiruv maldivsnantah dwipagalind hididu jagattinalle atyant janapriyawagiruv thilandinallin kelvu kadaltirad vishrantidhamagalvarege ellavu serive.
mal: otuvilai, krishicheiyukayo nagarvatkarikkayo chetitillat kingkanesiaute oru bhagavu dakshineshyayutayu tekkukiskൻ asiaute bhuribhagavu uൾkkollunn asiaute ushnamekhalapradesht, palatar ushnamekhalavandeu, maladwip polull otppet swaർggasamanmay dvipukൾ mutൽ thailൻdille locatille et janapriyamay chil beach resoർttukൾ varayull aairkanakin beachukalu supradhanmairiunnu.
ori: sheshre, poorb asian eka ansh eban dakshin o dakshin-poorb asian adhikansh bhagaku antarbhukt karuthiva, krantiya asia, yeunthareki chaash karyan kimba saharikaran karayainahin, taha vibhinna prakaarar krantiya aranya eban hajaar hajaar sankhyak belabhumi dra achdaadit hoi rahichhi, yaha madhyare madp pari ekaant paradys dpagudikaru nei thailandare thiva vishra ketek sabutharu lokapriya samudrkoossia risart rahichhi .
pan: ant vich, taptkhandi asia , jo ki poorabi asia ate jiadatar saikhan ate saikhan-poorabi asia nuun sarposh karada hai, jithe uthe naa kafat jaaa shahrikaran kita jandi hai, oh vividh prakaar de taptkhandi jungle te hazaaron khande naal prabhavit hoia hai, maldive varge ikant firdaus tapus ton li ke thailand vich dunia de sabh ton prasidh bich resorts tak.
tam: irutiyag, kisku ashiaill woru bagudi perumbalan thengu manllum thenginku ashiaum atankyl manllum vivchayamo nagaramyamo illat wepamendal ashiaill palverupatt wepamandalak kadugalum oiragankkana katankarum ulsana, ivartl maldive bonthe tanemayana ullasat divuesum thailandil ull ulagin chil micub prabhlaman katankarai vidutiksum atankum.
tel: chivariga, ushnmandal asialo, turpu asialo kont bhaganlo mariyu dakshin, aagneyasia lo dadapu chala varaku, sagobadi leda nagarikaran jargak, alage maldivulu vanti ekanth svarg dwipal nudi thailand loni konni prapanch prasiddi pondin samudratir ullas pradeshal varaku veladi samudratir prantallo vividh rakaal ushnmandal vanas vyapinchi unnai.
urd: aakhir main, haari asia jo mishraqi asia or beshtar janubi or janub mishraqi asia par muhit hai, jahaan kheti yaa shaharkaari naheen hui hai, vahaan mukhtalf kasam ke haari janglaat or hazaaron bechuun kii kasarat hai jin main maldive jese viran jannat nishaan jujhair se lay kar thai land main duniya ke sab se mashhuur sahili resort tak shamil hain.
eng: Finally, tropical Asia, covering a part of East Asia and most of South and Southeast Asia, where it is not cultivated or urbanized, is dominated by various kinds of tropical forests and thousands of beaches ranging from secluded paradise islands like the Maldives to some of the world's most popular beach resorts in Thailand.

ben: banking evan arthik vibhager prati amader sarkarer drushtibhangi hal arthik upalbdhatar prasar evan arthkari anumodan barie tola madhyam bazark gabhiratar karaar balishth tadarki nischit kara.
guj: banking ane nana kshetra tarafnu aapani sarkaranu valan pramanik dekharekh ane niyamanni khatari aapi nanakiya pravesh ane bajarona undanano vistar karvanu che.
hin: banking or vittiya kshetron ke prati hamaari sarkaar dwaara apanaai gai ranneeti paryvekshan or viniman ko majboot karte hue vittiya pahunch kaa vistaar karne or bazaaron ko gaharaai pradaan karne kii rahi he.
kan: banking mattu hanakasu valayad kuritad namm sarkaarad vidhanvu hanakasin sulabhagamyataynnu vistarisutta mattu marukattegalannu higgisutta sadruvvad melvicharane mattu niyantranavannu khataripadisuvudagide.
mal: sampattik itapetalukൾ vyapippikkayu vipanikൾ valutakkukyu cheayumpoൾ shaktmay meൽnotevu niyantranvu uthppuvaruttuk ennathayirunnu banking, sampattik mekhalayotulla sർkkariൻre sameepan.
ori: banking o bithtiya kshetra prati aam sarkarnkar abhimukhya heudi aarthik sugamathaku suvisthrut kariva tatha punyjivajaragudiku saghan kariva sahit sudrush parylevekshan o bidhivevasthaku sunishchit kariva.
pan: sari sarkaar di shaahukara kama ate arthic khetra vich mazaboot nigrani te niyama da palan nishchit karna hai naal hi arthic pahunch nuun vadhauna te bazaaraan vich hor ruzana I
tam: didaman meghbarvey manllum ohungumuraiys urudisaiyus adevele nitipenum vasati virivakkuvatum chandaikass aumackuvadume bangi manllum nidhit turaikalin pal namadhu arasin anukumuriyag irunduvarukintu.
tel: banking mariyu aarthik rangal pat man prabhuthwal vidhana aarthik saulabhyat mariyu vipanu vruddhipariche kramulo dhrudamin paryavekshan mariyu vyavasthikarnalku hami ichchediga undi.
urd: bnking or malyati shobe ke baare main hamari hukuumat kii approach ye rahi hai ki malyati rasai ko tosia de kar or mandiyon ko mustahkam karke majboot nigranee or ansubat ko yaqini banaaya jaaye.
eng: Our Government's approach to the banking and financial sector has been to ensure robust oversight and regulation while expanding financial access and deepening markets.

ben: paravarty shlokagulite amader bala hayes ye, manabjatike satyer path evan satya anusar jibanyapaner upa batle dite bhagwan jarathushtrake manabjatir shikshak hisabe niyukt karellen.
guj: nichinai panktioma aapanne kahevaayu che ke eeshwar jharthrushtani niyunkti manavjatana shikshak tarike kare che, teo satyana marg vishe ane sathyan sathe kai rite jeevavu te ange kaheshe.
hin: aage die gaye padyon main hamen bataaya jaataa he ki ishwar ne zarathushtra ko maanav jati ko satya ke maarg ke bare main or satya ke saath kaise jeena he, yah bataane ke liye shikshak ke rup main niyukt kiya he.
kan: mundin padyagamalli, devaru jaratushtranannu manavkulad guruvagi, avarige satyamargad bagge mattu satyavantragi badukuvudu hegendu bodhisalu nemisidanembudu namage tilidubaruttade.
mal: satyatine waiecurichu satyattinnusrich jivikentategynayennu manushyarashiot paryan jaratushtrae daiva guruvai niyamikunnuven tutrnnull padyas parayunnat nam keൾkkunnu.
ori: paravartti padagudhikare, amku kuhayaishi ye eeshr manavajathiku sater marg eban kipari satya anusaare vanychivaku heb kahiva pin jarathushtranku semanankar eka shikshak roope niyukt kariyanthi .
pan: ange dite padas vich saanuun oesia janda hai ki rab ne zarthusht nuun manukh jaati nuun saach de rasate 'te chalan ate saach naal kiven jiuna hai, ih dasan lai guru de roop vich niukat kita hai|
tam: isaivan manitakultuku satiyap patyske guriadduvadavkum satyatinpati watak karupukkoduppathankum jaratustraw achanak niyamitllar endu adashakaduddha vasanas gutaukindena.
tel: i krindi charnala, bhagwant jaratushtra manavjatiki satya marg gurinchi mariyu satyaniki anugunanga ela bratkalo telupamani wariki guruvuga niyaminchadni manaki teliajeyada jarugutundi.
urd: baad kii aayat main, hamen bataya jataa hai ki khuda zarathushit ko nasal insaani ke liye ek ustad ke tuur par muqrer kurta hai, taaki inhen sacchai kii raah ke baare main bataae or bataae ki sacchai ke mutabik zindagi kaise guzaarein.
eng: In the following verses, we are told that God appoints Zarathustra as a teacher for mankind, to tell them of the path of truth and how to live in accordance with truth.

ben: daler sadasyara paenter lakshyamatra thik kare nie scor kare, siddhanth neya, nijeder madhye alochana kare, parasparabirodhi paristiter samal deya evan yate tader lakshye paunchte par sejanya ekati anukul, vishwast pariweshe samasyar samadhan kare.
guj: juuthana sabhyo temana hetuone prapth karva ank ane gun nakki kare che, nirnyo le che, temani vachche sanvad kare che, sangharshamay paristhiteonu aayojan kare che ane sahayogi, vishwasaniya vatavaranma mushkelionu nivaran kare che.
hin: dal ke sadsy unke lakshyon ko praapt karne ke liye point or ank nirdhaarit karte hai, nirnay lete hai, aapas main charchaa kii jaati he, sangharsh kii paristhitiyon kaa prabandh kiya jaataa he or samasyaon kaa nivaaran ek samarthak, vishwasaneey maahaul main kiya jaataa he.
kan: tandad sadasyaru pointugalu hagu ankaganannu garisuttare, nirdhargainnu maduttare, tammatmmalle sanvahan nadesuttare, viparit paristaigalannu nibhaisuttare, mattu tamm uddeshgainnu sadhisuv saluvagi protsahak hagu vishwasapurna vatavrandalli samasyegaiannu pariharisicolluttare.
mal: tangute lakshyas neduvanai tea angarhs poiൻrukalu skorukalu nishchayikkayu thirumans adukkukayu tas savadikkayu sangർshabharitmay sandarbhas kaikaryam cheiyukayu parasparasahayakavu vishwasapoornavumay orantarikshattil prashnkhs pariharikkayu cheiyunnu.
ori: dashar sadasoumane nizer lakshya hasal kariva nimanthe paent eban score dharyan karanthi, nishpatti grahan karanthi, parasparank madhyare yogasutara raksha karanthi, pratikul paristaitegushikar parichakana karanthi, eban eka utsaah pradanakaari, vishsayukt pariveshare samasyagujaikar samadhan karithanthi .
pan: team de member ankde te score rakde han, faisle lende han, aapas vich vichar - vatandara karade han, pratirodh haalaat nuun sulakhhaande han ate aapne udesh nuun hasal karan lai saoesyas nuun ik sahik te vishwasyog mahaul vich hal karade han I
tam: ani ushupinars tangas kurikolkal adaivadaikak, parasbar adram nampikkes migundathoru suzlil pulligales scores amaikinowner, mudivuess edugginowner, tangalukul alosithuk kolkinowner, muranbadan suanililch samalikkinowner manllum sicallukud tiru kankinowner.
tel: tam lakshyas sadhinchatanii, brunda sabhyulu protsahakar, vishvasaniyamin paristhitul madhya. points, scor nishchainchukuntar, nirnyas tisukuntar, tamalo tamu samvadinchukuntar, virudhmin paristhitula sambalinchukuntar mariyu samasyal parishkarinchukuntar.
urd: tem ke mumbaran points or score te karte hain, faisale karte hain, aapas main baat chet karte hain, matayad halaat ko thik karte hain, or apne muqaasid ko haasil karne ke liye muavan, itmad waale maahaul main missale hal karte hain.
eng: Team members set points and scores, make decisions, communicate among themselves, manage conflicting situations, and solve problems in a supportive, trusting atmosphere in order to achieve their objectives.

ben: 1992-r januarite, sener a-yoddha shakha swalpakalin niog centrian sarkar nari antarbhukti anumodith kare.
guj: january 1992maa kendra sarkaare short sarvis kamishan ayojit karti vakhte lashkarni bin-ladaku shakhaoma mahilaone samel karvaani manjuuri aapi.
hin: janvari 1992 main kendriya sarkaar ne sena main laghu seva ayog ko sweekruti dete hue mahilaon kii ayoddha shakhaon main niyukti kaa anumodan kiya he.
kan: 1992r janvarialli, kendra sarkaarvu alpavadhi seva nemkatigal moolak seney yuddhodyogiallad shakhegamalli mahileyar serpadege anumodane niditu.
mal: hrasvakalakmmishanulote sainyatiൻre yuddha cheyenatillat shakhkaliൽ streee praveshipikunnatin 1992 januaryiൽ kendra sർkkaർ anumati naൽki.
ori: 1992 masiha january maasare, kendra sarkar slpakalin-seva kamishanar aajojan kari mahidamananku sthasenar vesamaric-shakhagudiku preran kariva anumodan karithile .
pan: janvari 1992 vich, center sarkaar ne shart service kamishan rakhade hoe fouj dis gair-ladaai shakhavan vich aurataan di jan-pachhan nuun manazuuri diti|
tam: 1992 januaril, onjhiya arasu pengans kurungalap pani oppantas mulam iranutin pore-charat brivukalil cherck oppudalalittatu.
tel: 1992 januarilo, short-sarvis kamishnlalo undgane mahillan sainyauloni porat rahit shakhalas niyaminchatanii kenter prabhutvan anumatinicchindi.
urd: janvari 1992 main, marcuji hukuumat ne short service khmeshan kaa inakad karte hue khwatin ko faoez kii gair jangi shaakhon main shamil karne kii manzooree di.
eng: In January 1992, the Union government sanctioned the induction of women into non-combatant branches of the Army while holding short-service commissions.

ben: ekati sanyukti paddhatir pare, avashishta 5ti sahakari bank (artha, state bank af bikaner and jaipur, state bank af haidrabad, state bank af mysore, state bank af patiala evan state bank af travancor) evan bhartiya mahila banker sang esbiai-era sanyuktikaran 15i june, 2016-e centrian mantrisvar nitigat anumodan labh kare.
guj: kendriya pradhanmandal dwara 15 june 2016na roj ekeekaran prakriya bad paanch bakini sahayogi benko (jemke state bank of bikaner and jaipur, state bank of hyderabad, state bank of mysore, state bank of patiyala ane state bank of travanakor)na ekeekaran ane bhartiya mahila bankana es.bi.ai. sathena ekikarane saiddhanthik manjuuri apai hati.
hin: vilay kii prakriya ke chalate, baaki 5 sahyogi bank (yani state bank of bikaner and jaipur, state bank of hyderabad, state bank of mysore, state bank of patiala, or state bank of travencor) evam bhartiya mahila bank ke es.bi.ai. main vilay ko kendriya cabinet ne 15 june 2016 ko saiddhanthik rup se anumodan diya.
kan: vilin prakrieya nantar, es.bi.i.ondige ulid 5 sahavarti bankugalu (avugalendare, state bank aaf bikaner and jaipur, state bank aaf hyderabad, state bank aaf mysoru, state bank aaf patiala, mattu state bank aaf travankor) mattu bhartiya mahila bankannu vilingolislu 2016r june 15randu kendra sachiv samputvu tattvik anumodane niditu.
mal: oru layanprakrie tutr, (state bank of hyderabad, state bank of bikaner and jaipur, state bank of mysore, state bank of paatyala, state bank of travenkur, enni) bakkiull 5 asssociate bankuayu bharatiya mahilabankinayu es.bi.ayumai layippikunnatin 2016 june 15 n kendramantrisabh tattvattil angikar nalki.
ori: eka mishran prakria pare, es.bi.aai. sahit avashist 5ti sahakaari bank (yatha: 'stet bank af vikaner and janpur', 'stet bank af hidrabad', 'stet bank af maheeshur', 'stet bank af patiala', eban 'stet bank af trabhancor') eban bharatiya mahila bankar mishranku kendra cavinat dra 15 jun 2016re saiddhanthik anumodan pradaan karayaithila .
pan: ralleven di prakiria ton bood, 5 baaki bache assosiate banks (jiven ki state baink aaf bikaner ate jaipur , state baink aaf hyderabad, state baink aaf mysore, state baink aaf patiala, ate state baink aaf travancor ) ate bharatia da rallevaan asa bi ai de naal mahila baink nuun union cabanit duara 15 june 2016 nuun sidhantak for 'te pravaanagi diti gai see|
tam: onainipu natwatikiait doderndu mabbbb 5 charpu vangigales (adavatu, state bank off bikhaner and jaipur, state bank off hyderabad, state bank off mysore, state bank off battiala manllum state bank off thiruvangur), bharatiya makhila banges espis-yuton orunginipatangurya kolkayalvilan oppudalai 15 june 2016 andu madhya amycharavai valangiyadu.
tel: ock vilin prakrian anusarinchi, migilin 5 anubandha bankulu (anaga state bank aaf bikaner and jaipur, state bank aaf hyderabad, state bank aaf mysore, state bank aaf patiyala,mariyu state bank aaf travenkor)nu mariyu bhartiya mahila bank asbiaito vilina cheyadaniki 2016 june 15na kenter cabinet sutaraprayanga aamoda telipindi.
urd: animam ke amal ke baad, 5 baaqi esosi it bainkon (yani estate bank of bikaner or jai pur, estate bank of hyderabad, estate bank of mysore, estate bank of patyaala, or estate bank of tarwankor) or bhartiya mahela bank ke es bi aai main animam ko marcuji coben ne 15 june 2016 ko usooli tuur par manzooree de di.
eng: Following a merger process, the merger of the 5 remaining associate banks (viz., State Bank of Bikaner and Jaipur, State Bank of Hyderabad, State Bank of Mysore, State Bank of Patiala, and State Bank of Travancore) and the Bharatiya Mahila Bank with the SBI was given in principle approval by the Union Cabinet on 15 June 2016.

ben: ei pathgat shrenivibhager viparite, bahu sammanit hindu granth o mathbad samajik shrenivibhager ei vyavasthar viruddhe prashn tule eti sang asammaya has.
guj: granthonan aa vargikaranthi viparit, ghana shraddhey hindu dharmagrantho ane siddhanto samazik vargikaranni prathani saame prashn uthaave che ane teni sathe asammath thai che.
hin: moulik vargeekaran ke vipareet, kai shradhdhey hindu mulgranth or vichaardhaaraein saamaajik vargeekaran kii is pranali par sawaal uthaati hai or isse sahamat nahin hai.
kan: i granthapathagamallin vingedonege virudhvagi anek poojaniya hindus granthagalu mattu tattvasiddhanthagalu i samajik vargikarand vyavasthayannu prashnisuttve mattu oppuvudill.
mal: mulagranthangൾkkanusrichull i vibhagikaranngൾk virudhmai pal hindugranthalu pramareslu i samuhikavibhagikaran reetie chodyam cheiyukayu atinote viojikkayu cheiyunnu.
ori: ehi granthgat bargeekaranar biparitre, anek namasya hindu granth eban tatt ehi samajik bargeekaran brivasthaku prashn karen eban eha sahit asahamathi prakash karen .
pan: inhan pat shrenia de ulat, kai poojanik hindus pat ate sidhant ish samajik vargikaran nuun prashan karade han ate asanmati rakhade han I
tam: nulkalil kanappatum ind vacaprittalluku majhak, pal manmay porundhia hindu noolkalum samayak kotbadugalum indech samukap pripu muraiys calvikullakhi manukkinsona.
tel: i pathantar vargikaranku virudhmuga, anno pujya hindus granthas mariyu siddhantalu i sanghik vargikaran vyavasthito vibhedinchi prashninchai.
urd: in mitni darja bandiyon ke barkhilaf, bahut se kaabil ehtiram hindu mitvan or najariyat sawal uthate hain or maashruti darja bindi ke is nizaam se matafiq naheen hain.
eng: Contrary to these textual classifications, many revered Hindu texts and doctrines question and disagree with this system of social classification.
