ben: 2021 avadhi, bharter 28 ti rajya royas, pratyekati nijasv sarkar alada aladabhave jatiya sarkar (centrian baa yuktarashtriya sarkar bala has) hate nirvachit evan 8ti centrashasit anchal royas ya centrian sarkar dwara parichalith has.
guj: 2021 sudhima, bharata 28 rajyo che, darek paase rashtriya sarkarthi alag pote chunteli sarkaar che (jene kendra ke samavayi sarkaar pan kahe che), ane jeno wahivat kendra dwara thai che, evaan 8 kendra shasit pradesh che.
hin: 2021 tak bharat main 28 rajya hai, jinamein unki khud kii chuni hui sarkaar hai jo rashtriya sarkaar se alag se chuni gai hai (jise centre sarkaar yaa sangheey sarkaar bhi kaha jaataa he) tathaa 8 centreshasit pradesh hai jo centre sarkaar dwaara prashasit hai.
kan: 2021r hottige, bharatadalli 28 rajyagaliddu, prationdu rashtriya sarkaaradind (kendra athwa sanyukt sarkaarvendu kareyalaguttade) bereyad tannade swanth sarkaarvannu hondide mattu 8 kendradlit pradeshgaliddu, avugal aadlitavannu kendra sarkaarvu nirvahisuttade.
mal: 2021le stateyanusrich indiail 28 sansthanau avayoronninu deshiyasarkari (union allengil fedral sarkar ennu vilicunn) lninnu vyatyastamai, tiranketukapat swanta sarkkarukalu, union gavnmeൻr bharikkunn 8 kendrabharanapradeshau und.
ori: 2021 anusaare, bharatre 28ti rajya rahichhi, pratyekar nizer sarkar jatiya sarkar (yahaku sangha athava sanghiya sarkar madhya kuhayaaye) tharu pruthak bhavare nirvachit hoithanthi, eban 8ti kendra shasit anychal rahichhi yeunguik kendra sarkarnk dra shasit hoithaye .
pan: 2021 tak bharat de 28 raj han, harek di apni sarkaar, rashtirya sarkaar ton bakh chuni hoi hai (jise nuun union jaaa fedral sarkaar ve kiha janda hai), ate 8 cendari shasat pradesh han, jinhan da prabandh center sarkaar duara kita janda hai|
tam: 2021aam antu nilavarapati, indiaill 28 manilas ulsana, avarkhil desiya arasu (onjhiya alltu gutatsi arasu endu anoaicopadukintu) allad dattamatu sondhat terndeducoppatt arasus irukkinsona, manllum 8 union pradesangs ulsana, are onjhiya arasal nirvkixpadukindena.
tel: 2021 nati, bharatvaeshalo (kenter leda samakhya prabhutvan ani kuda piluvabada) jaatiya prabhutvan kante veruga annukobadin, prati okati dani sonth prabhutvan kal 28 rashtras, mariyu kenter prabhutvan dwara palinchabada 8 kendrapalit prantalu unnai.
urd: 2021 main, hindustan kii 28 riyasatin hain, jin main se har ek apni hukuumat qaumi hukuumat se alag mantakhab krati hai (jise union yaa vafaaqi hukuumat bhi kehate hain), or 8 marcuz ke zer intazaam ilaka bhi, jo marcuji hukuumat ke zer intazaam hain.
eng: As of 2021, India has 28 states, each with its own government elected separately from the national government (also called the union or federal government), and 8 union territories, which are administered by the union government.

ben: ribounder duti shreni hayh akramanatmak ribound yekhane bal akramanatmak paksher dwara pun:prapth has o tara dakhal chade na aar rakshanatmak ribound yekhane rakshak dal phaanka baler dakhal prapth kare.
guj: riboundasni be shrenio che: akramak riboundas, jema akramanakarta jooth dado melve che ane kabajo badlaato nathi tatha rakshanatmak riboundas, jema bachavakarta juth chhuta dadano kabajo melve che.
hin: do tarah ke pratighaat hote hai: aakraamak or rakshaatmak. aakraamak pratighaat main aakraamak dal gend ko punah praapt karata he or us par adhikaar banaae rakhata he. rakshaatmak pratighaat main raksha karne vaala dal kamjor gend par kabja kar letaa he.
kan: himputitagamalli eradu prakaragalive: akramanakari tandvu chendannu punah vashapadisicond nantar, adnnu bittucodadantah akramanakari himputitagalu mattu rakshanatmak tandvu muktvad chendannu vashakke padeyuvantah rakshanatmak himputitagalu.
mal: rantu vidhttilull rebauntul und: akramikunn tea pantine kaivasha nashtappetuttate pant veendedukkunn ofnsive rebauntulu, pinne pratirodhikkunn tea lus boൾ kaivashmakkunn pratirodh rebauntulu.
ori: dui prakaarar 'rivound' rahichhi: 'afencibh rivound', yeunthireki baltiku afencibh pakshati dra punarlabh karayaaye o eha pajesan parivarttan karen naahin, eban 'defensibh rivound', yeunthireki decanding dashati mukt baltir pajesan hasal karithaye .
pan: ribound doo kisma de hunde han : afensive ribound jise vich geind nuun duja pakh baramad kar lenda hai te kabaza nahi badalde ate bakhyatamak ribound jise vich bakhyatamak pakh geind nuun baramad kar lenda hai I
tam: iruvakai reepoundues ulsana: offensive reepounds enpatil bandhu kamaramal munnerum aniye adai meedduk kolkintu, diffensive reepounds enpatil cavittup bona bandai tawkafu ani vachappaduttik kolkintu.
tel: rend rakaal ribonds untai: afenciv ribonds, indulo afenciv paksha bantini tirigi pondi patt vidvadu, alage diphenciv ribonds, indulo dephending jattu vadilunn bantini aadhinanloki techchukuntundi.
urd: rebound kii do qasamen hoti hain: jarhana rebound, jis main gend ko jarhana pahalu haasil kiralitha hai or apne kabze main tabadeli naheen aane detaa, or dafaai rebound, jis main dafaai tem khuli gend par kabja haasil kiraliti hai.
eng: There are two categories of rebounds: offensive rebounds, in which the ball is recovered by the offensive side and does not change possession, and defensive rebounds, in which the defending team gains possession of the loose ball.

ben: 2006-era july evan agst lebanon o israler yuddher samay claster yuddhastrer vyabhhar o prabhava nie antarjatik vitarcti ekati nishedhajna sukti janya vishwavyapi pracharna aro gurutva yoga kare.
guj: july ane august 2006maa lebenon ane ichrayel vachchena yuddh daramiyaan juth hathiyarona upayog ane teni aasar vishe antarrashtriya vivaad sarjayo ane tene pratibandhak sandhi mate vaishvik jhumbesh chalaavavaa par bhaar mukyo.
hin: july or agast 2006 main isroyal-lebanani sangharsh ke dauraan gucchh yuddh-saamagree ke istemaal or prabhaav se duniya bhar main ek bahes chhid gai, jisase unke upyog par pratibandh lagane vaali sandhi ke liye vaishvik abhiyaan ko or dridhtaa mili.
kan: 2006r july mattu augustnalli lebanan mattu israel naduve naded yuddhdallad guchh yuddhsamgrigal badke mattu prenamgal bagegin antarashtriya vivaldind avugainnu nishedhisuv oppandakkagin jagathik andolanakke innashtu ottase dorkitu.
mal: 2006 july augustl lebanonu israyelu tammilunay yudhttile klaster aayudhsute upyogavu aghatvu sambandhichch antarddeshiya vivada oru nirodhan utampaticayural agola pracharanttin akum kuti.
ori: july o agast 2006re, lebanon o isril madhyare sanghatit yudhre cluster astra-samoohar prayog o prenam nei uthithiva aantharjatiya vibad eka nishedh chukthi nimanthe chalithiva vishwapi abhiyanar bal badaai thila.
pan: july ate agast 2006 vich lebanon ate israel wichkaar jung dauraan clester hathyars di varton ate prabhav nuun li ke intersrashtirya vivaad ne pabandi sandhi lai vishva-vyapi muhim de mahatav nuun vadha ditha|
tam: 2006 july manllum agast lebanon-isrel foril koddukh gundugalin payanpadu manllum dakram kuritu edhunth sarwatech church, its tadai obbandatukan ulalaviya koriky iyakkaduku valuchertatu.
tel: july, agasht 2006lo lebanon mariyu israel madhya jarigin yuddh samayaulo samuhik sainik ayudhal viniog mariyu prabhavan gurinchin antarjatiya vivada anedi nishedh oppanda koraku chestunn prapanchavyapt pracharaniki balam chekurchindi.
urd: julai or agast 2006 main libanan or israel ke mabin jang ke dauraan cluster gola barodke istemaal or asarat par ben alaswami tanaazae ne paabandi ke maaade ke liye alami muhim ke vajan main azafa kiya.
eng: The international controversy over the use and impact of cluster munitions during the war between Lebanon and Israel in July and August 2006 added weight to the global campaign for a ban treaty.

ben: hemostat hiseve colagen: colagen yakhan platelet-era sang yogayog sthapan kare, takhan ta rakter drut jamaat bandie deya.
guj: hemostate tarike colejanah jayaare colejan platelet sathe kriya pratikriya kare che tyaare lohi ganthavani prakriya jhadpi banaave che.
hin: raktarodhak ke rup main kolajan: jab kolajan platelet ke saath abhikriya karata he to teji se rakt skandan hone lagata he.
kan: raktastambhakavagi kalajan: kalajan kirubillegalondige paraspar kriye nadesidag, adu shighravagi raktavannu heppugattisuttade.
mal: hemostat end nileil cologen: plate lettukalumai cologen pratipravartikshumpol at rakta pette katopitican izyakunnu.
ori: rakt-jamatakari bhavare 'colagen': yetevela 'colagen' 'anuchakrika' sahit antakkria ghate, eha kshipra rakt jamaat ghataithaye .
pan: kalejan hamiostate de tor te : jadon kalejan palatelits naal milade han , us naal khun tezi naal idhetha shuruu on lag janda hai I
tam: kolajan himostatak payanbaduddhudal: kolajan tattunukgaluton vinapuri podhu adhivekamak iratt uraivu erbadukintu.
tel: rakthasravanni nilipe sadhananga kolagen : kolagen platletsto sankarshan chendinapp, adi rakta veganga gaddkattett chestundi.
urd: colejinhemostot ke tuur par : jab colegin platelet ke saath taamil kurta hai to ye khoon ke tejai se jamne kaa sabab banata hai.
eng: Collagen as haemostat: When collagen interacts with platelets, it causes rapid coagulation of blood.

ben: bistarit vishay prashnsmuh yeman kibhave mrut vyaktike akraman kara hayesil, ke akraman karesil baa kohn paristhitite akraman kara hayesil sesav 174 aini dhara adhine caryadhara paridhi o kshetrer byre.
guj: mrutak par kevi rite humlo karvama aavyo, tena par kone humlo karyo athva tena par keva sanjogoma humlo karvama aavyo teni vigto angeno prashn kalam 174 heyelni kaaryavahini maryaada ane avkash baharno che.
hin: mritak par hamalaa kaise kiya gaya tha, us par kisne hamalaa kiya tha yaa kis paristhiti main us par hamalaa kiya gaya tha, in sab varnanon se sambandhit prashn, samhita kii dhara 174 ke tahat kanoonee kaarywahi ke daayre or vishay-kshetra ke baahar hai.
kan: mrutan mele hege halle nadeslayitu, avan mele hallemadidvaru yaaru athwa avanu hallegolgad sandarbhaventhaddu emb vivargal kuritad prashneyu dandasamhiteya kalam 174r kshetra mattu vyaptiallin nadavaligalige hortagide.
mal: marichchayal exne cayetinchayyapettu, aran cayetinchaytat, etu sahacharyatil addeha cayet cheyyappettat tutangia vishdanshaecurichull chodyangoൾ i chattatine 174 end vakuppanusrichull natapatikramateute parigannaparidhi puratta.
ori: mritkajanakanku kipari akramana karayaithila, tanku kie akramana karithila ba keun paristatire tanku akramana karayaithila se vishakere savishesh tatha samparkit prashnati samhitar dhara 174 anuyani rahithiva prakriar paridhi eban parisarar sampoorna bahaare .
pan: code de bhaag 174 de tahit ih jankari ki mrit te kida hamala kitha gya, kisane hamala kitha jaaa kihdia paristatea vich hamala kitha gya, ih sabh bhaag de dira ate simaa ton baahar hai I
tam: mrinittavar evvar dakrapatar, everal dakrapatar alltu endach suanilil dakrapatar bonthe vivrangs kuritt calvi, ind vidimuin 174aam brivin keel natabellum vanku visaranaikalin vattam manllum varambhuku apparpattathakum.
tel: mritudipai daadi ela jarigindi, daadi chassindi avaru leda atuvanti paristhitulas dadki guryyad vanti vivaralku sambandhinchin prashn shikshasmritiloni sekshan 174 krind chattaparamin charyal paridhi mariyu parimiti atita.
urd: mitufi ko kis tarah zid va kob kiya gaya, use kis ne zid va kob kiya or kin halaat main use zaddu kob kiya gaya, in tafsilat se mataalak sawal kanoon kii dafaa 174 ke tahat carrwai ke hadood or daayre se kaarij hai.
eng: The question regarding the details as to how the deceased was assaulted, who assaulted him or under what circumstances he was assaulted is foreign to the ambit and scope of the proceedings under Section 174 of the Code.

ben: susth hay uthche mane also jale dube durjetnar shikar haoya kono vyakti doctor dwara chickesar prayojan, kaaran 12.2 baksher vyakhya anuyayi, paravarty cale ekati dvitiya parayer dube yaoyar ghatna taar kshetre ghatte par.
guj: dubi javaana akasmatani ek aarogya adhikari dwara saarwar thavi aavashyakta che, te/teni saja thatan janay to pan, karanke, khaana 12.2maa samajavya mujab, tene/tenine aagami tabakkama farithi bijivar dubvanu banii shake che.
hin: bhale hi aisa lage ki vah sanbhal rahaa/rahi he, doobane ke durghatnagrast ko doctor ke ilaaj kii zarurat hoti he, kyonki, jaisaa box 12.2 main bataaya gaya he, baad main ja kar uske saath dwitiyak doobane kii ghatana bhi ho sakati he.
kan: muluguvikeindagi usirugattiruv vyaktiya chikitseyannu vaidyare madebekiruttade, aat/aake chetarisicolluttiruvante kanderu, chowk 12.2ralli vivarisiruvante, aat/aake amelin hantadalli mattomme usirugattuvikege olagagabahudu.
mal: welattil munjai atiyantir chikits aavashyamay orale, afzal sukha prapikkaanennu tonnial, box 12.2 ൽ vishadikarichchatupole ayaൾk oru secokൻdery doning anubhavppetamennatinal oru doctor chikitsikentatund.
ori: budiyiva durghanare aakrant brektinkar chikitsa jane dakranak dra karayiva aavashyak, yadiva se aarogy heuthivabhadi manehanthi, karan yemithiki baks 12.2re bujhaai diayaishi, paravartti samaure tankashare punithare aakrant heva bhadi state upujipare.
pan: duban ton pidat viakti da ilaaj ik medical doctors duara kita jaana chahida hai, bhaaven ajiha lage ki uh thik hoo riha/rahi hai, kiu ki, jiven ki bax 12.2 vich oesia gya hai, bood wale padse 'te us naal dubaara duban di ghatna ve hoo sakadi hai|
tam: neeril moonoki badikkapattaruku woru marudwar mulam sikichi alick wants, anenil avar ialpu nilikud thirumpiyathaghat donrinalum kuta, 12.2aam bettit takhavalil villcopattulupati avaruku ore erandamnilai moongudal arbadalam.
tel: nit munigi pramadlo unn vyakti, atanu/ambe kolukuntunnti kanipinchina kuda, vaiduni chet chikits cheinchali , andukante 12.2 baksulo vivarinchin vidhnga, atadi/ambelo aa taruvat dashalo rendosthai swasakosh kshint sambhvinchavacchu.
urd: doobne se lagane wali chot kaa ilaaj kisi medical doctor ke zarie kiya jaanaa chahiye, khwaah wo thik hi hota hawa kyon na lage, kyonki jaisaa ki box 12.2 main vizahat kii gai hai, baad ke marahale main is kii sanavi garqabi waaqa hosakti hai.
eng: A casualty from drowning needs to be treated by a medical doctor, even if he/she seems to recover, because, as explained in Box 12.2, a secondary drowning may occur in him/her at a later stage.

ben: kintu, sei sakalei, narpath sinher khalas kara ek shwetang bandi ingrej shibire ase senadhyakshake jana, se narpath sinhak balte shuneshwae ye pratishodh na nie trini durg tyag karaben na.
guj: parantu e ja sanvaare narapat sinhe gora kediomathi je ekane mukt karyo hato te angrej chavnima aavyo ane senapatine mahiti aapi ke ene narapat singhne evu kaheta sambhalya hata ke te killo khaali karshe pan jyaan sudhi te tenu ver vasule tyaan sudhi nahi.
hin: lekin usee subah, ek gora kaidi jise narpat singh ne choda tha, angrejon ke kheme main pahunch gaya or jeneral ko usne soochna di ki usne narpat singh ko kehete suna tha ki vah kile ko khaali kar degaa lekin tab tak nahin jab tak ki vah badla nahin le letaa.
kan: adare, aa belghgeye, narapat singhnu bidugadegolisid bili khidigkallobb anglar shibirkke bandu, narapat singhnu avan pratikarvannu tirisicond melashte koteannu khali maduvudagi matnaduttiddudannu tanu kelisicondiddene endu senadhikarige tilisidnu.
mal: ennal aa prabhatattiltane, narpath singh vittayachch wediakarnay tatvupullikal oral english campil varikayu, tan kotto obippikumennu ennal atinumunp tante pratikar cheitiriumennu narpath singh parayunnat ketuen generalin dharippikkayu cheitu.
ori: kintu, sehi din sakaala hin, narapat singh mukt karithiva gora kaedimanank madhyaru jane inrejamanank shiviraku asi generalanku suchana deithile ye tank shuniva anuyani narapat singh kahiyanthi ye se durgaku khali karideve, kintu keval nij pratishodh nei sarila pare.
pan: per us savere, ik godra qaidi jise nuun narapat singh ne riah kitha see , us ne angarezi camp te pahunch ke general nuun oesia ki us ne narapat singh nuun gal karade sunia hai ki oh qila nuun odon tak khaali nahi karega jadon tak us da balda puura nahi hoo janda I
tam: anal andu kalaiye, narapat singh viduvitt velaikkar chinek kathikalil oruvar angileyar mugamuku vandhu, than palitirtha piddke kottaiyske kaliseyyab bowen endu narapat singh sonnatik katttak dalpathiidom therivittar.
tel: kaani, ade udyam narpath singh vidudal chacin tellajati khaidillo okaru angleyul shibera vaddaku vachchi, narpath singh tanu kothan khali chestanani, ayite tan pag tirchukunent varaku cheyanni cheppada tanu vinnti generals teliajesad.
urd: lekin, isi subah ko, safed fome qaidiyon main se ek jise narpit singh ne raha kiya tha, angreji kheme main aayaa or jarnel ko itla di ki is ne narpit singh ko ye kehate hue sunaa tha ki wo qila khaali kar de gaa, lekin is vakt tak naheen jab tak ki wo apna badalaa na lay lay.
eng: But, on that very morning, one of the white prisoners whom Narapat Singh had released came to the English camp and informed the general that he had heard Narapat Singh say that he would evacuate the fort, but not until he had had his vengeance.

ben: 8i august, 1984-te, eubhippi, inak. evan paravartikale 3de systems karporeshner chaak halake baradd kara patent ues4575330-r viruddhe bikirner pravesh, kana varshan, rasyanik pratikria karie athva shudhumatra alore atibeguni lejarrashmi vyabhhar kare photoplimarer shuddhikaran ghatano janya ekati styriolithography jaliati paddhatir maamala dayer kara has.
guj: 8 august 1984na roj petant yu.es.4575330 yu.ve.pe. incorporeshnane ane tyar bad 3dee system corporeshnana chak halane sompayu hatu; je stirolithography fabrication system mate file thayu hatu, jema radiyeshanthi prabhavit photopolicers, sukshma bombamaro, rasayanic prakriya athva matra ultraviolet lite lesrsana vyaktigat lemina athva star umerta hatan.
hin: 8 agast, 1984 ko, you.ve.pi., ink. ne ek sterolithography nirmaan pranali ke liye you.es.4575330 ke liye ek patent aavedan daakhil kiya, jo ki pehle 3di systams korporation ke chak hal ko diya gaya tha, jisamen photopolimur ke saath atikaraman karne vaale vikiran, kan bambaari, rasinic pratikriya, yaa sirf parabangnee prakaash lezaron kaa sankalan karke alag-alag lemina yaa paraten jodi jaati hai.
kan: 1984r august 8randu, you.vi.pi., ink.ge hastantarisid mattu taruvay 3de systems corporeshnnin chak halge hastantarisalad you.es.4575330 hakkuswamyavannu trimitiya-shilamudran tayarika vidhanakkagi dakhlislayitu, idralli vikiran sanghattone, anu tadan, rasayanik kriye, athwa keval neralatit lesar belkinondige dhyutipalimargalannu gattigorisuv moolak pratyek patlagalu athwa padargathannu serislaguttade.
mal: 1984 august etta tiyati yu.vi.pi. iൻkoർpararudinu pinnite 3de. sistens corpationte chak hallinu nalkapat yu.es.4575330 end petraൻr , badhakamay radieshanprahar, kanangute aghaat, raas pravartana athva kewalam altravayalt light lesarul ennivayuprayogich photopolimarua pakappetuttunn pratyek lamainakal athva palikalulla stiriolittography phabrikkeshൻ sistottiൻre peryൽ rekhappetuttapettu.
ori: 8 agast 1984 re, eu.bhi.pi., nigamit nimanthe nirddist hoithiva eban pare 'chak hall af 3de sishtams karporesan' nimanthe nirddist hoithiva eka patent, 'eu.es.4575330'ku eka steriolithography nirman tantra nimanthe dakhal karayaithila, yeunthireki prabhavakari bikiran thiva fatopalimaragudikar sansadhan, kanikaguthikar aghat, rasarhnic prathikria, kimba keval athivigani aaloka rashmiguik dra nirddist parast ba staragudiku yodayaithaye .
pan: 8 agast 1984 nuun ik patent, US4575330, you ve pi, ink. nuun sonpia gya ate bood vich 3di cistum carporasion de chak hal nuun sonpia gya, ik steriaolithography fabrikesan cistum lai dir kita gya see, jise vich photopolimras nuun thik karke viaktigat lemina jaaa lzars nuun , impinging radiation, kana bambari, rasayanak pratikiria, jaaa siraf altraviolet lit nuun leisure naal jodia janda hai|
tam: 8 agast 1984 andu, yuvipi ing. niruvanaduku valangpattu binner 3di systems carpereshanin chak halluku valangappatt yues4575330 enum coffurims, stereolittografi kdduruv amaipickagab patiuseyyapattatu, itu katirvichu modal, tugas boycsutal, vedi vine alltu vellumane putt uta oli lesars mulam photobalimarx padapaduti tanittani menbhadalangs alltu men adukkugalaich cherkum ore amifu.
tel: 1984 agasht 8na styrio litographi fabrikeshan system kos yu.vi.pi, inck, aa tarvat 3de systemsku chendin chak hall ku ketoinchibadin yu.ass. 4575330 ane patent file cheyabadindi, andulo avarodhas date radiyeshan, nirantar anu daadi, rasayan praticharya leda kevalam atinilalohith kanti lejarlato photopalimartha meruguparchada dwara vide rekulu leda poral jodinchabadtai.
urd: 8 agast 1984 ko ek patent, yois4575330, jo yu vee pii inkorpurated ko tafviz kiya gaya tha or baad main 3dee systama corporation ke chuk hill ko tafviz kiya gaya, ek steriolithography fabrackeshan system ke liye pesh kiya gaya, jis main photo polimriz kii asar angez tabikari, jaraat kii bambaari, camiai rid amal yaa sirf balae banfishi roshni kii legores ke saath kevring ke zarie infradi work yaa tahoon ko shamil kiya jataa hai.
eng: On 8 August 1984 a patent, US4575330, assigned to UVP, Inc. and later assigned to Chuck Hull of 3D Systems Corporation, was filed for a stereolithography fabrication system, in which individual laminae or layers are added by curing photopolymers with impinging radiation, particle bombardment, chemical reaction, or just ultraviolet light lasers.

ben: sutarang, irane janapriya samaj madhyamgulo block kara hayes evan irani vikshover karna irane internet praharta bede gamee.
guj: tethi, lokpriya soshial networks temana dwara iranma bloke karaayaan che ane iranian virodhe karne iranma internetni censorship vadhi che.
hin: atah iran main lokapriy soshal media citon ko vahaan ke logon dwaara avaruddh kar diya gaya he, or irani virodh ke parinamswaroop, iran main internet sensorship bad gai he.
kan: hagagi, avugalind iraninalli janapriya samajik jalatangalu nishedhitvagive mattu irani pratibhatnegalindagi iraninalli antarjalavannu sencer maduvikeyu hechagide.
mal: atukond, iraൻkaaർ janakiya samuhik net waർkcookൾ tatangirikkayu iranille pratishedhaൾ karea iraniൽ iൻraർnet seൻsർship waർddhichirikukyu.
ori: sutaran, iranare semanank dra lokapriya samajik netrkagudik abarodh karayaushi, eban iraniyank andoson karanru iranare ingrnat nivnthran briddhi pichhi.
pan: ish lai, prasidh soshal netvarak iran vich onha duara balock kite gaye han ate irani virodh de kaaran, iran vich internet censership vadhi hai|
tam: eneway, prabhlaman samuk utagangluku iraniers tatibodukinsener, melum iranil natakkum boratangsal ange inayyat tanikky adhikaritlldu.
tel: kabatti, irania unde vaaru pramukh soshal netvarklan black chesar, iranian nirasanal karnanga iranloni internet censorship perigindi.
urd: lihaaja iran main maqbool soushal net works ko block kar diya gaya hai or irani mazaahiron kii vajah se iran main internet sansarship main azafa hawa hai.
eng: Therefore, popular social networks are blocked by those in Iran and because of Iranian protests, internet censorship in Iran has increased.

ben: dehradun sahar taar chahida metate gie duti prathmik us thek panian jal pa: prushtler jal o bhugarver jal.
guj: dehradun shaher teni jaruriyat puree karva matenu pivaanu paani sapati paranu paani ane bhugarbhajal em be prathmik srotomathi melve che.
hin: dehradun shahar kii pine yogya pani kii aapurti do praathmik sroton se hoti he: satahi jal or bhoojal.
kan: dehradun nagarvu ader sarbarajin agatyagainnu poorisuvudakkagi kudiyuv nirannu eradu praiamik moolagalind padeyuttade: melmai neeru mattu antarjal.
mal: rand prathamicasrotassukaliൽninna dehraduൺ nagarattin atiൻre kutivellam kittunnat : uparitalajalam, bhugർbh jalam enniv vitarnavashyaൾ nickverunnu.
ori: deradun seher ehar yogan aavashyakatagudik pin duiti pramukh utsaru paaniya jal prapth karithaye: bhooprushtha jal eban bhoothal jal .
pan: dehradoon shahir nuun peen da paani, doo mouth sarotaan ton milada hai : sathi paani te zamin da paani jise naal purti di zarurta puri hundia han I
tam: dehradoon nakrutingu neer vruttut devaiyap purtysey erandu muthanmay aadharangalilrundhu gudineer varukintu: meshbharapu neer manllum nilattati neer.
tel: dehradun nagarpu traguniti saraphra avasarai rend pradhan molal nudi tirthai: uparital jalam mariyu bhugarbh jalam.
urd: farahami kii apni zaruuryat kii takumel ke liye dehradun shahar ko kaabil nosh pani do ahim jaria se haasil hota hai: satahi pani or jameen doz pani.
eng: Dehradun city receives potable water from two primary sources: surface water and groundwater, to meet its supply needs.

ben: bhavanti mazkhane vruttakar madhyavarti chember evan ei chembertike gheere royas tinti ardhvrittakar halghar, ya chember af prince (bartaman library hal hiseve vyabhhar has), rajya parishad (bartaman rajyasvar kshetre vyabhhar has), evan centrian vidhansvar (bartaman loksvar kshetre vyabhhar has) adhiveshner janya nirman kara hayesil.
guj: aa imaratna kendrama ek vartulakar kendriya kaksha che, ane aa kakshani ajubaju tran ardhvartulakar ordao che, je chember of prinsisna satra (jeno atyaare pustakalaya kaksha tarike upayog thai che) mate, rajya parishad (je atyaare rajya sabha mate upayogma levaya che), ane kendriya vidhansabha (je have lok sabha mate vaparai che) mate baandhvama aavya hata.
hin: bhawan ke madhya main vrittakar kendriya kaksh he or uske chaaron ore teen ardh-vrittakar kaksh hai jinka nirmaan rajkumaar kaksh (jise ab pustkaalay kaksh ke rup main prayog main laayaa jaataa he), rajya parishad (jise ab rajya sabha ke liye prayog kiya jaataa he), or kendriya vidhaan sabha (jise ab lok sabha ke liye prayog kiya jaataa he) ke satron ke liye kiya gaya tha.
kan: kattadad madhyabhagadalli vrittakarad kendra pranganavide mattu i pranganad suttalu arevrittakarad mooru sabhanganagaliddu, avannu chhembar aaf princes (ig granthalayavagi baislaguttide), state kaunsil (ig rajya sabhegagi baislaguttide), mattu kendra shaskang sabhe (ig lok sabhegagi baislaguttide) ivugal adhiveshnagaligendu nirmislagittu.
mal: kettitatine madhyabhagat vruttakritiilull central chembaru, i chembarine chuty chembar of princes (ippol library halai upyogikunnat ), state kansil (ippol rajyasabhayckai upyogikunnat ), kendra niyamnirmman asambli (ippol loksabhaikkai upyogikunnat ) ennivyute sammekanngൾkkai niർmmicpat munn arddhavrittakritiilull hallukalu anult.
ori: attalikatir kendrare brittakar 'kendriya prakosht' rahichhi, eban ehi prakoshttiku gheri thinoti ardhdhavrittakar hall rahichhi yeunguik yuvarajmanank prakosht (varttaman 'pathagar hall' bhavare brebahrut) r adhiveshan, rajya upadeshta parishad (varttaman 'rajyasabha' bhavare brebahrut), eban kendriya vaidhanic sabha (varttaman 'lokasabha' bhavare brebahrut) pin nirman karayaithila .
pan: imarat de center vich ik circular cendari chember hai, ate ish chember duale tin ardh-golakar haal han, jo chember ouf prince (hun library haal vajon varte jaande han) de saishns lai banaye gaye san state consil (hun raj sabha lai varti jandi hai) ate cendari vidhan sabha (hun lok sabha lai varti jandi hai) |
tam: kddittain maiyapakudiil vatt vativ madhyap faerarai ulldu, indep faerariaich subari moondau araivatt vativak kutas ulsana, are semphor off princess (ibbodhu library hallagap payanbaduttapadukintu), arasu sabai (ibbodhu rajya sabhawagap payanbaduttapadukintu), madhya sattaperaw (ibbodhu log sabhawagap payanbaduttapadukintu) akhiyavain amarvuess natattuvadaikakak katoppattanu.
tel: bhavana nadimadhyan gundrati central chhamber, dani chuttuta mod ardhchandrakar harel untai, avi chhamber aaf princes (present library hall ga upyogo undi), state kaunsil (present rajya sabh kos upayoginchabadutondi), mariyu central legisletive asembli (present lok sabh kos upayoginchabadutondi) samaveshalakai nirmitmainai.
urd: imarat ke marcuz main daayrvi marcuji chember hai, or is chember ke arad gird teen niyam daayrvi hal hain jo chember of princez (ab library hal ke tuur par mastamal), riyasati konsil (ab rajya sabha ke tuur par mastamal) or marcuji kanoon saaz asambali (ab lok sabha ke ke tuur par mastamal) ke ujalaason ke liye tamir kiye gaye the.
eng: At the centre of the building is the circular Central Chamber, and surrounding this Chamber are three semicircular halls that were constructed for the sessions of the Chamber of Princes (now used as the Library Hall), the State Council (now used for the Rajya Sabha), and the Central Legislative Assembly (now used for the Lok Sabha).

ben: pi.es.ke-te agmaner sang sang vaidyuthik token pradaan kara aar kaaj shesh haowar pare vaidyuthik prasthaan chithi dewar madhyam kaagajvihin parisheba pradaan sambhava hayes, ya pariwesh raksha kare evan digital bharter sabuj udyoger prachar kare.
guj: kagbrahit seva, paryavaranna sanrakshan ane dijital bharatna harith aarambh mate pe.es.ke. par aagman samaye electronic token ane seva purn thaye ek electronic nikaas patr aapavaano aarambh thayo che.
hin: aagaman ke samay electronic token or pi.es.ke. main seva puri ho jane par electronic nirgam patr jari karne se kaagaj-rahit seva, paryaavaran kii raksha or harith pahalon ko badhaava dena sakasham ho sakaa he.
kan: pi.es.ke.ge agamisidag vidyunman tocan koduvike mattu seveannu odagisid balik niduv vidyunman nirgaman patrvu kagadarahit seve odagisuvudannu, parisar sanrakshaneyannu mattu digital indiad hasiru upakramagal pracharavannu sadhayavagiside.
mal: pi. es. kaile, atunn samayt oru electronic tokൺ naൽkunnatu seven puർttiyakia sheea oru electronic exit letaർ naൽkunnatumay sampradayam, paristate sanrakshichukondu digitaൽ indyayute paristaitek itapeale protsahippicchukondu papർrahit seven naൽkunnat sadhyamaki.
ori: aagman pare 'elactronik tokan isuans' eban pi.es.ke. re seva samapti pare eka 'elactronik ekjit letter', pariveshaku suraksha pradaan kari tatha 'dejital india'r sabuj padakshepagujaikar prachar o prasar kari kaagajabihin seva yogaibare sahayak hoichhi .
pan: agman te electronic token jari karna ate pe.se.ke te seva di samapati ton bood ecsit paper de jari on naal digital india de pahilkadami kaagaz mukat hona, watawarn di raakhi karnaa nuun nuun praphulat kitha hai I
tam: pieske-will ulle nutheumbodhu electronic docan varanguvatum panie muditt pin electronic velierudal katidam varanguvatum kakithamilla sevai alippathakum, sudduchulap bhadukappaddkum, digitale indiavin pasumait ditangss ukquibpathakum vakaisaitulldu.
tel: agamana ventne electronic token jari mariyu sevanu phurti chesak pieske vadd ock electronic agsit lever jari cheyada anedi kagith-rahit sevanu andinchada, paryavarananni rakshinchada mariyu digital india taluku harith karyakramas protsahingdanni sadhyam chassindi.
urd: pii es ke main kudamat kii takumel ke baad aamad par electronic token ujara or electronic eggsit litre ne paper les service faraham karne, maahuliat kii hifaazat or degetal india ke sabz ikdamaat ko farvag dene main madad faraham kii hai.
eng: Electronic Token Issuance upon arrival and an electronic Exit Letter after completion of service at the PSK has enabled in providing of paperless service, protecting the environment and promoting the green initiatives of Digital India.

ben: kono nishkriya kaanch (kaanch-jatiya) chhanche aichaelelublu achal hay ya, koek dashaker janya kono bhugarbhasth batanukul bhandar sanrakshit thake, evan pare kono gaveer aadhar dhele dewar janya parikalpit has.
guj: ech.el.el.dabalyu. e ek nishkriya kach (vetriyas) sanchama sthir che, je vatanukulit khanama thoda dayakao sudhi sangrahit che, ane pachhi tene unda bhandarma nikaal karvaani yojana che.
hin: ech.el.el.dablyoo. ko niskriy kaanch (vitrius) matrix main radiodharm ko sthir karne ke liye rakh kar vayushitit kaksh main kuch dashakon ke liye bhandaarit kiya jaataa he or phir unhen bhumigat aadhaan main niptaan karne par vichaar kiya jaataa he.
kan: ech.el.el.dublu.annu jad gazin (gajinanthi) koshavondralli nishchalagolisi, galiind tampisid gummatchavaniya nelamaligeyalli kelvaru dashakagalvarege sangrahicittu, tadanantar aalavaad jagadalli wilevari madlu yojiciralaguttade.
mal: ech .el.el.dublyuin oru nishkriyasphatikapatrattil chalanrahitmakiyu, vayukond shitikarichch orarail kueach dashakas sukshichuekukayu cheitashes oru aammulla sambhraniilaki ochiwakan paddhtiitunnu.
ori: ech.el.el.dablu. ku eka nishkriya kach (scch ) myatrics madhyare gatirodhit kari rakhayae, eka bau-sheetaleekrit kakshare alpakichhi dashandhi pin gachchit rakhayae, eban ta'pare eka gabhir sangrahagaar madhyaku nishkruti nimanthe yojana karayaaye .
pan: aich.ail.ail.dableu ik gatihin glass (oach varg) sarani vich sthir kar ke kuchh saalas lai tandi hawa de tahikhane vich sanchit kar ditaa janda hai ate phir ish nuun ik duunge bhande vich nasht karan da prabandh kitha janda hai I
tam: eseleltapleyu woru vinapuriyadh khannadi (patik) aniamle muthakkapattu woru kazzuk kuliruttap pettkatil oruchil pattandus chemicopatum, binner ore al kappeqtil appuopadudhat ditamidapatum.
tel: hacheleldebluni ock jad (gaju vanti) sphatik acchulo sthirikarinchi, galidvara challabarchabadin maligalo konni dashabdalpat nilv unchi, aa taruvat ock lotan giddangilo paresenduku pranalik cheyabadutundi .
urd: each el el dablyoo ek gair fial glaas (zjaaji) metrix main mustahkam kiya jataa hai, jise ek ayear cold walt main chand duhaiyon tak zkhera kiya jataa hai, or fir is ko ek gahare zakhere main thikaane lagane kaa mansuba banaaya hai.
eng: HLLW is immobilized in an inert glass (vitreous) matrix, stored for a few decades in an air-cooled vault, and then planned to be disposed of in a deep repository.

ben: bartaman, vruddhir hisaab pradhanath arthnaitik karmakshamata (vruddhir haar, jiddypi'r shatakara hisabe rajasav ghatti, jiddypi'r shatakara hisabe sarkarer run, jiddypi'r shatakara hisabe kar rajasav ityadi) evan samajik karmakshamtar (daridrya, baishamya, karmsansthaner haar, janasankhyar pushtir haar ityadi) upar nibaddha.
guj: atyaare, vruddhino hisaab mukhyatve aarthik dekhav (vruddhi dar, ji.dee.pe.ni takawari pramaneni rajkoshiya khaadh, ji.dee.pe.ni takawari pramanenu sarakaari devu, ji.dee.pe.ni takawari pramaneni kar aavak, vagere) ane samazik dekhav (garibi, asamantha, berojagari praman, vastinu poshan praman, vagere) par kendrit che.
hin: vartmaan main, vruddhi lekha mukhya rup se aarthik pradarshan (vikaas dar, ji.di.pi. ke pratishat ke rup main rajkoshiya ghaataa, ji.di.pi. ke pratishat ke rup main sarkari karj, ji.di.pi. ke pratishat ke rup main kar-rajasav, aadi) or saamaajik pradarshan (garibi, pakshpaat, rojgaar ke str, jansadharan ke poshan str, aadi) par kendrit he.
kan: presettdalli, belvanige lekkacharvu mukhyavagi aarthik sadhane (belvanige der, ji.de.pi.y shekadavaru korate hanakasu, ji.de.pi.y shekadavaru sarkaari sal, ji.de.pi.y shekadavaru terige varman, ityadi) mattu samajik sadhaneya mele (badtan, asamanathe, udyogad matt, gener paushtikateya matt, ityadi) kendrikrutwagide.
mal: ippol, grot akanding pradhanmayu shraddh kendrikarichirikunnat sampattikapravർttanaklattil (vaircchanirak, ji.de.pi.yute shatamanmenn nileil dhanakkammi, ji.de.pi.yute shatamanmenn nileil sarcarinte kat, ji.de.pi.yute shatamanmenn nileil nikutivarumana tutangiyav) samuhikpravർttanaklattil (daridryam, asamatva, topil labhyat, janathyute poshakaharanil, tutangiyav) aan.
ori: varttaman, abhivriddhir hisaavakitab mukhitah aarthik sampadan (abhivriddhi haar, ji.de.pir pratishat bhave bithtiya niant, ji.de.pir pratishat bhave sarkaari run, ji.de.pir pratishat bhave tikas rajas, ityadi) eban samajik sampadan (daridrya, asamanta, niyukthi haar, janasankhar poshan star, ityadi) upare kendrit.
pan: ish same, utpati lekha jiadatar arthic kiria(utpati di gati,ghat ji.di.pi di pratisht de te tor te , sarkari karajan ji.di.pi di pratisht de tor te, lagaan ji.di.pi di pratisht de tor te adi) ate samajik kiria (garibi, asmanta,ruzagaar da satar, abaadi di pustikata da satar adi ) te centerit hai I
tam: tarbodhu, valarchikan karanngan arivadangu mukhiamak porulatarach seyaltirnum (valarchi vikitham, jitipe-in villukadawk nidhippaxakurai, jitipe-in villukadawk arasukh gatan, jitipe-in villukadawk vari varwaii bhonrowai) samukach seyaltidhanume (vadhumay, arwattalu, velaivaifu nilai, makalin unavutt nilai bhonrowai) payanbaduttapadukindena.
tel: present, vruddhi ganan anedi pradhananga ardhik panithir (vruddhi rate, jidypi shatanga dravya lot, jidypi shatanga prabhutva runa, jidypi shatanga pannu rabadi) mid, alage samajik panithir (pedarikan, asamanath, upadhi sthai, janabha yokk poshkahar sthai modalgunavi) mid drushti pettindi.
urd: fi alhal, tarakkee accounting buniyadi tuur par iqtsaadi carakardagee (tarakkee kii shrah, ji dee pii ke faisad ke tuur par mali khasara, ji dee pii ke faisad ke tuur par sarkari karz, ji dee pii ke faisad ke tuur par tex aamdani, vagairah) or samaji carakardagee (gurbat, adam masawat, rojgaar kii satah, aabaadee kii gazaait kii satah, vagairah) par merccoz hai.
eng: At present, growth accounting is mainly focused on economic performance (growth rate, fiscal deficit as a percentage of GDP, government debt as a percent of GDP, tax revenue as a percent of GDP, etc.) and social performance (poverty, inequality, level of employment, nutrition level of population, etc.).

eng: Literature, on the other hand, is a sort of language art that can be read or spoken.

eng: So, if you enroll as a voter at your constituency, wherever you are, you need to come to your constituency to cast a vote.

ben: markin yuktarashtra ekabar nijer pratham upsthite pratistha kara hay gele halaka aakarer sthanian brander analine dokan chalu kara ya evan sampoorn caryakari markini webasite shuru ag parisheba o khyati nirman manonivesh karte has; aar abhijeeta barhte din evan natun grahak tana janya aro beshi akramanatmak o jhunkipurna bipanan kaushal vastawayan karun.
guj: ek vakhat tame americama pratham upsthite sthapit kari lo pachhi, sthanik branded online storani halvi aavritti present karvi ane saari seva tatha pratishtha banaavavaa par dhyaan kendrit kari jokhami amalikaran kartaan pahela sampurna kaaryakari american website ane gatishil anubhav puro padwo ane saari seva tatha pratishtha banaavavaa par dhyaan kendrit karvu ane nava grahako melvavaa mate vadhu akramak vechanani vyuharchana karvi joie.
hin: ek baar aapane sanyukt rajya america main pehali upasthiti sthapit kar lee to puri tarah se kriyasheel america website pradaan karne se pehle mobile utpaada upyogkarta dwaara anubhav or nae graahak paane ke liye ek adhik aakraamak or adhik jokhim-bhari vipanan ranneeti amal main laane se pehle online store ke sthaneey brands ke halke sanskaran ko aarambh karne or seva tathaa pratishtha nirmaan par dhyaan dene main adhik bhalaai he.
kan: omme nivu you.es.nalli modal astitvavannu sthapisicond mele, hoss grahakarannu honduv saluvagi purna pramandalli kaaryasamarthavad you.es. jalatan mattu mobail anubhavavannu odagisuv, hagu innashtu munnugguv mattu apayavuthal maratgarikeya tantravannu kaaryagatagolisuv munn sthaliya brandugathannull online angadia laghu aavruttiannu prarambhisi, seve odagisuvudu mattu hesaru galisuvudaredege gaman kendrikarisuvudralli auchityavide.
mal: yu. esiൽ ningtoൾ prathamikasannidhyam sthapichukavinjaൽ, putia upabhoktae labhikkaൻ puർnnapravർttansheshiull oru yu. es websiteu mobiൽ samvidhanvu orukkukayu sahasikataaritu apakatsadhyatyulatumay oru vipanananyam natappilakkukyu cheiyunnatinumump, pradeshik braൻdulltu cheria totilulatumay oru oൺliൻ stoർ tuingukayu seventtl salperuntakkunnatil shraddh kendrikarikunnat yuktipar.
ori: thare aapan americare pratham bavasaik upastate pratishthit karisariva pare, nuthan grahak hateiva nimanthe eka poornaroope karyanksham americiya bsait tatha bhramyaman anubhuti pradaan kariva o eka adhik akramanatmak tatha shankapoorna bazar vigyapan karyanpanthaku karyankaari kariva poorvaru, kaunsi eka sthaniya brandyukt anlin bikraikendrar eka laghu roopantar aarmbh kariva eban seva o khati pratishtha digre dhyankendrit karivata yatharth manehue.
pan: ik war tusin america vich apni pahili upstate sthapit kar lai hai , taan sianap ish vich hai ki ik puri kargeshil america di website banaun ton pihals ate mobile te anubhav ate ik hamlawar te jokhim bhari kharido-farokhat neeti jo nave gaahaks nuun hasal karan lai hai, us ton pahila ik sthalic brandid anline store kholo te seva te neknami te com karo I
tam: nings muthalil americail kaloondaya pingu, mitman alavill ore ulnaddu prant kont online storai dibandhu sevai varanguadil nagapayar peruatil mujhukkavanum selutti, adanbin woru munuch seyalbattu america inayatalam manllum mobile bayanar anubhavatai vabangi putiya vatikyalaryp pellum nokil melum munapan, dunivan chandaippadutal utty payanbadudhuatu arthamulldak irukkum.
tel: meeru yues lo tolisariga praveshinchak, kott viniogadarul sampadinchenduku phurti sthai yu. ass. vebsait mariyu mobile vinioganni andinchi marint fivratar mariyu pramadnto kudin marketing pranalikani avalambinche mundu, stanik brands andine store yokk chinnpati roopantarna prarambhinchi, sev cheyata mariyu parapati pempondinchukovadampai drushti pettada ardhavantanga untundi.
urd: ek bar jab aap america main apni pahali maujudagi kaayam kar lete hain, to ye baat makul hogi ki kisi mukami brand ke aan line store kaa ek halka varden shurua kiya jaaye or behatar khidamat or saakh banane par tawaja di jaaye, kabel is ke ki ek mukammal fial america web site, or mobile tajurba faraham karne or naye gahakon ke hissol ke maqsad se koi zyaada jarhana or jokhim bhari marketing hukmat amali lagu kii jaaye.
eng: Once you have established the first presence in the US, it makes sense to launch a light version of a local branded online store and focus on service and reputation building, before providing a fully functional US website, and mobile experience and implementing a more aggressive and riskier marketing strategy in order to acquire new customers.

ben: 2017 saler 12i november barakhamba rhode thek jantar mantar percent delhi taar dasham quir pride pradarshner yojan kare.

hin: 12 navambar 2017 main, dilli main barakhambha road se jantar mantar tak dasvin quyr pride parade yojit kii gai.
kan: 2017r navembar 12randu dehliyu barakhamba rasteind jantar mantarvarege ader 10nae salingigal hemmey nadigeyannu aayojisittu.
mal: barakhamba rodumutൽ jantർ mantർ varayull atiൻre pattamatte khviaർ pride paradine 2017 novembർ 12 n dൽhi atithayatva vahichu.
ori: 12 november 2017re, delhi ehar dasham samalingi gaurab shobhayatra barakhamba tharu jantar mantar paryyant aatojit karithila .
pan: 12 november, 2017 nuun dilli ne apni dasvin viakhan garab parade di mezabaani kiti janter mantra ton li ke barakhamba road tak.
tam: 12 november 2017 andu dilhiil natant putumap balial bhoku kondorukkan pattavatu perumay urvalam paragampa chalil dodangi jantar manter varai senttu.
tel: 2017 november 12 na, bazkhamba road nudi jantar mantar varaku delhi tan padav asadharan gaurav uregimpuku aatithya ichchindi.

eng: On 12 November 2017, Delhi hosted its tenth queer pride parade from Barakhamba Road to Jantar Mantar.

ben: bivinn raje gunamanti vinn also praia sab rajyei parikaamor gunaman, maanav sampader upsthite, oshudher yogan, evan nathiguli asantonjanak chhil.
guj: vividh rajyoma gunavattani bhinnata che, jayare malkhakiya suvidhaoni gunavatta, manav sansadhanoni upsthite, dawaono purvatho ane asantoshkarak dastavejo hovanu lagbhag tamam rajyoma janayu hatu.
hin: haalanki puure rajyon main gunvattta main antar the, lagbhag sabhi main buniyadi sanrachana kii gunvattta, maanav sansadhano kii upasthiti, dawaaon kii aapurti, or vivaran-dastavej asantoshjanak paae gaye the.
kan: rajyagaladyant gunamttadalli vyatyasavittadaru, bahutek ellavugaillu, moolsaukaryad gunamatt, maanav sampanmoolagal labhyate, aushadhigal poorike, mattu dakhlegalu truptikarvagiralill.
mal: sansthanangൾtoru gunnilvar vyatyastamairie, ottumica itaol atisthanasakaryaute gunnilvar, manushyavibhavaute labhyat, marunnulute labhyat, rekhakൾ enniv atruptikarmanen conteti.
ori: yadio rajngudik madhyare gunavathta bhinna bhinna thila, kintu praia sabuthare, bhitthibhumir gunavathta, manab sambader upastate, aushadhar yogan eban recordpatra adi santhonjanak nathila boli janapadishi.
pan: jad ki raajan vich guntata bhin see, lagabhag sara vich, buniadi dhanche di guntata, manukhi sarotaan di maujuudgi, dawia di supplai, ate ricard asantushtijanak paae gaye san|
tam: dharam manilangalidaiye vellupatrundal enfodhilu, aikuraiya anwatlume ulghatamipin dharam, manitval iruppu, marundugalin vriu, patientus akhiyawe tiruptikaramak ille endu khandawiapattatu.
tel: rashtral variga nanyath bhinnanga unna, dadapu annitlonu, maulik sadupayal nanyath, manav vanarul upsthite, aushadhal saraphra, mariyu vratpoorvak namodulu asantrikranga unnti kanipinchai.
urd: agarache mayar riyasato main mukhtalf tha, taahim kam va besh sab main buniyadi dhaanche kaa mayar, insaani vasile kii maujudagi, advyat kii farahami, or record gair itmeenaan baksh paae gaye.
eng: While the quality varied across states, in almost all, the quality of infrastructure, presence of human resources, supply of medicines, and records were found to be unsatisfactory.

ben: alaskar ankorage avasthit robert bi atud buildinyer naam ekasmay vyank af america centre dewa hayesil, tader bhadat sicurity pasific vyankke adhigrahan kare newar samay eksath ei punarnamkaran kara hayesil.
guj: alaskana ankarejanu dha robert bi. atwood building ek samaye bank of america center nam dharavatu hatu, jenu pun:namkaran bank dwara buildingna bhadut sathena jodanma sampadan thatan sicurity pasyphic bank karayu.
hin: ankerage, alaska main robert bi. atwood building ko ek samay bank of america centre naam diya gaya tha, lekin bank ke bhawan-kiraayedaar, security pasific bank ke adhigrahan ke saath iskaa naam badal diya gaya.
kan: alaskad ankarejnalliruva robert bi. atwood buildingannu ondomme ʼbank aaf america centreʼ endu hesarislagittu, aa banku aa kattadad badigedar security pacific bankannu swadhin padisicondiddarondige marunamkarnavayitu.
mal: alaskaile ankarajilull robart alltwood kettite avite vatakaundairunn secourity pasiphic bank eteetuttatote perumati orical bank of ameria centre enne namakarna cheythirunnu.
ori: aalascar ankarej thare thiva 'rabart aatud building', yahaki ekada 'bank af america censor' namere namit thila, taha banktir building bhadatia 'sicuriti pasifik bank'r adhigrahan sange sange punarnamit hoithila .
pan: ankarej, alasaka vich robert bi. atwood building nuun ik samen baink aaf america center da name ditha gya see , jisda name baink duara badal ke building kirayedar sudkhya paisific baink di prapati de naal rakhia gya see|
tam: alaskavin aangareil ull robert bhi. atwood kdditam munbu bank off america centre endu peyariopattrundatu, pingu akddittil watakiku irunth security pasibic banka mergant bangi wangy podhu itu tarboty peyarukku majhpattatu.
tel: alaskaloni yankares lo okapp bank aaf america center peru kaligin rashirt bi yatod buildingku indulo addekunn security pasiphic bankunu i banku adhigrahananloki tisukunnak danni kalupukuni peru marchada jariginadi.
urd: alaska ke shahar ankares main waaqa robert bi it wood building ko ek jamane main bank of america center kaa naam diya gaya tha, jis kaa naam bank ke zarie badal kar kiryh daar sekyoriti pisific bank kii imarat ke hissol ke saath rakha gaya tha.
eng: The Robert B. Atwood Building in Anchorage, Alaska, was at one time named the Bank of America Center, renamed in conjunction with the bank's acquisition of building tenant Security Pacific Bank.

hin: inhen kaarnon se satitv kaa nishchit rup se nirdhaaran yonichhad kii jaanch se nahin kiya ja saktaa he.

ben: aguli madhye khadya athva jal khawa comme yawa, alsya, cough thek jalin athva fakashe saada shleshma srab, cough fola, evan aswabhavik (rang o gaian) mal antarbhukt hate par.
guj: aama khorac athva paninu ochhu seven, susti, ankhomathi sajal athva fikka safed pravahino strav, ankhoni balatara ane asamanya mal (rang ane swaroop) samavisht hoi shake che.
hin: inamen bhojan or pani ke antargrahan main kami, aalasy, paniyal yaa feekaa safed shleshmabh netra srav, aankhon main sujan, asaamaanya vishtha (rang or rup) shaamil hai.
kan: ivu meyuvike athwa neeru kudiyuv pramandalli ilike, jadtva, kannugalind nirad athwa nasu bili bannad pisuru osaruvudu, kannugamalli uriut, mattu asahajavad malavannu (bann mattu aakaar) olagondirbahudu.
mal: kushanera thitetukalo weliankutio, alassyam, kannukaliൽninnu neർttato vidoriveluttato ay mucthpolull drava puchhattuvarൽ, kannuvikum, asadharanmay malam (nickttil rupattil) enniv itiൽ uൾppeta.
ori: khadrakhaiva o pani piibare hras, nishkriyatha, akhiru pania ba fika dhala lenyjara bahriva, akhi phula eban asbhavik matttag (rang o ganan) adi ethire antarbhukt hoipare.
pan: ihnas vich ait bhojan jaaa paani da seven , alls, paani varga jaaa fika safed mucoid discharge da awkhan ton vagana, awkhan vich sojash, ate asdhaaran eati (ranga ate roop) shamal hoo sakde han|
tam: ivarphil unu alltu neer udkolvatu kuraidal, sombal, gangalilrundhu neer bonthe alltu veleriya pinai, gankalil asslchi, (nilem manllum vativatil) ialpare malam akhiyawe uddlam.
tel: vitello ahara leda nitini tisukovailo taggudal, mandgati, kall nudi nitivanti leda polypoin telupu rangu shlesh srava, kallu vachi arrbadta, mariyu asahaj malam (rangu mariyu rupa) undavacchu.
urd: in main kam hawa fed yaa pani kii muqadaar, sasti, pani yaa pilaa safed bulgari kaarij hone waale made kaa aankhon se kaarij hona, aankhon main jalan or gair maamooli paakhaana (rang or shukla main) shamil hosakte hain.
eng: These may include reduced feed or water intake, lethargy, watery or pale white mucoid discharge from the eyes, inflammation in the eyes, and abnormal stool (colour and form).

ben: 797 christabdev (baa sambhavat 801 christabd) bagdader abbasin kaliph haroon al rashid ekati jalghdi "visesh kare vishad udahraner" aathey ekasang abul-abbas named ekati esian hathir madhyam sharlemanke upsthapit karechillen.
guj: isavisan 797maa (athva shakya che isavisan 801maa) bagdadana abbasid khaliph harun al-rashide charlmagnene ek abul-abbas namano asian haathi ane sathe ek ‘khas udaharan roop’ jalaadial bhet aapi hati.
hin: 797 isvi (yaa shaayad 801 isvi) main, baghdad ke abbasid khalipha, haaron al-raashid ne sharlemen ko jal ghadi ke ek "vishisht rup se alankrita namoonay" ke saath abul-abbaas naam kaa ek asian hathi bhent main diya tha.
kan: kri.sha. 797ralli (illave bahushah kri.sha. 801), baghdadin abbasid khalif, haroon al-rashidanu sharlmenge abul-abbas emb hesarin ondu eshyad aneyannu, adarondige jal gadiyarad "visheshwagi parishkarisid madri"yondannu udugoreyagie nididnu.
mal: bagdadille abbacid khaliryay haruൺ aൽ-rushid 797 e.de iൽ (801 e.diilumawan), abuൾ - abbas ennuperit oru esiaൻ anycoppam "kudia vishdanshangute udaharan"maay oru jalaghatikarvu shalamene sammanichu.
ori: 797 christabd (ba sambhavatah 801 christabd)re, bagdadra abbasidh khalipha, haarun al-rashidh, sarlemennku, eka jal-ghantar "vishesh bhave karyan hoithiva namuna" sahit, eka esiya haati pradaan karithile, yaahaar nam thila abul-abbas.
pan: 797 i, ( jaaa shaaid 801 i ) vich baghdad de awbasid kalif, haroon al-rashid ne sharlamen nuun paani di gadi da "khaas udaharan da vikhyan" den de naal ik asiai hathi named abul-abas ve pesh kitha I
tam: kibe 797il (alltu, satiyamak kibe 801il) baghtadin appasiya khalipha haroon ar-rasheed manner charlomenuku abul abbas enjh peyaritt ore aciya yanaes "taniveupatt woru pramandaman" neerk khatikartes parichak anupinar.
tel: krish 797 lo(lek bahusha krish 801), bagdad ki chendin abbasid kaliph, harun al rashid, sharliamain ku abull-abbas peru gal ock asia gajanni, danitobat "pratyekamain savivar udaharan" anadagg ock niti gadiaranni samarpinchadu.
urd: 797 isvi (yaa mumkin tuur par 801 isvi) main, baghdad ke abbasi khaliph haron alrshid ne sharlemin ko aabi ghadi kii ek "khaas tuur par mufasal misaal" ke alaava abvalabas nami ek asiai haathi pesh kiya tha.
eng: In 797 AD (or possibly 801 AD), the Abbasid caliph of Baghdad, Harun al-Rashid, presented Charlemagne with an Asian elephant named Abul-Abbas, together with a "particularly elaborate example" of a water clock.

ben: "ekasang bhalo kaaj kara" athach "ekati narbare kahini tene nie yete" baadhya haoya pradhan abhinetader prashansa kare dya indian expresser shubhra gupta 5-e 2.5 devan chalachchitratike.
guj: dha indian ekspracena shubhra guptae , ‘‘sathe maline saru bhajwataan’’ parantu ‘‘ek pangu vartane aagal dhapavavaa’’ vivash mukhya abhinetaone birdavataan aa filmane 5mathi 2.5 aapya hata.
hin: mukhya adaakaaron kii taareef main yah kehete hue ki unhone "ek saath acha pradarshan kiya he" kintu ve "ek marial kahani ko protsaahan dene ke liye vivash hai", da indian express kii shubhra gupta ne film ko 5 main se 2.5 die.
kan: indian expresn shubhra gupt, "ottige chennagi natisiruv" adare "sattvavillad katheyannu ettihidiyuv" ottadakke silukiruv mukhya kalavidarnnu prashamsisutta i chalanchitrakke 5kke 2.5r rating nididdare.
mal: indian expressille shubhr gupta chitrattin anchil 2.5 nalkukayu 'oru mughanta kathk uk nalkanai' nirbandhicppettengil 'nannai onnicchupravർttichtin' mukhyantinthanare abhinandikkukayu cheitu.
ori: indian eksapresr shubhra gupta ehi chakchchithraku 5ru 2.5 taraka pradaan kari mukhya kalakaranku prasansha karithile, yeunmane “ekatara bhal abhinaya kariyanthi” kintu semananku baadhyata mutak bhave “eka dhila kaahaniku dhari rakhivaku” padithila.
pan: da indian acspress di shubhra gupta ne film nuun 5 vichon 2.5 di reating diti, mouth kalakaars di tarif keeti jo ki "ieathe vadhia khedde" han, per "ik lungadi kahaani nuun vadhaun" lai majaboor han|
tam: thi indian expirus nabeetein shubhra gupta indep pattuku 5ku 2.5 matippen vabangi, "sinppak onduserndu naditll" anal "woru nontic kathikud dudiputum" katayatil ull munanik kadabatralap baratti edutirindar.
tel: di indian acspress ki chendin shubhra gupta i chitraloni pradhan patradharulu "kalisi baga natincharu" ani abhinandinchi, kani "pelvamin kathani packattatanii" ottidi cheyabaddarani chitraniki 5 ki 2.5 ichcharu.
urd: indian express kii shubhra gupta ne film ko 5 main se 2.5 diye, marcuji udaakar "ek saath acchhee tarah kaam karte hain" kehate hue taareef kii magar jo "ek langadi kahani ko baddhaava dene par" majaboor hain.
eng: Shubhra Gupta of The Indian Express gave the film 2.5 out of 5, complimenting the lead performers who "play well together" but are forced to "boost a limp story."

hin: ham aksar meghalaya jate hai kyonki vahaan kii sadaken or jagahen donon hi sundar hai.
kan: naavu aagagge meghalayakke hogtirthivi, alli rastegalu, jagagalu eradu chennagive.
mal: tes palpposhu pokunnat meghalayaia, karea avitte rodulu sthalajhlu sundar.

pan: aseen akasar meghalaya jaande haa jiven uthe sadakas ate thavaan doven khubasurat han|

ben: duti khudra nadee nunia o gauri asansoler pash die boy ya.
guj: be nanakdi nadeeo nunia ane gauri asanasolmathi vahe che.
hin: do choti nadikaayen, nuniya or garooi, asanasol se hokar guzarati hai.

tel: asansol prakk nudi nuniya mariyu gauri ane rend chinn erulu pravahistai.
urd: asanasol se guzarane wali do choti nadiyaan, navaniya or gori, bahati hain.
eng: Two small rivulets, Nunia and Gauri, flow past Asansol.

ben: biswa arthik sankater samay thek sarkari vibhagguli aro beshi o unnat tathy sangrah karche evan lucono durbaltar khonj karche.
guj: vaishvik nanakiya katokatine karne, caryalaya vibhag vadhare ane vadhu saari mahiti ekathi kari rahyo che ane chhupayeli nabalione shodhi rahyo che.
hin: vaishvik vittiya sankat ke samay se aadhikarik kshetra or zyada or behatar jaankaree ekatrit kar rahaa he or prachhann bhedyataayen khoj rahaa he.
kan: jagathik aarthik bikcuttinindichege, adhikari valayavu hchin mattu uttam mahithiannu sangrahisuttide hagu gurutisde hod daurbalyagainnu shodhisuttide.
mal: agolsampattikapratisandhikkushes audyogikamekhal annattiൽ kutitu mechchapetatumay vivarangൾ shekharikkayu marangirikkunn duർbalamekhalakൾ anveshikkayu cheitucontirikukyu.
ori: vish bithtiya sangkat per tharu, aadhikarik kshetrati adhik tatha veshi bhal tatha sangrah karuni eban lukkait asurakshittagushikar sandhan karuni .
pan: vishva arthic sankat aun ton bood, manasbadar khetra uddh ton uddh jankari ieathi kar riha hai ate chhupia hora kamias nuun saamane lyaun di koshish kar riha hai I
tam: ulalaviya nidhi nerukkadi ettpattatilrundhu, arasut turai melum adhikaman, dharaman takhavallch selleritu elitel pulapadat balavinangalait detiverukintu.
tel: prapanch aarthik sankshobha erpadinappati nudi, prabhutva rangam marint, merugan samachar sekarinchi adrushya balahinatal anveshistundi.
urd: alami malyati bahran ke baad se, daftari shobaa zyaada or behatar malomat jamaa kar raha hai or poshida kamazoriyon kii talash kar raha hai.
eng: Since the global financial crisis, the official sector is collecting more and better information and searching for hidden vulnerabilities.

ben: kono virus banshanusmagr ekabar kono bahak comme caryakar hay gele seti dooshit proteiner sanshleshan parichalnakari vartabah aar.in.e (em.aar.in.e) anu upann kare.
guj: ekavar vishanuni utpatti yajman koshma thai, atle te sandeshvahak ar.en.e. (em ar.en.e.) parmaanuo sarje che je viral proteinsna sanshleshnane disha suchve che.
hin: jab ek vishaanu sanjine mejabaan koshika main kaam karne lagata he to vah sandeshvahak aar.en.e. (em.aar.en.e.) anu utpann karata he jo vishaanu protein ke sanshleshan kaa nirdesh detaa he.
kan: omme vairanuvin vanshawahigal guchhvu aatitheya jivakoshdolge sakriyavaitendare, nantar adu vairanuvin protinugal sanshleshaneyannu nirdeshisuv aar.en.e. doot anugainnu (emar.en.e.) utpadisuttade.
mal: oru atitheyakoshttil oru viral jinon pravartanakshammakumpol at viral proteinute udgrathtte niyantriunn sandesvahak ar.en.e. (e. ar.en.e.) tanmatrakae srushtiunnu.
ori: thare gotie pariposhak kokere eka bhootaanu jinom karyankaari hevaku samarth hoigaale, ta'pare eha barttabeh aar.en.e. (em.aar.en.e.) anugudiku srushti karithaye yeungudikaki bhootaanu protin sanshleshanku parichalit karithaye .
pan: ik war jadon ik virus jinom ik mezbaan sel vich chaaluu hoo janda hai, taan phir ih macenger aar in e (mRNA) anu paidaa karada hai jo viral protein de sanshlation nuun nirdeshit karada hai|
tam: ore ompuiri celil viral jinom seyalpant dodangwital, pingu atu doodhu ahrene (emarene) moolakkooduess uhatttisaitu are viral puradangal uruvakkumaru eukindena.
tel: atitheya kanaulo virus janyu pani cheyada mughalupettak, adi viral protein srustini nirdeshinche messenger arene (anarane) anuulan utpatti chestundi.
urd: ek bar jab kisi mezbaan khaliye main koi virus jenom fial hojataahe to is ke baad ye massenjar aar en aye (em aar en aye) salam paida kurta hai jo wiral protein kii tarkeeb kii hidaayat karte hain.
eng: Once a virus genome becomes operational in a host cell, it then generates messenger RNA (mRNA) molecules that direct the synthesis of viral proteins.

ben: han. bhartiya sanvidhaner jan pratinidhitva ine, 1951 anuyayi, doshi savyast haoya sab bandira bhot dewar ayogya.
guj: haaa, bhartiya bandharanna lok pratinidhitva adhinium, 1951 pramane bharata gunegar tharela tamam lokoney matdan mate ayogya tharavavama aavya che.
hin: haan, bharat main, bhartiya samvidhan ke lok pratinidhitiv adhinium, 1951 ke anusaar, sabhi sazaayaftaa kaidiyon ko ayogy mana jaataa he.
kan: haudu. bharatadalli, bhartiya samvidhandalliro 1951r jan pratinidhitvad kaydeya prakaar, aparaadhigalunt sabitagiro ella khidigalu matdanakke anarharagirthare.
mal: u. indian bharanaghathanyute 1951 le janpratinidhyaniyama anusrich, shiksh vidhicpat ella tatvukaru indiail vottu cheiyan ayogyarayirik.
ori: han. bharatre, bharatiya sambidhanar lok pratinidhi adhinium-1951 anusaare, samast doshi sabost bandi bhot devapin ayogya atanthi.
pan: haa. bharat vich, bharati sanvidhan de lok pratinidhta act, 1951 de anusaar, saare doshi qaidis nuun vote paun ton ayog kar ditha janda hai.
tam: amam, indiaill, india arsiyalamaipin 1951 makas pratinidhitvach sattatinpati, kuriavaligalana chiraikathikaluku vackelikkum takuti ille.
tel: aveunu, bharatvaeshalo, bharat rajanganloni 1951 prajapratinidhya chatta prakara, shiksh padin khaidilandaru otu veyadaniki anarhulu.
urd: haan, hindustan main, hindustani aaen ke awami numandagi act 1951 ke mutabik sazaa paane waale saare qaidi vote daalane se maharoom kar diye gaye hain.
eng: Yes. In India, according to the Representation of the People Act, 1951 of the Indian Constitution, all convicted prisoners are disqualified from voting.

ben: bartaman bahu bashwar yav fatma begum pracharer alo thek dure jivan katachen, tai ganamadhyam kakhano kono saakshakar na dewa bhartiya chalachchitrer ei pratham mahila yakhan 3ra m, 2013-te amar sang katha balte raji hollen, aami tar ekakaler chittakarshak kintu bartaman kshayishnu basabhavan dhanraj mahal, yekhane trini tar may jabeidar sang thaken, sekhane takshana paunche yai.
guj: have photma begum ghanan varshothi arq litsthi dur jivi rahya che, tethi jayare bhartiya cinemani aa pratham mahila, jemane kyarey prasar madhyamone mulaaqat aapi nathi, 3 me 2013na roj maari sathe vata karva sammath thayan, tyaare men tarat ja ekavarna prabhavashali parantu halma bhaangi rahela nivasasthan dhanraj mahal taraf maaro rasto karyo ke jyaan teo temana putree jhubaida sathe rahe che.
hin: in dinon phatma begum kaaphi saalon sein apni zindagi arq lite se dur ji rahi hai, isliye jab bhartiya cinema kii yah pratham mahila, jisane kabhi media saakshaatkaar nahin diya he, 3 may 2013 ko mujhase baat-chit karne ke liye raji huin to main fouran dhanraj mahal main unke kisi samay bhavy kintu ab dhahte hue nivas kii ore chal padaa, jahaan ve apni beti zubaida ke saath rahati hai.
kan: fatma begham cinemalokad bedaginind durvulidu baduku sagisutta ig halvu varshagale kaledive, hagagi, bhartiya chitrarangad i modal mahile, endigu madhyamgalige sandarshan nidirdake, 2013r me 3randu nannondige matnadlu oppicondag, naanu kudley aake tamm magalu jubeda jotege vasisuttiruv dhanaraj mahalinallin ondomme bhavyawagidd adare ig shithilavastheyalliruva avar manege hode.
mal: ippoൾ ethrayo waർshanslai aaർk lightukaliൽ ninnkann oru jivita nayikkayu oru maddhyam abhimukhvu nalkatirikkayu cheit chhatma biga end indian sinimaile prathamavanit, 2013 may munnam tiyati ennote sansariam enne sammathicpoൾ, makal subidayotoppa avar tamasikkunn dhaൻraj mahalille, orical aakarshakavu ippol idivanuvirunnatumay viddi khan krityasamayat chennu.
ori: fathima begam aajiku kichhi barsh heb aark lit tharu durre rahi jeevan yapan kariasiyanthi; tenu, yetevela bharatiya chakchchitrar ehi pratham mahila, yieki kadapi kaunsi ganamadhimaku saakshaatakar deinahanthi, mo sahit 2013 masiha me' 3 tarikh din katha hevaku raji helle, mun aviumbe 'dhanraj mahel' sthit tangkar ekada-prashansaniya, matra varttaman bhagnapran avasthare rahithiva vasasthan abhimukhe yatra kali, yeunthare se nij jhia juvaida sahit baas karunnthi .
pan: faatma begum ne apna jeewan hun kai saalas ton camere di nazar ton daur bitaaiya hai ish lai jadon bharati cinema di frst ledi jise ne awj tak koi jan sanchar madhium te interviu nahi diti, onha ne meraa naal 3 May 2013 nuun mulaaqat karan lai haami bhari taan mai turat hi onha di dhannraj mahal vich rihaaish bal vadhia jithe oh apni dhi zubiada naal resinde han jo ki kise zamane vich ik alishan ghar see per hun chur- chur hoo riha hai I
tam: batma begum bhallandugalak tireulagak goverchic kaqtilrundhu vilakiye vayendhu varukihar, eneway iduvarai udagatil fattie alitrath indiat tirappattain ind munnodi nayaki 3 mee 2013 andu yennuton pech obbukkond podhu, udane naan danraj mahal bagudiil avar tanatu magas jubadaudan vasikkum ant munnal-viyaputia anal innal chithilamatindhu varukits vitingu virainden.
tel: fatma begum ippatii chala elluga arche litku duranga jivita gaduputunnar, annadu media intervyu ivvni i bhartiya cinemaku chendin modati mahil 2013 me 3na nato matladtanii angikarinchashanto, nenu ventne dhanraj mahalloni okappadu okattukunn, kaani ippo shithilamautunn ambe inti vellan, akkd avid tan kuturu jubedato kalisi nivasistondi.
urd: fatima begum kai barson se arche litis se daur zindagi guzaar rahi hain, lahza jab hindustani cinema kii ye khatun ol, jinhon ne kabhi media intervayo naheen diya, 3 mai 2013 ko mujh se baat karne par razi huin, to main ne foran dhanraj mahal main in kii ek vakt main mutasar kin lekin in dinon bosida rihaaish gah kii raah lee , jahaan wo apni beti zbida ke saath rahati hain.
eng: Fatma Begum has lived a life away from the arc lights for several years now, so when this first lady of Indian cinema, who's never given a media interview, agreed to speak to me on 3 May 2013, I promptly made my way to her once-impressive but now crumbling residence in Dhanraj Mahal, where she lives with her daughter Zubeida.

ben: ramka ei rushir sang pathan evan lakshmanakeo pathan.

mal: yuddhcutkrityak uttar nalkiyatinu gunalochanaiൽ kutucheർnnatinu addeha munp kutavimuktanackapettirunnu.
ori: se poorvaru yuddh aparaadh nimanthe aadesh deithiva tatha missit shatyanthrar abhiyogaru nirddoshre mukt hoithile .

tam: forkuingaluku uttaravidudal, gootuch sati aakhiya kurlchattugalilrundhu munbu avar viduixpatar.

eng: He was previously acquitted of ordering war crimes and of joint conspiracy.

ben: itimadhyei amra dekhesi ye, dharitri mata kivave kono ekajan rakshaker niyukti cheyesillen evan seimato jarathushtra keman kare niyukt han.
guj: aapne agau joi lidhu che ke kevi rite pruthvi mata ek rakshakani niyunkti ichchhati hati ane kevi rite jarthushtra aavi niyunkti thai.
hin: hamane yah pehle hi dekha he ki kaise prithvi mata ek rakshak ko niyukt karnaa chaahati thi or kis prakaar se zarathushtra ko is rup main niyukt kiya gaya.
kan: bhoomitaiyu hege rakshakanobbanu irabekendu bayasiddalu mattu hege adrante jaratushtranannu kaluhislayitu embudannu naavu igaagale nodiddeve.
mal: bhoomata oru sanrakshakane niyamikaൻ agrahichtinecurichu angne jaratushtra niyamicppettatinecurichu nammൾ neratetane kantu.
ori: aame janisarichhe ye dharitri mata kipari jane rakshakarta niyukt hevaku chaahinthile eban kipari jarathushtra sethipin niyukt hoithile .
pan: aseen pihals hi dekh chuke haa ki dharati matra nuun aapne lai ik rakhwala niukat karna see ate kidas zarthstra chunia gya see I
tam: appati woru bhadukappasher niyamickeppat wants endu bhuma devi virumbinar anpathes, appati abhpadviil jartustra niyamixpatar anpathes nam erganave parthom.
tel: nail talli ock rakshak niyamimpbadalani ela korukundo, anduvall jartustr ela niamituyado mana ippatike chushan.
urd: hum ne pahele hi dekha hai ki kis tarah madr jameen chaah rahi thi ki ek muhafiz muqrer kiya jaaye or kis tarah zarathushit ko yun muqrer kiya gaya.
eng: We have already seen how Mother Earth wanted a protector to be appointed and how Zarathustra was so appointed.

ben: semeniar desh biswa kridda tar maryaada, adhikar evan sthan raksharth tanke gheere samavesh karesil.
guj: cemenyana deshe tena gauravane surakshit raakhva, tena adhikaro ane vishv ramatagmat kshetre tena sthan mate sarghas kadhyu hatu.
hin: semenya ke desh ne uski maryaada, uske adhikaar or vishwa khelon main uske sthaan kii raksha karne main uskaa saath diya.
kan: semenyal rashtravu aakeya gaurav, aakeya hakkugalu mattu vishvad kridakshetradalli aakeya sthanvannu rakshisuvudakkoskar aakeya neravige nintitu.
mal: semenyayute antassu avkashanslu, lokakayikarangattull avarute sthanvu sanrakshian avarute rajyam oppam aninirannu.
ori: semenank maryada, tank adhikar eban vish kreedhare tank pad surakshit rakhiva pin tank desh tank samarthanare chhida hoigala.
pan: sermania di kaum ne us de sanmaan, us de adhikars ate vishva kheds vich usdi state di raakhi lai usde duale lambandi keeti|
tam: semanyavin desaddhawar avaraichuji anitrandu avritu khannium, urimis manllum vilyattulak andast kakk munandaner.
tel: semenya yokk desha prapanch kridallo ambe gaurva, ambe hakkulu mariyu ambe sthananni kapadtanii ambe chuttu kudindi.
urd: cemenia kii kaum ne alami khelon main is ke vakaar, is ke haquk, or is ke mukaam kii hifaazat ke liye is kaa saath diya.
eng: Semenya's nation rallied around her to safeguard her dignity, her rights, and her position in world sports.

ben: maida-chada khabar khunjchen eman grahakder janya amra chal, bhutta, shaner bij aar bajra vikalp rakhee.
guj: je grahako gluten mukt bhojan shodhi rahya che, temane ame chokha, makai, alsi, ane juvarna vikalpo aapie chhie.
hin: jo customer gluton-free diet chaahate hai, ham unhen chaaval, corn, alsi or bajra vagairah de sakate hai.
kan: gluten illad aaharvann kelo grahakarige naavu akki, jol, agase bij mattu siridhanyad paryay aaykeglenn nidtivi.
mal: glutanillat bhakshant avashyapadunnavർk ari, corn, cheruchanvit, thin enniv kondulla vibhavaa tes nalkunnat.
ori: gluten-mukt khadya chahunthiva atithimanank pin aam paakhre bhat, maka, angasi manyji eban bajra jatiya khadya sabu ajji.
pan: jihde gaharak galutan mukat khana chaunde han, onha lai aseen chaul, maki,alsi ate bajra de vikalp prstut karade haa
tam: glutton illat unu wantiavarluku arice, karn, placks sead, chirudaniya unvuess valangukirom.
tel: glutain leni ahara kavalkune kastmarlaki memu vari, mokkajonn, avish ginjal, alage chiru dhanyal pratyamnayas istamu.
urd: in gahakon ke liye jo glautan-free khaane kii talash kar rahe hain, hum chaval, makai, alsi ke beej or baajra ke mutbadal pesh karte hain.
eng: For customers looking for a gluten-free diet, we offer rice, corn, flax seed, and millet alternatives.

ben: baghti jant gavadi pashu tule nie yawar fale gana pratirodh shuru hawa keralar pradhan banyapran tattwavadhayak jantutike shikarer aadesh devan.
guj: e vagh pashudhanne lai jato hovaane karne samuhik virodh fati nikaltan keralana vanyajivan vordanna vadaae tena shikarno hukm karyo hato.
hin: kerala ke mukhya vanya jeev warden ne baagh kaa shikaar karne kaa aadesh diya jab baagh dwaara maweshiyon ko uthaa le jane par bade paimaane par virodh pradarshan hua.
kan: aa huliyu januvarugainnu eledoyyuttiddudarind samuhik pratibhatnegalu bhugileddag, keralad mukhya vanyajivi melvicharnadhikariyu aa praniannu beteyadalu aadeshisidru.
mal: katu kannukalie pitichukondupoirunnatukara janakiyapratishedhaൾ potipurapettatinettutർnn keralatiൻre chiph vaiൽd lif waർdൻ aa mrigattinuvendiull veteyckai uttarvittu.
ori: keralar mukhya bharaprapth banpprani tattbadharak jan andoson tejiva pare pashutir shikar pin aadesh deithile yehetu baghati pashusampadasabu neiyauthila .
pan: kerala de mouth jungle jeev warden ne bade virodh pradarshan shuruu on ton bood jaanwar di bhaal karan da adesh ditha kiunki shera pashu lija riha see|
tam: indep puli tangas kalndilait dookientu vidukintu endu gutai potumakalin boratas veditt pingu ant vilanga wattiadip ftikumaru kerala talams vanab bhadukavalar uttaravitar.
tel: pashuus puli attukellipotu undadanto pedd attun nirsanal welluvettin nepathyalo kerala pradhan vanyaprani sanrakshak aa jantuunu vetadmani adeshincharu.
urd: bade paimaane par mazahre shurua hogaye the kyonki sher moyashyon ko uthaa kar lay jaa raha tha jis ke baad kerala ke chef wild life warden ne is jaanvar ko talash karne kaa hukum diya.
eng: The Chief Wildlife Warden of Kerala ordered the hunt for the animal after mass protests erupted as the tiger had been carrying livestock.

ben: chalachchitrer shailite ei pravedti karnei pariveshak o prayojakara chalachchitrak du'ti pradhan bhag bibhak karen: ucchashreni janya chalachchitra evan sadharner janya chalachchitra.
guj: film shailima aa vibhaago atla mate che ke vitarko ane nirmatao be mukhya bhagama filmo nihalvanu chaalu raakhe che: khas vargni filmo ane samuh vargni filmo.
hin: filmon kii shaileyon main antar hi vah kaaran he ki vitarak or nirmaataa filmon kaa do shreniyon kaa vibhaajan karte hai – unche darje ke logon ke liye filmein or saadhaaran janata ke liye filmein.
kan: chalanchitra shailigamallin i vingedoneindagiye vitarkaru mattu nirmapakaru chalanchitragalannu eradu mukhya bagegalige seridvugalagi pariganisuvudannu munduvaresiddare: vidyavant vargadavarigagin chalanchitragalu mattu shrisamanya janarigagin chalanchitragalu.
mal: chalachchitrashililile i tarantirivukara vitarnakkaru nirmmatakkalu chitrase rand vibhagasliൽppettavayai kanunnat tutrunnu: uyർnn shreniiൽppettavർkkulla chitraslu janakuttangൾkkulla chitraslu.
ori: chakchchitra stylegudik madhyare thiva ehi vibhajan yogun vitaraka eban nirmatamane chakchchitragudiku duiti mukhya prakaarar boli bichaar kariasuganthi: sambhrantmanank pin uddist chakchchitra eban sadharan lokank pin uddist chakchchitra .
pan: niramata te vikreta films nuun doo shaylia vich vandade han : khaas locals lai films ate aam locals de lai I
tam: tirappadab panikalil ettptt indep brivu karanmaghat than, melkettu malukan patangas enllum vegujanangalukan patangas enllum tirappaangans iru mukiya vakaikalil onjhak vineokastarganum dayaripacrgallum parkinowner.
tel: i cinema shailul vibhajan karnangane pampinidarulu mariyu nirmats cinemala rend vargaluga chustu unnar: unnat shreni vaari kos cinemal mariyu jansamanyul kos cinemal.
urd: filmi andazon main ye taqasim hi vajah hai ki distry buter or prodeusar filmon ko do ahim zamaron main dekhte rahate hain: tabaqat ke liye filmein or avaam ke liye filmein.
eng: This division in film styles is why distributors and producers continue to see films as being of two main categories: films for the classes and films for the masses.

ben: 1972 thek 1975-era madhye 25 paisa, 50 paisa o 1 takaar mudra nickeler parivarte tama-nickel jaga kare neya; 1982-te tama-nickeler tiri dui takaar mudra pratham chalu has.
guj: 1972thi 1975ni vachche, 25 paisa, 50 paisa ane ek rupiana sikkaoma nikalnu sthan kupro-nikle lidhu ane kupro-nikalana be rupiana sikka chalanma avyan.
hin: 1972 or 1975 ke bich 25 paise, 50 paise or 1 rupee ke sikkon main gilat kii jagah tamranical ne le lee; 1982 main tamranical ke do rupee ke sikke saamne laae gaye.
kan: 1972 mattu 1975r naduve, 25 paise, 50 paise hagu 1 roopayiya nanyagamalli nical badalige tamra-nical balkege banditu; 1982ralli tamra-nicallin eradu roopayiya nanyagainnu horadislayitu.
mal: 1972nu 1975nu idil 25pis, 50pis, 1rup nickel nanayas kupro nikkalaki matukayu 1982l rantu rupeeue kupro nickel nanayas avataripikkayu cheitu.
ori: 1972 eban 1975 masiha madhyare, cupro-nikel 25 paisikia, 50 paisikia, eban 1 lankia mudraguthikare nikelr sthan neithila; 1982 masihare, cupro-nikelr dui lankia mudra prachalan karayaithila .
pan: 1972 ate 1975 de wichkaar, kaparo-nikal ne 25 paisa 50 paisa ate 1 rupee vich nikal di tha li lai; 1982 vich, kaparo-nikal de doo rupee de sike pesh kite gaye san |
tam: 1972 muthal 1975 varai, 25 faicha, 50 faicha manllum 1 rupee nanayankalil gupro-nickeluku patilak nikel payanbaduttappattatu, 1982il gupro-nikel 2 rupee nanayas arimugham seyyabpattanu.
tel: 1972 nudi 1975 madhya, 25 paisal, 50 paisal, 1 rupai nanello nickelku badulu tamranickel wadbadedi;1982lo rend rupees tamranickel nanes praveshpettar.
urd: 1972 se 1975 ke darmiyaan kaparo nakul ne 25 paise, 50 paise or ek rupee ke sake kii jagah lay lee; 1982 main kaparo nakul ke do rupee ke sake mataarf kiraye gaye.
eng: Between 1972 and 1975, cupro-nickel replaced nickel in the 25 paise, 50 paise and the 1 rupee coins; in 1982, cupro-nickel two rupee coins were introduced.

ben: kailas paharer kache ansi himavah thek era upatti evan eke yarlu sanpoo bala hay thake.
guj: te kailash parvat paaseni angsi himandimathi nikale che ane tene yarlung tsangpo pan kahe che.
hin: yah kailash parvat ke paas angsi himand se shuru hoti he or ise yaralung tsangpo bhi kaha jaataa he.
kan: adu kailas parvatd baliiruv angsi himarashialli huttatte, matte adnn yarlang tsangpo antlu kareetare.
mal: kailashparvatatin sameepamulla angsi himaniilninna atutbhavikkunnat, atin yarlang sampo end perumund.
ori: eha kailash parbat nikat aansi tushar rotharu bahrinii, o ehaku yaralung sangpo madhya kuhayaaye.
pan: ih kailash parbat de nede angasi galecier ton uthappan hunda hai ate ishnoo yaralung sangpo ve kiha janda hai|
tam: irukku miss, atu dondukits idam kailash malauchikqup bakkatil ull angsi baniparai, athangu 'yarjung sangbo' appatinnu innuru peyarum irukkintu.

urd: ye kailash pahaad ke qareeb angisi glacir se nikalata hai or use yarlong tasangpu bhi kaha jataa hai.
eng: It originates from Angsi Glacier near Mount Kailash, and it is also called Yarlung Tsangpo.

mal: sanghaws, avarute sharirik vikas, rupabhangi, vyaktitva ennivyute atisthanttil vilyiruttapettu.

ben: dvitiya chakrer lakshya cyaium udhdhaar kara also aichaeleldblu thek strontium-aktinide-lanthanide samyukta pruthkikarnti iii chakre sampadit has.
guj: sijium punampraptinu lakshya bija chakrama che, jayare strontium-aktinide-lenthenaidu sanyukt vibhajan ech.el.el.dabalyu. mathi trija chakrama prapth thai che.
hin: haalanki sizium kii punahprapti ech.el.el.dablyoo ke dwitiya chakra main kii jaati he, stronsium -actenide-lanthanide kaa sanyukt pruthakkaran tritiy chakra main punahprapt kiya jaataa he.
kan: sisiamannu pratyekisi padeyuudu eradne suttin uddeshvadre, moorne suttinalli ech.el.el.dublu.ind stronium-actinide-lanthanidgal sanyukt viyojaneyannu sadhislaguttade.
mal: randa parivrittiil sitaium veendetup lakshyam vaikkumpol ech .el.el.dublyu.vinte munnam parivrittiil stronshyam-actinide-lantanide sanyukta vertiriva sadhyamakunnat.
ori: yadio dtiya chakrare sijiam punarprapti hebar lakshya karayaithaye, ech.el.el.dablsou. ru strontiam-aktinid-lanthanaidra sanyukt prutkeekaran tritiya chakrare hasal hoithaye.
pan: jadon ki duje chakra vich sizium recovery da udesh hai, strontium-actinide-lanthanid sanyukat vibhaajan aich ail ail dabliu ton tije chakra vich praapat kita janda hai|
tam: seasium meetsi erandam susarqiil nickem ena uttesixpadukintu, adevele strancium-actinitu-landanitu oruserup prittal heceleltapilyu-vai aduttu moonssam susarqiil nataberukintu.
tel: rendav aavrittilo sisiam tirigi pondada laksya kaaga, hacheleldeblyu nudi strontium-actinide-lanthnide samyukt vibhajan mudav aavrittilo sadhinchabadutundi.
urd: jahaan sejiyam kii baazyabi kaa hadaf dusare daur main banaaya jataa hai, vaheen stroncium-actenide-linthanid mushtarki alihadagi each el el dablyoo se teesare daur main haasil kii jaati hai.
eng: While cesium recovery is aimed in the second cycle, Strontium-Actinide-Lanthanide combined separation is achieved in the third cycle from HLLW.
