ben: demboski tar, "teking dya state tu dya supreme court: pablik interest litigeshan end dya pablik sphere in metroplitan india," baite era bapar likhesilen, ya mulath 2001 sale acsfford university press dwara prakashith hayesil.
guj: demboskie tena vishe potana pustak ‘‘teking dha state tu dha supreme courth public interest littgeshan and dha public sphiar en metropoliton india’’maa lakhyu, je mule 2001maa oxfard university press dwara prakashith karvama aavyu hatu.
hin: dembovski ne apni likhi or pehali baar 2001 main oxford uniwarsity press dwaara jari kii gai pustak "teking da state tu da supreme court: public interest litigeshan and da public sphier in metropolitan india", main is vishay ke bare main likhaa.
kan: dembowski, multah oxford yuniorcity presnind 2001ralli prakatitvad “teking da state to da suprim cort: public intrest litigeshan and da public spheere in metropolitan indiya” emb tamm pustakdalli idar bagge barediddare.
mal: 2001ൽ adyamai osphoർd university pras prasidhikarichch "teiking da state tu da suprin koർtt : public iൻaurest littigeshൻ aaൻd di public sphiaർ iൻ metropolitaൻ india" end tൻre pustaktiൽ dembowski itinecurich anuti.
ori: e vishakere demvauski tank pustak, "teking da' stet tu da' supreme court: public intresht littgason and da' public sphear in metropolitan india"re lekhithile, yahaki prathame akshafford univercity press dra 2001re prakashit hoithila.
pan: dabovasaki ne ish baare apni kitaab, "teking da state tu da supreme court: public intrust litegeshan and da public safier in metropolitan india" vich likhia see, jo asal vich 2001 vich oxford university press duara prakashit kita gai see|
tam: "arasai ucch neetimanttingu illuppatu: indiab perungaranglil potunal vaookkum potu veleum" enjh tanatu buddhakatil tempovsky itsp basari esudinar, atu muthal muriyag 2001il axpord university pras niruvanattal velitepattatu.
tel: dembowski dini gurinchi modataga 2001lo aksbird univarsity pres vaaru prachurinchabadd tan pustakan "teaking di state t di supreme court: public intrest litigesion and di public spior in metropaliton india" lo rasar.
urd: dembosky ne is ke baare main apni kitaab "teking di estate to supreme court: public interest lutigeshan and di public safir in metro polatin india" main taharir kiya, jise asal main oxford university press ne 2001 main shaya kiya tha.
eng: Dembowski wrote about it in his book, "Taking the State to the Supreme Court: Public Interest Litigation and the Public Sphere in Metropolitan India," which was originally published by Oxford University Press in 2001.

ben: phenek balen, "pabitra sikh granth, guru granth sahib evan sahayogi pradhan dasam granth bhartiya puranic kahini chhadie ach evan bartamaner sikh evan atite tader purvapurushader pabitra pratiki vishwer madhyo sukshma parthakya o marm yoga kare.
guj: fenech kahe che, ‘bhartiya puraano shikhna pavitra niyam, guru granth sahib ane gaun niyam, dasam granthama praveshine umere che ke najuk sukshmata ane paxarth aajna shikhona pavitra pratikatmak brahmandna khyaal temana purvajo sathe jode che.
hin: fene kehete hai, "bhartiya puranic kathaon kaa ullekh sikhon ke pavitra dharmagranth, guru granth sahib or dwitiya dharmagranth, dasham granth main bhi kiya gaya he jo vartmaan sikhon evam unke purvajon ke dharmik sankethik jagat main najuk sookshmata or mulya jodta he.
kan: feneawn helikeyante, "bhartiya purana sahityavu angikrut sikhkh pavitra granthavad guru granth sahib mattu eradne angikrut pavitra granthavad dasham granthadalli hasuhokkagide mattu indin sikhkhar hagu avar hindin poorvajr pavitra sankethik vishwakke navirad sookshmate mattu sattvavannu serisuttade."
mal: "sikhumatattile vishuddh pramanmay guru granth sahibl randa pramanmay dasam granth indiaൻ puranangൾ kininjirangukayu innte sikhukarutayu avarute kachinjupoe pinmurakkarutayu vishuddhmay pratikatmakalokatin lolmay aർtthabhedalu kampu naൽkukyu cheiyunnu"wenne fenek prastavikkunnu.
ori: phenek kuhanthi, "bharatiya puranasshastra shikh pavitra granth guru granth sahib, eban annga eka madhramik sidant, dasham granth, madhyare pravesh karichhi, eban aajir shikh tatha semanankar poorvajamanankar pavitra prateekatmak jagatre sukshma bhava tatha tatt yogakariani."
pan: phenek diiva karade han, "bharati mithihas sikh pavitara sidhant, guru granth sahib ate duje madham de sidhant, dasam granth vich pravesh karada hai ate awj de sikhs ate onha de purana pooravjan de pavitara prateek srishti vich naazuk parmanu ate padarth jodda hai."
tam: indiab puranas chikharkalin punitak cuttans nulana guru kirant sahibill erandamniloup punitak cuttans nulana tacham kiranttil illiiodi insaiy chikhars manllum avarkandu moodatyarkalin samayak kuriittup parapuku ilkia nayamum porllum cherkhitu endu penak goorukihar.
tel: "sikkhul pavitra niyamal sangraha ayin guru granth saheb mariyu rendosthai niyamal sangraha ayin das granthala bhartiya purangadha vyapinchi, nati sikkhul mariyu vaari poorvikul yokk pavitra pratikatmak vishwaniki sunnithmin swalpabhedanni mariyu vishayanni jodistai," ani feneck teliajestar.
urd: phink bayaan karte hain, "hindustani asater devamaala sukh math ke muqaddas usool kanoon, guru granth sahab or sanavi usool kanoon, dasam granth main sarayat krati hai, or aaj ke sukhon or in ke gujare hue buzurgon ke muqaddas elaamati jahaan main naajuk fark or mawad kaa azafa krati hai.
eng: Fenech states, "Indic mythology permeates the Sikh sacred canon, the Guru Granth Sahib and the secondary canon, the Dasam Granth and adds delicate nuance and substance to the sacred symbolic universe of the Sikhs of today and of their past ancestors."

ben: saman mulyawan chhil jahazer rater (naviker nirdesh-pustak), yar madhye china, bharat evan japaner banisyapath sampark gurutvapurna tathy thakat.
guj: atlu ja mulyavan hatu jahajanu rater (khalasini nodhapothi), jema chin, bharat ane japanna vepari margo angeni mahatvani mahiti hati.
hin: utani hi bahumoolya thi jahaaj kii vivaran pustika (navik kii hastpustika), jisamen china, bharat, or japan ke vyapaar margon kii mahatvapurn jaankaree di gai thi.
kan: china, bharat, mattu japan vyapaar margagal kuritagee mahattvad mahithiannu hondidd i hadogin pustakavu (navikan kaipidi) ashte belebaluvanthaddagittu.
mal: chin, india, japan enni vanijyapatacurichull nirnnayakavivars atangunn chhatteru (navikarute cipustak) tulyanilil vilpitichchatayirunnu.
ori: saman bhavare muluban thila jahajatir 'ratar' (navikank sahayak pusthika), yeunthire china, bharat, eban japanner banijik gatipathagudik upare ati guruthpurna suchanaman rahithila .
pan: jahaaz da rater (mariner di handbook) barabar kimati see, jise vich chin, bharat ate japan de vpark ruts baare mahatavpurna jankari see|
tam: kappalin valiqattickum (malumis kaetu) itskuch samaman matipu irundatu, atil china, india manllum japan charnt vanip margangs basari adhdhiavasiyat takhavals atangirundal.
tel: od yokk ratter (navikuriki suchanal gal chinn pustakm) ante viluvindiga undedi, idi china, bharat, mariyu japan vanijya margal gurinchi mukhyamin samachar kaligi undedi.
urd: jahaaz kii rater (mariner kii handbak ) bhi itani hi keemtee thi, jis main chin, bhaarat, or japan ke tizaarati raasto ke baare main ahim malomat maujuud thim.
eng: Equally valuable was the ship's rutter (mariner's handbook), which contained vital information on the China, India, and Japan trade routes.

ben: khanan evan prakritik gas nishkashan tatha banking vibhag binioga vruddhi pa.
guj: khanan ane kudarti vayu nishkarshanma rokan vadhyu, je rite banking kshetra rokan vadhyu.
hin: khanan tathaa prakritik gas nishkarshan main nivesh main vruddhi hui, saath hi banking kshetra ke nivesh main bhi.
kan: ganigarike mattu naisargik anil horethegeyuikeyalli bandwal hoodike hechayitu, hageye banking valayadalliu hoodicayalli airikeyaitu.
mal: khananttilayu prakrutivatak khananttilayu nikshepavu banking mekhalile nikshepavu waർddhitchu.
ori: banking udogra nivesh badhithiva pari, khani khanan eban prakritik gas uttokanare nivesh badhithila .
pan: khan di khadai ate kudrati gas di ukhed de nivesh vich wadha hoia, baink de khetra vich ve nivesh vadhia I
tam: surangatosil manllum iauka vayu prittedutalil mudalidus adhikarittaj, vangit turail mudalidus adhikarittaj.
tel: ganul tavvaka mariyu sahaj vayu nu valikitiyatalo pettubadi perigindi, alage banking ranganlo kuda.
urd: kaan kani or kudrati gas nikaalane main saramy kari main azafa hawa, isi tarah bankaree ke shobe main bhi saramy kari badi.
eng: Investment in mining and natural gas extraction increased, as did investment in the banking sector.

ben: yugoslavian sadharan bajarer upar pashchathya nishedhajna thek shuru kare uttar macedonier upar greek nishedhajna percent, deshti poorvavarti naam, macedonier prajatantra jure.
guj: yugoslavani sahiyari bazar parani paschimni bandhithi mandi uttar messedonia parani greek bandhino anth lavine deshna purav nam ripublic of messedonia sudhi te vistari hati.
hin: yah eugaslavia ke aam bazaar par pashchimi deshon dwaara lagaae gaye pratibandh se shuru ho kar uttari macedonia ke pichley naam, macedonia ganraajya ke sambandh main yunaan dwaara lagaae gaye pratibandh ke saath samaapt hota he.
kan: yugoslaviad samanya marukatteya mele pashchatya vanijy nirbandhadind modalgondu, uttar masidonia deshad modalin hesarad da republic aaf masidoniad mele greek vanijy nirbandh heruvudarondige coneyaitu.
mal: yugoslaviaൻ potuvipanikumelull pashchatyavilkkiൽninn tuteni rajyatiൻre muൻnamamay republic of macydoniaute peryൽ uttar macydoniaute melull greek vilqkiൽ avasanikunnavyanav.
ori: yugoslobhiya sadharan bazar upare pashchatya banija nishedhadesh tharu aarmbh kari, eban deshatir poorb nam, 'di rippeblic af masedonia'ku nei uttar masedonia upare thiva greek banija nishedhadesh sahit samapt kari .
pan: yugoslavian aam bazaar `te pattmi pabandi de shuruaat naal ate uttari makadunia te unani pabandi naal ant hunde hoe, desh de purana naame, ganatantra makadunia I
tam: yugoslaviya botuch sandai mitan menokulakin vanikat tatail dodangi, macdoniack kutiarasu enjh adan munnal payar dodarpak wat macdonia mitan grekk vanikat tadai varai.
tel: yugoslaviya sadharan vipanipai pashchatya nishedhalato modali, uttar masadoniapai greek nishedhal varaku, deshaniki poorvapu peru ayin republic aaf masadonia peru gurinchi.
urd: yugoslaviai mushtarki mandi par mugharabi bandish se shurua ho kar, or shumali muqdunya par unani bandish ke saath khatm hone tak, malik ke sabiqa naam par, jo jamhori muqdunya hai.
eng: Starting with the Western embargo on the Yugoslavian common market, and ending with the Greek embargo on North Macedonia, over the country's former name, the Republic of Macedonia.

ben: yoga shabdati yukt athva sandhi athva ek haoya arthsampann sanskrit dhatu yuj thek udbhuth.
guj: yoga shabd sanskrit mul yaj parathi uddhrut karvama aavyo che, jeno arth thai che jorvu, jagruth karvu athva ek karvu.
hin: yoga shabd sanskrit kii yuj dhaatu se niklaa he, jiskaa arth he jodna yaa jotna yaa sammilit karnaa.
kan: ʼyogaʼ emb padvu serisuvudu athwa jotegudisuvudu athwa ondagisuvudu emb arthvannu hondiruv sanskritd ʼyujʼ dhatuvinind vyutpannavagide.
mal: kuticherrkyook, inakcook, allengil orumipikcook ennarthamulla yuj end sanskritdhatuvil ninn vyulpadippichtan yogashabda.
ori: 'yog' shabdati mul sanskrit 'uj'ru aasichhi, yaahaar arth heudi yodiva ba bandhiva ba ekatara kariva |
pan: sanskrit bhaasha to lya gya shabad, "yoga" da mul shabad hai "yuj" jise da arth hunda hai jodna jaaa icathe karna I
tam: yoga enjh sol yuj enjh samskrit vorcollrundhu pinkkiritu, athangu inaittal, pinatukh kddudal alltu onoubadudal endu arttom.
tel: yoga ane pada yuj ane sanskrit mula nudi udbhavinchindi, dinrtha daggariki cherchada, kalapada, eka cheyada.
urd: lafz yoga sanskrit kii jad yoj se makhuz hai, jis kaa matalab hai milana yaa jodna yaa matahad karna.
eng: The word Yoga is derived from the Sanskrit root Yuj, meaning to join or to yoke or to unite.

ben: 15°-27° selsiaser sarvapeksha anukul wapamatra evan 75 shatansh aapkshik ardrata sah dinman 24°-27° selsioas evan ratre 15°-17° selsioas wapamatra prayojan.
guj: wapamanani aavashyakta divas daramiyaan 24-27 aansh centegrade ane ratrina kalako daramiyaan 15-17 aansh centegrade, 75 taka sambandhit bhej sathe mahattam 15-27 aansh centegrade hoya che.
hin: din ke samay kaa taapmaana 24-27 degree celsium rahanaa chahie evam raat kaa 15 -17 degree celsius rahanaa chahie, or 75 pratishat kii saapeksh ardrata ke saath adarsh taapmaana 15-27 degree celsius ke bich rahanaa chahie.
kan: hagalinalli 24°-27° se. mattu ratri veleyalli 15°-17° se. wapamanad avashyakatayiddu 75 pratishat sapeksh ardrateyondige 15°-27° se. prashastvad wapamanavagide.
mal: pakalsamayam 24°–27° sellshyasu ratrinerat 15°–17° sellshyasa aavashyamay tapanilayennirie, 75 shatmana aapekshik irppamulla 15°–27° selshyasa et anukulam.
ori: dinare wapamatra aavashyakata 24°–27° celsius thiva bele, raatire 15°–17° celsius rahithae, yeveki anukul wapamatra 75 pratishat aapekshic ardratha sahit 15° –27° celsius rahiva katha |
pan: din da wapamana 24°–27° celcius rahina chahida hai, ate raat da 15°–17° celcius rahina chahida hai, ate 75 pratisht di saapekh nami de naal sarvotam wapamana 15°–27° celcius de vich rahina chahida hai|
tam: veppanil bhagal nertil 24°–27°C alvill eravil 15°–17°C alvill, its ugandanilai 75 satvikit charpunili irappatatton 15°–27°C alvill irukk wants.
tel: avasaramin ushnograth pagti veklo 24°–27°si, ratri veklo 15°–17°si kaaga, vanchaniyaminadi 75 shata sapeksh ardratato 15°–27°si.
urd: din ke auqat main darja hararat kii zarurat 24°–27° centi grad or or raat ke auqat main 15° –17° centi grad hoti hai, jis main 75 faisad azafee nami ke saath mozon trin darja hararat 15°–27° centi grad hota hai.
eng: The temperature requirement is 24°–27°C during the daytime and 15°–17°C during the night hours, with the optimum being 15°–27°C with 75 percent relative humidity.

ben: amanki florida, arlando evan era ashepashe asankhya anyanya aakarshaner majheo mouse house khara hay dandie royas, era batigharti prati bashwar laksh laksh paryatakke ei anchaler prati aakrisht kare.
guj: floridana orlendsma ane aasapaas anek anaya aakarshano hova chhataan, mouse houseni vata nyaari che, aa deewadandine karne e vistar varshe laakho pravasione khenchi laave che.
hin: orlando, florida main or uske aasapaas kai anya aakarshanon ke baavjood, mouse house kaa aakarshan sabase alag he, ek prakaash-stambh kii tarah, jo prayek varsh lakhon paryatakon ko apni ore khinchataa he.
kan: flaridad olandodalli mattu ader suttamutt iruva itar halvaaru aakarshanegal naduveyu maus house adellavannu mirisi nintiddu, i pradeshskke prativarsh lakshagattle pravasigarnnu seleyuv sujigallagide.
mal: floridile oർlaaൻdoil chuttilumulla niravadhi mat oakർshandooൾkkir i pradeshtteak oro waർshavu dashalakshakanakin vinodasanjarie oakർshikkunn prakashagopuramai mas has uyർnnuniൽkkunnu.
ori: epariki floridar arlando madhyare eban aakhapakhre thiva anek anyanya akarshan madhyare 'mouse house' lavdhapratishth bhave dandaman; eha heudi sehi sanketik aaloka yahaki varshaku niqut niqut paryletkanku ukt anychalaku aakarshit kari anithaye .
pan: orlando, florida dis anek akarshana de bawajood ve, mouse house, onha wichon alag khara hunda hai, oh moti jo ki har saal karodaa sailania nuun akarsheit karada hai I
tam: floridail ull arlandovin sularuvattil erauman innapitt chicint subarulat dalangs ulfodhilu, maous house uyyaramak vindu andap bakudiku battu lachakkanakkana subaulap bhayanis irkum kalankarai vivkkak irukkintu.
tel: floridaloni orlandolo mariyu chuttupakkal anek itar akarshanal madhya unna kuda, mouse house lakshal koddi paryatkula sanvatsaraniki orsari i prantaniki aakarshinche dipastambha vale garvanga nilustundi.
urd: yahaan tak ki orlando, floreda main or is ke aas pas ke matadad digar praksish mukaamat ke darmiyaan, di mouse house fakhr se estada hai, chiraag jo saal bhar lakhon siyaahon ko is ilaka kii taraf ragab kurta hai.
eng: Even amid numerous other attractions in and around Orlando, Florida, the Mouse House stands tall, the beacon that draws millions of tourists a year to the area.

ben: natun applikeshan baa shilper kshetre prathmikbhave yakhan machine larning kaushal vyabhhar kara has takhan veshirabhag samari buniadi prakria prayog karaar mato yathest prashikshan tathy upalbdh thake na.
guj: jayare nava prayog ke udyogma yantra shikshan takanik arambhe upayogma levaya che, tyaare ghanivar paramparik prakriyao laagu karva mate talimani purti vigto upalbdh hoti nathi.
hin: haalanki yantra adhigam takneekein jab nae prayogon yaa udyogon main shuru main prayukt kii jaati hai, tab aksar vahaan paaramparik prakriyaaon main prayukt karne hetu prashikshan ke liye paryaapt jaankaar uplabdh nahin hoti he.
kan: yantra kalikeya tantragarhnnu hoss anuprayoggamalli athwa kaigarikegamalli aarambhdalli balsidag, anek vele sampradayik prakriegalannu kalpisalu sakashtu tarbetu dattanshvu labhyaviruudill.
mal: putia applikeshnulilo vyavasayathilo meshiൻ lening sarsketikavidyakൾ adyamai upyogicumpoൾ parampragatmay prakriyakൾ natappilakkaൻ matiyay training datra palpposhu labhyamairikkaill.
ori: yetevela mesin larining kaushangudik prathame nuthan anuprayog ba udogaguikare brebahrut hue, paramparik prakria prayog kariva nimanthe adhikansh samaure yathest prashikshan nimitta uddist tatha nathaaye .
pan: jadon navi aplikeshnas jaaa udayogan vich masini sikhalai takniks nuun shuruati for te vartia janda hai, taan parampragat prakirias nuun shuruu karan lai akasar kaafi sikhalai data uplabadh nahi hunda hai.
tam: iandrak karusul nudbangs arampattil putiya payanpadus alltu tokhilduraikalil payanbaduttapatum podhu, perumballum bharambariyach seyalmuraikalap prayogicab podhumana pairchit druvues irupadill.
tel: yantra abhyas sanketikatal modatlo kott aplikeshnlalo lek parishramallo wadinpp, sampradayik prakrial wadtanii tarchuga saripada shikshana samachar andubatulo unddu.
urd: jab ibtidai tuur par nai appli keshanz yaa sanaaton main mashine laraning kii tachneeque istemaal kii jaati hai, to ravayati amal ko lagu karne ke litakasar tarbiti adaad va shumar dastyab naheen hote hain.
eng: When machine learning techniques are initially used in new applications or industries, there is often not enough training data available to apply traditional processes.

eng: After we saw the skin allergies occurring in many villagers, we stopped using it.

ben: safar nathir madhye passport, visa, mudra shansapatra athva passport mudra anumodan, safar vima, ayakar vivruti, swasthy shansapatra ityadi antarbhukt.
guj: pravas dastavejoma passport, visa, chalan pramanpatra athva passportma chalannu samarthan, pravas vimo, aavakavera nivedano, aarogya pramanpatro vagereno samavesh thai che.
hin: yatra dastavezon main shaamil hai passport, visa, mudra praaanpatr yaa passport main mudra kaa anumodan, yatra beemaa, iskar kathan, swasthya praaanpatr, aadi.
kan: prayankke bekad dakhlegamalli posport, visa, hanad pramanpatra athwa posportnalli hanad bagegin himbarah, prayan vime, aadaya terigeya vivaranpatra, aarogya pramanpatragalu muntadavu serive.
mal: pasport, visa, karaൻsi sർttiphicketo paspoർttille karaൻsi sakshyappetuttalo, travൽ iൻshuraൻs, aadayanikuti state meൻrukൾ, arogyasർttiphicketukൾ tutangiyav yatrarekaliൽ uൾppetunnu.
ori: yatrakalin kaagajpatragudik madhyare passport, visa, mudraagat pramanpatra athava passportre mudrar anumodan, yatrakalin bimaa, aan kar bivarani, ssthbhagat pramanpatra, ityadi antarbhukt .
pan: yatri de dasataveza vich passport,vizaa,mudra praman paper jaaa mudra di passport vich tasadiq, aamadan masool, sihat praman paper adi ounde han I
tam: bhayan aavanakalil katvuch sittu, visa, nanayach sandidal alltu katvuch chitle nanay uruti meloppam, bayanak kappedu, varuman vari arikkis, udalnalach sandues bhonrowai atankum.
tel: prayan patrala passport, visa, dravya dhruvapatra, leda passport lo dravya aamoda, prayan bimaa, aaday pannu nivedikalu, arogya dhruvapatras, mo. vi. untai.
urd: safari dastavezaat main passport, visa, krinsi kaa certificate yaa passport main krinsi kii tosiq, travel anshurnce, income tex ke bayanat, sahat ke certificate vagairah shamil hain.
eng: Travel documents include passport, visa, currency certificate or endorsement of currency in the passport, travel insurance, income tax statements, health certificates, etc.

ben: arevati prakaar halo rele tryathlan yekhane pratiyogita ekati pratiyogider dal palakrm aansh neya, pratyek pratiyogik santar, cycling evan dauder ekati kare aansh karte has.
guj: biji ramat rile-triathloni che, jema hariphoni tukri resma ek pachhi ek harifai kare che; darek harife farjiyat tarvanu, saycle chalaavavaanu ane dodevanu hoya che.
hin: ek or praaroop he riley tryalon jisamen pratispardhi baari-baari se daud main pratispardhaa karte hai; prayek pratispardhi ko tairaaki, saaikal chalaane or daudane ke khand ko puraa karnaa padataa he.
kan: innondu rupavendare riley tripandyavagiddu, adralli spardhalugal tandavondu pandyadalli saradi prakarvagi spardhisuttade; pratiobb spardhalu iju, cycle tulit mattu otad ondu vibhagavannu purtigolislebeku.
mal: matoru matsararupa oru sangha matsararthi uea vach matsarikunn rille trayatalonukala; oro matsaraർtthiu nintal, cycilotte, otea ennivil oru bhaga cheiyant.
ori: annga eka prarup heudi riley traethlan, yeunthi prathiyogeemanankar eka dal nij pali hisaabre eka daudre bhaganeithanthi; ethire pratyeka prathiyogeeku pahanra, sicel chalna, eban daudre gotie gotie ansh sampadan karivaku padithae.
pan: ik hor roop hai rilly trichlonus, jithe pratiogia di team, daud vich bhaag lan lai waria lende han ; harek pratiyogi nuun tiraqi, sycling ate daud da ik hisa puura karna penda hai I
tam: its manthoru vativam riley triathlon, itel botipotum andant anikalch sernt ovvoruvarum onhanpin onjhak botiil bankedudhu chiritu turam nichal, saikle otudal, ottam akhiyavaggrai aduttadudhu menokoll wants.
tel: riley traiyatlance anedi maro vidhana, indulo potidarul jattu vantulvariga pandemulo potipatar; okkok potidar tappanisariga it kottut, cycl tokkut mariyu parugu titallo ock vibhaganlo palgonalsi untundi.
urd: ek or formet rele traythalon kaa hai, jis main harifon kii ek tem daud main muqabla karne ke liye baari baari kaam krati hai; har harif ko tairaqi, saikaling or daud kaa ek hissaa puraa karna zaroori hota hai.
eng: Another format is relay triathlons, where a team of competitors takes turns to compete in a race; each competitor must do a segment of swimming, cycling and running.

ben: echadao, nyuremburg tryaler praktan pradhan abhishansak benjamin ferenj iraq akramanake "spost ine langhan" bale avihit karellen evan eti shanti viruddha ekati aparaadh gaian kare.
guj: vadhuma, nuremberg trylsana bhutapurv mukhya sarakaari wakil benzamin ferenjhe iraq parna akramanane ‘‘kaayadanu spasht ullanghan’’ ganavyu che ane te shanti virudho guno bane che.
hin: iske alaava, iraq par akraman "kanoon kaa spasht ulanghan" he or nurmburg mukademon main ek purv mukhya abhiyokta benjamin pherenz ke anusaar, is tarah se yah shanti ke khilaaf aparaadh kaa nirmaan karata he.
kan: idarondige, nurembourg vichaaranegal maji mukhya firyadi benjamin pherenge iraqin melin i akramanavannu “kanoonin spasht ullanghane”yendu karediddare mattu idannu shantige baged drohavende herrbahudagide.
mal: atinupurame, neurambergh vichaaranyute mun mukhya prosicuterairunn benchamin ferens, irakinte adhinivesham "niyamattine vyaktmay langhan"vu aa nilek samadhanttinetiraull oru kutakrityavumanennupainju.
ori: ta' sahit, neuremavarg bichaarar poorvathan mukhya abhiyogakari-paksha okil, benzamin pherenj, iraq upare akramanaku "spast bhave iner ullangghan" boli kahiyanthi, eban vasthabare eha shanthi virudhre aparaadh hin ate.
pan: ish ton ilava, nurmberg trilaan de saabaka mouth wakil benjamin pherenz ne iraki de hamale nuun "kaanoon di safsht ulangana" kiha hai, ate ish tarhaa ih shanti de viruddha apraadh hai|
tam: melum, neuramberg vashakkugalin munnal talams arasutrabbu valakkaringr benjamin perrence irag mitan patieduppai "woru telivana satt mishel" endu araitullar, awk atu amaitiku ethranathoru kuriamak vihangukintu.
tel: adnanga, neuremberg vicharanal maji pradhan nyayavadi ayin benjamin ferrenj irak mid jarigin dadini "spashtanga ock chatt ullanghan" ani, idi shantiki vyatirek neranga pariganinchabadutundani perkonnar.
urd: is ke alaava neurmburg triliz ke sabik chef parasicuter benjuman farianz ne iraq par hamale ko "kanoon kii wakaah pamali" qaraar diya hai or is tarah ye aman ke khilaaf jurm hai.
eng: In addition, former chief prosecutor of the Nuremberg Trials Benjamin Ferencz has called the invasion of Iraq a "clear breach of law," and as such it constitutes a crime against peace.

ben: gujarat rajya kartrupaksher pakshapatmulak paddhati suspast boza yawa nie tarkavitark hachche, ya shudhu dayer kara palta halynama upar upar padhlei praman pawa ya.
guj: avi dalil karvama aave che ke gujarat rajyama sattadhishono pakshapati abhigam bahola pramanma nondhayelo che, je dakhal karayel affidavitana vanchan matrathi spasht thai che.
hin: daleel ke mutabik, prastut kiye gaye javaabi halafname ko sarsari taur par padhane se bhi dikh jaataa he ki gujarat rajya ke adhikariyon kaa ravaiya pakshpatpurna tha.
kan: gujrat rajyad adhikarigal pakshapat dhoraneyu suspashtwagideyendu vadislagiddu, adu sallikeyagiruv prati shapathpatrad sadaa odinindale vedyavaguttade.
mal: samർppicpat ethiർ satyavangmulam matra vaichaൽ teliunn gujarat sansthante adhikarilute pakshapaata kalർnn sameepan suvyaktamanen vadicppetunnu.
ori: eha davi karayaushi ye gujrat rajya karttripakshankar pakshapati drushticonti pura spast, yahaki dakhal karayaithiva prati-sateepantir eka sadharan pashnaru suspast .
pan: ih mania janda hai ki gujarat raj de vich adhikaria di pakhpati jug rit vada hai jo ki saaf pataa chalda hai counter halafanama di ik chalak ton pataa chalda hai I
tam: gujarat manilatil adhikarielin parapatsamana anukumurai appartamak welipatukintu enjh vaataj munwaixpattuldu, itu daral seit edir urutimoqib patratai melotamak wasitale telivakap pulapatum.
tel: gujarat rashtra adhikaarul pakshavadi vidhana chala spashtamanadani savalu cheyabadindi, idi dakhalan kauntor afidvit prathamik pathanme spashta chestondi.
urd: aisi hujjat pesh kii jaati hai ki riyasat gujarat main hakam kaa jaanbudarana taqaarab saaf tuur par jaahir hai, jo mahaj jamaa kiraye gaye javaabi half naame ko pad lene se wakaah ho jataa hai.
eng: It is contended that the partisan approach of the authorities in the State of Gujarat is writ large, which is evident from a bare reading of the counter affidavit filed.

ben: uparntu, 2014-e gharoya videor khucharo bikretader ek japani sangathan yojit 4rth vidiwasan puraskare shreshth puraskar pa three ediyats; gharoya o bideshi halud prayojna sah hazar hazar chalachchitra, anim evan televishan anusthanke pittne phele 2013-e muktiprapth sarvashreshth video hisabe manonith hay three ediyats.
guj: vadhuma, 2014maa 3 idiatse japaniz home video retailor sanstha dwara ayojit chotha videoyasana evordsma grand prise jityu; sthanik ane videshi holivud nirman sahit hajaaro filmo, aneme, ane telividon karyakramone haravine 3 idiats 2013ni shreshtha video prastti tarike pasandgi pamyu.
hin: iske alaava, 3 edinuts ne 2014 main gharelu video khudara vikritaon ke ek japani sanghathan dwaara yojit chauthe videoyasana puraskaron main bhavy puraskaar jeeta; gharelu or videshi hollywood prastutiyon sahit hazaron filmon, anime, or televijan kaaryakramon ko maat dete hue 3 edinuts 2013 kii sarvottam video release ke rup main chuni gai.
kan: idar jotege, 3 ediats 2014ralli mane video chillare vyapaarigal japaani sanstheyondu aayojisidd 4nae videoyason prashastigamalli grand bahumanvannu garisitu; deshiya hagu videshi holliwood nirmangainnu olagondante saviraaru chalanchitragalu, anime, hagu durdarshanad kaaryakramagainnu hindikki 3 ediats 2013r atyuttam video bidugade endu aaykeyaitu.
mal: it kootate, 2014l ho video ritayleർsinte oru jappanise sanghaton natattia nalamat videoyasan puraskarattil 3 idiets grand pris netukyu, taddeshiya vaideshikavumay hollywood chitras ulppeteyull aairkanakkinu chalachchitrayasleyu, animeshnukalayu telivishan shokalayu tolppich 3 idiets 2013le mikachch video prakashanmavukyu cheitu.

tam: atu matuminri, 3 idiats 2014il woru japaniya home video chillerai wanikars amifu nattya 4aavatu videoyasan virtu vinavill mik uirnt parisai tattichenttu; melum, 3 idiats 2013aam antin mikachihant video veleithagaum terndeducoppattatu, apbodhu atu ulnaddu manllum ayalnaddu haliwood dayarippues udpat oiragankkana tirappatas, bommap patangas, dolicadsi nicktchis ena anaites tolkaditu mudalitttap fidittatu.

urd: is ke alaava , three edits ne 3 main home video retailoriz kii ek japani tanzeem kii taraf se manakad hone waale chauthe videvasana ewardiz main grand prize jeeta tha; three edits ko 2013 kii behtareen video reliz ke tuur par mantakhab kiya gaya tha, hazaaron filmon, eneme, or tele vision ke program ko haraate hue, jis main gharelu or gair milki hali wood prodakshan shamil the.
eng: In addition, 3 Idiots won the Grand Prize at the 4th Videoyasan Awards, held by a Japanese organisation of home video retailers in 2014; 3 Idiots was selected as 2013's best video release, beating thousands of films, anime, and television shows, including domestic and foreign Hollywood productions.

ben: computur sciences karporeshan evan aksencharer saathe dupan-r mukhya tathy aadhikarik sinda halamaner 10 bacharavyapi 400 koti markin dollarer outsortsing sukti vyavasthapanar bivaran outsors kara hayesil, evave "ghare base karaar mato ekati paddhati amra udbhavan kari."

mal: "chhangoൾ at svayn chetatanengiൽ oru prakriariti contupitikunnat" ochiwakuvidha, dyuppondiൻre chiph iൻfaർmeshൻ ofisaray siൻda haൾmaaൻre 400 koti dollaryൻre pattuvർsha nilunnatu computaർ sayൻsas koർpatishnu aksaൻcharu tammilulatumay autsoർsingh koൺtract kaikaryam cheiyunnatiൻre vishdanshanoൾ autsores cheyyapettu.
ori: dupant'r mukhya suchana adhikari sinda halmannkar 'kamputer sainces karporesan' eban 'aksenchar' sahit $400 koti dollar 10-barshar bahirrot chukthir bivaraneegudiku outso'rs karithila, yahadraki "aame anusthan madhyare karithile, eka prakriaku udbhavan kariva"ku edai diayiparithila .
pan: dupont di mouth sanvad afasar, sinda hallman de $4 karod de 10 saal lai baahron com lan de soma de kararaname di vistar computer vigyaan nigam ate acintur, outsos hai jise karke , " ik prakiria di kaaf jo ki ghar de under hi hoo sakadi see" us ton bach gaye I
tam: kamputter scincess carperehan manllum axentture niruvanangaluton dupont niruvan talams takhaval adhikari sinta hallmanin $4 billion matipull 10 varudap pani oppatipu obbandat nirvakibpadan dunaip panis pani oppatipu seyyabpattanu, eneway "adai niruvanatin ullaye nam saithrukkum batchetil puditak woru natwatikait dittats uruvakk wantia avvelai" tavircoppattatu.
tel: computer sainces carporesion mariyu yaksencharto dupant karyanirvahak pradhan samacharshakhadhikari synda hallman yokk yues $4 billian, 10 ell pat vaari nudi wastulu leda seval ponde oppanda dwara danini nirvahinche vivrase wariki ketoinchi, "maname antargatanga cheste daniki ock vidhananni kanipettvalsin" paristateni tappinchindi.
urd: dopont ke aali itlaati afasar cinda hollman ke computer sincez corporation or axcenture ke saath 4 arab dollar ke 10 saala out surasang countract kii tafsilat out souras kii gayiin, is tarah "agar hum use indron udara karte to amal ajjad karte" se griez kiya gaya.
eng: Details of managing DuPont's chief information officer Cinda Hallman's $4 billion 10-year outsourcing contract with Computer Sciences Corporation and Accenture were outsourced, thus avoiding "inventing a process if we'd done it in-house."

ben: tomas presishan (ekati gatipather pare taar prathmik bege phire aasa mott abrtan) ekati nikhad gatisankrant prabhava also eti shudhumatra bakrarikhik chalane sanghatit has evan tai kono tadi-chumbakian kshetra, mahakarshin kshetra athva kono yantrik baler mato sei bakrarikhik chalanti ghatano byrer kono bal chada alada kare paryavekshan kara ya na, ataev tomas poorbavartita sadharant gatishil prabhabasmuher anuhang ghate.
guj: bhale thomas prisishan (trajectori bad net rotation tena prarambhik vega taraf parat thai che) e shuddha kinemetic aasar che, e matra vakriya gatima ja upje che ane tethi swatantra rite koi bahya balne lidhe vakriya gati nipje che, tenu avalokan thai shakatu nathi; jemke e ek electromagnetic field, ek gurutvakarshan bal, ke ek yantric bal che; tethi thomas prisishan samanya rite dynamik asro sathe hoya che.
hin: haalanki thomas ayan (vaastavik ghurnan jab koi sanchhedi apni praarambhik gati par waapas aa jaataa he) purna rup se gatimetiya prabhaav he, yah keval vakrarekhi gati main hota he or isliye is vakrarekhi gati dene vaale vidyut-chumbakeey kshetra, gurutvkarshan kshetra yaa yantric bal jaise bahya bal se mukt nahin dekha ja saktaa he, atah aam taur par thomas ayan gatikeey prabhaavon ke saath hota he.
kan: thomas aynanshavu (ondu vikshep pathavu tann aarambhik vegakke hinthirugid nantarad nivval paribhraman) shuddhavagi gativigyanakke sambandhisid ondu prenamwagideyadaru adu keval vakrarekhiya chalaneyalli matra sambhvisuttade mattu aa karandind vakrarekhiya chalaneyannu aagamaduv vidyutkantiya kshetra, gurutva kshetra, athwa yantric baladantah yavudadaru bahya balad hortagi idannu vikshisuvudu sadhayvillvaddarind thomas aynanshavu samanyavagi chalkabal prenamgal jotegudiruttade.
mal: tomas priseshൻ (prarambhavegati mathngunn oru sancharapathtin sheshmulla net rotateshൻ ) oru kewalam chalanatmakamay prabhavamaankil, at vakrarekhiyamay chalanttiൽ matra sambhwikkunnatu atinaൽ vakrarekhiyamay chalanmuntakkunn vaidyutakantik mandla, gurutvakർshan mandla, mekanicaൽ balam tutangia bahyabalattiൽninn swatantramai nirikshikanakatatu ayatinaൽ tomas priseshൻ saadharanmai chalanatmak prabhavacalotoppa sambhwikkunnatan.
ori: yadio thomas prexesan (nizer prarambhik begaku pheruthiva eka trajectoreer net ghoornnan) eka vishuddh kinematik prabhab, eha keval bakrarekha gatire ghatithaye, tenu kari bakrarekhiya gati ghatauthiva bahya shaktir bahaare stantra bhave ehaku nirikshan karayai parib naahin, yepariki yaha eka vaiduthik-chumbakiya kshetra, eka madhakarshan kshetra, kimba eka yantrika shakti karanru ghatithaye, tenu thomas prexesan sadharanthati gatishil prabhab seh ekatara bhave aasithaye.
pan: halanki thomas priseishan (ik tregectory ton bood net rotation jo isde shuruaati veg 'te wapas oundi hai) ik shuddha kinematic prabhav hai, ih siraf karvillinior moshan vich hunda hai ate ish lai kise baahri bal sutantra for 'te nahi dekhia jaa sakda, jise naal karvillinior moshan hunda hai jiven ki ik electromagnaetic field, jaaa ik makanical bal de kaaran hunda hai, ish lai thomas prisacshan aam for 'te gatishil prabhaavaan de naal hunda hai|
tam: thomas munduka (ore evipaths tanatu tuakkat disaivegatukud thirumpia pingu ull nikarch subalchi) murill ore iangial vilaivu enfodhilu, atu valagottu nagarvil mattume nikavkintu, eneway minkandab pulam, bhuviirfup pulam alltu endra visai bhondu attaku valagottu nagarve erbadudukits welippune visai charamal adai urjunokk ialadhu, awk thomas munduka valakkamak ianguviel vilaivugaluton sernde irukkum.
tel: thomas chalana (dani prarambh veganiki tirigi vachchin ock patha yokk nikar bhramana) phurtiga chalan sambandhamin prabhavamayina kani, adi kevalam vakr rekhalo chalantion jarugutundi, anduvall danni ock vidyut askant kshetra, ock gurutvakarshan kshetra, lek ock yantric shakti, vanti ock bahya shakti niyanthran lekunda gamninchala kudardu, anduvall thomas chalana sadharannga yantragati prabhavalto kalisi untundi.
urd: agarache thomas presseshan (khat harakat ke baad kii khalis gardish jo apni ibtidai saraat par waapas aajaati hai) ek khalstan harakayati asar hai, lekin ye sirf kham khatee harakat main waaqa hota hai or yahi vajah hai ki is kaa mishahda kisi aisi beroni kaut se aazaadana tuur par naheen kiya jaa saktaa jo kham khatee harakat kaa sabab banati ho, jese barqnatesi maidan, kasish saqil kaa maidan, yaa ek mikaneki kaut, lahza thomas presseshan aam tuur par mataharak asarat ke saath ikattha hota hai.
eng: Although Thomas precession (net rotation after a trajectory that returns to its initial velocity) is a purely kinematic effect, it only occurs in curvilinear motion and therefore cannot be observed independently of some external force causing the curvilinear motion, such as that caused by an electromagnetic field, a gravitational field, or a mechanical force, so Thomas precession is usually accompanied by dynamical effects.

ben: micro, small o medium antarpraigeger (em.es.em.i) janya rajyer mantri (shwadhin dawitvaprapth) shri giriraj singh 2018 saler 19- 20she december naya delhite si.aai.aai-era anshidaritve em.es.em.i mantranalaya dwara yojit 15tam em.es.em.i global samiter udvodhane pradhan baktavya pesh karaar samay balen, ei lagatar pracheshter fale vishwavyapi i.o.de.bi rankingy amader retinyer evan ji.bhi.si-r sang yukt karaar kshetre em.es.em.i yesav samasyar sammukhin hayes seguloke samadhan kara unnati ghateche.
guj: satatyapurna prayasona priname amara vaishvik i.o.dee.bi. gunakama sudharo thayo che ane ji.ve.sii. na jodanma em.es.em.i. dwara samano karvama aavata padakaaro vishe sambodhta, sii.ai.ai.ni bhagidarima em.es.em.i. mantralaya dwara navi delhima 19-20 december, 2018na roj yojayel 15me vaishvik parishadana udghaton daramiyaan bij vaktavya aapta sukshma, laghu ane madhyam udyogona rajya kakshana mantri (swatantra havaalo) shri giriraj sinhe janavyu hatu.
hin: rajya mantri shri girija singh, laghu, kutir evam madhyam upkram (em.es.em.i.), (swatantra prabhaar) ke anusaar, jinhone disambar 19–20, 2018, ko nai dilli main 15wein es.em.i. vaishvik shikhar sammelan ke udghaatan main mukhya bhaashan diya, em.es.em.i. ke mantralay ke lagaataar prayatnon ne vaishvik i.o.di.bi. ke shrenee-kram main hamaari shrenee main sudhaar kiya he or ji.ve.si se judane main em.es.em.i. ko jin mushkilon kaa saamana karnaa padataa he, unhen sambodhit kiya he.
kan: em.es.em.i. sachivalayavu si.i.i. sahbhagitvadalli dicembar 19-20randu navdehlialli aayojisidd 15nae es.em.i. jagathik shrungasabheya udghatna kaaryakramdalli pradhan bhaashan madid sukshma, sann mattu madhyam kaigarikegal (em.es.em.i.) rajya sachiv (swatantra nirvahane) shri giriraaj singh, "nirantar parishramad prenamvagi global i.o.de.bi. shreyankadalli namm ratinggalu sudharisive mattu ji.vi.si.galondige sampark sadhisuvalli em.es.em.i.galu edurisuttiruv savalugagannu bagehrisuvudu sadhayavagide" endu hehidaru.
mal: agola i. o. de. bi rangingiൽ nammute sthana mechchappetuttunnatinu ji. vi. sikalumai bandhappetuttunnatiൽ e. es. e. i.kൾ nerit velluvilikൾ abhimukhikarikunnatinu tutർchchayay parishramngൾ karanmitnden 2018 disambർ 19 - 20 tiyatikaliൽ e. es. e. i mantralaya si. ai. ai. yumai cheർnn new dൽhiiൽ sanghatippichch patinanjam agola uchchakotiute udgharanttiൽ mukhyaprabhashaea nattave sansthante sukshm, cherukit, itatar sanrambhateute mantri (e. es. e. i) shri giriraj singh parannu.
ori: nooadilhire 19 - 20 december 2018 re, si.aai.aai.nk sahabhagitare em.es.em.i. manthralaya dra aatojit 15sh es.em.i. vishstariya sammirnir udghaton bele aadhar udbodhan vaktruta pradaan kariva samaure rajya anu, kshudra eban madhum udog (em.es.em.i.) manthri (sdhin prabhar) shri giriraj singh kahithile abirat udum falre vishwapi i.o.de.bi. sthanr moolankanare unnati eban ji.bhi.si. gudik sahit sanyukt hebare em.es.em.i. gudik sammukhin heuthiva aahnagubikar samadhan heva sambhava hoichhi .
pan: shri gireraj singh, 15 asa.aim.i de vishva sammelan , jo ki aim.asa.aim.i valon si.aai.aai naal mile ke yojit see 19 - 20 dismber 2018 , navin dili vich , kiha ki lagatar jatnaas ne sari vishva i.o.di.bi di shenikarn vich sudhaar lyanda hai ate aim.asa.aim.i naal ji.vi.si nuun jodan vich jo chunotia ia , onha thik karna I
tam: 19 - 20 december 2018 datekasil putudilliil sinai amaiputon inaindhu emesemi amychagam arbadu saithrunth 15aam esemi ulalaviya uchimanatin dotakk vinavill kuru, chiru manllum naduttarat toddil niruvanangalukan (emesemi) inai amychare (tanip potupu) shri giriraj singh talams urai arllum podhu, doder mushcikhalin balanak ulak iodipe druvarisil emesemi-khals gvici-galuton inipatil ull sawallukud tiru kanpathil namadhu dharamtipidus munneriuluna endu gurinar.
tel: new delhi 2018, december 19-20 varaku si. ai. ai. bhagswamyanto anes ani mantritva shakh nirvahinchin 15va esseni prapanch shikharagra sadssu prarambhotsavalo sukshma, chinn, madhya tarha parishramal (anes ani) mantri shri giriraj singh pradhanansha gurinchi prasangistu, nirantar prayasal falitanga global iodibi ryankingulo pampudal mariyu jivisi latho anusandhanation anesenies adurkunn savallan uddeshinchapha jarigayani annar.
urd: bahut choti, choti or darmiyaani sanaaton (em es em e) ke vazeer mamalkit (aazaadana charge) janaab giri raj singh ne 19 - 20 disambar 2018 ko nai dahali main si aai aai ke ishtarak se em es em e kii jaanib se manakda 15 vaein es em e global simat ke afatitah ke mauqaa par kaledi khataba dete hue kaha ki musalasal koshishon ke nattejey main alami e oo dee bi ranking main hamari darja bindi main behatari aai hai or em es em ez ko durpesh chelanjon se namatane main madad mili hai.
eng: The constant efforts have resulted in the improvement of our ratings in the Global EoDB ranking and addressing the challenges faced by MSMEs in connecting to GVCs, said Minister of State (Independent Charge) for Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises (MSME) Shri Giriraj Singh while delivering the keynote address during the inauguration of the 15th SME Global Summit organized by the Ministry of MSME in partnership with CII, on 19 - 20 December 2018 in New Delhi.

ben: deep modern chulha sociti af develpament and enabhiranment protechshan (deep) aadhunik deep chulha baniech ya kather vyabhhar 50 shatansh commie anar janya jaiv padarther vyabhhar kare.
guj: develapament and anvayarment protection (dee.i.i.pe.) ni deep modern chulha sosayadi aadhunik deep chulha viksavya che je lakdano vaparash 50% sudhi ghatadwa jaivik indhanno upayog kare che.
hin: vikaas or paryaavaran sangrakshan kii di.i.i.pi. aadhunik chulhaa socity (di.i.i.pi.) ne aadhunik di.i.i.pi. chulhaa viksit kiya he jisamen lakdi kii khapat ko 50% se kam karne ke liye jaev eendhan kaa upyog kiya jaataa he.
kan: development and enviranment protekshann (de.i.i.pi.) de.i.i.pi. modern chulha societiyu modern de.i.i.pi. chulhavannu abhivruddhipadisiddu, adu kattigeya banakeyannu 50% ashtu kadimagolislu jaivikarashiannu upayogisuttade.
mal: develpmeൻr aaൻd eൻviroൺmeൻr protekshൻre (de.i .i. pi) modyൺ chul sosity vickinte upabhoga 50% kurikkuvanai jaivadravyam upyogikunn aadhunik de.i .i. pi chulakൾ vidocippitchu.
ori: 'deep' bikash eban parivesh sanrakshan - aadhunik chaula samaj (de.i.i.pi.), aadhunik deep chaula vikashita karithila yaha kader bbbaharaku 50% hras kariva pin jaib indhan bbbahar karithaye .
pan: deep madran chulha society aaf development and unvirument protaction (DEEP) ne aadhunik deep chulha viksit kita jo lakkad di khapat nuun 50% tak ghataun lai biomas di varton karada hai|
tam: desibi enjh mambadu manllum sudduchural bhadukafbukkan (desibi) navina sune sangam, mrup payanbatte 50% kuraikum vitmak uirtralp payanbaduttum navina desibi sulys uruvakyldu.
tel: deipi modern chulha society aaf development and anviranment protekshan (deipi) jeevapadarthanni upayoginche aadhunik deipi poyin tayar chessi kattel wadkanni 50% tagginchindi.
urd: dip modern chulha societi of developament and anwarmint protection (dee e e pii) ne jadid dip chulha taiyaar kiya jo lakdi kii khapat ko 50 faisad tak kam karne ke liye biomas kaa istemaal kurta hai.
eng: DEEP Modern Chulha Society of Development and Environment Protection (DEEP) developed the Modern DEEP Chulha that uses biomass to reduce the consumption of wood by 50%.

ben: 2010-era 28 december qualishan tu aparute ryaging fram edukeshwan (kior) named besarkari sansthar sah-pratishthata harsh agrawal ekati nirdisht drushye agrajder dwara pradhan abhinetader ryaging nie kshover bivaran die poorvatan aich.aar.de mantri aar. ke. raghavaner netrutvadhin ekati panel, raghavan comitic ekati chithi lekhen.
guj: 28 december 2010na roj binsarkari sansthan, shikshanmathi karpatane dharmulathi dur karva matena jodan (sii.yu.ar.i.)na sahasthapak harsh agrawale purav ech.ar.dee. mantri ar. ke. raghavanna vadpanwali raghavan smitine patr lakhi mukhya kalakarona varishto dwara thatan karpat ange santap vyakt karyo.
hin: purv maanav sansaadhan vikaas mantri aar. ke. raghavan kii adhyakshata vaale ek samooh, raghavan cameti, ko shiksha-kshetra se raging ko jad se ukhaadne ke liye bane ek gathbandhan (kyor) ke sah-sansthaapak harsh agarwal kii taraf se 28 disambar 2010 ko, ek drishy ke bare main, jahaan varisht khilaadiyon dwaara praathmik khilaadiyon kii raging kii jaati he, apni nakhushi jataate hue ek patr mila.
kan: 2010r dicembar 28randu, sarkaretar sanstheyad kolishan and aprut ryagging fram ejukeshan (si.you.aar.i.) idar sah-sansthapak harsh agarwal maji ech.aar.de. sachiv aar.ke. raghvan netrutvad tajnar tandvad raghvan smitige mukhya nataru melinvarind pidenegolgaguv ondu nirdisht drushyad nidarshanadondige samasyeyannu vivarisutta ondu patrvannu baredru.
mal: 2010 disamsar 28n oru sarkkaritar sanghayanyay koyalishan tu aprut raging fram ajukeshante (si yu aaർ i ) sahasthapakanay harsh agarwal, oru pratyek sinil munnir natinthanmar muthirna vidyartthilal ragh cheyyapetunnatile manprayas vishadikarichukond ech .ar.de. muൻmantri ar.ke. raghawan nayikunn panalay raghawan committic oru katayachu.
ori: 2010 masiha december 28 tarikh din, besalkari anusthan, 'koalisan tu apru't raging fram ejukeshan' (cor)r seh-pratishthata harsh agral poorvathan ech.aar.de. manthri aar. ke. raghavannk netritrain eka panel, 'raghavan kamiti'ku eka patr lekhithile, yeunti eka nirddist drushyaku nei rahithiva kashtaku varnana karuthila, yeunthireki mukhya abhinetamanankar siniarmanank dra raging hue .
pan: 28 dasamber 2010 nuun gair-sarkari sanstha collision tu aproot reging frome ajukeshan (cur) de sahai sansthapak harsh agarwal ne, saabaka aich aar di mantri aar. ke. raghavan di sarprasati cha bane panel, raghavan kameti nuun khaas drish ton hoi preshaani nuun varnan karade hoe, ik paper likhia jad seniors duara mouth bhumika wale abhinetaws di reging keeti gai|
tam: 28 december 2010 andu, 'galvip pulatil rakinga verdupadaskana goottani' (gyur) enjh arasu chara amaipin dunai niruvaner harsh agarwal munnal manitval amychare aar.ke. ragavan talamailan ragavan committy enjh sicipbuk kuduuku woru katidam eduti atil, munnani natigarhs tangaluku mooddhavarkalal raking seyyapatum woru kufippitt katchi manavedan alickakudiyatak irukkintu endu vilukirindar.
tel: 28 december 2010 nadu, kolishan t apruit ryaging fram adyukesion (cur) ane prabhuthvetar sansth sahvyavasthapak harsh agarwal, pradhan patral senior chet ryag cheyabada ock pratyek sannivesha gurinchi badhanu vyakta chestu, manav vanarul mantritva shakh arke raghavan netritvanloni sabhyamandali, raghavan kamitiki lekh vrasharu.
urd: gair sarkari tanzeem, koleshan to aprot reagang firam ajokeshan (kivar) ke shariq bani harsh agarwal ne 28 disambar 2010 ko raghavan cameti, ek panel jis ke cerbrah sabik each aar dee vazeer aar ke raghavan the, ke naam ek khat likhaa, jis main ek makhsus manzar par tushwesh kii vizahat kii, jahaan marcuji udaakar seneron ke zarie haraasaan kiye jate hain.
eng: On 28 December 2010, the non-governmental organisation, Coalition to Uproot Ragging from Education (CURE) co-founder Harsh Agarwal wrote a letter to the Raghavan Committee, a panel headed by former HRD Minister R. K. Raghavan, explaining distress over a particular scene, where the lead actors get ragged by seniors.

ben: tar madhyam yama (dakshina anchale basbaskari mrityur devatha)-ke pratihat karaar janya pratidbandvita badhaparikar aro ek mrityur devathake prakashye aaney uttarer anchal.
guj: anama uttarna pradeshe jane mrityuno dev upsi aavyo, je yam (dakshinna pradeshma vasata mrityuna dev) satheni spardhama aagal nikali jawa makkam hato.
hin: yama ((dakshin kshetron main rahane vaale achche mrityu ke devtaa ) ko maat dene ke liye uttari kshetra unke rup main maano pratidwandvita main drudhsankalp ho kar ek anya mrityu ke devtaa ko saamne le aayaa.
kan: aatnannu uttarad pradeshsvu yamanannu (dakshind dikkinalli vasisuv mrityu devate) mirisuv hurudull innobb mrityu devateyo embantagisitu.
mal: (tekkudikiൽ vasikkunn marandevnay) yemena marikataan matsaryabuddhi mutt matoru marandevye addehtilute vaikkudi munnotukonduvannu enne paryam.
ori: tank madhyare, uttar kshetra aau jane mrittur devatanku khoji pithila, yie kipari yamanku (mrittur devatha yie dakshinanchasaare baas karanthi) harai agku yive boli prathiyogitha karuthile.
pan: us de under, uttari ilaake ne, mout da ik hor devataa, yam (ngkhani khetraan vich basada mout da dev) nuun pichhe chadan lai virodh vich jhukia hora see.
tam: wat nottle avritu uruvam innuru maran devanagap bhavixpattatu, atu emanuku (dhennatle nilavia maran devan) ethragum emenai vinjukih vaqail irundatu.

eng: They are constructed between 600 and 1000 CE, the Ellora Caves consist of 100 Hindu, Jain, and Buddhist caves, out of which 34 are open to visitors.

ben: bhalo samajik maryadasampann ingrej mahilara chhillen viral; shalyachikisak jan stuart 1785-te kanpur thek tar vaike lekhen: "ekhankar mahilader aneke ladgate hiler mahilader tupi presentakari dokan thek evan keu keu to kavent garden evan old druri [18m shatabdeer shesher dike london patitavrittir suparichit elaka] thek aasa duhsahasini matra."
guj: saro samazik mobho dharavati british mahilao juj hati; 1785maa sarjan jhon stuarte kanporthi potana bhaaine lakhyu ‘‘ahinni ghani streeo ladget hil parani milinrini dukano ane amuk to kovent garden tatha old dryuri (18me sadina uttarardhama veshyavritti mate janita landanna ketlak vistaro) kartaan pan vadhu romachak che.
hin: acchhee saamaajik haisiyat vaali angrej mahilaayein gini-chuni hi thim; 1785 main apane chote bhai ko kanpur se ek patr main shalya-chikitsak jon stfort ne likhaa: yahan zyaadaatar auraten paison ke liye sambandh banane vaali, ludgat hill kii mahilaon kii topi kii dukaan se hai, or kuch to old druri (18veen sadi ke landan ke jane-maane veshyavriti sthal) se bhi hai.
kan: uttam samajik sthanmanvuil british mahileyaru viralvagiddaru; 1785ralli shastravidya jaan stuart kanpuradind tann sodarnige hige barediddane: "illin anek mahileyaru bariya kutileyaragiddu ladgate hilnlliruva hengasar hatugaiannu maruv angadigalind mattu innu kelavrantu kavent garden hagu old dooriind [18nae shatmanad coneya bhagadalli landonnin prasiddh veshyavatike tanagalu] bandavaragiddare.
mal: nall samuhikanilyulla british stree apurvamairunnu; 1785l kanpuril ninn sargen john stuart sahodar anuti: "ivitayull strikal mivaru ladgate hillile millineres shoppukalilninnu, chilr (patinetta nutand otuville londonille prasidh vyabhichar kendranslairunn) kavൻr garden old druriil ninnu vare vann veru sahasikakalairunnu".
ori: bhal samajik pratishtha rahithiva inrej mahila kchith thile; 1785 masihare shalya chikitsak jan stert kanpuraru nij bhainku chithi lekhile: "ethakar anek mahila heutanthi keval duhsahasini yeunmaneki ludget hilre thiva milinar dokanamanankaru aasiyanthi, epariki ketek kobhent garden eban old druriru madhya [18sh shatabdee londonare thiva veshyabrittir janashuna anychal] .
pan: changi samajik state vaali bartaanavi aurataan san 1785 vich bohut ait san, sarajan johan stivart ne aapne bura karavan por nuun khat vich likhia, "ithe bohut saari aurataan siraf saahasi han, jo ki dhaugdad pahari vikhe sthit millineras dis dukanaas ton ate kujh taan kovent garden ate purana daruri ton ve han [athahrvin sadi de london vich jisam firoshi dis mushhoor thavaan de name] |
tam: nall samuk andastll british pengal vegu kuraivagave irundaner; 1785il kanpuril irunth aruvaisikichi nipunar jaan stuart tanatu chakodararukku ivvar esudinar: "ingll pal pengal ladkat hillil ull milliors katikalch sernt inches mangis, an chiller govant garden manllum oldu truri [18aam noorthandu londonil villimadhukkaluku nangarioppatt itangs] bakudilch serndavarlagak kuta irukkinowner.
tel: unnat samajik stategal british stries aruduga undevar; john stuvart 1785lo kanpur nudi tan sodrudi ila vrashadu: "ikkadunn chala varaku stries ludgate hilloni millinrs dukanalunudi, alag incontamandi kovent garden mariyu old druri [18va shatabdannati londonlo vyabhichargrihalku peruganchin pradeshal] ki chendin asabhy mahiies.
urd: acchhee samaji haisiyat wali bartanvi khwatin kam thim; 1785 main srijan jaan stewart ne kanpur se apne bhai ko likhaa: "yahaan par kai avratein mahaj muhim joi karne waliyaan hain jo lidagate hill par kalah saaz kii dukaan se or kuch quent garden or old drori se bhi hain [18vaein sadi ke avakhar main london main kahabba giri ke marof ilaka].
eng: British women of good social standing were scarce; in 1785 surgeon John Stewart wrote to his brother from Cawnpore: "Many of the women here are mere adventuresses from Milliners shops on Ludgate Hill and some even from Covent Garden and Old Drury [well-known areas of prostitution in late 18th century London].

ben: parsikara sindhu jalpather parippershvik sthalbhumik, sanskrit sindhu shabder bhul prayog kare hindu namankit karaar fale indas thek india namoti asese.
guj: sindhu jalmarg aasapaasni jameenne pershianoe sanskrit sindhune bhulathi hindu ganavi hati, ane am india nam inds parathi utari aavyu.
hin: farsi logon ne inds jalmaarg ke aas-paas kii bhoomi ko hindu kaha, jo sanskrit ke sindhu kaa galat rup he or is tarah india naam inds se aayaa.
kan: parshianneru indus jalmargad suttamuttalin pradeshskke sanskritd sindhuvin apabhranshvad hindus emb hesarann itru, hagagi indiya emb hesaru indsnind vyutpattiyagide.
mal: indus jalpatk chutumulla bhoomi pershyaar sanskrittilull sindhuviൻre abaddharupamay hindu enne vilickayu angne indsil ninn india end per rupankolaukayu cheitu.
ori: farsimane indas jawdhara pariparshre thiva sthalbhagaku hindu namit kale, yaha ki sanskrit sindhu shabdar eka apabhransh, sutaran indasaru india shabda srushti hoichhi.
pan: farsi locals ne inds de aale-duale di zamin nuun hindus vajon sonpia hai, sanskrit di ik galti sindhu ate ish lai india da name sindh ton lya gya hai|
tam: paarasigars indus natiy subari irukkum nilampakudiku indunnu payar vaitars, anal itu ‘sindhu’ enkires sanskrit collot pirayana uccharipu, appatio itsal than indusilrundhu india enkires payar vandatu.
tel: parpiani indus jalmarg chuttuprakk prantaniki hinduga perkonnadi, idi sanskrit nama sindhuki vikrut pada, ala india ane peru indus nudi vachchindi.
urd: farsiyon ne driyay sand kii guzargah ke arad gird kii jameen ko hindu naam diya, jo sancksarat ke sindhu kii ek bigdi hui shukla hai or is tarah indus se india kaa naam makhuz hai.
eng: The Persians assigned the land around the Indus Waterway as Hindu, an error of the Sanskrit Sindhu and hence the name India is derived from Indus.

kan: jotege hastelgamalli ilidukoleo vidyarthigalige poshana bhatyeyagie prati varsh 10,000/- roopai mattu hastelalli ulidukollad vidyarthigalige 5,000/- roopaigal nischit idigantonn nidelagatte.

eng: And the maintenance allowance will be given as fixed lump sum amount for an academic year of Rs. 10,000/- for hostellers and Rs. 5,000/- for day scholars.

ben: 1991-era tibra avamulayan evan 1994-era carent acount roopantarayogyatar pare, takaar mulyati vapkbhave bazaar shakti dwara nirdhari hay asese.
guj: 1991maa fiver avamulyan bad ane 1994maa chaalu khatana vyavahaaro matena roopantaranma parivartit thaya bad rupianu muly motebhage bazarna balo dwara ja nakki thatu aavyu che.
hin: 1991 main baari avamulyan or 1994 main chaalu khaataa parivartaneeyata main avasthaantar ke baad se rupee kaa mulya kaaphi had tak aarthik karkon dwaara nirdhaarit hota he.
kan: 1991ralli dhidir apamauleikaran mattu 1994ralli chalti khaate parivartaniyateedegin sankramanad nantar, roopayiya maulyavu bahumattige marukatte anshgalind nirdharitvaguttide.
mal: 1991le kuttanaull vinimamulyashoshanattinu, 1994le karaൻr akand parivartanakshamatilekulla matttinu sheea vipanishktikൾ rupeeue mulyate valia totiൽ niർndyitchukontiriunnu.
ori: 1991 masihar tibr avamoolaton, tatha 1994 masihar channthi khata parivarttaneeithaku parivarttan pare, lankar mool bahul bhavare bajarar shaktiguik dra nirddharit hoiasichhi .
pan: rupee da mul 1991 vich tezi naal giran kaaran ate 1994 vich chaaluu khaate di pariveratanshilta vich tabdeeli on ton bood, rupee di kimat ziadatar bazaar di taaktaan te nirbhar kardi hai I
tam: 1991il nanay matipu vinchi, 1994il patippatiak natapbuk ganakirku maderudal akhiyavaukqup pingu rupee matipu perumalvil chandaik karnikalal nirvicopattu varukintu.
tel: 1991 lo fivramin apamulyana mariyu 1994 lo vartaman khata parivartaniyataku marpidi taruvat, rupai viluv akkuvaga market shaktulche nishchainchabadutondi.
urd: 1991 main kadar main tej takhfif or 1994 main krint account main tabadeli ke baad, rupaya kii keemat kaa zyaada tar tain market kii kauuton ne kiya hai.
eng: After the sharp devaluation in 1991 and the transition to current account convertibility in 1994, the value of the rupee has been largely determined by market forces.

ben: ukrenian passport athva parichampatra sah sharnarthider poland evan germany madhye dirghapather trene vinamulye chalachaler anumodan pradaan kare german jatiya rail sanstha dorche ban.
guj: germanyni rashtriya railway company deutsech bahane ukrani passport athva ottkhapatra sathena nirashritone polandthi germany sudhini lamba antarni gadioma nishulk yatra karvaani manjuuri aapi hati.
hin: german rashtriya railway company, doiche baan, ne ukraini passport yaa pahchaan patr liye sharnaarthiyon ko nickshulk poland se germany tak lambii duuri kii trainon main yatra karne di.
kan: germaniy rashtriya railway sanstheyad doych baan, ukrenin posport athwa guruthin chitianneu hondiruv nirashritarige polandinind germanige dur sanchari railugamalli shulkarahitwagi prayanislu anumatisitu.
mal: ukriൻ paspoർto ai. deo ull abhayaർtthie jർmaniile deshiya raiൽwe companyyay doyich baൻ sajanyamai poland mutൽ jർmani vare diർghadur trainukaliൽ sancharikaൻ anuvadichu.
ori: german jatiya rel company, 'doich ba'n' ukreniya passport kimba aai.de. card thiva sharanarthimananku polandaru germaneeku durgami trainre deamukt bhavare yatra karivaku anumati deithila .
pan: dice bahan, german rashtirya rail company ne onha sharnarathis nuun jinhan col ukren da passport jaaa pahichan patar hai , onha lai poland ton germany tak lami duuri di train yatra mufat kar diti hai I
tam: germanein desiya railway niruvanaman tash paan, ugrainiya katvuch sittu alltu adayala atte kont agadiks polandilrundhu germany varum netundoor railil cuttanaminqip bhayanikk anumadittatu.
tel: dooyche ban anu germany jaatiya rile company sharnarthus ukrin pass port leda idi carduto poland nudi germanyki sudur raippllo uchithnga prayaninchadaniki anumatinchindi.
urd: germany kii qaumi railway company davish bahan ne ukrayini passport yaa shinaakhti card waale mahajran ko poland se germany jane wali tavel faasale wali trainon par muft safar karne kii izzaazat di.
eng: Deutsche Bahn, the German national railway company, allowed refugees with a Ukrainian passport or ID card to travel free of charge on long-distance trains from Poland to Germany.

ben: sheshvar 2020-te du'din dhare chala ghurniyer pare kichu elaka vidyu aste 15 din avadhi leag giesil.
guj: chhello chakravat 2020na varshma avelo, te 2 divas sudhi chaalyo ane amuk vistaroma vijali poorvavat kartaan lagbhag 15 divas laagi gaya hatan.
hin: pichhlaa chakravaat 2020 main aayaa tha, vah 2 din chalaa tha or kuch ilaakon main bijli waapas aane main lagbhag 15 din lag gaye the.
kan: hinde 2020ralli agid ciclonu erade din idru, kelvond ariagamalli hogid karent barkke 15 din hiditu.
mal: 2020 l unday chucliat nindu ninnat 2 divasatteanengil chil pradeshs kaornd tirichuvran 15 divasansolam aduttu.
ori: gat batya 2020re hoithila, taha 2 din dhari chalithila eban ketek anychalre elactricity feriva pin praia 15 din lagigala.
pan: akharee chakravat saal 2020 vich aia see, 2 din tak chalia see ate kujh khetraan vich bijali wapas aun vich lagabhaga 15 din lag gaye san.
tam: katisiag 2020il vant puyal erandu nal irunduchu, apbodhu chil bakudikasil 15 nal kalitutan krund thirumbh vandatu.
tel: gattlo tuphanu 2020 sanvatsaranlo vachchindi, 2 rojulpat nadichindi, konni prantall karent tirigi ravadaniki dadapu 15 rozulu pattindi.
urd: aakhri bar toofaan 2020 main aayaa tha, jo 2 din tak jari raha or kuch ilaakon main bijli kii bahaali ke liye takreeban 15 din lage.
eng: The last cyclone happened in the year 2020, went on for 2 days and it took almost 15 days in some of the areas to get the electricity back.

ben: sthanian taxiguloo cherrapunji percent ya evan shilng thek cherrapunji yawar path tara aapnake koekati viupaent evan darshanin sthan thamar vikalp deya (elephant jalprapat, maokadak dimpap vali viu evan anyanya) seisng cherrapunji darshanin sthangulite thamar suyog thake (maosmai guha, cherrapunji ico park, nohasnithiang jalprapat baa seven cyster jalprapat).
guj: sthanik texio pan cherrapunji lai jaaya che ane teo tamane shillong cherrapunji jataan raste thoda jovalayak kendro ane sthano (haathi dhodh, mavakdok dimpape khinnu drushya ane anyo) tatha cherrapunjima mulaaqat leva jevaan sthalo (mavasmai gupha, cherrapunji eco park, nohasangithiang dhodh athva seven sister folls) paase thobhavana vikalp aapshe.
hin: sthaneey texiyaan cherrapunji tak jaati hai, or ve aapako shilong se cherrapunji ke raste main (elephant jalprapaat, mossdock dimpape vaili vyuu or anya sthal) padane vaale kuch darshanik sthalon or jagahon par rukne kaa vikalp tathaa cherrapunji main paryatak sthal dekhne (mosamai gupha, cherrapunji eco park, noshnajithiyang jharne yaa seven sistar jharne) kaa vikalp bhi dete hai.
kan: sthaliya taxigalu chirapunjige sancharisuttve, mattu avu shillangnind chirapunjige hoguv margadalliruva kelvu vikshana sthalgalu hagu prekshaniya jagagamalli(elephant jalpat, makdakh dimpep kaniveya note muntadavu) nilluv aaykeyannu niduv jotege chirapunjielli bhetinidlu yogyavad tanagavigu (masmai guhe, chirapunji eko park, nohsgithiang jalpat athwa elu sahodariyar jalpat) nimmannu karedoyyuttve.
mal: local taxis chirapunchic yatra povukyu shillorl ninn chirapunchiu pokunn wayile (aliphant wellcchatea, mokdok dimpep vali vyu, tutangia) chil vyupoiൻrkal sightukal nilkkanu (mosmai guha, chirapunchi paristatekodyana, nohsingtiyang wellcchatea, sevൻ sister wellcchatea tutangia) chirapunchiile kendranoൾ sandarshianumulam swatantryam nickolk tarikayu cheiyunnu.
ori: sthaniya taksiguik madhya cherapunjiku yatra karanthi, eban semane aapananku shilanru cherapunjir rastaare angap ketoti dharshaniya sthan o drushya thiva sthanmanankare ('elifant jashprapat', 'makdok dimpep upatraka' drushya, eban anyanya) tatha cherapunyji thare thiva dharshaniya sthangudik ('masmai gumpha', 'cherapunyji iko park', 'nahshingithiang jashprapat', ba 'seven sishtar jashprapat') re atakibar bikalp deithanthi .
pan: local taxia ve charrapunji tak jandias han, ate oh tuhaanoon shilong ton charrapunji kai nazare ate dishra (elephant fals, mavakdok dimpape vaili viu, ate hor) vekhy lai ate charrapunji vich ghuman dis thavaan (mosamai guzaph, cherapunji eco parks, ​​nohasingthiang fals, jaaa saven cister fals) te rukan da vichhalp dinde han I
tam: sirupunjhiku cell ullur taxisum ulsana, are shillong-sirupunjhi valithattil oruchil dolainoku ianglilum katchit dalangalilum (yane aruvi, mactac timpep balladakuk katchi ullitt innapitt itangs) ninducelum vasaties, sirupunqiil ull surchaula dalangans (mavsmay kukai, sirupunjhi sudduchural poonga, nosangitiyang nirvinchi alltu seven systers nirvinchi) parkech cellsum vasaties ungs virupattirketap valangukindena.
tel: chirpunjiki stanik taxies kuda prayanistai, wallu miku shillong nudi chirpunji varaku margmadhyatlo konni vikshana sthalal mariyu pradeshal vadd (elephant falls, maudok dimpape vyali vyu, mo. vi), alage chirpujiloni sandarshana sthalal (masmai kev, chirpunji echo park, nohasgithiang falls, leda di seven sister falls) vadd agenduku kuda vies kalpistar.
urd: mukami taxyan cherapunji kaa bhi safar krati hain, or wo aap ko shilang se cherapunji ke raste main kuch mukaamat or sitis (eli fant aabishar, mokdok dimpap vaili wayo, or digar) ke alaava cherapunji main mukaamat (maosmaai gaar, cherapunji eko park, nausangi theong aabishar, yaa seven sister foliz) par rukane kaa akhtiyaar detii hain.
eng: Local taxis also travel to Cherrapunji, and they give you the option of stopping at a few viewpoints and sights on the way from Shillong to Cherrapunji (Elephant Falls, Mawkdok Dympep Valley View, and others), as well as visiting spots in Cherrapunji (the Mawsmai Cave, Cherrapunji Eco Park, the Nohsngithiang Falls, or the Seven Sister Falls).

guj: tethi, jameen sansadhano visheni vyapak mahiti ane temani shakti/ maryaada/ kshamta vividh hetuo mate aavashyak che jevake tabana vistarono vikas, jalavakana vistaroma jameen sanvardhan, tacau kheti, sinchai vyavasthapan, khavayeli jameen punarvasan, vagere.
hin: isliye, vibhinn uddeshyon ke liye jaise ki kaman kshetra vikaas, jalgrahan kshetron main mrudaa sangrakshan, tikaoo krishi, jal-sambar prabandhan, vikrut bhu-sthalon kaa bhoomi-punaruddhar, ityadi ke liye mrudaa sroton or unki sambhavyata/simaaon/kshamtaaon, par vyapak jaankaree kii aavashyaktaa he.
kan: addarind, jalashyagal acchukattu pradeshad abhivruddhi, jalanayan pradeshgamalli mannin sanrakshane, susthir krishi, jalanayan pradeshad nirvahane, savalu-jawalu bhoomiannu matte krishiogyavagisuvudu muntad vividh uddeshgalige mannin sampanmoolagalu hagu avugal sadhayate/itimitigalu/samarthyagal bagegin samagr mahithiyu agatyavagi bekaguttade.
mal: atinaൽ kamand eria develpmeൻr, vrushti pradeshte mannusanrakshant, sthiratyull krishi, niർttat manejmeൻr, gunamenm nashtapat bhoomiute veendetucal tutangia vividh uddeshyak manvibhavasampattinecurichu avayute saddhyat/parimitis/sheshi ennivayecurichu samagrmay vivar aavashyamund.
ori: tenu, vibhinna uddeshya yepariki kamand anychal bikash, adhithika anychalguthikare mrittika sanrakshan, dharaniya krushi, jawaya parichakana, avakshait bhoomir punaruddhar, ityadi nimanthe mrittika sambal tatha ehar kshamta/simittha/ samarthya upare bapak tatha aavashyak .
pan: ish karke miti di rasad-paani baare vyapak jankari ate us di sambhavaana/hadabandia/samarthanva di lod, kai udesh lai hai jiven ki almand arie develpamant , miti di sambhaal casement aria de vich, tikau khetibari, jal vibhaajak, kaya kalp karna buri zamin di adi I
tam: eneway, anaisutt bakuti mambadu, nirphitipup bakudikasil manwalub bhadukafu, valangunda whelanmay, nirthengu nile melanmay, chitaivurds nilangans meeteduttal bonthe palveru nokanglukkak man valangs kuritm avadhqin adddel/varampues/diddns kuritm mughaumayana takhaval devipadukintu.
tel: kabatti, bhu vanarulu mariyu vat samarthya/parimitulu/samarthatal gurinchin samagr samachar anedi aa praant abhivruddhi, parivatik prantallo nail sanrakshan, susthir vyavasayam, parivatik nirvahan, kshininchin bhoomul punaruddharan modalgunatuvanti vividh prayojnal nimitta avasaramvutundi.
urd: lahza, mitti ke jaria or in kii istaadaad/rukawaton/salaahiton par jamaa malomat kii mukhtalf muqaasid ke liye zarurat hai, jese command aria kii tarakkee, abugiri ilaakon main mitti kaa tohfiz, paidaar zarazzat, fasal aab kaa intazaam, tanzl shudaa arazyat kii baaziafat, vagairah.
eng: Therefore, comprehensive information on soil resources, and their potential/limitations/capabilities, is required for a variety of purposes such as command area development, soil conservation in catchment areas, sustainable agriculture, watershed management, reclamation of degraded lands, etc.

ben: masachusetser halyoke-e wai.em.si.e (america) dwara 1895-e william ji. margyan bhalibal khelati udbhavan karen.
guj: volibolni ramatani shodh 1895na varshma holyok, messchyusetus vaaya.em.sii.e.(yu.es.e.)na wiliam ji. morgan dwara thai hati.
hin: wollyboul kaa khel 1895 main wiliam ji. morgan ne holio, masochusets ke vaai.em.si.e. (you.es.e.) main avishkaar kiya tha.
kan: valiball aatvannu 1895ralli william ji. morgan masachusetsn holyoknalli vai.em.si.e.y mukhen (you.es.e.) parichaisidru.
mal: masachusetile (yu.es.e.) holiokil 1895 l villym ji. morgan volibol end kaayikavinoda contupitichot.
ori: bhalival khelti lingam ji. morgannk dra 1895 masihare i.em.si.e. (yuktrastra america) nikatare thiva masachusetsr holiok thare udbhavita hoithila .
pan: walibal de khed di khoj, 1895 vich william ji. margon ne holiok, maschustats de wiemsia (you. asa. e.) vich keeti |
tam: walibal vilyaddu 1985aam antu masachusetts maanil holyokevil ull ohemsie-will (america) william ji. margan enbawaral khandubhiticopattatu.
tel: 1985 lo holyok, masachyusets loni vaiensie (yu ass e) lo william ji morgan valiball atenu kanipettar.
urd: wali bal kaa khel william ji morgan ne suun 1895 main mesochostis ke holiva main wai em si aye (yu es aye) main ajjad kiya tha.
eng: The game of Volleyball was invented by William G. Morgan in the year 1895 in Holyoke, Massachusetts by YMCA (USA).

ben: dushan vruddhir udvegajanak harer karna, grher janya yaara praia ek-titiyansh oxygen upadan kare tader sanrakshan kara aavashyak.
guj: vadhi rahelam pradushanna chintajanak darne jotaan, e jaruri che ke aapne aa grah mate lagbhag ek-tritiyansh pranavayu sarjanaranu rakshan karie.
hin: pradooshan jis khatarnaak dar se bad rahaa he, usamen jaruri he ki ham us cheez kaa sangrakshan karen jo is grah par oxigen ke lagbhag ek-tihaai bhaag kaa utpaadan karata he.
kan: apayasuchak pramandalli malinya hechagtirodrind, naavu bhoomigagi andaju moorne ondu bhagadashtu aamlajanakavann yavudu utpadista idyo ader sanrakshane madbekirodu atyagatyavagide.
mal: varddhitchuvarunn malinikarantine bhayanakmay nirkkurecunokumpol i grahattin vende oxijnte etand munnilone utpadippikkunn onnin sanrakshicook ennat sarvvapradhana.
ori: yebhali udhvegajanaka matrare pradushan badichalithi, eha khuv jaruri ye yie grahati pin motamoti eka tritiansh amrjan utpadan karithaye, aame tahar sanrakshan kariva.
pan: vadhade pradushna de haal dekhade hoe, ih zaroori hai ki aseen us nuun bachaye jo ish graha de lai lagaing ik tihaai hise de oxijan di sirjana karada hai
tam: abhayakaramak adhikartvarum mashubattin karanmak, bhumikut devaiyana axjanil kiddattatt moonil woru bankin urbhatti sayes ondayp bhadukakk wandiadu migaum avasium.
tel: pramadakar sthilo kalushya perugutonn tarunulo, mana i bhumiki ande pranavayulo mudav vantu utpatti chestunn danini sanrakshinchada anto avasaram.
urd: badhati hui aaludagi kii pareshaan kin shrahon ke pesh nazar, ye zaroori hai ki hum is cheez to ko mahfuz rakhen jo jameen ke liye kam va besh ek tahai oxygen paida krati hai.
eng: Given the alarming rates of increasing pollution, it's essential that we conserve what produces roughly one-third of the oxygen for the planet.

ben: naagarikder digital najardari aota rakha evan baak shwadhinota prabal simavaddhata aroper madhyam maanvadhikar langhan karaar karna iti goshthi dwara vapkbhave samalochit has ei inti.
guj: ai.ti. samudaayo dwara aa kaayadaano vyapak virodh karaayo hato kaaran ke te nagarikone digital japta hethal mukine ane vaani swatantryane atyant maryadit karine manav adhikarono bhang kare che.
hin: ai.tii. samudaayon ne is kanoon kii vyapak rup se aalochana kii kyonki yah nagarikon kii digital nigaraanee karke or abhivyakti kii swatantraaa ko gambhir rup se simit karke maanav adhikaron kaa ulanghan karata he.
kan: i kanoonu nagarikarnnu digital kangavalinalliduv mattu walk swatantryavannu fivravagi nirbandhisuv moolak maanav hakkugainnu ullanghisuttadeyaddarind idu i.ti. samudayagalind vyapakavad tikegolgayitu.
mal: paranare digital nirikshanttinu vidheyamakiyu abhiprayaprakatnattinull swatantryam kർshanmai niyantrichu manushyavkashas lamghikunnatiൻre peryൽ ai.ti. samudayas i niyamatte vyapakmai vimarshichirunnu.
ori: ukt intiku aai.ti. samudangudik dra bapak bhavare samalochana karayaithila, yehetu eha nagarikamananku dejital nirikshan adhinare rakhi tatha bak sdhintaku tibr bhavare simit kari manavadhikarar ullangghan karshani .
pan: kannun di ai ti bhichara duara vyapak for 'te aalochna keeti gai see kiunki ih nagariks nuun digital nigrani heth rakh ke ate bhashn di azaadi nuun buri tarhaa simat karke harman adhikars di ulangana karada hai|
tam: indech sattam gutimales digitale ganganipuku udbaduty pechu sudndrattike gatumiagak kadduppadudhy manit urimikhal mirukintu endu gutai iti samukak kulukas itsp paravalak vimarchittana.
tel: paurul digital nighalo pettada mariyu walk swatantryanni kathinanga nishedhinchada dwara manav hakkul ullanghistunn karnanga i chatta aity vargal chet vistrutanga vyatikarekinchabadindi.
urd: is kanoon ko aai tii birdariyon kii taraf se bade paimaane par tanqid kaa nishana banaaya gaya tha kyonki ye shaharyon ko degetal nigranee main rakh kar or izhaar ray kii aazadi ko shadid tuur par mahadood karke insaani haquk kii pamali kurta hai.
eng: The law was widely criticised by IT communities as it violates human rights by putting citizens under digital surveillance and severely restricting freedom of speech.

ben: ganti belgium, bulgaria, hungary, yuktrajya, turask, albania, saipras, serbia o mantinegro, sweden o germany thek 12 paenter 10ta set sah 230 paent pa, evan bivinn desh, visesh kare grice, ekati jamati hit gane parint hayesil.
guj: geetne 230 points malyan sathe 12 pointsna 10 set belgium, balgeria, hungary, dha united kingdom, turki, albania, saipras, serbia and montanegro, sweden ane germanythi malyan; ane vividh desho, khas karine grisma tene tvarit safalta mali.
hin: belgium, bulgaria, hungary, united kingdom, albania, cyprus, srbija or montenegro, sweden, or germany se 12 ankon ke das seton ke saath geet ko 230 ank mili or yah vibhinn deshon main bhi, vishesh rup se greece main, zabardast rup se safal rahaa.
kan: i hadu belzeum, balgeria, hangeri, united kingdom, turkey, albeni, saipras, sarbij & montenigro, sweaden mattu germaniind 12 ankagal 10 settugalondige 230 ankaganannu padeyuudar jotege, vividh deshgamalli, visheshwagi greeshnalli bharjari yashassu garisitu.
mal: beljium, balgaria, hangary, unitod king, tarki, albenia, cypress, serbia and mondenegro, sweden, jarmani ennivitolilninn 12 pointulute 10 setukalumai i gana 230 pointul netukyu vividh rajyas, visheshich grisil, oru takർppൻ vijayamaithirukayu cheitu.
ori: ehi geethati 230 paent pithila yeunthire 12 paent vishist 10ti set belajiyam, bulgeria, hungary, briten, turki, alvania, cypras, sarvia o mantenegro, sden eban germaneeru missithila, eban annga deshamanankare madhya khuv lokapriya hoithila, visheshkari greesre.
pan: git nuun belgium, bulgaria, hungary, united kingdom, turaki, albania, cyprus, sarabia ate motonegron, swedens ate germany ton 12 points de 10 sits de naal 230 ank mile ate bakh bakh deshs, khaas karke greece vich ve ik samesh hit ban gya|
tam: indep patal 230 pullixp bellntu, itel belgium, palgarea, hangeri, ikiya rajgium, duruggi, albenia, cyprus, serpeya & mantinegro, sweden, germanyil aakhiya nadugalilrundhu kidaitt tala 12 pulligus kont 10 dokuppuelum atankum, melum itu kurippak kiris ullitt palveru nadugalil maperum vellqib paatalaqat digahandatu.
tel: i pat 230 points andukunnadi, andulo 12 points choppun 10 sett belzeum, balgeria, hungary, united kingdam, terki, albania, sypras, sarbia mariyu montenegro, sweden, mariyu germany nudi pondi vividh deshals, mukhyanga griculo pedd vijaya sadhinchindi.
urd: is gane ne belgiam, bulgaria, hungary, bartanya, turki, albanian, kabers, srbija or monti negro, sweden or germany se 230 points ke 10 seton ke saath 12 points haasil kiye or mukhtalf mamalik balkhsus unan main bhi dhooma machaa di.
eng: The song received 230 points with 10 sets of 12 points from Belgium, Bulgaria, Hungary, the United Kingdom, Turkey, Albania, Cyprus, Serbia & Montenegro, Sweden, and Germany and also became a smash hit in different countries, especially in Greece.
