ben: tai ajker ei upalakshye aami sara vishwer sansader mukhya aadhikarikder ekati pakapokt kajer parikalpana tiri karaar janya sakriya bhumika paalan karte balab ya janaganak pratikrear centre rakhe yate sakaler janya aro nyaisangat evan statesthapak falaphal arjan kara ya evan sansadgulike era caryakar vastawayaner janya gananamulak bhumika paalan karte have.
guj: tethi, aaje aa prasange, hun vishwabharani sansadona pramukh adhikarione ek nakkar kaarya yojanana ghadtar mate sakriya bhumika bhajvavaa mate aahvan karu chhu je loko mate vadhu nyayi ane state sthapak prenamo prapth karva matena pratibhavna kendrama che ane tena asarkarak amalikaran mate sansadoe rachnatmak bhumika bhajvavi padashe.
hin: adhik nyaaysangat or sabhi ke liye shashakt parinaam paane ke liye, main puure sansar kii sansadon ke peethasin adhikariyon se ek aisi thos kaary-yojana banane main agrim rup se sakriy bhoomika nibhaane anurodh karata hoon jo ki logon ko pratikriya ke centre main rakhti he, tathaa is yojana ke asarkaari karyanvayan ko sunishchit karneke liye sansadon ko ek rachanaatmak bhoomika nibhaani padegi.
kan: addarind, indu i sanderbhadalli, naanu vishwadadyantad sansattugal adhyaksharu, saklarigu innashtu nyayavad hagu statisthapakavad falitanshgainnu sadhisalu generannu spandaneya kendradallirisuv vastavik kriya yojaneyondannu roopisuvalli sakriya patravannu vahisabekendu kare nidlu bayasuttene mattu idu prenamkariagee kaaryagatvaguvudannu khatarigolisuvalli sansattugalu rachnatmak patravannu nirvahisabekaguttade.
mal: atinaൽ i avasaratiൽ, kututൽ tulyathyultu matresൾ uൾkkolluvaൻ sheshiyulatumay falangൾ ellavർku neduvanutakunnatu janae kendrasthanatuniർttunnatumay oru muർttama pravർttanapaddhati roopikarikunnatiൽ sakriyamay oru pank vahicnamennu, attarmoru padmati karyakshamamai natappilakkunnatiൽ paർlameൻrukൾ niർmanathmakamay pank vahicnamennu locatutanilamulla paർlameൻrukalute adhyakshൻare naൻ udbodhippikunnu.
ori: tenu, aajir ehi avasarare, mun samagra vishra sansadgurikar pittasin adhikareemananku epari gotie thos karyan yojana present karivare sakriya bhoomika grahan karivaku aahn karuni, yahaki samasthank pin adhik nyaochit tatha sbhavik falafal hasal kariva pin lokamananku kendrare rakhib eban sansadgudiku ehar fatprad karyankaritha sunishchit karivare eka gananamutak bhoomika grahan karivaku padib .
pan: lihaaza ish muka te awj mai vishva bhar di sansdas de pradhani afasaraan nuun kahina haa ki oh ange aa ke ik thos yojna banaun jo locals de duwale hoo ke sabh lai barabar te lachakile natije kaun ate sansdas nuun us di safal tamil lai usaru bhumika nibhaani pavegi I
tam: agave, indu naan indech chandarpattil ulakengum ull paralumangangalin talamap potupu vaqibvarluku araikuval vidudhu anivrukkum adhikach samatvamum urudi kont balangana adaivadaikak tiru natwatikyil makas maiyabbangu vakikum woru didaman seyaltitats vativipatil munipagab bangu kollumaru gattukkoll virumbukiheen, melum paralumaningas itityatait diumayagach seyalbadudhuwatil ore acgapurvamana bangu vakikk wants enllum gattukkolkiheen.
tel: kabatti, i sandarbhanga iroju, andriki marint nishpatpakshamin mariyu statesthapak prinamas sadhinchi pettenduku pratispandanalo prajaln pradhananga bhavinchi, nirdisht karyacharan roopondinchadalo kriyashil patra poshinchalani prapanchavyaptanga unn parliaments sabhadhyakshaul, alage sardhakanga danini amalu cheyadao shasansabhalu nirmanatmak patra vahinchalani nenu pilupunivvadalichanu.
urd: isi liye, is mauqaa par aaj, main puri duniya kii parlimanon ke nagaraan afasaran se mataliba karna chahata huun ki wo ek thos amali mansuba vazaa karne main fial kirdaar adaa karen jo avaam ko raspance ke marcuz main rakhata hai taaki sab ke liye zyaada muneefaana or lachakadar natise haasil kiye jaa saken or is ke nafaaz ko yaqini banane main parlimanon ko ek tamiri kirdaar adaa karna hoga.
eng: Hence, on this occasion today, I would like to call upon the Presiding Officers of the Parliaments across the world to play a proactive role in formulating a concrete action plan that puts people at the centre of the response to achieve more equitable and resilient outcomes for all and Parliaments will have to play a constructive role in ensuring its effective implementation.

ben: gathar sambhavat sabthek gurutvapurna shlok, adhya 45, shlok na. 8, yekhane shesh percent nabi jarathushtra tar manashchakshute sarvashaktimaan swaung ishwark upalvdhi karen, yeti anuvarti hisabe manabjatir anusarnian shubh chinta, shubh shabd evan shubh karm nie shubh traiti satyer path rupe pravaratet hayes.
guj: gathaoni kadaaya sauthi agatyani panktio, prakaran 45, pankti 8maa, upadeshak jharthrusht chhevate potana manchakshuma sarvashaktimaan eshwarne dharan kare che, jena anusandhane sara vichaaro, sara shabdo ane sara caryoni trewarisne satyana marg tarike niche lavavama aave che je manavjate anusaravaano che.
hin: shaayad gaathaon ke sabase mahatvapurn padya, adhyay 45, padya 8 main paigambar zarathustra ne antat sarvashaktimaan ishwar ko apane man kii ankhon se mahasoos kiya, jiske baad achche vichaar, achche shabd or achche karm kaa pavitra tritv sthapit kiya jo sachai kaa maarg tha jiskaa maanav jati ko paalan karnaa chahie.
kan: prayashah gaathagatalli atyant mahattvad padyavad 45nae adhyayad 8nae padyadalli, pravadi jaratushtrnu conegu sarvashaktnad bhagwantnannu tann managachakshuwinind ariyalu sadhayvaguttade, adkke anusarvagi uttam chintanegalu, uttam matugalu mattu uttam kaaryagalemb punya trayavu manavkulavu anusarisabekad satyad margavagi nirupitwagide.
mal: oruvel, gathakalile et pradhanpat, addhyayam 45 le etta padyattil jaratushtra pravacan otuil sarvashaktanay daivatte manakkannucond anubhavikanavukyu atettutr manushyarashi pintuterent, nall chintakalutayu nall wakkulutayu, nall pravrittikalutayu, vishuddhtritva end satyattiൻre way nirddeshippetukayu cheiyunnu.
ori: 'gaathas' r sambhavatah sabutharu adhik guruthpurna pad, adhan 45, pad 8 re, mahapurush jarathushtra sheshre sarvashakthimaan eeshranku nij manas chakshure prattaksh anubhava karivaku pivanthi, yaha anuyani, uttam bichaar, uttam shabda eban uttam karm prabhruti 'pavitra trith'ku sater marg bhavare nirddist karayaishi yahaki manavajathiku anusaran karibar ajji .
pan: shaaid gathaavaan vichon sabh ton mahatavpuuran pad, adhiai 45, pad 8 vich paigamber jarstharu ne sarav shaktiman rab nuun aapne man dis awkhan naal mahisus kita, jise magron change vichar, change shabad ate change karam di holi trinity sthapit keeti, jo sachai da marg see, jisdi manukh jaati nuun palana karni chahidi hai|
tam: anekamak katin mik mukhiaman vasanamagak karudapatum 45aam attiyayatin 8aavatu vasanatil, tirxrisiana jartustra irutiyag ellam vall iraivanai tanatu manakkannal kankizar, adait doderndu nallennam, nalvaku, naqseyals enjh punidhat tritvam manitakultinar pinbhaua wantia satiyap patiyag vkukkapadukintu.
tel: gathalloni 45va aadhyayam, 8va vakyanlo bahushah ati mukhyamin charanulo, jaratushtra pravakt tudaku tan manonetramutho swayanga sarvashaktimantudagu bhagwantudini avagahan chesukogalugutadu, dinini anusarinchi, sadbhavani, parishuddh wakku mariyu satkarmalu ane pavitra moorthitrayanni satyamargamuga manvali anusarinchku vidhinchabadinadi.
urd: shayd guthaun kii sab se ahim aayat, fasal 45, aayat 8 main, paigambar zarathushit ko aakhir car apne zahan kii aankh se khud kudaaye qaatir matalaq ko dekhne kaa mauqaa milataa hai, jis ke mutabik achche afacar, achche alfaaz, or achche emaal kii muqaddas taslis ko sacchai kii raah qaraar diya gaya hai jis par navaa insaani ko amal karna hai.
eng: In perhaps the most important verse in the Gathas, Chapter 45, Verse 8, Prophet Zarathustra finally gets to perceive Almighty God himself with his mind's eye, pursuant to which the Holy Trinity of good thoughts, good words, and good deeds is laid down as the path of truth which mankind is to follow.

ben: 2000-e drambadak dennis chembers (carlos santana, jan maclafalin evan anyanya)-era sang trini rescu record karen evan 2006-e, atithi diese lajic evan keller williams (gitar o base)-era sang tar shyato banaras muktiprapth has.
guj: 2000maa tene drumar denis chembers (charlos santaana, jhon makalaffin ane anaya) sathe maline rescu record karyu, ane 2006maa tene mahemano dije logic ane kelar williams (guitar ane bejh) ‘shato banaras’ pragate karyu.
hin: 2000 main, dramvadak denis chembers (carlos santana, jon mcloclin, or anya), ke saath usne rescue record kiya, or 2006 main deje logic or keller williams (guitar or baas) ke saath shato banaras kaa vimochan kiya.
kan: 2000dane varshadalli, aat drummar dennis chhembers (carlos santana, jaan meklafin mattitarru) jotegudy ʼreskyuʼvannu dhvanimudrisidru, mattu 2006ralli, aat atithi kalavidrad de.je. lajic mattu keller williamsrondige (guitar mattu bes) ʼshato banarasʼannu bidugade madidru.
mal: 2000 l drammar dennis chembersu(karlos santaan, john mak loglin tutangiawar)maai cheർnn addeha reskyu record cheiyukayu 2006l de.je.lojik keller williamsu (gitaru basu) atithilai 'shato banaras' purattikakkukayu cheitu.
ori: 2000 masihare, se dramar denis chambaras (carlos santana, jan myaklagalin, ityadi) sahit 'resakyu' record karithile eban 2006 re se atithi dije lajik eban kelr likhmsank (guitar eban bas) sahit 'satho benaras' lokarpan karithile.
pan: 2000 vich, usne darmar danise chembers naal reskiu ricard kita (karlos santana, jaan makshaughalin, ate hor ), ate 2006 vich, usne mahimanaas di ail lazik ate cyler villium (guitar ate dhol) naal chito benress nuun jari kita|
tam: avar 2000il truhmar tennis sembarsuden (carlos sandana, jaan meglaflin manllum anioruton) serndu reskiue isaiy patiu seydar, melum 2006il virundinars dije lajic manllum keller williamsuton (kitar manllum base) serndu satto banarasai velitar.
tel: 2000lo, atanu drums wadak dennis chembers (carlos santana, john mex laflin, taditrulu) to kalisi reskyu ni ricard chesad, mariyu 2006lo, atithulu dige lajik mariyu callar williams (gitar and bass) to kalisi chatau banaras vidudal chesar.
urd: 2000 main, is ne drumar denis chemburz (carlos santana, jaan make laafalan, or al) ke saath riskiyo record kiya, or 2006 main, is ne mehmanon dee jai logic or kiler williamz (gutar or bees) ke saath chetto banaras reliz kiya.
eng: In 2000, he recorded Rescue with drummer Dennis Chambers (Carlos Santana, John McLaughlin, et al.), and in 2006, he released Chateau Benares with guests DJ Logic and Keller Williams (guitar and bass).

ben: 2009-era 2ra julyer ag yatdin na delhi hai court icchuk prapthyaskader madhye sammathimulak vyaktigat yaun carboke aparadhamulak naya baleni, british aupaniveshik sarkar dwara pass karano 150 bashwar purano bhartiya dandabidhi (aai.pi.si) iner aspast 377 dhara vyakhya anusar samkamita aparaadh bale vivechit hat.
guj: delhi uchch nyayalaye be pukhto vachchena parasper sanmati sathena khaangi jaatiya sambandhone 2 july 2009na roj gunani vyakhyamathi bahar mukya, tyaan sudhi bhartiya dand samhita (ai.pe.sii.)ni british vasaahati sarkaar dwara pasaar karvama aavela kaayadaani 150 varsh juni kalam 377na aspasht arthaton hethal samalangikataane gunahit ganavama aavati hati.
hin: 150 saal puraane bhartiya dand samhita (ai.pi.si.) kii aspasht dhara 377 kii vyakhya ke anusaar british aupniveshik sarkaar dwaara paarit ek kanoon ke tahat samalangikta ko tab tak ek aparaadh ke rup main dekha jaataa rahaa, jab tak ki 2 july 2009 ko dilli ucch nyaayalay ne sahmati se vayaskon ke bich nijee yon krityon ko aparaadh kii shrenee se baahar nahin kar diya.
kan: 2009r july 2randu dehlia ucch nyayalayavu sahmatvull vayaskar naduvan paraspar oppigeiruv khasagi lingik kriyegalu aparadhvallavendu parigrahisuvavarege, british vasahatu sarkaarvu xarige tandidd 150 varsh haleya bhartiya dand samhiteya (i.pi.si.) aspashtvad kalam 377r vyakhyanagal prakaar salingakamavu aparadhvendu pariganitvagittu.
mal: 2009 july 2l delhi hyotati parasparasammatattoteull prayapurtiyayavarkidile swakaryalingikapravrittika criminal kutmallateyakuvare, british colonial sarkar passakia 150varsha pankkamulla indian penal kodi (ai.pi.si)nte rantutiൽ vyakhyaniavunn vakup 377nte vishdikaranailanusrich swavarggalingikat kutakarmai kanakkackapettirunnu.
ori: prapth batskank sahamathi aadharit brekthigat yun kriagudiku delhi hicort 2 july 2009re aparaadh bahirbhoot kariva poorvaru, upaniveshabadi british sarkarnk dra gruhith eka ine, 150 barshar puruna bharatiya pinggal code (aai.pi.si.)r aspast dhara-377r bakhya anusaare samalingi yun-sampark aparaadh boli bivechit heuthila.
pan: jadon tak dilli haai court ne 2 july 2009 nuun sahimati den wale balgas wichkaar sahimat niji jinsi karwaia nuun gair-apradhak nahi banaya, tad tak bartania bastivadi sarkaar duara 150 saal purana paas kite ik kanun bharati dand sanhita di aspasht dhaara 377 di vyakhya anusaar samlingakta apraadhik manni jandi see|
tam: delhi uir neetimanram 2 july 2009 andu vayaduvandor itieyana suyasammadap balupuch seyalbadugans kuraimanrowai endu anavikkum varai orincherky kuriamagak karudappattatu, itu british kalanituv arasal 150 varudaluku munbu bisspicoppatt india tandana sattatin (ipico) telivachuchu 377aam brivin villckapati amaindrundatu.
tel: sammathinchin vayojanul madhya ekabhiprayanto chese vyaktigat langik charyal delhi unnat nyayasthana 2009 july 2na chattabaddha chesent varaku, british valas prabhutvan aamodinchin chattamain 150 els bhartiya shikshasmriti (apisi) loni sandigdh sekshan 377 vivranal prakara swalingasamparka anedi neranga pariganinchabadedi.
urd: jab tak dahali hai court ne 2 julai 2009 ko razaamand baligon ke mabin razaamandi se nijee jinsi afial ko kanoonee qaraar naheen diya, tab tak hum jins prasti ko 150 saala indian panel code (aai pii si) kii mubaham dafaa 377 kii tashrihaat ke tuur par mujrmana faal samajha jataa tha, ye kanoon bartanvi noabaadati hukuumat ke jaria manzoor kiya gaya tha.
eng: Until the Delhi High Court decriminalised consensual private sexual acts between consenting adults on 2 July 2009, homosexuality was considered criminal as per interpretations of the ambiguous Section 377 of the 150-year-old Indian Penal Code (IPC), a law passed by the British colonial government.

ben: february 2006-e pratham vastavayit rashtriya gramin rojgar garanti ine (in.aar.i.ji.e)-ti vishal safalya vapkbhave swikrut.
guj: te vyapkpne janitu che ke kendriya gramin rozgar banhedhari adhinium (narega) je pahelivar february 2006maa amalma mukaayo hato, te bhavy saphal thayo che.

kan: 2006r febravarialli modal baarige xarigolislad rashtriya gramin udyog khatari kaydeyu (narega) amoghvagi yashasviagide embudannu vyapakwagi angikarislagide.

ori: eha bapak bhavare scar karayaaye ye 2006 masiha february maasare prathame karyankaari hoithiva rastriya grameen rojagar garenti adhinium ('narega') eka vishal safamta hoiasichhi .
pan: ih mannia-paramnia gya hai ki nesnal rural emploament garanti act (in.aar.i.g.aa) jo ki farvari 2006 vich lagu hoia see, ik shaandaar kamyaabi hai I
tam: mudanmudalil 2006 fibruariil natamuriku vant desiya urak velai urudich sattam (narekha) maperum vederiyag amaindatu enab paravalak attrukkollpadukintu.

eng: It is widely acknowledged that the National Rural Employment Guarantee Act (NREGA) first implemented in February 2006, has been a magnificent success.

ben: jaler gunagat manake prabhavit kara pradhan vishanguli halo bhasman poly, shibal, rasyanik samuh, dravibhuth jaiv upadan (de.o.em), ushna nishkashan, jalaj sanwahantantrik karkhana, pathogen evan tilraji.
guj: jalni gunavattane asarkarta mukhya paribalo che: sthagit thayelo kaanp, sheval, rasayano, ogli gayela sajiv padartho, thermal muktio, jaliya vescular vanaspatio, jivanuo ane tel.
hin: pani kii gunvattta ko prabhavit karne vaale pramukh kaarak hai nilambit talachat, shaiwal, rasayan, ghule hue jaivik padaarth (di.o.em.), thermal release, jaleey sanvahani padap, rogaanu, or tel.
kan: teladuv kalmashagalu, pachi, rasayanikagalu, kargiruv savyav paxarwagalu (de.o.em.), ushniya bidugadegalu, nirinlli beleyuv naissyagalu, rogkarakgalu, mattu tailagalu nirin gunamttad mele prenam biruttiruv pramukh anshagalagive.
mal: potaikitekunn kharapadartha kanikal, algakal, rasavastukal, layitchu chernna organic vastukal (de.o.e.), termal relisul, vaskular jalasasyas, patojenul, endkal enniva jalattine gunnilvarate badhikkunn pradhan ghankas.
ori: jaher gunavattaku prabhavita karuthiva mukhya karakagudik hela bhasaman kada kanika, shaival, rasarhnic paxarwa, draveebhut jaivik paxarwa (de.o.em.), tapiya nirgman, janj sanbahi udbhidha, rogaanu, eban tail .
pan: mouth kark jo paani de ranga- fung vich badlao lyande han, oh han sathagit hoi talajet, kaayi, rasayan padarth, dizolwad metar(DOM), thermal relies, jal naadi de paude,rogajanak padarth ate tel I
tam: tannirin druttap badikum mukiyak karnikalil mithkum wandel, pasi, rasayanas, karaint karimab porul (dioem), webbp welipadus, nirval kujaldavarangs, noikrumies, annaies akhiyawe atankum.
tel: niti nanyatanu prabhavita chese pradhan anshalu emitante, velade avakshepal, shaivalalu, rasayanal, karigin sendriya paxartha (deoe), ushn vidudala, jal vatika kanajala gal mokkal, vyadhi karkal mariyu nunes.
urd: pani ke mayar par asar andaz hone waale bade awamil malluk rasubat, tahalib, camyavi ashya, tahalil shudaa namyati maadaa (dee oo em), haraarati ikhraaj, aabi uroki pauddi, pathojan or tel hain.
eng: Major factors affecting water quality are suspended sediments, algae, chemicals, dissolved organic matter (DOM), thermal releases, aquatic vascular plants, pathogens, and oils.

ben: 1923 saler kampton prabhava aro najir pradaan kare ye visesh aapkshikta khat fotan-electron viksheper samay ekati kanar barnanar kshetre.
guj: 1923ni compton asare vadhu purawa puura padya ke photon-electron vikheravama kanna varnanana aa kissama vishisht sapekshawad laagu pade che.
hin: 1923 ke compton prabhaav ne or adhik sakshya prastut kiye ki vishisht aapekshikta vastav main lagu hoti he, is maamle main photon-electron ke bikharane ke kan ke vivaran par.
kan: 1923ralli kompton prenamvu, visesh sapekshateyu, i sanderbhadalli photon-electron chaduruvikeya kanad vivarnege, khanditwagiu anvayvaguttade embudakke hchin puraveyannu odagisitu.
mal: pratyek aapekshikat thiർchchayayu badhakamaumennatin, i sandർbhattiൽ photoൺ-electroൺ scatoringiൻre paർttikiൾ discripshan badhakamaumennatin, 1923le comptൺ prabhava kututൽ telivukൾ naൽki.
ori: 1923 masihar 'kamptan prabhab' ehi kshetrare vishesh aapekshikata fotan-elactran bichchuranar kanika sankrantiya varnana kshetrare lagu hoithaye boli adhik praman pradaan karithila .
pan: 1923 de kampatan prabhav ne hor saboot uplabadh karwaaye ki vishesh mapekhata nuun photone-electron khinda de partical jaaa kanas nuun varnan de maamle vich lagu nahi kita janda|
tam: indech chandarpattil oli-minnenuch chitarol kuritt tugas ritiyana vivkkaduku visesh charpial porundhum enpathangu 1923 kampton vilaivu melum sandugans valangiyadu.
tel: photan-electron parikshepa chenddanni, i vishyanlo, ock kan varnanalo,1923 nati krampton prabhavan pratyek sapekshat vartistundandaniki marint aadhara andinchindi.
urd: 1923 ke compton asar ne is baat ke majid shivahad mahiya kiye hain ki khasusi azaafait lagu hoti hai, is soorat main photone-electron bikhraao ke ek zarre kii tafsil ke liye.
eng: The Compton effect of 1923 provided more evidence that special relativity does apply, in this case to a particle description of photon-electron scattering.

kan: bheti niduvavarige ut-vasati kalpisuv, mahithiannu odagisuv mattu margadarshi sahit pravasgainnu aayojisuv saluvagi i vyapaar sansthey aashrayadalli, anek pravasi mandiragalu, vishrantidhamagalu mattu hotelugalu halvaaru pravasi tanagamalli kaaryanirvahisuttve.

ori: nigamar sahatare, parywakamananku rahani subidha pradaan kariva sahit suchana pradaan eban guidmanank sahatare parichalit bhramanar aajojan kariva nimanthe, anek paryletak grih, resourt o hotel vibhinna paryaton sthalre karyan karuni.
pan: carporasion de agavai heth, bohut saare sailaani ghar, resort ate hotal kai sair-sapata cits ton sailania nuun anukulit karan ate gaided tour da prabandh karan lai com karade han|
tam: intak kangatin meghbarvail, bhayanis tanguvathekum takhaval taruvatajkum valiqattyuten suharippark arbadu seyvathekum erauman bhayanier vidutis, oyvagangs manllum hotels pal subarulat dalankalil seyalpadukindena.
tel: i sansth sanrakshanlo, anek paryatak nivasal, resortulu mariyu hotels paryatkulku vasati kalpinchatanii mariyu samachar andinchatanii, margdarshakudito saha paryavana erpat cheyatanii kuda anek paryatak sthalal nudi panichestai.
urd: corporation ke zer ahtamam matadad siyaahti mukaamat se siyaahon ke qayaam or malomat faraham karne or guydid torika intazaam karne ke liye bahut se siyaahti ghar , resorts or hotel kaam karte hain.
eng: Under the aegis of the corporation, a number of tourist homes, resorts, and hotels operate from several tourist sites to accommodate visitors and provide information and also arrange guided tours.

ben: echadao, niramikari prayog chada tejascrian isotopty vyabaharkale tejascrintar conorkam anicchakrit vimukthi ghata atkate setic kono aparishodhanian avastha roopantarit kare nite have.
guj: vadhuma, upacharatmak amalikarane bad kartaan, redioisotopane jhami n shake tevaan swarupama roopantarit karvanu che, jethi tena upayog daramiyaan kiranotsarg ajanta pan prasarit n thai.
hin: iske saath, upachaaratmak prayogon ke alaava, vikiran samasthanik ko gaiyr-nikshaalaneey rup main parivartit kiya janaa chahie jisase iske prayog ke dauraan anbhipret radioactivity kaa utsarjan na ho.
kan: ishte allade, chikitsakavad badkegainnu horatupadisi, radioisotopannu ader badkeyaguvag yavude anuddishtvad vikiran bidugadeyagad hage yavudar moolkavu osaralagadanth rupakke parivartisbeku.
mal: matramall, chikitsayute aavashyaskulla prayogstee matiniർttiyaൽ, upyogikunn samayt apratikshitmai radio aktivity prasariateirikanvendi radio aisotoppine licchu cheiyan patatt rupatti parivartyppikka.
ori: punashch, chikitsatmak prajogagudiku baad dei, redioisotapku eka an-nikshaianiya roopaku roopantharita karayibar thae yaha falreki ehar bbbahar samaure kaunsi anicchakrit bikiranjanit nirgman ghatib naahin .
pan: hor ange ilaaj di varton nuun chad ke, radioscope nuun ik non-liecabel roop vich tabdil kar ditaa janda hai taaki galti naal koi radeoactivity naa nikal jeee prayog de vele I
tam: melum, sikichikana payangana oduggiwittup parttal, ind katriyakk oraghat tanimattap payanbaduttum podhu taesseyalak katirvichu veliyavatait tavirck attap bosivale vativatingu majochu wandyatum irukkum.
tel: inca, chikitsaparamin upayogas kakunda, radioesotop danini vineoginche samayaulo anukokunda radiodharmikat vidudal kakunda unddaniki danini chochchukupoleni rupanloki marustar.
urd: majid baran, ilaaj ke italaaqat se qataa nazar, radio isotope ko gair turviq pazeer shukla main tabdel karna hota hai taaki is ke istemaal ke dauraan tabikari kaa koi gair iradi ikhraaj na hojay.
eng: Further, excluding the therapeutic applications, the radioisotope is to be converted to a non-leachable form so that no inadvertent release of radioactivity occurs during its use.

ben: upasana athva prarthanar sthaner nirikhe, kapitayane sangar paribhashatio vyabhhar karellen wallysongo, ya hindutva athva buddha dharmer alokachata baa murthy parivarte shung hang tayar pratikswarup dewale ekati khali gart sah ek char-chatushkon sthapatyer pratinidhitva kare.
guj: puja ke prarthana sthalo mate valisongo kapitayanma sanggar shabdano upayog kare che, je ek char-chatushkon dharavati imaarat che, jema teni diwal par ek khaali kaanu che, je kapitayanma sang hyang tayanu prateek ganavayu che, je hindu ke bauddha dharmany jem arkaa ke murtio nathi.
hin: kapitayan main, valisongon ne "sanger" naam kaa upyog puja yaa prarthana ke sthanon ke liye bhi kiya he jo, hindu dharm yaa buddha dharm main arka yaa murtiyon ke vipareet, kapitayan main sang hyang taaya ke pratik ke rup main isaki diwaar main ek khaali suraakh ke saath ek chaar-vargi bhawan kaa pratinidhitiv karata he.
kan: valisongovu pooje athwa parthana sthalgal sambandhawagi kapitayannallin sangar emb padavannu upayogisuttade, idu kapitayannallin san hang tayad sanketavagi khali kindiannull godeannu hondiruv nalku chowkagal kattanavondannu pratinidhisuttade, hindus athwa bauddhadharmadalliruvante moorthi athwa pratimegalannall.
mal: aradhanakko prartthanyko ull itas end nilek kapitayan sampradayattil sanggar end shabda valisongo upyogicumpol artthamakkunnat, hindumatattilo buddhamatattilo ull aർkayo pratimkalo all, marich, kapitayanile sang hyang tayaute pratikamitull kaliay dwar chuvarilull nal chaturulla kettitetea.
ori: upasana ava prarthana sthangar katha dekhile, lisongo madhya kapithainre 'sangar' shabdar bbbahar karanthi, yaha eka vargakar attalikar pratinidhith karithaye yaahaar kanthare kapithainre 'sang hang taya'r prateeka bhave eka khali gahr rahithae, yaha hindu dharma ava buddha dharmare thiva arq kimba moortisabu tharu bhinna.
pan: puja jaaa prarthana de sthalaas de sandrabh vich,valesongo, kapitayan vich sanggar shabad da prayog karade han, jo ki char-vargi imarat darsounda hai jise di kandh vich khaali mori hai jo kapitayan vich sang hayang taia da chinh hai naame ki hindus jaaa buddha dharam di arka jaaa murtia I
tam: valaibhattu alltu brarthanait dalangalap boduddhavarai, kapidhayanil sangar enjh chollai vallisango payanbaduddukhirar, itu kapidhayanil sang hiyang dayavin sinnamak vihangum vaqail suaqinil vellru ottai kont woru naanku chaturg kdditatake kurikkintu, hindu alltu pautt madatil ulldu bhondu archcha alltu silelack kontirupadill.
tel: aaradhan leda prarthan sthalal paranga, kapitayan lo, saangar ane padanni kuda valisongo upayogisthar, idi hindus mata leda buddhamttlo madiriga gopuram leda vigrahal kakunda kapitayan loni sang hayang tayaku chihnanga dani godelo ock khali randhra gal nalugu mull chatursr bhavananni suchistundi.
urd: ibaadat yaa dua ke liye jagahon ke lihaaz se, valesango kapityan main sanggar kii istalah bhi istemaal kurta hai, jo is kii diwaar main khaali surakh wali char marabba imarat kii numandagi krati hai jo kapityan main sang haaing tiyaa kii elamat hai, na ki arka yaa majisame kii hindu math yaa budh math kii tarah.
eng: In terms of places for worship or praying, Walisongo also uses the term Sanggar in Kapitayan, which represents a four-square building with an empty hole in its wall as the symbol of Sang Hyang Taya in Kapitayan, not arca or statues as in Hinduism or Buddhism.

ben: 9i september, 2022-era hisabe banker amanath, ek bashwar ager 6.7 shatansher tulana, barshik 16.2 shatansh har drut gatite vruddhi paese.
guj: bank credit ek varsh pahelana 6.7 takani saame september 9, 2022 na roj 16.2 taka vaaya-o-vaaya ni jhadpi gatie vadhe che.
hin: ek saal pehle ke 6.7 pratishat ke mukaable 9 sitambar, 2022 tak bank saakh saal-dar-saal 16.2 pratishat kii twarit gati se viksit hui
kan: bank salvu ondu varshad hinde 6.7 pratishat iddudakke pratiagee, 2022r ceptembar 9r velege, varshadind varshakke 16.2 pratishtadashtu tvarit gatiyalli beleitu.
mal: oru waർsha mumpatte 6.7 shatamanatinetire, waർshancheൾ tammiൽ taratamyam cheayumpoൾ, 2022 septembർ 9 tille kanakanusrich 16.2 shatamantti adhikavegataiൽ bank credit valർnnu.
ori: bank credit september 9, 2022 suddha 16.2 pratishat tushanathmak barshik abhivriddhi bhadi trant begre briddhi pithila, eka barsh tashar 6.7 pratishat tuznare.
pan: ik saal pihals 6.7 percent de ulat hoo ke 9 satmber, 2022 nuun baink da karaj saal bhar saal uddh ke 16.2 percent hoo gya I
tam: vangik gatan iruppu, oranduku mun 6.7 satvikitham irundats opitumbodhu, 9 september 2022 nilavarapati varudavarut valarchiyag 16.2 satvikitham enjh durith vegatil adhikaritlldu.
tel: bank runa september 9, 2022 nati gat edadi 6.7 shataniki badulu thivragathin 16.2 shata sanvatsaraniki sanvatsar vruddhi chendindi.
urd: ek saal kabel 6.7 faisad ke muqaabale, 9 sitambar 2022 ko bank credit main saal ba saal 16.2 faisad kii tej raftaar se azafa hawa hai.
eng: Bank credit grew at an accelerated pace of 16.2 percent y-o-y as on September 9, 2022, as against 6.7 percent a year ago.

ben: ei anchale garh praia 10, 000 millimitre (390 inch) baa taar veshi parimaner uchch vrushtipater haar uchch bhukampin caryakalap evan banyasah bastutantrer janya samasya srushti kare.
guj: aa pradeshma khub varsaad pade che; jeni sarerash lagbhag das hajaar millimitres (390 inch)thi vadhu che, je echosystem mate bhupump pravritti ane poor sahitna prashno sarje che.
hin: is kshetra kii ucch varsha, jo ausatan lagbhag 10,000 millimetre (390 inch) or usase upar he, or uske saath-saath ucch bukampiy gatividhi or baadh, paristhitiki tantra ke liye samasyaayein paidaa karti he.
kan: i pradeshsdalli sarisumaru 10,000 milimiterugaishtu (390 inchugalu) mattu adkkint hechagi suriuv bhaari maleyu ati bhookmpanad kriyegalu mattu pravahgainnu olagondante illin parisar vyavasthege samasyegaiannu sristisuttade.
mal: bhookmpasambandhiyay kudia pravർttanalu wellppokkavu atangia avasvyavasthak i pradeshttiൻre 10000 millimetory(390 inch )ൽ kudia sharashariull uyർnn waർshapaata prashnangൾ srushtiunnu.
ori: anychantir harahaari 10,000 millimetre (390 inch) eban tatodhik uchch bristipat, parisansthati pin samasya srushti karithaye, yaha madhyare uchch sesmik sakriyatha eban banya antarbhukt.
pan: khetra di uch barish, ostan lagabhag 10,000 millimetre (390 inch) ate ish ton uddh, uch bhuchal di gatividhi ate hadaan samet iko-cistum lai saoesyas paidaa kardia han|
tam: sumar 10,000 milli mettre (390 inch) manllum koodudal sarasari alavu kont ibbrandhyatin migudiyana manipobivu uyaralu nilandukk nicklvues manllum vellam ullitt iarrkaichutal prachanl uruvakkukintu.
tel: i prantalo sagatun dadapu 10,000 millimitre (390 angulalu), antaku minchin adhik varshpata, paryavaran vyavasthiki adhik bhucamp charyal, mariyu varadal vanti samasyala kaligistundi.
urd: is ilaka kii zyaada barish, avasatan takreeban 10,000 mili meter (390 inch) yaa is se zyaada, ecosystem ke liye missale paida krati hai jis main aala bhunchali or sailab shamil hain.
eng: The region's high rainfall, averaging around 10,000 millimetres (390 inches) and above, creates problems for the ecosystem including high seismic activity and floods.

ben: gitar ei anshti ek vihbal kara darshaner madhye die shesh has: arjuner hriday traas udrekkari tar divya rup, vishwaroopaer darshan koran krishna.
guj: geetano aa bhag ek prachand darshanma parinme che: krishna arjunane temnu alaukik swaroop, vishwaroop jova de che, je arjunana hridayma bhay felaave che.
hin: gita kaa is bhaag kaa samaapan ek prabal alokik drishy ke saath hota he: krishna arjuna ko apane divya swaroop, vishwaroop, kaa darshan dete hai jisase arjuna ke hriday main bhay utpann ho jaataa he.
kan: geeteya i bhagavu adbhutavaddondu darshanadondige sampannagolluttade: krishnanu tann divyavad vishvaroopavannu arjunanige kanagoduttane, adu arjunan hridyadalli bhayavannu huttisuttade.
mal: gitute i bhaga athishaktamay oru daർshanttotea avasanikkunnat: vishwarupa end tൻre atindriya rupam kanaൻ krishnaൻ aർjjune anuvadikkayu at aർjunൻre hridayattiൽ katutt bhitiundakkukyu cheiyunnu.
ori: gitar ehi anshati eka bhavabhibhoot antardrushtire sheershare pahanchichhi: krishna arjunanku nizer divya rup, 'vishrup' dekhivaku anumati deivanthi, yahaki arjunank hridyare bhan sanychar karichhi .
pan: gita de ish bhaag da samapan ik shaktishali aalokic drish naal hunda hai, krishna, arjun nuun aapne divyaroop, vishvaroop de darshan karavaunda hai, jise naal arjun de dil vich dar paidaa hoo janda hai|
tam: gitain indep bakuti woru dicaputum katseudon mudivatikintu: krishna tanatu aibudaman viswaroop vativats arjunuku welipadudukhirar, itu arjun manatil payankar achchatai undakukintu.
tel: gitloni i bhagamu ock mahattar drushyanlo parakashtaki cherutundi: krishn arjununiki tan divya rupamain vishwaroopanni saakshatkaristadu, adi arjununi gundello bhayabhrantula puttistundi.
urd: gita ke is hisse kaa akhtatam ek jabardast khwaab se hota hai: krishna arjun ko apni sumavi shukla, vishwaroopa, dekhne kii izzaazat dete hain, jo arjun ke dil main dahshat paida kar detii hai.
eng: This part of the Gita culminates in an overwhelming vision: Krishna allows Arjuna to see his supernal form, the Vishvarupa, which strikes terror into Arjuna's heart.

ben: upadhara (3) anuyayi, ei dharner avedan pawar par upayukt kartrupaksh dui pakshake shunani suyog die evan maamla paristiter kshetre upayukt mane haley tadanter ei dharner sankshiptsar tiri karaar pare, has likhitabhave anumati pradaan karbe baa ei dharner anumati dite ashwikar karbe.
guj: peta kalam 3 anusaar, aavi araji maltan, saksham adhikari lekhitma aadesh apine, pakshakarone sambhalwani tak aapya bad ane kesana sanjogoma tene yogya laage tevi tunki puchhaprach karya pachhi aavi manjuuri aapi shake athva aavi manjuuri aapavaano inkar kari shake.
hin: up-khand (3) ke anusaar, is prakaar kaa aavedan praapt karne par, donon pakshon ko sune jane kaa avasar de kar or maamle kii paristhitiyon ke sambandh main sankshipt jaanch-padtaal karne ke baad, yogya adhikari likhit aadesh main aisi anumati ke liye sahmati de bhi sakate hai yaa asweekaar bhi kar sakate hai.
kan: up-kalam (3)r prakaar, antah arjianneu swikarisidag, saksham praadhikarvu, pakshakararige vichaaraneya avkashavannu kott nantar mattu prakarand sandarbhad kuritagee antah kshipra vichaaranegathannu nadesid nantar ader vivechanege saridoridante antah anumatiannu nidlu oppabahudu athwa nirakarisabahudu.
mal: attarmoru apeksh kitial bandhappet kakshikalk tangute bhaga padyuvanuol avasar naൽkiyasheshvu, tangൾk yuktamennu tonnunn vidhttil sahacharyasli atiyantirmay anveshans natattia sheshvu, uttarvadapet adhikari upvakup (3) anusrich rekhamulmay uttarvuway attar anumati nalkukayo nalkan visammathikkayo cheyyavunntan.
ori: up-dhara (3) anuyani, ehipari eka aavedan prapth heva pare, kshamtapanna karttrupaksh, likhita bhavare nirddesh dei, paksha dianku nij paksha rakhibar suyog deva pare eban mammlatir paristaitegushikar eka saransh anudhyan karisariva pare, yepari uchith boli prathit heb sehi anusaare, epari anumati pradanku manjur kimba khaaraj kariparanthi .
pan: up-dhaara (3) de anusaar, ajihi arzi praapat on 'te, samarath atharty, likhti roop vich adesh de ke, doven dhirs nuun suinn da muka den ton bood, ate case de halaataan baare sankhep puchh-gichh karan ton bood jaaa taan ajihi ijazat de sakadi hai jaaa inkaar kar sakadi hai, jiven uh thik samajhan|
tam: dunaip brivu (3) prakaram, dagudil anaiyam attakaiya vinnappam ondayp pewdan feril sambandappatt trupinarin gutapugalack katak waifu valangy pinkum porudhamantu ena tham karudiapati vanakkin suanilis kuritu vaymophi visaranis menokont pinkum eduddupurv anai mulam athangu anumati valanglam alltu manukalam.
tel: up vibhagam(3) prakara, atuvanti darkhastu svikarinchinapp, samarthadhikari, likhitapoorvak adesha dwara, irupakshalk vadani vinipinche avakash kaliginchin taruvat, mariyu kesu paristhitula batti edi tagindani bhaviste andulo aa vidhmain sankshipt vicharanas jaripin taruvat atuvanti anumati manjur cheyavacchu leda tiraskarinchanoovachch.
urd: zeli dafaa (3) ke mutabik, is tarah kii darkhwaast musuul hone par, majaaz atharty, tahariri hukum naame ke zarie, frican ko samat kaa mauqaa dene ke baad or is tarah kii sarasari tafteesh ke baad jaisaa ye munasib samajhe aisi izzaazat dene se inkaar kar sakati hai.
eng: As per sub-section (3), on receipt of such an application, the Competent Authority, by order in writing, may either grant or refuse to grant such permission after giving an opportunity to the parties of being heard and after making such summary inquiries into the circumstances of the case as it thinks fit.

ben: natishitoshna parnamochi baner byomaguli halo uttar o dakshina america, esia, himalayer dakshina dhal, europer evan oshenia chashabader uddeshe chhadie thaka udvid samprada.
guj: samshitoshna kharau jungal bioms vanaspati chhod samudaayo uttar ane dakshin america, asia, himalayas dakshin dhalo, europe ane osenia vistaroma kheti hetuthi vahenchayelam che.
hin: samshitoshna parnpaati van jivom padap samooh hai jo uttari or dakshini america, himalay ke dakshini dhaalon, europe main faile hai or oshinia main kheti ke prayojan se faile hue hai.
kan: samashitoshna eleuduruv kadugal jeevasamoohgalendare uttar hagu dakshin americagamalli, eshyadalli, himalayad dakshin bhagad ilijarugamalli, europeenalli, mattu vyavasayad uddeshgaligagi oshianiyadalli beleyuv sasya samudayagalagive.
mal: watnakൻ america, tekke america, esia, himalayatiൻre teckൻ malancherivukൾ, europe ennivitol kaaർshik aavashyaൾkkai oshyanailumulla sasyasamutea mitshitoshna kalavasthayu ilapoliyumraalumulla jaivamekhalakൾ.
ori: nathisheetoshna parnamochi aranya jeevaliguik heudi uttar eban dakshin america, asia, himalayar dakshinanchaliya dhalu, europe, eban chadakaryan uddeshyare osheniare bapt hoi rahithiva udbhidha gosthi .
pan: sanjami patjhad jungle biomas ped-paude de smooh han jo ki uttari ate ngkhani america, asia, himalaya dis ngkhani kolanas, europe, ate oshania vich kheti de udishs lai vanday gaye han I
tam: mitt tadbhavepp illudhir gaddu urinak kullumangan enbhave watakku manllum kisku america, acia, imayamalin thevkuch sarivues, airopa aakhiya bakudikasil parvil manllum oshianawill sagupati nokanglukkak valarcopadukinso tavrak kuluxlakum.
tel: samashitoshna akuralche atavi jeevaprinamas anevi uttar, dakshin america, asia, himalayas dakshin valulu, airopa, mariyu sagobadi uddeshyalakai oshinialo vyapinchi unn vriksha samuhl.
urd: matidal patjhadi janglati biomiz podon kii biradariyaan hain jo shumali or janubi america, asia, himalay kii janubi dhalawaanon, europe or okiyanoosy main kashit kari ke muqaasid ke liye faili hui hain.
eng: Temperate deciduous forest biomes are plant communities distributed in North and South America, Asia, the southern slopes of the Himalayas, Europe, and for cultivation purposes in Oceania.

ben: guru granth sahib japaji saheb die shuru has edike dasam granth shuru has jap saheb die yake japu sahebo bala has.
guj: guru granth sahibani japaji sahibathi sharu thai che, jayaare dasam granth jaap sahibathi sharu thai che, jene japu sahib pan kahe che.
hin: guru granth sahib kaa aarambh japuji sahib se hota he jabaki dasham sahib kaa aarambh jaap sahib se hota he jise japuji sahib bhi kehete hai.
kan: guru granth sahibavu japji sahibdind aarambhwadare, dasham granthavu japu sahib endu kareyalaguv jaap sahibdind aarambhvaguttade.
mal: guru granth sahib japji sahibiൽ arambhikumpoൾ dasam granth japu sahib ennu vilicppedunn jap sahibiൽ arambhikunnu.
ori: guru granth sahib 'japaji sahib' sahit aarmbh hoithiva bele 'dasam granth', 'ja'p sahib' sahit aarmbh hoichhi, yahakuki 'japu sahib' madhya kuhayaaye .
pan: guru granth sahib di shuruvat japji sahib naal hundi hai, dasam granth di shuruvat jaap sahib jaaa japu sahib naal hundi hai I
tam: guru kirant sahibin dotakkum, jhabji sahib akum; adevele tasam kiranttin dotakkum, japu sahib enllum anoaicopatum jab sahib akum.
tel: guru granth saheb japji saheb to aarambhmavga, dasha granth japu saheb ani kuda pilvabade jap saheb to aarambhmavutundi.
urd: guru granth sahab kaa aagaaz jap ji sahab se hota hai, jabaki dasam granth jaap sahab se shurua hota hai, jise japu sahab bhi kaha jataa hai.
eng: The Guru Granth Sahib starts with Japji Sahib, while the Dasam Granth starts with Jaap Sahib, also called Japu Sahib.

ben: january-march 2015 samaikale chinese 7%-era tulana bharter jiddypi vruddhi chhil 7.5%, ya bharatka druttam vardhanshil pradhan arthaniti kare tole.
guj: chinana 7%ni sarkhamanima january-march 2015na galama bharatno ji.dee.pe. vikasadar 7.5% hato, je tene sauthi jhadapathi viksatu mukhya arthtantra banaave che.
hin: 2015 kii janvari se march kii avadhi ke dauraan china ke 7 pratishat kii tulana main bharat kaa sakal gharelu utpaada vikaas 7.5 pratishat tha, jo ise sabase teji se badhane vaali arthvyavastha banaata he.
kan: 2015r janvary-march avadhialli chinad 7%ge holicidare bharatad ji.de.pi. belvanigeyu 7.5%rashtu iddudarind adu atyant vegavagi beleyuttiruv pramukh aarthikateyenicitu.
mal: chinaute 7 shatamanvumai taratamyam cheayumpoൾ 2015le january-maaർchch kalayalviൽ indyayute ji. de. pi valർchch 7.5 shatamanmairunnuvennat, indyaye et vegattiൽ vairunn atipradhan sampadvyavastheyakunnu.
ori: 2015 masihar january-marchch avadhire, bharatar ji.de.pi abhivriddhi chinr 7% tuznare 7.5% thila, yahaki ehaku drutatam bhave abhivriddhi ghatuthiva pradhan arthvavastha karithila .
pan: bharat da ji.di.pi vikas, 2015 vich janvari-march de doran 7.5% see, jise de mukaabale chin da 7% , jo bharat nuun sabh ton tezi naal vadhadi hoi arth- vivstha banaundi hai I
tam: 2015 january-march kaalakttil, chinavin 7% udan opitumbodhu indiavin jitipe valarchi 7.5% awk irundatu, eneway india pery poruladhar nadugalul mik vegamak valarum nadagat digahandatu.
tel: 2015 lo january-march kalamlo china yokk 7% to poliste bharat jidipi perugudal 7.5% vadd nilichi atyant veganga adugutunn bruhat aarthikavyavasthi aindi.
urd: 2015 ke janvari-march muddat ke dauraan bhaarat kii ji dee pii kii namo chin kii 7faisad ke muqaabale main 7.5faisad thi, jis ne use tejai se tarakkee karne wali ahim maishith bina diya.
eng: India's GDP growth during the January-March period of 2015 was at 7.5% compared to China's 7%, making it the fastest-growing MAJOR economy.

ben: polish simant rakshider dike pathar, bottle evan kather tukro chhundte shuru kare evan asthayibhave bandh brujgi-kujanicha checkpayant vene dhokar prayas simant vestniti dhvans karaar cheshta kare tara.

ori: semane poland desh sima rakshakamanank uparaku pather, bottle, eban kathkhandaman fingivaku lagile eban asthani bhave bandh thiva vrujgi-kunika checkpaent thare sima madhyadei dhasei pashibar udimare sima-bactiku dhs karidevaku udum karithile .
pan: baroongi-kunika di asthai for 'te band keeti chauki nuun todan di di koshish vich onha ne pathar, bottle ate lakkad de tukde poland simaa sipahia te sute ate pher simaa di nuun todan di koshish kiti I
tam: avarkas polandu ellike kavalar midhu krugus, puttis, mrik kttis akhiyavaggrai visat dodangi, bruski-kunicail taiakalikamak mudapattulu chodanai sawati aruke ellait tatupu valli dakartu ellyske katakk murpattanur.
tel: tatkalikanga mosiveyabadin tanikhi kendra vadd sarihaddun atikraminche prayatnation wallu polish sarihaddu rakshakulapai rallu, sisal, alage checkk mukkalu visarea mughal petti sarihaddu kanchenu dhvansa chatenduku prayatincharu.
urd: unhon ne polistaani sarhadi nigahabaanon par pattharon, botalon or lakdi ke tukde fekna shurua kar diye or brozgi-conesa ke aarzi tuur par band jaanch ke marcuz par sarhad abor karne kii koshish main sarhadi baad ko todne kii koshish kii.

ben: 2007-e, new england journal af mediciner praktan pradhan sampadak evan harvard medical scule samajik chickesar ek adhyapak, mersia angel, german bhashar saptahik ek khabarer patrika, starn-e, "[pratity oshudher] sambhavya tulanamulak matra vyavharer parivarte sansthati vigyanira uchchatar matra nexium vyabhhar karellen" bale balen ye, oshudhti caryaaritar upar tander gaveshanake bhulbhave upsthapit karellen astragenekar vigyanira.
guj: 2007maa new england jarnal of medicinena maji varishtha sampadak ane harverd medical skoolna sosial medicinena vyakhyata marsiya angele german bhashana neuz megesin saptahik sternma janavyu hatu ke estradeenekana vaignanichoe drugsni kaaryakshamata angena temana sanshodhanma khoti rajuat kari hati ke ‘(darek dwani) sambhavatah tulanatmak matrano upayog karvaane badle companeena vaignanichoe nexiamani uchch matrano upayog karyo hato.’
hin: 2007 main, marsia angel, new england jarnal of medicine kii purv pradhan sampadak or harvard medical skool main saamaajik chikitsa main vyaakhyaata, ne german bhashaa kii saptahik samachar patrika stern main yah kehete hue ki estrogeneka ke vaigyanikon ne dawa kii prabhavakaarita par apni shodh ko galat tareeke se prastut kiya tha, daawa kiya ki "[prayek dawa kii] sambhavit rup se tulaneey khuraaq kaa upyog karne ke bajaay, company ke vaigyanikon ne ucch maatra main nexium kaa upyog kiya."
kan: 2007ralli, new england gernal aaf medisinn maji pradhan sampadki mattu harvard medical scoolinalli samajik vaidyad aadhyapakiad marsha angel german bhasheya saptahik samacharapatrike ʼsternʼnalli, "sambhavyavagi holisabahudad pramandalli (prationdu muul aushadhawastuvannu) balsuv badlu, sansthey vigyanigarhu nexiamannu hchin pramandalli balsiddare" ennutta, austrajenakad vigyanigarhu aushadhiya samarthyad bagegin avar sanshodhanayannu tappagi nirupisiddare endu hehidaru.
mal: 2007ൽ new england jenൽ of mediciniൻre muൻ mukhyapatradhiparu haർwaർd medicaൽ skuliൽ soshyaൽ mediciniൽ adhyapikayumay maaർsia enchൽ, astraenakkayute shastrajnaർ marunniൻre phalapraptiyecurichull avarute gaveshatte thetti avatarippitchuvennu "[oro marunniൻreyu] samanmen karutapetunn dosukൾ upyogikunnatin pakar companyile shastrajnaർ uyർnn dosiൽ nexium upyogicchuvennu" jർmmൻ bhashailull prativar waർttamasikayay stateniൽ parannu.
ori: 2007 masihare, 'niu england jornal af messicine'r prakthan mukhya sampadak eban harbhard medikal sculare samajik aushadh adhapika, marsia engel, eka german bahasha saptahik sambad-patrika, 'stan're astra-yenekar vaigyanikamane aushadhatir parangamata vishakere semanank gaveshanaku trutipurna bhave upasthapana kariyanthi abhiyog kari kahile, "[prati aushadhar] anumanic tupaniya pan bbbahar kariva parivartte, companyr vaigyanikamane adhik matrare neksiamar pan bbbahar karithile."
pan: 2007 vich, marsia anjil, neu england jarnal aaf medicine di saabaka sampadak-in-cheef ate harword medical skuul vich samajik dawai di lekcharar, ne germany bhaasha di saptahik nioose magazine, steran vich kiha ki estera zenika de vigyania ne aushadhi di nipunnata upper apni padchol di galat peshkari kiti hai, ih kahinde, "sambhavat for 'te tulanatamak khuraks [harek aushadhi di] di varton karan di bajaae, company de vigyania ne uch khuraks vich neassium di varton keeti."
tam: 2007il niu england journal off medicin italin munnal talams asiriarum harentu maruduvap pailaktil samuk maruduat turaiil perasiriaruman marcea angel varandra germon mobich saydip pattrictyana sternuden pesumbodhu, astrasenika vinjanis marundin seyaltision kuritt araichi dhawatakach chittaritlsanar endu gutai, "anniruvanatin vinjanis [ovvoru marundukum] anekamak charinikarana marundalvugalap payanbadudhuvadaikup patilak nexiumay adhik marundalvkalil payanbaduttyuner" enjhar.
tel: german bhashaloni saptahik vaartha patrik stern lo, 2007 lo new england gernal aaf medicine pradhan sampadkuram mariyu harvard medical skull samajik vaidyaulo bodhakuram ayin marsia angil, austragenika shastravettal i aushadh gunampai tam parishodhananu tappuga vivarinchayani cheptu, "[prati ockk aushadha yokk] sumaruga polodagin motadulku badulu, company shastravettal nexiamnu adhik motadulo upayogincharani" telipar.
urd: 2007 main, new ungland jarnal of medicine kii sabik madir aala va harvard medical skool main samaji tibb kii ek lucturer marsiya angel ne ek german jubaan ke hafta war akhabaari magazine stern main kaha ki estrazenica ke sincedanon ne is dawa kii carakardagee par apni tahaqiq kii galat tavel kii thi, ye kehate hue ki "[har dawa kii] gaaliban kaabil mawaazan khuraaqon kaa istemaal karne ke bajaay, company ke sincedanon ne nexim kaa istemaal zyaada muqadaar main kiya hai."
eng: In 2007, Marcia Angell, former editor-in-chief of the New England Journal of Medicine and a lecturer in social medicine at the Harvard Medical School, said in Stern, a German-language weekly newsmagazine, that AstraZeneca's scientists had misrepresented their research on the drug's efficiency, saying, "Instead of using presumably comparable doses [of each drug], the company's scientists used Nexium in higher dosages."

ben: dvitiya-bi amri samaikaler mrushilper sang sampratik si14 samay-nirdharan evan shailigat tulanaguli dekha ye pratham duti paryayke prack-harappan dholaviriya sanskruti bala evan samargulike nimnarupe punrnirdharan kara uchit: pratham para (anumanik 3500-3200 christpurbabd) evan dvitiya para (anumanik 3200-2600 christpurbabd)
guj: amari dwitiya-bi samaygalani matikala satheni tajetharana sii14 datting ane shailigath sarkhamnio darshave che ke pahela be tabakkane purav-hadappiya dholavira sanskruti nam aapvu joie ane tene aa pramane punavdinankit karvu joieh pahelo tabakko (aashare i.sa. purve 3500 - 3200) ane bijo tabakko (aashare i.sa. purve 3200 - 2600).
hin: haal hi main kiye gaye si14 nirdharanon or amari dwitiya-bi yug ke mitti ke paatro ke saath shailigat tulana se pataa chalata he pratham do charnon ko purv-hadappa dholavira samskruti kaha janaa chahie or iske hone kii avadhi main punahparivartan nimnlikhit he: pratham charan (lagbhag 3500 - 3200 isa purv) or dwitiya charan (lagbhag 3200 - 2600 isa purv).
kan: ittichin si14 kalagananegalu mattu amri II-bi kaalad kumbarikeyondige shailiallin tulanegalu, modalin eradu hantagainnu harpp-poorv dholavira sanskriti embudagi kareyabekendu mattu hant I (sumaru sa.sha.pus. 3500-3200) hagu hant II ( sumaru sa.sha.pus. 3200-2600) endu kalavannu marunigadipadisabekendu torpadisuttve.
mal: atutt kalatte carbon 14 kalanirnaysu amri II bi kalatte manpatraislumayull taratamyavu kanikunnat adyatte rantu ghattase harpan purv dholavirasanskar enne peritanmennu takeanunvidhttil kalapunarnirnay natattanamennu: onnam ghatea (etand 3500 - 3200 bi.si.i.) randa ghatea (etand 3200 - 2600 bi.si.i.)
ori: nikat atitar si14 kalanuman tatha 'amari-2du-kh' kal mrinman shifp sahit stylesakrantiya tushana darshaaye ye pratham dui paryanku 'prak-harappa dholabeera sanskruti' nam diayiva uchith eban nimnare pradutt hoithiva pari punar kal nirddist karayiva uchith: 1ma paryan (praia khri.pus 3500 - 3200) eban 2du paryan (praia khri.pus 3200 - 2600) .
pan: amari II-bi kaal de miti de baratnas naal tajia carbon-14 datings ate shailegat tulana darsoundi hai ki pahile doo faijan nuun poorav haspa dholvira sabhiachar da name dena chahida hai ate ish tarhaa punar mitikran 'cha injh karna chahida hai: stage- I (see. 3500 - 3200 bisii) ate stage II (see. 3200 - 2600 bisii) |
tam: amri II-bhi kaalaktt manpandangans sameepatil chi14 kalakkanippues manllum vativeu oppeedugaluku udbadutdhya podhu, muthal erandu kaalaktangass harrapavuku mundaiy dolaveyrap banpadu enab peyariddu finwarumaru kaal variyarai seyy wants endu atu gattiyadu: kaalaktam 1 (chu. kimu 3500 - 3200) manllum kaalaktam 2 (chu. kimu 3200 - 2600).
tel: anri 2-bi. kalam nati kundalatho itivali si14 tedis shailul pontanal modati rend dashaln harappa kante poorvapu dholvira samskritii chendinviga perkonalani suchinchi krindi tedigal vidhnga punamperconabadinavi: 1va dash (sumaru kri pus3500 - 3200) mariyu 2va dash (sumaru kripu3200 - 2600).
urd: halay si14 kii taarikh andaazi or amari dum-bi ke daur kii koza giri ke saath aslobi mawaazane bitaate hain ki pahele do murahil ko majubal hadapa dholvera muqafat kaha jaanaa chahiye or is kii dobara taarikh andaazi darj zeel tuur par kii hai: marahala ol (3500 - 3200 kabel messiah) or marahala dum (3200 - 2600 kabel messiah).
eng: Recent C14 datings and stylistic comparisons with Amri II-B period pottery show the first two phases should be termed Pre-Harappan Dholaviran Culture and re-dated as follows: Stage I (c. 3500 - 3200 BCE) and Stage II (c. 3200 - 2600 BCE).

eng: Kailasanatha is a stunning cave temple, which is one of the 34 ancient caves of Ellora.

ben: karnatka, 7m evan 8m shatabdeer pattadacaler mandir samuh, gambujakruti chader chaityas kaksha dharner parikalpana thaka sattweo iholer matoi, paravartikale uttar o dakshina ubhayer sang samparkit vikhyath dhara melbandhan ghata.
guj: karnatakama pattadakal mukame satami ane athmi sadina mandiro swaroopone bhegaan karva janitan che, je pachhalothi uttar ane dakshin bannema sankalaya che, jemke aihole mukame, jema haji pan chapakar chaityas khand prakarani yojana samel che.
hin: karnataka ke pattadakal main sthit 7veen or 8veen shatabdi ke mandir mishrit shaileyon ke liye jane jate hai jinhen baad main uttar or dakshini shaileyon kaa mishran mana gaya jaisaa ki aihole main bhi he jisamen abhi bhi gajaprishthakaar kaksh jaisi vyavastha najar aati he.
kan: karnatakadalli, pattadakallin 7nae mattu 8nae shatmanad mandiragal samuhvu amelin kaldalli uttar mattu dakshind shailigalige aropisalad rupagal atyuttam mishranavannu hondide, anteye gajaprushtakarad chaitya pranganadantah nirmangainnu innu olagondiruv aiholeya mandiragal samuhavu intahude mishranwagide.
mal: kർnatakaiൽ, pattaikkalile elanutandileyu eitanutandilayu kshetrasute kuttangൾ, aiholeletennatupolull, ipporau aർddhavrittakritiilull chityahaൾ tarattilull planukൾ uൾkkollunnatu piൽkkalat vaikkumau tekkumau bandhappetuttapetatumay rupaeee prashastmay ritiiൽ kuttikalർttunnu.
ori: karnatakare, pattadhakal thare avasthit 7ma eban 8ma shatabdeer mandirgudik ullekhaniya bhavare sehi stylegurikar mishran kariyanthi, paravartti kalre yaahaar ubhay uttar eban dakshin sahit sampark rahichhi, yaha iholre madhya dekhivaku missithae, yeunthare eparynant ardhdhavrittakar prashast chitya grih bhadi naksassbu rahichhi.
pan: karnataka de pattdkal vich, 7 ve ate 8 ve sadi de mandira de smooh, uttar te daksini tor de prasidh roop nuun jodda hai, ihole de saman, jise vich hun ve apsidel chitia haal-kism dis yojnavs han I
tam: karnatakatin pattatakallil ull 7aam manllum 8aam noorthanduk koilil watakkatya manllum dherkatya enab birkalatil sutoppatt iruvakai vativangsum kalandulldu prabhlaman ondu, eholail ullves idebolat than, angu inllum kaviya vativamull saitya kutam bonthe meghatopus amibbues atankyluna.
tel: karnatakaloni, pattadakll unn 7va mariyu 8va shatabdpu aalayas samudayam aa taruvat uttarm, dakshinanga bhavinchabadd iru roopal sammilita chassindi, alage aihole lo unnadi kuda, idi ippatiki vrittakar chaityas sabha mandiram vanti nirmanmulatho kudi undi.
urd: karnataka main, patadakul main saatveen or aathaven sadi ke mandiron kaa group baad main kshamal or janub dono se wabasta, heaton ko marof tuur par milaa detaa hai, jaisaa ki ehal main hota hai, jis main ab bhi spadal chity hal kasam ke mansoobey shamil hain.
eng: In Karnataka, the group of 7th and 8th-century temples at Pattadakal famously mixes forms later associated with both north and south, as does that at Aihole, which still includes apsidal chaitya hall-type plans.

ben: "sei muhoorth thek," 1945-era pratibedne bala ach, "kolkatavasik khawanor kshetre ei sadharan banisya vyavasthar upar aashtha rakha chale na."
guj: ‘e kshanathi’ 1945na ahevale nondhyu, ‘kalakattaane ann pooru padwa mate samanya vepari vyavastha par aadhar raakhi shakay tem nahoto.’
hin: 1945 kii report main kaha gaya, "us kshan se kalakatta kaa pet bharne ke liye saamaanya vyapaar vyavastha par nirbhar nahin kiya ja saktaa tha."

pan: "us andolan ton", 1945 di report vich kiha gya hai ki, "kolkata nuun bhojan den lai aam vpark mashinari 'te bharosaa nahi kita jaaa sakda see|"
tam: "andat tarunm muthal calkatauku unu valang valakkaman vanigamurai amaipai nampirukk mudiavilly" endu 1945aam antu arikky guriyatu.
tel: 1945 nivedik ila perkondi, "aa kshana nudi sadharan vanijya yantranga kalakattaku ahara andingdaniki danipai aadharpalenidi ayepoindi."
urd: "is lamhe se," 1945 kii report main kaha gaya hai, "kalakattaa ko khilaane ke liye aam tizaarati mashinary par anqasaar naheen kiya jasakta ."
eng: "From that moment," the 1945 report stated, "the ordinary trade machinery could not be relied upon to feed Calcutta."

ben: shaharti aparikalpit vruddhi yanchalachal viraat vighn srushti kare; shudhumatra parimitrupe safal ekati uralpul vyavastha evan ekamukhi traffic vyavastha pravaratet has.
guj: shaherma vikaasni aniyojit prakrutine karne motapaye traffic jam thayo; flyover paddhati ane van-ve traffic paddhati raju karvama aavi hati, je matra anshtah saphal rahi hati.
hin: shahar ke aniojit tareeke se badhane ke kaaran yatayaat main vaahanon kaa jamghat ho jaataa tha jisase yatayaat thap ho jaataa tha; fli-over pranali or ekamargi yatayaat kii pranali shuru kii gayi jo bas kuch had tak hi safal raheen.
kan: nagardalli yojitvallad belvanigeya lakshanad prenamvagi mitimirid vahan sanchar dattaneya gridlakgalu untadavu; malsethuve vyavasthe mattu ek-mukh vahan sanchar vyavasthegamannu parichayislagi, avu svalpamattigashte yashasviadvu.
mal: nagarattile vairchchayute aasutranmillat riti vampich gatagatastambhanangൾk karanmai; oru fly ower samvidhanvu vanvegatagat sampradayasu avatarippitcheakil av parimitmaye vijayitullu.
ori: saharatire abhivriddhir yojanahin prakruti yogun prabal traffikjanit gatirodh; eka fliobhar brivastha o eka-margi traffik brivasthaman pranathan hoithila, yahaki keval madhum bhavare safal hoithila .
pan: shahir vich vikas di gair-yojnabedh prakyria de natije kaaran bade padhar te awajai vich rok hoi; ik mandalau ate ik tarfa awajai pranali shuruu kiti gai, jo ki thodi hi safal san.
tam: nakruttil ditamidat valarchiin vilaivak peruddha bhokuvarattu stambhippues ettpattana, woru mambalad thogudi oruvaqip patkalum puditak amaicoppatt fodhilu are oralway menopati praschanikud thirvalittana.
tel: naggaranlo abhivruddhi yokk niyamarahit swabhavan bhari traphic pratishthambhanalku daaritisindi; ock flaiover vyavasthan mariyu ek-deesh traphic vyavasthal praveshpettar, avi mostruga matrame vijayavantmayyai.
urd: shahar main tarakkee kii gair mansuba band navsheet ke nattejey main bade paimaane par traific jam hote the; ek flai over system or yak tarfaa traific system mataarf kiraaya gaya, jo kam kam hi kaamyaab tha.
eng: The unplanned nature of growth in the city resulted in massive traffic gridlocks; a flyover system and one-way traffic systems were introduced, which were only moderately successful.

ben: vikhyath ajanta guhagulor aansh hiseve mott 29ta pathar-kata buddha guha royas ya prashanti aar nirmaltar srushti kare. aguli christopoorv 2ya shatabdite tiri aar ete math o chaityas grih royas.
guj: janiti ajanta gufaono ek bhag, pathar kapine baneli 29 bauddha gufaao che, je shanti ane nirmalata pragatawe che, e isavisana biji sadi jetali juni che ane tema matho tatha chaityagruho che.
hin: 29 buddha rock-cat guphaayen hai jinamein shanti or pavitrataa mahasoos hoti he or jo prasiddh ajanta kii gufaaon kaa ek hissaa hai, jo duusari shatabdi isa purv main banaai gai thim or jinamein math or chaityas grih hai.
kan: ajanta guhegal bhagwagi ottare 29 baudhdh guhalayagalive, shantate mattu prasantagambhiryavanna susuv avugal kalavann kri.pus. 2nae shatman anth andajislagide, alli pradhanvagi irodu baudhdh viharagalu matte chaitya grihagalu.
mal: bi.si. rantanutandietenne karutapetunnatu sanyasimathangu chityagruatelu ulppetunnatu, shantiyu pavitrathyu kinimanothukunnatumay aake 29 baddhashilaguhal ajantaguhalute bhag.
ori: prasiddh ajanta gumfar kichhi anshare, samudaya 29ta pather-khodei buddha gumpha ajji youthuki shanthi aau sthirata jharithae, yahaki christpoorb 2du shatabdeer aau youthi baudhdhabihar aau caityagrih dekhivaku mile .
pan: ih mashhoor ajanta guphawaan da hisa hai, kul 29 chattans naal katia gaia bodhi guphawaan han jo shanti ate sahijta nuun darsoundis han, jo ki dooji sadi isavi poorav dis han ate ish vich math ate chitia graha han.
tam: ajanta kukaikalil mottom 29 pautt kudaivarike koils irukkinsona, avarkhil chandhamum amaide nirainthrukkum. kimu 2aam noorthanduku munpe madangalutanus saitya valaibhattu mandabangalutanus are uruvacopattanu.
tel: ajanta guhalalo ock bhaganlo, motta 29 ratilo chekkin buddha guhalunnai, avi nishshabd prashantathanu vedjallutai, ivi kripu 2va shatabdpu nativi, vitello mathalu, chaityas grihal untai.
urd: mashhuur ajanta gaaron main, jamla 29 pattharon se kaat kar banaaye gaye buddha gaar hain jo bahut paraman or prasukun hain, ye duusari sadi kabel messiah ke gaar hain or in main math or chetya grah hain.
eng: Part of the famous Ajanta Caves, there are a total of 29 rock-cut Buddhist caves that ooze out calmness and serenity, which date back to the 2nd century BC and feature monasteries and chaitya grihas.

ben: banigyik bank run, kraitar amanath, jogandarer amanath, asthayi harer note evan sthayi harer bander mato surakshit dalel ityadi, antarjatik arth nigam (washington), e.de.bi, e.ef.aai.si, si.de.si prabhruthir mato bahupakshik arth pratisthanguli besarkari vibhag thek aagat banigyik dharsmuh i.si.biguli madhye antarbhukt thake.
guj: i.sii.bi.maa samel che vividh vyavasayik bank lon, kharidanar ane apurtikarne dhiran, taral darani nodh ane niyath darna bond vigere jevaan salaamati dharavataan kararpatro, sattavar nikaas dhiran sansthanomathi dhiran ane internetional finance corporeshan (voshington), e.dee.bi., e.epa.ai.sii., sii.dee.sii. jevi bahupakshiya nanakiya sansthao jevaan khaangi kshetrai sansthaomathi vyavasayik dhirano.
hin: antarrashtriya vitt nigam (washington), e.di.bi., e.epa.ai.si., si.di.si., aadi jaise bahupaksheeya vittiya sansthaanon ke nijee kshetra ke gatividhi-kendra se vanijyik bank rin, kreta-rin, aapurtikarta-rin, floating-rate note or phixd-rate band aadi jaise pratibhutikrut upkaran, aadhikarik niryaat rin agenciyon se rin, or aadhikarik niryaat rin agenciyon se rin vanijyik udhaar i.si.bi. ke udhaaharan hai.
kan: i.si.bi.galu vanijy bank salgalu, kollugar sal, sarbarajudarar sal, vyatyayit baddia kaipatragalu mattu sthir baddia kararupatragalu modlad bhadrata sadhangalu, adhikrut raftu sal agensigalind jamavane, mattu antarashtriya aarthik mandali (washington), e.de.bi., e.f.i.si., si.de.si. muntadavugaintah bahupakshiya hanakasu sansthegal khasagi valay terapinind vanijy salagainnu olagondive.

ben: antrer madhye 80-85% upkaari bacteria evan 15-20% sambhavya kshatikar bacteriar ekati anupat sadharant swabhavik hisabe vivechit has evan sharirik sustaite baja rakhe.
guj: antardamana 80-85 taka upkarak jivaanu ane 15-20 taka sambhavit hanikarak jivaanu e samanya rite pramansarana manay che ane te sanavastha jalve che.
hin: aanton main 80–85% laabhakaari bacteria or 15–20% sambhavit rup se hanikaarak bacteria kaa anupaat aamtaur par saamaanya mana jaataa he or yah samasthiti banaae rakhata he.
kan: karulugal olage, 15-20% hanimadball bactyriagalige 80-85% prayojanakari backtiriagal anupatavannu samanyavagi sapramanavadudendu pariganislagide mattu adu santhulanavannu kapaduttade.
mal: gunapradmay bacteria 80–85% vu doshasadhyatyull bacteria 15–20% vu end anupata kutalukalull saadharanmanennu homeostasis nilenirtumennu potuve karutapetunnu.
ori: upakaari beejanugudikar 80-85% sahit sambhavya haanikarak beejanugudik 15-20% r anupathaku sadharanthati antranaliguik madhyare sbhavik boli bichaar karayaaye eban eha samavasthan bajang rakhe .
pan: 80-85% lahevand bactyria da anupaat 15-20% sambhavi for 'te nuksandeh bactyria aam for 'te antedia de under aam mannia janda hai ate homeostasis banai rakhada hai|
tam: kutalukul 80-85% nanmilickum bacteria manllum 15-20% satiyaman kodea bacteria enjh vikittil iruppatu botwak ialputan enak karudapadukintu, melum atu chirchamanilies paramrikintu.
tel: prayojnakar bacteria 80–85% , hanikarm kagal bacteria 15–20% ane nishpattini pregul lopal mamuluga sadharanmindiga pariganistar, adi samanawasth stateni konsagistundi.
urd: 80-85 faisad mufeed bacteria kaa tanasib 15-20 faisad mumkin tuur par nuqasaan dah bacteria ke saath aam tuur par aanton main aam samajha jataa hai or homostasis ko barkaraar rakhata hai.
eng: A ratio of 80–85% beneficial bacteria to 15–20% potentially harmful bacteria is generally considered normal within the intestines and maintains homeostasis.

ben: ganitik paribhashar jatilata boza maan uparer sima nirna kara baa katagulo saral crear hisseb kara, yeman schalerer yoga o gunan, udaharanswarup kichu kichu ganitik paribhashar kshetre matricksear gunan hal aavashyak.
guj: algoridhamani jatilata nakki karavaano arth e che ke uparni seema shodhvi athva skelarna sarwala ane gunakar jevaan ketla prathmik caryonu anuman lagavi shakay che, te ketlank algoridham karva mate jaruri che, daakhla tarike, metrisisano gunakar.
hin: kisi kalan vidhi kii jatilta kaa pataa lagane kaa arth hota he uski upree seemaa gyaat karnaa yaa anumaan karnaa ki kisi kalan vidhi ko karne ke liye, udhaaharan ke liye, avyuuh kaa gunan karne ke liye, kitne adishon ke yoga or guna jaisi moulik sankriyaaon kii aavashyaktaa hogi.
kan: ondu gananapaddhatiya sankirnateyannu nirdharisuvudu endare udaharanege, matrukegal gunakardantah ondu gananapaddhatiannu nirvahisalu sadishgal sankalanagalu mattu gunakargalantah eshtu mulkriegal avashyakateide embudar andaju athwa garisht mitigalannu kanduhidiuvudagide.
mal: matricksukൾ gunana cheiyunnat pole oru aൽgorit cheyyaൻ sankhyakalute kutel gunical polull etra praiamikapravർttanangൾ aavashyaa ennatiൻre uyർnn paridhikalo astimettekalo contettuk enna oru aൽgoritattiൻre sankiർnat niർnayikcook ennatukond aർtthamakkunnat.
ori: eka algoridamar jatilatha nirnade kariva arth heudi upar sima khojiva kimba aakalan kariva ye ketek algoridham kariva pin kete praxmik karyan aavashyak, yepariki scalarar yog eban gunan, udaharan srup, metricur gunan.
pan: ik elgoritham di gundalta nirdharat karan ton bhav uparle bonds jaaa maathle apreshna di ginti da andaaza lagauna, skalras de ajihe jod ate guna kujh algoritham chalaun lai zaroori han, udaharan lai matrisj di guna |
tam: woru patimusait tiru evvalou sikalandu anpats nirnibpatangu, anikalin perucal bonthe edovoru patimusait tirvaich seyalbadutt - disailic goottal manllum perucal bonthe - atans taninilch seyalbadus avasium enbhadan mel varampugans alltu ganipugans khandavia wants.
tel: ock kramsutra yokk sanklishtathanu ganinchada ante, ock kramsutranni, udaharanku matrikal hechchavethanu nadupuku skelar kudikal mariyu hechchavetal vanti prathamik lekkal anni avasaram untayo pai haddul anchana leda pradhamik krial kanukkovada.
urd: algoratham kii pechedagi kaa tain karne se murad wo balai hadood yaa takhmaine maalum karna hota hai ki kitne ibtidai aaprassant, jese skelaron kii jamaa or zaroben, kuch algoratham kii anjaam dahi ke liye zaroori hote hain, misaal ke tuur par, metrixon kii zarab.
eng: Determining the complexity of an algorithm means finding upper bounds or estimates of how many elementary operations, such as additions and multiplications of scalars, are necessary to perform some algorithm, for example, the multiplication of matrices.

ben: swachh bharat abhiyan (parichchhannata o pariwesh dushan, khola jayga shauch bandh kara evan kathin varjya vyavasthapanar unnatir kshetre ganasachetanta tiri kara) evan namami ganger (ullekhayogyabhave dushan hras kara, ganga nadeer sanrakshan o punarutthan) mato kichu kichu sarkari udyoger bapar ekhane ullekh karata uchit.
guj: sarkarani ketlic pahel jevi ke swatch bharat abhiyan (swachchhata ane paryavarniya pradushan ange janjagriti kelvavaa, khullama shauchkria nabud karva, ane ghan kacharaana vyavasthapanma sudharo karva) ane namami gange (ganga nadeena pradushanma nondhapatra ghatado, sarakshan ane punarutthan) ahin ullekh yogya che.
hin: svachh bharat abhiyaan (safai or paryaavarniya pradooshan ke prati saarvajanik jaagrukta jaagrit karnaa, khule main shouch ko samaapt karnaa, or thos apshisht prabandhan ko sudhaarna) tathaa namaami gange (ganga nadi main badi seemaa tak pradooshan ghataana, use sangrakshit karnaa, or punerjeevit karnaa) kuch aisi sarkari pahalen hai jinka yahan ullekh karnaa zaruri he.
kan: swachh bharat abhiyan (swachchhate hagu parisar malinyad bagge janajagriti moodislu, bayalu mal visarjaneyannu coneganislu, mattu ghan tyajya nirvahaneyannu uttampadislu) mattu namami gangeyantah (ganga nadiy malinyadalli gamnarh ilike, sanrakshane mattu punashchetan) sarkaarad kelvu upakramagalu illi ullekharhavagive.
mal: (shuchitvattecurichu paristatimalinikaranttecurichu potubodha srushtikanu potusthalaille malavisarjjana illatackanu kharmalinya maneament mechchappetuttanu ull) swachgh bharat abhian, (ganga nadiile malinikaran ganyamai kurkanu atin sanrakshikanu punarujjivipikanu ull) namami gange tutangia chil sarkar udyams ivite paramarshayogyama.
ori: 'scch bharat abhiyaan' (parishkar parichnnatha tatha parivesh pradushan samparkare jan sachetantha srushti kariva pin, padare matttyagaku radd kariva, eban kathin varjawasthu parichanare unnati aniva pin) eban 'namami gangge' (pradooshnar ullekhaniya hras, gangga nadeer sanrakshan o punarujjeeban) bhadi sarkaari padakshepaguik madhyaru ketek ethare ullekhayogya .
pan: kuchh sarkari abhiaan jive ki saluchh bharat abhiaan( safaai te watavarna de pardushan baare smoohik jagarukta paidaa karna, khule vich vach te rok lagauni ate thos kuda da niyantaran sudhaarana) ate namami ganga(pardushan nuun ghatauna,ganga nadi di sambh te usnoo puner saprasht karna) ithe jikryog han I
tam: swach bharat abhiyon (suttom manllum sudduchural mashu basari vegujana vitipunarve erbadutum, dihant veliil malam galikkum palakkatai olixum, titakkaliu melanmiai membadutum tuvakgappattatu), namami gange (ganga nadi masadaivats ganismagak kuraittu, banikadu, puttuirutudal) bonthe chil arasut dittangs inge kufippitttakara.
tel: swachh bharat abhian (shubhrath mariyu paryavaran kalushya gurinchi prajallo avagahan kalpinchada, bahirang malavisrjannu nirmulinchada, ghan vyarth padarthal nirvahannu meruguparchada), namami gange (kalushyanni gananiyanga tagginchada, gangandini punaruddarinchada) vanti konni prabhutva karyakramas ikkad prastavincharginavi.
urd: svachh bhaarat abhiyaan (safai sthirai or maahulyati aaludagi ke baare main bade paimaane par bedaari paida karne, khile main rafaa hajit ko khatm karne or thos koode crookat ke intazaam ko behatar banane ke liye) or namami gange (ganga nadi kii aaludagi main numayan kamee, is kaa tohfiz or bahaali) jese hukuumat ke kuch ikdamaat yahaan kaabil zikr hain.
eng: Some of the government initiatives like Swachh Bharat Abhiyan (to create mass awareness on cleanliness and environmental pollution, to eliminate open defecation, and improve solid waste management) and Namami Gange (significant reduction of pollution, conservation and resuscitation of the river Ganga) are worth mentioning here.

ben: ekati manushya cough evan ekati kshatsah dhatav chokher superstark yekhane amra dekhi, khal yantramanvati "terminater" srushti karaar ghoshnati shudhumatra drushyati naya, icchakritvave vishadev vyakhya kare.
guj: matra dekhavani rite ja nahi, parantu aapne jayaare aa superstarne ek manav ankh ane ek dhatuni ijagrast ankh sathe joie chhie tyaare kharab robot jaherat kare che ke tene ‘‘terminater’’ banavya che, e rite eeradapurvak kahevama pan aave che.
hin: na sirf dekh kar, jahaan ham ek maanav aankh or ek kshatigrast dhatvik aankh vaale superstar ko dekhte hai, balki jaan-boojh kar spasht rup se bol kar bhi bataaya gaya he jab bura robot ghoshnaa karata he ki usne "terminetaron" kii sristi kar di he.
kan: souparstar ondu maanav kannu mattu innondu gayad guruthiruv lohad kanninondige namage kanasiguv drushyatmakateyalli matravallade, kutil yantramanvanu tanu “termineter”ganannu srushtisiruvudagi ghoshisuvudralliu adnnu uddeshpoorvakavagi vyaktpadislagide.
mal: oru manushyakkan matoru muripatuila lohakkannumulla super stari kanumpol kalochakondumatramall uddeshpuർvvakmayu tan "terminetre" are srushtichuven dushtakathapatramay roboat prakhyapiunnu.
ori: keval aakhire nuhen, yeunthare aame gotie manab akhi eban aau gotie kshatvikshat dhatab akhi thiva jane suparastarku dekhithau, baran uddeshyamutak bhavare kuhayaithaye madhya, yetevela sehi dust rovatti ghoshna karithaye ye se “terminetar” srushti karichhi.
pan: siraf drishtigat for 'te hi nahi, jithe aseen superstar nuun ik manukhi awkh naal ate ik daagi dhatu vaali awkh naal dekhade haa, per ih ve jan-budj ke kiha janda hai ki jadon bura robot ghoshna karada hai ki usne "termineterz " banaye han|
tam: itu, soopperstarukku woru pakkum manitak gan manllum mahupakkum tannumb ulokak gan iruppadan mulam, vellum katchi ritiyakak gattapaduvatu matuminri, kett robo than "derminatterss" uruvakyfatak assivipathan mulam, itutan nogkum enpatum welipaduttapadukintu.
tel: aa super star ni ala ock manav netra mariyu ock gayapumacchagal loh netranto chulin chot drushyaparangane kak, tanu 'terminaterlas" srustinchanu ani aa chedd robo prakatinchinapp adi uddeshyapoorvakamani spashta avutundi.
urd: na sirf basri tuur par , jahaan hum sper star ko ek insaani aankh or ek zakhm ke nishaan wali dhaati aankh waala dekhte hain , balki jaan bojh kar is vakt bhi bayaan karte hain jab bure robot ne elaan kiya ki is ne "termenetterz" banaaye hain.
eng: Not just visually, where we see the Superstar with one human eye and one scarred metallic eye, but also intentionally spelled out when the bad robot announces that he has created "Terminators."

ben: 8m shatabdeer vedic pandit o guru (acharya) adi shankar yekhane brahmaner sada upsthiter karna brahman-gyan saral evan kono 'cria' artha pracheshta o udyamer aprayojanita jor devan, sekhane gnaner madhyam hisabe mahakavyer anushilan evan yoga samadheer swikruti sah bistarit prastutimulak anushilner nirdesh die anyanya aadhyatmik shakha o pratha swikrut baiparityer janma deya advaitha pratha.
guj: athmi sadina vedic rishi ane shikshak (acharya) adi shankara dratapurvak janave che ke, brahmintva hanmesha hajar hoya che, brahmintva gyan tvarit che ane teni jaruriyat ‘akarm’ che, atle ke dridh prayas kare to advaith pranali pan kahe che ke vistrut purav tayari abhyas, mantrona dhyaan dharine yogic samadhi dwara gyanprapti karine, virodhabhas rache, je anaya aadhyatmik vidhao ane paramparama pan sweekrut thai che.
hin: prasiddh vaidic vidwaan or shikshak (acharya) aadi shankaracharya ne tab ek virodhabhas utpann kiya, jise anya aadhyatmik vishyon or paramparaon main bhi sweekaar kiya gaya, jab unhone jor dekar kaha ki kyonki brahm hameshaa maujuud he, brahm-gyaan tatkaal he or iske liye kisi "kriya", arthath, mehnat or prayaas, kii aavashyaktaa nahin he; mahavakyon ke bare main sochane or yogic samadhi ko gyaan ke maarg ke rup main sweekaar karne sahit advait parampara bhi vistrut praarambhik abhyaas kii anushansa karti he.
kan: brahmavu shashvatawagiruvaudaddarind brahmagyanvu pratyakshavadudu mattu adakkagi yavude “karm” endare parishram hagu prayatnad agatyaviruudill endu 8nae shatmanad pramukh ved vidwans mattu bodhakarad (aacharya) aadi shankararu otti heliddaradare, adit parampareyu, itar aadhyatmik shakhegalu mattu paramparegamalliu angikarislagiruvante, gyanad ondu sadhanvagi mahavakyagal chintane mattu yoga samadhiannu swikarisuvudannu olagondante jatilvad poorvasiddhateya anushthanvannu vidhisuv moolak virodhabhasvannu odduttade.
mal: brahma shashvatamanennatinal brahmagyana asananvu 'karmma', atayat, parishramvu adhvanvu aavashyamillatatanen etta nutandie pramukh vedapunditnu aacharyanumay aadishankar unnipparandeengil, adwaithasampradayam mahavakyaute dhyanvu gyanatinull marggamai yogasamadhiyu ulppatayull vipulmay prarambhkamay anushilanngൾ nirddeshikkayu angne mat aadhyatmikapaddhatikalu sampradayasu angikarikunn oru virodhabhas sambhwikkukayu cheiyunnu.
ori: 8ma shatabdeer vishist vaidik vidn eban shikshak (aacharyan), adi shankar guruth deithile ye, yehetu brahman sarvada upasthit, brahman-gyan tatkshanath ate eban ethire kaunsi 'karyanusthan'r, arthath sanggharsh o prayasar, darkaar padi nathaaye; adt parampara madhya savisthar sadhana pin nilem dharyan karithaye, yeunthire mahakabya vishakere bichaar kariva, eban yog aadharit samadhiku gyanar eka sadhan bhave bbbahar kariva antarbhukt, yaha eka virodhabhas srushti karithaye, yahaku anyanya aadhyathmik dhara o paramparare madhya skruti diayaishi.
pan: jadon 8 vin sadi de pramukh vedic vidawan ate adhiapak (acharya) adi shankara ne ish gal utte jor ditha ki, kiunki brahman srabviapak hai, brahman-gyan tatkaal hai ate us nuun kise 'sanghrush' di lod nahi hai, mathlab ki koshish ate jatan, adwait parampra ve vistrit dasadi hai. tiari abhias, mahavakia da chintan ate yogic samadhi nuun gyan de saadhan vajon savikar karna, ik virodhabhas pesh karna jise nuun hor adhyatmik anushasanas ate parampraavaan vich ve manta praapat hai.
tam: pradan 8aam noorthandu ved aricirum asanuman (aacharia) adi chankar, brahman nidhthiyamantu enpatal brahm gyanm nickonilai charndatu athangu 'vine' - adavatu ushipum muilse - devaill endu valiyuuttya fodhilu, adwaith mripu anatu mahavakkialack kuritch scindittal manllum yog samadhi gyantukan valiyag attrukkolludal udpat vilavariana ayattap pairchigales vidikkintu, itu oruvit muranbatte erbadudhuadakat donralam, anal pitt aanmikak kaddupattu valaies manllum mripughalilum itu angikricapaduvatu kufippittakkadu.
tel: brahman nityaminadi ayinandun brahmagyana takshnamainadi, daniki e 'charya', anaga e krishi mariyu prayatna avasaram ledu ani 8va shatabdpu pramukh ved pandit, guru (acharya) ayin adi shankar nokki cheppaga, advaith vidhana anedi mahavakyal gurinchi aalochinchada, yogasamadhini gyanmarganga parigrahinchada, itar aadhyatmik paddhatulu, sampradayala kuda gurtenchabadin vairudhyanni pradarshinchashanto saha vistrutamin sannahak abhyasanni kuda nirdeshistundi.
urd: jabaki 8 vaein sadi ke namor vedic iscollar or ustad (aacharya) aadi shankara ne jor diya ki, chunki brahman hamesha maujuud hota hai, brahman kaa ilm mitsal hota hai or use kisi 'amal' yani, jaduujahad or koshish kii zarurat naheen hoti, adwaitha ravayat mufasal tumhedi mishq bhi tijwez krati hai jis main mahavakyun kaa dhyaan or yogi samadhi ko ilm ke ek zarie ke tuur par kabuul karna shamil hai, ek jaahri tazad kaa izhaar kurta hai jo dusare ruhani nizaam amal or ravayat main bhi muslima hai.
eng: While the prominent 8th-century Vedic scholar and teacher (acharya) Adi Shankara emphasized that, since Brahman is ever-present, Brahman-knowledge is immediate and requires no 'action', that is, striving and effort, the Advaita tradition also prescribes elaborate preparatory practice, including contemplation of the mahavakyas and accepting yogic samadhi as a means to knowledge, posing a paradox which is also recognized in other spiritual disciplines and traditions.
