ben: tave, sei samay italy kanyarashir interferometreti kaaj karchil na, evan jiio600ti enginearing mode chhil o yathest sanvedanshil chhil na, tai seti sankettike nischit karte pareini.
guj: joke italima virgo interpherometer te samaye karyarat nahotu, ane ji.i.o.600 ijneri statema hatu ane te puratu sanvedanshil nathi, aathi te sanketani pushti kari shakyu nahi.
hin: haalanki us samay italy main virgo interpherometer kaam nahin kar rahaa tha or ji.i.o.600 ejineering mod main tha tathaa vah itnaa sugrahi bhi nahin he jiske kaaran usase sanket kii pushti nahin kii ja saki.
kan: aadagyu, aa samayadalli italiallin vargo vyatikaranamapakavu kaaryanirvahisuttiralill, mattu ji.i.o.600 sudharna hantadallittu, allade adu ashtu samvedanashilavallavaddarind adkke sanketavannu drispadislu agalill.
mal: ennaൽ aa samayt italile viർgo iൻraർferometർ pravർttanrahitu, enginiyaring modilayirunn jiio 600 matiyay grahyasheshiillatatu ayatinaൽ atin signൽ sthirikariaൻ kachinjill.
ori: avashya, italire bhargo interpherometer sehi samaure karyan karunathila, eban ji.i.o.600 enginishring modare thila eban yathest samvedanashil nathila, tenu eha sanketatiku nishchit karipari nathila.
pan: halanki, italy vich us samen virgo interpherometer com nahi kar riha see ate ji i o 600 engineering moud vich see ate naame hi bahutaa sanvedanshil see | ish lai ih sanket di pushti nahi kar sakda|
tam: eninu, achamayam italil irunth virco interperometre velai seyyevilly, manupuram jiyo600 poriial payanmuril irunghatal bodhia unardision kontrukkavilly, eneway athanal samikye urudisey mudiavilly.
tel: edemanappatiki, aa samayaulo italy loni vargo kanti tarangadairghya mapaka panichestu ledu, alage ji. i. o. 600 yantrasadhaka paddhatilo undi, taguvidhmain sukshmagrahakanga lekapovada to adi sanketanni rudiparchalekapoindi.
urd: taahim, is vakt italy main virgo tadaakhil paima kaam naheen kar raha tha, or ji e oo 600 engineering mod main tha or wo khaatir khwaah hasas naheen hai, is liye ye signal kii tasadiq naheen chriska.
eng: However, the Virgo interferometer in Italy was not operating at the time, and the GEO600 was in engineering mode and is not sensitive enough, so it could not confirm the signal.

ben: paypranali vyavstha ghatti thaka gramguli evan shahrer bastigulite swasthyakar swasthyavidheer janya jaiv-shaugagarjanit samadhaner srushti kareque enbiolet sabuj samadhan sanstha (ji.es.ef).
guj: enbiolet green solyushan foundeshan (ji.es.epa.) e gamdao ane shaheri jhuparpattima swachchhata mate ek byo toilate upay banaavyo che ke jema gater vyavasthano abhav che.
hin: enbiolet green solution foundation (ji.es.epa.) ne un gaanvon or shaharon main jhuggi jhonpadiyon main swasthkar safai vyavastha ke liye jaivik-shauchalay banaae hai jahaan par mel vyavastha thik nahin he.
kan: enbolett green salyushan foundeshan (ji.es.f.) charandi vyavasthayannu hondirad halligamalli mattu nagargamallin kosschegerigamalli aarogyakar nairmalyakkagi jaivik shauchalayad pariharavannu roopiside.
mal: malinajal sanskaran samvidhanmillat gramngutayu nagarsille chericautayu arogyapradmay shuchikaranttinai eൻbiolet green solyushan fauntion (ji.es.eph.) oru bio toy let pariharmarggam srushtichu.
ori: enbaolet green saljusan foundesan (ji.es.ef.), yeun gram o sehri basti manankare mal nishkasan pin kichhi brivastha naahin, se sabu anchader ssthokar parimal pin eka jaib-shaucharoor samadhan baahaar karichhi |
pan: onha pinds te shahirn vich basatia jinha vich sashachhata te mal-pravaah di vivstha nahi hai, onha lai inbyolat green salushan faundaishan ne byo-toilette da avishkar kitha hai I
tam: kavivunir agardudal amifu illat gramagalilum nagarfuck kudisep bakudikalilum arokiuman kalivarai vasadita valang anbiolet kirin solyushan poundeshan (jiesef) woru bio-toylett tirve uruvakyldu.
tel: anbyolet green solyushan foundesion (jiesef) muruguniti vyavasthal leni gramalas mariyu nagaralaloni murikivadlas arogyakarman parishudhyam kos ock bayo-toilet parishkaranni roopondinchindi.
urd: anbivilet green solyoshan foundation (ji es epa) ne in shaharon main dehaaton or kuchi aabaadiyon main hafizan sahat se mataalak safai sthirai ke liye ek bive twilt hal taiyaar kiya hai jahaan gand nikasi ke nizaam kaa fiqdaan hai.
eng: Enbiolet Green Solution Foundation (GSF) has created a bio-toilet solution for hygienic sanitation in villages and slums in cities that lack sewage systems.

ben: in.si.de antarbhukt kare anek pariweshgat roger ya maanav swasthyer pariharya o apariharya avasthar bistrut vibhagake kabhar kare, ya suryer alo, pushti, dushan evan jivandhara bikalper matan bahik karangulo dwara srist.
guj: en.sii.dee.maa suryaprakash, poshan, pradushan ane jeevanshailini pasandgio jevaan bahya paribalone karne manav swasthy stateni tali shakay tevi ane anivary stateoni vishal shrenine aavari letee paryavarniya bimariono samavesh thai che.
hin: en.si.di. main kai paryaavarniya rog shaamil hai jinke antargat vyapak virgon kii parihaary or aprihaary maanav swasthya sthitiyaan hai jo dhoop, poshan, pradooshan or chuni gai jeevanstyli jaise bahya karkon se hote hai.
kan: en.si.de.galu anek parisarik koilegannu olagondiddu, adralli sooryan belku, paushtikate, malinya, mattu jivan paddhatiya aaykegalantah bahya anshgalind untaguv tadegattabahudad mattu tadegattalagad maanav aarogya statigal vishalvad vargavu seride.
mal: suryaprakasham, poshanaharavyavasthi, malinikaran, jivitashileute teranjeetuppukൾ tutangia bahyaghankangൾ karanmunthakunn, ochiwakaൻ kaviunnatu allatatumay arogyaprashnathute oru vishalvibhagamaingunn niravadhi paristatebandhitmay rogangൾ eൻ. si. dikaliൽ uൾppetunnu.
ori: en.si.de. gudik madhyare anek pariveshika rog antarbhukt yaha madhyare bahya karakagudik yatha: suryaaloka, poshan, pradushan, eban jeevanastyligat abhiruchigudik dra srust bapak prakaarar pariharyan eban apariharyan manab ssthya avastha antarbhukt .
pan: in see di vich bohut saria watawarnak bimaria shaamil han jo ki suraj di raushani de poshan, pradushn ate jeevansaili de vikalpas, jiven ki ackstamal karks de kaaran, bachanyog ate atal manukhi sihat statea di ik vishal shreni nuun dakda hai|
tam: enciti enpatil pal sudduchural charnt nobenotis atankum, avantl vail, unavutam, mashu, vatakky muris bonthe pujak karnikalal erbatum tavirck mutiki manllum tavirck mudiyath woru parandhupatt manit noi nilis udbadukindena.
tel: sooryarashmi, ahara, kalushya mariyu jivan style ampikal vanti bahya karkal karnanga erpade niwarinchagal, mariyu niwarinchaleni manav arogya paristhitulu gal vistrut vargal kudin anek paryavaran sambandha vyadhulu ancidillo untai.
urd: en si dez main bahut se maahulyati amaraz shamil hain jo beroni awamil jese sooraj kii roshni, gazaait, aaludagi or taraz zindagi ke intakhaabat ke zarie hone wali kaabili ajitanaab or nagizir insaani sahat kii caphyat ke vasia zamre kaa ahaata karte hain.
eng: NCDs include many environmental diseases covering a broad category of avoidable and unavoidable human health conditions caused by external factors, such as sunlight, nutrition, pollution, and lifestyle choices.

tel: lavanikarna anedi tir prantalku, kott ondr maidanalku sambandhinchinadi kaaga, ksharikaran anedi akkuvamtuku lottt prantalu, paat ondr maidanalas jarugutundi.
urd: agarache selnabheeshan zyaada tar sahili ilaakon or chhote jazere ke maidaanon se wabasta hai, taahim ilclabheeshan zyaada tar indron malik or purane jazayri maidaanon main hoti hai.
eng: While salinization is mostly associated with coastal areas and younger alluvial plains, alkalization happens mostly in inland and older alluvial plains.

ben: islamer aagman buddha dharmer math aitihyer prati rajkian prushthaposhaktake apasaarit kare evan dirgha-durtber banijye musalmaan dwara buddhader pratisthapanti prushthaposhaktar sutaraguli kshaysadhan kare.
guj: islamna aagmane bauddha dharmany math paramparane maltu shahi samarthan dur karyu ane bauddhono lamba antarno vepar muslimo paase aavata temana samarthan matena sadhano pan sukai gayan.
hin: islam ke aane se buddha dharm ke mathvaadi parampara ko milane vaala shahi sangrakshan hat gaya or lambii duuri ke vyapaar main musalamaanon dwaara buddha dharm ke paalan karne waalon ko visthapit kar die jane se sangrakshan ke sambandhit strot bhi khatm ho gaye.
kan: islamn aagamanvu bauddhadharmiya bhikshugal paramparegidd rajashrayavannu illvagisitu, mattu doordeshgalondigin vyapaaradalli bauddhar sthanvannu muslimaru akramisicondudarind adarondige sambaddhawagidd protsahak moolagalu kshaisidvu.
mal: buddhamatatine sanyas sampradayattinull rajkiya rakshakartrutva islaminte varavote nikum cheyyappetukayu, dirghdur vyaparttil buddhamatakkaർkkupakar muslims vannatumulam bandhappet rakshakartrutvasrothassukal ashaktamavukyu cheitu.
ori: islamr aagman hetu buddha dharmar baudhdhabihar paramparaku missuthiva rajakiya prushtpogukathar ant ghatithila, eban dooravartti bavasacre buddhadharmabalambimanank sthan musalmanmane neva pare sehi sambandhiya utsaru aasuthiva prushtposhkatha madhya bandh hoiyaithila.
pan: islam de an naal, bodhi dharam de math rivaaj nuun milan vaali shahi sarprasati katam hoo gai,ate musalmaanaas duara lami duuri de wapar vich bodhiya di tha lan naal sarprasati de sambandhit sarot khatam hoo gaye.
tam: islatin varuki tuddvachu mripan pauttom pellruvant arach adrav agarriyatu, melum netundoor vardakatil bhauttarkass muslimgas pathilidu seyttal menopati adroud dodarpana aadharangs nirthup boina.
tel: islan rakato buddhamat sanyas sampradayaniki racharik poshan agipoindi, sudur vanijyanlo buddhul sthanaion muslim ravadanto sambandhit poshak vanarulu tarigipoyai.
urd: islam kii aamad se budh math kii khankaahi ravayat kii shahi suraprasti khatm hogai, or musalamanon ke zarie tavel faasale kii tizarat main budh math ke pairokaron kii jagah lene se suraprasti ke mataalika jaria khatm hogaye.
eng: The arrival of Islam removed the royal patronage to the monastic tradition of Buddhism, and the replacement of Buddhists in long-distance trade by the Muslims eroded the related sources of patronage.

ben: bagha yatin, khudiram basu, bhag tsing, chandrashekhar azad, surya sen, evan subhash chandra bosser mato biplavira ingrej shasanar viruddhe tander abhiyane sahinstar prayog gandhiji thek alada chhillen.
guj: wagha jatin, khudiram boj, bhagath singh, chandrashekhar azad, surya sen ane subhash chandr boj jevaan kratikario angrej raj sameni temani ladatma hinsana upayog ange gandhithi alag vichaarata hatan.
hin: bagha jatin, khudiram bose, bhagat singh, chandrashekhar azaad, surya sen or subhash chandra bose jaise krantikari british shashan ke khilaaf apane abhiyaan ke dauraan hinsa ke prayog ke sambandh main gandhi se bhinn the.
kan: bagha jatin, khudiram bos, bhagat singh, chandrashekhar aazad, soorya sane, mattu subhash chandra bosarantah kratikarigalu british aadlitad virudh tamm chaluvaligamalli hinseannu balsiddudralli gandhigint bhinnaveniceidru.
mal: british bharanatinetiraull tangute rashtriyapravർttanattil hinsa upyogikunn karyattil bagha jatin, khudiram bose, bhagat singh, chandrashekhar azad, soorya sen, subhashchandrabos enni viplavakaril gandhiot viojicchu.
ori: bagha yateen, khudiram bosh, bhagath singh, chandrashekhar ajaad, suryasen eban subhash chandr boshank bhadi vipleveemane inrej shasan virudhre semanankar abhiyaan samaure hinsar prajogaku nei gandhink tharu bhinna thile .
pan: bagha jatin , khuderum bose, bhagat singh, chandrasekhar ajaad, suria sen, ate subhash chandra bose varge krantikari british shashan viruddha apnia hinsk muhima kaaran gandhi ton bakhre san|
tam: british arasuku ethrana tangas borattin podhu vanmuraiyike kaiyalvatu kuritu baga jatin, kudiram bose, bhagat singh, chandraseker aajad, surya sen, subhash chandra bose bonthe puradsialarlukum kandhiatilukum itie karutu vedupadu nilaviyadu.
tel: bagha jatin, khudiran bose, bhagat singh, chandrashekhar azad, soorya sen, subhash chandr bose vanti viplavakarulu british palanku vyatirekanga chese tam udyamalas hinsan upayoginchadalo vaaru gandhito vibhedincharu.
urd: bartanvi hukmrani ke khilaaf apni mahimon ke dauraan baga jatan, kudi ram bose, bhagat singh, chandra shekhar azaad, surya sen, or subhash chandra bose jese inkulabyon kaa apne tushdad kaa istemaal karna inhen gandhi se alag kurta tha.
eng: Revolutionaries such as Bagha Jatin, Khudiram Bose, Bhagat Singh, Chandrashekar Azad, Surya Sen, and Subhas Chandra Bose differed from Gandhi in their use of violence during their campaigns against British rule.

ben: trini dekhan ye, prakrutir vismay athva brahmander aapat niyamanuvartita thek sangruhith bhagwaner astitva pramaner pradhan yuktiguli sabak'ti virodhitayogya (nirdisht kichu jaghanya kittpatanger astitve vismyer kii ach, samast grahaguli praia anurup samatle ghurnaner paryavekshane niyamanuvartitar ki ach, anurup samatal lakshanian hate parto kintu 'praia anurup samatal' anek kam vishwasayogya).
guj: teo daakhve che ke eshwarne sabit karva mate thati moti dalilo, prakrutini ajayabiothi mandi, brahmandni dekhiti niyamitata, badhu ja virodh mate khullu che ( aashcharya e che ke ketlak khas pratikul jantuonu astitva che, tamam grahona nirikshanma kai niyamitata che ke te tamam lagbhag ek sarkha vimaan jevaan che, kadaaya age vimaan tratake pan kharan, aa ‘lagbhag ek sarkhan vimaan’ e khub ochhu pratithijanak che.
hin: ve dikhaate hai ki bhagwaan ke astitv ko siddh karne ke liye die jane vaale tark, jaise ki prakruti ke chamatkaar yaa brahmad kii spasht niyamitata, sabhi ko chunauti di ja sakati he (kuch vishesh rup se ghrinaaspad keedon ke astitv main kya aashcharya he, or is avlokan main kya niyamitata he ki sabhi grah lagbhag ek hi samakshetra main ghoomte hai, ek hi samakshetra asaadhaaran ho saktaa tha, lekin "lagbhag ek hi samakshetra " bahut kam vishwasaneey he).
kan: prakrutiya vismayagalind hididu illave melnotekke kaanuv vishvad krambaddhateyavarege devar astitvavannu pratipadislu mundivlad pramukh tarkagalellavu aakshepanege idagabahudu endu aat torisicoduttane (kelvu nirdishtwagi asahyakarveniceuv krimigal astitvadalli yav adbhutavide, ell grahagalu hecchukadime onde samatladalli thiruguttve emb avalokanadalli yav niyatateide, onde samatal endiddaradaru gamnarhavagiruttittu, adare ʼhecchukadime onde samatalʼ ennuvudannu adbhutavendu oppuvudu sadhayvill).
mal: daivatte sthapican munnottu wekkunn, prakrutiille vismayaso prapantatine pratyakashniyatattvamo polull pradhanvadaellam ethiർppukൾk vidheyamanen addeha kaniunnu (visheshichu arapulawakkunn chil pranicute nilenilppil entu vismayam, grahaellam etand one talattil bhramant cheiyunnuvennatil entu niyatatva, oruvel one talattil chalichirunnengil at manassൽ kollumairunnuvengil 'etand one talattil' ennuparyunnatin vairekkuchchalle vishwasyat).
ori: se dekhaiyanthi ye, eeshranku siddh kariva pin upasthapit pramukh yukthiguik, prakrutir vismangudik tharu kimba brahmander pratirman nitmanuvarttitha, e sabugudik upare aapatti uthayaipare (kichhi nirddist ghrunya keetamanank asthithre emithi ka’na ashcharyokar ajji, samast grahamane ye pakhapakhi gotie samathal kshetrare bulithanthi, ehi sadharan nirikshanre epari kana nishmitatha rahichhi, eka nirddist samathal kshetra huet eka chamatkar hoi parithanta, kintu 'pakhapakhi gotie samathal kshetra' khubb kam vishsayogya ate).
pan: oh ih darsounda hai ki bade vivaad rab nuun saabat karan lai kithe gaye, kudrat de nazara ton li ke braman di safsht niyamtata tak, saabh itaraaz lai khulhe han (khaas for 'te ghenaune keede-makuras di hond vich ki hairaani di gal hai, ish nirikhan vich ki niyamtata hai ki saare graha lagaing iko hi samatal vich badalde han, uhi jahaaz shid takraa riha hove per lagaing uhi jahaaz kaafi ait yakinn hai) .)
tam: iyaskain atikyangana alltu prabhanjatn chirmaye munwaittu kataul iruppads nirupick murbatum mukiya vatangs yaum adchepanyuriyane (kufippitt chil vellukkattakk puchigalin irupill appadienna atichyam ulldu, anaukh kirahanglum aittang one samadaqtil suhalkinsona endu kavanicoppatt gutail appadienna chirmay irukkintu, are one samadaqtil sulangal achariappatalam anal 'aittang one samadaqtil' enpatu peritak endach sansham alifpatill) anpats avar viskik gaddukirar.
tel: devunni niroopingdaniki mundukochin pradhan vadanlanni abhyantaral svikarinchadaniki siddhanga unnavenni aayan chupistar (konni pratyekamain asahyamin kitakal unikilo e vismayam undi, grahalanni dadapu one samatlatlo thirugutunnayann parishilnalo e kramtvan undi, one samatalam anedi adbhutamavavacchu kani ""dadapu one samatalam"" anedi antaga aamodayogyamindiga ledu).
urd: wo dikhaata hai ki kudarat ke ajayabaat yaa qaynaat kii jaahri najam se khuda ko saabit karne ke liye pesh kiye jane waale ahim dilayal par har ke itrazat kiye jaskte hain( balkhsus baaz karahat angez kede makudun ke vajood main kiya ajooba hai, is mishaahide main kiya najam hai ki tamaam siyaare takreeban ek hi satah main gardish karte hain, ek hi satah hairat angez ho sakati thi lekin 'takreeban ek jaisi satah' bahut kam kayal kin hai).
eng: He shows that the major arguments advanced to prove God, from the wonders of nature or the apparent regularity of the universe, are all open to objection (what wonder is there in the existence of certain particularly repulsive insects, what regularity is there in the observation that all the planets turn in nearly the same plane, the same plane might have been striking but 'nearly the same plane' is far less convincing).

ben: yaihok, packejati drut vastawayaner puraskar swarup, bank avedanpatrati grahan karaar 90 diner madhye anumodith packejati vastavayit haley, punargoner avedanti bank grahan karaar samarkar avastha sampader shrenivibhager avasthanti firie aana yete par.
guj: am chhataan, pekejana jhadpi amalikaranna protsahan tarike, jo bank dwara araji maliana 90 divasma manjuur pekejane amalma mukavama aave che, to mudi vargikaranni paristhite e state sudhi punahasthapit thai shake che, je bankane punavrachanani araji malya samaye astitvama hati.
hin: tathaapi, package ke twarit karyanvayan ke liye protsaahan ke rup main,agar anumodith package bank dwaara aavedan praapt karne ke 90 dinon ke bheetar karyanvit kiya jaataa he to aasti vargeekaran kii sthiti bank dwaara punarrachana kaa aavedan praapt karne ke samay vaale str par punah sthapit kii ja sakati he.
kan: aadagyu, pakejannu shighravagi kaaryagatagolisuvudannu uttejislu, banku manjurad pakejannu tannind arji swikrutvad dinankadind 90 dinagal olage kaaryagatagolisidare, swattu vargikaran stateannu bankinind marurchaneya arjiyu swikrutwadag idd sthandlliye punatesthapisabahudu.
mal: ennirunnal, apeksh bankin kiti 90 divasaiateull angikrut pakkej natapakukaanangil, pakkej vega natappilakkunnatinull protsahana end nileil, pun:sanghayanyculla apeksh bankin kittunnatinu munpural nilei asthiute varggikaran nilevar pun:sthapicenstan.
ori: matra, pakejtir shighra karyankaritha nimanthe, eka protsahan bhavare, yadi anumodith pakejti bank dra aavedan patr prapth hebar 90 din madhyare bankti dra karyankaari hue, ta'helle sampatthi bargeekaran statetiku sehi stateku punathasthapit karayyparib yahaki bankati dra punargathan aavedhanati gruhith heva samaure vidyaman thila .
pan: parantu protsahan de tor te, gathdi di cheti tamil de lai , jeee mazurshuda gathdi baink wichon arzi di raseed de 90 dinaas wichon lagu hoo jandi hai, taan jaaidad da vargikaran da darja wapas usi sthal vich aa jaavega jithe pahilaan see jadon arzi baink valon praapat hoi see I
tam: eninu ind packajai virivag natamuripadutt ukkamalikkum vaqail, ankikarmalitt packajai ant bangi tamaku vinnappam vant dateilrundhu 90 natgalukul natamuripaduti irindhal, manugatamibbukkan vinnapatai ant bangi pellibodhu nilavia ade niliku syettu vakipadutal nilai meedgappatalam.
tel: ayite, banku darkhastunu svikarinchin tedi nudi 90 rojullopu amodinchabadin packegini amalu cheste, packegini tvaritanga amalu chessinanduku protsahakanga, sampad vargikaran stateni banku punarvyavasthikaran darkhastunu svikarinchinappati stateki punaruddharinchavacchu.
urd: taahim, package ke foree nafaaz ke liye ek targeb ke tuur par, agar manzoor shudaa package ko bank ke zarie darkhwaast musuul hone kii taarikh se se 90 din ke indra bank kii taraf se nafiz kiya jataa hai, to asaappa jaat kii darja bindi kii haisiyat ko is mukaam par bahal kiya jasakta hai jo is vakt tha jab bank kii taraf se ri stricturang kii darkhwaast musuul hui thi.
eng: However, as an incentive for quick implementation of the package, if the approved package is implemented by the bank within 90 days from the date of receipt of the application by the bank, the asset classification status may be restored to the position which existed when the restructuring application was received by the bank.

ben: ei mahakumar praia 45% (upakulian anchaler kshetre praia 60%) barshik vrushtipat ei samaikaler vrushtipater madhye antarbhukt.
guj: aa petavibhaagana aashare 45% varshik varsaad ( dariyankanthana vistaro mate aashare 60% dwara) ni ganna aa galana varsaad dwara thai che.
hin: is samyavadhi main hone vaali varsha is upkhand kii vaarshik varsha ke 45 pratishat (tateey kshetron ke liye lagbhag 60 pratishat) ke liye uttaradaayi he.
kan: i upavibhagad 45%ashtu varshik maleyu (karavali pradeshsgalige sumaru 60%ashtu) i avadhialli baruv maleindle aguttade.
mal: i sab divishanile varshik varshpatatine etand 45% (tiradeshttanangil etand 60% ) i kalayalville marr mulama.
ori: ehi upakhandatir barshik bristipatar praia 45% (upakookvartti anychalguthikare praia 60%) bristipat ehi samaure hoithaye.
pan: ish upmandal (tatvarti ilakaia lai 60 pratisht) di 45 pratisht warshik barsh ish daur vele hundi hai I
tam: ind udbirandhyatin sumar 45% varudandra manai (katalorap bakudiluku 60%) indep paruvakalatil erbatum manipocivin mulame kidikiritu.
tel: i upavibhagauloni varshik varshpatalo dadapu 45% (tir prantalku sumaru 60%) i vyavadhilo kurise varshpata dwara wastendi.
urd: is zeli dvision kii salana barish kaa takreeban 45 faisad (sahili ilaakon ke liye takreeban 60 faisad) is muddat ke dauraan hone wali barish se mahasuub kiya jataa hai.
eng: About 45% of the annual rainfall of this subdivision (about 60% for coastal regions) is accounted for by the rainfall during this period.

ben: purushader parkiyagat sharirik samparker ghatnake 6ti sabhyata "vishwajanin" hiseve, 29ti sabhyata "madhyapanthi" hiseve, 6ti sabhyata "aksmik" hiseve evan 10ti sabhyata "viral" hiseve barnana kara has.
guj: purush dwara lagn bahya jaatiya sambandhonu ch sanskritima ‘sarvatrik’, 29 sanskritioma ‘sadharan’, ch sanskritima ‘kavachit’ ane 10 sanskritioma ‘asadharan’ roope varnan thayu che.
hin: purushon dwaara vivahetar yon sambandh rakhana 6 samskritiyon main "saamaanya" hone ke rup main varnit he, 29 samskritiyon main "kuch had tak saamaanya" kaha gaya he, 6 samskritiyon main "kabhi-kabhaar" hone vaala kaha he or 10 samskritiyon main ise "asaamaanya" mana gaya he.
kan: purusharalli vivahetar lingikateya sambhvavannu 6 sanskritigamalli "sarvatrik"vendu, 29 sanskritigamalli "sadharan"vendu, 6 sanskritigamalli "sandarbhik"vendu, mattu 10 sanskritigamalli "aparup"vendu bannislagide.
mal: purushanmarute vivahetar lingikabandha aru sanskaras "sarvatrica" ennu 29 sanskaras "mit" ennu 10 sanskaras "asadharan" ennu vivaricppetunnu.
ori: purushamanank dra vivah bahaare yun samparkaku 6ti sanskrutire "sarvajanin", 29ti sanskrutire "madhum", 6ti sanskrutire "anikhmit" eban 10ti sanskrutire "asbhavik" bhavare varnana karayaishi .
pan: maradas duara vyah ton bood bahrle srirak sambandhs di maujuudgi nuun 6 sabhiachars vich "sarav vyapak" , 29 sabhiachars vich "madham" ate 6 sabhiachars vich "kade kadai" ate 10 sabhiachars vich "asadharan" vajon darsaya gya hai|
tam: angus manavalouku vellie udalunu kollum bhoky 6 kalacharangs "bodhwanavai" enllum, 29 kalacharangs "safru bodhwanavai" enllum, 6 kalacharangs "awwapodhu natapparai" enllum, 10 kalacharangs "aritanus" enllum chittarikinsona.
tel: magavarilo vivahetar sambhog sanghatnal 6 samskritulas "sarvatrikan" ani, 29 samskritulas "mosthru" ani, 6 samskritulas "appudapp jarigedi" ani, 10 samskritulas "asadharana" ani varninchabadindi.
urd: mardon ke zarie shadi se baahar jinsi taalkat kii maujudagi ko 6 muqaafaton main "alamgir", 29 muqaafaton main "matidal", 6 muqaafaton main "kabhi kabhi" or 10 muqaafaton main "gair aam" ke tuur par bayaan kiya gaya hai.
eng: The occurrence of extramarital sex by men is described as "universal" in 6 cultures, "moderate" in 29 cultures, "occasional" in 6 cultures, and "uncommon" in 10 cultures.

ben: labu jatiya fal mulath jamaicar centrian anchale visesh kare 1000-2,500 foot uchitar madhye upadan kara has.
guj: santaranu fal mukhyatve jamaicana kendriya bhagama ugaday che, khas karine 1,000 - 2,500 footni vachcheni unchaaie.
hin: nimbu vansh ke fal mukhya rup se jamaica ke madhya bhaagon main, vishesh rup se 1000-2500 feet kii oonchaai par ugaae jate hai.
kan: nimbe jaatiya hannannu mukhyavagi jamaicad madhyabhagagamalli, nirdishtwagi 1,000-2,500 adigal naduvin ettarad pradeshgamalli beleyalaguttade.
mal: jamaicayute maddhyabhaga, visheshichu 1,000 mutal 2,500 ativarayull uyaralila, narakvarggappate pradhanmayu krishi cheiyunnat.
ori: lembu jatiya briksh mukhitah jamaicar kendriya anychalguthikare, visheshtah 1,000-2,500 footor uchch sthangudik madhyare, chaash karayaaye .
pan: nimbu jaati da fal mouth for 'te jamaika de cendari hisas vich ugaya janda hai, khaas karke 1,000-2,500 foot di uchaayi de wichkaar |
tam: citrus palangas mukhiamak jamaicavin maiyab bakudikasil, kurippak 1,000-2,500 adi uyarattil valarcopadukindena.
tel: jamaica kenter prantallo akkuvaga nimmajati pands penchtaru, mukhyanga 1,000 -2,500 adugul madhya attulas.
urd: jamaica ke vasati hisson main khaas tuur par 1,000-2,500 foot kii bulandi ke darmiyaan trunji fal ugaye jate hain.
eng: Citrus fruit is mainly grown in the central parts of Jamaica, particularly between the elevations of 1,000-2,500 feet.

ben: hindu dharmagranth bahu sahastr kaal dhare sammanit evan samrudh sanskruthik aitihyer dharak o bahak hay ach naditi.
guj: hindu shastroma aa nadi ghani sahastrabdiothi pavitra ganati aavi che ane te ek samrudh samskruthik warsae aashray ane poshan aapti rahi che.
hin: yah nadi kai hazaron varshon se hindu dharmagranthon main bahut poojaneey maani jaati rahi he or ek samrudh saanskrithik viraasat ko aashray or poshan detii rahi he.
kan: i nadiynne sahasraaru varshagalind hindus dharmagranthagamalli poojyabhavadind kanalagide, mattu iglu adu samrudhvaad sanskruthik paramparege neleyagie porita ide.
mal: pal sahasrabdanslai hindumatgranthas adritchuporunn i nadi ipporau oru sampannmay sanskarikapitruka potivalartunnund.
ori: sehi nadi hajaarahajar barsh dhari hindu shastrare poojniya hoi rahichhi eban eka samrudh sanskrutik aitihkar sanrakshan o poshan karichalithi.
pan: ish nadi nuun kai hajaar saalas ton hindus granths vich vaapis lya gya hai ate ik amir sabhiachark viraasat nuun bandargah ate poshan dinda hai|
tam: ind nadi ballaram varushmak indu vedalil poschopattrukkintu, atot inniku varikum athangu romp senipana kalasarap​ bharambariamum irukkintu.
tel: anno sahasrabdaluga i nadi hindus granthala poojinchabadi ippatiki susampannamin samskritik varasatva rakshan poshistondi.
urd: hazaaron saalon tak hindu sahifon main is dariya kaa ehtiram kiya gaya or ye aaj bhi ek matmol muqaafati varkee kii hifaazat kar raha hai or use paravan chadhaa raha hai.
eng: The river has been revered in Hindu scriptures for many millennia and continues to harbour and nourish a rich cultural heritage.

ben: 1912 sale dadasaheb phalke pratham bhartiya animeshan chhabir prayojna karechillen yar pare 40 bachreroo beshi samyer ekata birati pade ya.
guj: 1912maa, dadasahib phalkee pratham bhartiya anemeshan cinemanu nirman karyu ke jenu anusaran ek shrunkhlae karyu je 40 varshathi vadhu chaali.
hin: 1912 main dadasaheb phalke ne pehali bhartiya anemation film banaai or uske baad 40 se zyaada varshon tak ek antaraal bana rahaa.
kan: 1912ralli, dada saheb phalkeyavaru mottamodal bhartiya animeshan chalanchitravannu bidugade madidru, ader nantar 40 varshagaligintalu hechu kaal shoonya aavarisittu.
mal: 1912l daada saheb phalke chalikunn adyatte indiansinim nirmmikukayu atettutr nalpathylate varsha ninduninn oru vit undavukayu cheitu.
ori: 1912 masihare, dadasahib falke pratham bharatiya animesan chakchchitra nirman karithile, yaha pare pare eka shoonesthan srushti hoithila yahaki 40 varsharu adhik samay dhari rahithila .
pan: dadasahib phalke ne bharat di pihali jeewant chitra film 1912 vich pesh keeti , jise ton bood agali film 40 saalas ton bood ai I
tam: 1912il dadasaheb phalke muthal india bommap badaddait dayarithar, adanbin atil woru 40 andukal peru idiveli ettpattatu.
tel: 1912 lo, dadasaheb falke toli bhartiya aanimesion chitranni nirmincharu, dani taruvat vachchin viram 40 ell pine konsagindi.
urd: 1912 main dada sahab phalke ne pahali hindustani anemishan film taiyaar kii, jis ke baad ek tauqf aayaa jo 40 saal se zyaada urse tak jari raha.
eng: In 1912, Dadasaheb Phalke produced the first Indian animation movie, which was followed by a hiatus that lasted over 40 years.

ben: sindhu sabhyataa bivinn kshetre sekhankar prayuktigat gnaner janya parichit.

hin: sindhu ghati sabhyataa vibhinn kshetron main apane takneekee gyaan ke liye jaani jaati he.

mal: vividh mekhalkalile sarsketikagyanatinu peruketta sindhunaditatsanskar.

ben: si.de.aich.aar.aai pratyekke "taar desher sadharan prashasana pratyaksh athva parokshabhave anshgrahaner adhikar"-era pratishruti pradaan kare.
guj: sii.dee.ech.ar.ai. avi pan tamam vyaktione ‘pratyaksh ke paroksh rite tena deshni jaher babatoma bhag levanan adhikar’ni banhedhari aape che.
hin: si.di.ech.aar.ai. yah bhi sunishchit karata he ki har ek vyakti ko "apane desh ke lok kaaryon ke prashasan main pratyaksh athwa apratyaksh rup se bhaag lene kaa adhikaar he."
kan: pratiobb vyaktigu "pratyakshvagi illave parokshvagi tann deshad sarvajanik vyavahaargal aadlitadalli bhagwahisuv hakkannu" sah si.de.ech.aar.i. dhrudapadisuttade.
mal: " avanavൻre rajyatine potuvishyasute natatippil nerito allathayo pankucheranural avkash"vu ella vyaktikalku si.de.ech .ar.ai. udhapu nalkunnu.
ori: si.de.ech.aar.aai. madhya samast brekthivisheshank nimanthe "nij deshar sarvajanin baparagudikar parichanare, prattaksh kimba paroksh bhavare, bhaag nebar adhikar" tiku sunishchit karithaye .
pan: si di aich aar aai saare viakatia nuun "aapne desh de jantak mammlas de pradarshan vich sidhe jaaa asidhe for 'te hisa lan de adhikar" di garanti ve dinda hai|
tam: cedihesarai ella manidharlukum "avaravritu nottin potu vivkarangana nirvakipatil neradiakao mahimukamakavo bankeekum urimiku" utravadaj alikkintu.
tel: sidihecharai vyaktulandariki "tam desh praja karyakalapal nirvahanalo, neruga gani parokshanga gani, palgone hakku" ki hami kalpistundi.
urd: si dee each aar aai tamaam afarad ko "apne malik ke awami maamlat kii intazaamy main brah rasat yaa bolwasta tuur par hissaa lene kaa haq" bhi detaa hai.
eng: The CDHRI also guarantees all individuals the "right to participate, directly or indirectly, in the administration of his country's public affairs."

ben: eti basar ghare ekati 60.6 inch (154 semi) chaora du'jan basar mato helan dewa sopha evan 32 inch (81 semi) tube monitor visisht; shawar sah lagoa ekati bathroom; showar ghare ekati 82 inch (210 semi) lamba, 47.5 inch (121 semi) chaora du'janer bichaana, yar madhye ekati 27 inch (69 semi) tube monitor evan ekajan vyaktigat khansamao antarbhukt.
guj: ema samel che vishram khandama 60.6 inch (154 semi) paholo be betkawalo lachilo sofa ane 32 inch (81 semi)na padadavalu telivithan ane phuvara satheno sankalit snanakhand ane tatha 27 inch (69 semi) padadawala telivithan sahitna shaynkhandma 82 inch (210 semi) lambo ane 47.5 inch (121 semi) paholo bevado palang tatha ek vyaktigat babarachi.
hin: ek 32 inch (81 se.me.) kaa tii.ve. monitor, 60.6 inch (154 se.me.) chaudaa do siton vaala letne vaala sopha, kamare se laga hua phuhaare vaala snanaghar, 82 inch (210 se.me.) lanbaa, 47.5 inch (121 se.me.) chaudaa dabl bed, or saath hi saath ek nijee naukar, sab-kuch is kamaron ke set ke saath shaamil he.
kan: idu aramkhaneyalli eradu asanagalull 60.6 inchu (154 cem.me.) agalad orgu sofa mattu 32 inchin (81 cem.me.) ti.vi. parde; ader bhagavagiye iruva, vrishtisnanad sadhanvull snanagrah; malaguv koneyalli 82 inchu (210 cem.me.) udd, 47.5 inchu (121 cem.me.) agalad jody manch, jotege 27 inchin (69 cem.me.) ti.vi. parde, mattu obb khasa maniannu hondide.
mal: leൻjil 60.6-inch (154 seൻrimetre ) vidiyultu randuperk changiriavunnatumay sofayu 32-inch (81 seൻrimetre ) ti vi monitteru shavarulla attachd bath rumu, 82-inch (210 seൻrimetre) niqvu 47.5-inch (121 seൻrimetre) vidiyumulla duble beddu 27-inch (69 seൻrimetre) ti viyu atangia oru kiloppumuriyu kute oru swakarya pachakakarnu undaku.
ori: ethire baithk ghare eka 60.6-inch (154 se.mi.)-osarayukt dui-sit-vishist ouji heuthiva sofa eban 32-inch (81 se.mi.) ti.bhi. monitor; eka shar thiva sanlagn bathroom; shoiva ghare eka 82-inch (210 se.mi.)-lamb, 47.5-inch (121 se.mi.)-osarayukt dubal beh yeunthi madhya 27-inch (69 se.mi.) r eka ti.bhi. monitor, tatha jane brekthigat paricharak rahiyanthi.
pan: ish dis vishestas han; 60.6 inch (154 saimi) chuda, doo sits waala letwa sofa ate diudhi vich 32 inch (81 saimi) tivi manitor; fuhaare waala naal lagvaan guslkhana; 82 inch (210 saimi) lambai, bedroom vich 47.5 inch (121 saimi) dabal baibba, ish vich ve ik 27 inch (69 saimi) tivi manitor hai ate ik niji khansamas
tam: ingu varaverbaqil woru 60.6 ankul (154 semi) akalamull iru sayu-irukki chopa manllum 32 ankul (81 semi) divi tires, woru visal soguchin bagudiyag shawar vasadil kuliyalathes, badukkiyaqil 82 ankul (210 semi) nilmum 47.5 ankul (121 semi) akalamum kont ruttiep badukkes adanuton ore 27 ankul (69 semi) divi tires, tanippatt unup parimale ulier vasade undu.
tel: i vishranti gadilo 60.6-angulal (154 se.mi.la)-vadalpugal tu setar ricklaining sofa mariyu 32-angulal (81 se.mi.la)tivi monitor; prakkane shavarto kudin snanalagadi; padak gadilo 82 angulalu (210 se. mi.) podw, 47.5 (121 se. mi.) vedlpu gal jat manchan, dinitopat 27 angulalu (69 se. mi.) ti. vi., mariyu ock vyaktigat paricharak untar.
urd: is kii khasuseyat main baraande main ek 60.6 inch (154 centi meter) chaudaa do nishasti khamida hone waala sofa or 32 inch (81 centi meter) kaa tii vee monitor, shower ke saath ek milehka gusul khaanaa, khwaab gah main ek 82 inch (210 centi meter) lambaa, 47.5 inch (121 centi meter) chaudaa dubbal bed, jis main ek 27 inch (69 centi meter) kaa tii vee monitor, or ek zaati butler bhi shamil hai.

ben: bharte du'to iner adhine vivah nivandhikaran kara ya, 1954-era visesh vivah ine evan 1955-era hindu vivah ine.
guj: bharata be kaayadaa hethal lagnni nodhani karavi shakay che, 1954no special merage act ane 1955no hindu merage act.
hin: bharat main shaadiyaan do adhiniyamon ke tahat register kii ja sakati hai, vishesh vivaah adhinium 1954 or hindu vivaah adhinium 1955.
kan: bharatadalli maduvegathann eradu kaydegavdialli nondaisbahudu, 1954r visesh maduve kaide mattu 1955r hindus vivaah kayde.
mal: indiail vivaha rantu niyamngsu kisheel register cheyya, 1954 le spashyal maryej aktu 1955le hindu maryej aktu.
ori: bharatre vivah punjeekaran duiti adhinium anuyani karayipare, speshal myaraj aakt-1954 eban hindu myaraj aakt-1955.
pan: bharat vich vyah doo adhinium heth rejist hunde han, 1954 da speshal marij act ate 1955 da hindus marij act I
tam: indiaill kalyana riginster pann erandu chattas irukkinsona, 1954 sicipu tirumanach sattam, 1955 indu tirumanach sattam.
tel: bharatvaeshalo vivahalni rend chattal kind namodu cheyavacchu, okati, pratyek vivah chatta, 1954, inca rendodi hindus vivah chatta, 1955.
urd: hindustan main do kavanian ke tahat shaadiyaan register kii jasakati hain, 1954 kaa khasusi shadi kanoon or 1955 kaa hindu shadi kanoon.
eng: Marriages can be registered under two acts in India, the Special Marriage Act of 1954 and the Hindu Marriage Act of 1955.

guj: gondvana ane vindhyanani pankhama madhya pradesh, chhattisgarh, odisha, bihar, jharkhand, paschim bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu ane kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan ane uttarakhandna bhag samayelam che.
hin: gondvanaa or vindhyas apni simaaon main madhya pradesh, chhattisgarh, odisha, bihar, jharkhand, pashchim bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu -kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan or uttarakhand ke bhaag shaamil karte hai.
kan: gondvan mattu vindhya parvatgalu tamm vyaptiyalli madhyapradesh, chhattisgarh, odisha, bihar, jharkhand, paschim bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu mattu kashmere, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan, mattu uttarakhandd bhagagainnu olagondive.
mal: madhyapradesh, chhattisgarh, odish, bihaർ, jhaർand, paschim bangaൾ, andhrapradesh, maharashtra, jammu-kashmiർ, punjab, himachൽ pradesh, rajasthaൻ, uttrakhand enni sansthanaute bhagangൾ gondwanyutayu vindhyaൻreyu matakukaliൽ uൾppetunnu.
ori: gandana eban bindhor parbat-bhang madhyare madhyapradesh, chhatishagadh, odisha, bihar, jhangkhand, pashchimavang, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu o kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan, eban uttrakhander kichhi kichhi ansh rahichhi.
pan: gondvana ate vindhya de under madh pradesh, chatisgarh, orissa, bihar, jharkhand, pattmi bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu ate kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan ate uttarakhand de hise ounde han I
tam: kondwana manllum vindavin aravanifukul madhya pradesam, chhattiskar, otisa, bihar, jharkhand, mengu bengalam, andhra pradesam, maharashtra, jammu kashmiri, punjab, himachal pradesam, rajasthan, uttarakhand akhiyavain bakudis atankyluna.
tel: gondwana mariyu vindhya parvatavalulu vat naduman madhya pradesh, chhattisgarh, orisha, bihar, jharkhand, paschim bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jammu kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan, mariyu uttrakhand laloni bhagal cherchukuni unnai.
urd: gondwana or vindhya ke daman main madhya pradesh, chhattis garh, odesha, bihar, jharkhand, mugharabi bengal, andhra pradesh, maharashtra, jamuun va kashmir, punjab, himachal pradesh, rajasthan or uttarakhand ke hisse shamil hain.

ben: kintu natun sarkar taar baidhata pratishtha vyarth has evan taar adhikansh arthik sahayata hras pawa, sthanian o madhya shreni netara evan tader bahini shudhumatra nijeder madhye ladai-i karennie, kshamata o labh adawer janya dirghakalin vikshipt sangharshe ekaguchchha manaar ayogya paddhatio abalmban kare.
guj: parantu navi sarkaar potani yogyata sabit karvama nishphal rahi, ane mota bhaagani nanakiya sahaya veravikher thai gai, sthanik ane madhyam shrenina commander ane temna sanyo andarander ja ladya atlu ja nahi, parantu satta ane nafa mateni temani lambi khenchatanma ashvikarya paddhationo pan ashro lidho.
hin: lekin nai sarkaar apni vaidhata sthapit karne main vifal rahi or usko praapt vittiya samarthan jaise-jaise khatm hone laga, sthaneey or madhyam darje ke commander or unki naagarik senaayen na sirf aapas main ladane lageen balki adhikaar or laabh praapt karne kii hode main kai asweekaarya krityon main bhi shaamil ho gayi.
kan: adare hoss sarkaarvu tann kanoonubaddhateyannu sthapisalu vifalvayitu mattu adkke doretidd hanakasin nervin bahupalu polad mele, sthaliya hagu madhyam mattad nayakaru hagu avar nagarik senapadegalvaru tammatmmalle kittaduvudu matravallade adhikaar mattu labhakkagi avar dirghvaad melacgamalli anek oppalu yogyavallad chatuvatikegamalli todagisiconderu.
mal: ennal putia sarkar atine niyamsadhut sthapichedukkunnatiൽ parajaypetukayu,atine sampattikapintudilarayu illatayatote taddeshi madhyanirilulatumay sainikattalavanmaru avarute natൻsenekalu tammilttammil poraticook matramall adhikarattinu lamattinumai natattia nint pitivalil ashvikaryamay oru kutte natapatikal erppetukayu cheitu.
ori: matra nuthan sarkar nizer vaittaku pratishtha karivare bifal hoithila, eban ehar aarthik sahayatha yethiki ksheen heuthila, sthaniya eban madhum-bargee senadhikshamane tatha semanank sainevahinigulik keval parasparank madhyare kareh karunathile, baran kshamta eban labhar deerghakalin prathiyogitha madhyare anek agrahaniya karyopaddhathiku upan bhave bangineithile .
pan: per navin sarkaar apni jaizata sthapat karan vich asafal rahi, ate isdi viti sahita da bohut hisa khatam hoo gya, sthanak ate madh-raj de cmandrs ate uhanaas de millitians naame siraf aapas vich lade , balki shakti ate munafe lai uhanaas de lambe samen vich aswikaranyog abhiasas da sahara lya|
tam: eninu putiya arasu tamakurya satt ankikarti nilainatat dhawariyatu, adait doderndu adan perumbalan nidhi aadharam vashipfoi vattar manllum natunilai dashapatigarhm avarkalin aayuthap patigalum atchiyatikaram manllum aadhayatukan nindakalap botiil tangalukitie chandai botuk kondotu matuminri pal virumpathakat seyalbadugalilum edubhatat dodanginer.
tel: kaani nuthan prabhutvan dani chattabaddhatani sthapinchukovailo vifalamindi, mariyu dani aarthik maddattu chepragottabaddanto, stanik mariyu madhya shreni kamandar, mariyu vaari sainyam parasparam kalahinchukovateme kak, balam mariyu labha koraku bahudinal porata anek aamodayogya kaani vidhanath ashraincharu.
urd: lekin nai hukuumat apna kanoonee jawaaz kaayam karne main naakam rahi or jese jese is kii beshtar mali amudad khatm hoti gai, mukami or darmiyaane faasale ke commandron or in kii malaysiaon ne na sirf aapas main ladaaii ladi balki iqtidar or jalab manfaat kii apni tavel koshishon main matadad naakaabil kabuul tareekon kaa sahaara bhi liya.
eng: But the new government failed to establish its legitimacy, and as much of its financial support dissipated, local and middle-range commanders and their militias not only fought among themselves but also resorted to a host of unacceptable practises in their protracted scrambles for power and profit.

ben: 2023 cricket vishwakaper bachaiparve, du'ti daler madhye liga 2-era dalti uchchatar sthan shesh karale, 13tam sthan thaka dalti parivarte sidblusi liga 2-era shirshasthanian daltike paravarty 2020-2023 isici cricket vishwacap super lig tule dewai chhil asal uddeshya.
guj: mule teno hetu evo hato ke jo lig 2 team 2023na cricket world cap quolifyrema be timomathi uncha krame lakshyasthan par rahe to sii.dublue.sii. lig 2maa sarvochch kramake raheli timne tema 13ma krame raheli timne badle tyarapachhina 2020-2023 ai.sii.sii. cricket world cap super ligama padonnath karvama aavashe.
hin: mul rup se aisa sochaa gaya tha ki yadi agle 2020-2023 ke ai.si.si. cricket vishwa cap qualifire main donon tiimon main se lig 2 kii team behatar pradarshan karti he to 13wein sthaan kii team ke badale lig 2 ko aagaamee 2020-2023 ai.si.si. cricket vishwa cap super lig main aage badhaayaa jayega.
kan: modalalli, 2023r cricket vishvakpn arhata pandyadalli lig 2r tandvu eradu tandgamalli hechu uttam pradarshanavannu nidid pakshadalli ader 13nae shreyankad tandavannulidu si.dublu.si. lig 2ralli agr shreyankit tandavannu munde 2020-20234r i.si.si. cricket vishvakp souper ligge kaluhisuvudendu uddeshislagittu.
mal: 2023 le cricket weld kap qualiyar rantu timuli vach lig 2 tea munnil varumengiൽ, ai.si.si. weld kappille patimunnam sthanttull timin pakar si.dublyu.si. lig 2 le et mikachch timin 2020-2023 ai.si.si. weld kap super ligi sthanayatm nalkapet ennayirunnu adyam thirumaniachirunnat.
ori: aarmbhare, ehar uddeshya thila ye si.dablsou.si. lig 2re sarbochch rankre thiva timku, ehar 13 nambar rankre thiva tim busaare, 2020-23 aai.si.si. cricket vish cup super lig pin unnat karayib, yadi rlad cup clifairre lig 2 dashati dui dal madhyare unnat sthan arjan karen.
pan: asal vich, ih iraadaa see ki see.dabalyu.see.lig 2 vich choti di darje vaali team nuun agali 2020-2023 ai.see.see. cricket vishva cup super lig vich usdi 13 vin darje vaali team di kimat utte tadaki diti jaavegi, jekar 2023 vich lig 2 di team cricket vishva cup kualifire vich dovan tims uch darje di team de roop vich khatam hundi hai I
tam: chitapusi leek 2in mudalittil ull ani 13aam itttil ull anie veet 2023 cricket ulagak gobbait daqudib boaticain mudivil adhik pointle edutthrindhal adutta 2020-2023 essici cricket ulagak goppai supper likingu mundaiy ani daqudibengu munnerum, bindaiy ani veliecopatum endu muthalil ditamitapattatu.
tel: modatlo, sidblusi rendav lig lo agrasthanaion unn jattuni 2020-2023 nisisi cricket world kap super lig ki, rendav lig jattu 2023 cricket world kap qualifar lo, rend jatlalo aadhikyat sadhinchite danni13 va sthanaloni jattuki badulu pampinchalani uddeshinchabadindi.
urd: durasal, ye kusud kiya gaya tha ki agar lig 2 tem 2023 crookat world cap cavaliphar main dono teemon main se aala ke tuur par akhtatam karee gi to si dablyoo si lig 2 main aala durje kii tem ko aainda 2020-2023 aai si si crookat world cap super lig ke liye is kii 13vaein durje kii tem ke badle tarakkee di jaaye gi.

ben: bhartiya cinema aashcharyajanak veshi pariman chhabi tiri janya vishve janapriya: ei sankhya pratiniyat vruddhir dike thake evan sampratik sutrer anuman ye madras, bangalore, kolkata o haidrawader mato bivinn shahare bachre praia mott 800 ti chhabi banano has.
guj: bhartiya cinema teni aashcharyajanak sankhyama nirman paamati filmone karne vishwaprasiddh che: sankhya satatyapurna rite vruddhiman che ane tajetarna strot anuman kare che ke ek varshma kul maline lagbhag 800 filmo alanlag shaheroma bane che, jema madras, bangalore, kalakatta ane hyderabadano samavesh thai che.
hin: ascharyajanak sankhya main filmon kaa utpaadan karne ke liye bhartiya cinema puri duniya main vikhyath he: yah sankhya lagaataar bad rahi he or aadhunik aankadon ke anusaar madras, bangalore, kalakatta or hyderabad sahit vibhinn shaharon main kul mila kar 800 filmein prati varsh banaai jaati hai.
kan: bhartiya chitrarangavu tanu nibberagagisuvashtu pramandalli nirmisuv chalanchitragaligagi vishvaprasiddhvagide: i sankhyeyu nirantaravagi hechuttale ide, mattu madras, bangalore, kalkatta mattu hyderabad seridante berebere nagargamalli varshawondakke ottare sumaru 800 chalanchitragalannu bidugade madelaguttide endu ittichin moolagalu andajisive.
mal: amparappikunnatra chitras nirmmikunnatil lokprashasta indian sinim: enea nirantar vardhitchuvarunnuvennu matramall atuttakalatte kanakkul anusrich madras, bangalore, kalkatta, hidrabad ennivyutepate vividhnagarslilninn oru varsha etand motta 800 chitras nirmmicppetukayu cheiyunnu.
ori: ashcharyajanaka parimanr chakchchitra nirman karuthiva hetu bharatiya cinema vish prasiddh: ehi sankhya lagatar badichalithi, eban sampratika sutararu janapade ye prati barshar mot utpadan heudi pakhapakhi 800ti chakchchitra yaha madras, bangalore, kolkata eban hidrabad samet vibhinna saharre nirmit hoithaye .
pan: mavhangi ginti vich films prakashit karan lai bharati cinema vishva bhar vich prasidh hai:ih ginti lagatar uddh rahi hai ate awj de ankrias anusaar madras, bangalooru, kolkata ate hyderabad de naal- naal hor shahirn vich kulmala ke kuchh 800 filma har saal bania jandi hai I
tam: india cinema aparimitmaghat tirappaangsait dayaripatil ulagappugal bellntu: adan annikky doderndu adhikaritt vannam irukkintu, sameepatya aadharangs tarum ganakidin pati anduthorum madras, bangalore, calcutta, iderabad ullitt vevveru manakranglil mottom sumar 800 tirappatas dayaaricapadukindena.
tel: bharat chitra parishram, adi nirmistunn cinemal bhari sankhyaku prapanchavyaptanga suprasiddha: i sankhya nirantaranga perugutune undi, alage madras, bangalore, kalakatta mariyu hyderabadto saha vividh nagarall motta mid sumaru 800 chitras nirmimpabadtunnayani itivali nivedikalu anchana vestunnai
urd: hindustani cinema apni taiyaar karda filmon kii hairat angez muqadaar ke liye duniya bhar main mashhuur hai: ye taadaad musalasal badh rahi hai, or halay jaria kaa andaaz hai ki madras, bangalore, kalakattaa or hyderabad samet mukhtalf shaharon main ek saal main takreeban 800 filmon kii kul taiyaari kii jaati hai.
eng: Indian cinema is world famous for the staggering amount of films it produces: the number is constantly on the increase, and recent sources estimate that a total output of some 800 films a year are made in different cities including Madras, Bangalore, Calcutta and Hyderabad.

ben: arevati niramikari tejascrian oshudher gurutvapurna sthanian-anchalik prayog hepatocellular carcinoma (yakru cancer)-r chikisa dekha gamee, yekhane tejascrian lebelyukt nirdisht aakarer anukana athva tejascrian lebelyukt lipiodal (post danar tel thek labdh snehaj asider atyant athalo ekati taral ethil ester) yakruter dhamni madhyam rogir sharir pravesh karano has.
guj: roganivarak radiopharmaceuticals anaya mahatvapurna antar pradeshiya vyavasthapan hepatocellular karsinoma (yakruthanu cancer)ni saarwar mate nodhavama aave che, jema readiolabel lipiod (khasakhasana bijna telmathi melvela charabiyukt acidnu atyant chikashwalu pravahi- ithil -easter)na niyath kadana readiolabel sukshma golao dardini hepetic dhamnima soyathi dakhal karvama aave che.
hin: yakritkoshikeey durdamy arbud (yakrut cancer) ke ilaaj ke liye, ek anya mahatvapurn vikiran-bheshajvarg ke sthaneey chikitsarth die jane ke bare main bataaya gaya he, jisamen vishisht aakaar ke radiolabalikrut sookshmgolak yaa radiolabalikrut lipeodol (khaskhas ke tel se vyutpann fatty acid kaa ek atyadhik gadha fatty acid ethil aster) rogi ko radiolabalikrut karne ke liye injection se yakrut dhamni ke madhyam se die jate hai.
kan: baadhit bhagakke kendrikrutagolislad chikitsak radiopharmaseuticalgal innondu mukhya prayogvu hepatoselular carcinomad (yakruttin adiganti) chikitseyalli varadiagiddu, idralli vikirangrahiyendu lable madlad nirdisht gatrad sukshma-golagalu athwa vikirangrahiyendu lable madlad lipiodallannu (gasagase enneind teged cobbin aamlad adhik snigdhateyul drav-itail ester) rogiy pittajanakangad apadhmaniy moolak chuchchumaddu nidelaguttade.
mal: heppatosellulaർ kaaർsinom (karaliൻre aർbudam)yute chikitsaikkai radiolebൽ cheyyapret nischit valipattilull sukshmagolaslo, radiolebൽ cheyyapret lipiodolo (poppivittukaliൽ ninnetutatu kudia shyanathyulatumay koyutt amlattiൻre dravarupattilull ithiൽ esteർ ) rogiute heppatic dhamaniilute kuttivaikkunn radiophaർmasuticaൽ chikitsayute lokko-rijyanൽ prayogattiൻre matoru pradhanprayoga repoർtt cheyyapettu.
ori: therapiutik radiopharmasyutikalsar annga eka guruthpurna nirddist-sthaniya prayog hepatoselular karasinoma (yakrit karkat)r chikitsa pin report hoichhi, yeunthire eka nirddist aakarar radiolevlad micro sphiar kimba radiolevlad lipiodal (eka attant bahassia charvibahul amlar tarala-ithail eshtar yaha afim manjir tilaru present karayaithaye) ku rogeer yakrut dhamnire enject karayaithaye.
pan: hepentocellular karsinoma (jiger de cancer) de ilaaj sambandhi redeopharasutical di ik hor mahatavpuuran loko-rijinal prasasana di report pesh keeti gai hai, jise anusaar khaas aakaar de radio-level wale micro gola jaaa redioleblad lipeodol (ik bohut ziada lesdar taral ithail ester bhuki de bij de tel ton praapat fatty acid) nuun mariz di hepatic dhamni raaheen tikaa lagaya janda hai|
tam: sikiikurya katriyakk marundugalin manthoru urupusar payanpadu, hepato cellular garcinoma (kalliral purrunoi) sikiil iruppadakat therivixpadukintu, itel radio labilit kufippitt alavilan nunkulikis alltu radio labilit lybiodal (kasakasa annailrundhu edukoppatt koloubbu amilatin ore uir baguddhanmall liguid-ethl ester) noyalin iral tamani valiyag usibotuch selutopadukintu.
tel: hepatoceyular carsinoma (liver cancer) chikitsaku stanik pradeshlo vedya sambandhit radiodharmik aushadhal prayog chessintt nivedinchabadindi, ikkad radiodharmikat kalapabadin nirdisht parimanaloni sukshmagonalu leda radiodharmikat kalapabadin lipidal (gasagsal nune nudi utpann vasamlamu yokk atijigtin dravarupao atill aaml sammerna) rogi yokk kaleymani dwara ekkinchada jarugutundi.
urd: hepatucellolar carcinoma (jigar ke cancer) ke ilaaj ke liye tabi radiopharmacutecliz kii ek or ahim mukami ilakaai dawa daalane kii itla di gai hai, jis main makhsus jisamit ke radiolabld micro spirez yaa radiolabld lipeudol (post ke beej ke tel se haasil karda feeti acid kaa ek intihaai chipachupa miyaa ethael easter) kaa injection marij kii hepaatak shriyan main lagaaya jataa hai.
eng: Another important loco-regional administration of therapeutic radiopharmaceuticals is reported for the treatment of hepatocellular carcinoma (liver cancer), where radiolabeled micro-spheres of specific size or radiolabeled Lipiodol (a highly viscous liquid-ethyl ester of fatty acid derived from poppy seed oil) are injected through the hepatic artery of the patient.

ben: amader, darshakder yeti chalith kare seti halo upanyastite bartaman samay, asten-era nyika athva paniol o forstere charitrader baanchaa muhoortar prati ek smritimedurata, se amader kalpit atit, asal pathyer atit naya yar nirikhe sei bartaman samaiti halo abanchit paribartaner pratinidhi.
guj: aapanne prekshacone je game che te navalkathano vartaman samay, ostin nayikaoni jivayeli palo, athva pegnolna tatha forsterna patro, je aapano kalpanashil bhutkal che; tenu mul lakhan, jene mate vartaman samayma thatan anpekshit pherfaronu pratinidhitva nahi.
hin: ham darshak jisase prerit hote hai, ve hai upanyaas ke us kaal kii smritiyaan, jo austin kii nayikaon yaa pagnol evam forster ke paatro ke jeevant kshan the, hamaara kalpit ateet, na ki mul paath kaa ateet jiske liye us samay kaa vartmaan kaal avaanchit parivartan darshata he.
kan: prekshakarad nammannu prerisuvudu kadambariyu nadeyuv kaalad bagegin bhavuk hambal, austennal kathanayakieru athwa panyol mattu forstern patragalu badukidd samay, namm kalpit gatakalve hortu aa samayad varthaman kalvu bedad badlavaneyannu bimbisuv muul pathyadallin haleya kalavall.
mal: anuvachakaray namme prachodeeppikunnat novalile varttamanakalattecurichu, ostinte nayikmarutayu pagnolinteyu, phosterutayu kathapatrautayu jivattay nimishatecurichu, nammute sankൽppattilull bhutakalattecurichu, tonnunn grihaturatvama, allae anavashyamay matom pratinidhikarikunn mulakritiille varttamanakalamall.
ori: darshak roope, amku yaha andolit karithaye, taha heudi upanyasar tatkalin samay nimanthe eka aabegaman lamasa, ashtennk nanikamane jeeinthiva muhurtta, kimba paganol eban fostarank charitramanank kalpanic atit; eha mul pat vishakere kichhi kahi nathaaye, yaha pin sehi tatkalin samay avanchit parivarttanaku chitrit karithaye.
pan: saanuun darshaks nuun prerita karada hai oh us kaal dis yaads han jise vich osten di nika jaaa paagnol te forster de kirdhar rihande san, saada bitit atit, naame ki moulik pat jise vich awj da same naame chahia badlao di karada hai I
tam: vasakarkalakiya nam navalin nikavkalatye rasikirom, adavatu ostenin kathanayakikalo pagnalin manllum porsterin kadabatrangalo vayendhu anubhavitt taruangan, andak karupnayana kadand kalat rasikirom, achal nawal edudappatt nikavkalat all, ivviru nigaiakalangaum onduckondu avachiyamrittak ulsana.
tel: manani, prekshakulani, prerapinchedi navalloni vartaman stategatulu, ostine hiroini jivinchin kalam gurinchin bhavodvega , leda pagnol mariyu forustore patral, man uhlloni gat taluku smritule gani, anavasar marpul suchinche alanati vartaman mul rachanal smritulu kad.
urd: jo cheez hamen, yani samain ko, baandhee rakhti hai, wo naval ke isr ravaan, austin kii heroinon ke zarie jiya gaya lamha, yaa pagnol or forister ke kirdaar, hamare khayali maazi kaa nastilgia hai, na ki asal muthan kaa nastilgia jis ke liye wo isr ravaan napsandida tabadeli kaa numazind hai.
eng: What drives us, the audience, is a nostalgia for the present times of the novel, the lived moment of Austen's heroines, or Pagnol's and Forster's characters, our imagined past, not that of the original text for which that present time represents unwanted change.

ben: staitishil arthpradaner bharsamya, paryapt suder haar, evan yoth binioger janya bahiragat muldhaner ekati susthi pravah baja rakhte eti apariharya.
guj: aa chukvanina sthir santulan, vajbi vyaj daro ane khaangi nivesh mate bahya mudina sthir pravah jalvavaa aavashyak che
hin: bhugtanon ke sthir santulan, ausat darje kii byaaj daron or nigamit niveshon hetu bahya poonji ke niyamit pravaah ko banaae rakhane ke liye yah aavashyak he.
kan: sthirvad pavati shilku, madhyam buddy dargalu mattu corporat hoodikegagi bahya bandwald nirantar harivannu ulisicoreelu idu agatyavagide.
mal: santhulithmay paymeൻrukൾ, mitmay palishanirakcookൾ,koർppate nikshapattinai purameninnull muladhanttiൻre sthirmay vara enniv niloniർttaൻ it anivarya.
ori: aadan pradaanare samatuson, madhum parimanr sud haar, eban karporet nivesh nimanthe bahya punyjir eka nikhmit pravah pin eha anivaryan.
pan: ih zaroori hai, ik sthir adaaigi da santulan barqarar rakhn de lai, sanjami vyaj rates de lai ate partak pravaah dhan ate carporate nivesh de lai I
tam: nilaiyana ettrumati ishakkumati michattoka, mitman vatti vikithas, peruniruvan mudalitukkan veliyar mooladanangalin nilaiyana vriu akhiyavayap paramrik itu adhdhiavasiumakum.
tel: chellimpul khatan sthirapargtanii, madhyasth vaddi shatal mariyu carporate pettubadul kos bahya muladhanpu sthiramain pravahanni konsaginchadaniki idi chala avasaram.
urd: ye adaegyon ke mustahkam tawazon, itdal pasand sood kii shrahon or corporet saramy kari ke liye beroni suramaaye ke ek mustahkam bahaav ko barkaraar rakhane ke liye zaroori hai.
eng: This is essential for maintaining a stable balance of payments, moderate interest rates and a steady flow of external capital for corporate investment.

ben: 1981 thek 1994 saal percent vere board pradhanmantri evan 1960 thek 1981 saal percent antiger mukhyamantri chhillen, shudhu 1971 thek 1976 saler samaita chada, yakhan pragatishil shramik andolan (pi.el.em) tar dalke harie deya.
guj: vere bird 1981 thi 1994 daramiyaan vadaa pradhan ane 1960 thi 1981 daramiyaan antiguana mukhya pradhan hatan, sivaay ke 1971 thi 1976 na samaygala daramiyaan progressive laber muvament (pe.el.em.) e temana pakshane haraavyo hato.
hin: sivaay 1971-1976 kii samyavadhi ke, jab pragatisheel shramik andolan (pi.el.em.) ne unki party ko parajeet kar diya tha, vir bird 1981 se 1994 tak pradhanmantri or 1960 se 1981 tak antigua ke mukhyamantri the.
kan: wer bird avar pakshavannu progresive labour moovment (pi.el.em.) solisidd 1971-1976r avadhiannu horatupadisi, aat 1981rind 1994r varege pradhanmantri mattu 1960rind 1981r varege ontigad mukhyamantriagiddaru.
mal: vier bad 1981 mutal 1994 vare pradhanmantriyu, 1971-1976 kalaghtattil prograssi lebർ movemeൻr (pi.el.e) tante parttie parajaypetuttiapoloike, 1960 mutal 1981 vare antigvayute mukhyamantriyu irunnu.
ori: bhidhar barge 1981 ru 1994 paryyant pradhanamanthri rahithile eban 1971-1976 kal, yeve 'progracibh levar mubhment' (pi.el.em.) tank dattiku parast karidheithila, sehi samay bpatit, 1960 ru 1981 paryyant antiguar mukhimanthri rahithile .
pan: vere bird 1981 ton 1994 tak pradhan mantri ate 1960 ton 1981 tak antigua de mouth mantri rehe, 1971-1976 de samen nuun chad ke jadon pragatishil majadoor lahir (pi ail aim) ne usdi party nuun haraya|
tam: vere perdu 1981 muthal 1994 varai pratam mandriagaum, 1960 muthal 1981 varai antigua muthalmicharagaum irindar, 1971-1976 kaalaktam mattume itasku vidivilaku, apbodhu mufokud tokhilauar iyakkum (bielem) avarait tolkaditthrundatu.
tel: progesive leber moument (piele) aayan partini odinchin 1971-1976 samayaulo minaha, vere bird 1981 nudi 1994 varaku pradhan mantriga mariyu 1960 nudi 1981 varaku antigwa mukhyamantriga unnar.
urd: veer bird 1981 se 1994 tak vazeer aazam or 1960 se 1981 tak antigua ke vazeer aala rahe, sivaay 1971-1976 kii muddat ke jab progressive liber moomint (pii el em) ne in kii party ko haraa diya tha.
eng: Vere Bird was prime minister from 1981 to 1994 and chief minister of Antigua from 1960 to 1981, except for the 1971-1976 period when the Progressive Labour Movement (PLM) defeated his party.

hin: yangun ke hlaaing thar yaar township main galati se kai bamon ke fatne ke baad, tatmadow sainikon ne 12 kathith pratirodh senaniyon ko hiraasat main liya, jinamein se teen ladaake ghayal ho gaye.
kan: yangann lang thar yaar townshipnalli aaksmikavagi halvaaru bambugalu sphotvad nantar tamado sainikaru 3 gayagond horatgarru seridante 12 shankit virodhi horatgarrannu serehididru.
mal: yangonile laaying taryaർ tൺshipyൽ niravadhi bombukൾ akasmikamai potitterixtinettutർnn tatmado sainikർ pariete 3 poralikaluൾpete cheruttunilpukarenne sanshayicpat 12 poralie pitikuti.
ori: yanganar ling thar der saharre aaksmika bhave anekagudie boma bisforan hela pare, thatmad sainemane 3 jan aahat yoddha samet 12 jan sandhigdh vidrohi yoddhanku dharinele.
pan: yangon de haling thar yara tunship vich durgatna vich kai bamb dhamaakas ton bood, tatmadav sipahia ne 12 luki virodhi ladaakus nuun fad lya, jinhan vich 3 zakhmi ladaaku ve shaamil han|
tam: yangonin hilying thar yaar towunshipple taesseyalagab pal gundues veditt pin, 3 gayamadainth poralis udpat 12 chandekatisurya ethirfup poralies datmato sipaiess fidittanar.
tel: angonloni hling thar yar townshiplo pramadavashattu anek bambulu paleen tarvat, tatmadav sainikulu mugguru gayapadin yodhulatho saha 12 mandi anumanit pratighathan yodhus pattukunnar,
urd: tutmadu faujyon ne yangon ke hilaaing thar yaar taun ship main haadasati tuur par hone waale matadad bam dhamaakon ke baad 3 zakhmi jangjoon samet 12 mushtabaa mazaahmati jangjoon ko giraftaar kar liya.
eng: Tatmadaw soldiers captured 12 suspected resistance fighters, including 3 injured fighters, after several bombs exploded by accident in Yangon's Hlaing Thar Yar Township.

ben: aichaeleldblu-r madhye bidarak dravya, laghu aktinide, uranium o plutoniamer chihnmatra, jark dravya, evan punra prakriakarner samarkar rasyanik samuh thake.
guj: vibhajit banaavato, thodu aktinide, yurenium ane plutoniyamana ansho, katayukt banaavato ane punavprakriya daramiyaan umerayela rasayanono ech.el.el.dabalyu. maa samavesh thai che.
hin: ech.el.el.dablyoo. main vikhandan utpaada, laghu actenide, uranium or plutonium ke avshesh, sanksharan utpaada, or punahsansaadhan karne ke dauraan daale gaye rasayan hote hai.
kan: marusanskarnad samayadalli serisalad vidson vastegalu, laghu actinidgalu, alp pramand uranium mattu plutonium, sanksharan vastegalu, mattu rasayanikagainnu ech.el.el.dublu. hondiruttade.
mal: ech .el.el.dublyu il fishan utpannas, miner actinids, yuranium, plutonium ennivyute sukshmamay anshaies, punർsanskarana cheayumpoൾ cheർkkunn rasavastukal, enniv atariiriunnu.
ori: ech.el.el.dablsou. re bilondon paxarwa, kshudra aktinid, atpulp parimanre uraniyam o plutoniom, avakshan paxarwa eban punavaprakriakaran samaure brebahrut rasarhnic dravya antarbhukt thae.
pan: aich ail ail dabliyu vich fishan utpad, maamooli actenoids, urenium ate plutonium de nishaan, khor utpad ate reprosescing dauraan paae gaye rasayan shaamil hunde han|
tam: heceleltapilyu-will anupluu vilghporuts, chiru actinatus, yurenium manllum plutonium suadues, ariman vilghporuts, manuseyalaxtin podhu chercopatum rachayanas akhiyawe ulsana.
tel: heach. el. el. dablyu. lo vicchitt utpadital, swalp radiotharmik padarthas, yurenium mariyu plutonium anvallu, harimp utpadital, mariyu punahsamvidhanaion cherchabadin rasayanal untai.
urd: each el el dablyoo main anshkaki misanuaat, miner actenids, uranium or plutonium ke traes, zangi misanuaat or dobara processing ke dauraan shamil karda chemical shamil hain.
eng: HLLW contains fission products, minor actinides, traces of uranium & plutonium, corrosion products, and chemicals added during reprocessing.

ben: samashtigat arthanitir mul vishyati hal sadharant ekati desh evan sab bazarguli kivave paraspar sanyog ghatie bada prapanch srushti kare, arthanitividara yake mott chalarashi bale thaken.
guj: mechroiconomikasma vishay che mulbhut rite ek desh ane badhi bajaaro kevi rite viraat ghatnaa utpann karva kriya-pratikriya aape che, jene arthshastrio agriget veriabals kahe che.
hin: samshti arthshaastra main, vishay vishisht rup se ek raashtra hota he or iske bazaar kis prakaar se un vyapak ghatnaon ko utpann karne main ek-duusare ko prabhavit karte hai jise arthshaastri samgr char kehete hai.
kan: samagr arthshastradalli, vishayavu samanyavagi ondu rashtrawagiddu, arthshastrajaaru samashti chalaparimangalendu kareyuv bruhat vidyamanagainnu untumadlu ella marukattegalu hege parasparvagi kaarya nadesuttave embudagide.
mal: sthulsampattikashastrattiൽ vishyam sampattikavidagdhർ agrigate veriyabilukൾ enne vilicunn, saadharan oru rashtra ella vipanilu exne pratipravർttikkayu valia pratibhasamundakkukyu cheiyunnu enntan.
ori: samastigat arthshastrare, vishatvasthuti heudi sadharanthati eka rastra eban samast bazar kipari parasparik aanthalakria dra brihat paridhrushya ghatnaman srushti karithanthi, yahaku arthaneethijna mane samagric chalarashi boli kahithanthi.
pan: samashti arth shastra da adhin aam tor te ik rashtra baare hunda hai ate kive saare bazaar ik hoo ke badi asacharaj ghatna paidaa karade han jise nuun arth vigyani " egrigate veribals" kahinde han I
tam: paruvinab porulial valakkamak woru nadu barjee, angull anwattuch chandaikalum appati ondodondu dodarpukondu goottu maghis endu poruladhar nipunars amaikum maperum niyatis uruvakukindena enpatu barjee than pesukintu.
tel: sadharanmuga deshmu, mariyu aarthikavettal samishti vaividhyaluga piluchukune gopp drugvishayanni rabttenduku vipanulu parasparam ela vyavaharistai anedi stul arthashastraloni vishyam.
urd: kalan maashiyat main, aam tuur par modua ek malik hota hai or kis tarah saare bazar bade majaahir ko paida karne ke liye taamil karte hain jise mahrain maashiyat majamuai mithgiraat kehate hain.
eng: In macroeconomics, the subject is typically a nation and how all markets interact to generate big phenomena that economists call aggregate variables.

ben: udaharanswarup, "ek vyakti rashtrahintar jhunki hate par yadi se eman ek raje janmagrahan kare yekhane banshasutre naagarikatva prayojya edike taar mata pita eman ek raje janmagrahan karellen, yekhane janmasutre naagarikatva prayojya, yar fale parasparabirodhi iner karna vyakti ubhay rajyei naagariktber janya ayogya hay pade."
guj: daakhla tarike, ‘‘ek vyakti rashtravihinatana jokhamma mukai shake che jo teno janma eva rashtra thayo hoya je jus sanguinis laagu kare, jayaare tena matapita eva rashtra janmyan hoya je jus soli laagu kare, to virodhabhasi kaayadaaone karne te vyakti banne rashtra nagarikatva mate ayogya thare che.’’
hin: udhaaharan ke taur par, "kisi vyakti ko tab rajyaviheenta kaa khatra ho saktaa he jab vah ek aise rajya main paidaa hua ho jahaan naagarikta kaa aadhaar rakt se mana jaataa he, jabaki uske mata-pita ek aise rajya main paidaa hue the jahaan yah aadhaar janm se mana jaataa he, jis vajah se us vyakti ko paraspar virdohi kanoonon ke kaaran donon rajyon main naagarikta ke liye ayogy bana detaa he."
kan: udaharanege, "obbakeyu yus sanwinisannu anvayisuv rashtradalli janisiddu, aakeya palkaru yus solianneu anvayisuv rashtradalli janisiddare, intah paraspar virodhi kanoonugalind aa vyaktige eradu rashtragalalliu pauratvakke arhateilladantagee vyaktiyu arashtriyatege guriyagabahudu."
mal: udaharanttin, " oraൾ janikunnat jas sangvinis badhakamakkunn oru rashtratil, avarute matapitackൾ janicht jas soli badhakamakkunn oru rashtratilanengiൽ parasparvirudhmay niyamngoൾ karea avർ irurashtrasl paratvattin anർhayavukayu angne avർ rashtramillatavarakanural apakatsadhyathilavukayu cheitekam."
ori: udaharan srup, "jane bsakthi upare rastra-hin hebar bipad asipare, yadi se eka rashtrare janma hoithanthi, yeunthi nagarigatha pin 'raktar adhikar' neeti lagu karayaaye, athach tangkar pitamata eveli eka rashtrare janmit, yeunthare 'matir adhikar' neeti lagu hoithaye, fattah, parasper-virodhi inagudik yogun, bsakthi janak ubhay rashtrare nagarikata piva nimanthe ayogya hoipavanthi."
pan: udaharan lai, "ik viakti nuun rajhinta da khatra hoo sakda hai jekar uh ik ajihe raj vich paidaa hundi hai jo zeus sanginis nuun lagu kardi hai jadon ki usde matra-pitaa ik ahije raj vich paidaa hoe san jo zeus di dharati nuun lagu karada hai, jise naal viakti nuun dovan raajan vich nagariks nuun doshi wheraun wale kaanoonnas de kaaran ayog hoo janda hai|"
tam: udarantingu, "oruval jas saanquinis (pellnore poorvikak kudiurims) kotbattrup pinbhauaum nottilum avaltu pevors jas choli (daqbiabbuk kudiurims) kotbattrup pinbhauaum nottilum bimanthrindhal aval nataky naparakum apattu ulldu, aval chattangalin muranbattinal menopati iru nadugalilum kudiurimikud dagudiidokk waifuldu."
tel: udaharanku, "ock vyakti jus sanguinis vartinche rashtralo janminchi ambe talidandrulu jus soli vartinche rashtralo janmiste aa vyakti e deshaniki paurulu kaani state erpade pramada untundi, ala aa vyakti virudh chattal karnanga iru rashtralasonu paurasatwaniki anarhuraluga migilipotundi".
urd: masalan, "koi shaks adam qaumiti ke khatare kaa shikaar ho saktaa hai agar wo kisi aisi riyasat main paida ho jo haq shahrit baar banaaye valdet ko lagu krati hai jabaki is ke valdin kisi aisi riyasat main paida hue huun jo haq shahrit baar banaaye mukaam vilaadit ko lagu krati hai, is tarah mataarz kavanian is shaks ko dono riyasato main shahrit ke liye naahal bina dete hain."
eng: For example, "A person may be at risk of statelessness if she is born in a State that applies jus sanguinis while her parents were born in a State that applies jus soli, leaving the person ineligible for citizenship in both States due to conflicting laws."

ben: buddha dharm brahma hollen ek pradhan devatha (dev) evan swarger raja.
guj: brahm agrim bhagwan (dev) che ane buddhismma swargna raja che.
hin: buddha dharm main brahm pramukh bhagwaan (dev) or swarg ke raja hai.
kan: baudhdh dharmadalli brahmanu pramukh devate (dev) mattu swargad adhirajnagiddane.
mal: buddhamatattile muൻniradivavu (devൻ) swaർggiya raja brahma.
ori: buddhadharmare 'brahma' heutanthi jane pradhan eeshr (deb) eban srgeeth raja .
pan: bodh dharam vich brahm ik muhari bhagvaan (devaa) ate swargi raja hai I
tam: bhauttattil brahma woru mudanmike katavulagaum (dheyvam) suwarkalok archaragaum karudapadukirar.
tel: buddhaist lo brahma ock pradhan dev [dev) mariyu daivik paripalk.
urd: brahma ek marof bhagwan (dev) or budh math main aasmani baadshaah hai.
eng: Brahm is a leading god (deva) and heavenly king in Buddhism.

ben: ei vishyatite visesh manoyog dewa prayojan ye, 1960-era chalachchitra tattwer ei natun chintati (1950-era mato) chalachchitra samalochanar madhyam naya, varang gaiangat bhashavigyan evan chihnvignaner mato anyanya vishayer madhyam pravaratet hayesil.
guj: te vichaar pan parishramane patra che ke aa punavvichaar 1960na dayakano film sidhanth film vivechan dwara aavyo n hato (je rite 1950na dayakama thayu) parantu biji vidhao dwara, jena nam che bandharniya bhashavigyan ane ardhvishyak.
hin: is par jor dena bhi mahatvapurn he ki (1950 ke dashak ke vipareet) 1960 ke dashak main filmi siddhant kaa punarvichaar filmon kii aalochana se nahin balki anya vishyon, jaise sanrachanaatmak bhashavigyaan tathaa lakshanikta, se aayaa tha.
kan: jotege, cinema siddhanthad kuritu 1960r dashakadalli naded i maruchintaneyu (1950r dashakadalli adante) cinema vimarshey moolak agalill, adare rachanik bhashavigyan mattu sanketashastradantah bere bodhanshakhegal moolak untaiitu emb anshavu tilidiruvude aadaru punaruchcharislu arhavagide.
mal: ghatanaparamay bhashashastra, chihnashastra tutangia shastrashakhkaliluta, allae sinimaute pratyayashastrattecurich 1960 kaliൽ sambhavichch i punashchintana, (1950 kalil sambhavichchatupole) sinimavimർshanttiൽckuteairunnill end karyam kututൽ chintakൾk vidheyamakkunnatu yuktamairik.
ori: ehi prasangatiku madhya guruth diayiva yukthiyukt ye 1960 dashakar chakchchitra tattra ehi punarbichaar chakchchitra samalochanaru (1950 dashak bhadi) nuhen, baran annga bishany-shakhamanankaru aasithila, yatha sanrachanatmak bahasha vigyan eban sanket vigyan .
pan: ish gal te ve jor den di lod hai ki (1960 de dor de ulat) 1960 de daur vich film sidhant di punar pragati filma di nuktachini ton nahi sagon hor vishe, jive ki sansthagat bhasha vigyaan ate ardh-vigyaan ton ai see I
tam: 1960kalil tirapphatak kotbadu kuritt ind milayu (1950kalil ettpattatu pol) tirippat vimarsanas vilak arpatvilly, majhak ghatamifu mofiial manllum borudguriial enum pitt turais vilak ettpattana enjh karuddai valiyuuttik gooruvatum mukhgium.
tel: chalanchitra shastrasiddhantha gurinchi 1960 lalo ituvanti punralochan cinema vimarshana dwara (1950 lalo jarigints) vachchindi kad, kani vyavasthikrut bhashashastra mariyu bhav prakatnadhyayana vanti itar vishayalanudi nudi vachchindann abhiprayam gurinchi chese preyas upayogyamanadi.
urd: ye baat bhi kaabil gaur hai ki 1960 kii duhai main film najariye par nazar saani filmi tanqid ke waaste se naheen aai (jaisaa ki ye 1950 kii duhai main aai tha) balki digar moduaat, yani sakhti lusaaniyaat or elaamatiyat ke zarie aai thi.
eng: It is also worth labouring the point that this rethinking of film theory in the 1960s did not come via film criticism (as it did in the 1950s) but through other disciplines, namely structural linguistics and semiotics.

ben: uparntu, ayurveda evan jaiv-oshudh anushilankarider madhye yogayoge baadha, ayurvedic oshudh evan chickesar suraksha o caryaaritar vishay yasamanya gaveshana, evan aparapt naitik udyoggulike tanra ayurveda evan jaiv-oshudher caryakar milaner path gurutvapurna baadha hisabe chihnit karellen.
guj: aagal, teoe janavyu ke ayurveda ane biomedisin vyavasayiko vachchena sanvadma avarodh, surakshane dhyanma laine thatu alp sanshodhan kaarya ane ayurvedic dawaao ane saarwar paddhationo prabhave ane apurti niti-pahel, ayurveda ane biomedicin vachchena kaaryakari samantane samajvama agatyana vighno che.
hin: iske alaava, unhone kaha ki kamazor niti pahalen, ayurvedic dawaaon or upachaaron kii suraksha or prabhavakaarita main shodh kii kami, or ayurveda tathaa jaevchikitsa ke chikitsakon ke bich samvadaheenata ayurveda or jaevchikitsa main kaaryaatmak ekikaran paane main pramukh avrodh hai.
kan: jotege, ayurveda mattu biomedisin vaidyar naduvan sanvahanakkiruv tade, ayurvedad aushadhigalu mattu chikitsavidhangal surakshitte hagu prenamkaritvad kuritagee atyalp pramandalli agiruv sanshodhana kaarya, hagu aadlitnitielli upakramagal korate - ivu ayurveda mattu biomedisin naduve kaaryakari samanvayvannu sakaragorisuvalli pramukh toderugalagive embudagi avaru anisike vyaktpadisidru.
mal: kootate, aayuർvedachikitsakർku bio mediciൻ chikitsakർku idilull ashayvinimayattile tarussm, aayuർvedamarunnulutayu chikitsayutayu surakshayumayu phalaprapthiyumayu bandhappet gaveshanpaeenathute aparyaptat, aparyaptmay nayaparipatikൾ enniva aayuർvedattinu bio medicinumitiൽ pravർttanaparamay udgrathna sadhyamakkunnatinull pradhan tarussathenne avർ parannu.
ori: adhikanthu, semane kahiyanthi ye aajurveda eban jaivabheshaj chikithsakamanank madhyare yogayogar abhab, aajurvedic aushadh o chikitsar nirapatta tatha karyankarithaku nei khuv kam gaveshana, eban neethigat starare yathest udqamar abhab adi heudi aajurveda o jaivabheshaj madhyare babaharika-sanhati hasal karivare guruthpurna pratibandhak.
pan: ish ton ilava uhanaas ne kiha ki ayurveda ate baomedicine de abhias karan valyan wichkaar sanchar rukavats, ayurveda dawia ate therapya di sudkhya ate prabhavashilta de pakh ton maamooli khoj karge ate naakaafi neetia di pahilkadami, ayurveda ate baomedicine wichkaar kargeshil ekikarn nuun saakar karan vich badia rukavats han|
tam: melum, ayurveda manllum uerial maruduvam parkum marudvargaluku itieyana karutup parimahrat tatikes, ayurveda marundues manllum sikichlin bhadukafu manllum seyaltision dodarpak vegu kuraivana aywup panis, kolka charnt munippughalil paxakurai akhiawaiye ayurveda manllum uerial maruduvam itie seyalmurai orunginibbai erbadudhuwatil mukhiyat tatikshakalak irukkinsona endu avarkas therivittaner.
tel: adnanga, ayurveda mariyu jeevavedya vaidyul madhya samachar avarodha, ayurveda aushadhal mariyu chikitsal bhadrat mariyu samarthyalaku sambandhinchin atikoddi parishodhana panulu, mariyu sariponi vidhan prayatnalu ayurveda mariyu jeevavaidyam madhya kriyashil anusandhananni sadhinchadaniki mukhyamin avarodhal ani vaaru vyaktbaricharu.
urd: is ke alaava unhon ne is baat kaa izhaar kiya ki ayurveda or byomedicine ke practeshnaraz ke darmiyaan mawasalaat kii rukawat, ayurvedic advyat or therapi kii hifaazat or afaadit ke silsile main kam tahqiki kaam, or naakafee polisi ikdamaat ayurveda or byomedicine ke darmiyaan fial animam ko samajhane main ahim ruqawatein durpesh hain.
eng: Further, they expressed that the communication barrier between practitioners of Ayurveda and Biomedicine, meager research work with respect to the safety and efficacy of Ayurvedic medicines and therapies, and inadequate policy initiatives are the important obstacles in realizing functional integration between Ayurveda and Biomedicine.

ben: nirdisht moolye chahidar saman yoganer prayojan dwara bharsamya mulyati nirdhari has.
guj: market clearing muly e kimmatna saman mangana puravthani jaruriyat dwara niyath thai che.
hin: bazaar samashodhan keemat tay karne ke liye aavashyaktaa hoti he ki us keemat par purti or maang ek baraabar ho.
kan: marukatte-santhulan beleyannu aa beleyalli poorikeyu bedicayannu sarigattabeku ennuvudar mele nirdharislaguttade.
mal: chodanttiൻre ate alvilull pradanmundavuk end nibandhanil maaർcket-cliaring vil niർnayicppetunnat.
ori: bazar-nikash mool sehi aavashyakata dra nirddharit hoithaye ye sehi moolkere yogan o chahida saman rahithae .

urd: bazari takhlis kii keemat kaa tain is zarurat ke zarie hota hai jo is keemat par masavi mang kii farahami krati hai.
eng: The market-clearing price is determined by the requirement that supplies equal demand at that price.
