ben: ye, ekati nirdisht dine ekati matra pi.o.aai laksh laksh minuter kal bi.es.in.el-ke hastantar kare evan ei avastha ta banijikbhave udhdhaar kara sambhava naya ye kohn kalti satyikarer evan kohn kal si.el.aai chada baa kaler si.el.aai nast kare dewa.
guj: ke, aapela divase, ek pe.o.ai. laakho minitsana colsanu niyaman kare che je bi.es.en.el. ne soupayelam che ane aavi paristhitema, kayo kol asali che ane kayo kol sii.el.ai. vinaano athva chhedchhad thayel sii.el.ai.no che te samajvu vyavasayik rite shakya nathi.
hin: ki, kisi bhi din ek-ek pi.o.ai. dasiyon lakh minuton kii kol sambhalata he jo bi.es.en.el. ko saunpi jaati hai or aisi paristhiti main vanijyik rup se yah pataa karnaa vyavhaarya nahin he ki koun si kol asli he or koun si kol bina si.el.ai. ke yaa ched-chhaad kiye gaye si.el.ai. kii he.
kan: dinavondaralli bi.es.en.el.ge vahislaguv lakshagattle nimishgaishtu karegaynnu keval ondu pi.o.i. nirvahisuttade mattu inth statiyalli, yav kareyu nijavadudu hagu yav kareyu si.el.i.yannu hondill athwa akramavagi badlayislad si.el.i.yannu hondide embudannu kanduhidiuvudu vanijikavagi caaryasadhayvall embudu nirupitwagide.
mal: oru divas oru pi.o.ai. dashalakshakanakkinu minuteukൾ nilunn kolukal kaikaryam cheiyukayu, av bi.es.en.ellinu kaimarukayu cheiyunn sahacharyattil etu colan yatharthamenno etan si.el.ai. illatato ketuvann si.el.ai. uxtenno weർtirichoriyuk vanijyaparamai prayogikamall.
ori: eha ye, eka nirddist dinare, ekamatra pi.o.aai., bi.es.en.el. ku hastantharita heuthiva laksh laksh minutesra kal parichakana karithaye, eban epari paristatire, keun kalti asali, eban keun kaltir si.el.aai. naahin ba eka avaidhabhave badalayaithiva si.el.aai. rahichhi taha nirddharan kariva bavasaik drushtiru sambhava nuhen .
pan: kise ve din, ik pi.o.aai bi.se.in.ail di karodaa de mints dis kalas nuun sambhalde han, ahiji state vich ih vpark tor ton mumkin nahi hai pataa lagana ki kihadi kaal asali hai ate kihadi kaal binaas si.l.aai de hai jaaa jise naal chedchhad kiti gai hai I
tam: woru pios mattume woru kufippitt nalil piesenel mulam varum million ganakkana assifu nimiangalack kayalukintu enjh suanilil ent assifu unmaiyantu manllum ent assifu chielai illamalo bholi chielai utano varukintu anpatek khandarivatu vanik ritiyakas satyamandu enak gutappattatu.
tel: inca, ye rogyna, biessenel ki appaginchin kots nimishal kals nu ockk pioai nirvahan chapadutundi, ik atuvanti paristatelo, ye kal yatharthaminadi, yedi si. el. ai. rahit kal lek cherrgottabadd sielai do telusukonut vanijyaparanga sadhyam kad.
urd: ye ki, kisi bhi diye gaye din main, ek hi pii oo aai lakhon minute kii kaalon ko sambhalataa hai jo bi es en el ko saunp jaati hain, or aisi soorat hal main, ye samajhnaa tizaarati tuur par mumkin naheen hai ki kaun si kaal hakiki hai or kaun si kaal si el aai ke bagaiyr yaa ched chhad wali hai.
eng: That, on a given day, a single POI handles millions of minutes of calls that are handed over to BSNL, and in such a situation, it is not commercially feasible to decipher which call is genuine and which call is without a CLI or a tampered CLI.

guj: tene bi.bi.el.ai.el. sathe samagr utpadanna vechan mate karar karyo hato, je pachhithi vipanan vyavastha mate ech.el.el. sathe jodi devama aavyo.
hin: usne puure utpaadan kii bikri bi.bi.el.ai.el. ko karne ke liye samjhauta kiya, jisamen bi.bi.el.ai.el. baad main vipanan ke liye ech.el.el. ke saath vilay ho gai.
kan: adu idi utpadaneya maratakkagi bi.bi.el.i.el.nondige oppandavondakke ozpattitu, munde bi.bi.el.i.el. maratgarikegagi ech.el.el.nondige vilinavayitu.
mal: vipannattinai pinnite ech. eൽ. ellumai layichch bi. bi. eൽ. ai. ellumai mubhuvൻ ulpadanvu viൽkkanural oru karariൽ avർ oppuvachu.
ori: samagra utpadan bi.bi.el.aai.el. ku bikran nimanthe, eha eka chukthi scshar karithila, yahaki paravartti samaure bipanan pin ech.el.el. sahit mishiyaithila .
pan: oh aapne saare utpadans di vikri lai bi.bi.ail.aai.ail naal ik kararaname vich aa gaye jo ki bood vich aich.ail.ail naal lan-dain de udesh naal mile gaye I
tam: atu bipielaiel niruvanatin mott urbatties virbhans seyvadaikak ore oppandam saydukondotu, binner anniruvanum chanditelukkak hecelel niruvanaton inaikpattatu.

urd: is ne bi bi el aai el ke saath puri paidavar kii farvakht ke liye ek maahda kiya, jo baad main marketing ke liye each el el main zam hogya.
eng: It entered into an agreement for the sale of the entire production to BBLIL, which later merged with HLL for marketing.

ben: bristol bears (ragabi union) evan glucestershayar jela cricket clabo ei shahare avasthit.
guj: bristole bears (rugby sangthan) ane glostershair counti cricket club pan aa shaherma sthit che.
hin: bristol bears (rugby sangh) or gloustershar county cricket club bhi shahar main sthit hai.
kan: bristol bers (ragby ockut) mattu glosteshire counti cricket club kud i pattanadalli nelegondive.
mal: (rugby unionay) bristol beyelsu glstersheper kanti cricket clubu i nagara aasthanmakitutet.
ori: brishtal beorse (ragvi unian) o glosestarshaar kounti cricket club madhya ehi saharre avasthit.
pan: bristol bieras (ragbi union)ate galostershir counti cricket club ve shihar vich sthit han I
tam: bristal pearse (rugby union), clachestershyare coundi cricket club akhiaves innakruttil than amaindulsana.
tel: bristal bers (rugby unian) mariyu gloucestershair kaunti cricket club kuda i naggarm aadharitanga unnai.
urd: bristol beruz (rugby kii union) or glocister shair county crookat club bhi shahar main waaqa hain.
eng: Bristol Bears (rugby union) and Gloucestershire County Cricket Club are also based in the city.

ben: yadio eti ekati filmphayar puraskar hiseve anumit, trini ekati saakshakare balesillen ye "aami to filmphayar puraskar likhini."
guj: bhale teni dharna filmpher eward roope thai, temane ek mulakatma kahyu ke "men ek filmpher eward evu lakhyu nahotu."
hin: unhone ek saakshaatkaar ke dauraan kaha ki haalanki anumaan lagaaya gaya ki vah film fere puraskaar tha lekin "maine film fere puraskaar nahin likhaa tha."
kan: adnnu filmpher prashastiyendu uhislagideyadaru, aat sandarshanavondaralli "naanu filmpher prashastiyendu baredill"vendu heliddare.
mal: atoru philim fener awardai karutapetunnundeakil "khan oru philim fener award enne anuthitill" enna oru abhimukhttil addeha paranjat.

ben: 7m shatabdeer bharatvarshe juanshang-era sammukhin haoya praia ardhek sannyasi mahayani haowar ag percent, besh khanikata samyer janya, bhartiya buddhader madhye mahayan chhil dhirgatite vruddhi pawa ekati sankhyalghu goshthi.

mal: kullchukalam mahayana indiaille buddhamatakkaർkkiteiൽ neunapakshamai kachindeeakil, etha nutandiൽ suvaൻsangh indyaiൽ condumutia sanyasikaliൽ ekadesha pakutiyu mahayanikൾ akunvidha avർ kramen vairukaairunnu.

tam: mahayanam chiritu kalam india bhauttarkalitaye chinubanmap brivakave irundatu, pingu atu patippatiak valarndu 7aam noorthandu indiaill suvanjang sanditt otumott bhautdhat tuavikalil aittang badip per mahayanarglak irundaner.
tel: bhartiya buddhulalo mahayan kont samayam varaku alpasankhyak varganga undepoindi, nemmadiga adigutu, 7va shatabd smayaniki bharatvaeshalo shuwangjang adurkonn bikshuulalo dadapuga sagan mandi mahayanule ayyar.
urd: mahayan kuch urse tak hindustani budh math ke pairokaron main iqilit rahe, ahista ahista badhate gaye yahaan tak ki saatveen sadi isvi ke hindustan main kowan zang ko milne waale tamaam rahabon main se takreeban aadhe mahayani the.
eng: Mahayana remained a minority among Indian Buddhists for some time, growing slowly until about half of all monks encountered by Xuanzang in 7th-century India were Mahayanists.

ben: eti upatvake shoshit has, yekhane eti garam o thandar prati sanvedanshil snayu prantagulike uddipit kare sable prayukt haley ushna anubhutha evan mridubhave prayukt haley thanda anubhutha upadit kare yeti taar pradaah pratirodh baishishtya suchak.
guj: e chamdi bahyatvachama shoshay che, tyaan te chetanaa garami ane thandak pratye sanvedanshil chhedaane uttejit kare che, priname jayare jorthi lagavaya tyaare humphalu ane narmashthi lagavaya tyaare thandu laage che, je te virodhi tatwo hovanu darshave che.
hin: yah bahyatvacha main avashoshit hota he, jahaan yah taap or thandak ke prati samvedansheel tantrika antarsanghanon ko prerit karata he, jisase, jab ragad kar ise lagaaya jaataa he to ek garmaahat mahasoos hoti he or agar halke haathon se lagaaya jaataa he to thandak mahasoos hoti he, jo iske pratikshobhan gunon ko darshata he.
kan: charmad horapadarvu adnnu hiricondag alli ushna mattu sheeta sanvedi nargal tudigainnu prachodisuv adu, birusagi ujjidag shakhad samvedaneyannu athwa hagurvagi nividag tannaneya samvedaneyannu nidutta pratyudrekakariagee ader gunawannu torisuttade.
mal: at tvakkinte uparitalpaliil valicchetucpetukayu, avitayull tanuppinotu chudinotu pratikariunn nadiute atse uttejitamaki, oru kander iritൻr end nileilull atine swabhava suchippikmattle, thirummippitippicchaൽ chutiൻre anubhavvu mriduvai purtial tanupyൻre anubhavvu untakkukyu cheyu.
ori: eha charmar adhicharmare avashoshit hoithaye, yeunthareki eha uttap eban sheetalatha prati samvedanashil snaobik pranthagudiku uddipit karai, jorre lepan karagale eka ushna anubhuti kimba dheer bhavare lepan karagale eka sheetal anubhuti utpanna kari, eka pratikshobhak bhavare nizer vaishishtvagudiku suchithaye .
pan: ih chamarhi de epidrims vich rach janda hai, jithe ih garam ate take prati sanvedanshil nasaan nuun utejit karada hai, jadon jordar fung naal lagu kita janda hai taan ik nighi sanvedana paidaa karada hai jaaa haulli haulli ik tandi sanvedana paidaa hundi hai, jo ish dis visheshtas nuun ik virodhi vajon darsoundi hai|
tam: atu charumatin mel adukkukul urinchapattu angu chudu manllum kulirchi unrakutia narmbhu munaralait tundukintu, awk atu viduviruppaqat deyxpatum podhu sudana unarvum menmayagat deyxpatum podhu kulirnth unarvum erbadudukintu, its mulam adan uduttal-ethirfup panpues welipadukindena.
tel: adi charmapu bahyacharmanlo grahinchabadutundi, akkd adi vedimki, challadananiki pratispandinche nadi chivarala uttejparustundi, chiraku pratirohakanga dani lakshanas suchistu balanga pusinpp vechchani anubhuthani leda sunnitanga pusinpp challati anubhuthani utpatti chestundi.
urd: ye jald ke epidermis main jazb hojata hai, jahaan ye garmi or sardi ke liye hasas asbi suron ko mataharak kurta hai, jab shiddat se lagaaya jataa hai to garmi kaa ehasaas paida kurta hai yaa narmi se lagane par thandak kaa ehasaas paida kurta hai, jis se is kii khasuseyat kii nishandahi hoti hai.
eng: It is absorbed in the skin epidermis, where it stimulates nerve endings sensitive to heat and cold, producing a warm sensation when vigorously applied or a cool sensation when applied gently, indicating its properties as a counterirritant.

ben: stryatospher salphet erosler rasyanik bikria ozon starer kshati karte par evan hydrogen chloride (HCl) o hydrogen florider (HF) math assid mati upar assid vrushti hay jhar paadate par.
guj: urdhvamandama sulphate arosolsni rasayanic pratikriya pan ozon starne nukasaan pahochari shake che; ane hydrogen chloride (ech.sii.el.) ane hydrogen floride (ech.epa.)jevaan acid dharti par acid varsha roope padi shake che.
hin: samtapamandal main sulphate erosol kii rasinic abhikriya se ozone parat kshatigrast ho sakati he or hydrogen chloride (HCl) or hydrogen fluoride (HF) bhoomi par amla varsha ke rup gir sakate hai.
kan: samoshnamandaladalli salfete vayukalilagal rasayanik kriyegalu ozone padravannu haanigolisabahudu mattu hydrojan cloride (ech.si.i.) hagu hydrojan floridnantah (ech.f.) aamlagalu aaml macheyagie nelakke suriabahudu.
mal: stratosphyarille sൽphate erosolukalute rasapravർttanangൾ osoൺ palic ketuvaruttukayu hydrajൻ chloridu (ech . si. eൽ) hydrajൻ floridu (ech .eph) polull amlangൾ amlamadyai tajeak vidukayu cheyya.
ori: stratosfiurre salephet erosolguikar rasarhnic prathikria ojon starar kshathisadhan madhya karipare, eban hydrogen chlorime (ech.si.el.) o hydrogen florime (ech.ef.) amlavrushti bhavare bhooprushthare padipare .
pan: stretosphiler vich sulphet arosol dirsayanak pratikria naal ozone di parat nuun nuksaan pahunch sakda hai, hydrogen chloride (aich.si.ail) ate hydrogen fluoride (aich.aif) varge tezab dharati utte tezabi varkha de roop vich digde han I
tam: aduku valimandalatil ull sulphat dusuppadalangalin rasayan vinlum oson padalatch chetappadutalam, adebol hyderajan chloride (HCl), hyderajan fluride (HF) bonthe amilangs bhumiil amil mahiyagab pogialam.
tel: stratospior lo sulphate kaligin drav tuparal rasayan charyal ozon poran debbatiyavachchu, alage hydrogen chloride (heach si el) mariyu hydrogen floride (heach eff) vanti amlamulu nail midaku amlavarshanga padsgalvu.
urd: kirah kaayama main lacket erosuliz ke camiai taamlat bhi ozone kii parat ko nuqasaan pahunchaa sakte hain or hydrogen chlorid (each si el) or hydrogen florid (each epa) jese tezaab tezabi barish ke tuur par jameen par baras sakte hain.
eng: Chemical reactions of sulphate aerosols in the stratosphere can also damage the ozone layer, and acids such as hydrogen chloride (HCl) and hydrogen fluoride (HF) can fall to the ground as acid rain.

ben: yadio eta kshinbhave prakashith chhil ye, akhil bhartiya ayurvigyan sansthaner kshetre, gangadharer mammla, hari sinher mammla, minu kumari mammla evan ramesh kumari maamla kshetre ekati mathvirodh chhil, amra dekhte paai ye, ramesh kumari mammla ye matamat prakash kara hayesil ta pulisher najre aasa kono amalyogya aparadher samay tader ye vyavastha newar prayojan chhil, taar sang mile royas.
guj: ol india institut of medical saynsna kesama, gangadharna kesama, hari sinhana kesama, minu kumarina kesama ane ramesh kumarina kesama abhipryoma virodhabhas hovanu aachhu suchavavama aavyu hova chhataan, amane laage che ke ramesh kumarina kesama vyakat thayela abhipray mujab jayare koipan kognideebal gunani policene jaan thai tyaare police dwara karvaani kaaryavahi jaruri che.
hin: haalanki halke se sujhaayaa gaya tha ki akhil bhartiya ayurvigyaan santhaan main maamle, gangadhar ke maamle, hari singh ke maamle, minu kumari ke maamle, or ramesh kumari ke maamle main vyakt vichaaron ke bich takaraav tha, hamane paaya ki ramesh kumari kaa maamla police ke saamne sangyeya aparaadh laae jane par uske dwaara kii jane vaali kaarywahi se sambandhit tha.
kan: akhil bharat vaidyakiya vigyan sansthey prakaran, gangadhar prakaran, harising prakaran, minu kumari prakaran, mattu ramesh kumari prakarangamalli abhipraia bhedavideyendu aspashtvagi aropishlagideyadaru ramesh kumari prakarandalli vyaktvad abhiprayavu yavude vichaarnarh-aparadhvannu policer gamnakke tandag avaru kaigollbekad kriege sambaddhavagiruvudu namage kandubaruttade.
mal: ol india institute of medical saynsas case, gangadharyൻre case, hari sincinte case, minu kumariute case, ramesh kumariute case enniv tammil nilepatuute karyattil oru abhiprayabhinnathunden durbbalamai suchippicppettengil, ramesh kumariute kaseil prakatipicpat kauchapat shiksharhamay kutam policinte shraddhil pettal adukkent natapatikaracurich parayunnatanen nam kanunnu.
ori: yadio 'akhil bharatiya aajurvigyan pratishthan' mammla, ganggadharank mammla, hari sinhank mammla, meenu kumarink mammla eban ramesh kumarink mammlare matamatre virodhabhas thila boli ksheen sanket missithila, ramesh kumarink mammlare prakashit mat, kaunsi dharttavya aparaadh policer drushtiku anagaale, ta'dra niayivaku aavashyak thiva karyanusthan sahit samparkit thila .
pan: halanki ih thoda jiha sujhv ditha gya see ki aal india institute aaf medical sincis de case gangadhar de case, hari singh de case, minu kumari de case ate ramesh kumari de case vich vichaars da takraw see, aseen dekhia hai ki ramesh kumari da mammla police de sahmne apraadh nuun saaf for 'te pesh karan 'te ve us duara keeti jan vaali karwai naal sambandhat see|
tam: aal india institute off medical scincess vanku, gangadran vanku, hari singh vanku, meenu kumari vanku, ramesh kumari vanku akhiyavail karuddukalil muranpadu ulldak sushakamakach suddapatalum, evvoru kadukurya kullemum kavalturin kawnatiskuk konduvarapatum podhu avarkas edukk wantia natwatiky dodarpak ramesh kumari vanggil therivixpatum karutu.
tel: akhil bharat vedya vidhya sansth kesu, gangadhar kesu, hari singh kesu, minu kumari kesu mariyu ramesh kumari kesulaloni samikshallo vibheda unnadani ospashtamuga suchinchabadinppatiki, ramesh kumari kesulo vyaktamin samiksh edaina vicharinchatagin aparaadha gurinchi polisuvari drushtii vachchinapp vaaru tisukovalasin charyaku sambandhinchinadi ani manaku telustundi.
urd: agarache mubaham tuur par ye kaha gaya tha ki aal india insiti tute of medical sincez ke maamle, gangadhar ke maamle, hari singh ke maamle, menu kumari ke maamle or ramesh kumari ke maamle main khayalaat main tazad hai, lekin hum dekhte hain ki ramesh kumari ke maamle main jo ray jaahir kii gai hai, wo police ke zarie kii jane wali carrwai se mataalak hai, jab koi kaabil dast andaazi jurm is ke ilm main laaya jataa hai.
eng: Though it was faintly suggested that there was a conflict in the views in the All India Institute of Medical Sciences case, Gangadhar's case, Hari Singh's case, Minu Kumari's case, and Ramesh Kumari's case, we find that the view expressed in Ramesh Kumari's case related to the action required to be taken by the police when any cognizable offense is brought to its notice.

ben: varna, gunaman, aakaar, naksha, evan anyanya bastur sang samparker mato drushyaman ingitguli sahayog bivinn bhoomi sima chihnit karaar cajti vyakhyakari upar nirbhar kare.

hin: vibhinn bhu-aavaran virgon kii pahchaan karne ke liye vyakhyaakaar dwaara rang bhed, sanrachana, aakaar, praturup abhigyaan or anya vastuon ke saath sambandh jaise drishy sanketon ke prayog par yah nirbhar karata he.

mal: vividh bhamoparital vibhagae niryian nirum, pratalaghathan, akriti, pattiൺ, matu vastukalotulla bandha, enni drushya suchanal upyogient chumtal vyakhyatavina.
ori: eha vibhinna bhu-aavaran shreneer chihnat kariva pin varna, vinyas, aakruti, ruparekh, eban anyanya wastegudik sahit ehar sampark bhadi chaakshush sutaragudiku nitojit karivaku bakhakarajankank upare nirbhar karithaye .
pan: alag-alag zamin shrenia di pachhan karan de lai ih ihatarajman te nirbhar karada hai ki oh drish sanket jive ki bolan da lahija,banaavat,saroop,namoone ate baaki chiza naal sambandh bana ke age vadhe I

tel: vividh bhoomyacchadan vargal gurtinchenduku varna, uparitalam, akar, nirmankram, mariyu itar wasteulatho gal sambandha vanti drushya gamnikal avalimbinchenduku idi vyakhyatpai aadharpadutundi.
urd: mukhtalf arji ahaaton ke durjon kii shinaakht karne ke liye ye mitrajim par manhsir hai ki wo basri ishaaron jese sir, sakht, shukla, namoonaa or duusari ashya se taalluk kaa istemaal karee.
eng: It relies on the interpreter to employ visual cues such as tone, texture, shape, pattern, and relationship to other objects to identify the different land cover classes.

ben: ayush doctorder prapyata anuyayi homeopathy, ayurveda, siddh evan unani paddhatir 18ta jeller (rajya) madhye 13tar janya presskripashanguli upalbdh chhil.

hin: aayush chikitsakon kii uplabdhta ke aadhaar par 18 main se 13 zilon (rajyon) main homeopathy, ayurveda, siddh or unani pranaaliyon ke aushadhiy nuskhe uplabdh the.
kan: 18ralli 13 jillegamalli (rajyagalu) aayush vaidyar labhyatege anusarvagi homiyopati, ayurveda, siddh, mattu yunani paddhatigal aushadh suchanegalu labhyaviddavu.
mal: 18 jillakal (sansthana) 13 anttil ayush doctormarute labhyatayanusrich homeopathy, ayurveda, siddh, unani enni sampradayasille prescripshanul labhyamairunnu.
ori: aatush daktharamanank upalavita anuyani homiopathi, aajurveda, siddh, eban unani pranalir aushadhpatra 18ti jilla (rajya) madhyaru 13ti pin upalavdh thila |
pan: homeopathy, ayurveda,sidha ate anaani pranali de anusaar, nuskhe ayush doctors di uplabadhta anusaar 18 wichon 13 raja vich uplabadh san I
tam: ayush marudvars iruppatap boruttu, 18il 13 mavatangsil (manilas) homeopathy, chiththa manllum unani vaitalukan marunduk kuripu sevaigus kidaittana.
tel: ayush vaidyul labhyat prakara homeopathy, ayurveda, siddh, unani vidhanai gal 18 jillal(rashtral)lo 13tiki aushadhpatras andubatulo unnai.
urd: aayush doctron kii dastyabi ke mutabik homeopathy, ayurveda, sudhaa or unani nizaam ke 18 ajala (riyasato) main se 13 ke liye naskhe dastyab the.
eng: The prescriptions were available for 13 out of 18 districts (states) of Homeopathy, Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani systems, as per the availability of AYUSH doctors.

ben: vapak arthe, ektiar bahirbhoot cryakander prekshite, kono prashasonic siddhanth ayauktik (canadian ine anuyayi sarbochch aadalte dancemuter banam new brancuike "spastoti ayauktik"-era mandand pratyakhyaan anusar), widenesaveri ayauktik (ingrej iner antarbhukt) athva yadruchh o anirbharayogya (markin prashasonic paddhati ine evan new yark rashtra iner antarbhukt) haley punarvibechana aadalat setic kharij karte par.
guj: baholi rite satta baharna caryo mate, samikshak adalat samaji shakay tevu hoya to vahivati nirnay baaju par muki shake, jo te gervajbi (canadana kayadama sarvochch adaalte dansamuir virudh new brunsavik kesama nakki karela dhoran mujab ‘spashtapne geravyajbi’ (british kaayadaa hethal)no ashvikaar thavane pagale) ane ekapakshi ke tarangi (yu.es. vahivati prakriya dhara ane new york rajyana niyam) hoya.
hin: vyapak arthon main adhikatit kriyaaon ke sandarbh main, samiksha karne vaala nyaayalay ek prashasnic nirnay ko palat saktaa he yadi yah anuchit (canadai kanoon ke tahat, sarvocch nyaayalay dwaara dansmur banaam new brunsvik main "spasht rup se anuchit" maanak kii asweekruti ke baad) vednesbari anuchit (british kanoon ke tahat), manamaana or swechhachari (america prashasnic prakriya adhinium or neuyork rajya kanoon ke tahat) he.
kan: adhikarkke mirid kramagal paribhasheyalli sthulvad arthdalli, ondu parishilana nyayalayavu aadlitatmak nirnayavondannu adu asamanjas (canadad kanoonin adiyalli, dansmyur virudh new bransvic prakarandalli sarvochch nyayalayavu “spatassiddhvagi atarkik”vendu tiraskarisid manadandavannu anusarisi), wednestory vicharashunya (british kanoonin adiyalli), athwa avicharit mattu abaddh (newyark rajyad kanoonu mattu you.es. aadlitatmak kaaryavidhan kaydeya adiyalli) enicidare tallihakbahudu.
mal: vishalaർteattiൽ niyamparmay adhikar kootatayull pravർttanae kanumpoൾ, oru bharanaparmay thirumana anyayamanengiൽ ( aa "vyaktamayu anyayamay" pramatte dൺsmuyru new breaൺswik tammilull kaseiൽ kanadiaൻ niyamamanusrich suprinkotati duർbalmakiyatinettutർnn), vensbery anyayam (british niyamamanusrich), vastunishthmallatato chapalmayato (yu. es administretive prosijyർ aktu neuyoർk state niyamamanusrich) oru meൽckotati at raddakkaൻ kaniyu.
ori: adhikar-bahirbhoot karyor bapak arthare, eka samiksha karuthiva adalat gotie prashasanic nishpattiku pratyakhan karidheiparanthi, yadi eha ayatharth (canadiya ine adhinare, dansamifer vanam niu bransik mammlare, "spast bhave ayatharth" manadand supreme courtank dra pratyakhaat heva pare), danesavari ayatharth (british ine adhinare), kimba manamukhi eban khamakhiali (yuktrastra prashasanic paddhati ine eban newark rajya ine adhinare) hoithaye.
pan: vyapak arathas vich altara virus karwaia de sandrabh vich, ik samikhia karan vaali adaalat ik prasaski faisle nuun ik paase rakh sakadi hai jekar ih gair-vaajab hai (canadian kaanoon de tahit, dansmuir banaam neu baranzavik vich supreme court duara "safsht for 'te gair-wajib" miar nuun rad karan ton bood), wednessbari gair-vaajab (bartania kaanoon de adhin), jaaa manmani ate sanaki (you. asa. prasaski prakiria act ate neuyarak raj de kaanoon adhin)|
tam: ore arasu mudiveu niayambatu (canada sattatin keel, itu dunsmiur edir niu pransvick vanggil ucch neetimanram "chandekaminti niayamda" niyamat maduddhatap pindadukintu), appartamak niayambatu (british sattatin keel) alltu edechsaiyanatu manllum thandonditanamantu (america arasu nirvag seyalmuraich sattam manllum neuyark manilach sattatin keel) endal, mahubarichilanai sayes neetimanram ant mudire parant nokil adhikar varambhuku miria natwatiky enbhadan feril rattu seielam.
tel: vistrut bhavanlo nyayaparimitini minchin charyal vishyanlo, samikshinche nyayasthana, ock paripalna nirnyam anuchitanga unte (canedian nyayashastra prakara, dunsmuir lo supreme court pratiga new brunswic) "phurtiga asamanjasaminadi" ga tiraskaran cheyabadin pramana prakara, (british nyayashastra prakara) vednusbari asamanjas, lek (yues paripalna vidhan chatta mariyu new yark rashtra shasana prakara) nirhetukamainadi mariyu chalchittaminadi ayina danni kottivey vachchu.
urd: vasia maanon main dayera akhtiyaar se baahar carrwai kii aitbaar se, ek nazar saani karne wali adaalat kisi intazaami faisale ko mistrad kar sakati hai agar ye gair makul (canada ke kanoon ke tahat, supreme court kii jaanib se dansmor bamqabla new branzook maamle main "wakaah tuur par gair makul" mayar ke astrdad ke baad), vednsburi gair makul (bartanvi kanoon ke tahat), yaa man mana or namnasib (america intazaami tareeqa car act or new york state kanoon ke tahat) ho.
eng: In terms of ultra vires actions in the broad sense, a reviewing court may set aside an administrative decision if it is unreasonable (under Canadian law, following the rejection of the "Patently Unreasonable" standard by the Supreme Court in Dunsmuir v. New Brunswick), Wednesbury unreasonable (under British law), or arbitrary and capricious (under the U.S. Administrative Procedure Act and New York State law).

ben: yuktraje sansadin sarvabhaumatber mathvader adhine sansader ingulike alada kara yave na kintu parishader ine, arek dharner prathmik ine ya sansad dwara pash karano naya, tader kara ya (dekun civil service unioner parishad banam civil sarviser janya mantri (1985) evan miller/cheri (2019)).
guj: united kingdomma sansadiya sarvbhramatvana siddhanth hethal sansadana kaayadaaone kore muki shakata nathi, jayaare parishadana adesho-sansad dwara pasaar n karayela prathmik kaayadaano anaya prakaar-ne muki shakay che (juo council of civil sarvis unions virudh ministar four civil sarvis (1985) ane milar/cheri (2019)).
hin: united kingdom main sansadeey samprabhutaa siddhant ke anusaar, sansad ke adhiniyamon ko alag nahin rakhaa ja saktaa he, jabaki parishad main aadesh, jo ki ek anya prakaar kaa praathmik kanoon he jise sansad dwaara paarit nahin kiya ja saktaa he, ko alag rakhaa ja saktaa he, (dekhen civil seva sangh banaam civil seva mantri) (1985) or miller/cheri (2019)).
kan: united kingdomnalli sansattin kaydegamannu sansattin sarvabhaumatva siddhanthad adiyalli anoorjitgolislu sadhayvillvadare, sansattu angikarisad innondu bageya praiamik kaidegalad parishattin aadeshgainnu anoorjitgolisabahudu (nodi, kaunsil aaf civil service unions virudh minnester far da civil sarvice (1985) hagu miller/cherry (2019)).
mal: unitod kingdemyൽ paർlameൻryൻre paramadhikar end siddhanthmanusrich paർlameൻr niyamngoൾ raddakkaൻ kaviyuillennirie, paർlameൻr passakatt matoru tarattilull praiamik niyamniർmmanmay kൺsilile uttarvukൾ mativekkaൻ kaviunnava (kൺsiൽ of civiൽ sർvis unionulu civiൽ sർvis mantriyu tammlu (1985), millർ/cheriyu (2019) kanuk).
ori: britenre, sansadiya samprabhutar neeti anuyani sansadar inagudiku khaaraj karayyparivanahin, athach sansad dra gruhith heunathiva, aau eka prakaarar praxmik bidhan, 'arderas in counsil'ku karayyparib (counsil af sibhil sarbhis unians vanam minishter fer da sibhil sarbhis (1985) eban millar/cherry (2019) dekhanthu).
pan: united kingdom vich, parliment de act nuun parlimentary prabhutata de sidhant de tahit ik paase nahi rakhia jaaa sakda, jadon ki consal de adeshs vich, ik hor kism da primary kanun sansad duara paas nahi kita gya, dekhko (siwal seva union di consal banaam siwal seva lai mantri (1985) ate mari/cherries (2019 ))|
tam: ikiya rajjiyattl, paralumanow iraiyanmike kotbattin keel paralumaneech chatangss rattu seyy mudiyadhu, encallum paralumanjattal niraivecoppadat manthoru vaka mudanmaych chattanglana merkulu anaikal rattu seyy mudi (kank, nirvagap pani changangs edir nirvagap panikan amychare (1985), millar/cherry (2019)).
tel: united king, parliament yact lu prabhutva siddhantal kind upekshinchabadw, ayite parliament pravesha pettani pradhan shasana ane arder aaf di kaunsil upekshinchabadutundi (kaunsil aaf civil sarvis unian varses ministor for di civil sarvis (1985) mariyu miller/cherries (2019) ni churgalru).
urd: bartanya main, parlimani hakimit ke usool ke tahat parleman ke kavanian ko bartaraf naheen kiya jasakta, jabaki ehkaamat ko konsil main, jo ek or kasam kii buniyadi kanoon sazi hai jise parleman ke zarie manzoor naheen gaya, kar sakte hain (dekhen konsil of civil servaice vrisz minister for di civil servaice (1985) or milar/cheri (2019)).
eng: In the United Kingdom, Acts of Parliament cannot be set aside under the doctrine of parliamentary sovereignty, whereas Orders in the Council, another type of primary legislation not passed by Parliament, can (see Council of Civil Service Unions vs Minister for the Civil Service (1985) and Miller/Cherry (2019)).

eng: The goalkeeper must remain on his line until the ball has been kicked, and all other players must be outside the penalty area behind the penalty spot.

ben: anyanya french shilpira, yanra tander kaje ei khelar pratinidhitva karellen, seguli madhye royas albert gliges-era le juur dya phutbal (1912), robert delaner phutbal l'kip dya cardiff (1916), evan andre loter parti dya ragabi (1917).
guj: anaya evaan french kalakaaro jemane khelma pan karyarat rahine pratinidhitva karyu che tema albert gleizesna les jours footbolma (1912), robert delunayna footbol likvip dee cardiff (1916) ane andra lhotena party dee rugby (1917)no samavesh thai che.
hin: apni kalakritiyon main is khel ko darshane vaale anya french kalakaaron main albert glices le jour kii da footbal. (1912), robert diloni kii footbal l' equip da cardiff (1916), or andre lhote kii party da ragabi (1917) the.
kan: i krideyannu chitrisiruv itar french kalavider chitrakalakritigamalli albert glejn ʼle juwah de footballʼ (1912), robert duloney ʼfootball lekip de cardiffʼ (1916), mattu andre lhotn ʼparty de ragbyʼ (1917) serive.
mal: i kaayikavinodas tangute rachanakl pratiphalippichch mat franch kalakaranmaril le shuve de futbol (1912) cheit alber glayses, futbol lekvip de cardiph (1916) cheit robart delone, parti de rugby (1917) cheit andre lote enniwar ulppetunnu.
ori: annga ferasi kalakar yeunmane nij kalakritire ehi khelku darshaivanthi, semanank madhyare angnthi, alavart gleijes 'le jupurs de phutaval're (1912), rabart delaune 'phutaval l'kuip de cardiff're (1916), eban andra lhote 'party de ragvi're (1917).
pan: hor fransisi kalakaar jinhan ne kheds nuun apnia kala vich pesh kitha hai oh han, alburt galeizas 'les jeeeras di football (1912), robert dailone di football l'kip di cardif (1916), ate ander hote di party di ragbi (1917).
tam: ind vilyatte pitt frenchkh kalaiarkathum tangaldu patipughalil chertlsanar, avarkhil albert clechasin les uvers di football (1912), robert delanein football la'egvib di kardiff (1916), antre lothein parti di rugby (1917) akhiyawe atankum.
tel: i krida tam kalakhandala varninchin itar french kalakarulu albart gluj' le juvars di football (1912), rashirt delune football. lekip di cardiph (1916), mariyu andr lhot party di rugby (1917).
urd: dusare francisi fankaar jinhon ne apne fan paaron main is khel kii akasi kii in main albert glez lee jor kii di foot bal (1912), robert dee loni kii foot bal laa ecoip di cardiff (1916) or andre lahote kii party di rugby (1917) shamil hain.
eng: Other French artists to have represented the sport in their works include Albert Gleizes' Les Joueurs de football (1912), Robert Delaunay's Football. L'Equipe de Cardiff (1916), and Andre Lhote's Partie de Rugby (1917).

eng: The rare and threatened animal species identified are green sea turtle, dugong, Irrawaddy dolphin, blackbuck, Spoon-billed sandpiper, Chilika limbless skink, and fishing cat.

ben: yehetu pudendal snayu bahan kare motor o indriya sakrant fiber ya pelvik peshi snyusansthan kare, ei pudendal nerve block prasav yantrana thek rehai deya.
guj: aenu kaaran e che ke pyudental snayu gatishil ane sanvedanatmak tantuonu vahan kare che je pelvic snayuone uttejit kare che ane janma samayna dardene antre che.
hin: guhya tantrika main kyonki prerak evam samvedi tantrikaayen hoti hai jo shroni mansapeshiyon main tantrikaon kii aapurti karti hai, to guhya tantrika rodh se prasav pidaa se aaraam miltaa he.
kan: bahya jananendriyad narvu shronia snayugalige narshaktiannu odagisuv chalak mattu samvedana tantugainnu haisuvudarind, bahya jananendriyad narvannu pratibandhisuvudarind prasav vedaneyu upashamanvaguttade.
mal: pudental nadi arekette peshik nadibalam nalkunn motor, censari fibarukൾ atangiyatinal pudental nadiile tarussm prasavvedan kurikkunnu.
ori: yehetu guhya snatou prerak eban sambedi tantugudiku bahan karithaye yeungudikaki shroni mansapeshigudiku achdaadit karithaye, eka guhya snatou punyj prasab vedanar upasham karithaye .
pan: kiunki podingle naadi motor neuron ate sanvedi fibers nuun chukadi hai jo ki ped dis mass-peshia nuun reshedaar rakde han, podingle naadi da khand paidaaish dard vich raahat dinda hai I
tam: pack narumbil idupukuddut dasiluku unarvutum iyakk manllum unarchi narkas irupatal, pack narmbutt tadai erbadudhuatu prasav valiys nikkum.
tel: pudendal nadi anedi kati kandarase uttejit chese kadalikanu, gyan tantuus kaligi untundi kabatti, pudendal nadi addgimp prasav vedann taggistundi.
urd: chunki padandal aisabab motor or hasee rishon ko lay kar jataa hai jo pedo ke pathon main isbyon ko daalate hain, lahza ek padandal asbi dard za se nijaat dilaataa hai.
eng: Because the pudendal nerve carries motor and sensory fibers that innervate the pelvic muscles, a pudendal nerve block relieves birth pain.

ben: 1875 sale kathamoke wingphilder sanskarner anurup chihn sah taar anganer balighrhi aakruti ekati yatkshetre badul kare bartaman vidyaman anganer naksha paribartan kara hayesil.
guj: 1875maa aa namunama pherfar karine courtney dizine aaje astitvama che tevi karai hati, tenu marking vingfildna jevu ja hatu pan tena courtno kalakashishi jevo aakaar badline lambchoras karaayo hato.
hin: is ferme main 1875 main sanshodhan karke vartmaan court kaa praaroop banaaya gaya, jisamen chihnan wingfield sanskaran ke samaan the lekin unke court ke retagdi ke aakaar ke bajaay court aakaar kaa aayat tha.
kan: i madariannu 1875ralli presettdalliruva ankanad vinyasakke marpadislagi, adu vingfildon madarige sadrushyavad gurtugalind kudideyadaru, aathan maralu gadiyarad aakarad ankanavannu ayatakarakke badlayislagide.
mal: 1875l i ruparekh innte cort designilo roopantarappetuttukayu marking vingphildinte matrukak oppichanengil addehtine cortine nabhikamanirupa dirghachaturmakkukyu cheitu.
ori: ehi namunatir 1875 masihare aanshik parivarttan karayai varttaman dinare thiva court praroopaku parinat karayaithila, ethire thiva santak sabu ngafilank namuna seh saman rakhayaithila, kintu tank courter balighadi aakaar eve aayithakshetra aakaarre parivarttan karayaithila.
pan: ih namoona 1875 vich awj de de hisaab naal badalia gya see, nishaan wingphild de anuvadnal milade-julde han, per us da roop ghanta glass ton badal ke chaukore kar ditha see I
tam: ind munwativeu 1875il insaiy adugal vativatingu maderiyamicopattatu, atil vingbieldin vativamifu bhonjee kotus kurickhapattrundal, eninu adugalam avritu khatikarak kudurai vativatukup patilak sevvak vatiwil mallchum pervrundatu.
tel: 1875 lo i namoonan, vingfild roopantarnanni polin gurtulato, present wadukalonunn aat sthal rupaniki savarincharu, kani isuk gadiara akarmuloni atani aat sthalanni dirgh chatursraniki marchru.
urd: is saanche ko 1875 main aaj ke maujod court ke dezine ke mutabik tarmium kiya gaya tha, wing field ke varden kii tarah ke nishanat ke saath, lekin is ke ret ghadi kii shukla ke court ko mastatel se badal diya gaya.
eng: This template was modified in 1875 to the court design that exists today, with markings similar to Wingfield's version, but with the hourglass shape of his court changed to a rectangle.

ben: mott abhyantarin upadner 21.6% har abhyantarin sanchay evan mott abhyantarin upadner 1.6% har bideshi sanchay sah abhyantarin evan bideshi us thek binioger janya prayojanian sanchanguli aasaar katha chhil.
guj: rokan mateni bachat swadeshi ane videshi sadhanomathi aavanar hati, je kul gharelu utpadanna 21.6 % dare deshmani bachat ane kul gharelu utpadanna 1.6 % videshi bachat hati.
hin: nivesh ke liye bachat gharelu ev videshi sroton se aani thi, jisamen se gharelu bachat kii dar sakal gharelu utpaada kaa 21.6% tha or videshi bachat kii dar sakal gharelu utpaada kaa 1.6% tha.
kan: hoodikegagi ulitayavu, ottu deshiya utpannad 21.6%dashtu deshiya ulitay daradalli mattu ottu deshiya utpannad 1.6%dashtu videshi ulitay daradalli deshi mattu videshi moolagalind barbekagittu.
mal: nikshepicppetuvanuol sampadyam abhyantarvu vaideshikavumay srotassukaliൽninn varunnatayirie, abhyantar sampadyanirk motta abhyantar utpadanttiൻre 21.6 shatamanvu videsh sampadyanirk motta abhyantarutpadanttiൻre 1.6 shatamanvumairunnu.
ori: nivesh nimanthe uddist sanychay gharoi eban videshi utsagushikaru aasibar thila, yaahaar gharoi sanychay haar samudaya gharoi utpadar 21.6% eban videshi sanychay haar samudaya gharoi utpadar 1.6% thila .
pan: nivesh lai bachat gharelu ate videshi sarotaan ton auni see; kul utpad da 21.6% di gharelu bachat dar naal ate kul gharelu utpad di 1.6% videshi bachat de naal|
tam: mudalitukkan semibbu nidhi ulnadu, velinadu ena iru aadharangalilrundhum varum eneum, atil ulnadduch semibbu vikitham mott ulnaddu urbattil 21.6% alvill velinadduch semibbu vikitham mott ulnaddu urbattil 1.6% alvill irukkum eneum ditamitapattatu.
tel: stul deshiotpattilonchi deshiya muldhana 21.6% choppun mariyu (stul deshiotpattilonchi) videshi muldhana 1.6% choppun, pettubadi kos muldhana deshiya mariyu videshi aadharal nudi ravalsi unden.
urd: saramy kari ke liye bachatein gharelu or gair milki jaria se aane wali thim, jin main gharelu bachit kii shrah majamuai gharelu paidavar kaa 21.6faisad or gair milki bachit kii shrah majamuai gharelu paidavar kaa 1.6faisad thi.
eng: The savings for investment were to come from domestic and foreign sources, with the rate of domestic saving at 21.6% of gross domestic product and that of foreign saving at 1.6% of gross domestic product.

ben: mexicoi yoth udyog pratishthan sthapan kara bideshi sansthaguli madhye ullekhayogya halo sampoorn televishan, saada panya, mudrit circuit board, el.si.de panel, evan ardhpariwahi nakshakar o presentkarak ekati sthanian disinar samex gaian kara samshang; evan electronicser aansh, televishan, evan karkhana bhari yantrapati upadankari toshiba dev mexico, es.e. di si.bhi. name prashasanicbhave swashasit ekati sahayak gaian kara toshiba.
guj: mexicoma nondhapatra videshi companyo dwara sthapayela sanyukt sahasoma semsang samavisht che, jene samex sthapi che je ek sthanik dijhiner roope tayaar telivithan nirmata, shwet mal ane chhutak electronic bhaago jevake printed circuit bords, alsidi panls ane semicndctarsana utpadak che; to toshiba che, jene toshiba dee mexico sthapi che, vahivati rite swayatt avi gaun sanstha je electronic bhaago, telivithans ane bhaare udyogna sadhanonu utpadan karti es.e. dee. sii.ve. samel che.
hin: prasiddh videshi companiyaan jinhone mexico main sanyukt udhyam companiyaan sthapit kii hai, unamem hai samsung jisane sthaneey diziner or nirmaataa, samex, kii sthapana kii he jo taiyaar television, frij, kapade dhone kii mashin, aadi or bhinn prakaar ke electronik purje jaise ki print kiye hue circuit board, el.si.di. panelle or ardhchalkon kaa utpaadan karte hai; or toshiba jisane toshiba da mexico, es.e. da si.ve. kii sthapana kii, jo prashasnic rup se swytt sahaayak company he or yah electronik purje, televishan or baari audyogic upkaran kaa utpaadan karti he.
kan: mexicodalli zanti sahasodyamagal astitvavannu sthapisiruv pramukh videshi companigamalli, siddh durdarshanagalu, bili sarkugalu, hagu mudrit vidyunmandal falakgalu, el.si.de. falakgalu, hagu arevahakagalantah pratyek vidyunman ghatkagainnu vinyasagorisuv hagu taarisuv sthaliya sanstheyad sameksannu prarambhisid samsung mattu vidyunman yantragal bhagagalu, durdarshanagalu, hagu bhaari kaigarika sadhanagainnu utpadisuv aadlitatmakavagi swayatt angasanstheyagiruv toshiba de mexico, es.e. de si.vi.yannu sthapisiruv toshiba serive.
mal: mexicoil sanyukta nikshep sanrambhas tutangia pradhanpat videsh companyl, pani purtiyakia telivishanul, vittupakaranws, prinod sarkute bordu polull tani electronic ghankas, el.si.de. panlukൾ, semikanaktrukൾ ennivyute utpadakaru pradeshik designarmarumay samexine rupankotutt sansang; electronic ghankas, telivishanul, ghanvyavasayangൾkkuvena upakarnws, enniv utpadippikkunn swayanbharan sabsidieriay toshiba de mexico, es.e. de si.vie roopikarichch toshiba enniv ulppetunnu.
ori: mexicore sanyukt udum sansthaman sthapit karithiva prasiddh vaideshik companygulik madhyare rahichhi 'samasang', yie 'samex' ganan karithila, yie eka sthaniya dejiner tatha present hoiyaithiva telebhijan, grihopayogi vaiduthik upakaran, eban mudrita sarkit borde, el.si.de. panel, ardhdhaparibahi bhadi gotikia vaiduthik upadangudikar utpadhanakarta; eban 'toshiva', yie prashasanic drushtiru snshasit sahayak sanstha 'toshiva de mexico, es.e. de si.bhi.' ganan karithila, yie vaiduthik yanthransh, telebhijan o bhari shifp saranjam utpadan karithaye.
pan: zikryog hai ki videshi companie jinhan ne ganjod naal sansthavaan nuun macciko vikhe sthapit kita gya, jo ki ti ve de purze ate kale-kale electronic puraje jiven printed circuit board, ail see di panels, ate ardh-chalik yantran de local diginer ate niramata han| ise tarhaa toshiba ate toshiba maccico, asa. e. de see. ve. sthapit keeti, jo ki ik khud mukhtiar prasashan sahik ikai hai, jo electronic purze, ti ve ate udayogic darje de upkaran banaundi hai |
tam: mexikoil gootuanik niruvananglait tuwakil kufippitttakk velinaddu niruvananglil udbadubhavai: chamchung, itu chamex enjh ulnaddu niruvantai uruvakyldu, atu niraivubettn dolixtchigus, vellait dayarippues, melum prindot sarqiute ports, elceti banals manllum semicontaktas bonthe tani minnenup bhagangs akhiyavaggrai vativamipatil urbhatti saywatil edupattuldu; manllum toshipa, itu toshipa di mexico es.e di chi.vi enjh nirvag ritiyana dhannatchit dunai niruvantai uruvakyldu, atu minnenu utiri bhagangs, dolixtchigus, canarakat dolirsalai upakarans akhiyavawait dayarikintu.
tel: mexicolo samyukt venture erpat chacin pramukh videshi sansthallo, tayaran telivijanle, vidyut upkarnal, mariyu mudrinchabadin sarcut boardulu, elsiri panaillu, mariyu semikandaktor stanik rupakarth mariyu tayaridarin syamex ga erpadin syamsang; mariyu electronic bhagal, telivijanle, mariyu bhari parishramik yantrangas tayaruchese, nirvahanaparanga svayn pratipatti gal anubandha sansth toshiba de mexico, esedicivi ga erpadin toshiba unnai.
urd: mexico main joint venture udaarekaayam karne wali kaabil zikr gair milki companiyon main samsung shamil hai, jis ne simiks ko tashkeel diya, jo taiyaar shudaa tele vaibhanon, bade gharelu mashini alaat or infradi electronic izza jese print sarakat boradon, el si dee benalon, or semi conductron kaa ek mukami maujid or sanaat car hai, or toshiba jis ne toshiba dee mexico, es aye dee si vee tashkeel diya, ek intazaami tuur par khud mukhtar zeli udara jo electronic izza, tele vision or bhaari sanati saaman banaata hai.
eng: Notable foreign companies that have set up joint venture entities in Mexico include Samsung, which formed Samex, a local designer and manufacturer of finished televisions, white goods, and individual electronic components like printed circuit boards, LCD panels, and semiconductors; and Toshiba, which formed Toshiba de Mexico, S.A. de C.V., an administratively autonomous subsidiary that produces electronics parts, televisions, and heavy industrial equipment.

ben: trini tar make, yini a-dharmik abhivavakder dwara bada hay uthesillen, "dharmabodh thek bicchin" ekajan maanush bale ullekh karala anek kshetre "amar jana aadhyatmbodhe sabche jagrit ekajan vyakti" evan "dharmanirpeksh manabtabodher ekajan ekaki saakshi" baletten.
guj: temane temana matane varnavata janavyu ke teo bin-dharmik ma-baap dwara ushrya, jane ‘dharmathi alag’, chhataan ghani babate ‘pote janeli sauthi vadhu aadhyatmik rite chetanasabhar vyakti’ ane ‘binasapradayik manavvaadana ekala saakshi’.
hin: gaiyr-dharmik mata-pita kii parvarish main pali apni maan ke bare main ve kehete hai ki ve "dharm ke prati anasakt" thim, tab bhi kai arthon main, "meri jaankaree main aadhyatmik rup se sabase adhik jaagrit vyakti" or "dharmanirpeksh maanavtawaad kii ekaaki sakshi" thim.
kan: aat dharmikarllad poshakaru belesid tann tayiannu, "dharmadind berpatt" hage iddaru, halvu ritiyalli, "nanage tilidiruvavaralle aadhyatmikavagi atyant jaagrut vyakti"yendu mattu "matadharmathitvad manaviyatege ekangi sakshi"yendu bannisiddare.
mal: matavishwasamillatavray matapitakalaൽ valർttappett tൻre matavin addeha "matattiൽ ninn weർpettavar" pakshe pal riti "enic ecalavu ariaൻ itavann et athmiyamay udbuddhatyotukootia vyakti"yayu "matetarmay manvikatute oru ekayay sakshi"yayu aan visheshippicht.
ori: an-dharmik pitamatank dra palitha, tank maanku se "dharmatharu bichinna", athach anek prakaare, "mo gyathasarare aadhyathmik drushtiru attant jaagrath bsakthi", eban jane "dharma-nishpaksh manabbad pin ekakini saakshi" bhave varnana karithile.
pan: usne apni maa nuun, gair dharmic mapias duara palya gya oesia, "param ton nirlep" oesia, phir ve kai tarika naal sabh ton uddh "adhyatmik for 'te jagaruk viakti jisanu mai kade jaanya hai", ate "dharam niraikh manav-vad lai ieale gavaah" vajon varnan kita hai|"
tam: madappardu illat pevorkalal valarcoppatt tan taiai avar varniumbodhu, "madappardu illadhavar" encallum pal vithkalil "naan abhindavarkalileye aanmik ritiyag" mikhat "telindhavar" manllum "madacharparey manidhaneyatin tanitt satsyalar" endu gurinar.
tel: loukikavad talidandrul pempakanlo adigin tan tallini atanu,"mataniki atitamani", ayinanu, tanu yerigin, anno vidhala atyant "aadhyatmik spruh gal vyakti", mariyu "loukik manavtavadaniki ekac sakshiga" abhivarninchadu.
urd: unhon ne apni maa ko, jin kii parvarish gair majahabi valdin ne kii thi, ko "majahab se latalak" qaraar diya, lekin kai tareekon se "ruhani tuur par bedaar shaks" or "sicular insaaniyat kii tanhaa gavaah" ke tuur par bayaan kiya.
eng: He described his mother, raised by non-religious parents, as being "detached from religion", yet in many ways the most "spiritually awakened person I have ever known", and as a "lonely witness for secular humanism".

ben: lal ded evan habba khatuner kashmir rachanaguli tader rahasyamita evan abhivyakti tibra yantranar janya parichit, rajasthanite mirabaier rachanaguli anany bhaktiguner janya parichit, tamile andaler rahasyamita evan kannde aakka mahadebi bachanguli takalin sahitye nareeder mah avadaner praman.
guj: lal ded ane hubba khatuni kashmiri rachnaao tena rahasyawadi ras ane abhivyaktini fiver peedana karne janiti che, mirabaii rajasthani rachnaao anany bhakthi gunne karne janiti che, tamilma andalni rahasyavad ane kannadama akka mahadevina vachno mahilaona tatkalin sahityana mahan pradaanna purawa che.
hin: hubba khatun or lall-dyad kii kashmiri rachanaaen unke aadhyatmik andaaz or gahan bhaawanaaon kii abhivyakti ke liye jaani jaati hai, rajasthan main mirabai kii rachanaaen unki adwitiya bhakthi ke liye lokapriy hai, tamil main andal kaa gudh gyaan tathaa kannada main akka mahadevi ke vachan us samay ke sahitya main mahilaon ke vyapak yogadan ke pramaan hai.
kan: lal ded hagu habba khatoonr kashmiri rachnegalu avugal aadhyatmik sogadu mattu fivravad paritapad abhivyaktige hesaruvasiagive, mirabayiya rajasthani bhajangalu avugal anany bhakthiya lakshanakke hesaragive, tamilinalli andauil anubhav mattu kannadadalli akk mahadevia vachanagalu aa kaalad sahityakke mahileyar mahattaravad kodugege sakshigalagive.
mal: laaൽ dediൻreyu habb khatuniൻreyu aadhyatmikabhavattinu prakatitmay fivraduhkhttinu peruket kashmirirachanakalu, savisheshamay bhakthirasattin peruket rajasthaniilull mirabaiute rachanakalu, tamilille andalute aadhyatmikadർshanvu, kannadailull ack mahadeviute vachanau aa kalatte sahityattiൽ streekൾ naൽkia mahattay sambhavankulla sakshyapatraa.
ori: lal dedh o hava khatuntak kashmiri rachana segurikar aadhyathmik ras eban abhivyakthir tibr vedana pin janashuna, mirabaink rajasthani rachana nij niara bhakthi bhava pin prasiddh, tamilre andalank rahasyabad, eban kannadare aakka mahadeveenk bachansabu heudi sehi kader sahithyaku nareemanank mahan abadanar saakshya.
pan: laal ded te habba khatoon dia kashmeri rachnavaan apni rahasmai ranga te under di pida bayan karan lai jaana jaande han, mirabai di rajasthani rachnavaan apni anokhi dharmic gun, annal da tamil rafasalad ate awkka mahadevi di kanda vich vachnas , ih tub mahilaas de saahit vich mahaan yogadan de gavaah han I
tam: lal dhat manllum hubba katunin kashmiri kavitis marainanab bhokum desire vedan welipatus konduluna, rajasthani mofiil ull meerabai kavitis tanitwamikk iraibhaktit dhanmikub peyarbonavai, tamilil antalin marainanak kavitikalum kannadatil akka mahadeviin vasanangalum andak kaalakttin ilakyatisqup pengal alitt maperum banglipin sandugalak vihangukindena.
tel: lal ded mariya hubba khatoon vanti kashmiri rachnal vatloni aadhyatmik kammadana, fivramin aavedana bhaval vyaktikarnaki, rajasthan mirabai rachnal adwitiya bhakthi gunaniki, tamiluloni andal bhavayogam, mariyu kannadanlo akk mahadevi vachanal alanati sahityaranganiki stril ghanamin todpatki nidarshanal.
urd: lal did or hubba khatun kii kashmeri tasanef apni sofiana chaashni or kurab ke shiddat izhaar liye mashhuur hain, rajasthani main mirabai kii nazamein anokhe bhakti mayar ke liye jani jaati hain, tamil main indul kii batinet or kannada main aka mahadevi kii vaachnaen is vakt ke adab main khwatin kii azim hissaa dari kii gavaah hain.
eng: The Kashmiri compositions of Lal Ded and Habba Khatoon are known for their mystical flavour and intense agony of expression, Mirabai's compositions in Rajasthani is known for unique devotional quality, Andal's mysticism in Tamil and Akka Mahadevi's vachanas in Kannnada are testimonies to the great contribution of women to the literature of the time.

ben: gowar rashtriya praani gaur, rashtriya pakhee halud bulbul evan rashtriya galle halo bhartiya laral.
guj: govanu rajya praani gaur che, rajya pakshi flame-throted bulbul, ane rajya vriksha indian loral che.
hin: gaur goa kaa rajkeey pashu he, flem-throted bulbul rajkeey pakshi he, or rajkeey vriksh indian laurel he.
kan: govaad rajya prani gaur, rajya pakshi kesari kattin pikalar mattu rajya vrakshavu matti marwagide.
mal: goayute sansthanmrigam kattupottu sansthanapakshi manikanthanu sansthanvriksha punnamaravumakunnu.
ori: goar rajya pashu heudi gaur, rajya pakshi heudi manik-kanthi bulbul, eban rajya briksh heudi bharatiya larel .
pan: goa da raj jaanwar gaur hai, raj pakshi laal kanth bulbul hai ate raj rukh bharati sihara hai I
tam: goavin maanil vilangu gotterutu, manilab barowai shivaput dondaich chinnan, maanil marum punnai.
tel: goa rashtra jantu gaur, rashtra pakshi flem-throted bulbull, mariyu rashtra vrikshan indian larel.
urd: goa kaa riyasati jaanvar gaur hai, riyasati parinda gluatishi bulbul or riyasati darkht hindustani lorl hai.
eng: Goa's state animal is the Gaur, the state bird is the Flame-throated Bulbul, and the state tree is the Indian Laurel.

ben: inuiter prathagat kahini, achar evan vidhinishenguli praiashi hal tader ruksh sumeric pariwesher bipader viruddhe satrkta.
guj: inuitani parampragat vartao, rivaajo, ane pratibandho ghanukharu temana kathor arctic vatavaran dwara mukayela jokhamo saame savachethiroope hoya che.
hin: inuit logon kii paaramparik kahaniyaan, rivaaj or varjanaayen aksar arctic ke nishthur vaataavaran ke kaaran aane vaale khataron ke khilaaf ehtiyaat hote hai.
kan: inyuitgal sampradayik kathegalu, paddhatigalu, mattu nishedhgalu samanyavagi avar kathinavad arctic vatavranavu odduv apayagal virudhad munnechcharikegalagive.
mal: inutuute parampragatkathalu aacharaslu vilckukalu palpposhu avarute parukkanay uttardhruvparistate srushtiunn apakatangൾkketiraull muൻkarutalula.
ori: inuitnk paramparik kaahaani, reetineeti eban samajik nishedhaguik anek samaure semanank meru anchader krur parivesh yogun ghatuthiva bipad prati sabadhanta dra abhipret.
pan: inute dis parampragat kahania, riti rivaaj ate manahia onha de kathor arkatic watavarna ton bachan lai saavdhania han I
tam: inute makalin bharambariyak kataikas, chadangus manllum aidigangs perumballum tangas gatumayana artic suzlil ull apattues kuritt munnecharikis akum.
tel: inuvit ki chendin sampradayak gathal, aacharah, mariyu nishedhal tarchu vaari uttardhruvaprant kathin vatavrana kaliginche pramadalku mundu jagrattal.
urd: anuit kii ravayati kahaaniyan, rasomat or mamanuaat aksar in ke sakht arctic maahaul se paida hone waale khatarat ke khilaaf ehtiyaati tadaber hain.
eng: Traditional stories, rituals, and taboos of the Inuit are often precautions against dangers posed by their harsh Arctic environment.

kan: hwan manuval fanjio nalku bhinn tandgavdialli aidu baari farmula one vishv champion agiddu, tamm 184 antarashtriya resgamalli 102nnu geddiddare mattu sarwakalik sreshth chalkanendu vyapakwagi manyate padediddare.
mal: nal vyatyasttimuil ninn anchutavan phormula van champyanavukyu 184 antarashtriya matsaras 102 enea jayikkayu cheit juan manual fangio ecalattayu et mahanay driverai parkke karutapetunnu.

ben: sarbochch dharmik kartavya hisabe ahimsar dharmatattvik vittitiqu "daan thek arjeeth sadgun athva anyanya prani prati sahanubhutha baa samast praani uddharer kartavya dwara chalith" hisabe naya varang "kramagath aatma-shrunkhala", shesh percent nirvana evan punarjanma thek muktike prabhavit kara nijer aadhyatmik unnati sadhankari aatmar shuddhikarner prenam hisabe vyakhya karellen koekajan jain pandit.
guj: ahimsa ek uchchatam dharmik faraj hova angenu dharmagyannu ketlak jain vidvano dwara evu arthaton ke ‘anaya jivone aapava ke temana pratye karuna dakhavavaa, ke tamam jivonu rakshan karvaani faraj’ puratu ja nahi, pan ‘satt svayn shist’ne priname, atmashuddhi dwara jaate potano aadhyatmik vikas pamavo, je ante potana nirvan ane punarjanmamathi mukit mate aasar kare che.
hin: kuch jain vidwaanon ne sarvocch dharmik kartavya ke rup main ahimsa ke dharmik aadhaar kii vyakhya kii he ki jo “daan karne yaa anya praaniyon ke prati dayaa-bhav rakhane kii yogyata se prerit na ho, na hi sabhi praaniyon ko bachaane ke kartavya se ho”, balki "nirantar aatm-anushaasan" ke parinamswaroop ho, jo ki aatma kii shuddhi he jo swayan ke aadhyatmik vikaas kii ore le jaati he, jo antat vyakti ke uddhaar or punarjanm se mukti ko prabhavit karti he.
kan: atyunnatvad dharmik kartavyavagi ahinsey matadharmasastriya aadharvannu kalavaru jain vidwansaru, adu “daan maduvudu athwa itar jivigelli dayeyannu hondiruvudarind siguv punyad hambaladind preritawageerabaradu mattu ella jivigathannu rakshisuvudu kartavyavendagali all”, badalige adu “nirantaravaad svayn-shistin” prenamvagiruttade, adu atmad shuddhiagiddu tannade aadhyatmik pragatige karanwagi, antimawagi vyaktige mokshavannu dorkisi, punarjanmagalind bidugadegoaisuttade endu vyakhyannisiddare.
mal: "danttiൽninno anyajivilotulla karunaiൽninno, ella jivikalayu rakshicook end karttavyatiൽninno kittunn punyattal tvarippicppetate" "nirantarmay atmaniantranttilute" avanavne aadhyatmikavikasattiletikkunn atmashuddhikaranttilute, atyantikamai mokshatteyu punarjjanmattiൽninnull mukthieyu swadhinikkukaa atyunnatmay matadhർmmamai ahimsaye karutunnatiൻre daivashastraparmay atitara enna chil jainapundithanmar vyakhyanikunnat.
ori: ahimsa sarbochch dharmik karttavya heva padsr dharmatattk aadharaku kichhi jainas vidn bakhya kariyanthi ye, "eha annga pranimanank upare daya ba karuna bhavaru srushti heuthiva yogatharu asi nathaaye, kimba samast praninku uddhar kariva karththavyaru madhya asi nathaaye," baran keval "kramagat s-anushasan" dra prapth hoithaye, aatmaar eka vishuddhikaran yaha nizer aadhyathmik bikash ghataithaye, yaha sheshre nizer moksh prapthiku prabhavita karen, eban punarjanmaru mukt karithaye.
pan: ahimsa da dharmic adhar , sabh ton sarvotam dharmic seva, kuchh jaini vidhwaana vajon vyakhya kitha gya see "hor jivaan nuun den jaaa daya karan di yogata duara chalaia jaa sakda hai, naa hi saare jivaan nuun bachaun da farz hai, per "nirantar sajai-anushasana de natije vajon, aatamaa da shuddhikaran jo ki apna hi adhyatmik vikas, karada hai, jo akharirkaar, viakti de moksha ate punarajnam nuun nuun prabhavit karada hai I
tam: ahimsaiye mik uirnt samayak katamay enbhadan samay adippatiku chil saman aricirs vivkkamalikkum podhu, atu "mabbbb jivarasiluku varanguvadu alltu itakkum gadduvadan nanmainal undapphatak goodadhu manllum anatu jivarachigales kaffact wants enjh kadamas all", majhak "dodernth suyak kaddupadu" banutan balanak anmap parisuttom adaindhu irutiyag tanatu motchates manubhiaviilrundhu vidudalai peruvates badikkattakk vaqail suy aanmik munnenram peruvateyakum endu gurinars.
tel: atyunanat matparamin vidhiga ahinsak vedantaparamin aadhara anedi kontamandi jain panditulche ila anavayinchabadindi, "migta pranulku ivvada leda vaari pat karun chupinchada leda anni pranus rakshinche kartavya nudi vachche patrath karnanga sphurti pondakuddu," kevalam "nirantar sviya-kramshikshan" nudi tam aadhyatmik purogtiki daaritise atm shuddhi nudi ravali, adi tudaku vaari mokshanni prabhavita chessi, punarjanmal nudi vidudal chestundi.
urd: adam tushdad kii majahabi buniyaad ko sab se bada majahabi frija qaraar dete hue baaz jain ilma ne is baat kii tashrih kii hai ki wo "duusari makhluqat ko dene yaa raham karne kii kaabilit se mutasar na ho, or na hi tamaam makhluqat ko bachane kaa frija ho", balki "mustaqil zabbat nafas " kaa nateeza ho, ruuh kii safai ke tuur par jo insaan kii apni ruhani nishvonima kaa baais banati hai, jo balakhir insaan kii nijaat or punarjanm se chutkaare par asar andaz hoti hai.
eng: The theological basis of non-violence as the highest religious duty has been interpreted by some Jain scholars not to "be driven by merit from giving or compassion to other creatures, nor a duty to rescue all creatures," but to result from "continual self-discipline," a cleansing of the soul that leads to one's own spiritual development, which ultimately affects one's salvation and release from rebirths.

ben: 2014 thek, sadharan bhartiyader janya desh evan bidesh ubhay sthanei passport pawa evan punarnvikarnti sahajtar kare tolai modi sarkarer agradhikar thek asese.
guj: 2014thi modi sarkarani e agrata rahi che ke deshma ane videshma samanya bhartiya mate passport melvavaa ke punarjivitha karvanu saral karvu.
hin: 2014 se modi sarkaar ne praathamikta di he ki aam bhartiya ke liye desh evam videsh main passport praapt karnaa or naveekaran karnaa aasaan banaaya ja sake.
kan: 2014rindichege, swadesh mattu videsh eradu kadegayllu posportgannu padeyuudu mattu navikarisuvudannu samanya bharatiyanige innashtu sulabhasadhyavagisuvudu modi sarkaarad adyatayagide.
mal: sharashari indyakkar swadeshttu videshattuwech paspoർtt karsthamakkal putukkal eluppamakkukyennat 2004 mutൽ modi sർkkariൻre muൻgananavivyama.
ori: 2014 tharu , modi sarkarnkar agradhikar heudi, ubhay desh madhyare tatha desh bahaare, sadharan bharateeinkar passport hasal kariva eban nabikaran karivaku adhik sahaj kariva .
pan: saal 2014 ton modi sarkaar di prathmikta ban gai hai ki aam bharati nagarik nuun passport banavaun ate usnoo bharat jaaa videsh vich rineu karwan di pricria vich saralta praapat hove I
tam: 2014 muthal, woru sarasari indian ulnadu, velinadu ena erandu suanilkalilum melum sulapamagak katvuchittu peruvatu manllum putuppippadaskana natwatikiku moti arasu munnurims alitu varukintu.
tel: 2014 nudi, sagt bhartiy swadesh, videshal rendintilo passports pondada mariyu punaruddharinchkovadanni sulabhtaram cheyada modi prabhutvan yokk praadhanyataga undi.
urd: 2014 ke baad se, modi hukuumat kii trigeh rahi hai ki ausat hindustani ke liye ghar or berun malik passport haasil karna or tajdid karna aasaan banaaya jaaye.
eng: Since 2014, it has been the Modi Government's priority to make it easier for the average Indian to obtain and renew passports, both at home and abroad.

mal: upyogichotinu adhivasiritinumulla nashtaparihar, atikramitchukyria aaൾkketiraull natapatiiൽ uthmasthൻ yathaർteattiൽ avkashppetunnundo illayo ennat aprasaktama.
ori: malikajankank dra anupraveshakarijankank virudhre grahan karayauthiva karyanusthanare bbbahar eban bhogadakhal hetu hoithiva kshaukshati nimanthe vasthabare davi karayib ki naahin taha nirarthaka ate .
pan: ish gal da fida nahi hai jekar varton te kaarobaar da harajaana malik ne ulangana karan wale ton lae hai jaaa nahi I
tam: attumiri nuraipavruku ethrana woru natwatikyil urimayalar unmail andap prayogm manllum akhramibbukkan batiput dokaiy korukhihara illaiya enpatu mukhiyamall.

eng: It is immaterial whether damages for the use and occupation are in fact claimed or not by the owner in an action against the trespasser.

ben: pradarshan vyavstha ei paribartan pashu rakshakader kshetra rakshanavekshan, gacher yatn, abhawa niyantran evan bivinn shreni aro anek prajatir pashupalaner prashast gyan sah basbaser pariwesh tattwavadhane aavashyak karm abhijeeta sah avas rakshake parint kare kajer suyogke parivartit karche.
guj: nidarshan vyavasthamana pherfarne karne pashupalakona kaarya vistar badalaai rahyan che karanke teo e pradeshna rakshako bane che, temane jeevant paryavarniya sambhavna jaruri gyan sathe chhodni sambhal, abohwa niyantran ane vividhvargna pashupalannu vistrut gyan male che.
hin: pradarshan vyavasthaaon main badlaav pashupalkon ke liye kaam ke vistaar main parivartan laa rahaa he kyonki paridrishy rakrakhaav, paudhon kii dekhbhaal, jalwaayu niyantran, or rahane ke maahaul kii dekhbhaal, or sabhi vargeekrut shreniyon main kai or prajatiyon ke liye pashupaalan kii vistaarit samaj sahit kaarysadhak gyaan rakhte hue ve prakritik awaas-paalak ban rahe hai.
kan: pradarshanad airpadugalallin marpatinindagi prani palkaru bhudrushya nirvahane, sasyagal arike, havaman niyantran, mattu jeevavargagaladyant innu anek prabhedgal pashusangopaneyalli vistarvad arivannu olagondante jeeva parisar vyavastheya palanege agatyavad kelsadarivinondige swabhavik neley palkaraguvudarind avar kaaryavyaptiyu badlaguttide.
mal: bhuprakrutiparipalan, sasyaparipalan, kalavasthaniyantrana, vyatyast jivivർggackslilull kututൽ inateute paripalanvumai bandhappet waർddhitmay arive ennivyuൾpete jivattay paristateute paripalanttin atyavashya vende prayogikavigyanmulsavray avasvyavastyute sukshipukarai avർ marunnatote, pradർshan kramikaransille matom avarute joliute vyaptiiൽ matom varuttunnu.
ori: pradharshani aajojanare parivarttan hetu pashu rakshakamane prakritik vasasthan rakshak heva sange sange, eha semanank pin rahithiva karyor suyogaku parivarttit karshani, yeunthireki prakritik drushyabhoomir rakshanavekshan, udbhidhamanankar yatn, jalbatou nivnthran, eban samagra bargeekaranagat shreneegudik madhyare ahuri anek prajatir pranimanank pin uddist pashupaaner vistrut gyan samet sajeeb parivesh tattbadhanar eka aavashyakiya karyansadhan gyan rahichhi .
pan: pradarashani intzama vich tabdeeli kaaran janvars de rakhtaka karan walia lai com da daera badal riha hai kiunki hun uh nivasi sthal rakhtak ban jaande han, jise vich jeevat watavarna di dekhbhaal, landscape di sambh , paudias di dekhbhaal, jalavayu niyantaran, ate kai hor prajatia lai pashu palan da vistrit gyan taxonomic clasaas vich shamal hai.
tam: katchi arbadugalil nickhandull mallchum vilanguk kappaurkalin pani warumbai majori varukintu, ibbodhu avarkas vilangu vashippitak kappazarkalagaum maghi valvial sunal paramripu basari avasiuman natamurai ariwap perukinsener, itel nilavelip paramripu, davrangs paramripu, chitoshnak kaddupadu, chagal vakapattu warkanglidaiye melum pal inangalukan kalnd vaurfu basari koodudal arivu akhiaves udpatum.
tel: pradarshan erpatlo marpu jantu sanrakshakulu nivassthan parirkshakuluga marea, sahjaranya bhubhag sanrakshanto kudin prakruti, parisaral nirvahan, vriksha sanrakshan, vatavaran niyanthran, mariyu shastriyanga vargikarinchin anekanek jantula gurinchi vistarinchin pashusanvardhan gyana avasarapadata, vaari karyaparidhini marchtondi.
urd: numaayishi intazaamat main tabadeli moyashi pravari karne walon ke kaam ke daayre ko tabdel kar rahi hai jese jese wo zindagi ke maahaul kii dekh bhaal kii zaroori amali malomat, bishmol kudrati manazir kii dekh rekh, podon kii dekh bhaal, aab va hawa ke control or tamaam tar anqasami zamaron main or bhi bahut se anua ke liye moyashi pravari kii azafee malomat ke saath, muscan ke rakhwale bin rahe hain.
eng: The shift in exhibit arrangements is changing the scope of work for animal keepers as they become habitat keepers, with a necessary working knowledge of living environment care, including landscape maintenance, plant care, climate control, and expanded knowledge of animal husbandry for many more species across taxonomic classes.

eng: Paddy, the main food crop, is mostly cultivated in the Andaman group of islands, whereas coconut and areca nuts are the cash crops of the Nicobar group of islands.

ben: radiopharmaceuticals atyant vishuddh tejascrian oshdhi dravya ya manusher upar prayog karaar kshetre yathest nirapada evan has rog nirnyer kshetre baa manusher bivinn dharner asusthatar janya chikisa kshetre vyabhhar kara has.
guj: radiopharmaceutical e uchchatam shuddha radyoektive pharmaceutical banaavato che je manav vyavastha mate purta pramanma surakshit che ane vividh prakarani manav bimariona nidan mate athva ilaj mate vaparai che.
hin: vibhinn prakaar ke maanav rogon ke nidaan or upachaar ke liye radiodharmee aushadhiyon ko atyadhik shuddh radiodharmee padaarthon se nirmit hona chahie jo manushyon ko die jane ke liye paryaapt rup se surakshit hon.
kan: radiopharmaseutialgalu atyant shuddha vikiranshil aushadhiya utpannagalagiddu manushyarige nidebahudadashtu surakshitvagive mattu manushyarallin vividh bageya koilegal roganidan mattu chikitseyalli badkeyaguttave.
mal: manushyaprayogtin vendetra surakshittvamullathu vividhtelay manushyarogatee niർnaiano chikitsiano upyogappatunnatumay uyർnn parishuddhiull radio aktive ay phaർmasuticaൽ uൽppannaa radiophaർmasuticaൽs.
ori: bikiran aushadhiguik heudi atsadhik shuddh tejaskriya aushadhiya samagri yeunguik ki manushya kshetrare prayog nimanthe yathest nirapad eban vibhinna prakaarar manaviya rogar nidan kimba chikitsa nimanthe brebahrut hoithaye .
pan: radiopharmacutical shuddha radeoactive farmacutical prayojan han jo inasana de upyog de lai mahfoos hai te tashais de lai ate kai prakaar di bimaria di ilaaj lai vartia janda hai I
tam: katriyakk marundub boruts enbhave manitap payanpattukkup batkappan manllum balavit manit nobenotigalin khandwithal alltu sikiikub payanbaduttapadukis migaum tuya katriyakk marunduk kalavilakum.
tel: radiodharmik aushadhal atyant swachchamin radiodharmikat kaligin aushadh tayaris, ivi manav vinioganiki taginant surakshitmainavi mariyu manuullo vividh anarogyalku roganirdharanku leda chikitsaluga vadbadtai.
urd: radiopharmasuticliz intihaai khalis tabikar advyati naskhe hain jo insaan ko dene ke liye coffee mahfuz hain or mukhtalf kasam kii insaani bemariyon kii tushkhis yaa therapi main istemaal kiye jate hain.
eng: Radiopharmaceuticals are highly pure radioactive pharmaceutical preparations that are safe enough for human administration and used for either diagnosis or therapy of various kinds of human ailments.

ben: david i. nicholser mate, "oshudh tiri shilper saathe yukt bahu sahakarmir sang bakhrer par bashwar yav alochana amake avahit kareque ye, yadi sambhavya natun oshudher screening karaar samay serotonin 5-aich.ti.2.e agonistojanit caryakalap pawa ya, tave eti praia sab kshetre sei anur aro vruddhir samapti sanket deya".
guj: david i. nicholas mujab, “dawaan udyogma kaam kartaan ghanan sahakaryakaro sathe varsho sudhi charchaae mane janavyu ke navi dwani tapasma serotonin 5 - ech.ti.2e. agonist pravritti jova male che, e hanmesha e anuna vadhu vikasana lagbhag antano sanket male che.”
hin: david i. nicols ke anusaar, "aushadh kshetra main kaam kar rahe apane kai sahakarmiyon ke saath charchaa karne ke baad mujhe yah pataa chalaa he ki kisi sambhavit nai dawa kii jaanch karne par agar usamen serotin 5-ech.tii.2e. kriyaprerak gatividhi dekhi jaati he to yah us anu ke praayah hameshaa hi aage viksit hone ke ant kaa sanket hota he.
kan: david i. nicholesr prakaar, "pharmaseutical kshetradalli kelas maduttiruv anek sahodyogigalondigin varshagattleya charchegalind nanage tilididdenendare, parikshegolpadisidag ondu sambhavya hoss aushadhiya vastevu cerotonin 5-ech.ti.2e. eduru sangharshak chatuvatikeyannu hondiruvudu kandubandare, adu hecchukadime yavagalu aa anuvin yavude hchin abhivruddhige aantyavannu sanketisuttade."
mal: "auodhaniർmmanavyavasayattiൽ pravർttikkunn anek sahapravർttakarumayull kure waർshanslai natakkunn chർchchakൾ, oru putia marunin parishodhikumpoൾ atiൽ sereൻtoniൻ 5 - ech ti 2 e yute virudhpravർttana contettukaanengiൽ at etand micpposhu aa tanmatrayute ethenkil tarattilull punർvikasattiൻre antyam kuriunnu" enna david i. nikkoൾsiൻre abhiprayam.
ori: debhing i. nicolsank matre, "anek barsh dhari aushadh presenthakari udogra karyan karuthiva anek sahakarmeenk seh hoithiva aalochanassbu mote ehi suchana deichhi ye yadi scrining pare eka sambhavya nuthan aushadhare serotonin 5-ech.ti.2e. prachank sakriyatha rahithibar dekhivaku mile, eha, praiathanga sabubela, ukt anutir adhik kramavikashar samapthiku suchit karithaye ."
pan: david i. nicholas, de mutabik," inhan saalas vich aapne sathis naal, jihde farmacutical udayog vich com kar rehe han, onha ne minuun oesia hai ki ik sambhavi navin aushadhi di chanbin karade samen ,jekar us vich serotin 5-hat 2 aa angonist pratikria hundi hai , oh humesha hi, us anu upper hor vikas te rok paa dindi hai I
tam: "marundial turaiil panipuri sagauliargauton pal andus kalanduraiyatic pingu, scriningl woru satiyaman putiya marunduku seratonin 5-hesti2e aganist seyalbadu iruppadakak kavanixpattal, ant moolakduku menokondu ent valarche irukkadu anpataiye atu aittang apodhum kuripatak irukkintu enab purindukondan" endu david i. nicoles gutaullar.
tel: david i. nicols prakara, "ellatarbadi aushadhiya parishramalo pani chestunn andaro sahodyogulatho charchl naku teliajasindi emanga, sambhavya nuthan aushadha parikshinchinapp serotonin 5-heach. ti.2 e. pratispandan charya kanipiste, adi dadapu ellappudu aa anuvuki jarige tadupari vruddhiki mugimpuni suchistundi."
urd: david e nicholas ke mutabik, "in saalon ke dauraan dwasazi kii sanaat main kaam karne waale kai saathiyon ke saath hone wali baat chet ne mujhe aagaah kiya hai ki agar jaanch padtaal ke baad kisi mumkin nai dawai main serotonin 5-each tii 2 aye kii manaazaa sargarmi kaa patta chalata hai to ye takreeban hamesha is salme kii majid nishv va numa ke khatm hone kaa ishaara krati hai.
eng: According to David E. Nichols, "Discussions over the years with many colleagues working in the pharmaceutical industry have informed me that if upon screening a potential new drug is found to have serotonin 5-HT2A agonist activity, it nearly always signals the end to any further development of that molecule."

ben: swaynsampoorn evan dharmian nirdesher aar prayojan na thaka shwayitu hollen sarbochch; bipath yawa thek atkate manusher sang bandhutva kara airyamn athva bandhu; evan math nem kaaj kara sakriya karmi evan vishwaser pracharak verejana athva karmi.
guj: jhevitu sarvochch che, je atmanirbhar che ane temane have pachhi dharmik suchanani jaruriyat nathi; airyamna, athva mitra, je mitra banii lokoney bhataki javathi bachaave che, ane verezanah, athva kaaryakar, je bhoomi parano sakriya kaaryakarta che, je vishwas felaave che.
hin: sabase sheersh par he jwaetu, jo swatahparyaapt he or ab unhen dharmik nirdesh dene kii aavashyaktaa nahin he; airyamn, yaa mitra jo logon ke saath mitrataa karte hai or unhen pathbhrashtha hone se rokte hai; or hai verezana, yaa karmi jo sakriy kaaryakarta hai or jamini str par dharm kaa prachaar karte hai.
kan: kswaytu atyuchchanagiddu, swayampoornanad ivanige innu dharmik bodhaneya agatyaviruudill; iryamn, athwa snehithanu janaru addadari hidiadante avarondige sneh belesuttane; mattu verestnah athwa kelasagarnu talmattadallin sakriya kaaryakartanagiddu math prachar maduttane.
mal: swayamparyapti nedia alu matavidyabhas ini aavashyamillatayalumay 'swaitu'van et unnat; 'airyamna' athva suhrut, alul waitetipokatirian avarote changatta kutunnayal; oppam, take karmmarangat sajivavu vishes pracharipikunnavnumay , 'veresan' athva pravർttakൻ.
ori: sarbochchajanak heutanthi 'khithu', yieki sein-sampoorna atanthi eban aau dharmik margadarshan aavashyak karanthi naahin; 'airyeeman', ba 'bandhu', yieki lokamananku kupothare yivaru raksha karivaku semanank sahit bandhuth sthapan karanthi; eban 'berejana', ba 'shramika', yieki kshetra upare thiva sakriya kshetra karyankarta atanthi tatha yahanku vishs sanychar karibar thae .
pan: sabh ton shikhar 'te jawaetu hai, jo swai-nirbhar hai ate hun us nuun dharmic niradesh den di lod nahi; airman jaaa dost, jo locals naal dosti karada hai ate uhanaas nuun gumrah on ton rokda hai; ate verejanh jaaa kama, jo ki chusat kargekarata hai ate jamini padhar 'te dharam da prachar karada hai |
tam: itel mik uirndhawar swaydu, iver tanniriu peweaver, ivaruku ini samayab bodhanai devaill; aduttu ariyamna alltu nanber, iver makaluton natbu kondu avarkas nervati dhawaramal pardukolwar; moonravatu verachana alltu donder, iver munippack kauppani saitu samayanety parabuwar.
tel: atyunnatmamainavadu jvaitu, itadu svayn samriddhito atuvanti matparamin bodhan avasaram lentuvantiwadu; airyamn, leda mitr, prajalku mitrudai vaaru tappudari pattakunda kapadevad; alage verejna, leda shramik, itadu bhoomipai vishwasamunu vyapticheyavalsin kriyashil kshetra karyakarta .
urd: sab se aala kisavetu hai, jo khud muktafee hai or majahabi hidaayat kii majid zarurat naheen rakhata, riman yaa dost hai, jo logon se inhen gumraahi se bachane ke liye dosti kurta hai, or veerzana yaa carkan hai, jo jameen par fial jamini carkan hai or emaan ko failane ke liye hai.
eng: The highest is the Xvaitu, who is self-sufficient and no longer requires religious instruction; the Airyamna, or friend, who befriends people to keep them from going astray; and the Verezanah, or worker, who is the active field worker on the ground and is to spread the faith.

kan: vayumandalavu kadime aavarthanagal microtarangagalige parvahakavagiddu, avu modgainnu bhedisicondu hoguvudarind microtarang dur samvedak tantragalu sarva-ritu samarthyavannu hondive mattu sooryan belkinind prabhavitvagad microtarang sanvedigalindagi hagalu hagu ratri caryacharanegalige takkudagive.
mal: kushanera aavrittikal antariksha microvevulot sutaryat pulartunnatinal, av meghae tulecchukyrunnatinal microvev remot sensing sanketikavidyakൾk oru sarvakalavasthasheshiunden matramall, suryaprakashatilninn swatantramayatinal av raavu pakalumulla pravartanak yojyav.
ori: microbh rimot sensing kaushangurikar samast panipag nimanthe uddist dakshata rahichhi karan nimnatar aabrittire microbhguik nimanthe baumandal subhedya ate, segoik badalamadhiku pravesh karipare, eban microbh censoragurikar suryaaloka upare an-nirbharasheelatha hetu din o raatir sanychason nimanthe segoik upayukt hoithaye .
pan: microwave remote senscing taknika col har mosam di samphtha hundi hai kiunki jive vayumandal ait warwarta di microvevez ton pardarshi hai, oh badla wichon nangh sakde han ate oh suraj di kirans ton microwave senss ton alag han jise kaaran oh din te raat di varton lai uchith han I
tam: nunnalait dolaitur nudbangs chagal tadbhavepp nilaikalilum velcsaiyus,anendal kuraint adhirvenkalil nunnalis valimandalam vaqiye cell mudi, are meghangss uthuruum, melum nunnalai unarigaluku surya oli devaill enpatal are ervu, bhagal ena iru samayankalilum iyakkatisqup porudhamanus.
tel: sukshmatarang sudur grahakat sanketik prakrialku anni rakaal vatavaran samarthya kaligi untundi andukante vatavrana takkuv vyaptivadd sukshmatarangalk atitanga untai, avi meghalloki chochchukuni potai, mariyu suryaprakashamu nudi sukshmatarang censor valan avi ratri pagal jaripe karyacharanlaku anukulanga untai.
urd: microwave remote sensong takneeken har mausam main kaam karne kii salaahit rakhti hain kyonki kirah fizai kam fracunci par microwave ke liye shafaf hota hai, wo badalo main nafoz kar jate hain, or wo sooraj kii roshni se microwave censor se azaad hone kii bina par din or raat ke kaamon ke liye mozon hain.
eng: Microwave remote sensing techniques have the all-weather capability as the atmosphere is transparent to microwaves at lower frequencies, they penetrate clouds, and they are suitable for day and night operations owing to the independence of microwave sensors from the sun's illumination.

ben: vidyu centra o shilp (rasyanik saar) centraguli parichalna vyavahrut hawa shakti vibhag vruhattar gurutva dhaaran karche tarlikrut prakritik gas (elenji).

hin: bijligharon or audyogic (khaad) sanyantron main apane upyog ke kaaran tarlikrut prakritik gas (el.en.ji.) urja kshetra main bahut mahatvapurn hoti ja rahi he.
kan: vidyut sthavragalu mattu kaigarika (rasgobbar) sthavragal kaaryanirvahaneyalli dravikrut naisargik anilvu (el.en.ji.) badkeyaguvudarind indhan kshetradalli adu hchin pramukhyavannu garisuttide.
mal: vyavasay (rasavalam) shalaku vidyuchyakti nileyasu pravർttippikkaൻ upyogicppetunnatinaൽ dravikrut prakruti vatak (eൽ. eൻ. ji) uർjjamekhalayiൽ valia praadhanyam kaivaricchukontirikkaa.
ori: taraveekrit prakritik gas (el.en.ji.) shakti kshetrare adhik guruthpurna sthan grahan karuni karan eha vidyauth utpadan kendra tatha audogic (sar) utpadan kendragudiku parichakana karivare brebahrut hoithaye .
pan: urja pradhan karan wale khetra vich " likueficoad natural gas" ziada pramanta praapat kar riha hai ih power plant ate udayogic (khaad) plant nuun chalaun lai varte jaande han I

tel: vidyut centras mariyu parishramik (aruul) centeral nirvahanalo viniog karnanga dravikrut sahaj vayu (elen ji) vidyut ranganlo atyadhik pramukhyath vahistondi.
urd: miyaa kudrati gas (el en ji) tawanai ke shobe main bahut zyaada ahmiyat haasil kar rahi hai is liye ki ye tawanai plants or sanati (khaad) plants ko chalaane ke liye istemaal kii jaati hai.
eng: Liquefied Natural Gas (LNG) is assuming greater importance in the energy segment as it is used to operate Power Plants and Industrial (fertilizer) Plants.
