ben: 1978-era balyavivah nirodhak inti mayeder kshetre 18 evan celeder kshetre 21 bachrke vivaher baidh badus hisabe dharya karala samajik prathaguli aprapthyask vivahake ekhano usahit kare.
guj: baal lagn pratibandh kayado, 1978 lagnni kayadesarani unmar chokario mate 18 ane chhokarao mate 21 nakki kare che, parantu samazik rivaajo aaje pan vahela lagnne protsahan aape che.
hin: bal vivaah pratishedh adhinium,1978 ke anusaar vivaah karne ke liye kanoonee rup se ladakiyon kii umr 18 varsh or ladakon kii 21 varsh honi chahie, lekin saamaajik prathaen abhi bhi kam umr main vivaah karne ke liye protsaahit karti hai.
kan: 1978r balyavivah tade kaydeyu maduveyagalu kanoonubaddh vayassannu hennumkkalige 18 varsh mattu gandumkkalige 21 varshavendu nirbandh vidhisideyadaru samajik paddhatigalu igleu muncheye vivahaverpadisuvudannu protsahisuttve.
mal: 1978le shaishavavivah nirodhananiama vivahaprayam peൺkuttikൾk 18u aaൺkuttikൾk 21u aai nishchayiunnundeakil ipporau samuhikacharasൾ neratayull vivaham protsahippikunnund.
ori: 1978 masihar balya vivah nirodh adhinium, vivahar inagath badus jhiamanank pin 18 eban pamanank pin 21 boli dharyan karichhi, matra eve madhya samajik paramparagudik nirddharit samay poorvaru vivahaku protsahit karuni .
pan: bal vyah roktham act, 1978 de anusaar, ladakis de vyah di kaanooni umar 18 saal hai ate mundia di 21 saal per samajik rit hun ve cheti vyah karan lai uksaunde han I
tam: 1978aam antu kuiandait tiruman tatupbuch sattam sattapurv tiruman vaydai pennuku 18 enllum, anuku 21 enllum nirvitlldu, eninu samuk valakkadues inllum kuta balyap paruvat tirumanangal ukquikinsona.
tel: balya vivahal nirohak chatta, 1978 chattprakara ammayilaki vivah vayasu 18 ga mariyu abbailaki 21 ga nirdeshinchindi, kani ippatiki samajik aacharah shighrapu vivahanni protsahistunnai.
urd: paabandi izdwaj itfal kanoon 1978 shadi kii kanoonee umr ladakiyon ke liye 18 or ladakon ke liye 21 muqrer kurta hai, lekin samaji rasm va riwaaj ab bhi kam umari kii shadi kii hausalaa afzaai karte hain.
eng: The Child Marriage Restraint Act, 1978 stipulates the legal age of marriage as 18 for girls and 21 for boys, but social customs encourage early marriage even now.

ben: brahmasutara (christopoorv pratham sahasrabdev rachit vedant sutara hisabe parichit) etiqu shlok 1.1.4-e swikruti deya evan dabee kare ye, upanishdian shikshagulike shudhumatra aanshik, bachyer vittite naya varang vedic pathye nihit bhavanagulike upalvdhi, anuman, evan avashishta pramanadir sang sangatipoornabhave samgrik rupe burute have.
guj: brahmasutra (jene vedant sutara pan kahe che, te i.sa. purve paheli sadima rachaayu hatu)e shloke 1.1.4maa swikarelu che ane upanishadne amuk chuntela tukdaoma nahi, parantu sarvagrahi rite shikhva par bhaar muke che, ke jema vedic lakhano vyakt thayela vichaaro gyanna anaya madhyamo jevaan ke drushticon, dharna ane baaki rahelam pramaano sathe samanjasya dharave che.
hin: brahmasutra (jise vedant sutara bhi kaha jaataa he, pratham sahasrabdi i.pus. main rachit) ke pad 1.1.4 main ise sweekaar karte hue upanishdeey shikshaaon ko tukdon main nahin balki ek aise vyapak tareeke se samajhane kii aavashyaktaa par jor diya gaya he jahaan vaidic granthon main vichaaron ko dharna, anumaan or shesh pramaanon jaise gyaan ke anya roopon ke saath dekhnaa bhi shaamil he.
kan: brahmasootravu (sa.sha.pus. 1nae sahasramandalli rachitvad idannu vedant sutravendu kareyalaguttade) sutra 1.1.4ralli idannu angikarisuttade mattu aupanishadhik upadeshgainnu churuchuragi, aayd bhagagal aadharadallashte arthisuvudakkint ved granthagamallin chintanegathannu pratyakash, anuman, mattu ulid pramangalantah gyanad itar sadhangalondige samanvaygodaisuvantah samagravad ritiyalli arthisabekiruv agatyavannu ottiheluttade.
mal: brahm sutara ( bi.si.i. onnam nutandil rachicpat it veydantsutra ennu ariapatunnu ) 1.1.4- sutrattil it swikarikkayu, upanishad pathas oteickoteiku tiranketut peruiki yetuttumayallae, pratyakas, anuman, matu pramas enni gyanmaർggarhlot vedapathae samanvayippich, oteoce ekikrutmai manassilakook end aavashyate sthirikarikkayu cheiyunnu.
ori: 'brahmasutra' (vedhant sutara madhya kuhayaaye, yahaki christpoorb 1ma sahasrabdeere rachit hoithila) ehaku pad 1.1.4. re skruti pradaan karichhi eban upanishdiya shikshagudiku pruthakbhave, bachavachhi aadharare nuhen, baran eka ekikrit upayre bujhayibar aavashyakata upare drushokthi prakash karichhi, yeunthiki vaidik rachanabalir dharnagudik gyanar anyanya madhumaguik yatha indriyalavdh anubhuti, anuman, eban avashist pramangudik sahit samanyjas hoithanthi .
pan: brahmasutra sutara (jisanu vedantaa sutar ve kiha janda hai, pahili shatabdi isa poorav vich likhia gya see) vich ih gal 1.1.4 shalok vich kahi gai hai ate manni ve gai hai ki upanishda dis sikhiavaan nuun tukarias vich ate waclpanik aadhar 'te sikhsn di zaruurat nahi hai balki vedic granth anumaanit sikhiavaan ate sikhia de hor saadhns naal talmel vich sikhan di zaruurat hai|
tam: brahmasutra (kimu mudlam oiramantil thogukkappattatu manllum vedhant sutra enllum anoaicopadukintu) its 1.1.4aavatu vasanatil angigarikintu; melum, upanishtap bodhanil dunduduntak, suavirupukketap teru saitu purindukolvatait tavirtu ore orunginaint muriil purindukoll wants, atil ved vasanangans alnoku, uittunarthal manllum itar pramanangas bonthe mabbbb aritl valigalotu otisaivakqib payanbadutt wants enkintu.
tel: dinini brahmasutra (idi kripu modati sahasrabdilo rachinchabadin vedant sutaraga kuda peru kaliginadi) 1.1.4va padyaulo angikaristu upanishttul bodhanla okkokkatiga, erch kurch ardhanchesukovada kakunda, anduku bhinnanga vaidic vachanamulaloni bhaval itar gyan sadhanalin grahyath, avagahan, mariyu migilin pramanalatho ekikrut vidhananga telusukovalsin anavasaranni vakkanistundi.
urd: brahma sutara (jise vedanta sutara bhi kaha jataa hai, jo pahele hazaare kabel messiah main martab kiya gaya tha) ne aayat 1.1.4 main is ko kabuul kiya or openishdi talimat ko thodaa thodaa, man mani chunaav kii buniyaad par naheen balki ek masavi andaz main samajhane kii zarurat par jor diya jahaan afacar vedic mitvan main ilm ke digar jaria jese udra, stanbat, or baaqi pramanon ke saath hum aahing hain.
eng: The Brahmasutra (also called Vedanta Sutra, composed in the 1st millennium BCE) accepted this in verse 1.1.4 and asserts the need for the Upanishadic teachings to be understood not on a piecemeal, cherry-picked basis, but rather in a unified way wherein the ideas in the Vedic texts are harmonized with other means of knowledge such as perception, inference, and remaining pramanas.

eng: Ok, the most important document you need is a passport.

ben: krushi evan anyanya sambandhyukt caryakalaper janya madhyamkalin o dirghakalin runguli madhye krushi yantrer khariddari, khamar dwara grihith sech evan anyanya unnayanamulak kaaj antarbhukt thakave.
guj: kheti ane teni sathe jodayeli pravrittio mate madhyam ane lambi mudatani lon kheti machikarini kharidi, sinchai ane khetarma karvama aavati anaya vikas pravrittione aavari leshe.
hin: krishi evam usase sambandhit sanchalanon ke liye madhyam yaa dirghakaalik rin khet main sinchai or anya vikasaatmak kaaryon hetu krishi yantron kii kharid ke liye die jate hai.
kan: krishi mattu adkke sambandhisid kaarya chatuvatikegal melin madhyam mattu dirghavadhi salgalu krishi yantropakaranagal kharidi, niravari mattu krishibhumielli kaigond itar abhivruddhi kaaryagainnu olagondiruttve.
mal: krishik anubandhapravartanalkkumulla maddhyakal, dirnkal, vaypal kaaർshikayantrasൾ vangunnatinu jalsechanattinu krishibhumiil ateedukent viksanpravartanalku prayojanapatunnu.
ori: krushi eban anushangic karyankalapagudik pin madhum eban deergha-kalin run adhinare krushi yanthrapati kray, jatsechan tatha krushikshetrati upare sampadan karayauthiva anyanya bikashamutak karyankalap prabhruti antarbhukt heb.
pan: kheti-bari ate us de milade julde karia de lai madhium ate lambe same de karze, kheti-bari dia mashina jo sinjai ate hor vikas sambandhi dak da hai I
tam: vivchayam manllum adaich charnt panilukan naduttar & nind kalak gatankasil, vilainilatil menokolopatum nirpasana manllum itar valarchib panilukkak whilan iantrangana vanguvatum atankum.
tel: vyavasayam mariyu tatsambandhit karyakalapal koraku madhyam mariyu dirgh kaalik rinal vyavasay yantral konugol kharchulku, nitiparudal, itar abhivruddhi panulku saripotai.
urd: zarazzat or mataalika sargharmiyon ke liye darmiyaane or tavel muditi karzon main zardi mashinary kii kharidari, aabpashi or farm par kii jane wali digar taraqyati sargharmiyon kaa ahaata kiya jaaye gaa.
eng: Medium & long-term loans for agriculture and allied activities will cover the purchase of agricultural machinery, for irrigation and other developmental activities undertaken on the farm.

ben: chamakpradbhave, biswa swasthy sanstha (hu)-r mate, bartaman shudhumatra 43 koti manui ye shravansakti hraser akshamata nie benche ach ta-i naya, sangitik anusthan evan club athva tader yantrer uchch awager sansparsher karna 12 thek 35 bashwar baisi 100 kotiroo beshi manusher shravan kshamata comme yawar jhunki royas.
guj: aghatjanak babat che ke, vishv aarogya sansthana janavya anusaar, halma 4.30 abaj loko apurti shravan shakti sathe jivi rahya che atlu ja nahi, pan 12 thi 35 varshani vay vachchena 1 abajathi vadhu loko sangeetana jalsao ane melawadaoma temana sadhano dwara thatan mota avajone karne bahrashna jokhamma che.
hin: ascharyajanak he ki vishwa swasthya sanghathan (dablyoo.ech.o.) ke anusaar vartmaan main na keval 43 karod log niryogyakari shravan haani ke saath ji rahe hai balki 12 se 35 varshiya 100 karod se adhik logon ko tej sangeet ke kaaryakramon or klbon yaa apane yantron se tej sangeet sunne ke kaaran shravan haani hone kaa khatra he.
kan: aghatkari vishayavendare, vishv aarogya sansthey (dublu.ech.o.) prakaar, presettdalli 43 koti janaru asamarthagolisuv kiuduthanadondige badukuttiddare, matravallade, sangitad giggamalli mattu klabbugamalli athwa avaru balsuv sadhangamalli jorad shabdagalige oddicolluttiruvudarindagi 12rind 35r vayassin 100 kotigu hechu janaru kiudutanakke olagaguv apayadalliddare.
mal: lokarogya sanghaton (dublyu. ech . o) chettiuvidha parayunnatnusrich, 430 dashalaksha alukൾ keൾvishaktiillaymayute vaikalyattote jivikunnavranennumatramall, 12nu 35nu itsiൽ prayamull 100 kotiiladhik alukൾ sangit paripatikalutayu clbbkalilayu swanta upakarateutayu valia shabdangൾk vidheyamakunnatukara keൾvishakti nashtapetunn bhishaniil.
ori: ashcharyajanaka katha heudi, vish ssthya sangason (dablsou.ech.o) anuyani, varttaman ye 430 niqut lok shraban shakti hareisari banchukanthi, keval ethiki nuhen, baran 12ru 35 barsh badus madhyare 100 kotiru adhik lok sangeeth utsab o clubguthikare kimba nij upakaranare praia samaure uchch shabda shunuthiva hetu shraban shakti haribar aashanka rahichhi.
pan: hairaani vaali gal hai ki, vishva sihat sanglen de anusaar vartaman vich naa siraf 43 karod lok suinn di ayogata naal jeee rehe ne balki 12 ton 35 saalas vich 1 arabia ton uddh locals nuun tej sangeet de programs ate kaambs jaaa aapne sands ton tej sangeet suinn kaaran suinn shakti guaun da khatra hai|
tam: 430 million makas tarbodhu mudemakum sevipulan iopputon vayendhu varukirars enpatu matumallamal 12 muthal 35 vayatull 1 billion per isai nicktikhalilum chank vidudiksilum alltu tangas olych chadanas mulmak sabdman ochiluku welipatutal sevipulanai ishakkum aapattil ulsanar enjh ulagach chugadhar amaipin gutaru adhirchiutuatak irukkintu.
tel: abburpariche vidhnga, prapanch arogya sansth (dabluhech o) prakara, 430 milian mandi present vinikidi lopanto jivistu undadame kak, 1 billian kante akkuv mandi 12 nudi 35 ell vayasu galwariki sangit karyakramalas mariyu clubbullo leda tam parikaral nudi valeuvade biggaran shabdal karnanga vinikidishkti lopinche pramada undi.
urd: hairat kii baat ye hai ki alami udara sahat (dablyoo each oo) ke mutabik, na sirf 430 milin afarad hain jo fi alhal samat ke mazor kin nuqasaan ke saath zindagi guzaar rahe hain, balki 12 se 35 saal ke darmiyaan 1 arab se zyaada afarad ko mousiki ke programon or kalabon yaa in ke alaat se paida hone wali tej aawaaz kii numaayish kii vajah se samat ke nuqasaan kaa khatare hai.
eng: Shockingly, according to the World Health Organization (WHO), not only are 430 million people currently living with disabling hearing loss, but more than 1 billion people aged between 12 and 35 years are at risk of hearing loss due to exposure to loud sounds at music gigs and clubs or on their devices.

ben: kichu bhajan shatabdi-prachin, samast anchal jure janapriya o samajik aitihya hisabe sancharit, abar anyanyaguli natun kare rachit.
guj: ketlank bhajan saicao joonan che, je tamam pradeshoma lokpriya che, ane samudayik prathao tarike utari aave che, jayaare anaya navan rachaayelam che.
hin: kuch bhajan shatabdiyon puraane the, jo sabhi kshetron main lokapriy the or samudaayon kii paramparaon ke rup main viraasat main saunpe gaye jabaki kuch kii rachana haal hi main kii gai thi.
kan: kelvu bhajanegalu shatmanagaishtu haleyawagiddu, ell pradeshgalllu prasiddhvagive mattu samudayad sampradayavagi haridu bandiveyadare, ulidavannu hosadagi sanyojislagide.
mal: chil bhajanngൾ nutandukൾ pankkamullathu vyatyast pradeshsliൽ pracharattilultu samuhikacharaslai kaimaom cheyyapetivayumanengiൽ pututai rachicppetta matulsav.
ori: keteke bhajan bahu shatabdeeru rahiasichhi, samagra anychal bhittire segoik lokadrut eban goshthir parampara bhave hastantharita hoiasichhi, matra aau ketek nua bhave rachit hoichhi.
pan: kujh bhajan sadia purana han, kai khetraan vich prasidh han, samajik parampraavaan vajon age bitaa dite jaande han, ate horaan di navin rachna kiti gai hai I
tam: chil bhajanile noorthandugalak nidippara, pal prantakalil prabalmanavai manllum samuk mripughalak valivantavai, veruchil bhajanile puditak iyasoppatubhavai.
tel: konni bhajanalu shatabdal nativi, anni prantallo prasiddhikekkinavi, mariyu sang paramparagatanga andipucchukunnvi kaaga, migilinvi kottaga rachinchabadinavi.
urd: kuch bhajan sadiyon purane hain, jo ilakaai buniyaad par mashhuur hain, or maashruti ravayat ke tuur par aage badhaye jate hain, jabaki dusare naye naye banaaye gaye hain.
eng: Some bhajans are centuries old, popular on a pan-regional basis, and passed down as community traditions, while others are newly composed.

ben: "green iconmi" namta blueprint fer aa green iconmi shironame, pratham 1989-era ekati pratibedne yuktrajya sarkarer janya ekadal mukhya pariwesh arthanitibider dwara srushti hayesil.
guj: "green economi" shabdano saupratham prayog 1989maa united kingdom sarkaar matena ahevalma bluprint four e green economi sheershakthi agrani paryavarniya arthshastriona mandal dwara karvama aavyo hato.
hin: vaakyansh "harith arthvyavastha" kaa prayog pehali baar united kingdom kii sarkaar ke liye 1989 main taiyaar kii gai blueprint for e green iconomi sheershak vaali report main agrani paryaavaran arthshaastriyon dwaara kiya gaya tha.
kan: "hasiru aarthikate" emb padavannu 1989ralli parisarik arthshastrajnar tandavondu united kingdammin sarkaarkke sallisid ʼhasiru aarthikateya nilanaksheʼ emb shirshikeya varadialli modalbarige baislayitu.
mal: oru sangha munnir paristaitek sampattikashastrajper tayyarakia 'haritsampadvyavastikkayural ruparekh' enne peritaitu british sarkkarinuvendiumulla 1989le oru reportl "haritsampadvyavasthi" end walk adyamai upyogicht.
ori: "sabuj arthaneethi" padatir prachalan prathamakari agrani pariveshika arthaneethijamanankar eka gosthi dra united kingdam sarkarnk nimanthe uddist 1989 masihar eka reportre karayaithila, yaahaar shirshak thila "bluprint fer e green ikonami" .
pan: " green iknomi" shabad da prayog pahili war 1989 vich ughe watawarnak arthshastria ne bartania di sarkaar de lai ik reaport " bluprint four e green iknomi " vich vartia see I
tam: "pasumab poruladaram" enjh sol mudanmudalil woru munnenich sudduchural poruladhar nipunarkalin kunual 'pasumab poruladharatukan varaiuddhittam' enjh talibble ikiya rajjiya arasukkak 1989il thogukkappatt ore arickyil uruvacopattatu.
tel: harith aarthik vyavasthi ane pada, pramukh paryavaran aarthikavettal brunda che 1989lo united kingdam prabhutvan kos, harith aarthik vyavasthaku namoonapaten ani piluvabada nivediklo modat avishkarinchabadindi.
urd: "green icanomi" kii istalah sab se pahele 1989 main bartanya kii hukuumat ke liye ek report main marof maahulyati mahrain iqtsadayat ke ek group ne taiyaar kii thi, jis kaa unwan green icanomi kaa bleue print tha.
eng: The term "Green Economy" was first coined in a 1989 report for the Government of the United Kingdom by a group of leading environmental economists, titled Blueprint for a Green Economy.

ben: korbader sawai maara yaan; shudhumatra pandab bhaiera evan krishna benche chhillen.
guj: badhan ja kauravas mrityu pamya; matra paanch pandav bhaaio ane krishna jivitha rahya.
hin: sabhi kaurav mar jate hai; keval paanch pandav bhai or krishna jivit bachate hai.
kan: kauravarellaru madiyuttare; ivaru pandavas sahodararu mattu krishnanu matra badukuliyuttare.
mal: karavarellam mariunnu ; anchu pandavasahodaranmaru krishnu matra atijivikunnu.
ori: samast kaurab mrittu baran karanthi; keval panychu pandab bhrata eban krishna jeevita rahanthi .
pan: saare kaurava di mirtu hoo jandi hai ate siraf panch pandav bhai ate krishna bachde han I
tam: kauravars anivarum madindu pogirars, panch pandavasum shrikrishnarum mattume uirtabbukinsener.
tel: kauravalandaru maranistar; aiduguru pandav sodrulu, krishn matrame sajivanga migulutharu.
urd: saare kauru mar jate hain; sirf panch pandav bhai or krishna zindaa batch jate hain.
eng: All the Kauravas die; only the five Pandava brothers and Krishna survive.

ben: cremar et al-era shikshakder upar kara ekati gaveshana pawa gamee ye, sameekshar samay 25 shatansh besarkari khater shikshak evan 40 shatansh sarcari khater chickisakarmi anupsthith chhillen.
guj: cremar at al dwara thayela shikshakona abhyasma janavyu hatu ke khaangi kshetra 25 % shikshako ane 40 % jaher kshetra tabibi kaaryakaro sarvekshan daramiyaan gerhajar hatan.
hin: krimar evam anya logon dwaara shikshakon par kiye gaye adhyayan main paaya gaya ki nijee kshetra ke 25% shikshak or saarvajanik kshetra ke 40% chikitsa karmchaaree surveykshan ke dauraan anupasthit the.
kan: shikshakar bagge cremer hagu itarru kaigond adhyayanavondaralli khasagi-valayad 25%dashtu shikshakaru mattu sarkaari-valayad 40%dashtu vaidyakiya sibbandi samiksheya samayadalli hajarilladiruvudu kandubantu.
mal: kremർ tutangiyavർ adhyapakarecurich natattia oru paddna, swakarya mekhalile 25% adhyapakaru potumekhalaile 40% medicaൽ jeevanakkaru sർwe samayt hajarundairunnille conteti.
ori: cremar eban antmanank dra shikshakamanank upare karayaithiva eka anudhyanru janapadithila ye besalkari-kshetrar 25% shikshak eban sarvajanic kshetrar 40% daktori karmachari ukt sarvekshan samaure anupasthit rahithile .
pan: karimar ate horaan ne adhiapks upper kite adhian de sarve dauraan private khetra de 25% ate sarkari khetra de 40% sihat kaame gair-hazar paae hai |
tam: karuttaywinbodhu 25% taniar turai asiriarkanum 40% bfatut turai maruduvap paniyalargallum varuki taravilly ena asiriarkas basari gremer manllum anayore nattya aaywil khandawiapattatu.
tel: upadhyayul pai kremer mariyu itarul adhyayantion praivate rang upadhyayulas 25%, mariyu prabhutva rang vedya karmicullo 40% mandi aa tanikhi samayaulo hajaru kaledani kanugonnar.
urd: crimar or digar ke asatou ke baare main ek matala se patta chalaa hai ki survey ke dauraan nijee shobe ke 25 faisad asatou or sarkari shobe ke 40 faisad tabi carkan gair haazir the.
eng: A study on teachers by Kremer et al. found that 25% of private-sector teachers and 40% of public-sector medical workers were absent during the survey.

ben: 1750-era dashake pratishthit hembaldon club khelati vibartane ek gurutvapurna bhumika paalan kare.
guj: hembladen club, jeni sthapana 1750na dayakama karvama aavi hati, ramatani utkrantima nondhapatra bhumika bhajvi hati.
hin: hambledon club kii sthapana 1750 ke dashak main hui thi jisane khel ke kramik vikaas main mahatvapurn bhoomika nibhaai thi.
kan: 1750r dashakadalli sthapanayad hambalden club, i aatd belvanigeyalli mahattvapurna patravannu vahisitu.
mal: 1750kalil sthapitmay hamblon club i kaliute prenamattil ganyamay pankuvahichu.
ori: 1750 dashakare sthapit hoithiva 'hambaldan club' ehi kreedatir kramavikashare eka guruthpurna bhoomika grahan karithila .
pan: hembalden club, jise di sthapna 1750 vich hoi see, ne kheds de vikas vich ahim bhumika nibhaai|
tam: 1750kalil niruvappatt hamplton club, ind vilyatin valarchiil perumbangu vakittatu.
tel: 1750lalo sthapinchabadin hambulden club i aat prenama chendalo ock mukhya patra poshinchindi.
urd: hamblden club ne, jis kii buniyaad 1750 kii duhai main rakhi gai thi, khel ke irtaka main ahim kirdaar adaa kiya.
eng: The Hambledon Club, which was founded in the 1750s, played a significant role in the evolution of the game.

ben: vaike alrady bale diesi aar o tomar ticketgulo bukow kare dies.
guj: men kyarani mara bhaaine jaan kari didhi che ane ene tamari ticketo lai lidhi che.
hin: maine apane bhai se kah diya he or usne pehle se hi tumhaari tikat book kar di hai.
kan: naanagle nammannange heliddu aaytu, avnu nin ticketganan book madiddu aaytu.
mal: khan bradarinote parannu kachinju, pulli nicksute ticket book cheitukarinju.
ori: mun mo bhainku kahi saringi, aau se thummanank ticket buk karidheleni |
pan: mai pahilaan hi aapne bhai nuun kos ditha hai ate usne tuhadia tickets book ve karavaa ditia han|

tel: ma annaki cheppesan, atanu me tickett book chesseshad kuda.
urd: main ne apne bhai ko bataa diya hai or is ne tumhari tikaten book kar di hain.
eng: I have already informed my brother and he has booked your tickets already.

ben: mantraguli tittirian upanishad, shikshavali 1 11.2 thek newa, yekhane bala has: matradev bhava, mitradev bhas, pitrudev bhava, putradev bhava, acharyae bhava, atithidev bhava.
guj: aa mantro taittiria upanishadni shikshavali 1.11.2na che; je kahe che: matradevo bhav, pitrudevo bhav, acharyadevo bhav, atithidevo bhav.
hin: ye mantra taittiriya upanishad, shikshavalli I.11.2 se liye gaye hai jinamein kaha gaya he: matrudevo bhav, mitradev bhav, pitrudevo bhav, putradev bhav, acharyadevo bhav, atithidevo bhav.
kan: i mantragarhnnu taittiriya upanishattin shikshavalli 1.11.2rind aidukolelagiddu, idu matrudevo bhav, pitrudevo bhav, aacharyadevo bhav, atithidevo bhav endu heluttade.
mal: tittiriya upanishttile shikshavalliile I.11.2 mantra parayunnu: matrudevobhav, mitradevobhav, pitrudevobhav, aacharyadevobhav, atithidevobhav.
ori: manthragudik tittiriya upanishad, shikshavalli-1ma.11.2 ru aasichhi, yeunthire kuhayaishi: 'matradebo bhava', 'pitaahdebo bhava', 'aacharyandevo bhava', 'atithidevo bhava' .
pan: mantra titria upanishd sikhavali I.11.2, de han, jo kahinde han: matrudevo bhav, mitradevo bhav, pitrudevo bhav, putradevo bhav, acharyadevo bhav, atithedevo bhav |
tam: ind mandras dathriya upanihattin sikshavalli I.11.2 bagudiil ullvai, are matrudevo bhava, mitradevo bhava, pidrudevo bhava, putradevo bhava, aachariyadevo bhava, adittidevo bhava enak goorukintu.
tel: i mantras taittiriopanishattu,okatav shikshavalli 11.2 lonivi,idi: matradevo bhav, mitradevo bhav, pitrudevo bhav, putradevo bhav, acharyadevo bhav, atithidevo bhav ani chebutondi.
urd: ye mantra thitareey upanshad, shikshavali aai I.11.2 ke hain, jin main kaha gaya hai: matrodevo bhava, mitradevo bhava, patradevo bhava, patradevo bhava, aacharyadevo bhava, atithidevo bhava.
eng: The mantras are from the Taittiriya Upanishad, Shikshavalli I.11.2, which says: matrudevo bhava, pitrudevo bhava, acharyadevo bhava, atithidevo bhava.

ben: 1932 thek 2011-era madhye hazar tirishti gujarati chhabi banano hayesil kintu khub kam archive kara hayes.
guj: 1932 ane 2011ni vachche lagbhag ek hajaar ane tris gujarati filmo banii che pan khub ochhi sangruhith thai che.
hin: 1932 or 2011 ke bich lagbhag ek hazaar tees gujarati filmein banaai gai thim, lekin bahut kam hi ko sangrah main rakhaa gaya.
kan: 1932 mattu 2011r naduve sumaru savirad moowattu gujarati chalanchitragalannu nirmislayitadaru kalavannu matrave dakhlikarislagide.
mal: 1932 nu 2011 nu idil etand aayirati muppat gujarati chitras nirmmicppettengil valare kuncche arkai cheyyapettullu.
ori: 1932ru 2011 masiha madhyare pakhapakhi eka hajaar thirishati gujarati chakchchitra nirman karayaishi, kintu sethi madhyaru khuv kam abhilekhagarare sanrakshit hoichhi.
pan: 1932 ate 2011 de wichkaar lagabhaga ik hajaar ate tih gujarati films bania gaia san, per bohut ait sankuchit kitia gaia han|
tam: 1932 muthal 2011 varai sumar aairattu mubbadu gujarati tirappatas dayaaricapattanu, eninu avarkhil vegu chilte kappeqtil chemiccapattuluna.
tel: 1932, 2011 madhyalo ock vayyinnu muppai gujarati cinemal tayarayai, kani ati koddi sankhya matrame arjaiv cheyabaddai.
urd: 1932 or 2011 ke darmiyaan takreeban ek hazaar tees gujarati filmein bani thim, lekin bahut kam arqio hui hain.
eng: About a thousand and thirty Gujarati films were made between 1932 and 2011, but very few are archived.

ben: bhartiya arth bazark besarkari, sarkari evan bideshi malikanadhin banigyik bank o samba bank, ekatrabhave "tafasilvukt bank" name parichit sangarhit shakha evan vyaktigat baa pariwarer malikanadhin swadeshi banker athva mahajan evan nan-banking arth sanstha sambolit asangarhit shakha shrenivaddha kara has.
guj: bharatna nana bazarnu vargikaran khaangi, jaher ane videshi malkini vyavsayik bank ane sahakari bank, bhegi maline olkhati ‘shidyul bank’na sangthit kshetra ane binasangthit kshetra vyaktigat ke parivarani malkina deshi bankar athva nana dhirnar ane non-banking nanakiya companiono samavesh thai che.
hin: bhartiya mudra bazaar vyavasthit kshetra or avyavasthit kshetron main vargeekrut hai, jisamen vyavasthit kshetra main shaamil hai nijee, saarvajanik or videshi swaamitv vaale vanijyik evam sahakaari bank jinako ek saath milakar anusuchit bank bhi kaha jaataa he, or avyavasthit kshetra main ekal vyakti yaa paariwarik swaamitv vaale swadeshi banker yaa sahuukaar evam gaiyr-banking vittiya companiyaan shaamil hai.
kan: bhartiya hanad marukatteyannu, ottagee "anusuchit bankugalu" endu kareyalaguv khasagi, sarvajanik hagu videshi-odethanad vanijy bankugalu hagu sahkari bankugainnu olagondiruv sanghatit valay, mattu vaiyaktik athwa kautumbik-odethanad sthaliya bankarugalu athwa saldataru hagu bankingetar hanakasu sansthegamannu olagondiruv asanghatit valayavendu vargikarislagide.
mal: indiaille dhanvipanie swakarya, potumekhala, videsh, komersyal bankuu, sahakaran bankuu ulppet shedyuld banku ennariapadunn sanghatit mekhalyayu, vyaktikalo kutubamo natattunn pradeshikamay bankarmaru pana kat kodukkunnavru bankingitar dhanakarya companyu ulppet asanghatitmekhalayayu tar tirichiriunnu.
ori: bharatiya arth bajaraku epari vibhakta karayaishi - sangathit kshetra, yaha gharoi, sarvajanin, videshi-malikanare thiva banijik bank eban samavan bankasabuku nei gathit, yahaki ekatara "anusuchit bank" bhavare janashuna, eban asangathit kshetra, yeunthire brekthigat ba parivarika malikanare thiva sdeshi bank malik ba sahukar eban an-banking bithtiya companysabu antarbhukt.
pan: bharati mudra bazar nuun sangthit khetra vich shrenicadh kita gya hai, jise vich niji, jantak, ate videshi malki wale vpark baink ate ko-operative baink shaamil han, jinhan nuun ieathe "anusuchit banks" vajon jaanya janda hai, ate asangthit sector, jise vich viaktigat jaaa parivark malki wale savdeshi banker jaaa mahaajan ate gair-banking viti companie shaamil han|
tam: india panch sandai erantak vakipaduttapadukintu: ondu muraisarnt brivu, itel taniar, bfatut turai manllum ayalak-urims vanik vankigaasm gootujhu vankigaasm atankum, ews otumottamak "shetuld vangigus" endu anoaicopadukindena; maharondu muraisara brivu, itel taninabar alltu kudumbh urimayalar kont ulnaddu vangisar alltu vatticaton niruvananglum bangi chara nidhi niruvananglum udpatum.
tel: bhartiya dravya market praivate, public, mariyu videshi yajmanya vanijya bankulu, sahakar bankulatho kalypi "sheiduld bankulu" ani pilvabade sanghatit ranganga, mariyu vyaktigat leda kutumb-yajmanya deshiya byankar leda appulichevar mariyu bankingetar aarthik sansthalto kudin asanghatit ranganga vargikarinchabadindi.
urd: hindustani mani market ko manzim shobe main taqasim kiya gaya hai, jis main nijee, sarkari or gair milki milkiyat waale tizaarati bank or coffprato bank shamil hain, jinhen mil kar "shadooll bank" or gair manzim shobaa kaha jataa hai, jis main infradi yaa khandaani milkiyat waale desi banker yaa sahukaar or gair bankaree malyati companiyan shamil hain.
eng: The Indian money market is classified into the organised sector, comprising private, public, and foreign-owned commercial banks and cooperative banks, together known as "scheduled banks," and the unorganised sector, which includes individual or family-owned indigenous bankers or money lenders and non-banking financial companies.

eng: In these hands, the cinema lost much of its visual character and was turned into a literary and wordy product.

ben: amal palekar o gerina wahav abhinit gharounda (1977), evan sharmila thakur o uttam kumar abhinit durian (1979)-era mato samalochakder dwara bahul prashansit chalachchitraguli parichalnar janya trini sarvadhik parichit.
guj: teo vivecko dwara vakhnayeli filmo amol palekar ane jharina wahaab abhinit gharonda (1977), ane sharmila tagore ane uttam kumar abhinit durian (1979)na nirdeshan mate sauthi vadhu janita che.
hin: unhen amol palekar or zarina wahaab abhinit gharonda (1977) tathaa sharmila tagaur evam uttam kumaar abhinit dooriyaan (1979) jaisi samikshakon dwaara saraahi gai filmon ke nirdesan ke liye sabase zyada janaa jaataa he.
kan: aat vimarshatmakavagi mechchuge paded chalanchitragalad amol palekar hagu zarina wahaab natneya gharonda (1977), mattu sharmila tagor hagu uttam kumar natneya dooriyam (1979) ivugal nirdeshnakkagi hesaruvasiagiddare.
mal: amol palakkaru sarin vahabu abhinaich gharaunda (1977), sharmila tagore utta kuma abhinaich duriyon (1979) enni nirupakprashans nedia chitras samvidhana cheitatina addeha prashastnayat.
ori: se sameekshakamanank dra prashansit hoithiva chakchchitra yatha, amol palekar o jarina hav abhinit gharaonda (1977), eban sharmila tagore o uttam kumaar abhinit durian (1979) r nirddeshana pin adhik parichit thile.
pan: uh apni aalochnatamak for 'te prashansayog films gharonda (1977), abhinit amol palekar ate zarina wahib ate duria (1979), abhinit sharmila tagore ate uttam kumar, lai sabh ton uddh jaanya janda hai|
tam: amol palekar manllum zareenah wahab munanik kadabatratil naditt karaunda (1977), sharmila tagore manllum uttom kumar munanik kadabatratil naditt dooriyan (1979) aakhiya vimarsagar baraddulap penichu tirappaangans iyakiavar ena avar micub prabhlamadaindwar.
tel: amol palekar mariyu jarina vahab natinchin, gharonda(1977) mariyu shrmil tagur mariyu uttam kumar natinchin durian(1979) vanti vimarshkul prashansalandukonnchitral darshakatvaniki aayan kirti gadincharu.
urd: wo tanqidi tuur par saraahi jane wali filmon gharonda (1977), jis main amol palekar or zarina wahab hain, or dooriyan (1979) jis main sharmila tagore or uttam kumar hain, ko diract karne ke liye mashhuur hain.
eng: He is best known for directing the critically acclaimed films Gharaonda (1977), starring Amol Palekar and Zarina Wahab, and Dooriyaan (1979), starring Sharmila Tagore and Uttam Kumar.

ben: 14 februarite, uen mahasachib antonio guterrace myanmarer paristhite sampark gaveer udveg prakash kare "kramavardhaman balprayog evan pradhan shahargulite atirikt sanjoa yaan motaiener khabar"-tike praadhanya die ekati vivruti prakash karen.
guj: 14 february sanyukt rashtrasanghana secretary-janaral antonio guterse myanmarani paristhati ange gheri chinta vyakt karta nivedanma ‘dalona vadhi rahela upayog ane vadharana sashastra vahnone mota shaheroma tahenath karvaana aheval’ par prakash padyo hato.
hin: 14 farvari ko you.en. mahasachiv antonio gaterres ne myanmar kii sthiti par gahari chintaa zaahir karte hue "bal ke badhate prayog or mahatvapurn shaharon main atirikt sainya shastron se las vaahanon kii tainaati" par jor dete hue vaktavy jari kiya .
kan: febravari 14randu, you.en. pradhan kaaryadarshi antonio guterras mayanmarnallin paristaiya bagge fiver kalavalavannu vyaktpadisutta helikeyannu nidi, "hechuttiruv seney badke mattu varadiagiruvante pramukh pattanagamalli hechuvari shastrasajjit vahangal neojane"yannu etti hehidaru.
mal: february 14n myaൻmarille statigatikaliൽ agadhamay ashank prakatipicchukondu "waർddhitchuvarunn balaprayogvu repoർtt cheyyappettvidha pradhanangarslilekulla kututൽ kavachitvahanaute vinyasavu" uyർtticatticondu yueൻ secretary janeraൽ aൻroneo guteras oru prasthavan iokki.
ori: 14 februariire, jatisanghar secretari-general, antonio guteras "adhikaru adhik balar bbbahar eban pramukh sahargudikare athirikta sashastra yaan mutaunar report" upare guruthrope kari, mianmarar paristate samparkare gabhir chinta prakash karuthiva eka vibruthi jari karithile .
pan: sanyukat rashtra de sastar-general antonio guterace ne 14 farvari nuun ik bayan jari karia jise vich onha ne myanmar di state baare chinta jataunde hoe,"jor-jabar di uddh rahi varton ate bade shahirn vich wadhu bakhtarband vahnas di tainati" utte jor ditha I
tam: fibruary 14 andu aina botuch seyalazar antonio kuttares mianmar suanilai kuritu auint kavalai therivittu ore arikky velitar, atil "balaprayogm adhikarippatu barjee mukiya nakranglil koodudal kavach vaganas itubaduttapatum saydigus barjee" kurippak valiyuuttirindar.
tel: fibravari 14na, aikyarajyasmiti sekratory general antonio guteres mayanmar lo paristate pat fiver andolan vyaktparustu ock prakathan jari chestu, "perugutunn balaprayog mariyu pradhan nagaralas adanpu saayudh vahanal moharimp gurinchin vadantul"gurinchi nokkicheppar.
urd: 14 farvari ko, ikvam matahda ke scretary general antvanio gotres ne myanmar kii soorat hal par gahari phikar mandi kaa izhaar karte hue ek bayaan jari kiya jis main unhon ne "taakat ke badhate hue istemaal or bade shaharon main azafee bikatar band gaadiyo kii mabina saf arai" ko ujagar kiya.
eng: On 14 February, UN Secretary-General Antonio Guterres issued a statement expressing deep concern about the situation in Myanmar, highlighting "the increasing use of force and the reported deployment of additional armoured vehicles to major cities."

ben: udaharanswarup, ekati balber satrkatake agrahya kara evan taar avagnar falswarup shasti pawa "vrudh locti"r kahini vyakt kare "dya trickster and dya taking bulb".
guj: daakhla tarike, ‘dha tricuster and dha toking bulb’ "ek vruddha purush"ni vata kahe che jene ek balbani chetavnini avaganna kari hati, ane tene lidhe, teni avagna mate te shiksha paame che.
hin: udhaaharan ke liye, "chalbaaz or bolne vaala balb" us "buudhe aadmi" kii kahani he jo balb kii chetavaniyon ko nazarandaaz karata he or parinamtah, avagya ke liye use dandit kiya jaataa he.
kan: udaharanege, "da tricster and da talking balb", "obb vruddhanu" geddeyondu niduv echcharikeyannu kadeganisi, aa moolak tann asaddegagi takk shastigidaguv katheyannu heluttade.
mal: udaharanttin, oru balbinte munnariipu avaganikukayu aa dhaർshtyatin shikshicppetukayu cheit "aa vriddhante" kath parayunntan "tattipukaranu sansariunn balbu".
ori: udaharan srup, "da' trikshtar and da' taking bulb" sehi "bruddha bsakthi"ngkar kaahaani kahe, yieki eka balbar chetavaneeku upeksha karanthi eban, prativadhasaare, nizer abadhitha pin dandit hanthi .
pan: udahaaran de lai, "da tricster and da taking balab" "da old main" di kahaani dasadi hai, jo ik balab dis chetawania nuun nazshandaaz karada hai ate site vajon, aapne juram di sazaa pounda hai|
tam: edutoukattak, "vittaikaranum pechum kumil vivkum" enjh katail "woru kieaver" kumil vihakin echarikylap putkkanitu adan vilaivak tanticcapadukirar.
tel: udaharanku, "d tricstor and d talking balb" ock balbu ichche hechcharikal alakshyapatete, atani dhikkaraniki pratiga shikshimpbade "musali manishi" kadh cheptundi.
urd: misaal ke tuur par, "chal baaz or bolane waala balb"buudhe aadmi" kii kahani bayaan krati hai, jo ek balb kii tanbihath ko nazar andaz kar detaa hai or is ke badle main, apni surakshi ke liye sazaa paataa hai.
eng: For example, "The Trickster and the Talking Bulb" tells the story of "The Old Man", who disregards the warnings of a bulb and, in turn, gets punished for his defiance.

ben: udaharanswarup, siman blackbern evan jegawan kim dwara pradutt sangyatii halo jan palkinhorn-era paribhasha 'dharnamulak' athva 'gyantattvik' khandtabad: sei dharner khandtabad yeti ek dharner adhivachaner sang yukt tathy athva astitvagulike anaya dharan thek grihith anyanya tathy athva astitva die pratisthapit karaar caryakramer sang samparkit haowar fale tader madhye ekati sampark sthapan kare.
guj: daakhla tarike, jene john polkinghorn ‘kalpanatmak’ athva ‘gyanagatata’no ghatadavad kahe che, tene mate simon blackbern ane jigavon keem dwara aavi vyakhya apay che: ghatadavadnu swaroop ek prakarana pravachanma sankalayelam tathyo athva vyaktitvone badle aayojanabaddh rite anaya tathyo athva vyaktitvone raju karine e dwara teo vachchena sambandho janavavaa babatne kahe che.
hin: udhaahranswaroop, jon polkinghorn ne jise 'dharnatmak' yaa 'gyanamimasiy' newnikaran ke rup main sanderbhit kiya use simon blakebern or jagavon kim ne paribhaashit kiya: newnikarnavaad kaa vah rup jisamen ek prakaar ke vaartalap main shaamil tathyon yaa sansthaaon ko anya tathyon yaa sansthaaon se badalane kaa kaarykram, un donon ke bich main ek sambandh banaate hue, shaamil hota he.
kan: udaharanege, yavudannu jaan polkingorn ʼkalpanatmakʼ athwa ʼgyanamimasatmakʼ saralikarnavad emb padgalind suchisuttarayo, adu simon blackbarne mattu jegwan kim nidiruv vyakhyanwagide: ondu vidhd adhyayanakke sambandhapatt vastavanshgalu illave mukhyagunagathannu mattondu bageya adhyayanad bere vastavanshgalu athwa mukhyagunagalondige badlaisi, aa moolak avugal naduve sambandha kalpisuv karyavannu olagondiruv saralikarnavadad rupavagide.
mal: udaharanttin, saimൺ blackbenu eygvൺ kimmu naൽkia niർvachana joൺ poൾkkinghoൺ 'aashayaparmay' allengiൽ 'gyanashastraparmay' rickkshanism enne visheshipikunnat: oru tarattilull vyavahartiൽ uൾppettirikunn wastutakൾku unmakൾku matoru tarattilull vyavahartiൽninnull mat wastetkalu unmakalu pakar wech angne avaikkiteiൽ oru bandha srushtiunn oru programumai bandhappedunn aa rickkshanisattiൻre rupam.
ori: udaharan srup, jan polakinharna yahaku 'vaicharika' ba 'gyantattak' abawakhabad boli kuhanthi, taha heudi siman blakvarn eban jaigan kimnk dra pradaan karayaithiva sangya: sehi prakaar abawakhabad yaahaar karyankramare gotie prakaar bimarsh seh jadit tatha ba sattasawku annga eka prakaararu and, taha jagaare rakhi, semanank madhyare eka antavsampark sthapan karayaithaye.
pan: udaharan de for 'te, jon polkinghoran nuun 'sankalpic' ate 'gyan-vigyanak' katotivad ki hai di paribhasha siman balakebaran ate jagvon kim duara pradaan keeti gai : katotivad da uh roop, jise vich shaamil prasangic ikai di kism naal hor sabandhit ikia jaaa ikia nuun kise hor kism vich badalan, jise naal uhanaas vichale koi sabandh sthapit hove, de program naal sabandhat hai|
tam: edutoukattak, 'karuddhial' alltu 'ahitalial' surukgalvadaj enjh cholladelil jaan polkinhan munvaippatu, simon plackban manllum jackwan kim valangy ade varaiyasaiyait than kufipidukintu, adavatu woru vaka uraiyatel sambandappatt takhavals alltu borudbheyaroukqup patilak innuru vaka uraiyatel charnt takhavals alltu borudbheyarkayap payanbadutti avacharukkitie dodarpukanum woru ditam charnt surukgalvad vativats atu kurikkintu.
tel: udaharanku, john polkinghorn 'bhavadharith' lek 'gyanadharith' taggimpuvadanga perkonnadi, semone blackbern mariyu jeguon kim ichchin nirvchana: ock vidhmain charchku chendin vastaval lek nijal, marok vidhnto marpidi chessi, tadwara aa rendity madhyalo sambandhanni erpat cheyata taggimpuvada yokk ock rupa.
urd: misaal ke tuur par, jise jaan polking horn 'tasuraati' yaa 'almyati' takhfif pasandi kaa naam dete hain, wo simon blike bern or jegon kam ke zarie faraham kii gai taareef hai: takhfif pasandi kii wo soorat jo ek kasam ke bayaan main shamil haqayak yaa maujodaat ko duusari tarah ke haqayak yaa maujodaat se badalane ke program se taalluk rakhti hai, nitejetan in ke darmiyaan ek taalluk kaayam hota hai.
eng: For example, what John Polkinghorne terms 'conceptual' or 'epistemological' reductionism is the definition provided by Simon Blackburn and by Jaegwon Kim: that form of reductionism which concerns a program of replacing the facts or entities involved in one type of discourse with other facts or entities from another type, thereby providing a relationship between them.

ben: 1980-r dashake, spanish sanstha asperanja i sia astra-virodhi 21ti samrik upasambhar sambolit ekati 120-mimi kaman bomb nirman kare.
guj: 1980na dayakama spaini company esparanza vaaya siaye 120-mimi mortar bomb viksaavyo hato, je 21 bakhtar-virodhi sabamunishan dharavato hato.
hin: 1980 ke dashak main spani form esparanza vaai siya ne 120 mi.me. kaa mortar bam viksit kiya jisamen 21 choti astr-virdohi yudhsamagriyan thim.

ori: 1980 dashakare, speniya bavasaik pratishthan 'espera'nyja jji sia' eka 120-mi.mi. golabarud boma present karithila yahaki 21ti astra-pratirodhi upastra dharan karithila .
pan: 1980 de dashak vich, spani waparik sanstha aspernaza ya sia ne 120 millimetre da kharal bamb di usaari kiti jise vich 21 anti-armur sabmuniticans san I
tam: 1980kalil, esbarunse sia enjh spain niruvanum 21 chiru kawsat tulifu gundues adangy 120 mimi kuliotu gundu onrai uruvakkiyadu.
tel: 1980lalo, spanish sansth ayin asperanja vai sia 21 anti-armar sabmunishni kal ock 120-mimi mortar bambunu roopondinchindi.
urd: 1980 kii duhai main haspaanvi firam aspiranzai siya ne 120 mili meter kaa martir bam taiyaar kiya tha jis main 21 aarmar kush zeli islhe maujuud the.
eng: In the 1980s, the Spanish firm Esperanza y Cia developed a 120-mm mortar bomb that contained 21 anti-armour submunitions.

ben: ei inguli conorkam asarkari rajnaitik caryakalapke prabalbhave simavaddh kare dies: path vikshov, annumodith rajnaitik sammelan evan anivndhit arthik anudan anushthanikbhave nishidh kara has.
guj: aa kaayadaaoe koipan bin-sarakaari rajakiya pravritti par atyant ankus muki digho hatoh rastao par dekhavo, manjuuri vinani rajakiya sansthao, ane n nondhayelam nanakiya daan par sattavar rite pratibandh laadi devaayo hato.
hin: yah kanoon kathorta se kisi bhi gaiyr-sarkari raajnneetik gatividhi ko pratibandhit karte hai: jaloos nikaalnaa, gaiyr-anumodith raajnneetik sanghathan or apnjikrut vittiya yogadan vidhiwat rup se nishedh kiye gaye.
kan: i kanoonugalu yavude sarkaretar rajakiya chatuvatikeyannu tikshnavagi nirbandhagolisidvu: bidi horraigalu, angikrutvagirad rajakiya sanghatnegalu, mattu dakhlati illad hanakasin denigeyannu adhikrutwagi nishedhislayitu.
mal: ella sarkkaritar rashtriyapravarthanvu i niyambs parimitppetutti: theruville prakatans, angikarmillat rashtriya sanghathankal, register cheyyatt sambhavnkal, enniv audyogikamai nirodhicppettu.
ori: ehi aaingudik teevrabhave yekunsi besalkari rajanitik karyankalap upare pratibandhak lagidheithila: rastaare bikshobh pradarshan, an-anumodith rajanitik anusthan, eban an-punjikrit aarthik anudanku aupachaarika bhavare nishiddh karidhiayaithila .
pan: inhan kanunnas ne kise ve gair-sarkari rajnitik gatividhi nuun tikhe for 'te gher lya: sadki pradarshan, gair pravaanit rajnitik sansthavaan,ate gair-registerd viti daan nuun rasmi for 'te pabandi lagaai gai see|
tam: indech chattas arasu chara arasiel seyalbadus anaites diviremakaak kadduppaduttina, terup boratas, ankikarmanchu arasiel amibbues, patiu seyyapadat nidhi nankots akhiyawe satdapati tadai seyyabpattanu.
tel: i chattal atuvanti prabhuthvetar rajkiya karyakalapalaki nirdishtanga sarihaddulu gishai: vidhi pradarshanal, aamodinchabadni rajkiya sansthal, mariyu namodu kaani aarthik viranalu adhikarikanga nishedhinchabaddai.
urd: in kavanian ne kisi bhi gair sarkari siyaasi sargarmi ko sakhtee se mahadood kridya: sadakon par mazahre, gair manzoor shudaa siyaasi tanzeemein, or gair registerd mali atyat par bazabata tuur par paabandi aayad kardi gai.
eng: These laws sharply circumscribed any non-governmental political activity: street demonstrations, non-approved political organizations, and unregistered financial donations were formally banned.

eng: Will Harry Kane and Son Heung-min blow Milan away with their quality, or will former Chelsea and Arsenal forward Olivier Giroud return to haunt Spurs again?
